Comment: Settled well back from a wide gate, switched widest turning in, showed a great turn of foot inside final 250 metres, asserted authority close to home.
Taken back from a wide gate for rails run, towards the rear most of way to straight, saved ground turning for home, quickened well to hit the front 150 metres out only to be caught close to home.
Settled in midfiled on rails, snuck up on rails to reach 3L 2nd turning for home, lost position over 200 metres out, one-paced closing stages.
Taken back from a wide gate and waited with, saved ground on rails turning for home, fought on steadily without threatening.
Attempted to make all, broke 3L clear on straightening, but unable to sustain effort and swamped 150 metres out. (Tactic questioned)
Ridden early, settled behind midfield, hampered when under pressure early in straight, checked again 200 metres out, kept on.
Raced wide behind midfield, in similar position turning in, one-paced in the run home.
Slowly away, settled in last few, last and wide into straight, kept on steadily down the centre of the straight.
Settled wide in midfield in 6th, in similar position turning in, found nothing in the run home.
Settled in forward of midfield, gave ground under pressure from approaching home turn.
Sluggish at start, gradually picked up to 2L to 3L back in 3rd or 4th on rails far side, dropped out after straightening. (Distressed) (Blood in trachea)
Chased leader to straight, soon weakened under pressure.
Pressed forward from a wide gate, raced wide prominently in 4th or 3rd within 3L of pace, dropped out from approaching home turn. (Bled)
Shared the lead, clocked slow sectionals, ran on strongly to win.
Settled just off the leader, favoured by the slow sectionals, ran on well for 2nd.
Bumped start, pushed forward, benefited by the slow tempo, just held ground for 3rd.
Midfield, not suited by the slow tempo, little dash 200M.
Bumped start, at back, blocked 4-2, dashed well when clear despite not suited by the slow pace.
Hard ridden to lead at advantageous slow sectionals, ran on until 200M flattened.
Pushed early, midfield, not suited by the slow pace, ran on ok.
Bumped start, just off the leaders, lack room final furlong, just ran on.
At back, not suited by the slow tempo, ran on ok.
At rear, harmed by the slow tempo, ran on fairly.
Very slow away, not suited by the slow pace, lack turn of foot.
Eased back, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
At rear, not suited by the slow tempo, never progressed.
At back, dropped off 300M.
Raced midfield, 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, suited by the fast pace, dashed well to score comfortably.
Settled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, ran on well for 2nd.
Settled in front of midfield about 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the fast sectionals, ran on gradually to get 3rd.
At rear, travelled 8Ls behind the leader, swung wide turning in, benefited by the fast pace, ran on nicely for 4th.
Rolled forward to obtain the box seat, despite harmed by the fast tempo, kept on nicely until weakened final 100M.
Rolled forward to take the fence and share the lead, despite harmed by the fast sectionals, kept on steadily until weakened final 100M.
Pushed to midfield, 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite the fast tempo, one paced home without threatening.
Taken back as usual, travelled 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite the fast sectionals, ran on only fairly.
At back, travelled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite the fast pace, ran on fairly.
Raced midfield, 4Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, despite the fast tempo, never ran on.
Prominent, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, flattened 300M.
Pressed forward to park outside the leader at fast tempo, weakened soon after straightening.
Prominent, harmed by the fast sectionals, dropped off rounding the Home Turn, tailed out.

Placing: PU
Comment: Broke down and was retired out of the race near 1200M. (Lame left front fetlock)

Smart break, relaxed to midfield & shifted 1 off with cover, steadied off heels exiting back stretch, dropped to rail 700m, shaken up 430m, quickened between rivals 350m, driven to lead 120m, worked clear.
Broke ok, niggled initially & wide on track, advanced to sit 3L 2nd 1 off no cover, joined leader 500m & shaken up, drifted centre & 1L clear 350m, all out 200m & flagging, headed 100m, no extra.
Missed break, raced 1 off with cover behind midfield, dropped to rail 1st turn, shaken up 430m, ran on for even headway to nick 3rd.
Taken back from wide gate, caught 3 wide no cover midfield until slotted 1 off on turn, driven into stretch, stayed on evenly, just missed frame.
Missed break, recovered to park 4th on rail, advanced a spot 820m, edged 1 off on turn & driven 430m, boxed on evenly until tapered final 100m.
Tardy start, raced rearward on rail, shifted 1 off 800m, niggled on turn, driven into stretch & ran on for minor late headway.
Slow start, detached & bustled, soon joined at rear at sat 3 deep, progress into 1st turn, driven 550m, plugged on for moderate inroads.
Started well, settled 3rd 3 wide no cover, relegated to 4th 820m, under pump 500m, outpaced in stretch & weakened out.
Slow start & bustled last trio 1 off, raced 3 deep 700m, widest final turn & driven centre track, plugged on evenly.
Outpaced at break, raced towards rear 1 off, minor progress into 1st turn, ridden into stretch, found nil.
Fast start, soon led & clear at 1st turn, joined 500m & headed, driven 400m but found nil & faded tamely.
Broke ok but outpaced, niggled rail behind midfield, continued to retreat under pressure, hard driven last trio turning in, plodded on same speed until eased final 100m.
Eased from wide draw, nudged along 800m, last of main pack on rail, pulled 1 off into straight, sprinted strongly 400m between runners, nifty turn of foot to score.
Strong start, pushed between runners to be near speed, settled 3rd 1 off, travelled boldly, moved up to leaders on turn, outright lead 320m, challenged but fought on gamely, just beaten.
Roused along to go forward, settled just behind lead 1 off, overraced slightly and shuffled back 720m, short of room to 350m, sprinted through shortly after, hit top gear late.
Good start, pushed to race handy, outpaced slightly, settled fore of midfield 1 off, niggled at times throughout, pulled centre track in straight, sprinted to lead 150m but gave out late.
Began on terms, ridden to improve, settled midfield 1 off, ridden along 500m, bumped 200m, stayed on.
Jumped well, settled ahead of midfield on the rail, short of room 380m, ridden along 250m, no match.
OK beginning, slow to muster, settled near rear 3 deep with cover, pushed along 550m, very green, short of room 300m, made significant late ground.
Away strongly, pushed forward, took outright lead 1030m, led on rail, joined 580m, headed 320m, fought on solidly until 200m, weakened thereafter.
Jumped on terms, ridden to go forward, settled just behind leaders 3 deep with cover, overraced slightly, ridden along 500m, near lead 320m, checked sharply 140m, eased.
Good start, squeezed slightly, settled beyond midfield on rail, hard-ridden 450m, effort short-lived, eased.
Slightly slow, unable to get in, settled beyond midfield 3 deep no cover, niggled 730m, ridden along soon after, no impression.
Smart to begin, unable to cross, joint lead 3 deep, never further than 0.25L behind leader on circle, joint lead again 580m, under ride 370m but weakened quickly.
Away on terms, slow to muster, eased, outpaced, 3L behind 2nd last horse 800m, ridden 450m, never in it.
A step slow, eased, checked slightly 1000m, settled beyond midfield between runners, pushed along 450m, wayward, weakened.
Raced in box-seat, sat 1-1/4L off the lead, shifted out into clear running at 350M, kept on nicely to score by a nose.
Eased and then raced at the rear, 6-1/4L behind 2-3 wide, swung widest and closed off strongly, just missed by a nose.
Settled into midfield, 3L behind 2 wide, ran on gamely in the Straight to finish 3rd.
Settled in worse than midfield, 4-1/2L behind 3 wide with cover, ran on fairly from 200M for 4th.
Eased back and raced at the rear, 8-1/2L behind along the rail, made good ground and ran on okay.
Travelled in front of midfield, 3L off along the rail, closed off only one paced.
Rolled forward to take up a prominent position but over-raced, settled outside lead at 700M, kept on till 250M.
Sent forward to take the rail and led by a short head, under hold until 300M, but only produced slight dash thereafter.
Awkward start and then taken back, 9-3/4L behind on the fence, made slight ground in the Straight.
Raced in front of midfield, 2-1/2L off but 4 wide without cover, taken wider around turn, ran on till 200M flattened.
Eased to race towards the rear, 8L behind 2 wide, found nothing in the Straight.
Pushed forward and sat outside the lead until 700M, crowded at 350M when giving ground, not competitive.
Slotted into midfield, 3L off 3 wide with cover, taken wider rounding turn, weakened passing 250M. (Lame right front and blood in trachea)
Sent forward and took one-off one-back position, pushed wider around turn then gave ground abruptly. (Irregular heart rhythm)
Away nicely. settling one-off 2L from leader. Turned 3-wide, urged forward to hit front 300m, kept grinding away in front before pulling clear final 100m.
Broke with field, taken in for cover settling one-off behind midfield. Swung wide into straight, shaken up 350m, kept grinding but unable to close gap on winner.

Broke well, pressed forward from outside draw before being restrained, dropping 4L from leader but without cover. Turned in behind horses, switched out 370m to get run, boxed on gamely to snatch 3rd place close home.
Began OK, rolled forward along fence but unhappy with slow pace and over-raced. Settled better home turn, barged through gap 300m, finished off nicely.
First out, racing wide before crossing to fence 1100m and slowing pace. Caught 350m out but kept batting till swamped final strides.
Quickly into stride, racing inside leader till slipping into box seat 1100m. Stayed on rail entering straight, rolled forward to look a chance 150m, no extra close home.
Began well but restrained and taken back while shifting closer to fence. Made up some ground approaching turn, hampered 400m when racing between horses, ran on fairly final 100m.
Broke well but quickly restrained and taken back, settling in last pair away from fence. Taken to centre track on straightening and ran on steadily.
Began fairly then hampered, dropping towards rear but wide. Kept wide around turn, one-paced in straight.
Began well, ridden forward, settling behind pace in one-off position. Lost position turning for home and one-paced in straight.
No early pace, dropping towards rear but away from fence. Swung wide into straight, crowded and unbalanced 400m, then raced in restricted room. One-paced final 200m.
Began well, rolled forward to sit 1L behind and outside leader on settling. Edged closer turning into straight, joint leader 300m, ran out of stamina 200m and faded quickly.
Lifted feet at start, losing ground. Ridden to make up ground, settling behind midfield turning for home. Under pressure soon after straightening and faded gradually.
Outpaced early and soon last. Trailed field thereafter without looking competitive.
Held up last of 7 about 4Ls off the pace, quickened up strongly passing 350M, led near 200M and powered away for a solid win.
Fractious in barriers, began only fairly then ridden along reaching the lead 1050M, pressed by rival home turn, unable to repel winner near 200M but battled on to hold 2nd.
Reserved near the rear 3-4Ls off the pace, challenged up the inside but raced in restricted room 300M, well held under top weight over final stages.
Never far off the pace in a small field of 7, couldn't get the clearest run 250M-100M and was closing on the 3rd towards finish.
Chased pace, left with no cover 900M then strode forward to be up on the speed, matched strides with leader until weakening 150M.
Took early lead, sat behind leader passing 1000M, in touch top of straight, gave chase hard but unable to sprint quickly enough over final 200M. (Lame RF leg)
Held up 5th of 7, taken wide 500M, gave brief response turning in, couldn't go on mid-straight, eased 150M. (Jockey : action deteriorated passing 300M / Mucus)
Jumped OK, eased and taken to fence, settling behind midfield. Left fence turning for home, caught in traffic top of straight, blocked 200m, forced through gap between horses 50m to win close home.
No early pace, dropping towards rear in one-off position. Swung wide entering straight, picked up momentum gradually, doing best work final 100m to just miss.
A little slow to move before picking up the bit and pressing forward to sit midfield in one-off position passing 1200m. Swung wide into straight, finished off strongly to miss narrowly.
Broke well, ridden to hold forward position, settling midfield but wide. Kept wide around turn, got clear run from 400m, finished off strongly only to miss a placing in blanket finish.

Began awkwardly, losing left front plate, but pressed forward to race outside leader before settling 2L back 1400m when wide without cover. Urged forward from 600m, looked chance 100m, swamped final stages.
Began well, shared early pace before settling 1L behind leader in one-off position. A little flat-footed top of straight when leader kicked, then picked up momentum and ran on strongly.
Pressed forward to lead on settling but unable cross to fence till passing 1000m. Kicked clear top of straight, kept on strongly to 50m when swamped.
Beaten for early pace, dropping to behind midfield but kept away from fence. Had clear run in straight but didn't pick up the bit till 200m when ran on fairly.

Took a few strides to find feet then rolled forward along fence to snatch box seat on settling. Left flat-footed top of straight, picked up momentum passing 200m but reluctant to improve in restricted space final 100m.
Restrained soon after start and shifted across behind runners, settling in last pair but away from fence. Put under pressure turning for home and ran on fairly in straight.
Ridden along early to hold forward position, racing between horses 2L from leader. Got shuffled back turning for home, boxed on gamely in straight without looking dangerous.
Shifted across behind runners soon after start, settling towards rear on one-off position. Hard ridden in straight but made little impression.
Ridden early to hold fence, settling 2.5L from leader back stretch. Lost position around turn, one-paced in straight.
Shifted across behind runners soon after start and last on settling. Trailed field thereafter and never competitive.
Slow away, but recovered to sit midfield, on the fence. Ridden for luck early in the straight, finding a run at 200m when needed. Pulled away from there and in easy under hands and heels.
Taken up early to eventually take the box seat, 1 off and 1 back. Nosed in front at the 250m and ran gamely in the straight, but couldn't match fast finishing winner late.
Taken up early to be handily placed in 3rd. Came off heels at 900m. Battled on gamely in the straight, but struggling to run down the first 2.
Pushed forward early to lead, before slowing the tempo in front. Still in front at 300m, but peaked soon after and faded out late.
Taken up to sit just forward of midfield, on the fence. Battled on solidly in the straight, without threatening a place.
Pushed forward early to sit 2nd, but raced onto heels when leader slowed pace at 1000m. Only fair in the straight, drooping out and not pushed late.

Crowded away and eased back early to settle at rear of the field, stuck 3-4 wide no cover. Tended to over race slightly in the back straight and lay out on home turn. Ran well late, but too far off to make a difference.
Settled forward of midfield with cover early, but badly placed on heels before coming off 900m and racing 3 wide. Prominent at the top of the straight, before fading out and not ridden out late.
Began awkwardly and dropped back to sit towards the rear of the field. Held up on the turn, and had to come in off heels at 400m. Only ran fairly to the line.
Settled midfield, 1 off the fence. Looked to run on from 300m, but stalled and went to the line 1 paced.
Eased back early to sit last. Ran onto heels and checked at 1000m. Only ran on fairly under minimal urging in the straight.
Settled just behind midfield, 2-3 wide with cover. 1 paced in the straight, and eased late.
Dropped back early to settle in the last pair. Made no impact and eased from a long way out.
Settled midfield, 3 wide with limited cover. Gave nothing early in the straight, and was eased out a long way from home. Unacceptable performance.
Held up behind midfield in the first half, worked his way through on the outside making the turn, made steady headway to close the gap on leader, led 100M out and kept going well to the finish.

Fractious in stalls and blew the start, 8Ls off the pace in last at 800M, challenge on the inside passing 400M, let down strongly and made up plenty of lost ground to go 2nd near line, ran out of ground.
Ridden along from wide barrier, crossed to the lead near 1000M, shook off nearest pursuers 300M, ran on well enough only to be headed by winner 100M and lost 2nd near line.
In 8th settled 3-4Ls back in midfield, shifted out for clear run 450M but got held up early straight, made good progress over final 250M.
Reserved near the rear 5Ls off the pace, held up behind runners and unable to obtain clear running until after 100M, stayed on towards the finish.
Bustled along after the start, proved difficult to settle when crossed by rival 900M, in touch turning home, couldn't reel in leader, one paced final 200M.
In mid-pack, 3-wide trip to the straight, couldn't sprint quickly enough passing 200M, out of contention.
Eased to a rearward spot 5-6Ls off the pace, brought wide 450M for a run, ran on moderately down outside, no serious threat to leaders.
Caught wide no cover, up with leader from 750M, couldn't go on inside 200M, weakened noticeably towards the line.
Eased back from widest draw, settled 12th and no closer than 3-wide to straight, gave limited response inside 400M and couldn't get near to leaders.
Held up midfield along the fence, shifted out 450M to improve but unable to obtain clear running in the straight, not tested.
Positioned ahead of midfield, used a bit in middle stages to hold his position, didn't respond to riding top of straight, dropped out of contention 250M.
Began awkwardly and always near the tail, offered very little on the run home, never in the picture.
Chased leader, dropped out rapidly passing 300M.

Settled in mid-division on the rails, angled out for a run on straightening, ran on well inside final 200 metres to just get up on line.

Broke well from the widest gate, gradually crossed to the inside settling 1L back in 2nd in back straight, came to dispute the lead rounding home bend and hit the front entering straight, but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Prominent in 3rd on rails, came under pressure upon straightening but failed to quicken to threaten.
Broke well, travelled 3-wide in midfield far side, commenced run rounding home bend, kept on same pace under pressure.
Gradually shuffled back towards the rear on rails, in similar position entering home straight, produced good late impression closing stages.
Ridden early, settled 2L to 3L back in 4th, gained closer to reach 1L 3rd entering straight, unable to sustain effort in straight.
Waited with in rear, made up good late ground inside final 100 metres.
Settled at the back, made up some late ground inside final 200 metres.
Ridden positively from a wide draw, took up running on rails after straightening onto back straight, led the field until joined rounding home bend, headed into straight and weakened.
Travelled in rear of midfield, made no impression in straight.
Slowly away and wide throughout, soon recovered towards the rear of the field at the 1000 metre bend, gained closer to midfield along back straight, gave ground approaching home turn.
Never seen with a chance in last few.
Took rail easily and led at advantageous slow sectionals, made all.
On heels early, eased back, took rail, not suited by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 250M.
Slow away, eased to sit in midfield 2-3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, dashed strongly 250M for 3rd.
Settled in box seat, benefited by the slow sectionals, just held ground in straight.
Eased to rear, took rail, harmed by the slow tempo, held up most straight, dashed strongly when clear, on heels close to the line.
Eased at start, too cover at rear but still 3 wide, dashed strongly 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Hard ridden to sit in front of midfield, 2 wide, weakened 200M.
Eased back, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, blocked most straight, ran on fairly when clear.
At back, 2-3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, ran on ok.
Awkward away, midfield, trapped 3 wide throughout, out of fuel 250M.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, suited by the slow tempo, however soon emptied 300M.
Raced 4-5 wide and hung out badly throughout, never a factor.
Pushed forward to park outside the leader, accelerated strongly and drifted away 150M to score by 2-1/4Ls.
Raced midfield, 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, dashed well for 2nd.
Pushed to occupy the box seat, ran home steadily for 3rd.
At back, travelled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran home nicely for 4th.
Settled worse than midfield about 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, swung widest turning in, ran on steadily.
Ridden forward to take the lead along the fence, kept on fairly and headed 250M.
At rear, travelled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, made minor ground along the inside.
Pushed to midfield, 3Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, never looked likely.
Sent forward, however, trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, weakened soon after straightening.
Eased back from a wide draw, 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never ran on.
Raced midfield, 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, made no impression in straight.
Pushed forward to take a prominent spot with cover from a wide draw, flattened over the last furlong.
Broke well, eased to midfield, shifted 3 wide no cover for advance 900m & rolled to lead 750m, extended & raced 1.5L clear turning in, shaken up & drew clear.
Sharp break, restrained to fore of midfield on rail, bustled 650m, shifted 1 off 600m, held up on turn & shifted wider, driven 7L back 350m, strong closer to nick 2nd.

Front rank initially, snagged 1420m to fore of midfield 1 off with cover, switched out 820m to chase winner, to 2nd 650m, hard driven on turn, 1.5L down into stretch, tapered final 100m, lost 2nd late.
Smart start, settled 1 back 1 off in 4th, shuffled back 750m & driven along 650m, 3-wide advance to 3rd 550mm, hard driven into stretch, soon all out, boxed on one pace.
Taken behind from wide gate to park rail at tail, niggled 600m, shifted out 400m & driven, stayed on for solid late headway.
Rousted early strides, settled 3rd 1 back on rail & steadied out of 1st turn, shuffled to 6th & niggled 600m, soon under pump, stayed on evenly.
Speed to lead wide, crossed to rail 1st turn & steadied, headed 750m, 3rd & bustled 650m, plugged on one pace.
Missed break, raced rail near rear, niggled 600m & soon under pump, kept on one pace.
Broke well, pace to sit 2nd 1 off at 1200m, shuffled to 5th & driven 600m, one-paced into stretch, tapered to wire.
Restrained to 1 off with cover near rear, advanced a spot 800m, soon niggled & wide on turn, driven into stretch, plodded home tamely.
Taken back from wide gate, trapped 3 wide no cover back of midfield, bustled forward a spot 850m but unable to go on, wide into stretch, plodded on tamely.
Outpaced & niggled initially last pair, rolled forward 1 place 750m, under pump 550m, hard-ridden into stretch, found nil & weakened.
Away well, hampered slightly after start, edged forward, settled fore of midfield on rail, pulled 1 off 950m, ridden 450m, accelerated quickly, moved to lead 150m, raced clear.
Jumped strongly, eased, settled near rear 1 off, improved along rail 500m, ridden up inside 310m, pulled across heels 230m, charged into 2nd late.
Broke on terms, under a heavy drive to push forward, overracing and eased behind leaders, sat 3rd 1 off, pulled his way into 2nd 1050m, pushed along 400m, stayed on dourly.
Hampered at start, ridden along early, settled beyond midfield on rail, improved 850m, ridden 700m and off rail soon after, boxed on.
Ridden along early, took lead 1500m, across to rail 1250m, 2L lead 950m, travelling strongly throughout, 3L lead 500m, under riding 400m, grabbed 150m, weakened late.
Very awkward start, trapped deep, settled 3 deep near rear, hard-ridden 650m, outpaced 500m, sprinted between horses 200m, stayed on.
Jumped strongly, eased behind leaders, settled just ahead of midfield 1 off, lost position 800m, under a strong drive 670m, checked 250m, ran on late.
Checked soon after start, settled beyond midfield 1 off, shuffled back 700m, short of room 600m, quickened 380m, outpaced.
Even break, outpaced early, ridden along, settled beyond midfield on rail, pushed along 600m, made up some ground, shifted out in straight, couldn't go on.
Broke inwards at start, settled just beyond midfield 1 off, shifted 3 deep 1000m, under vigorous drive 650m, no response.
Jumped very strongly, drifted out significantly soon after, back down to rail, settled 2nd on rail, overracing and eased to 3rd 1050m, under a ride 550m, dropped out.
Slightly awkward start, eased to rear on rail, under riding 650m, quickly beaten, eased right out.
Eased and raced in behind midfield, 5-1/4L behind 2 wide, swung widest and ran on well to score by 1/2L.
Taken back and travelled at the rear, 7-1/2L behind 2 wide, closed off nicely to finish 2nd on the outer Straight.
In midfield, 3-1/2L off 3 wide with cover, hung in and stopped riding at 100M when closing off strongly, still ran on for 3rd.
Pushed forward and raced outside the lead, sat 1L off, in touch until final 50M when outgunned, kept on for 4th.
Niggled and settled into box-seat, raced 2L off the lead, awkward to heels passing 200M, closed off well thereafter.
Travelled in midfield, sat 4L behind along the fence, found no daylight in the Straight, not tested.
Slotted into midfield, raced 3-1/2L off 2 wide, crowded at 100M, but overall one paced in the Straight.
Eased back after the jump, raced at the rear 7-3/4L behind along the rail, made good ground in the run home.
Taken back and raced near the tail, 5-3/4L behind along the fence, no clear run prior to 200M, made slight ground late.
Sent forward to take the rail and led by 1L, maintained lead until 200M when flattened.
In front of midfield, 2-1/4L off the lead but 3 wide and without cover, in touch until checked at 100M, run ended thereafter.
Travelled just fore of midfield along the rail 3L off, interrupted run in the Straight, not tested.

Restrained on jumping, shifted across behind runners and last on settling. Improved position first turn then hard ridden 700m when back markers moved up. Straightened behind horses, got split 200m, powered home to win narrowly.
Shared early pace before easing 4L back first turn. Put under pressure 700m when tempo increased, bumped 450m but pressed forward to hit front 100m, pipped on line.

Pressed forward from outside draw, racing wide before taking lead 1500m and crossing to fence 1350m. Increased tempo when put under pressure 700m, joined up front 100m but battled on gamely till swamped on line.

Broke well, shared early pace before easing 3L back along rail first turn. Taken off fence 700m when field speeded up, bumped 450m, severely checked 200m when attempting to improve, kept on well despite racing tight.

Began well but restrained, dropping to behind midfield in one-off position. Began forward moved 700m, circling field to race outside leader 600m. Swung wide entering straight and battled on gamely under hard riding.

Eased off heels shortly after start, settling along rail in midfield. Got shuffled back to last when field speeded up 700m, took inside run in straight, finished off strongly though raced tight concluding stages.

Jumped well, steadied, taken in to find cover, settling in last pair. Dropped to last 1150m, then started forward move 700m, racing 4-wide to reach midfield. Taken to centre track on straightening and finished off nicely.
Got off nicely, shared early pace before settling one-off, one-back first turn. Urged forward 700 when pace increased, 3-wide into straight, battled on gamely till swamped final 50m.
Began well, pressed forward to take box seat on settling. Caught flat-footed 700m when field speeded up, hard ridden to hold position, started to improve 200m but lost momentum when bumped 100m.

Crowded out start, dropped to rear but kept away from fence. Shaken up 700m when tempo increased but unable match speed, dropping to last. Taken to centre field on straightening and boxed on one-paced. Lame left front leg.
Pressed forward from wide draw to race outside hindquarters of leader on settling. Hard ridden from 600m when field packed up, kept on well to 150m before running out of steam and fading.
Had a ground saving trip from draw 1, reserved behind mid-division and travelled strongly to straight. kicked on well to assert over final 150M, too strong for rivals.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, not hurried and settled towards the rear, 6Ls back halfway, kept grinding to the line but at no stage did he seriously trouble winner.
Dropped back to the rear in a strongly run race, 8Ls behind leader middle stages, headway 450M, stayed on well without reaching winner, missed 2nd narrowly.
Jumped on terms to be 3rd in a strongly run race, moved to a striking position 400M, worked home steadily but no match for winner, outpaced by a couple of rivals late on.
Set early pace, tracked leader from 1200M, moved up to be up on the speed 600M, led down the straight until collared 150M out, lost several placings near line.
Settled 4Ls off the strong pace in the first half, crept closer home turn, continued to give chase but couldn't reel in leaders.
Held up in mid-division 4-5Ls off the strong pace, couldn't muster the speed to be closer, eased final stages when no chance. (Jockey : didn't feel comfortable in its action in the straight.)
Lost ground at the start, raced much further back than intended, travelled keenly 1300M and shifted to a position without cover, pursued for the lead but gave ground home turn. (Jockey questioned.)
Moved up gradually to lead passing 1200M, set fast pace to straight, couldn't keep up 300M, soon weakened out of contention.
Not far off the pace early, sat back in midfield as they settled, raced wide throughout, weakened noticeably 250M, never in the finish.
Settled down 3-wide towards the rear, 6Ls off the pace halfway, never near to challenge, no extra and eased 200M.
Slow to begin, near the rear always, outpaced and left behind 400M, tailed off and well beaten on debut. (Unacceptable Performance.)

Moderately away, raced in 3rd, 5 lengths or so back on turn, kept on well in straight, took the lead near 200M, held off late challenges to score narrowly.
Bumped shortly after start, positioned wide with cover behind midfield, 9 to 10 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to get 2nd.

Began awkwardly and bumped, failed to muster, raced 2 wide at rear, inconvenienced near 900M, still 11 lengths back on turn, steadied early in straight, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Bumped shortly after start, positioned 2 wide in midfield, 8 lengths back on turn, made reasonable progress in straight to make frame.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, still well back on turn, made some headway in straight without threatening the first few.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced in midfield, 9 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Slowly away, positioned on rail at rear, 12 lengths back, similar position on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced at rear, travelled wide with no cover after 900M, carried wider turning in, finished off one-paced in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear to turn, finished off one-paced.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned nicely in 4th, saved ground throughout, 7 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, emptied final 100M.

Jumped with them, raced on rail behind midfield, 10 lengths or so back on turn, failed to close off in straight. (Lost right front plate after 800M; Blood in trachea; Had small cut on lower right front cannon.)
Began well, showed early speed to take the lead, difficult to settle near 1400M, sped about 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in 5th, 7 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well, raced prominently, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight.
Pushed forward, sat outside the leader, benefited by the slow sectionals, kicked away 200M to score.
Pushed to occupy box seat, held up 400M, ran on strongly when clear.
Rolled forward, sat 2 wide, suited by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Pushed early but not muster, midfield 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, no turn of foot in straight.
Pushed to take rail and lead, clocked advantageous slow sectionals, hung on until 200M weakened.
Bumped start, dropped back, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Slow away, behind midfield along the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, ran on ok.
Eased to rear for cover, 2 wide, lack room 4-2, dashed well when clear despite not suited by the slow pace.
Rolled forward, trapped 3 wide, out of fuel 300M.
Eased back, clipped heels and blundered badly, at rear along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, no dash.
Eased back, 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, no turn of foot.
Eased back, trapped 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, checked early, harmed by the slow tempo, never improved.
Eased back, trapped 3-4 wide, raced keenly, not suited by the slow pace, emptied 350M.
At back, travelled 4.5Ls behind the leader along the outer fence, shifted to middle part of the track 400M, dashed well to score by 1.5Ls.
At rear, travelled 6Ls behind the leader along the outer fence, switched to middle part of the track 300M, ran on well for 2nd. (Questioned for tactics)
Prominent, travelled 1.5Ls behind the leader on the outer fence, unable to find a day light until final 200M, ran on gradually for 3rd.
Sent forward to take the lead along the outer fence, headed and weakened 250M.
Prominent, travelled 2Ls behind the leader, found nothing when asked. (Questioned for disappointing performance & was found to have substantial amount of blood in its trachea.)
Hard ridden forward to share the lead, under pressure near the course proper, weakened 300M.
Smart break but out-sped & driven, settled back of midfield 1 off with cover, shifted 3 deep for progress 600m, rolled into contention home turn, shaken up 300m, grinding run to lead close home.
Speed to lead, pressed 1000m, niggled to outright lead 1 off, clear & to rail 700m, headed & shaken up 380m, rallied to lead again 100m, caught close home.
Broke with others, rousted forward & vied for lead 1000m, soon settled close 2nd on rail, shifted 1 off 700m, driven to edge lead 380m, all out & headed 100m, fought on in defeat.
Smart start, settled 1 back on rail, driven 380m & shifted 1 off, out-sped, battled on evenly & back to rail closing stages, always held.
Broke ok & raced handily initially, soon eased to midfield 1 off with cover, niggled 800m, driven 350m, boxed on evenly.
Bumped start, recovered & speed to press lead, snagged 900m to 3rd 1 back 1 off, bustled along, pushed 3 deep 700m, driven 420m, one-paced & tapered late.
Tardy & squeezed out at start, bustled last pair on inner, progress on turn & shifted out 500m, driven & stayed on for moderate late headway.
Broke with others but outpaced & rousted back of midfield on inner, progress to midfield 700m, overraced & restrained off heels 500m, driven 350m, found little in tepid run home.
Eased back from widest to sit 4 deep near tail, driven widest into home stretch, kept on for minor headway.
Taken back at start, soon last pair & bustled, snagged off heels 700m & soon bustled again at tail, driven into stretch, plodded on one pace.
Buffeted at break, bustled along to race 3 wide with cover near rear, under pump 600m, wide & driven into stretch, found nil & emptied.
Broke ok but lacked toe &bustled along, trapped 3 wide no cover midfield, very wide on turn, driven 400m, soon emptied & struggled.
First to jump, taken behind runners, settled beyond midfield 3 deep with cover, taken widest into straight, ridden 450m, sprinted strongly, hit lead 200m, stayed on doggedly to score.
Began well, settled fore of midfield on rail, pushed up to 3rd 900m inside, pushed off rail 600m, under drive 370m, sprinted solidly, stayed on.
Even start, eased to last, settled at rear 3 deep with cover, nudged along 1300m, hard ridden momentarily 800m, ridden along 500m and under a heavy drive soon after, strong late.
Jumped well, settled midfield 1 off, overraced slightly, shuffled back 950m, stuck to inside 400m, under a ride soon after, limited room 250m, boxed on.
Slightly slow start, niggled throughout, settled just beyond midfield 3 deep with cover, ridden 550m, outsprinted centre track 200m, plugged away.
Sprung out to early lead, ridden along to maintain position, settled midfield on rail, ridden 500m, took time to wind up, sprinted along rail, one-paced.
Slightly awkward start, settled near rear 1 off, last 900m, improved near inside, short of room early straight, checked 300m, switched off heels 220m, ate up ground late.
Began evenly, settled beyond midfield on inside, improved 900m, short of room 400m, searching for a run 200m, made ground slowly late.
Bumped at start, settled beyond midfield on rail, switched 1 off and improved 1300m, overracing slightly 1000m, hard-ridden 500m, short of room 350m, outsprinted late.
OK start, settled just behind leaders 1 off, shuffled back 1050m, short of room 400m, checked 200m, never in it.
Awkward at start, pushed forward but quickly restrained and overracing soon after, settled fore of midfield 3 deep no cover, ridden into straight, couldn't quicken.
Jumped on terms, ridden to go forward, made it to lead 1 off 1200m, restrained to joint lead 1020m, sat 2nd soon after, raced to lead momentarily 300m, claimed quickly.
Jumped steadily, pushed forward, raced to lead on rail, passed 1200m, back to joint lead 1020m, passed again 400m, battled away but beaten 250m.
Away on terms, ridden to press forward, sat 2nd & 3rd 1 off, lost position slightly 850m, under riding 500m, dropped out meekly.
Sent forward and raced in one-off one-back position, 2L off the lead, finished off nicely to score by 3/4L.
Raced fore of midfield, 3-1/4L off on the rail, held up and had interrupted run, ran on strongly once cleared at 200M.
Pushed forward and raced outside the lead, sat 3/4L off, kept on going to the line, just held onto 3rd.
Eased and settled towards the rear, 8-1/2L behind and 3 wide from 700M, ran on gamely for 4th.
Raced just fore of midfield, 3-1/4L off 2 wide, kept on one paced to the line.
Rolled forward and took up box-seat, sat 1-3/4L off, one paced but kept on to the line.
No speed and at the rear, 9-1/2L behind and wide until 800M when shifted to rail, made nice ground steadily.
Settled in midfield, 5L behind the lead 2 wide, did not improve position and ran on same paced.
Raced in midfield, 5-1/4L behind along the rail, kept on one paced to the line.
Eased back and at the rear initially, improved slightly around turn, however did not get any closer.
Travelled in behind midfield, 7L behind 2 wide, found nothing in the Straight.
At the rear throughout, never a factor.
Pushed forward to take the rail and led, out of steam and faded passing 300M.
Hard ridden to hold forward position before taking over lead 1000m. Pulled 2L clear on straightening but soon joined up front by another before finding a little extra to win in final strides.

Quickly away from wide draw, leading to 1000m before giving way to inside runner and taking box seat. Rolled forward to join leader 200m but lay in on winner under pressure and jockey unable to ride out fully.
Began well, not pushed, settling behind midfield in one-off position. Checked 900m, swung wide into straight, closed off strongly down centre track to finish a close third.
Crowded out shortly after start, dropping towards rear in one-off position. Not pushed until straightening when taken to centre track and ran on well.
Crowded out shortly after start, then taken to rail, settling behind midfield. Saved ground around turn, stayed on rail in straight, ran on nicely.
Steadied soon after start and shifted across behind runners, settling in last pair along rail. Came off fence turning for home, shifted wide in straight and ran on fairly.
Jumped well, pressed forward but caught wide without cover 3L from leader 800m. Left flat-footed top of straight when leaders kicked, but battled on gamely before flattened final strides.
Fractious in gate, lifted feet at start and slow into stride, settling along fence towards the rear. Switched out turning for home and boxed on gamely in straight.
Restrained on jumping, shifted across behind runners, settling in last pair. Taken very wide in straight and ran on fairly past beaten horses.
Quickly into stride from widest draw but allowed to find feet, slipping 3L back from leader but 3-wide without cover. Kept on gamely early straight turning one-paced final 200m.
Broke fairly, picked up momentum along rail to get within 3L of leader when became unbalanced and lost ground 950m. Boxed on fairly to 200m when flattened and swamped.
Jumped with field, ridden to hold forward position, settling 4L from leader passing 800m. Took home turn a little wide and one-paced in straight.
Jumped OK, ridden to hold one-off position in midfield, but proved difficult to settle. Checked off heels 950m, shuffled back around turn, found nothing in straight under pressure.
Began awkwardly, recovered and pressed forward close to rail to settle 4L behind leader at turn. Under pressure soon after straightening and gave ground steadily.
Held up 2-wide in midfield, held position to the turn, chased well from 450m, gained narrow lead 150M and kept going well to pull away near the finish.

Strode forward from wide barrier, tracked leader in a steadily run race, hit lead briefly mid-straight, rallied on when headed 150M, held by winner towards the finish but easily accounted for the rest.
Close up in 4th, 3-wide 500M and moved up to challenge, couldn't match strides with first 2 passing 200M, kept on but non-threatening 3rd.
Jumped on terms, settled ahead of midfield along the rail, held up early straight but couldn't quicken enough to challenge first 2 over final 300M.
Urged forward under 10lb claimer, steadied the pace once in the lead, led down the straight until 250M, faded late stages.
Well placed in 3rd tracking leading pair, couldn't come on when pace quickened 400M, no threat in the run home.
Settled down 5Ls behind midfield, moved closer passing 600M, stayed on fairly entering straight, not reach leaders.
Dropped back from wide draw, difficult to settle 1000M when pace slackened, 6Ls off the pace 400M, gave limited response and never a threat to leaders.
Towards the rear 5-6Ls off the steady pace, couldn't muster the speed to be closer passing 450M, never got involved.
Slow to begin, ended up near the rear 4th from last, kept on same pace turning in, never in contention.
Caught wide no cover in midfield from draw 12, moved closer to pace home turn, tried hard but couldn't go on passing 250M, weakened to line.
Settled down in rear 7Ls off the slow pace, driven passing 500M but made no progress.
Eased back to rear after the jump, 7-8Ls off the pace middle stages, not quickened under pressure 350M, made no impression on debut.
Began only fairly, improved to a midfield position along the rail, couldn't keep up inside 350M and weakened noticeably.
Hard ridden to lead narrowly passing 1000m, crossing to fence. Put under pressure soon after straightening but kept finding to score narrowly.
Broke well, ridden to hold rail, settling in box seat passing 1000m. Blocked for run early in straight, got clear 200m, gave chase but failed narrowly.
Jumped well, pressed forward in one-off position, settling 2L from leader passing 800m. Got clear run soon after straightening, picked up momentum to close off strongly.
Slow into stride, hard ridden to make up ground, setting behind midfield. Taken wide around turn, checked 400m, switched in to rail, picked up momentum doing best work final 150m.
Began well, ridden along to hold midfield position but kept wide. Bumped and taken wider passing 600m, then bumped and unbalanced 500m. Kept on gamely in straight.

Hard ridden from the gates, racing 3-wide before settling outside hindquarters of leader approaching turn. Kept on well early in straight before feeling the pinch passing 200m, giving ground steadily.
Began fairly and last on settling. Improved position around home turn, taken wide in straight, boxed on one-paced.
Began OK, no pace, settling along rail close to rear. Made turn awkwardly, switched out in straight, found nothing.
Beaten for early pace, dropping to rear and taken in closer to fence. Last into straight, found nothing.
Broke well, pressed forward from wide draw but left 3-wide passing 1000m. Came off bridle passing 400m and gave ground steadily. Not ridden out. Unacceptable performance.
Jumped with field, ridden to hold midfield position along rail. Held position turning into straight, boxed on gamely to 200m before tiring.
No early pace, shifted in after jumping from wide draw, settling at rear. Found nothing in straight and finished tailed out. Had irregular heart rhythm and bled from both nostrils.

Taken up early, before running onto heels 1400, checking and dropping back to midfield 2-3 wide. Pushed on from the top of the straight, nosing ahead at 200m. Solid to the line, and just holding on late.
Taken forward early to share the lead, 1 off the fence. Stayed on well in front in the straight, battling with the winner and just peaking before the line.

Leapt out of the barrier, slow away and dropped back to sit 3rd last, 1 off the fence. Still at the rear on turn, before coming wide. Huge run in straight, going around nearly every horse, almost running down 1 and 2 late.
Scrambled forward early, but managed to get stuck 3 wide no cover in a share of the lead. Battled gamely in front down the straight, just peaking at the 50m and losing a place.
Dropped back early from the wide draw to sit at the rear of the field, on the fence. Weaved through the field late, and finished strongly.
Cruised up from the inside draw to be handily place 5th, on the rail. Held up for a run until 300m. Ran on solidly when clear, but no threat.
Handily placed 4th, 1 off the fence. Awkwardly placed on heels early in the straight, before switching out at 200m for a clear run. Came to nothing and faded late.
Cruised up early to settle just forward of midfield, 1 off the fence early. Never kicked and went to the line 1 paced.
Eased back from the wide draw to sit last, 2-3 wide. Still last and widest at the 200m. Given an impossible task, and ran well late to pick up a few late.

Gradually taken up to sit midfield, before crowded out of his run at 900m and losing ground. Held up early in the straight, and only started to get moving at 150m, and had no time to make any impression.
Pushed forward early to share the lead, on the rail. Offered nothing in the straight.
Eased forward from the wide draw to settle worse than midfield, 3-4 wide with limited cover. Looked to run on from 400m, but never kicked and only fair to the line.
Settled around midfield, 1 off the fence. Off heels at the top of the straight and bumped 350m. Never pushed out, and eased to the line late.
Eased forward and settled worse than midfield, 2-3 wide. Never responded to urgings, and eased out late.

Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, improved from 500M, finished off well very strongly to score.
Slowly away, raced 6 to 7 lengths back at rear, bumped near 1300M, similar position on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to get 2nd.
Jumped with them, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, kept on well after turning in but couldn't hold off the first two late.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned a length or so behind the leader, easy run to turn, finished off evenly in straight without threatening.
Crowded out start, positioned on rail in midfield, 5 lengths back, similar position on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly.
Moderately away, raced prominently, 2 wide throughout, peaked on turn, one-paced in straight.

Began fairly from a tricky gate, unable to slot in early, taken back to race at rear but difficult to settle, bumped near 1300M, still 7 to 8 lengths back on turn, taken widest in straight and made some progress.
Bumped start, unable to slot in, raced wide with no cover early, slotted in near 1100M, positioned 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced at rear, checked near 1100M, still 7 lengths or so back on turn, finished off one-paced.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, hampered near 1100M, still last turning in, one-paced in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 3 lengths back on rail in 5th, saved ground throughout, failed to close off in straight and eased final 100M.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced 2 wide in 4th, 3 lengths back, similar position on turn, showed no response to riding, weakened from 200M and eased thereafter. (Blood in trachea.)
Eased to obtain cover just off the leaders, box seat, closed off strongly 250M to score.
Eased to find cover in midfield, took rail, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 250M for 2nd.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, suited by the fast tempo, dashed well 250M.
Slow away, hard ridden along the fence to keep up behind midfield, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M.
Hard ridden forward, just off the leaders, 2-3 wide, held ground in straight.
Hard ridden early, 2-3 wide behind midfield, favoured by the fast tempo, ran on ok.
At back, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, made steady ground 200M.
Hard ridden to take the rail and lead, clocked fast sectionals, ran on until 200M weakened.
Rolled forward, 2 wide, not suited by the fast pace, emptied 200M.
Failed to muster at start, on the rails, suited by the fast pace, never improved.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide outside the leader, not suited by the fast tempo, dropped off quickly 300M.
Rolled forward to park outside the leader, suited by the slow tempo, ran on nicely to score by a short head.
Ridden forward to take the fence and led by 1L at slow sectionals, kept on strongly to the line until headed by the winner over the final stride.
Pushed to obtain the box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on steadily for 3rd.
Settled in front of midfield, 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the slow pace, ran on steadily for 4th.
Taken back from a wide draw, 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite harmed by the slow tempo, finished off nicely along the inside.
Settled worse than midfield about 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite harmed by the slow sectionals, swung widest and made some ground in straight.
Raced midfield, 3.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite not suited by the slow tempo, made some ground in straight.
Raced midfield, despite trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, ran on steadily.
At rear throughout, harmed by the slow sectionals, made no impression in Straight.
Always at back, never ran on.
At rear throughout, never looked likely.
Never looked competitive.

Front rank at break, eased to rail 1 back, shuffled back a spot 700m, shifted out & niggled forward 600m, strong traveller 3 wide on turn, cruised to 2nd turning in & shaken up to lead 250m, drew clear.
Disputed early lead, restrained close 2nd & overraced 1200m, edged ahead 820m & lengthened 1L clear to lead on rail, driven turning in, all out & headed 250m, just held 2nd.
Prominent at break, taken back to stalk fore of midfield 1 off with cover, overraced 1100m, outpaced down the back, 6th & under pump 600m, wide into stretch, boxed on dourly to closing 3rd.
Broke ok, taken back & 3 wide into 1st turn, soon slotted 1 off behind midfield, steadied 1000m & shuffled back 900m, driven on turn & wide into stretch, stayed on centre to just miss frame.
Dropped in last at break, advanced 1 off to 2nd last 600m, ridden along 400m, wide into stretch, shifted centre track 200m, stayed on for minor late inroads.
Good break wide, steadied to slot 1 off with cover near rear, shifted 3 deep 1000m & rolled to 2nd at 720m, parked 1 off, niggled 400m, 3rd & driven 300m, found nil & weakened.
Sharp start, disputed early lead, slight advantage when restrained 1200m but overraced, headed 820m & soon 1 back & niggled, driven into stretch, plodded one pace.
Snagged back to settle rail behind midfield, shuffled to near rear 750m, shifted out home turn & driven, plugged on one pace.
Crowded & taken behind at start, raced midfield 1 off with cover, overraced 1100m & shuffled back a spot, bustled a touch 500m, driven into stretch, one-paced in tepid run home.
Fast break & prominent initially, settled 1 back 1 off, niggled 700m, forced 3 wide 550m & shuffled back, hard-ridden under pressure 400m, driven wide home turn, struggled in run home.
Broke ok, taken back to slot rail near rear, to last 600m, under pump 450m, found nil in weak run to wire.
Missed start & bustled to rail, checked 1400m, settled midfield, niggled 700m & soon under pump, emptied top of stretch, faded tamely.
Jumped fairly, pressed forward, settled outside lead 1 off, travelled strongly, ridden along 450m, hit lead 150m, raced clear.
Away on terms, eased, bumped heavily 1550m, settled beyond midfield on rail, ridden along 700m, short of room shortly after, under vigorous drive 380m, railed up, checked slightly 150m, flew late.
Broke well, down to box seat, settled 3rd on rail, ridden 550m, switched over heels 280m, boxed on.
First to break, straight to lead, 1L lead 1100m, even sectionals, under a ride 420m, kicked solidly, claimed 150m, weakened very late.
Jumped well, pushed on, settled 4th 1 off, under pressure 450m, picked up again late.
Away evenly, settled just ahead of midfield on rail, ridden along 400m, one-paced to the line.
Broke fairly, settled midfield 1 off, shuffled back 650m, under heavy drive 400m, picked up very late, outpaced.
Slightly slow to jump, eased, bumped heavily 1550m, settled near last 1 off, under a ride 500m and pulled 3 & 4 deep shortly after, widest straight, stayed on.
Jumped well, eased to rail, settled just beyond midfield on inside, ridden 400m, loomed, eased near line.
Ridden along early, stuck wide first turn, eased to get in, settled beyond midfield 1 off, overracing slightly, 3 wide 650m, couldn't pick up 400m, sprinted very late.
Jumped OK, eased to midfield, settled just beyond midfield 1 off, pulled 3 wide 700m & pressed forward, up to 3rd 500m, died on run 200m, weakened up.
Slightly awkward start, outpaced, settled a clear last on rail, ridden along 500m, never competitive.
Pushed forward to take the rail and led, slowly pulled away in the Straight to score comfortably by 3-1/2L under a hold.
Sent forward and took box-seat and sat 1-1/4L off the pace, kept on going to the line but was no match to the winner.
Travelled in just behind midfield, 4-3/4L behind 2 wide, battled on gamely to the line to take 3rd.
Awkward start and raced at the rear end, 6-1/2L behind 2 wide, made nice ground and finish off strongly for 4th.
Settled in midfield, 3-3/4L behind along the rail, slight dash early but ran on only one paced from approaching 100M.
Pushed to race just front of midfield, 3-1/4L off 2 wide, kept on until flattened inside 150M.
Eased back, sat 7-1/2L behind the lead along the rail, made ground steadily and ran on okay.
Niggled and settled in front of midfield, 2-1/4L off along the rail, dropped off gradually in the Straight.
Raced towards the rear along the rail, 6-1/2L behind the lead, did not improve.
Travelled in behind midfield, 5-1/2L behind 2 wide, slight dash early but showed nothing thereafter.
Sat in front of midfield, 3-3/4L off but 3 wide and without cover throughout, not competitive in the Straight.
Rolled forward and raced in front of midfield, 2-1/2L off 2 wide, eased down at 200M. (Lame right front leg)
Jumped well, allowed to stride forward at own pace, settling one-out, one-back first turn. Steadied 700m when pace increased, urged forward 450m to hit front 150m, pulling clear final stages.

Niggled after start to hold forward position before settling one-out, 3L from leader back stretch. Rolled forward to race outside leader 600m when pace slackened. Took over running 350m, no extra when joined 150m.

Broke well but bumped shortly after and taken to fence 3L from leader. Not happy with slow pace and travelled keenly first turn. Left fence 700m to go forward, taken to centre track on straightening, finished off strongly.

Off OK, rolled forward but over-raced before settling between horses behind midfield back stretch. Swung widest into straight and picked up momentum gradually doing best work final 100m. Lame right front leg.

Allowed to stride forward at own pace from widest draw, racing 3-wide without cover before settling behind midfield back stretch. Given more rein passing 700m, circling front runners to look a chance 200m. Swamped final stages.
Kicked up from inside draw to hold rail, leading initially before sliding into box seat 1100m. Got shuffled back when pace hotted up 700m, got inside run in straight but only one-paced.

Jumped OK, urged forward 4-wide first turn to sit outside leader 1150m. Forged ahead 900m when pace slackened, and increased tempo 600m when challenged. Led field to 200m before running out of stamina.
Off OK, steadied and taken fence, settling 5L from leader first turn. Travelled comfortably to turn, swung wide into straight, boxed on gamely one-paced.

Bumped start but quickly into stride, racing with pace before taking lead 1300m. Dropped back to 3rd 1000m when rivals moved forward. Got inside run in straight, battled gamely to 100m when flattened.
Restrained on jumping and taken to fence, settling in last pair. Trailed field thereafter and only one-paced under hard riding in straight.
Shifted across behind runners soon after start, settling in last pair. Ridden patiently to 400m when put under pressure but made little headway. Jockey claimed not suitable to HV.

Placing: PU
Comment: Began OK, no speed, dropping to rear taking first turn. Fractured left front leg when clipped heels passing 900m and pulled up.
Sped to the fore and allowed an easy lead, opened up 2L gap 200M, kept going well to hold off pursuers final stages.
Chased pace in 3rd, tried hard to reel in winner final 300M, stayed on well late but ran out of ground.
Tracked leader along the 2-path, chased winner steadily passing 300M, nearest finish but ran out of ground.
From wide barrier taken back to last after the start, proved difficult to settle 800M in a slowly run race, over 6Ls to make up 400M, closed off strongly for 4th but not getting to top 3.
Began only fairly, held up behind midfield 5Ls back in a slowly run race, stayed on well and continued to give chase but not reaching top 3.
Reserved near the rear, 6Ls back at 800M, pulled wide 400M, stayed on without threatening.
Caught 3-wide no cover in mid-division, improved to 4th passing 600M, finished off fairly from 350M, faded late stages.
Not hurried after the jump, sat 2-wide midfield, couldn't quicken enough to challenge leaders passing 350M, never threatened.
Dropped back to a rearward position after the jump, saved ground hugging the rail, in 9th 5Ls off the pace making the turn, couldn't muster the speed to go closer.
Settled down 4Ls in mid-division, couldn't quicken turning home, soon out of it and weakened noticeably final 100M.
Towards the rear and caught wide from outside barrier, niggled along 600M, made the home turn awkwardly and gave ground soon entering straight, eased.

Jumped well from gate 9, showed early speed to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kicked clear after turning in and won easily.
Taken back to race at rear, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made good progress to get 2nd.
Began fairly from gate 1, raced 3 lengths or so back on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, made some good late headway when clear to get 3rd.
Began well, sat handily right behind the leader, easy run on turn, finished off evenly in straight, never a threat to the first few.
Bumped start, recovered to race 2 wide, a length or so back in 2nd, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover, 3 to 4 lengths back behind midfield, awkwardly placed near 700M, switched out turning for home, finished off evenly.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, still well back on turn, taken wide in straight and made minor progress in straight.
Bumped start, recovered to race wide in midfield, no cover throughout, bumped near 500M and carried wider turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back in 5th, angled out turning in, showed no progress in straight.
Began fairly from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide with no cover at rear throughout, emptied early in straight when hard run took effect.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced 4 lengths back in 9th, there to turn, taken wide early in straight, made no progress. (Lame left front leg next day.)
Hard ridden early, midfield 2 wide, dashed strongly 300M despite not suited by slow pace and scored.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, checked 900M, lack room 400M, closed off strongly when clear for 2nd.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, benefited by the slow sectionals, held ground for 3rd.
Eased back, took rail, not suited by the slow tempo, dashed well in straight along the fence.
Eased at start, trapped 3-4 wide at back, harmed by the slow pace, demonstrated strong finishing efforts 300M.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, lack room 400M, ran on fairly when clear.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, unleashed strong finishing efforts 250M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Behind midfield along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, lack room 4-2, dashed well when clear.
Pushed forward, trapped 3 wide just off the leaders without cover, out of fuel 200M.
Hard ridden to take rail and lead, clocked slow sectionals, soon emptied 300M.
Very slow away, at rear, raced 3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Eased back, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Sent forward to lead along the fence, kept on strongly to score by 3/4Ls.
Pushed forward to park outside the leader, kept on gamely until headed by the winner final 150M.
Raced midfield, 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on steadily for 3rd.
Raced midfield, 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on steadily for 4th without any serious threat to the placegetters.
Settled worse than midfield about 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, made some ground in straight.
Raced midfield, 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, one paced to the line.
Checked soon after jumping, then settled 9Ls behind the leader on the fence, made minor ground in straight.
Raced midfield, 6Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, made minor ground in straight.
Settled worse than midfield about 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, one paced home.
At rear throughout, never looked likely.
Prominent, found nothing when asked and weakened badly 250M.
Taken back from a wide draw, 7Ls behind the leader 3 wide without cover, never ran on.

Ducked down at start & lost ground, recovered to park midfield on rail, crept closer from 950m, shifted out home turn, shaken up 370m, quickened between rivals to 2nd 250m & led 110m, kept on under pressure.
Taken back from wide to rail behind midfield, edged 1 off 600m, wider home turn & bumped rival, clear running & driven 400m, to 3rd 160m & closed to nick 2nd at wire.
Slow start, taken to rail & rolled to 3rd 1 back at 1000m, strong traveller & shifted out 430m, hard-ridden to edge lead 290m, wandered under pressure, headed 110m, boxed on, lost 2nd close home.
Missed break, 2L detached & bustled, under whip 700m & advanced to join main body at 600m, hard-ridden centre track, stayed on for strong late headway.
Broke ok & widest until crossed 1300m to 3 wide back of midfield, niggled 1000m, under pressure wide on turn, bumped 430m, driven & kept on four dour progress.
Smart break, taken back to midfield 1 off with cover, shifted 3 deep 700m, smooth progress wide into stretch, 1L down & shaken up 300m, found little, emptied 150m.
Started ok, snagged back, lacked toe & bustled on rail near tail, worked for progress on turn, shifted out 600m, driven wide into stretch, stayed on for minor headway.
Broke ok & bustled forward to park 2nd 1 off no cover at 1300m, niggled along, ridden 500m & boxed to lead 400m, all out & headed 290m, faded.
Smart break & prominent but trapped wide, snagged 1250m to 1 off 1 back & niggled 1050m, shuffled back & under pressure 650m, crowded & checked off heels turning in, driven 350m, tepid run home.
Broke ok, taken back, soon outpaced & bustled near rear 1 off with cover, shifted 3 deep & ridden on turn, last trio & under pump into stretch, plodded on tamely.
Broke ok, travelled wide & soon 4th, trapped 3-wide no cover, niggled 550m, driven into stretch, found nil & faded tamely.
Fast break & rousted initially to lead on rail, 0.5L ahead & shaken up turning in, found nil & headed 400m, weakened feebly.
Broke ok & chased front rank initially, drifted back to midfield & soon felt pinch, bustled in retreat, last turning in, eased when beaten.
Started ok, worked wide until slotted midfield 3 wide with cover 1050m, niggled along & unable to hold spot, drifted back on turn, tailed off in home straight.
Broke well, nudged forward, settled 4th rail, travelled strongly, switched over heels 400m, pushed out 360m, checked 300m, hit lead 150m, lifted late.
Away on terms, ridden to cross, settled beyond midfield 3 deep cover, pulled centre track 400m and sprinted strongly, just missed.
Slightly slow, edged along, settled midfield on rail, short of room 400m, made ground late.
Alert break, pressed forward, couldn't get in, fore of midfield 3 deep no cover, ridden along 480m, boxed on.
First to jump, ridden with urgency, settled 3rd 1 off, pulling hard, ridden 400m, hanging in badly, bumped 300m, stayed on fairly.
Sharp start, eased, settled beyond midfield 1 off, unbalanced near 900M, similar position on turn, switched over heels and sprinted 300m, hit line well late.
Away well, hunted forward, settled 2nd 1 off, ridden 550m, hit lead 350m, short burst, claimed 150m, weakened late.
Slow start, eased behind runners, settled near rear on rail, overracing fiercely, pushed 450m along rail, not ridden out.
Ridden vigorously from gates, quickly to lead, 0.5L lead 900m, steady sectionals, ridden along 570m, grabbed 350m, tried to fight on but effort short-lived.
Jumped fairly, eased, settled near rear 3 deep cover, under pressure 500m, one-paced in straight.
Away well, outsped, settled midfield 1 off, on heelds 750m, ridden along 550m, faded.
Awkward start, bumped shortly after, settled rear 1 off, racing erratically, asked for response 350m, gave little.
In midfield, 4-3/4L off, moved to 2 wide from rail near 800M, awkward to heels 300M, ran on steadily to score by 1-1/4L.
Travelled in midfield, 3-3/4L behind but trapped 3 wide and without cover, kept on nicely to take 2nd.
Taken back after fair start, raced 9-1/2L behind but wide when improving around turn, made ground steadily for 3rd.
Eased from a wide draw and raced in behind midfield, 6-1/2L behind 3 wide with cover, kept on well to the line.
Awkward start and pushed to settle in front of midfield, 3-1/2L off 2 wide, kept on only one paced to the line.
Raced at the rear, 7-3/4L behind 2 wide, made good ground but was help up from 150M to 50M, ran on nicely thereafter.
No speed and raced near the rear, 6-1/2L behind 2 wide, checked at 600M, made nice ground and ran on.
Sent forward and raced in one-off one-back position, 1-1/4L off, ran on one paced to the line.
Niggled forward and settled to race outside the lead, kept on one paced and out of steam inside 50M.
Pushed forward to take the rail and led by a nose, headed passing 150M but kept on until flattened inside 100M.
Raced near the rear, 6-1/4L behind along the rail, nice dash from 250M until 150M, held up thereafter not fully tested.
Prominent but wide initially, shifted into box-seat after 900M, not competitive in the Straight.
Travelled in front of midfield, 3-1/4L behind along the rail, showed nothing and eased out at 250M.
Settled in midfield, 5-1/4L behind 2 wide before eased down rounding turn. (Bled from both nostrils)
Steadied soon after start, shifted to rail, then ridden to hold position behind midfield. Left rail 500m, got split 250m finished strongly while hanging in to win close home.
Broke well, hard ridden to hold forward position before settling in box seat 3L from leader. Edged closer turning for home, vigorously ridden to go forward, hit front 100m but run down close to line.
Hard ridden from widest draw to lead 950m before crossing to fence. Kicked ahead on straightening, kept on strongly to 100m before running out of steam and swamped.
Got off well then eased off pace and taken to rail in midfield. Stayed on rail around turn, got clear run 300m out, kept on gamely to line.
Hard ridden early while seeking cover, settling in midfield in one-off position. Turned into the straight behind a wall of horses, got clear run 200m, ran on steadily.
Got away well, sharing early pace but 3-wide until steadied passing 950m, dropping to midfield. Swung very wide into straight but ran on steadily under hard riding.
Broke well, pressed forward before settling 1L behind leader passing 950m. Lost position when swung wide entering straight, kept on gamely to 200m before giving ground gradually.
First into stride before being eased 3L back 1000m. Travelled strongly to straight, got clear running but lay in on several occasions making it hard to ride out, losing ground.
Jumped OK, restrained and shifted across behind horses to be last on settling. Taken wide entering straight but only one-paced under hard riding.
Eased soon after start and shifted across behind horses, settling at rear. Stayed on fence around turn but found little in straight when asked. Lame right front leg.
Unable handle early pace, dropping towards rear in one-off position. Swung wide into straight but only one-paced.
Began well, pressed forward, settling one-out, one-back. Swung wide into straight, lay out while giving ground steadily. Had substantial amount go blood in trachea.
Chased leader in a strongly run race, quickened up smartly early straight and took charge 300M, raced away from them under hands and heels riding. Class above.
Settled down midfield 4Ls off the strong pace, worked home well to go 2nd near line but never a threat to runaway winner.
From wide barrier showed good gate speed to lead, set strong pace to straight, unable to fend off impressive winner 300M but kept grinding to the line, edged out to 3rd close home.
Began only fairly, towards the rear early, improved to a spot behind midfield 6Ls back home turn, stayed on steadily final 300M to go 4th near line, no threat to first 3.
Urged along to take up a trailing position just behind leaders, pace strong, driven out 400M but couldn't get closer to leaders on the run home.
Jumped on terms to be 3rd/4th in a strongly run race, kept on same pace inside 400M, no impression on leaders.
Began only fairly, waited with near the rear 8Ls off the good pace, gave limited response passing 400M, not reach leaders.
Taken back from wide draw, ended up 8Ls off the good pace near the tail, stayed on only fairly on the run home, never threatened.
Began only fairly, 6Ls off the good pace behind mid-division, niggled along to hold its position home turn and couldn't get closer in straight.
Held up 2-wide in midfield, 5Ls off the pace middle stages, kept on same pace early straight, faded 200M.
Dropped back to last in a strongly run race, 10Ls behind leader mid-stages, plenty to do top of straight, couldn't come on.
Failed to muster speed early stages, ended up racing 3-wide behind midfield, plugged home to the finish, never likely. (Blood in trachea.)
Began only fairly, settled down 6-7Ls behind midfield along the inside, couldn't keep up 450M, soon weakened, eased.
Not far off leaders in a strongly run race, lay out 600M, dropped out early straight, finished tailed out. (Jockey : uncomfortable action / Unacceptable performance.)
Began well, allowed to slide forward at own pace, settling one-off 3L from leader. Niggled at when pace increased 800m, swung wide into straight, hit front 300m and kept finding when challenged.
Got off nicely, ridden to hold forward position but away from fence, settling one-off 3L from leader. Ridden along turning for home, rolled forward to look a chance 300, chased winner to post.
Slow into stride, dropping to rear, shifted in and improved position. Shaken up 900m when rival moved forward, barged through gap 350m, finished strongly while laying in to grab minor placing.
Began awkwardly, shifted in and bumped heavily, unbalancing jockey. Ridden to make up ground settling one-off in midfield. Taken wide in straight and ran on nicely.
No early pace, dropping to last pair in one-off position. Dropped to last around home turn, taken wide in straight and finished off nicely to be closest at finish.
Steadied soon after start and shifted across behind runners to be last on settling. Raced ungenerously back stretch, switched out entering straight, ran on fairly.
Began fairly, ridden to hold forward position, settling midfield close to rail. Shaken up top of straight and boxed on one-paced.
Hard ridden from outside draw to lead on settling, then slowed pace. Increased tempo 800m when challenged but collared on straightening and gave ground gradually.
Began OK, outpaced, dropping to rear close to fence. Got shuffled back approaching turn, took inside run in straight, one-paced.
Stumbled on jumping, recovered and driven up to midfield before losing position approaching 1200m. Well back on straightening and found little in straight when asked.
Pressed forward from outside draw, racing wide behind the pace before pressing ahead to race outside hindquarters of leader 1200m. Took over lead 400m but ran out of stamina 300m and faded.
Began well then ridden along to hold forward position ahead of midfield. Not happy with pace and set off 900m, circling field to race 3-wide outside leader 700m. Gave ground soon after straightening.
Bumped heavily shortly after start, but recovered and held position behind midfield close to rail. Come under pressure soon after straightening and faded.
Broke well, pressed forward, grabbing rail 3L from leader. Travelled well to 800m before giving ground rapidly from 600m and eased down. Bled from both nostrils.

Away well, prominent early before dropping back midfield, 1 off the fence. Strong down the outside and looked like he would clear out in the straight. Struggled once he got the lead at 150m, just ground the win late.
Taken up from the wide draw to be well placed 3rd, 1 off the fence. Lead at 300m, before being tackled at 150m. Pushed winner all the way to the line, and just missed late.
Taken up early, before easing back slightly to be 4th/5th, 1 off the fence. Ran solidly in the straight to hold a clear 3rd, but no hope of getting the first 2.

Began awkwardly, but quickly recovered to be handily placed 4th/5th on the fence. Held up early in the straight, before getting a clear run from 300m. Ran solidly, until peaking last 50m and dropping out of place contention.

Didn't muster early and got back, before eventually pressing forward to sit midfield on the rail by 1000m. Ridden for luck in the straight, and progressed well late when given the opportunity to stretch out.
Pushed forward early to lead. Battled only fairly in the straight, before peaking late.
Eased forward early to sit just forward of midfield, 1 off the fence. Wider on the turn and 1 paced to the line.
Inconvenienced on jumping, and dropped back early to sit worse than midfield, 1 off the fence. Stayed on fairly in the straight, and picked up a few slower ones late.
Pushed forward early and stuck 3 wide, before pressing to share the lead at 900m. Never responded when asked in the straight and went to the line 1 paced.
Dropped back early from the wide draw to sit a clear 2nd last. Plugged away fairly under minimal urging in the straight.
Lifted front feet on jumping and was slow to begin. Taken up to sit just forward of midfield, on the fence. Only fair in the straight and eased late. Vet-bled both nostrils.
Dropped back early to settle a clear last, 3-4L off the 2nd last horse. Plugged away in the straight, only under hand and heels late.
Taken up early to be handily placed 5th/6th, but stuck 3 wide with limited cover. Dropped out quickly from the 300m, and eased to the line. Unacceptable performance. Jockey and trainer questioned.
Eased back from the wide draw to sit 3rd last, 3 wide with limited cover. Never looked to press on in the straight, and was eased to the line late.
