Fast into stride, took the lead easily, uncontested throughout, kicked clear early in straight and scored comfortably. (Lost left front plate shortly after the start.)
Began awkwardly, recovered to race 2 wide in 4th, same position on turn, finished off evenly to get 2nd without threatening.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 3 lengths back on rail in midfield, improved on turn, raced tight early in straight, finished off evenly thereafter to get 3rd.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 6 to 7 lengths back at rear, taken widest after turning in, finished off well to make frame without threatening the first few.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced wide in midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.
Away with them, sent forward to race 2 lengths or so back on rail in 3rd, saved ground on turn, peaked near 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Crowded out start, recovered to race 5 lengths or so back in midfield, similar position to turn, closed off one-paced.
Taken back from a tricky gate, raced 6 lengths back at rear, there to turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off one-paced.
Began fairly from a wide draw, showed no early speed, raced 3 wide behind midfield, similar position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, failed to close off in straight. (See racing incidents.)
Moderately away, raced prominently, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight and eased final 100M. (Lame right front and right hind legs; See racing incidents.)
Slowly away, raced at tail throughout, never competitive. (Lame right front leg next day.)
Slow away, at back along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 350M to score.
Pushed early, trapped 3 wide throughout in front of midfield, not suited by the fast tempo, ran on strongly to the line, just beaten by narrow margin.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, not suited by the fast sectionals, lack room 400M, held ground for 3rd.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M.
Hard ridden take rail and lead, clocked fast sectionals, hung on until 200M flattened.
Hard ridden forward to cross, sat outside the leader, harmed by the fast pace, ran on until 200M flattened.
Behind midfield along the fence, suited by the fast pace, however lack room in straight, ran on well when clear.
Very slow away, took rail behind midfield, benefited by the fast tempo, ran on fairly.
Pushed to occupy box seat, not suited by the fast pace, lack room 400M, flattened 200M.
Pushed forward, 2-3 wide in front of midfield, emptied 250M.
Failed to muster, favoured by the fast pace, never better than midfield.
Eased back, suited by the fast tempo, never nearer.
Never a factor at rear.
Never competitive, tailed out.
Raced midfield, 3.5Ls behind the leader 3 wide without cover, suited by the fast tempo, ran home strongly to score by a nose.
Pushed forward to obtain the box seat, despite harmed by the fast pace, ran on strongly for 2nd in a tight finish, missed by a nose.
Jumped awkwardly, then settled 5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, suited by the fast tempo, stormed home for 3rd in a tight finish.
Sent forward to take the fence and led by 1L at fast sectionals, kept on strongly until final 50M headed, hung on for 4th in a tight finish.
At rear, 6.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, benefited by the fast pace, ran on nicely.
Settled worse than midfield about 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite the fast tempo, never ran on.
Pushed forward to park outside the leader at fast sectionals, weakened soon after straightening.
Failed to respond and finished tailed of the field despite hard ridden along throughout. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Sharp jump, eased to rail midfield, roused 950m, settled just beyond midfield on rail, improved steadily along inside, travelled into race powerfully 400m, just prevailed.
Broke evenly, scrubbed to settle handy, settled 3rd 1 off, pushed along early stages, reached joint lead under hold, ridden 400m, one-paced in straight, hit lead 50m but grabbed near lien.
Slow to muster, settled near rear 3 deep with cover, erratic on bend, stoked up 450m, hit top gear late, found line very strongly.
Even start, pushed towards lead on rail, joint lead 800m, neck lead 650m, travelled strongly on bend, ridden 400m, fought on tenaciously in straight, succumbed 50m, lost 3rd late.
Away well, eased out of speed battled, settled just fore of midfield on rail, ridden to improve 700m, short of room 500m, ridden 400m, held up slightly early straight, boxed on.
Slow break, settled beyond midfield 1 off, saved ground into straight, ridden 420m, stayed on evenly.
Slightly awkward start, eased to back, settled near rear on rail, back to last 600m, railed up, ridden 350m, one-paced.
Jumped well, ridden along but outpaced, settled beyond midfield 3 deep, pulled 4 wide 550m, widest into straight and asked for an effort, outsprinted.
Strong beginning, ridden towards lead, bumped 900m and began pulling, eased, settled midfield 1 off, ridden 600m, couldn't sustain long run, eased 50m.
First to break, pushed to lead, joined 800m, stuck 3 deep 1st turn, niggled to get across, neck 2nd 650m, under pressure 450m, faded tamely, eased.
OK break, eased from outside, trapped deep, pushed to go forward, 4 deep near rear 750m, under significant pressure 500m, quickly a clear last, eased 100m.
Away on terms, natural speed to contest lead, stuck 4th 4 deep 750m, gave ground from 650m, ridden along 500m, dropped out meekly, eased right down 250m.
Slow to muster, roused along to push towards lead, settled 2nd 1 off, joint lead 450m, ridden 380m, narrow advantage 250m, stayed on grimly to win.
Slightly slow start, up towards lead quickly, settled 3rd 3 deep, up to 2nd 720m, joint lead 600m, under pressure 400m, responded, fought on but couldn't quite pass.
OK break but pushed early, settled fore of midfield 1 off, roused along 650m, gradually picked up, best work late to just miss.
Jumped well, up near lead early, initially eased out of speed battle 4 deep no cover, allowed to stride forward 650m, made line of 4 for lead 450m, fought on gamely to wire .
First to jump, settled just behind speed on rail, asked for effort 370m, little room 300m, crowded 100m, not properly tested.
Fast jump, back to last from outside gate, outpaced early, distant last to 600m, railed through, niggled along until hard ridden 350m, ate up ground late.
Broke on terms, showed superior natural speed to lead quickly, slow pace, joined 650m, under pressure 450m, response short-lived, weakened 250m.
Began OK, roused along to press leaders, soon outsped, settled midfield 3 deep with cover, under heavy drive 450m, one-paced.
Fair start, down to rail, ridden aggressively to improve, settled beyond midfield on inside, overracing 800m, ridden along 450m, never likely.
Jumped well, eased, settled beyond midfield 4 deep limited cover, ridden 400m, faded tamely.
Down on nose at start, outsped, eased to settle near rear 1 off, checked slightly 650m, ridden along soon after, never in it.
Away on terms, outpaced early, settled near rear 3 deep, severely checked 650m, eased right down.
Raced in midfield, 3-3/4L behind along the rail, found extra passing 150M to run on strongly and scored by a nose.
Took box-seat, sat 2L off the lead, kicked ahead passing 200M but couldn't hold off the winner's effort in final 50M.
Pushed forward to take the rail and led by 1L, headed passing 200M, but kept on going to the line.
Settled in midfield, 4L behind 2 wide, kept on nicely to the line despite being one paced only.
Travelled towards the rear, 6-3/4L behind 3 wide with cover, continued to make steady ground from straightening.
Niggled forward to obtain one-off one-back position, sat 2-1/2L behind, in touch until 150M but still ran on.
Raced in behind midfield, 5-1/2L behind 2 wide, in the Straight ran on only one paced.
Sat in behind midfield, 5-1/2L behind along the rail, slightly closer at turn, kept on one paced to the line.
Pushed forward and sat outside the leader 1L off, kept on until passing 250M when couldn't find extra.
Travelled towards the rear, 8L behind 2 wide, improved slightly rounding turn but ran home one paced.
Raced in midfield, 5L off the pace 3 wide with cover, dropped off steadily in the Straight.
Taken back, travelled at the rear 8-1/2L behind along the rail, not competitive and finished tailed out.
Settled just in front of midfield, 3-1/2L off 3 wide without cover, gave ground on straightening and finished tailed out.
At rear and finished tailed out, never a factor.

Began fairly, ridden but no speed, dropping to midfield along rail 4L from leader. Made good ground around final turn to be 2nd into straight, hit the front 280m, bolted home under hands and heels riding.
Began fairly, no early speed, dropping behind midfield but holding fence. Shaken up passing 550m, tracked winner into straight, kept chasing despite widening gap.

Hard ridden from widest gate to get forward position, taking first turn 3-wide before settling 3L from leader back stretch but without cover. Shaken up 500m, looked chance on entering straight, boxed on gamely.
Began awkwardly but picked up quickly, settling in box seat 2L from leader back stretch. Shaken up 650m when tempo increased, looked chance on straightening, then one-paced.

Jumped OK, restrained and shifted across behind horses, settling at rear in one-off position. Dropped to last passing 950m, still last entering straight before finishing off nicely, doing best work final stages.
Broke well, unable to handle early pace and slipped back to rear in one-off position. Was not asked for an effort until straightening for home when taken to centre track and ran on steadily.
Began fairly, restrained and shifted across behind runners to rail, settling at rear. Left flat-footed 600m when tempo increased, took rails run in straight, ran on nicely to 100m when flattened.
Broke well, ridden to obtain forward position, settling midfield in one-off position. Lost position passing 1000m, swung wide into straight, ran on fairly.
Got off well, pressed forward, took first turn 3-wide, before settling in one-off position 2L from leader back stretch. Steadied and lost position passing 600m, one-paced in straight.
Restrained shortly after start and shifted across behind runners, settling last. Made a short forward move 950m, swung wide into straight, boxed on fairly.
Bounced best, taken to front and travelled strongly, setting good pace. Well clear entering straight but under pressure passing 300m and weakened. Unacceptable performance.
Quickly away, pressed forward, seltling 4L from leader in one-off position. Under pressure home turn, losing position, and found nothing in straight under hard riding.
Began OK, ridden along to hold one-off position in midfield. Kept on steadily to straight when gave ground quickly, finishing tailed out. Unacceptable performance.

Broke well, charged forward to race outside but a length behind leader first turn and back stretch. Started to throw out distress signals around final turn and finished tailed out. Unacceptable performance.
Chased leader in a strongly run race, improved up took over nearing 200M, drew clear for a comfortable win.
Held up 2-wide midfield in a strongly run race, let down well from 300M but couldn't reel in winner, went clear 2nd late stages.
Failed to muster speed early stages, ended up behind midfield 6-7Ls off the good pace, finished off strongly up the inside rail final 300M, got up for 3rd just in time.
Urged along to be 3rd on settling, caught 3-wide no cover, gave chase 450M and but couldn't get closer to first 2, tried right to the line.
Sped to the lead, set good sectionals to straight, all out 300M but couldn't hold off winner, faded to 5th towards the finish.
Jumped on terms to be 3-4Ls behind leader in a strongly run race, kept on only fairly in straight, never troubled leaders.
Lost ground at the start, towards the rear 7-8Ls off the good pace middle stages, made limited progress over final 300M.
Niggled along to hold a position towards the rear, couldn't go on inside 400M, never threatened.
Lost ground at the start, ridden along to make up lost ground but failed to muster speed, on straightening plenty of work to do, (Lame Left front.)
Caught wide early stages, slotted into a 2-wide spot ahead of midfield making home turn, 5th at 400M, couldn't quicken on the run home and weakened inside 200M. (Lame next day.)
Lost ground at the start, in last detached over 10Ls off the good pace, failed to pick up at any stage, never involved.

Moderate start but soon picked up to race just inside the leader near stands rails, took up running soon after coming onto course proper, just held on under pressure.
Minor interference jumping out, settled towards the rear, finished off race well.
Settled in midfield, briefly baulked over 300 metres out, ran on well.
Settled better than midfield when about 3L off the pace, came to challenge inside final the 300 metres reaching 1L 2nd 200 metres out, unable to sustain effort closing stages.
Settled in midfield after beginning from the lowest draw, kept on steadily without threatening.
Jumped fairly, niggled along but soon dropped to midfield, produced some late impression closing stages.
Settled just worse than midfield near stands rails, given reminders approaching the half-way mark , produced good late impression closing stages.
Jumped fairly, soon dropped to the rear, ran on past beaten horses in the closing stages.
Moderate start, soon dropped to last few, kept on past beaten horses in the closing stages.
Jumped well from a low draw, travelled in a prominent position near the centre of the track, faded under pressure inside the final 300 metres.
Not far off, briefly gained 3rd position just over 1L off the pace coming onto course proper, folded up quickly.
Slow out, always well behind.
Held narrow lead on stands rails, headed passing the 400 metres, dropped out.
Always in last few and never seen with a chance.
Pushed to take rail and lead, clocked fast sectionals, drifted away 300M and scored.
In front of midfield, 2 wide, ran on well for 2nd.
Box seat, held ground for 3rd despite not suited by the fast sectionals.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast pace, made steady ground 300M.
Eased back, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 250M.
Midfield, 3 wide, suited by the fast pace, made ground 300M, run ended 100M.
Eased back, 3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, ran on fairly in straight.
Eased back, benefited by the fast tempo, made ground 200M.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide outside the leader, harmed by the fast pace, emptied 250M.
Pushed forward, 3 wide just off the leaders, not suited by the fast tempo, out of fuel 300M.
Behind midfield, suited by the fast pace, never improved.
Eased back, raced 4-5 wide throughout, never competitive.
Eased back, never a factor.
Never better than midfield, hung out badly and checked round the home bend.
Raced midfield, 4Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, suited by the fast tempo, ran on strongly to score by 1/2L.
Taken back, 7Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, benefited by the fast pace, stormed home for 2nd.
Ridden forward to park outside the leader, despite harmed by the fast tempo, kept on strongly until headed 100M, hung on for 3rd.
Settled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, benefited by the fast sectionals, ran home well for 4th.
At rear, 8Ls behind the leader on the fence, suited by the fast tempo, ran home nicely.
Prominent, despite harmed by the fast tempo and travelled wide and without cover throughout, kept on steadily until weakened over the latter stages.
Rolled to obtain the box seat, harmed by the fast tempo, blocked early straight, however unable to be tested when clear due to racing manners.
Taken back, 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite the fast tempo, ran on fairly.
Raced midfield, 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite the fast tempo, ran home fairly and weakened over the latter stages.
Settled in front of midfield about 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, harmed by the fast tempo, weakened 250M.
Raced midfield, 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite the fast tempo, made no impression in straight.
Eased back from a wide draw, 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite the fast sectionals, never ran on.
Prominent, harmed by the fast pace, weakened soon after straightening.
Ridden forward to take the lead along the fence at fast tempo, out of fuel 300M.
Broke ok but lacked toe & bustled, drifted back to 4th last 1 off & niggled, 3 wide 550m, driven widest into stretch, green but charged centre track to lead 150m, drew clear.
Quick to stride, bustled to stalk front rank on rail, shuffled back & checked off heels when overracing 850m, driven into stretch, quickened on fence to press lead 150m, no match for winner,
Tardy start, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, finished off well in straight to claim 3rd.
Speed to lead, settled & headed 1120m, 3 wide & kicked up to lead again 900m, shared lead turning in, kept on well early in straight, headed near 150m, stayed on for 4th.
Slow start & bustled forward on outer to be handy 3 wide no cover at 800m, driven wide into stretch, all out to challenge 250m, plugged on one pace.
Taken back at start, raced rail near rear, niggled on turn & driven into stretch, hard-driven 300m, one-paced but plugged on for late inroads.
Snagged back at start, raced near tail 1 off with cover, niggled along, driven 400m & shifted wide, stayed on for moderate late headway.
Tardy start, worked forward to fore of midfield 1 off with cover 850m, in pocket turning in, switched inside 300m, crowded, kept on moderately.
Broke well, taken back from widest gate, raced 3 wide with cover midfield, wide home turn & driven 400m, kept on evenly.
Broke well & rousted wide front rank, crossed to lead 1120m, trapped 4 wide & headed 900m, settled 2nd 1 off 850m, 3rd & driven turning in, boxed on one pace until emptied 100m & tapered.
Broke ok, bustled forward to rail fore of midfield, minor advance on turn, in pocket 400m, minor check 300m, soon emptied & faded.
Fast break, bustled to hold handy spot 1 off with cover, settled 1 back on rail 850m, shifted wide on turn, every chance when driven 350m, found nil & weakened.
Good break wide & bustled initially, worked wide no cover until briefly 1 back 1 off 850m, shifted 3 deep no cover 800m, vied for lead turning in & driven, emptied 380m, faded.
Sluggish start, soon detached at tail on rail & bustled, hard driven into stretch, found nil, never a factor.
Baulked slightly at start, eased, settled near rear 1 off, pushed wider 600m, ridden 450m, unleashed big run centre track, just got there.
Jumped well, ridden along to go forward, settled midfield 3 deep no cover, shuffled 4 deep 620m, ridden 500m, sprinted quickly, hit lead 300m, caught final strides.
OK to begin, eased, crowded 1000m, settled beyond midfield 1 off, checked 600m, impeded again 480m, no room 330m, clear 250m, sprinted powerfully, luckless.
Began well, eased to settle beyond midfield 4 deep no cover, back to 3 deep with cover 650m, widest into straight and ridden, stayed on.
Even break, natural speed, settled just fore of midfield, racing alone but 1 off, pulled wider 520m, bumping duel 420m, momentary lead 300m, boxed on.
Away fairly, under a throttlehold from gates, back to 3L last 1000m, asked for effort widest 420m, finished willingly very late.
Jumped fast, eased, settled midfield 3 deep no cover, roused along 850m, lost position 700m, checked 480m, stayed on, outpaced.
Awkward start, eased, settled beyond midfield on rail, improved to midfield 900m, ridden 500m, never in it.
First to break, stoked up to push forward, settled 3rd 3 deep no cover, ridden 450m, hanging towards rail, dropped out sharply.
Away on terms, natural speed to join leaders, eased to settle 5th 1 off, short of room 600m, ridden 480m, bumping duel, effort short-lived, eased 100m.
Slightly awkward jump, eased, back to near rear on rail, clicked up 600m, railed through, checked 380m, short of room thereafter, clear 240m, struggled to pick up.
Slightly slow, driven hard to muster speed, improved rapidly on inside, settled 4th on rail, ridden through gap 450m, faded quickly, eased 120m.
Sharp break, ridden vigorously to go forward, early leader, narrow lead 1 off 800m, relinquished lead 700m, under pressure 600m, dropped out tamely.
Strong start, ridden up towards lead, near joint lead 1000m on rail, outright lead 700m, ridden 450m, claimed quickly, weakened, eased 200m.
Prominent and sat behind the lead on the outside rail 1-1/4L off, ran on nicely to score once cleared from 200M.
Bumped start then raced behind the leaders, stand side 1-3/4L off, kept on strongly but couldn't hold off winner's finish.
Rolled forward to lead by a nose along the outside fence, headed passing 50M but kept on to the line and took 3rd.
Awkward start, raced slightly behind midfield, 5L behind stand side, made nice ground and kept on nicely for 4th.
Slotted into midfield and raced on the outer rail, 4L behind the lead, ran on and nearest at the finish. (Bled from both nostrils)
Crowded start, raced at the rear, 6-1/4L behind stand side, dash at 300M then help up, closed off strongly from 150M.
Crowded start and raced towards the rear, 5-1/4L behind stand side, made slight ground when taken to centre track.
Raced in midfield, 3-1/4L off stand side, shifted to centre track from 400M but finished off only one paced.
Travelled behind the leaders, 1-3/4L off stand side, in touch with the leaders until weakened passing 200M. (Lame left front leg)
Awkward start then remained towards the rear, 5-3/4L behind on the outer rail, did not improve.
Pushed forward and raced amongst the lead on centre track, weakened gradually after 400M.
Ridden forward and shared lead, dropped off after 400M. (Blood in the horse's trachea)
Always towards the rear, never a factor.
Pushed forward and shared lead, showed nothing when tested. (Blood in the horse's trachea and lame left front leg)
Began fairly, pressed forward from widest draw but forced to race wide 3L from leader. Began forward move 600m, rolled up join leaders 250m before pulling clear under hands and heels riding.
Crowded out start, dropping towards rear between horses. Allowed own pace to turn, blocked for room early straight, then weaved passage between horses, finishing strongly final 100m.
Jumped OK, ridden to find cover but held 3-wide at midfield on settling. Swung wide into straight, taken to centre track and finished off strongly to grab minor placing.
Outpaced and soon towards rear but three-wide. Taken to centre track on straightening and picking up momentum steadily before finishing off nicely.
Quickly into stride but eased out off pace battle, settling 3L back in one-off position. Niggled at top of straight but took time to pick up momentum doing best work final stages.
Jumped OK, ridden vigorously but didn't muster, dropping to last on settling. Switched out entering straight, picked up momentum gradually and doing best work at the finish.
Began well, pressed forward to lead from outside draw but made to work by inside runner forcing the pace. Dropped to second passing 1200m but battled on strongly to 150m when tired and dropped out.
Bumped and unbalanced start then hard ridden to hold forward position and prevent leader from crossing. Took over lead 1200m, kept on well to 150m before giving ground.
Bounced OK, unable handle early speed, settling behind midfield in one-off position. Made short-lived effort early straight before racing in restricted room 150m, turning one-paced.
Outpaced and soon at rear in one-off position. Switch out in straight to make run but found little under hard riding.
Began well, ridden along to hold the rail, settling midfield. Urged along top of straight, made up some ground before tiring and turning one-paced.
No early pace and soon at rear but along fence. Improved position approaching home turn but still well back on straightening and only one-paced.
Used early to motor forward from an outside position to sit 2L from leader in one-off position. Kept on strongly on straightening to look a chance 200m before running out of stamina and fading.
Ridden early to hold rail position, settling in box seat 2L from leader 1400m. Kept on steadily to turn but under pressure on straightening and faded.

Settled down 3-4Ls off the pace in midfield, 3-wide trip to straight, worked home powerfully final 250M to wear down the race favourite in the shadows of post. (Trainer : improved performance attributable to gear change.)
Jumped well from draw 1, soon moved up to share the lead on the inner, fought on well under pressure passing 300M, headed near finish.
Positively ridden to find the lead under 10lb claimer, on the pace 2-wide, fought on well final 300M, turned one pace final 100M holding on for 3rd just.
Jumped on terms to be 5th just over 2Ls off the pace, driven out 400M and kept up his chase on leaders, just missed 3rd.
Guided to a midfield spot along the rails, 7th at 400M and 3-4Ls off leaders, plugged on into modest 5th near 100M but at no stage did he seriously threaten leaders.
Began well, restrained to a midfield position along the 2-path, 4Ls to make up 400M, stayed on mildly without threatening.
Eased back from draw 13, in rear pair 6-7Ls behind leaders, brought wide 500M, finished off reasonably well but had too much ground to make up.
Not hurried early stages, near the rear 6Ls off the pace, hung out passing 600M and jockey unable to ride it out fully until 150M, made some late headway. (Racing manners unacceptable)
Chased leaders, raced fiercely when steadied to obtain cover 1000M, ran on one pace entering straight, couldn't go on 250M.
Taken back to be last on settling, 7Ls off at 400M, failed to present as a winning chance on straightening, only made minor headway.
Restrained on jumping, shifted to a 3-wide spot with cover, 5Ls off the pace midfield 800M, ran on one-pace in straight, never likely.
Towards the rear, badly hampered by a rival rounding home turn, took a while for the jockey to balance the horse early straight, closed off fairly when ridden out 300M. (Jockey questioned.)
Caught wide in midfield throughout from draw 14, failed to pick up ground turning home. (Irregular Heart Rhythm / Blood in trachea.)
Rushed forward and chased leaders 3-wide without cover, no extra 300M and gave way.

Broke well, pressed forward to grab third but shuffled back to fifth as field packed up. Stayed on rail around turn, got split 350m, powered through to lead 200m before pulling clear on hands and heels riding.
Began OK, not pushed, settling behind midfield along rail. Left fence 700m but found little room top of straight. Got clear 250m and finished off nicely.
Away nicely, not pushed, settling in midfield in one-out position. Given more rain 700m, swung wide into straight, ran on strongly to grab minor placing.
Checked after jumping fairly, ridden to make up ground racing 3-wide 1300m. Rolled forward to race outside new leader 880m, looked chance on straightening, battled well to 100m when flattened.

Began nicely, rolled forward but over-raced before settling 3-wide, 3L from leader. Wide around turn, bumped and unbalanced 450m, loomed up to join leaders approaching 200m, turning one-paced final 100m.
Jumped with field, ridden along before hampered 1100m and shifted closer to fence behind midfield. Switch out entering straight, got clear running 400m, finished off nicely down centre track.
Began well but outpaced, dropping to rear in one-off position. Not asked for effort until straightening, taken to centre track and finished off nicely.
Bumped and unbalanced start, recovered quickly and driven forward to take lead 1250m before crossing to fence 1000m. Collared approaching 200m but kept on gamely till swamped final stages.
Jumped fairly, outpaced, dropping to rear. Attempted to improve potion but over-raced and checked 1000m. Swung wide entering straight and ran on fairly.
Began fairly, ridden to hold position behind midfield. Not suited by tempo and had to be ridden to hold position middle stages. Swung wide into straight but only on-paced.
First out, taken to rail and then settled behind the pace, some 2L from leader. Closed in top of straight to look a chance, kept on gamely to 100m before tiring.
Began well, urged forward, settling along rail ahead of midfield. Lost position around home turn, under pressure from 300m, giving ground gradually.
Outpaced and soon in last pair along rail. Made forward move around home turn but ran out of stamina shortly after straightening and faded.
Hard ridden from widest draw to hold forward position, racing outside early leader before dropping to third when another took over. Started to feel the pinch on straightening and faded.
Eased out and settled just behind midfield, 1 off the fence. Had clear run in the straight and progressed steadily from the 400m. Strong over last 150m to fall in on the line.

Eased forward early to be handily placed in 5th, 1 off the fence. Ran well from the turn to lead by the 250m, and clear away from the main pack. Lead until last 20m, but couldn't hold out fast finishing winner.
Taken up early, before dropping back to sit midfield, 3 wide with no cover from 700m. Ran solidly in the straight without kicking and snuck into 3rd on the line.
Cruised forward from the low draw to sit midfield, 1 off the fence. Ran solidly in the straight and was just nosed out for 3rd on the line.
Taken forward from the wide draw to sit in the leading group, 3 wide. Eased back to 3rd with cover rounding 1st turn. Checked off heels at 200m. Steady to the line, lost a place in the last 50m.
Cruised forward from the inside draw to sit just forward of midfield. Plugged away steadily in the straight, but never looked to be a threat.
Dropped back early to sit slightly worse than midfield, 3 wide. Progressed steadily in the straight, without ever threatening a place,
Went forward early and travelled keenly in front. Burnt up his fuel early, had nothing left in the straight and dropped out from the 200m. Jockey questioned.

Taken forward early but didn't want to get caught in a 3-way speed dual, dropping back trailing position 1 off/1 back. Came to the rail before turn. Unbalanced on heels 200m. Steady to the line late. Jockey questioned.
Bounded on jumping and lost ground. Settled in last position. Only fair to the line and never a threat.
Taken forward early to share the lead. Only plugged to line fairly in the straight under minimal urging.
Worked up in the barrier, lifted feet on jumping and slow to begin. Settled worse than midfield, on the fence. Ran flat in the straight and not pushed out to the line.
Dropped back early to sit at the rear of the field, 3-4 wide. Widest on the turn, but never progressed and was eased late.
Dropped back from the jump to sit 2nd last. Never looked like running on, and eased out late.

Soon led, obtained rails run 800 metres out, kicked over 2L clear after straightening, just held on. (Questioned for improved performance)
Settled well behind, saved ground turning in, ran on well under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Niggled along just off the pace on rails, kept on without quickening in straight, lost 2nd late.
Soon taken back from a wide gate, trailed the field to straight, finished off race well near the centre of the track.
Ridden along wide in just better than midfield, switched out for a run entering straight, fought on steadily without quickening.
Settled in midfield on rails, commenced move rounding home bend improving to within 2L of leader in 3rd entering the straight, soon faded under pressure.
Niggled along in midfield, ran home one-paced.
Settled just worse than midfield on rails, saved ground turning in, ran home one-paced.
Well there, lost position entering straight, gave ground steadily.
Broke well, settled in last few, kept on one pace without quickening.
Driven along from the widest gate, raced wide without cover in a prominent position to straight, dropped away quickly.

Placing: UR
Comment: Reared at start and jumped out riderless.
Took rail in front of midfield, dashed well 300M to score.
Box seat, enjoyed the slow sectionals, ran on well for 2nd.
Eased back early, trapped 3 wide, moved forward 1000M to take the rail and lead, took advantages from the slow pace, hung on well until 150M overhauled, ran on for 3rd.
Hard ridden to sit in front of midfield, 2 wide, just held ground in straight.
At rear, 2 wide, checked severely on two occasions early, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 250M despite all negative racing situations.
Pressed forward, sat 2 wide, benefited by the slow sectionals, out of fuel 200M.
Midfield, took rail, not suited by the slow pace, ran on fairly.
Failed to muster, at rear, 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, not suited by the slow tempo, never improved.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, weakened 300M.
At back, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, emptied 400M.
Checked early, never a factor.
Settled worse than midfield about 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, switched wide turning in, finished off strongly to score by a nose.
At rear, travelled 9Ls behind the leader on the fence, benefited by the fast sectionals, swung wide turning in, stormed home for 2nd, missed by a nose.
Raced midfield, 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, suited by the fast tempo, ran on steadily for 3rd.
Settled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the fast tempo, made some ground for 4th without threatening.
Prominent, 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, not suited by the fast sectionals, kept on one paced initially, however, was checked 150M, well beaten thereafter.
Pushed forward to obtain a box seat from a wide draw, harmed by the fast tempo, made minor ground initially, however, was bumped heavily 150M and weakened thereafter.
Raced midfield, 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite the fast sectionals, kept on fairly and weakened final 100M.
At back, travelled 9Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite the fast tempo, never ran on.
Rolled forward to park outside the leader at fast tempo, kept on until final furlong weakened.
Sent forward to share the lead on the fence at fast sectionals, dropped off rounding the Home Turn, tailed out.
Good break, settled 4th 1 off with cover, niggled 550m, driven wide into stretch, quickened smartly & shifted in, led100m, extended clear.
Fast start widest, to lead 1100m, crossed to rail 950m, 0.5L up & ridden 330m, all out & headed 100m, tapered, just held 2nd.
Broke well, snagged to race midfield 1 off with cover, bustled 400m to close, very wide off turn & driven, closed strongly, just missed 2nd.
Sharp start, settled 3rd 1 back on rail, shifted out final turn & driven 300m, boxed on one pace.
Snagged at start, trapped 3 wide no cover & taken back to slot 1 off behind midfield, driven on turn & wide into stretch, stayed on for minor late gains.
Speed to lead at break & bustled, headed 1100m, parked 2nd 1 off but overraced, 0.5L down & niggled 400m, driven into stretch, out-sped, tapered closing stages.
Taken back from wide to rail, raced rank last until 800m, settled last trio, niggled 450m, driven into stretch, boxed on.
Missed break, crossed to rail & rolled to park behind midfield, driven into stretch, plugged on one pace centre track.
Caught wide no cover & overraced, snagged to tail 800m, raced last trio 3 wide with cover, wide home turn & driven, kept on without threat.
Moderate start, trapped 4 wide no cover initially, soon 3 wide no cover behind midfield, wide into stretch, ridden 250m, found little in even run home.
Slow start, raced last trio 1 off with cover, under pump 450m, hard ridden 300m, found nil.
Sharp start, lacked toe & soon bustled, settled midfield on rail, niggled 550m, emptied turning in & faded.
Dipped at start, settled fore of midfield 1 off, travelled strongly throughout, short of room 500m , in clear 430m, sprinted to lead 230m, raced away.
Rousted along early, settled 3rd and 4th on rail, took inside run and ridden along 310m, sprinted well but no match, grabbed 2nd late.
Fast to break, eased out of speed battle, settled just beyond midfield 1 off, ridden 1100m, shuffled back 650m, asked to improve 450m, sprinted centre track, no match.
Away OK, outpaced early, settled midfield on rail, travelling well but nowhere to go 500m, railed through 350m, stayed on.
Good jump, taken back in search of a spot, overracing slightly, settled beyond midfield on rail, shuffled back 600m, held up 200m, sprinted through but too late.
Awkward at start, restrained to rear, settled near tail 1 off, shifted 3 deep 900m, pulled wider and ridden 500m, widest into straight, ran about under pressure, limited impression.
Even break, ridden strongly to press forward, 3 deep 1st turn near lead, posted wide fore of midfield, pushed up into 3rd 3 deep, ridden 480m, up to lead 280m, claimed shortly afterwards, one-paced.
Half-step slow, settled at rear on rail, racing keenly at times throughout, ridden 300m, checked and shifted course soon after, plugged away.
First to begin, allowed to stride forward, overracing 1st turn, settled 3rd 1 off 1000m, refused to settle, shuffled back to 5th 900m, ridden along 600m, checked 100m, no extra.

Jumped well, ridden vigorously, narrow lead at 1st turn on rail, led at moderate sectionals, attacked for lead 950m, held together until 370m, drifted off rail into straight, joined 250m, beaten quickly.
Slightly awkward break, under a drive from the gates, settled beyond midfield 1 off, shifted 3 deep 700m, improved quickly around field, 4 deep 500m, effort short-lived.
Slightly slow to break, ridden to press forward, stuck 4 deep 1st turn, pushed on, sat 2nd 3 deep overracing, attacked for lead 1 off 950m, ridden 500m, joint lead 400m, shunted 300m and dropped out.
Settled into box-seat, sat 1-1/4L off, kicked clear at 150M and kept on to score by 1L under hold.
Crowded after the start, raced in midfield 2-3/4L behind along the rail, hampered at 250M, finished off gamely for 2nd.
Raced in front of midfield, 2-1/4L off 2 wide, kept on strongly to the line and just missed out on 2nd.
Taken back, in worse than midfield 4-1/4L behind on the rail, held up from 200M to 150M then ran on nicely to the line.
Slotted into midfield, 3-1/2L behind 2 wide, ran on well once shifted out into clear running approaching 250M.
Settled in one-off one-back position, 1-1/4L off the lead, bumped heavily at 250M, one paced thereafter.
Eased back, at the rear 6L behind along the rail, raced tight at 150M, nonetheless made nice ground on inner Straight.
Bumped start, raced in worse than midfield 5L off 2 wide, improved steadily in the Straight.
Pushed forward and shared lead on the rail, bumped a runner heavily at 250M, dropped off from 200M.
Sent forward and shared lead in a 2 wide position, was bumped heavily at 250M, did not run on thereafter.
Steadied and took cover after initially racing wide, remained at the rear 6-1/4L behind and 2 wide, did not improve.
Travelled in midfield, 3-1/4L behind 3 wide without cover, not competitive in the Straight.
Jumped fairly, taken to fence, settling 4L from leader first turn. Shaken up passing 500m, hard ridden around turn, battled on strongly under vigorous riding to win close home.
Broke well, raced in 2nd, travelled well throughout, kept on very well in straight but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Jumped well, pressed forward to take lead on settling. Travelled keenly back stretch setting up big lead before steadied home turn. Caught passing 150m but kept battling to line.
Jumped with field but bumped shortly after, then shifted in, settling in one-off position 4L from leader. Switched out approaching home turn, wide into straight, ran on steadily.
Bumped on jumping then shifted across behind horses, settling towards rear in one-off position. Hard ridden from 500m, wide into straight, ran on steadily.
Off nicely, pressed forward from an outside draw, finding cover behind midfield entering first turn. Put under pressure from 500m, wide into straight, boxed on fairly.
Got off OK, eased off early pace and taken to fence towards the rear. Stayed on rail around turn, kept shifting in straight to get run but only one-paced when clear.
Hard ridden to hold forward position, racing 3-wide around first turn till settling 3L from leader back stretch. Under pressure from 450m, kept on fairly to 150m before giving around.
Bumped start, restrained, shifted across behind runners, dropping to rear, more than 10L from leader back stretch. Took rails run in straight but only one-paced.
Began awkwardly, taken to fence but travelled keenly before settling 5L from leader passing 900m. Got inside run in straight, kept on gamely to 100m before tiring.
Jumped OK, restrained, switched in to rail and long last on settling. Never competitive.
Vigorously ridden to go forward, then steadied 1400m and shifted in to get cover in midfield. Left without cover from 900m, wide home turn, given reminders but running on empty from 150m.
Positively ridden from 12, crossed to sit outside leader in a slowly run contest, chased hard inside 300M and wore down leader close home for a narrow win.

Jumped on terms from 11 and crossed to a 2-wide spot in midfield, 3Ls off leader at 600M in a slowly run race, kept responding to pressure from 300M, did best work late and just failed to nail the winner.
Away well to share lead on the inside, pace slow, led down the straight until headed by first 2 in the shadows of post.
Sat just off the pace, raced keenly when leader steadied the tempo passing 1000M, worked to the line hard from 300M, narrowly beaten to 4th in a blanket finish.
Jumped fair to be 7th on the inside 3Ls back on settling, finished off well over final 300M and was nearest at the finish beaten only a neck in 5th.
Eased back to near the rear, difficult to settle 900M, about 4-5Ls off the slow pace home turn, held up near 200M, switched lane and closed off steadily for a close 6th.
Began fairly, 5Ls off the pace early stages, switched to 3-wide 700M, closed off moderately without threatening leaders.
Taken back from wide barrier, in 2nd last 6Ls off the slow pace, bumped and taken wider 800M, brought wide 350M, stayed on without threatening.
Began awkwardly, taken back from wide barrier, held last spot to straight, checked 300M, made some progress after but never reach contention.
Chased leaders in a slowly run race, couldn't muster the speed to be closer passing 300M, weakened from 150M. (Lame next day.)
Never far off but caught 3-wide no cover passing 1000M, outpaced 400M and plodded home behind runners.
Sat behind midfield in a slowly run race, 5Ls off leaders, couldn't finish off in the straight.
Began fairly, taken straight to fence and settled about 4L from leader. Left fence 500m, swung very wide into straight, rolled forward to lead 150m, pulling clear under hands and heels riding.
Broke well, sharing early pace before easing 3L back along fence first turn. Switched out approaching home turn, 4-wide into straight, looked chance 150m but unable to match winner closing stages.
Began well, bumped and unbalanced 1600m before settling one-off 3L from leader. Urged forward passing 600m, swung very wide into straight, ran on steadily.

Restrained after jumping and shifted across to fence behind horses, settling at rear. Entered straight behind a wall of horses, picked up momentum while weaving between horses to be closest at finish.

Jumped well but restrained and shifted in behind horses to fence to be last on settling. Last into straight before picking up the bit and finishing strongly though not ridden out final stages when tightened.

Jumped fairly, rolled forward taking first turn 3-wide before settling one-back, one-out back stretch. Urged forward 500m to lead momentarily before feeling the pinch 150m. Raced tight final stages and not ridden out.
Broke well, pressed forward to lead on settling, setting good pace to back stretch when slowed tempo. Caught on straightening but kept battling till swamped final 50m.
Bumped shortly after start then shifted in to fence settling behind midfield. Stayed on fence around turn, made ground to 150m when blocked. Boxed on.
Away nicely, urged forward, sharing early pace till settling in box seat first turn. Shaken up entering straight but found little and gave ground steadily final 150m.
Began OK, ridden along early, settling behind midfield in one-off position. Put under pressure turning for home but found little, plodding home one-paced.

Pressed forward from widest draw, taking first turn 4-wide without cover. Allowed to improve to settle outside leader passing 1000m. Under pressure from 400m and spent force 200m, giving ground gradually.
Shifted across behind horses from wide draw, settling at rear in one-off position. Taken wide passing 700m by inside runner but never really in the hunt.

Taken back from a wide gate early, ridden forward to 8th and wide in midfield passing the 1000 metres, obtained a clear run near the centre of the track 350 metres out, quickened well to snatch victory short of line.
Ridden to take up running on rails shortly after the first 200 metres, broke over 2L clear early in straight, nearly stole the race but tired badly and caught final strides.
Settled in midfield on rails, ran on under pressure in straight, unable to sustain effort closing stages.
Well behind, switched out for a run upon straightening, ran on steadily down the centre of the straight to be nearest at finish.
Towards the rear on rails, made modest progress in straight without threatening.
In last few to straight, ran on steadily in straight to be nearest at finish.
Travelled in rear of midfield on rails, saved ground turning for home, kept on steadily without threatening.
Ridden along wide in midfield after beginning from the widest gate, took closer order rounding home bend, kept on steadily without quickening in straight.
Slightly slow out, quickly recovered to a prominent position, held clear 2nd into straight but swamped over 100 metres out.
Broke well from the one draw, settled just off the race on rails, faded out of contention from approaching home straight.
Settled in rear of midfield, shuffled further back coming out of back straight, kept on steadily without quickening.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, still well back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
With leaders briefly before settling in 3L 4th on rails, faded under pressure after straightening. (Bled)
Moderate start, soon recovered to midfield, slightly worse turning for home, soon weakened.
Pushed early, settled in front of midfield 2 wide, suited by the fast tempo, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Pushed forward, took rail and lead, clocked fast sectionals, hung on well until 100M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
In front of midfield on the fence, favoured by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M for 3rd.
Eased back to take rail, benefited by the fast tempo, lack room 400M, made steady ground when clear.
Box seat, not suited by the fast sectionals, held ground in straight.
Eased back, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M.
Eased back, trapped 3-4 wide, suited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 250M.
Midfield, trapped 3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, ran on fairly in straight.
Hard ridden early, at back along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, made ground 200M.
Pushed forward to hold the rail, not suited by the fast tempo, flattened 200M.
Eased back, trapped 4-5 wide, suited by the fast tempo, made ground 200M.
Hard ridden early but not muster, at back, 2 wide, favoured by the fast pace, no dash.
Eased back, trapped 4-5 wide, never improved.
Pushed forward, not suited by the fast tempo, soon emptied 350M.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on well to score by a neck.
Prominent, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, finished off nicely until headed by the winner final 70M, missed by a neck.
Hard ridden to settle in front of midfield, 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on gradually for 3rd.
Raced midfield, 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, switched wide turning in, ran on steadily for 4th.
Pushed to midfield, 4.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, made ground steadily when clear 300M.
Rolled forward to obtain the box seat, kept on one pace to the line.
Pushed forward to park outside the leader, kept on one pace until weakened final 150M.
At rear, travelled 9Ls behind the leader on the fence, swung wide turning in, ran on nicely.
Settled worse than midfield about 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, made some ground in straight.
Settled worse than midfield about 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, made minor ground in straight.
At back, travelled 9Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, made no impression in straight.
Rolled forward to take the fence and led by 1L, kept on until weakened final 300M.
Always at rear, never ran on.
Raced midfield, however, trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, eased down 300M. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Speed to lead, soon to rail & dictated tempo, shaken up 400m & kicked clear, kept on willingly under hard drive, in command at wire.
Broke with others, settled 4th 1 off with cover, shifted 3 deep home turn & shaken up, quickened to 2nd 300m, dug deep to close but held through final 100m.
Broke well & bustled initially, tracked 3rd 1 back on rail, driven 380m, outkicked, boxed on to hold 3rd.
Broke with others, snagged to behind midfield 1 off with cover, niggled a touch 600m, driven 350m, quickened to close until peaked on run 150m, fought on to wire without threatening.
Slow start, bustled at tail on inner last pair, bumped rival 820m & overraced, forced an opening turning in & driven, ran on for solid late gains.
Broke in line, settled rail midfield, niggled 500m, shifted out entering stretch, driven 400m, lacked toe, kept on evenly.
Snagged to last pair on outer, bumped 820m & overraced 3 wide no cover, ridden 500m, forced widest on turn, boxed on moderately.
Fast break & bustled to race 2nd 1 off no cover, shaken up 430m, outkicked & found nil, faded out tamely.
Broke on top, surrendered lead 1080m, eased to enjoy trail 3rd 1 off, travelled strongly throughout, 3 wide 550m and asked to improve, sprinted evenly, hit lead 80m, strong late.
Began well, pushed forward, vigorously ridden 950m, took lead shortly afterwards, 2L lead 700m, clicked up 420m, kicked strongly, claimed 80m, fought on doggedly.
Quick break, let speed go, settled midfield 1 off, down to rail 700m, ridden 520m, under drive 400m, bumped 200m, not clearest of runs but no match last 150m.
Jumped fast, outpaced slightly, settled fore of midfield on rail, asked for an effort 450m, switched over heels 250m, stayed on.
First to begin, unable to match leaders, settled just fore of midfield 1 off, began to improve 570m, in the clear 400m, outsprinted last 100m.
Began evenly, scrubbed up to improve, stuck 3 deep beyond midfield into 1st turn, 2 wide 750m, hunted along 550m, no clear run 350m, comfortably held.
Jumped strongly, poked through to lead 1070m, headed 920m, sat 2nd on rail overracing slightly, pushed off rail and ridden up 550m, struggling when bumped 200m, weakened.
Slight step slow, eased to near tail, settled well back 3 deep, ridden to improve 650m, asked 510m, made steady ground late without challenging.
Slightly slow to break, pressed to improve out deep, settled fore of midfield 3 deep no cover, ridden along 500m, one-paced entering straight, limited response.
Away on terms, stuck 4 deep just beyond midfield 1st turn, ridden to improve into midfield spot 3 deep cover, niggled 600m, under pressure into straight, never likely.
Slow jump, eased to rear, 2L last 900m, 3L last 800m and nudged along, tacked on 550m, widest into straight, nothing to offer.
Slow to break, outpaced early, ridden to hold spot, sat near rear on rail, back to last 550m, no impression.
Away OK, settled beyond midfield 1 off, outpaced and hard ridden 750m, vigorously ridden again 520m, never in it.
Slightly slow, just beyond midfield on rail, ridden 400m, eased down soon after.
Always prominent and raced amongst the lead, pulled away from the pack at 200M and scored comfortably by 1-1/4L.
In midfield initially and settled in line behind the leaders, 1-1/4L off stand side, kept on but couldn't match the winner.
Eased and raced towards the rear, 3-1/4L behind stand side, ran on gamely once cleared approaching 150M.
Travelled in the line behind the leaders, 1-1/2L off on outer fence, kept on nicely to take 4th.
Fair start only and failed to muster early speed, towards the rear 3-1/2L behind on outer rail, improved steadily for 5th.
Raced in the line behind the leaders, 1-1/2L off on centre track, made good run until 100M flattened.
Settled in midfield, 2-3/4L behind on centre track, kept on but was one paced going to the line.
Sent forward and shared lead on the outside rail, under pressure from 250M, weakened soon after.
Travelled in behind midfield, 4-1/4L behind on centre track, kept on one paced home.
Raced at the rear throughout, 6-1/2L behind stand side, made good ground from 150M.
Sent forward to share lead on centre track, weakened and headed at 350M.
Raced in midfield, 3L behind on centre track, showed nothing when asked passing 400M.
Bumped start, prominent 1-1/2L behind stand side, dropped off gradually and checked when crowded at 200M.
Crowded start, raced in behind midfield 3L behind stand side, not competitive.

Checked on jumping, dropping to last. Improved position gradually along the rail. Took rails run in straight but held for clear running until 250m when got clear and finished powerfully to win close home.
Away quickly, holding rail, racing inside leading pack till 1000m when eased back, settling one-away from fence 3L from leader. Three-wide entering straight, took over lead 250m, run down final 50m.
Snagged back soon after jump and shifted across behind horses, settling in one-off position at rear. Well back on straightening, ran on strongly under vigorous riding to snatch minor placing on line.
Broke well, allowed to stride forward at own pace before seeking cover 1200m, 4L from leader in one-off position. Swung wide entering straight, battled on gamely under hard riding.
Hard ridden to lead on settling then tried to slow pace but forced to increase tempo 1000m when challenged. Collared passing 250m but kept on gamely until flattened final 50m. Lame left front leg.

Bumped start, dropping to rear. Taken to rail and improved position to behind midfield passing 1000m. Left fence turning for home, wide into straight, shifted out abruptly 250m then shifted in 150m. Boxed on.

Began fairly before pressing forward from outside draw to race outside leader passing 1000m. Eased back slightly when tempo increased. Rolled forward again entering straight, bumped and lost position 300m, one-paced.
Began well but steadied and shifted across behind horses, dropping to rear. Last into turn. Hard ridden from 700m making ground steadily but awkwardly placed final 100 and not fully tested.
Began well, taken to fence, settling in box seat 2L from leader. Not much room top of straight, bumped 300m, got clear run 150m but only one-paced.
Bumped heavily at start, recovered and taken to fence, improving to midfield 4L from leader 1000m. Turned behind horses, had clear running but only one-paced.
Jumped with field but soon outpaced, dropping to rear but away from fence. Shuffled to last turning for home, taken to centre field but found nothing under hard riding.
Outpaced soon after jumping, dropping to behind midfield in one-off position. Came under pressure turning for home and gave ground gradually.
Hard ridden to go forward, sharing early pace before settling one-back, one-off at 1000m. Under pressure soon after straightening and gave ground gradually after passing 300m.
Broke well, pressed forward, settling midfield in one-off position. Started to feel the pinch soon after straitening and dropped out.
Jumped on terms, restrained to sit behind midfield along the 2-path, moved strongly into contention 300M, quickened to lead 150M and kept going well to hold off the late challenge of runner-up.
Dropped back from widest barrier, 6Ls off the pace at 800M, not clear until 300M, fought hard and came with strong challenge late stages, ran out of ground. (Jockey dropped whip 100M.)
Bustled along early, led along the rail from 1100M 2Ls in front, steadied the pace home turn, all out 250M, not pace of first 2 over final 150M but held on for 3rd well.
In 3rd never far off from leaders, 3Ls to make up 400M, kept on the chase to the line but no match for the leaders.
Shaken up early to sit 4th along the rail, just over 3Ls off the pace 400M, couldn't muster enough to be closer, well held by leaders on the run home.
Slow to begin, settled 4-5Ls off the pace and much further back than intended, unbalanced 250M, couldn't make up ground on leaders.
Jumped well to take early lead, raced keenly 1200M when steadied behind rival, kept up the chase early straight but peaked on his run 150M, no extra late stages.
Not hurried, settled down in the rear 6Ls off the pace, gave limited response only passing 400M, never threatened.
From draw 5 ended up 3-wide without cover towards the rear, 5Ls off the pace turning in, responded only fairly, couldn't go on final 200M.
Jumped with field but eased back, settling midfield in one-off position. Under tight hold turning for home, barged through gap 340m and stormed home to win close to line.
Broke well but eased back, settling towards the rear. Was 3-deep passing 900m, taken wide entering straight but inconvenienced 400m when improving. Ran on strongly to just miss.

Got off OK but snagged back, shifted across behind horses dropping to rear along fence. Began forward move turning for home but checked 400m, then held for clear run from 300m to 100m. Finished off nicely.
Jumped well, shared pace before easing 1L back in one-off position. Took closer order around turn, hit front 200m, battled on gamely till swamped final 50m.
No early pace, dropping to rear but kept away from fence. Inconvenienced soon after straightening, taken to centre track and finished off nicely.
Began awkwardly but recovered and pressed forward along fence to take box seat 2L from leader. Closed in top of straight to look a chance but only one-paced final 200m.
Bumped start, rolled forward, settling ahead of midfield 5L from leader but away from fence. Bumped soon after straightening, switched out for run but only one-paced.
Outpaced and long last on settling. Trailed field to straight, still last passing 200m, ran past beaten horses final stages.
Pressed forward from an outside draw, racing 3-wide without cover 1.5L from leader. Kept wide around turn, boxed on fairly to 200m before tiring.
Ridden to hold forward position, settling 2L from leader in one-off position 1000m. Stayed in contention around turn but under pressure from 200m and faded.
Began OK, taken to fence, settling behind midfield. Closed in around turn, took inside run in straight, but found little under hard riding.
Pressed forward on jumping to lead on settling. Set steady pace to 200m when collared and faded.

Taken up early, before easing back at 1000m to sit midfield, 1 off the fence. Came wider on the turn and ran solidly early in the straight. Good turn of foot from 200m, leading by 100m and eased slightly late.
Eased forward to sit midfield, on the fence. Snuck up the rail in the straight, kicking from 200m. Didn't have the same turn of foot as winner, but went well clear of the rest.
Stuck wide early, before easing back to a midfield position, 1 off the fence. Widest on the turn, and looked to be fading at 300m. Kicked again, and showed great turn of foot late to nab 3rd.
Taken forward early, but had a 3-way battle for the lead up the back straight. Ran out of gas late, fading over the last 150m.
Taken up early, before finding a position forward of midfield, 1 off the fence. Came wider on the turn, and 1 paced early in the straight. Got on to the bit late and finished the last 200m solidly.
Pushed up early to be handily placed 4th/5th, on the fence. Ran solidly early in the straight, but faded from the 150m.
Cruised forward early to sit just behind midfield, 1 off the fence. Held up until the 300m, but only went to the line fairly after finding clear ground.
Taken forward early to settle 4th/5th, 1 off the fence. Came wider on the turn, and progressed well initially. Peaked at 250m, dropped back and not pushed to the line late

Pushed forward early to sit 1L behind the leader in 2nd and 1 off the fence. Battled on gamely early in the straight, before starting to fade from 250m. Came off heels 100m, and wasn't pushed to the line subsequently.
Dropped back from the wide draw to sit 2nd last, 1 off the fence. Plugged away in the straight, without making an impact.
Began awkwardly, dropped back and settled near the rear of the field, 1 off the fence. Ran on 1 paced in the straight, and not pushed out late.
Missed the kick, and dropped back towards the rear of the field, on the fence. Only plodded away in the straight, and was eased out a long way from home.
Pushed hard early to ensure a position in the first 3, but stuck 3 wide no cover. Had nothing left in the tank by the turn, and dropped out quickly from the 300m.
Slowly away, off heels and dropped back early to sit last. Beaten horse by the turn, and not pushed out in the straight.
Began well, positioned 2 wide in 5th, there to turn, ridden final 300M, showed very good response and scored easily.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide with cover, 4 lengths back in 9th, slightly improved on turn, finished off well in straight to get 2nd.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover, 5 lengths or so back at rear, improved on turn, finished off strongly in straight to be nearest on line. (See racing incidents.)
Jumped well from the widest draw, positioned outside leader, same position on turn, took the lead early in straight, headed near 200M, stayed on for 4th.
Moderately away from gate 13, raced 3 wide with cover in 6th, bumped turning in, no clear running in straight, raced tight and checked in the closing stages.
Began awkwardly, raced 6 lengths or so back at rear, there to turn, kept to inside after straightening and made good progress to be nearest on line.
Away with them, taken back to race at tail, slightly improved on turn, taken widest in straight and made good progress.

Began fairly from gate 1, positioned a length or so back behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, no clear running early in straight, finished off evenly when clear thereafter. (Lame right front leg next day.)
Jumped well, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with no cover in 3rd, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly, checked in the closing stages.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, one-paced in straight. (Lost right hind plate near 300M.)
Slightly slow out, raced in midfield, difficult to settle throughout, saved ground on turn, no daylight early in straight but showed no progress when clear thereafter.
Jumped well from a wide draw, took the lead easily, headed after turning in, weakened gradually thereafter, eased final 150M.
Steadied start, raced 4 lengths or so back on rail at rear, checked heels near 1000m, similar position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide at rear, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight.

Fast into stride, positioned a length behind the leader, easy run on turn, finished off strongly in straight to score.
Jumped with them, raced 3 lengths back on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, make good progress in straight to get 2nd.
Began well, sent forward to the lead, easy lead on turn, headed near 200M, stayed on for 3rd.
Began very awkwardly and lost ground, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths back, similar position on turn, taken widest in straight and finished off well to make frame without threatening the first few.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Began awkwardly, positioned 4 lengths or so back on rail, same position on turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off one-paced.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide in 4th, similar position on turn, failed to close off in straight. (Blood in trachea.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 5 lengths or so back at rear, similar position on turn, finished off one-paced.
Slightly slow out, unable to slot in, raced wide with no cover in midfield, peaked turning in, weakened gradually in straight when hard run took effect. (See racing incidents.)
Moderately away from a wide draw, showed no early speed, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight, finished tailed out.
Raced at tail throughout, never competitive.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, favoured by the slow tempo, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Eased back, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 300M for 2nd.
Hard ridden early but not muster, steadily improved into the lead from 1600M, favoured by the slow tempo, hung on until 150M overhauled, ran on for 3rd.
Pressed forward as usual, sat 2 wide, enjoyed the slow sectionals, just held ground in final stages.
Eased to rear, 2 wide, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Behind midfield along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Pushed early, took rail in midfield, not suited by the slow pace, ran on fairly in straight.
Pushed forward, box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, emptied 200M.
Eased back, trapped 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
At back, never a factor.
Midfield, trapped 3 wide throughout, moved forward 1000M but failed to cross, dropped off 500M.
Never competitive, tailed out.
Pushed forward to obtain the box seat, ran on strongly to score by a neck when clear 250M.
Eased back, 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, disappointed for a run 250M, finished off strongly for 2nd, missed by a neck.
Prominent, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on steadily for 3rd.
Raced midfield, 4.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, finished off one pace for a distance 4th.
Pushed forward to take the fence and led by 1L, kept on until weakened final 150M.
Raced midfield, 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, one paced home without threatening.
Settled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, ran home fairly.
At back, 8Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, made minor ground in straight.
Raced midfield, 3.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, never looked likely.
At rear, 10Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, made minor ground in straight.
Prominent, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, weakened soon after straightening.
Rolled forward to park outside the leader, found nothing when being asked soon after straightening, weakened badly thereafter.
Quick to stride & bustled wide to 1 off no cover 2nd, sat 0.75L off lead until applied pressure 550m, bustled 450m & soon driven, grinding run to lead 200m, all out to hold on.
Started ok, camped rail fore of midfield, niggled 550m, shifted 1 off on turn & driven into stretch, switched into clear 280m, wound into full stride for late inroads, just failed.
Broke well, eased to sit rail back of midfield, nudged along 500m, hard-ridden home turn & shifted out, late inroads to nick 3rd late.
Tardy break & rousted initially, raced rail near rear, 2nd last when bustled & reminders 650m, under pump 450m, progress & switched out 250m, rattled home, just missed frame.
Prominent at break, parked 1 off 1 back, niggled 550m, clear 3rd & driven 300m, boxed on evenly, beaten when crowded close home.
Smart start, slotted fore of midfield 1 off with cover, under pump 500m, hard-ridden 400m, stayed on evenly.
Early speed & soon led, to rail 1st turn, pressed from 550m, narrow lead & shaken up turning in, all out & headed 200m, tapered.
Taken behind from wide & sat back of midfield 1 off with cover, nudged for progress 650m, driven 530m, shifted wide 400m, plugged on one pace.
Dropped in from wide to sit rail 2nd last, to tail 780m, progress & driven into stretch, plugged on without threat.
Taken back from wide to tail, soon shifted 1 off, bustled up 3 deep no cover 800m to back of midfield, unable to go on & last on straightening, one-paced past beaten rivals.
Slow start, settled 1 off with cover near rear, niggled a touch 600m, ridden 400m, tame run home.
Smart start, sat 1 back on rail, niggled 550m, under pump in 4th turning in, soon folded & faded.
Jumped on terms, eased, settled just beyond midfield on rail, keen at times, travelling strongly into straight, checked slightly 300m, powerful sprint when balanced up, prevailed final strides.
On back foot at start, ridden through to take forward spot, settled 3rd 1 off, clicked up 400m, sprinted powerfully, hit lead 120m, collared 20m.
Jumped on terms, let speed go, settled midfield of main bunch on rail, bullocked into clear 350m, dashed solidly but no match.
Slow to begin, mustered quickly, settled 4th on inside, railed through, clicked up 320m, green in stretch, boxed on.
First to break, ridden to maintain lead, 2L lead 950m, extended to 4L lead 800m, 5L lead 600m, ridden 350m, kicked strongly, claimed 120m, weakened late.
Away OK, eased, last early, improved around field to settle beyond midfield 3 deep no cover, ridden to improve 500m, searching for runs 200m, stayed on.
Jumped well, eased to settle just beyond midfield, at first 3 deep, then 1 off, slightly keen, under a drive 450m, widest into straight, drifted out further under pressure, even finish.
Broke evenly, ridden to gain a forward spot, overracing, settled midfield of main bunch 1 off, ridden along 420m, short burst 250m, then one-paced soon after.
Moderate jump, eased, ridden along 340m, stayed on moderately.
Slightly patchy break, vigorously ridden to press forward, settled clear 5L 2nd 600m, asked to improve 400m, effort short-lived, swamped.
Fast break, eased towards rear settled beyond midfield on rail, clicked up 350m, OK sprint, died on run 50m and weakened.
Slow start, clear last, ridden to improve and did so momentarily but back last again 970m, niggled 750m, further behind 550m despite riding, dropped out.
Sent forward to lead by 1/2L in a 2 wide position, kicked clear passing 200M and ran on very well to score by 3/4L.
Rolled forward and settled into box-seat, sat 3-1/4L behind the lead, kept on to the line to take 2nd.
Raced in midfield, 4-1/4L behind but 3 wide and without cover, despite that ran on gamely from 200M to finish 3rd.
Settled towards the rear, 6-3/4L behind along the rail, continued to make ground and finished off strongly for 4th.
Sent forward to take the race and raced inside the lead at about 1/2L behind, kept on one paced to the line.
Travelled in front of midfield, 3-1/2L behind 2 wide, finished off one paced without threatening.
Eased to race towards the rear, 8-1/4L behind 2 wide, continued to make ground steadily when going to the line.
Settled to race in behind midfield, 6-3/4L behind 2 wide, one paced and made no impression.
Taken back and travelled at the rear, 8-3/4L behind along the rail, made minor ground only.
Sent forward to race in one off-one back position, sat 2-1/2L off, weakened and dropped off at 200M.
Raced in slightly behind midfield, 5-3/4L behind along the rail, not competitive in the Straight.
Failed to muster and travelled in worse than midfield, 7-1/2L 3 wide and without cover from 600M, did not feature.
Pressed forward from outside draw to race outside leader on settling. Urged forward on straightening, hit front 150m, held off late challenge for narrow win.
Crowded out shortly after start and taken to fence, settling 4L from leader passing 900m. Had clear run soon after sraighteing and finished strongly to just miss.
Crowded out shortly after start, dropping to rear. Taken to rail and improved position approaching and negotiating home turn, ran on strongly in straight to grab minor placing.
First out, leading clearly to 1000m before slowing pace. Overtaken passing 150m but boxed on gamely before being swamped final 50m.
Jumped with field, ridden to hold forward position, settling in box seat 3L from leader 900m. Looked chance turning for home but only one-paced when popped the question.
Hampered shortly after start, dropping to rear between horses. Switched out approaching home turn to make run but only one-paced in straight.
Crowded out shortly after start, recovered and pressed forward to midfield but over-raced passing 700m and lost ground. Kept on fairly in straight.
Slow into stride, then shifted across behind horses, settling at rear along fence. Was momentarily unbalanced passing 700m, made progress early in straight before turning one-paced final 200m.
Hard ridden from widest draw to hold forward position, racing 3-wide without cover 1.5L from leader. Kept tabs to 200m when ran out of stamina and faded.
Broke well, pressed forward, settling 2L from leader in one-off position. Travelled keenly approaching turn, switched out in straight but spent force passing 250m and faded.
Began OK but no early speed, settling behind midfield but away from fence. Made some ground around turn but soon out of puff and plodded home.
Steadied soon after start and shifted across behind horses, settling at rear. Clear last entering straight and found nothing when asked.
Eased to near the rear from 12, made early move 700M looping the field on outer, chased leader from 450M and gradually wore down leader in the shadows of post.
Emerged as leader 1300M, set steady pace first half, pressed by rival 500M and quickened up to maintain the lead, kept going well only to be headed last stride.
Caught 3-wide early, moved up to 2nd 1200M, bustled along home turn to keep up with quickening leaders, kept up the chase well but never totally clear final 200M.
Began well from draw 1 tracking leaders along the rail, awkwardly placed 400M, ran on steadily to chase leaders, nearest finish.
With leaders early, tracked leaders 2-wide from 1200M, tried hard final 300M and was gradually getting close to leaders late stages.
Fractious in stalls, began awkwardly losing ground, towards the rear and got held up inside 400M, ran on well when clear 250M.
Held up 2-wide in midfield, 4Ls to make up 400M, couldn't muster the speed to go closer over final 300M.
Began awkwardly, eased back to the tail of the field , still last at 400M, made up some ground without threatening.
Settled down behind midfield, shuffled further back rounding home turn, 2nd last 400M, couldn't go on, never a factor.
Jumped on terms, sat behind midfield 5Ls off the pace on settling, didn't respond to urging from 350M, eased when no chance final stages.
Chased leaders from 11, caught 3-wide no cover after 1200M, under pressure 500M, gave ground early straight. (Jockey questioned.)
Began only fairly, settled down along the rail in midfield 4Ls back, driven turning in but soon weakened.
