Never far off, produced good late run inside final 200 metres to prevail by a narrow margin.
Jumped well, settled 3-wide in midfield, wider into straight, ran on quite well under pressure to miss narrowly.
Settled in rear of midfield and wide without cover, commenced move around field home bend, hit the front narrowly 200 metres out, unable to sustain effort close to home.
Always prominent on rails, baulked for a run early in straight, only produced moderate headway under pressure inside final 200 metres.
Settled towards the rear, baulked for a run early in straight, fought on steadily inside final 200 metres to narrowly miss the place-getters.
Settled in rear, switched out to the centre of the track to challenge after straightening, ran on.
Travelled in midfield, attempted in vain to switch out early in straight, obtained a run over 250 metres out, kept on steadily without quickening.
Driven to lead from a wide gate, led the field on rails before joined into straight, folded up quickly inside final 200 metres.
Jumped awkwardly, settled mainly in midfield on rails, saved ground turning for home, did not find much room in straight.
Raced prominent and wide without cover, kept on early in straight before fading inside final 200 metres.
Slowly away, settled well behind, kept on steadily without quickening.
Taken back from the widest gate, trailed the field to straight, remained wide turning in, one-paced down the centre of the straight.
Towards the rear throughout.
Began from a poor gate, chased outside leader, dropped out tamely inside final 200 metres.
Shared the lead easily at advantageous slow sectionals, drifted away 200M to score.
Pressed forward, suited by the slow sectionals, ran on well for 2nd.
Awkward away, dropped back, dashed well 250M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, lack turn of foot in final furlong.
Pushed early, in front of midfield, just held ground in final stages.
Pressed forward to share the lead at slow sectionals, out of fuel 300M.
At back, not suited by the slow tempo, ran on fairly.
At rear, harmed by the slow pace, ran on fairly.
Midfield, not suited by the slow pace, flattened 250M.
Eased to sit just off the leaders, soon emptied 350M.
Bumped start, at rear, not suited by the slow tempo, no progress.
Never improved at rear.
At back, never a factor.
Tailed out, never competitive.
Hard ridden forward to take the fence and led by 1L, kept on strongly to score by 1L.
At rear, 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, stormed home for a dead heat 2nd.
Prominent, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on well for a dead heat 2nd.
Pushed forward to occupy the box seat, kept on one pace to the line for 4th.
Pushed forward to occupy a prominent position with cover from a wide draw, one paced home without serious threats.
Hard ridden forward to park outside the leader, kept on only fairly and weakened over the last furlong.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on fairly.
Taken back as usual, 5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, ran home fairly.
Raced midfield, 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, made no impression in straight.
At rear throughout, never a factor.
At back throughout, never looked likely.
Settled midfield, however trapped very wide without cover throughout, weakened badly soon after straightening.
Smart start, parked 1 back 1 off, to fence 850m, shifted out 350m & driven between horses, quickened to lead 150m, drew clear, rolled home final strides.
Missed break & impeded, mustered from rear to race midfield on rail, edged out 550m, shaken up 400m, rattled home centre track to snag 2nd at line.
Broke ok, settled fore of midfield 1 off with cover, switched 4 wide turning in & driven 400m, quickened centre track to lead 230m, peaked & headed 150m, lost 2nd last strides.
Sluggish start, urged forward 3 wide to press lead 1 off no cover at 1000m, eased to 1L 2nd & niggled 500m, driven turning in but outkicked, boxed on evenly.
Slow to stride & soon bustled at tail, settled on rail last trio, progress on turn but snagged off heels 700m, driven 420m, ran on for minor gains.
Speed to lead wide, crossed to rail 1200m, keen in front, 1L up & ridden 430m, all out & headed 230m, faded out.
Hampered straight, overraced 1200m, niggled 650m, shifted out & driven into home turn, kept on for moderate progress.
Taken back at start, checked off heels 1300m, settled last trio 1 off, last & driven into stretch, outpaced, stayed on to pass beaten rivals late.
Taken back at break & eventually parked last trio 3 wide with cover, shifted very wide on turn & widest in run home, driven 400m, kept on for modest inroads until bottomed out 100m.
Broke ok, snagged to back of midfield 3 wide with cover, overraced & restrained near rear from 800m, crowded on turn, fanned wide & driven 420m, plodded tepidly.
Broke ok, raced 4th 3 wide no cover & overraced, slotted 1 off 1 back 850m, shifted out & driven final turn, bumped 370m & continued to be buffeted in run, tapered out.
Awkward start, mustered to sit rail froe of midfield, shifted 420m, rolled out & bumped rival 370m, continued to buffet in close quarters to 150m through fading stretch run.
Broke well widest, taken back to midfield & unable to slot, trapped wide no cover throughout, found nil in run home.
Reared right at break & hampered rivals, raced midfield & 3 wide no cover most of trip, 5 wide & driven into stretch, found nil & weakened.
Jumped away clean, eased to settle beyond midfield 1 off, raced strongly throughout, ridden along 550m, held up 400m, pushed out soon after, unleashed powerful sprint, just got there.

Slow to jump, outpaced early, ridden 1600m to press forward, settled 2nd 3 deep, then 1 off 1100m, moved up to pressure leader 650m, asked 420m, ding-dong battle until 75m when finally asserted, just grabbed on wire.
Broke fast, natural speed to lead, even fractions, clicked up 450m, first headed 300m but in for the fight, succumbed 75m, battled on doggedly.
Jumped on terms, pressed to go forward, settled 4th 1 off, overraced slightly, ridden 420m, boxed on.
Up in air at start, clearly missed break, settled last on rail, slightly keen, pushed off rail 1450m, ridden 440m, switched inside, finishing strongly when blocked 50m, not ridden out.
Began well, eased in search of a spot, settled midfield 3 deep no cover, asked to improve 550m, stuck on evenly.
Rank out of the gates, eased to rear, settled near tail 3 deep, clicked up 500m, widest into straight, finished off evenly.
OK start, raced fiercely early, settled just fore of midfield 1 off, still green throughout, pushed 420m, bumping duel 350m, showed inexperience again late, even effort.
Slightly slow to jump, settled just fore of midfield on rail, keen at times, tried to push out 350m, one-paced when clear.
Awkward break, restrained to near rear, bustled to pick up soon after, settled beyond midfield 1 off, niggled 650m, pulled centre track in straight, picked up very late, still green.
First to break, ridden to settle forward, box-seat spot 3rd on rail, under pressure 600m, quickly beaten.
Broke strongly, settled just beyond midfield on rail, niggled 600m, railed up, gave very little.
Slightly awkward to begin, restrained to settle near rear on rail, under pressure 530m, couldn't pick up.
In midfield, 4-1/4L behind 3 wide with cover, passed at 150M but fought back to score in a tight finish.
Travelled in midfield, 4-1/4L behind 2 wide, ran on strongly for a tight finish, only beaten in the final strides.
Sent forward and raced 1-1/4L off and outside the leader, in touch until 150M, nonetheless kept on going to the line.
Raced in behind midfield, 4-3/4L behind along the rail, ran on gamely to take 4th.
In behind midfield, 5-1/2L behind 2 wide, continued to make steady ground, then hit the line strongly from 100M.
Slightly crowded at start, raced in worse than midfield, 5-3/4L behind 3 wide with cover, made ground steadily.
Sent forward and settled into box-seat, sat 1-1/4L off, dropped off slightly at 250M, one paced thereafter.
Taken back and raced towards the rear, 6-3/4L behind 2 wide, improved steadily and hit the line well.
Sat just front of midfield, 3L off along the rail, kept on one paced going to the line.
Rolled forward and raced in front of midfield, sat 2-3/4L off 2 wide, ran on okay after slight dash at 200M.
Pushed forward to take the rail and led by 1-1/4L, weakened and headed passing 200M.
Pushed forward and settled front of midfield, 2-1/2L off but 3 wide without cover, dropped off gradually after straightening.
Crowded start, raced towards the rear, 6-1/4L behind along the rail, did not feature in the Straight.
Eased and raced at the rear throughout, never a factor.
Broke well but eased to behind midfield in one-of position. Not happy with pace and took off passing 1100m to lead 950m, crossing to fence 700m. Kept finding in straight to hold off late challenge.

Jumped with field, ridden to hold rail, sliding into box seat 2L from leader passing 1500m. Shuffled back to 5th rounding turn, blocked for run early in straight, got split 250m and finished off strongly.

Quickly into stride, pressed forward from widest draw, settling outside leader passing 1500m. Shuffled back to 5th when rivals moved forward, picked up momentum on straightening but only one-paced final 200m.
Hard ridden from wide draw to lead on settling, then slowed pace to a crawl. Overtaken passing 950m but kept battling until flattened close home.
Away nicely, settling one-back, one-off 1500m. Got shuffled back when several rivals moved forward before turn, shaken up entering straight but only one-paced.
Jumped OK, ridden to hold midfield position before crossing to fence 1600m. Lost position after 1000m when rivals moved forward, left fence 600m to make run but only one-paced.
Crowded out start, dropping to rear between horses then checked 1500m. Unhappy with slow pace and over-raced until 1000m when tempo increased. Lay in top straight but boxed on one-paced.
Ridden early to obtain a forward position but did not respond and shuffled back to rear. Clear last entering home turn, found nothing when asked in straight.
Began OK but not asked for an effort, dropping to rear in a 3-wide position. Rolled forward passing 1100m to sit 2L behind leader turning for home. Spent force on sraightening and plodded home.
Taken back to last from 9, waited with till 500M, brought widest off the bend and sprinted to the lead near 100M, won impressively running out the fastest 400M of the day.
Hugged the rail from draw 1 and always close up, raced up to the lead 300M, kept on solidly just found winner too strong in the closing stages. Gap to 3rd.
Began only fairly, eased back to near the rear for cover, 3-wide from 800M, ran on well to claim 3rd without troubling first 2. (Riding tactics questioned.)
Jumped on terms to be 2Ls behind leader in the slowly run first half, keenly 1000M, didn't have the clearest of runs until 150M, stayed on well final stages to just miss 3rd.
From draw 10 caught 3-wide no cover chasing the pace, kept on evenly in straight not matching the finishing pace of first 2, lost 3rd late.
Sat outside leader, had his chance and kept up the chase until weakening inside 100M.
Held up 2-wide behind midfield, 4Ls to make up 400M, plugged to the line without threatening. (Jockey : not suited by the slow tempo in middle stages)
Crossed to the lead 1100M, led slowly before quickening up 600M, headed 300M out, no extra inside 100M and swamped by rivals.

Eased back from 11, raced keenly early stages due to slow pace then improved to a midfield spot along the 3-path, awkwardly placed on the run home and had to steady off the heels of a rival a few times, unable to get closer.
Settled down midfield along the rail, 3Ls to make up 400M, couldn't muster the speed to challenge.
Not hurried early stages, dropped back to near the rear 5Ls behind leader, saved ground on inside but failed to run on passing 400M, detached from field mid-straight. (Mucus.)

Began awkwardly, ridden to go forward, settling a half length behind leader before turn. Joint leader passing 450m, kicked ahead on straightening, under pressure final 100m but had enough in hand to hold off challenger.
Began fairly, not pushed, settling behind midfield along rail. Stayed on rail around turn, blocked for run top of straight, got clear passage 200m out and finished strongly to miss narrowly.
Hard ridden from an outside draw to lead on settling before slowing pace. Joined up from 450m but kept battling in straight to hold on to minor placing.
Steadied soon after jump and shifted across behind horses, settling towards rear in one-off position. Swung wide into straight and ran on steadily down centre field to make the frame.
Jumped well but bumped, then unable match pace, dropping to midfield in one-out position. Three-wide into straight before running on steadily.
Began OK, taken to fence, settling 3L from leader. Took inside run entering straight but got squeezed out passing 200m, nearly dislodging jockey. Boxed on.
Hard ridden from an outside draw to hold forward position, racing 3-wide without cover 3L from leader. Boxed on well early in straight before running out of puff 150m and fading.
Began fairly, ridden but didn't respond, dropping to last on settling. Improved along rails turning for home but only one-paced in straight under hard riding.
Bumped start, hard ridden to go forward, cutting to rail 1100m 2.5L from leader. Stayed in contention to straight when under pressure, giving ground gradually.
Bumped start, ridden to share early pace before easing 3L back 1000m. Took closer order turning for home, kept on fairly to 200m before tiring.
Slow into stride, ridden to make up ground, settling one-off in last pair. Put under pressure turning for home but found nothing under hard riding.
Jumped OK, steadied, then shifted in, settling towards rear in one-off position. Stated to give ground from 600m, last into straight, found nothing.

Steadied early to get cover, worse than midfield and off the fence. Towards the rear of the field on the turn. Had a clear run in the straight, and ran solidly early. Good turn off foot last 150m, and comfortable late.

Taken forward to be a clear 2nd, 1L off the leader. Ran solidly in the straight, and nosed in front at 200m. Couldn't match winner as he went past at 100m, accepting 2nd and only hands and heels late.
Cruised forward early, settling midfield, 1 off the fence. Wide no cover from the 700m. Looked to have run out of gas at the 200m, but gained a 2nd wind late to run solidly and just take 3rd.
Taken up early from the inside draw to be well placed in 3rd. Awkward on heels 800m. No run early in the straight and only got clear at 200m. Showed good speed late, and only just missed 3rd late.
Taken forward early to be the clear leader. Still in front at the 200m, but ran out of gas, and went to the line 1 paced thereafter.
Fairly away, settling worse than midfield, 3 wide with cover. Wider on the turn, but only went to the line fairly and never threatened. Jockey questioned.
Began awkwardly, lost ground and settled towards the rear of the field. Came off heels at 900m. Stayed on fairly in the straight, picking up a couple of slower ones, but never a threat.
Began awkwardly, but recovered to settle handily 4th, 1 off the fence and keen. Didn't respond to urging in the straight and was flat in the run to the line.
Dropped back early from the wide draw to sit at the rear of the field. Off heels 700m when racing greenly. Last on the turn and only ran fairly to the line.
Cruised forward early, settling midfield on the fence. Never responded to urging in the straight, and went to the line tamely.
Easily taken forward early to be handily placed 5th. Came off heels at 650m, and lost ground. On heels until the top of the straight, but never kicked and dawdled to the line late.
Dropped back early from the wide draw to sit last early. Taken wide when attempting to go forward at 700m. Gave nothing in the straight, and not pushed to the line late.

Worked his way to the front from the widest gate, obtained rails run over 1200 metres out, maintained 1L lead to straight, headed when no extra 100 metres out.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, settled in rear of midfield on rails, obtained run to challenge about 250 metres out, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Soon taken back to the rear on rails, saved ground turning in, finished off race well under pressure.
Settled in forward of midfield on rails, commenced move approaching home straight holding place chance early on but failed to quicken to threaten.
Settled well behind from a wide gate, switched out for a run 300 metres out, made modest progress down the centre of the straight.
Niggled along to hold prominent position early, 3-wide without cover onto home bend before going forward near the 1000 metres to be 1L 2nd off the rails, found no extra after straightening.
Crowded at start settling at the back, commenced move turning into straight, fought on steadily under pressure.
Close up early, taken back to 2L 4th far side, weakened under pressure in straight.
Settled wide in midfield after beginning from a wide gate, no cover down back straight, found nothing under pressure in the final stretch.
Settled in rear of midfield, slightly worse far side, came wide rounding home bend and widest into straight, never a danger.
Travelled in forward of midfield, dropped away quickly on home bend.
Pushed forward, took rail and led at good pace, made all.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, pace good, closed off strongly 300M for 2nd.
Took rail behind midfield, on heels 600M, pace good, made steady ground 300M for 3rd,
Pushed to obtain box seat, pace good, just held ground in straight.
Took rail at back, on heels early, pace good, progressed steadily 250M.
Hard ridden forward, sat outside the leader, pace good, flattened 150M.
Hard ridden early, took rail in midfield, pace good, emptied 200M.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, 2-3 wide, pace good, made ground 200M.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, pace good, made minor ground 200M.
Behind midfield, 2 wide, checked 600M, pace good, lack turn of foot.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, 2-3 wide, pace good, ran on fairly.
Eased back, checked early, trapped 3 wide throughout, no progress.
Pushed forward to occupy the box seat, ran on well to score by 1/2L.
At rear, 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, stormed home for 2nd, missed by 1/2L.
Eased to settle worse than midfield about 4Ls behind the leader with cover, improved around the field from 600M, kept on nicely to get 3rd. (Questioned rider for riding)
Raced midfield, 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, swung wide turning in, ran on steadily for 4th.
Pushed forward to take the fence and share the lead, kept on until headed final 150M.
Hard ridden forward to cross from a wide gate and park outside the leader, kept on until weakened final 100M.
Slow to muster despite hard ridden along, 4Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, made minor ground in straight.
Raced midfield, however trapped wide throughout, never a factor.
Eased back to rear from a wide gate, 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on fairly.
Always at rear, never ran on.
Raced midfield, 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, never looked likely.
Sent forward to settle 1L behind the leader with cover, dropped off soon after straightening.
Broke ok, bustled to lead on rail 1100m, eased & headed 1000m, stalked 1 back, ridden 500m, rousted to close at 300m, quickened to lead 80m, kept on under hard drive.
Good break widest, bustled to lead 1000m, 2L clear & to rail 850m, 1.5 L up & kicked on 320m, emptied & headed 80m, tapered.
Tardy start & bustled on rail to park midfield, niggled 400m, 4th & driven 350m, switched out 250m, grinding effort to close, just missed 2nd.
Sharp break, sat midfield 3 wide with cover, shifted out & driven 400m, very wide into stretch, stayed on for minor headway.
Broke ok, taken back to park behind midfield 1 off with cover, overraced 950m, soon settled, swung out home turn & driven centre track, picked up final 300m for limited headway.
Fast start & disputed lead, restrained to 2nd 1 off no cover, ridden 420m, 3rd under pressure turning in, drifted out &tapered to wire.
Broke well but outpaced & snagged to near rear 3 wide with cover, driven widest into stretch, plugged on moderately.
Dropped in at break & crossed to rail, bustled a touch to sit back of midfield, niggled 400m, driven turning in, boxed on one pace.
Snagged back at start & soon bustled along at tail, 2L detached & under pump 400m, outpaced on turn, ran on for modest late inroads.
Broke well, snagged back from wide to race 2nd last on rail, shaken up turning in, plodded on one pace.
Good break, raced midfield 1 off with cover, driven turning in, found nil & faded.
Led at break, soon headed & shuffled back to midfield 4 wide no cover, pushed on to handy 4th 3 wide no cover, bustled on turn, under pump 400m, emptied early in stretch & eased.
Dropped in to race back of midfield on inner, tapped for toe 750m & niggled 2nd last, smooth advance on turn, switched out 400m, driven wide & quickened in stretch, stormed to lead 100m, drew clear.
Settled rail midfield, niggled 760m, shifted out for progress 500m, steadied 400m, hard-ridden 300m, ran on centre track to take 2nd close home.
Broke ok & sat midfield 1 off with cover, bustled forward 700m, shifted out final turn & driven, quickened to lead 200m, all out & headed 100m, weakened to line.
Tardy start, bustled forward to race handy 2nd 1 off no cover, pushed on to lead 820m, soon clear, 2L up turning in & driven, emptied & headed 200m, faded.
Dropped in at break to race 2nd last, niggled 950m, bustled forward a spot 750m wide with cover, hard-ridden 400m, plugged on one pace.
Taken back to 3rd last 1 off with cover, shifted out 900m & bustled forward to handy 4 deep no cover at 750m, hard-ridden 3 wide 650m, plugged on tepidly.
Taken behind at start to race at tail, ridden along 750m, shifted out on turn, wide in run & stayed on for minor inroads.
Started prominently, raced 1 off 1 back, bustled forward 800m to vie for 2nd 1 off no cover, scrubbed to hold position & all out turning in, emptied 300m & faded.
Broke well, sat 1 back on rail niggled 550m, hard-ridden 450m, shifted out in run, found no extra & eased final 100m.
Smart start & led, headed 820m & bustled, driven 700m, all out to hold 3rd position on turn, emptied upon straightening, eased final 100m.
Pushed forward from wide gate, soon trapped 4 wide no cover & snagged 1650m to behind midfield 1 off with cover, driven 3 wide for progress 850m, soon stalled & weakened out.
Broke ok, initially overraced midfield 3 wide no cover, niggled forward to vie for 3rd 850m, under pump & in retreat 680m, faded quickly, tailed off.
Sent forward and settled in one-off one-back position, kept going and held on in a tight battle to score.
Jumped away well, shared lead in 2 wide position, ran on but couldn't pass the winner and had to settle for 2nd.
Awkward start, in just behind midfield, 3-1/2L behind along the fence, continued to make ground, ran on fairly well.
Slow to jump, raced in behind midfield, 4-1/4L behind 2 wide, made steady ground ran on nicely, just missed 3rd.
Settled in midfield, 2-1/2L off along the rail, kept on one paced going to the line.
Eased back and raced at the rear, 5-1/4L behind along the rail, nice dash at 200M, ran on ok.
Travelled in behind midfield, 3-1/2L behind 3 wide with cover, continued to make ground, kept on well.
Raced in midfield, 2-1/4L behind but 3 wide without cover, kept on going to the line one paced.
Sent forward, crossed to take the rail and shared lead at 800M, emptied passing 150M.
Eased back and raced at the rear, 5L behind 2 wide, never looked to threaten.
Rolled forward and took box-seat, sat 1-1/4L off, dropped off gradually passing 200M.
Travelled in midfield, 2-3/4L behind 2 wide, failed to feature in the Straight.

Broke well, crossed quickly to fence to lead field before giving way to rival and taking box seat 1200m. Urged up alongside leader at turn, kicked ahead passing 300m, kept finding to deny late challenge.
Began well but eased off pace, settling in midfield in one-off position. Urged forward around home turn, took inside run in straight, motored home final 200m.
Pressed forward from an outside draw, racing wide around first turn before taking over lead 1200m and crossing to fence. Collared passing 300m but battled on strongly until final few strides.
No early pace, dropping to rear along fence. Stayed on fence around turn, finished strongly final 300m to just miss a placing.
Began awkwardly, recovered and taken to fence, settling midfield. Improved position round turn, switched out in straight and finished off nicely.

Began well, ridden to hold rail, sliding into box seat at first turn. Got shuffled back passing 1200m, settling 3L from leader. Closed in around final turn, swung wide into straight, boxed on gamely while laying in under pressure.
Began awkwardly but quickly into stride, pressing forward between horses before settling 3L from leader in one-off position. Swung wide into straight but only one-paced under hard riding.
Jumped well, pressed forward from outside draw before getting cover behind midfield turning into back stretch. Shaken up passing 500m, took inside run in straight but only one-paced.
No early pace, dropping to rear but kept away from fence. Lost contact when main rivals on straightening and never competitive.
No early pace and soon at rear along fence. Shaken up approaching final turn but no response and struggled home.

Ridden to go forward covering extra ground before settling 3-wide without cover 2L from leader back stretch. Swung very wide into straight, continued to layout and eased final stages. Racing manners unacceptable.
Bounded in the air when gates open and slow to begin. Trailed field thereafter and finished tailed out.
Driven to take the lead soon after the start, took them along steadily, kicked away well by 2L passing 300M, led all the way.
Tracked leaders in 4th, 2Ls behind leader at 400M, moved up to 2nd 200M, tried hard to reel in winner but ran out of ground.
Jumped on terms and settled ahead of midfield 4Ls back, into clear 250M, stayed on to go 3rd nearing 50M but well held by first 2.
Began well tracking leader along the 2-path, had every hope inside 300M, peaked on his run 150M and fading towards the line.
Urged along early to take up a midfield spot along the 2-path, inclined to lay out during race, 4Ls off at 400M and proved difficult to ride in straight, kept on steadily without troubling first 3.
Not hurried on jumping from wide barrier, settled down behind midfield 5Ls off, brought widest 350M, stayed on without threat.
Failed to muster speed despite ridden along, shuffled back to a position behind midfield 6-7Ls off the pace, made limited progress up the rail final 300M, never likely.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, ended up behind midfield in 8th, 6Ls to make up 400M, made no real progress over final 300M.
Began fast to be 3rd 3Ls behind leader, struggled to hold ground in the run home, weakened mid-straight.
Taken back to near the rear from a wide draw, raced keenly down the back straight, had plenty to do 400M, not quickened.
Dropped back to a rearward spot 8Ls behind leader, couldn't pick up ground entering straight, no impression.
Taken back from widest barrier, always at rear, eased off when well beaten 200M. (Irregular Heart Rhythm / Bled / Lame next day.)

Never far off, improved to 2nd outside heels of leader halfway down back straight, hit the front under pressure over 200 metres out, just held on to the line.

Moderate start, settled at rear, took closer order 4w 1000 metres out, made another move from rounding home bend to join the leaders, issued serious challenge closing stages but just failed to peg back the winner while hanging in.
Driven from a wide gate to take up running on stables bend, led until headed passing the 300 metres when one-paced.
Waited with well behind, widest runner entering straight, finished off race well down the centre of the straight.
Settled in rear of midfield, came under pressure approaching home straight, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Driven to midfield, shuffled back to last few far side, came under pressure again rounding home bend, finished off race well near the centre of the straight.
Ridden positively from a wide gate, settled just off the pace on rails far side, in similar one back position when became 5th on top of home bend, kept on same pace under pressure in the run home.
Ridden early, settled in midfield, came under pressure rounding home bend, one-paced in straight.
Close up early, racing keenly on rails when hampered and shuffled back to midfield far side, faded from a similar position into straight.
Moderate start, remained in last few on rails, saved ground turning in, kept on before fading inside final 200 metres.
Began fairly, wide in midfield early stages, progressed to dispute 2nd 1000 metres out before taken back to a lesser position onto home bend, dropped away quickly into straight.
Settled in midfield on rails, hampered and shuffled back towards the rear coming onto home bend, no further impression.
Settled wide towards the rear, made swift progress to midfield early in back straight, took closer order to join the leaders coming onto home bend, folded up quickly in straight.
Raced wide in last few, never seen with a chance. (Bled)
Pushed forward early, however trapped wide, eased to sit in midfield 1400M, 2 wide, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Settled in midfield on the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 400M for 2nd.
Pushed to take rail and led at fast sectionals, hung on well until 150M overhauled, hold on for 3rd.
Box seat, not suited by the fast sectionals, ran on well until 200M flattened.
Behind midfield, 2 wide, suited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M.
Hard ridden early but not muster, at rear, on the rails, benefited by the fast tempo, made ground 200M.
Midfield, 2-3 wide, suited by the fast pace, no turn of foot.
Hard ridden early but not muster, at back along the rails, benefited by the fast tempo, no progress.
Pushed early, worst than midfield along the fence, favoured by the fast pace, never improved.
Pushed forward, 2 wide, harmed by the fast tempo, emptied 400M.
Settled in prominent spot along the fence, not suited by the fast pace, out of fuel 250M.
Never better than midfield.
Never competitive, tailed out.

Placing: UR
Comment: On jumping stumbled badly and rider being dislodged.
Ridden forward to take the fence and share the leader, kept on strongly to score by 1-1/4Ls.
Prominent, travelled 1.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on gradually for 2nd.
Rolled forward to obtain the box seat, ran on gradually for 3rd.
Eased back from a wide draw, 4Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, ran on steadily for 4th.
Eased to settle worse than midfield about 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran home nicely when clear 250M.
Raced midfield, 3.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, one paced home without threatening.
Jumped slowly, 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, swung widest turning in, made minor ground in straight.
Sent forward to park outside the leader, stayed on until weakened final 250M.
Prominent, however, trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, kept on fairly and weakened final 250M.
At rear throughout, never a factor.
Failed to muster despite ridden along early, 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, found nothing when asked.

Smart break but outpaced & bustled, settled rail fore of midfield, shifted 3 wide with cover 850m, steadied inside to 1 off at 600m & advanced, wide on turn & driven, gradual progress to lead 110m, drew away.
Sharp break, bustled initially, settled 1 back on fence, shifted 3 wide home turn & ridden, quickened to lead 200m but peaked, headed 110m, no extra.
Good break & bustled to 1st turn, rolled 3 wide to park 2nd outside leader without cover at 1050m, shared lead turning in & shaken up to narrow lead, all out & headed 200m, boxed on.
Sharp start, led 1350m, crossed to rail 1150m, challenged & shared lead final turn, driven 420m, soon headed but kept on dourly.
Taken behind at start to race rail back of midfield, steadied 700m, shaken up 430m & switched out, driven centre track for gradual gains.
Rousted initially, settled midfield on rail, niggled 900m, under pump 650m & minor headway, hard-ridden into stretch, stayed on dourly.
Outpaced & scrubbed to 1st turn, raced 2nd last until 3 wide advance 950m to travel midfield on turn, driven 400m, switched off heels 200m, stayed on soundly to wire.
Taken behind from widest gate to race at tail, progress on home turn & driven, stayed on moderately.
Fast start & led until snagged 1st turn to sit 1 off 1 back, driven 650m, out-kicked top of stretch & tapered to line.
Dropped in from wide gate to 3rd last 1 off, 2nd last from 920m, shifted 3 deep with cover 800m & niggled, driven final turn, plodded same speed.
Rousted from gate & slotted midfield 1 off with cover, niggled along, in retreat from 600m, hard-ridden into straight, plodded home weakly.
Smart break wide, outpaced to 1st turn & dropped to eventually slot behind midfield 1 off with cover, niggled 650m & shuffled back, 3rd last turning in, found nil & weakened.
Handy at break & wide no cover, taken back to midfield & slotted 3 wide with cover 1000m, forced 4 deep no cover 850m, in retreat on turn & found nil thereafter.
Broke ok, bustled along fore of midfield 3 wide no cover & advanced backstretch to share 3rd at 850m, under pressure & in retreat 650m, rear rank & emptied turning in, eased.
Slightly awkward break, sped through to settle 4th 3 off, on 1 rein and raw 600m, centre track soon after, clicked up 400m, hit lead 220m, found plenty despite greenness.
Broke strongly, natural speed to settle 2nd centre track, ridden 450m, found line powerfully but no match.
Bounced well, eased out of speed battle, settled midfield 1 off, ridden 700m, to grandstand rail shortly afterwards, under a drive 600m, made ground steadily, boxed on.
Jumped on terms, unable to match early speed, settled well back 1 off, clicked up when travelling strongly 550m, checked slightly 470m, limited space 350m, finished strongly when in clear room.
Bounced out to lead comfortably on grandstand rail, travelled very strongly, ridden 450m, fought on until claimed 220m, faded late.
Jumped evenly, settled beyond midfield on grandstand rail, ridden 580m, picked up late.
Slightly awkward start, racing fiercely, settled just fore of midfield 2 off, pushed along 600m, switched over heels 400m, ran about under pressure, faded.
Slightly slow to begin, settled beyond midfield centre track no cover in awkward spot, ridden 550m, struggled to pick up, found line very late.
Jumped awkwardly, squeezed shortly afterwards, eased to near rear, ridden 450m and pulled centre track, checked 200m, outpaced.
Dipped shortly after start, settled midfield 3 off, nudged 550m, ridden 400m, fought on, checked 220m, weakened thereafter.
Moderate break, raced up to sit handy 1 off, under pressure 450m, almost joint lead 400m, eased out.
Restrained from gates, settled beyond midfield 4 off, overraced, under a ride 400m, weakened.
Hopped in air at start, restrained to tail, last centre track 700m, driven along 400m, never in it.
Bumped shortly after start, quickly outsped, settled beyond midfield 2 off, hampered 620m, giving ground 500m, no response under a drive, eased down.
Rolled forward and took box-seat, sat 1-3/4L off, kicked clear near 150M to score comfortably by 2L.
Raced in midfield, 3-3/4L behind 3 wide with cover, ran on well to finish 2nd.
Slotted into midfield, 3-3/4L behind along the rail, held up until 250M, closed off well once cleared.
Travelled in front of midfield, 2-1/4L off 3 wide and without cover, still ran on okay to take 4th.
Slow to jump then raced at the rear, 7L behind along the rail, closed off nicely when shifted out passing 300M.
Pushed forward to take the rail and led by 1L, headed passing 200M but kept on going to the line.
Travelled in behind midfield, 5-1/2L behind 3 wide with cover, closed off once paced in the Straight.
Raced in just behind midfield, 4-1/2L behind 2 wide, kept on one paced going to the line.
Slow start and settled in behind midfield, 5-1/4L behind along the rail, did not show turn of foot in the Straight.
Travelled towards the rear, 6-1/2L behind 2 wide, one paced but kept on going to the line.
Sent forward and raced outside the lead, sat 1L off, kept on until 300M and then dropped off.
Slotted into midfield, 3-3/4L behind but wide and without cover, niggled to keep up from 700M, not competitive.
Settled in front of midfield, 3-1/4L off 2 wide, found nothing when asked in the Straight.
At the rear throughout, never a factor.

Broke OK, rolled forward in one-off position, settling 3L from leader. Tightened passing 1100m and lost position. Swung wide into straight, got clear run 400m, finished off strongly hitting the front 50m and pulling clear.

Jumped fairly, ridden to obtain forward position but didn't muster, dropping to behind midfield in one-off position. Lost ground passing 1050m, held for run early in straight, got clear 200 and finished off strongly.
Pressed forward from an outside draw to lead on settling, setting ready pace. Put under pressure soon after straightening but kept finding until flattened 50m.
Broke well, shared early pace before easing 2L back in one-off position. Edged closer turning for home to look a chance 300m. Kept battling to line without closing gap.

Crowded out at start, dropping to rear. Taken to rail 1400m and improved to midfield approaching turn. Blocked for run early in straight, got clear but blocked again 200m, switched in and ran on strongly but tightened final 50m.
No early pace, dropping to rear. Clear last from 1200m. Taken wide entering straight and ran on steadily.
Jumped OK, ridden along from an outside draw but trapped three-wide without cover behind midfield. Wide around turn and only one-paced in straight.
Ridden forward from inside draw to grab box seat 3L from leader on settling. Took closer order around home turn, boxed on fairly to 200m before tiring.
No early pace, settling at rear along fence. Made up some ground turn for home but then ran into series of traffic jams up the straight and not properly tested.
Broke well, hard ridden to hold forward position, settling 1L behind leader in one-off position. Kept tabs until after straightening before feeling the pinch and faded.
Tracked leaders in 3rd, travelled sweetly to straight, quickly raced up to the lead 250M, drew clear and well in control towards the finish.
Settled nicely in midfield, 5Ls behind leader 400M, took a while to get off, worked home well final stages to go 2nd near 50M, not reach winner.
Held up in midfield, 5Ls off the pace home turn, chased winner 350M but was unable to bridge, flattened 100M and lost 2nd final stages.
Held up towards the rear 8Ls back, moved out from the rail 600M, shifted widest to challenge inside 350M, stayed on well and just missed out on 3rd.
Behind midfield, caught 3-wide no cover until 700M, in 8th 7Ls off the pace 400M, ran on moderately without troubling the winner.
Taken back from wide draw, settled down 10Ls back in rear pair, stayed on well enough but too much to make up on front runners.
Away well enough, sat in 4th 3-4Ls behind leader, boxed on final 350M without making an impression.
Sped forward, led along the rail 1L on the turn, headed 250M, weakened 100M and swamped.
Restrained to a midfield position among the 2-path, keen during race, under urge 500M and ran on one pace, never threatened.
Rushed forward on jumping from wide barrier, tracked leader 2-wide to straight, run ended 250M, weakened noticeably towards the finish.
Dropped back to rear pair, over 10Ls off the pace middle stages, pushed along 500M, no response and soon beaten.
Began awkwardly and bumped at the start, ended up near the tail 9Ls behind leader, brought wide 500M but couldn't finish off, left behind 200M.

Broke well, allowed to slide forward along rail settling 3L from leader. Came off fence passing 600m, 4-wide into straight, made ground steadily to lead passing 150m and kept finding to hold off challengers.
Jumped with field but allowed to find feet, settling behind midfield between horses. Slightly inconvenienced passing 1000, improved position around turn, ran on strongly in straight.

Began OK but eased back and shifted across behind runners, settling at rear. Improved position around turn, swung wide into straight, taken to centre track and finished powerfully, doing best work final 100m.
Began fairly, dropping to rear before picking up momentum and improving to behind midfield. Took inside run on straightening and finished off strongly.
Jumped OK, restrained, shifted across behind runners, settling at rear. Last into turn, still well back passing 300m before picking up the bit and finishing strongly.
Outpaced early and last on settling. Became unbalanced passing 1000m, improved position around turn, ran on well in straight though raced in restricted room concluding stages.
Began fairly, not pushed, hampered passing 1000m, dropping to rear. Made up some ground around home turn, taken wide in straight, finished off nicely.
Jumped with field not pushed, settling ahead of midfield and taken to fence. Niggled at turning for home, got clear run 300m, finished off well.
Broke well, hard ridden to lead for a few strides before settling in box seat 1.5L from leader 1100m. Urged forward home turn, hit front 400m, battled strongly till flattened 100m.
Hard ridden from widest draw to lead passing 1300m, crossing to fence 1100m. Collared shortly after straightening and gave ground gradually.
Pressed forward from an outside draw to hold a forward position, settling 3L from leader in one-off position. Kept on steadily in straight before running out of condition 200m and fading.
Began well, pressed forward from an outside draw before shifting in abruptly 1200m when racing greenly. Lay in top of straight, and already a spent force when checked 400m.

Began fairly, then raced greenly early and middle stages dropping towards the rear. Lay out from 900m and last into straight where continued to lay out badly and eased down. Racing manners unacceptable.
Hard ridden early to go forward, settling in midfield but wide without cover from 900m. Gave ground rapidly around home turn and finished tailed out. Unacceptable performance.
Easily got to the front from the wide draw to set his own tempo in front. Let down from the 250m. Challenged hard by 2nd all the way down the straight, but outlasted and kicked clear in the last 50m.

Checked on jumping and dropped back to be worse than midfield, 3-4 wide and with no cover from 900m. Pushed forward to be 2nd at 400m. Challenged winner in the straight, but couldn't produce a kick to get past him.
Taken up early to settle 4th/5th, 1 off the fence. Came wider for a clear run from 300m, and ran solidly to the line from there and making up some ground on the first 2.
Taken forward early to share 2nd, on the fence. Battled on gamely in the straight, holding his place, but only picked up real speed last 100 and no threat to first 3.
Broke well, before opting to drop back midfield, 3 wide. Wider on the turn and ran solidly to the line, without threatening a place.
Dropped back from the wide draw to sit towards the rear of the field, 1 off the fence and tending to over race. Ran steadily under limited urging in the straight, but never a threat.
Pushed to be midfield early, before drifting back to be 4th last, 3 wide with cover. Steady in the straight, and picked up some of the slower ones late.
Slow away and cruised forward early to sit midfield, 1 off the fence. Had every chance on the straight, but only went to the line 1 paced.
Cruised forward early to be handily placed in 4th, 3 wide without cover. Crowded on the turn, and only plodded to the line under hands and heels in the straight and was eased late.
Pushed hard early to share 2nd, 1 off the fence. Nothing left in the tank in the straight, and dropped out rapidly from the 300m.
Dropped back to sit last early. Never responded to urgings, and dawdled to the line in the straight.
Slow to begin, before settling around midfield, 1 off the fence. Unsettled and checked off heels at 900m, and lost some ground. Didn't have much to give in the straight, and just plodded to the line.
Didn't settle early when trying to get a position midfield. Came off heels 1200m and dropped back towards the rear of the field. Wider on the turn, but gave nothing and was eased late.

Ridden positively to make all, kicked over 2L clear into straight, won with ease.
Moderate start, settled one back in 3rd on rails, gained 2nd when over 2L back entering straight, fought on under pressure without threatening.
Jumped fairly from a wide gate, travelled wide in 5th to straight, fought on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Jumped well, settled 2L back in 4th, in similar position turning for home, kept on same pace without quickening.
Settled in midfield, in similar position turning into straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Midfield, given reminders early, made no impression in the run home.
Taken back to just worse than midfield from the widest gate, in similar position turning in, one-paced.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, soon recovered to just worse than midfield in 10th or 9th, similar turning into straight, ran home one-paced.
Broke well, disputed lead early stages, faded under pressure from home bend.
Lacked pace, trailed the field to the 400 metres, went past beaten horses in straight. (Lame next day)
Taken back towards the rear on rails, no further impression.
Never a danger.
Slow away, settled in midfield, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Pushed to hold the rail and led at fast sectionals, hung on well until 50M overhauled, just beaten by narrow margin.
Pushed to occupy box seat, not suited by the fast tempo, ran on strongly for 3rd.
Eased back, took rail, suited by the fast tempo, made early move 700M, ran on well until 100M emptied.
Took rail in midfield, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 250M.
Hard ridden forward, sat just off the lead 2 wide, harmed by the fast pace, flattened 300M.
Eased back, took rail, benefited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 200M.
Eased back, 2 wide, suited by the fast tempo, no turn of foot in straight.
Eased back, 2 wide, favoured by the fast pace, no progress.
Pressed forward, sat 2 wide, not suited by the fast pace, checked 600M, emptied 500M.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 2-3 wide, soon out of fuel 500M.
Never a factor.
At rear early, improved around the field to take the lead from 750M, kept on strongly to the line and scored by 1-3/4Ls.
Pushed forward early, however, was checked near 1400M, 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, suited by the fast pace, ran on gradually for 2nd.
Taken back early, travelled 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, switched back to the inside rounding the Home Bend, finished off well for 3rd.
At back, travelled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, swung widest turning in, ran home nicely for 4th.
Rolled forward to obtain the box seat, kept on steadily until weakened over the latter stages.
Prominent, 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on fairly.
Raced midfield, 4.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never ran on.
Raced midfield, 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, never a factor.
Rolled forward to take the lead from a wide draw, under pressure rounding the Home Turn, weakened soon after straightening.
Raced midfield, 5.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, made no impression in Straight.
Taken back as usual, travelled 8Ls behind the leader on the fence, improved around the field 750M, kept on until weakened over the final furlong.
Sent forward to park outside the leader, dropped off rounding the Home Turn.
Smart start, parked 1 back on fence, closed to leaders' heels turning in, driven 300m for rail run home, quickened & battled to lead 75m, all out to win.
Broke ok widest, pace to lead 1050m, crossed to rail 800m, 0.5L up turning in & driven, shifted out under pressure, headed 75m, boxed on when beaten.
Taken back to race rail near tail, steadied off heels 950m, steadied again 550m, shifted 1 off 400m & driven turning in, strong run for closing 3rd.
Led at break, headed 1050m & handy 1 off no cover, soon snagged to 1 back 1 off in 5th, shifted out & driven into stretch, boxed on evenly.
Bustled forward at break to 3 deep no cover, pushed on to 2nd & slotted 1 off 650m, soon shuffled to 3rd & niggled, bustled 400m & progress to 2nd turning in, hard ridden 300m, tapered in run.
Broke well, snagged back to park 1off near rear, shifted 3 wide 750m, progress on turn & widest into stretch, stayed on moderately.
Started ok, caught wide early & taken back to 3 wide with cover midfield, pushed on a spot 650m & under pump for progress 450m, very wide final turn, 2.5L down on straightening, tapered.
Tardy break, raced rail midfield, niggled along, driven into stretch, plodded home evenly.
Broke with others, snagged to race midfield 1 off with cover, shifted out home turn & driven 300m, one-paced in run.
Taken back to tail, 2L detached & niggled, kept on past beaten rivals but no impact in tame run home.
Started ok & bustled forward, trapped fore of midfield 4 wide no cover, pushed on to 2nd 3 wide 650m, under pump to hold spot, wide final turn, emptied 300m, tailed off.
Started ok, snagged to midfield, restrained off heels & shuffled to 4th last 800m, continued to retreat & last turning in, spent force & eased down thereafter.
Strong start, quickly to lead, 1L lead 800m in moderate fractions, travelled strongly throughout, clicked up 350m, found just enough.
First to break the line, quickly headed, restrained into 2nd 1 off, back to 3rd on rail 900m, ridden 350m, railed through, almost on terms 75m but just missed.
Fast to jump, unable to match early speed, settled 4th 1 off, keen at times, ridden 500m, still green and laying in, one-paced early in straight, strong through line late.
Slightly slow, eased early to settle midfield 1 off, ridden 380m, ducked out on turn, made solid ground but no threat.
Away on terms, natural speed to press forward, awkward 1st turn and trapped 3 deep, settled 2nd 1 off, a little keen at times, asked for effort 320m, faded very late.
Slow into stride, mustered through to settle midfield on rail, got head up 750m, switched over heels entering straight, ridden 340m, only hit top gear very late.
Jumped well, let speed go, settled fore of midfield on rail, overraced 850m, settled better soon after, ridden along 500m, never likely.
OK start, last early, railed through to sit near rear on inside, travelled strongly throughout, pushed along 400m, made significant ground without ever challenging.
Even jump, eased to beyond midfield on rail, on heels 750m, under a ride 350m, never a chance.
Eased from gate, settled beyond midfield 3 deep, eased to 1 off 750m but threw head about, niggled 450m, pulled centre track straight, no impression.
Began well, eased, settled beyond midfield 1 off, pulled widest into straight and ridden, weakened.
Good start, eased to 2nd last, back last 1000m, racing ungenerously, nudged along 380m, faded.
Raced in front of midfield, 1-1/2L off along the rail, kept on going and hit the line strongly for a dead-heat.
Sent forward and in box-seat from 700M, sat 1/2L off, looked unchallenged at 200M, got tired but held on for a dead-heat.
Bumped start, travelled in midfield 2-1/2L off 2 wide, crowded at 500M, finished off gamely for 3rd.
Raced in behind midfield, 4-1/4L off along the rail, checked at 500M, ran on strongly once cleared near 150M.
Sat just front of midfield, 3L off 3 wide with cover, dropped to the rear at 400M, made good ground inside final 100M.
Bumped start, in midfield 2-3/4L off along the rail, checked near 500M when tempo slackened, kept on one paced.
Raced in worse than midfield, 4-1/4L behind 3 wide with cover, checked at 400M, kept on one paced home.
Eased and raced towards the rear, 5-1/4L behind 2 wide until shifting to rail at 600M, made minor ground late.
Awkward start, raced prominently 1-1/2L off stayed 2 wide until taken to 3 wide at 600M, ran on once paced.
Sent forward, wide and without cover until leading on the rail at 800M, headed at 250M, found nothing in the Straight.
Taken back to race on the rail from a wide barrier, slight dash after straightening but not competitive.

Hard ridden from widest draw to get forward position, taking first turn 3-wide before settling 1.5L behind leader passing 1100m. Edged forward 550m, narrow leader 300m, kept finding when challenged to win by a head.

Broke well but allowed to set own pace, settling along rail behind midfield. Got shuffled back entering home turn, took inside run in straight and surged forward, bursting through between horses final 100m only to lose narrowly.

Began OK, not pushed, settling behind midfield in one-off position. Began forward move passing 700m, swung very wide into straight, picked up momentum gradually, finishing off the final 100m strongly.
Jumped straight into the lead from an outside draw before crossing to the fence 1470m. Raced keenly on the lead, joined up front passing 400m, kept battling until swamped final strides.
Broke well, ridden to stay with pacemakers before settling 3L back in one-off position. Under pressure from 550m, swung wide into straight, ran on strongly to be closest at finish.

Began well, ridden to hold rail but kept out of early speed battle, settling 3L from leader. Stayed in contention to straight, got clear rails run, kept on steadily without looking dangerous. Had small cut to left hind coronet.
Quickly into stride, shared early pace before taking box seat 2.5L from leader. Took closer order around home turn, 3-wide into straight, boxed on gamely under hard riding.

Began fairly, restrained and shifted across behind horses, settling at rear in one-off position. Ridden to improve position passing 500m, straightened behind horses, one-paced when put under pressure final 200m.
Slow into stride, ridden but didn't pick up speed, dropping to last back stretch. Travelled better when tempo steadied passing 1100m, but did not finish off when asked in the straight.

Hard ridden to share early pace before settling one-out, one-back around first turn. Put under pressure turning for home, hard ridden to hold position in straight before tiring and giving ground final 200m.
Steadied soon after start and shifted across behind horses, settling at rear. Taken wide passing 700m when trying to improve position and left without cover. Turned wide and gave ground in straight.
Towards the rear early stages, made mid-race move 800M, loomed up behind leader home turn, driven to lead 250M and pulled away for a dominant win.
Travelled strongly in midfield just over 4Ls off leader as they settled, riven to chase leaders 400M, couldn't close the gap on winner but stayed on well to go 2nd near line.
Jumped well from draw 2 and tracked leaders on the rail in a fast run race, stuck to inside on straightening, tried hard but couldn't match the finishing pace of winner.
Sped to the lead and led them at strong pace throughout the trip, headed 250M, faded to 4th.
Settled down 7th spot 4-5Ls back in midfield in a strongly run race, 3-wide from 500M, peaked on its run 200M, one pace towards finish.
Jumped well to be 4th on settling, shuffled back to midfield passing 600M, gave limited response when driven top of straight, unable to make any impression.
From wide barrier taken across to the fence behind runners, towards the rear throughout, stayed on mildly final 300M and not troubling leaders.
Not hurried, restrained to a position behind midfield as they settled, 3-wide until 1200M, couldn't muster the speed to be closer inside 300M.
Held up behind midfield 6Ls back, saved ground on the inside but could only run on at the same speed to line. (Jockey: disadvantaged when whip entangled in the reins 200M out.)
Eased back to the rear, about 8Ls off the pace middle stages, responded moderately on straightening but ran into heels of rivals 100M, had no clear run to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Unable to slot in, caught 3-wide no cover in mid-division from 1400M to 500M, bustled along making the turn for home, checked 400M and gave ground afterwards.
Hampered on jumping, drove forward to be 2nd along the 2-path, pace strong, gave ground abruptly from 600M before finishing tailed out. (Irregular Heart Rhythm.)

Soon took up one back position near rails, gained upper hand over 100 metres out.
Settled just worse than midfield, finished off race well.
Broke well, settled in midfield on rails, came under pressure entering straight, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Soon took up running and attempted to make all, kicked over 1L clear early in straight, unable to sustain effort and swamped closing stages.
Ridden along in midfield early stages, similar in midfield when 4-wide turning in, fought on steadily closing stages.
Jumped moderately losing ground, improved steadily down back straight to reach 1L 2nd coming onto home bend, soon faded pressure in straight.
Settled towards the rear, kept on same pace in the run home.
Began fairly, settled mainly 3L back in 4th, dropped to 5th entering straight, faded steadily.
Niggled along wide in midfield, widest runner turning in, one-paced without quickening in straight.
Always well back, trailed the field into straight, ran past well-beaten horses closing stages.
Ridden along from a wide gate, soon dropped towards the rear 3-wide, made no impression in straight. (Questioned for disappointing performance).
Lacked pace and given reminders early, no response and remained a back-marker throughout.
Pushed to obtain box seat, favoured by the slow sectionals, closed off strongly 300M and scored.
Pushed to take rail and led at advantage slow sectionals, hung on well until 100M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield along the fence, harmed by the slow tempo, lack room 400M, unleashed strong finishing efforts when clear.
Very slow away, behind midfield along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, held up 4-2, demonstrated strong finishing efforts when clear.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 2 wide, dashed well 300M despite not suited by the slow tempo.
Slow away, hard ridden forward, 3 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on until 200M flattened.
Eased at start, 2 wide, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow tempo.
Eased to rear, took rail, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Behind midfield, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Hard ridden early, behind midfield, 3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, no dash.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, favoured by the slow tempo, soon emptied 400M.
At back, 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
At back, on the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, no progress.
At rear, 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, never improved.
Eased to settle worse than midfield about 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, accelerated strongly to score by 1L.
Prominent, 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on well until headed by the winner final 50M.
At back, travelled 8Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, switched wide early straight, finished off strongly for 3rd.
Raced midfield, despite travelled 3 wide without cover throughout, ran on gradually for 4th.
Settled in front of midfield about 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on steadily without extra acceleration.
Rolled forward to occupy the box seat, kept on one pace to the line without serious threats.
Settled midfield, 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, kept on steadily to the line.
Raced midfield, 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on only fairly.
Taken back from a wide draw, 9Ls behind the leader with cover, made minor ground in Straight.
At back throughout, never looked likely.
Raced midfield, 6Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, made no impression in Straight.
Rolled forward to take the fence and led by 1L, out of fuel 300M.
Slow to begin, never a factor.
Rolled forward to park outside the leader, weakened badly 350M.
Outpaced & bustled, raced last trio on rail, advanced a spot 600m, 5L back & shifted out on home turn, driven 320m, quickened centre track, strong closer to lead at line.
Fast start & soon led on fence, 0.5L up turning in, shaken up 350m, hard-driven to hold challenger in tough stretch duel, pipped at post by late closer.
Sharp break & settled 2nd 1off no cover, 0.5L down & driven 350m, grinding effort to duel for lead, nip & tuck but always just held, lost 2nd last stride.
Tardy start, taken back to tail & rousted to form line of 3 at rear, parked 1 off, off heels 600m & to rail, crowded & checked 330m, shifted out & driven to close for minor inroads.
Tardy break & rousted initially to race 1 back on rail, 3rd & niggled 650m, steadied 600m, driven 300m, one-paced in run.
Broke well & 3rd 3 wide co cover early, niggled & retreated to 1 off position, ridden along 5th turning in, outpaced & plugged on tepidly.
Started ok, taken back from widest to last trio 3 wide with cover, last pair turning in & shifted out, kept on one pace.
Fast start & briefly vied for lead wide on track, trapped 3 & 4 wide no cover midfield, bustled forward on turn, 4th into stretch & driven 300m, found nil & faded.
Broke ok, bustled wide midfield, unable to slot & eased back 850m to race 4 wide no cover near rear, very wide turning in, plodded on same speed under drive.
Missed break & bustled rear rank, worked forward to race midfield on rail, driven turning in, unable to quicken, tapered.
Awkward start & raced back of midfield 1 off with cover, checked off heels 650m & niggled thereafter, crowded & checked 400m , driven 250m & shifted in, plodded home tamely.
Fast start & front rank, eased & raced 3 wide with cover back of midfield, off heels 650m, ridden widest into stretch, soon emptied & weakened out.
Jumped briskly, driven hard, settled 2nd on rail, clicked up 880m, hit front 750m, 1L lead 600m, began hanging out severely shortly afterwards, placed under ride 480m, stayed on grimly to score.
Broke on top, eased to settle at rear of main bunch, railed through and ridden 380m, blocked 250m and again 190m, clear soon after and motored home, held at line.
Slightly slow start, ridden through but eventually settled beyond midfield on rail, niggled throughout, clicked up 500m along inside, almost joint lead 400m, never quite on top, stuck on doggedly.
Even jump, natural pace to press forward, eased out of speed battle to settle 4th on rail, bumping duel 440m, ridden 360m, weakened noticeably from 100m.
Broke well, pushed on to take narrow lead 1000m, relinquished front 750m, under pressure 550m, squeezed out 430m, looked set to drop out but found again when balanced up.
Awkward start, quickly dropped away, under heavy drive 1150m, 5L behind main pack 900m, ridden quietly until 500m, pulled widest into straight, finished off OK late.
Away well, outsped early, back to beyond midfield 1 off 700m, shuffled back 550m, ridden 430m, pulled centre track straight, closed fairly.
Slightly awkward start, ridden through to settle fore of midfield, shuffled back and keen 650m, limited room early straight, stayed on evenly.
Away fast, ridden to go forward, trapped 3 deep 3rd at 1st turn 700m, bumped heavily 440m, under drive 360m, faded from 250m.
Slightly slow, roused along, settled midfield 1 off, keen at times, improved between runners 620m, limited room 500m, clipped heels shortly afterwards, clicked up 300m, fair to line.
Even jump, eased, settled beyond midfield 3 deep, improved 4 deep 550m, made a bid top of straight, effort short-lived, weakened.
Good start, natural speed to settle forward, eased to settle fore of midfield, trapped 4 deep no cover and overracing 700m, pressed forward 600m, almost joint lead 400m, weakened badly.
Settled to race in worse than midfield, 5-3/4L behind 3 wide with cover, took lead inside 50M and held off challenge late.
Eased and travelled towards the rear, 7L behind 3 wide with cover, made good ground and ran on strongly for 2nd.
Raced in midfield, 4L behind the lead 3 wide with cover, kept on nicely to the line to take 3rd.
Slotted into midfield, 4-1/4L behind 2 wide, found good dash near 150M and finished off well for 4th.
Travelled in behind midfield, 5-3/4L behind along the rail, continued to improve until held up at 200M, not fully tested.
Sent forward, led by 1L on the rail, headed at 150M, kept on but not fully tested when shifting ground inside 100M.
Taken back and raced at the rear, 8-3/4L behind 3 wide with cover, made good ground in the Straight.
Settled to race in box-seat, 2-1/2L off the pace, kept on but not fully tested close to the line when shifting ground.
Travelled in midfield, 4-1/4L behind along the rail, kept on until steadied near 150M, one paced thereafter.
Eased and raced at the rear, 8-1/2L behind along the rail, ran on and made ground in the Straight.
Raced in front of midfield, 2-1/2L off 2 wide, dropped off at 350M, not competitive.
Awkward start and lost ground, raced towards the tail 7L behind 2 wide, found nothing in the Straight.
Sent forward and raced outside the lead, sat about 1L off, dropped off passing 250M.
Prominent but 3 wide and without cover throughout, consequently gave ground upon straightening.

Began awkwardly, shifted across behind runners, settling three-wide at rear. Not pressed until turning for home, taken to centre field and surged forward to share four-way lead 200m before edging ahead final stages.

Began awkwardly, ridden to make up ground, settling behind midfield in one-off position. Urged forward approaching 900m, swung wide into straight, ran on strongly to share lead 200m but unable match winner final strides.
Broke well, pressed forward, grabbing box seat and trailing leader to straight. Got rails run, looked a chance passing 200m, unable match first two final stages.

Jumped OK but allowed to travel at own pace, settling behind midfield in one-off position. Still well back turning for home, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly, doing best work final stages.
Jumped with field, allowed to stride forward, settling behind midfield along the fence. Took inside run on straightening but temporarily held up by traffic before finishing strongly final 200m.

Got off nicely, sharing early pace before being eased back first turn, 5L from leader in one-off position. Began forward move 3-wide passing 1000m to third entering straight, kept battling to 200m before turning one-paced.
Away OK but no early pace, dropping to rear along fence. Still well back turning for home before running on fairly final 200m.
Pressed forward from an outside draw to lead passing 1750m, setting steady pace. Increased tempo turning for home, still in front passing 200m before running out of steam and fading.

Began fairly, hard ridden to go forward before settling 3L from leader in one-off position. Put under pressure turning for home, raced in restricted room early in straight before giving ground final 300m.
Shifted across behind runners from an outside draw, settling at rear. Clear last from 1600m, never competitive.

First out of the gates, shared early pace before giving way passing 1750m, settling 2L from leader in one-off position. Rolled forward to race outside leader passing 850m but spent force shortly after straightening and faded.
Settled nicely in midfield 5-6Ls off the pace, pushed along 500M, sprinted to the lead 200M, drew clear for another emphatic win over his 4yo peers.
Eased to last on jumping from wide barrier, over 10Ls back in middle stages when pace was strong, switched widest to challenge 450M, ran on strongly behind the winner making good late impression.
Sat behind midfield in 9th, 6Ls off the pace 800M, tried hard final 400M but couldn't make up ground on winner, stayed on to go 3rd late stages.
Taken back from wide barrier, reserved in 2nd last well off the pace early stages, swung wide 450M, stayed on moderately towards the line without threatening top 2.
Had rail run from inside draw, in 5th 3-4Ls off the pace as they settled, responded well early straight, moved up to 2nd 250M, peaked on its run 200M, beaten to 5th towards the finish.
Close up in 4th along the 2-path, travelled well and loomed a chance early straight, got out-stayed final 200M.
Restrained to a position behind midfield, 6Ls off the pace 800M, switched wide 550M, ran on only fairly, held ground over final 200M.
Slotted into a 2-wide spot ahead of field, 4Ls off the pace midway, kept on same pace in straight and couldn't muster the speed to go closer.
Settled down midfield along the rail, 4-5Ls off the pace middle stages, lacked a finishing response when asked 450M, no impression on leaders.
Driven to find the lead setting fast early sectionals, steadied the pace from 1200M, maintained lead to 300M, run ended soon and weakened away.
Chased leader and more prominent than before, pace strong early, couldn't pick up speed leaving the bend, soon beaten. (Jockey : early work resulted the horse not being able to travel comfortably.)
Taken back from wide barrier, settled down in 11th 7-8Ls behind leader, 3-wide no cover from 700M, fanned wide into straight, couldn't quicken.
Urged along to take a trailing spot behind leader, pace strong early stages, weakened badly from 450M, finished tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance.)

Began well, steadied passing 1000m, shifted across behind horses and clear last on settling. Tagged on to main field turning for home, took rails run in straight and surged forward to win drawing away.
Away nicely, steadied and shifted across behind horses, settling at rear in one-off position. Clear last entering straight, taken to centre field and finished off strongly.

Jumped OK, pressed forward 3-wide but raced keenly before settling 2L from leader passing 1000m. Urged forward turning for home, looked a chance passing 200m but unable match first two closing stages.
Broke fairly, hard ridden to go forward but didn't muster, settling ahead of midfield but wide. Urged forward approaching home turn, 4-wide into straight, boxed on gamely.
Began well, stayed with early pace before being eased 3L back in one-off position. Got shuffled back turning for home, held for clear run from 350m to 200m when switched wide and finished strongly.
Fractious in gates when start effected, losing ground. Ridden to go forward, settling behind midfield in one-off position. Turned wide and ran on steadily without looking dangerous.
Began fairly, pressed forward, grabbing box seat on settling. Kept tabs on leader to straight, raced tightly passing 200m, boxed on fairly.

Began well, sharing early pace but racing keenly. Eased 2L back passing 1000m, travelled well to straight, turning behind horses. Held for clear run from 200m to concluding stages and not fully tested.
Hard ridden from an outside draw to get forward position, racing 3-wide 1L behind leader. Took closer order turning for home, still in contention 200m before running out of steam and fading.
Jumped fairly, pressed forward in one-off position to get within 4L of leader. Got caught behind horses in the straight, got close to heels final 100m and not ridden out.
Slow into stride, settling towards rear along the fence. Switched out on straightening to make run but only one-paced.
Pressed forward from inside draw to lead on settling, setting steady pace. Increased the tempo on straightening, still in front 200m out before running on empty and fading.
Began fairly, taken to fence, settling behind midfield 5L from leader. Took closer order turning for home, kept on fairly to 150m when held for clear run and not fully tested.
Slow into stride, dropping towards rear. Switched out turning for home to make run, kept on fairly to 200m before tiring.

Showed good early speed to go to the front and set the tempo. Surprised everyone with big turn off foot from the 350m, and pulled away under minimal urging. Eased early, and still pulling away under a hold on the line.
Taken forward early to be handily placed in 3rd, 1 off the fence. Progressed solidly to the line and held off 2nd place challengers, but no match for winner.
Cruised forward from the inside draw to be handily placed 4th, on the rail. Looked gone at the 200m, but kicked again to just miss 2nd in a head bobber.
Began well, but eased back early to sit midfield, 3 wide. Looked gone at 300m, but had a second wind and was closing in on 2nd and 3rd late.
Unsettled early, and was checked off heels 1200m, before settling worse than midfield. Stuck to the rail in the straight and ran steadily without ever threatening a place.
Dropped back early to sit in the last pair. Widest on the turn, and last at the 400m. Progressed solidly in the straight, and stayed on OK late.
Cruised forward early to settle forward of midfield, 1 off the fence. Came wider on the turn for a run, but only battled fairly to the line and under hands and heels late.
Dropped back early to sit towards the rear of the field, 3 wide. No clear run early in the straight, but plugged on steadily when clear from the 300m.
Taken forward to sit forward of midfield, 3 wide no cover from the 1000m. Well positioned on the turn, but went to the line 1 paced.
Began well, but eased back early to sit midfield, 4 wide no cover until the 900m. Wider on the turn, and only plugged away to the line.
Dropped back from the wide draw to sit dead last. Plugged away non-threateningly in the straight.
Steadied around the back of the field early, before taking up a position midfield. Dropping off before the turn. Had no impact in the straight, and eased late.
Slow to begin. Recovered to sit forward of midfield, on the fence. Off heels at 400m, but had nothing in the straight.
Pushed forward early to eventually share the lead by 1000m. Fading by the turn, and faded out meekly in the straight before easing a long way from home.
