Well poised one-back in 3rd on rails, switched out to challenge upon straightening and hit the front over 100 metres out.
Settled just worse than midfield after beginning from a wide gate, commenced move approaching home turn, ran on to hold every chance in straight but unable to peg back winner throughout.
Settled towards the rear on rails, angled out for a run on straightening, ran on steadily without threatening.
Raced keenly in 5th about 3L off the pace, commenced move on top of home bend to hit the front briefly after straightening, unable to sustain effort closing stages.
Settled just worse than midfield, in similar position entering straight, fought on steadily between runners.

Taken back from the widest gate, took closer order passing the 800 metres, circled the field rounding home bend and went very wide in midfield into straight, unable to sustain progress under pressure.
Settled in midfield on rails, saved ground turning in, kept on well to the line.
Broke well from the middle draw, soon took up running on the rails setting a smart pace, swamped when found no extra over 200 metres out.

Began from a wide gate, given reminders early before settling 3-wide in midfield rounding stables bend, commenced move passing the 500 metres and very wide in midfield into straight, ran home one-paced.

Niggled along, met minor interference coming out of home straight, given reminders in 2L 4th on stables bend, travelling wide without cover down far side before pressing forward to challenge on home bend, checked and lost ground.
Tailed off from the 1000 metres, found nil in straight.
Slow out, ridden to dispute the lead, dropped away quickly from over 400 metres out.
Settled in midfield along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M, just ran on to score.
Detached early, suited by the fast pace, made steady ground 300M, just beaten by very narrow margin.
At back, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward, box seat, not suited by the fast sectionals, held ground in straight.
Took rail at back, favoured by the fast tempo, however badly held up and checked 200M, not tested.
Pushed forward, sat outside the leader, harmed by the fast pace, ran on until 200M weakened.
Very slow away, at back, benefited by the fast tempo, made minor ground 200M.
Pushed to take rail and lead, clocked fast sectionals, soon emptied 300M.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, not suited by the fast pace, out of fuel 250M.
Eased back, trapped 2-3 wide, never competitive.
Hard ridden forward, harmed by the fast pace, trapped 3-4 wide throughout, emptied 300M.
Never a factor, tailed out.
Hard ridden forward to park outside the leader, finished off gradually to score by a short head.
Prominent, travelled 2.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on well for 2nd, missed by a short head.
Pushed forward to take the fence and led by 1L, kept on gamely until final 70M headed by the winner.
Pushed to settle midfield with cover from a wide gate, ran on steadily for 4th.
Raced midfield, 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, badly checked 200M, made minor ground thereafter.
Rolled forward to obtain the box seat, kept on one pace to the line without serious threats.
Settled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, made some ground in straight.
At back throughout, never a factor.
Settled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never ran on.
At back throughout, never looked likely.
Taken back from a wide draw, never a factor.
Raced midfield, however, trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, dropped off soon after straightening.
Early speed & parked rail 1 back, shuffled to 3 back 1000m, progress & shaken up turning in, switched out 300m, ran home strongly to lead last stride.
Speed to lead, snared rail 1300m, eased & headed 1200m, parked 1 back from 1100m, shifted out 400m, driven 300m & quickened centre to lead 180m, all out & headed last stride.
Broke ok, sat rail midfield initially, shuffled back a spot 1000m, overraced 900m, shaken up & shifted out turning in, hard-ridden centre track, closed to 3rd late.
Snagged to tail at break, raced 1 off, slotted 3 deep with cover, ridden for progress 520m, checked out from heels 350m & forced wide, switched inside 300m, driven & closed for solid gains.
Started well, slotted 3 wide with cover midfield, exposed 1100m, rolled on 900m to edge lead 700m & slotted 1 off, ridden 400m & 0.25L up turning in, emptied & headed 180m, tapered.
Started ok, rousted forward & settled 1 off 1 back initially, shuffled back a spot & shifted 1 off 650m, soon niggled, under pump 450m, hard-ridden centre track, plugged on evenly.
Steadied start & settled 3 wide with cover back of midfield, exposed 700m, hard-ridden home run for minor headway, checked 60m, no extra.
Broke ok & bustled, lacked toe & sat midfield 1 off with cover, scrubbed along 400m, hard-ridden into stretch, plodded tepidly.
Started ok but lacked toe, raced rail last pair, of heels 1000m, niggled 500m, driven in stretch but found little in weak run home.
Smart start, pushed to lead 1 off 1200m, to rail 1100m, headed 700m, vied for lead on turn & under pressure, weakened tamely.
Stumbled start & rousted, raced near rear 1 off, under pump 680m, outpaced on turn & checked off heels, hard-ridden but found nil, eased.
Broke ok & bustled forward, caught wide until slotted 2nd 1 off no cover 1100m, shuffled back to 3rd 750m & niggled 650m, soon under pump & retreated weakly, eased in stretch.
Sharp start, bumped soon after, ridden through to settle comfortable 2nd on rail, shifted out and ridden 320m, sprinted strongly, hit lead 200m, came away.
Began strongly, eased to 3rd 1 off, clicked up 400m, chased willingly but no match.
Jumped on terms, bustled towards front, crossed to lead 650m, 2L lead 500m, under pressure 320m, joined and headed 200m, stayed on.
Very awkward start, missed break by 3L, ridden through to settle beyond midfield on inside, held together until 350m, sprinted well.
Fast jump, unable to match early speed, settled 4th on rail, keen, ridden 400m, stuck to inside, stayed on OK.
Even break, eased to just beyond midfield 1 off, ridden 400m, one-paced to line.
Awkward break, outpaced, settled near tail 1 off, ridden 380m, picked up when race was over.
Jumped OK, outpaced badly early, back to beyond midfield 1 off despite riding, shifted 3 deep 450m, pulled centre track 300m, never in it.
Outpaced early, settled midfield 3 deep, improved 450m, widest entering straight, weakened out.
Slightly slow break, settled at tail on inside, pushed along 300m but quickly beaten, eased right down.
Bumped start, raced in midfield but trapped 3 wide without cover, made move rounding turn, kicked clear at 200M, ran on nicely to score.
Initially in behind midfield, followed the winner to move closer at 700M but 3 wide with cover, ran on nicely for 2nd.
Raced close to the tail, 5-3/4L behind along the fence, made nice ground and ran on gamely to take 3rd.
Eased and raced towards the rear, 6-1/4L behind 2 wide, continued to make good ground to finish 4th.
Raced in midfield, 3-3/4L behind 2 wide, kept going until steadied passing 200M, nonetheless ran on thereafter.
Travelled in just behind midfield, 4L behind along the rail, made slight ground and kept finding to the line.
Sent forward and raced outside the lead, sat 1L off, kept on one paced going to the line.
Raced in front of midfield, 2-1/2L off 2 wide, slight dash after 200M then awkward to heels at 150M, one paced thereafter.
Pushed forward before checked at 1000M, settled in front of midfield 2-3/4L off on the rail, held up from 200M, not tested.
Bumped start, sent forward but trapped wide until assumed lead at 800M, dropped after 200M, not competitive.
Sent forward and settled into box-seat at 800M, lay out rounding turn, held up after 200M, not fully tested.
Always at the rear, never a factor.
Broke well, pressed forward 4-wide before settling 3-wide without cover 3L from leader. Swung wide into straight, gradually picked up momentum under hard riding to win on the line.

First out, set early pace before giving way and taking box seat passing 1000m. Stayed on rail entering straight but blocked for clear run from 200m to near 100m when got split and powered home, only to fail by narrow margin.

Bumped heavily on jumping, shifted across behind runners, settling towards rear in one-off position. Began forward move passing 400m, swung widest into straight, finished strongly final 200m to fail narrowly in 4-way finish.
Hard ridden from widest draw to take clear lead passing 1000m and shifting to fence. Kept finding when placed under pressure in straight before flattened final strides.

Taken across behind runners shortly after start settling along rail towards the rear. Swung wide entering straight, shifted out 200m to get clear run, ran on strongly to finish just behind place-getters.

Began well but eased back, settling along rail 5L from leader. Lay in 600m, bumped running rail and became unbalanced. Hard ridden in straight, making ground steadily until tightened near finish line and not ridden out.
Hard ridden to get forward position, settling one-off 1L from leader. Urged forward turning for home, joint leader passing 200m before running out of steam 100m and weakening.
Began awkwardly, losing ground, then ridden but didn't muster, settling in last pair along rail. Took inside run in straight and boxed on gamely to finish just behind place-getters.
Jumped OK but unable to stay with early pace, dropping behind midfield in one-off position. Turned a little wide and boxed on one-paced in straight.
Broke well, ridden to get forward position, settling 3L from leader in one-off position. Looked a chance early in straight but tired passing 150m and faded.
Bumped heavily on jumping, shifted across behind runners, settling in last pair. Clear last from 800m and never competitive.
Began well, hard ridden to hold position between horses 3L from leader. Taken wide in straight before giving ground noticeable from 180m. Lame right front leg.
Began well from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, easy run throughout, finished off well to score. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kept on well after turning in but couldn't hold off the winner final 100M. (Lost left hind plate after 400M.)
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, taken wider near 600M, slightly improved on turn, finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide in 9th, 6 lengths or so back, 3 wide on turn, taken widest in straight and made good progress despite shifting in near final 50M.
Steadied start, raced at rear on rail, 7 lengths back, angled out on turn, taken wide in straight and made some progress without threatening the first few.
Away with them, raced 8 lengths back at rear, same margin back on turn, made reasonable progress in straight without threatening.
Moderately away, positioned 5 lengths back on rail in 8th, same position on turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off evenly.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced prominently, there to turn, peaked early in straight and weakened gradually thereafter.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, couldn't maintain position from 600M, showed no response in straight.
Bumped start, unable to slot in, travelled 3 wide with no cover, peaked on turn, failed to close off.
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, similar position on turn, emptied early in straight and eased.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced at tail throughout, emptied early in straight, never a factor.

Always well there, hit the front inside final 300 metres, just held on to the line.
Led or disputed lead racing greenly, headed inside final 300 metres.
Settled within 3L of pace on stands rail in rear of midfield, made modest progress under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Never far off on stands rail, kept on steadily under pressure without quickening.
Badly bumped at start, settled within 2L of pace in midfield, ran home one-paced.
Settled within 3L of pace in rear of midfield, kept on one pace under pressure.
Jumped well, settled just off the pace, kept on until making no further impression inside final 200 metres.
Settled well behind, ran on past well-beaten horses before steadied over 150 metres out.
Well behind travelling near the centre of the track, went past well-beaten horses closing stages.
Settled just worse than midfield, hampered when switched in for a run towards the centre of the track coming onto course proper, baulked again passing the 300 metres, no further impression.
Raced keenly just off the pace near the centre of the track after beginning from the one draw, weakened under pressure inside final 400 metres.
Jumped awkwardly and badly squeezed, tailed off most of way thereafter.
Well there to halfway down the centre of the track, dropped out.
Recovered quickly from a moderate start, brief lead before dropped out of contention half-way out.
At rear, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, ran on strongly for 2nd.
In front of midfield, 3 wide, just held ground in straight.
Pushed early, behind midfield along the fence, suited by the fast pace, on heels 300M, made steady ground 250M.
Eased back, 3 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M.
Pressed forward, sat outside the lead, harmed by the fast sectionals, flattened 200M.
Eased back, 3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, made steady ground 200M.
At back, 2 wide, suited by the fast pace, lack room 300M, made some ground when clear.
Eased back, 3 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, however blocked most straight, not tested.
Eased back, trapped 4 wide, hung out badly, no progress.
Hard ridden forward, 3 wide, harmed by the fast pace, reduced 300M.
Trapped 4 wide throughout in midfield, flattened 200M.
In front of midfield along the fence, out of fuel 250M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail and led at very fast sectionals, soon emptied 400M.
Taken back to rear, 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, improved gradually rounding the Home Turn, kept on strongly to the line and scored by 3/4L.
Raced midfield, 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on nicely until headed by the winner final 50M.
At back, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on strongly for 3rd.
Rolled forward to park outside the leader, kept on nicely until headed final 100M, hung on for 4th.
Sent forward to take the fence and led by 1/2L, kept on gamely until weakened final 150M.
Raced midfield, 3.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on steadily without serious threats.
Rolled forward to obtain the box seat, briefly held up in the early part of the straight, one paced home thereafter without threatening.
Prominent, 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, found nothing when placed under pressure.
Fast start & prominent, snagged 1200m to park fore of midfield 1 off with cover, switched 3 deep 650m, smooth advance to lead 250m, driven clear, in command.
Taken back at break to race last, soon 2L detached & niggled, joined tail 650m, shifted out on turn & driven, strong run to 2nd at 100m, no threat to winner.
Taken back at break to sit behind midfield 3 wide with cover, forced widest into stretch, shaken up 350m, stayed on gradually to 3rd.
Snagged at start to park near rear 1 off with cover, snatched off heels 720m, last pair & wide on turn, driven 350m, quickened up & ran home for solid inroads.
Missed break & raced rail near rear, overraced & checked 750m, shifted 1 off, edged wider final turn & driven 430m, ran on for minor headway.
Good start but soon outpaced & rousted, soon midfield wide no cover, sharp advance 800m to press lead 600m, driven turning in, emptied 250m & faded.
Broke well from widest gate & prominent, pushed on to lead 1050m, crossed to rail 950m, narrow advantage & pressed turning in, headed 250m & no extra, tapered.
Smart start & front rank on fence, snagged to 1 back 1000m, shifted out 350m & driven, some progress but soon peaked & tapered out final 50m.
Broke ok, taken back, bustled 1200m to rail back of midfield, niggled along, progressed a spot at 800m & steadied, driven turning in, switched out & plugged on moderately.
Tardy start & niggled rail to race fore of midfield, overraced & checked 900m & again 550m, shifted out & not clear run 400m, crowded until ridden 200m, one paced.
Lacked toe, niggled to midfield 1 off with cover, steadied 850m, edged out on turn, switched centre 400m & driven, kept on one-pace until tapered final 100m.
Slow start & rousted along midfield 3 wide with cover, wide into stretch, hard-ridden 300m, found nil & weakened.
Prominent from gate, vied for lead 3 wide no cover, raced close 2nd & went to 1 off 750m, driven to press lead 400m, emptied 300m & faded.
Front rank from start, 1 off & pushed on to lead 1200m, headed 1050m & to 3rd 1 off 1 back, shuffled back 600m, driven 400m, found nil & weakened.
Fast to jump, natural speed to cross into clear 2nd, over to rail 650m, clicked up 450m, green, struck lead 275m, raced right away for big win.
First to break, ridden initially to get to outside rail, eased to take trail 3rd, shifted off outside rail 620m, bustled 450m, hanging out at times, stayed on well but no match.
Jumped towards outside rail at start, natural speed to settle fore of midfield 1 off, pushed towards centre track 500m, switched back towards grandstand side and ridden 300m, stuck on.
Slightly awkward to jump and then carted to outside fence, outpaced early, settled beyond midfield on grandstand rail, improved to midfield 700m, clicked up 450m, stayed on but never a threat.
Very awkward start, ridden along but unable to get into it early, settled 2nd last on outside rail until 620m, improved steadily, under strong ride 400m, made ground late.
Ridden from the gates but unable to match early speed, settled midfield 3 out, pulled centre track and ridden 400m, one-paced to line.
Slightly awkward start, ridden early, no speed, settled beyond midfield 1 off, niggled 600m, never on bridle but stayed on.
Jumped well, natural speed to push forward, ridden to maintain lead, across to 2L lead on outside rail 850m, under a drive 340m, found little.
Dipped at start, ridden to hold position but unable to muster, settled just beyond midfield 3 off, ridden 520m, pulled centre track, weakened from 200m.
Even start, settled fore of midfield 1 and 2 off, under riding 620m, weakened, eased last 100m.
Jumped on terms, niggled to push forward but quickly outpaced, dropped to near tail 1 off, showed a little acceleration 450m, green, never in contention.
Even break, allowed time, settled beyond midfield 4 and 5 out, outpaced 450m and ridden, green, eased down from 200m.
Fractious, awkward to jump, squeezed shortly afterwards, quickly outpaced and under a heavy drive centre track, never in it, eased right down.
Prominent, sat 2-1/2L off 2 wide, found extra at 200M, closed off strongly and held off close challenge to score.
Raced in front of midfield, 3-1/2L off 2 wide, kept battling in a close finish, just missed by a nose.
Eased and raced at the rear, 7-1/4L behind 3 wide with cover, made nice ground and finish off gamely for 3rd.
Travelled in worse than midfield, 6-1/4L behind 2 wide, made nice ground and finish off nicely for 4th.
Raced just behind midfield, 5-3/4L behind 2 wide, made ground steadily and kept on well to the line.
Pushed forward to take the rail and shared lead, headed approaching 100M, kept on one paced thereafter.
Crowded start, raced at the rear 9L behind 2 wide, made good ground in the latter part of the Straight.
Settled to race in behind midfield, 6-1/4L behind 3 wide without cover, made slight ground in the Straight.
Sent forward and shared lead in a 2 wide position, kept on until 150M and swamped.
Travelled in front of midfield, 3-1/2L off along the fence, kept on one paced in the run home.
Pushed forward and raced prominently, sat 1-3/4L off 2 wide, weakened passing 250M.
Travelled in worse than midfield, 6-3/4L behind along the rail, found nothing in the Straight.
Awkward start and taken back, raced 8-1/4L behind 3 wide with cover, showed nothing in the Straight.
In midfield, about 5L behind initially 2 wide until taking the rail at 600M, under whip rounding turn, not competitive.
Bit keen early on, settled one off fence three back, face breeze at 1450 metre, checked at 600 metre and no room just before 500 metre, lay in early part of straight, before running on well.
Face breeze early part before taking box-seat run, shifted out slightly before home turn, looked the winner at 100 metre under hard riding, nailed by winner.
Settled on rails four back, travelled, saved ground turning in, ran on under riding. Followed the winner, one off fence, improved at 600 metre, tight soon after and checked at 550 metre, battled on.
Set a clip to suit himself, under ridden soon after turning in. No match in end.
Followed the winner, one off fence, improved at 600 metre, tight soon after and checked at 550 metre, battled on.
Settled at rear as usual - 8 lengths off leader - took off at 800 metre, bumped twice at 600 metre and before the turn, went wide at home turn. One paced.

Placing: PU
Comment: Eased out passing the 900 metre. Bled.
Close up tracking leader along the rail, responded well and wrestled the lead 180M, kept going final stages to keep pursuers at bay.
Eased back to the rear 8Ls adrift of the leader, bid his time along the inside, closed off final 400M fastest, pushed winner final 150M but always held.
Caught 3-wide no cover from 14, taken wider 600M, moved into contention nearing top of straight, battled well but always held by winner in the run to the line
Urged along after the jump, sat 3-4Ls off leader along the rail, chased hard final 300M but couldn't reel in leaders.
Not hurried early stages, towards the rear 6Ls behind leader, shaken up 500M, ran on moderately, effort leveled off over final 100M. (Blood in trachea.)
Emerged as leader 1300M, set good pace to straight, caught 180M, faded towards the line.
Dropped back to the rear 8Ls off the good pace, 3-wide trip to straight, made some progress down outside but too much to make up on leaders.
Held up midfield 4-5Ls off the good pace, had every chance from 400M but not going the pace to challenge.
Niggled along early stages, not mustered the speed and fell back to the rear before entering the turn, gave mild response passing 300M, got past a few but never threatened.
Began only fairly, settled down midfield along the rail, 5Ls off the good pace halfway, ran on only fairly and no impression on leaders.
Settled down ahead of mid-division, 3Ls off the good pace in first half, close enough top of straight but couldn't go on passing 250M and faded.
Taken back from wide barrier and settled near the rear 7Ls off the good pace, brought wide 450M but found less than expected in the finish, not reach leaders.
Began very well, shifted across to track leader 2-wide, under pressure 500M, gave way passing 350M. (Jockey questioned re riding tactics.)
Restrained to a 2-wide spot behind midfield, 6Ls off at 800M, crept closer home turn, gave limited response on straightening, faded 200M.
Settled three back fence, travelled, shifted out at 550 metre, challenged leaders at 350 metre, ran on well.
Back early on, checked at 1500 metre, took off at 1000 metre, led 950 metre, battled on under riding.
Settled back one off fence early on, improved to sit midfield rails, at 1500m, shifted out at home turn, no room at 400 metre, closed off well when clear.
Bumped start. Settled midfield, unsettled when at heels at 1100 metre, went out wide turning for home, ran on under hard riding without threatening.
Fairly handy rails, travelled, kept battling away.
Mid-rail, travelled, save ground turning in, no room at 280 metre. Good run.
Handy face breeze, travelled same pace, challenged leaders at 350 metre, run emptied at 200 metre.
Settled back one off rails, travelled, ran on without a threat.
At rear rails, came off rails at 900 metre, no room at 800 metre, checked and held up badly at 350 metre. Forget the run.
Settled rear, made no impression. Needed the run anyway.
Began poorly, improved to settle midfield one off at 1400 metre, very erratic at 1100 metre, tracked to sit fairly handy face breeze at 900 metre, gone at 350 metre.
Led easily, set a slow clip, challenged at 910 metres, weakened at final 150 metre.
Erratic on a number of times, travelled better when settled, fairly handy one off fence, went wide home turn, gone at 300 metre.
Slowly away, sat back rear rails, checked at 1100 metre. Never a factor.
Crowded on jumping, settling worse than midfield, on the fence. Off heels 250m when progressing well in the straight. On the rails with a clear run last 200. Too strong to the line under the stick.
Best away, but elected to drop back to sit midfield, 3 wide with cover. Widest in the straight, and ran solidly to chase down front runners and share 2nd.
Pushed forward early to be handily placed 2nd/3rd, on the rail. Battled on gamely in the straight, kicking again slightly late to share a piece of 2nd.
Pushed forward early to be clear early leader by 3L.Still in front at 150m, but faded out from that point and battled to the line late.
OK away, and eased slightly early to settle forward of midfield, 1 off the fence. Slightly tight in the straight, and off heels when fading at 100m. OK late, but never threatened a place.
Bumped and then crowed on jumping, before settling at the rear of the field. Ran solidly in the straight without threatening.
OK away, and moved to midfield. Awkward on heels when keen at 1400m, losing ground and dropping back to worse than midfield. Plugged on OK in the straight, picking up a few slower ones.
Settled forward of midfield, 3 wide with no cover. No kick in the straight, and went to the line 1 paced.
Taken up early to be handily placed 2nd/3rd, 3L off the leader and 1 off the fence. Peaked 250m, and dropped out of the race from there.
Dropped back from the wide draw to sit at the rear of the field. Only plugged to the line, making minimal inroads late.
Dropped back early, settling towards the rear of the field, 3 wide. Plugged to the line late under minimal urging.
Eased forward early, settling around midfield, on the fence. Made no impression in the straight, and eased out just after the 200m.
Fractious in the barrier, reared on jumping and lost plenty of ground. Found it hard to recover from that and made no impact on the race.

Tightened early, settled well behind, made steady headway out wide down back straight and around home bend, widest runner when over 4L back in 8th when straightening, fought on dourly to hit the front over 100 metres out.
Moderate start, settled in rear of midfield, baulked for a run early in straight, finished off race well.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, raced wide behind midfield from stables bend, switched onto the centre of the track on straightening, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Ridden from the one draw, taken back to settle just behind the leader on rails, hit the front under pressure at the 200 metres but unable to sustain effort and caught over 100 metres out.
Prominent before steadied and dropped to forward of midfield near the rails, in similar position to straight, baulked and switched in for a run over 200 metres out, fought on well late.

Broke well, settling just off the pace when hampered coming onto stables bend, travelled in one-out-one-back position in 4th and then 5th down far side, ran on under pressure early in straight but found no extra late.

Settled in last few on rails after beginning from a wide gate, gained closer briefly coming onto home bend, snuck up on rails turning in and went within 2L of pace 200 metres out, unable to sustain effort final stages.
Settled at the back after beginning from the widest gate, came under pressure entering home straight, produced good late impression inside final 200 metres.
Jumped well, settled in rear of midfield, 4-wide rounding home bend, forced to steady 300 metres out, kept on same pace under pressure.
Jumped well and given reminders early, drifted back to some 3L back in midfield in back straight, dropped out under pressure inside the 500 metres.
Ridden along from a wide gate early, improved steadily down back straight to be upside of joint leaders rounding home bend, folded up quickly after straightening.
Soon took up running and led most of way to the 200 metres, folded up under pressure. (Questioned for disappointing performance) (Blood in trachea)
Jumped well, raced keenly before travelled wide in midfield in back straight, remained wide in similar position turning in, soon dropped out.
Ridden forward racing wide on stables bend, led or disputed lead down back straight, unable to sustain effort and weakened under pressure inside final 300 metres.
Pushed forward, shared the lead, dominated from 700M, just ran on to win by narrow margin.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, dashed strongly 300M for 2nd.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, unleashed strong finishing efforts 300M and ran 3rd.
Hard ridden forward, took rail, dashed well 300M.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, little dash 250m.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, little dash 200M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in the lead, overhauled 700M, ran on until 200M flattened.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, 2-3 wide, dashed strongly 200M.
Very slow away, at back, 2 wide, little dash 200M.
Eased to sit behind midfield, trapped 3-4 wide, little dash 200M.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, lack turn of foot.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide, soon emptied 300M.
Very slow away, never improved.
Trapped 3 wide at back, never competitive.
Pushed forward to get a prominent position, despite travelled wide and without cover throughout, ran on strongly to score by 1/2L.
Hard ridden forward to park outside the leader, kept on strongly until headed by the winner final 100M.
Sent forward to hold the fence and share the lead, kept on steadily until weakened final 100M, hung on for 3rd.
Rolled forward to obtain the box seat, finished off one pace for 4th without threatening.
Raced midfield, 3.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on nicely.
Raced midfield, 4Ls behind the leader 2  3 wide with cover, ran on only fairly.
Prominent, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2  3 wide with cover, kept on one pace and weakened final 150M.
Settled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, made no impression in straight.
Settled worse than midfield about 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never ran on.
Ridden forward to settle 1L behind the leader 2 wide with cover, weakened badly soon after straightening.
At back throughout, never looked likely.
Always at rear, never a factor, tailed out.
Good start, rolled to lead 1650m, clear & to rail 1400m, 1L up & driven turning in, kept on well in straight and scored.
Started well, camped 1 back on rail, niggled 650m & soon under pump, driven turning in & shifted centre track, grinding closer final 300m, held.
Ragged start & ridden along, outpaced & raced back of midfield on rail, niggled 850m, hard-ridden 350m, switched out 250m, stayed on to 3rd late.
Buffeted at break, bustled to snag rail midfield, niggled 750m, driven 500m, in pocket 350m, switched out 300m, one-paced thereafter.
Badly impeded start, rousted along initially to settle 2nd last, 3 wide advance from 1150m to midfield 820m, driven forward 5 wide on turn, led 280m, emptied & headed 170m, tapered.
Taken back at start, sat 3 wide near rear, minor advance 1000m to back of mid-rank 750m, niggled 600m & driven very wide final turn, moderate headway centre track.
Impeded at break, taken to near rear on inner, progress 700m, niggled along 500m, hard-ridden home turn, switched out 300m but bumped rival & unbalanced, stayed on evenly.
Bustled forward at break, parked 2nd 1 off no cover, niggled 650m, 1L down & driven 400m, in touch until emptied 150m & faded.
Started well, nudged along to handy 4-wide 1st turn, slotted 1 off 1 back, shifted 3 deep 800m but short-lived advance, under pump 500m & soon hard-ridden, weakened tamely.
Shifted in at break & impeded rivals, snatched back to tail, niggled along 600m & ridden for minor progress on turn, plodded home tamely.
Tardy start, raced midfield 1 off with cover, switched 3 deep 750m & ridden along, under pump 500m & hard-ridden turning in, found nil.
Awkward & bumped start, nudged along to midfield & 4 wide 1st turn, trapped 3 wide no cover, advanced a spot 850m & forced 4 wide, 4th & driven 650m, emptied turning in.
Led at break & bustled but soon collared & snagged to midfield 1 off with cover, bustled 800m, snatched off heels 700m & in retreat, last turning in, eased.
Bumped start and lost ground, raced behind midfield 1 off with cover, shuffled back 900m, under pump 800m & hard-ridden on turn, no extra & eased in stretch.
Broke well, unable to match early speed, ridden through to settle just off lead, settled 3rd 1 off, ridden 450m, in clear 370m, joint lead 250m, raced clear soon after.
Good start, hard-ridden to press forward, settled midfield of main bunch 1 off, ridden 400m, switched off heels 290m, found line strongly.
Jumped on terms, settled fore of midfield on rail, niggled 700m, ridden 380m, short of room 280m, sprinted strongly when clear.
Slightly awkward break, beyond midfield 1 off early, under a vigorous drive 900m, travelled better from 800m, pushed 4 deep 450m and ridden along, kept coming, peaked on run 100m.
Away OK, little early speed, ridden vigorously to get nearer to the lead, settled 4th 3 deep, clicked up 440m, stayed on OK although faded last 100m.

Jumped well, ridden hard to press towards pace, finally reached lead 750m, narrow lead 1 off 600m, headed again 500m, ridden 350m, narrow lead 250m, grabbed soon after, stuck on OK before weakening 50m.
Even dispatch, eased to settle beyond midfield 3 deep, niggled 550m, under a ride soon after, pushed 5 deep 450m, widest into straight, found line OK very late.
First to break, ridden along but unable to muster, settled fore of midfield 4 deep, ridden 360m, one-paced to line from 200m.
Awkward start, under heavy drive from gates but couldn't muster, 3L behind second last horse 1000m, 4L at 700m, tacked on by 400m but pushed along, made ground between runners, peaked 100m.
Even break, natural speed to quickly lead, joined 800m, headed soon after, narrow 2nd on rail 600m, regained lead 500m, ridden 270m, beaten 250m, weakened.
Broke well, eased to near rear of main bunch, last of pack 3 deep and ridden 750m, pulled centre track in straight, couldn't come on.
Slightly slow to begin, restrained to last of main bunch, improved along rail to position beyond midfield, ridden 500m, never a threat.
In behind midfield, 8L behind 3 wide with cover, under whip from 700M, continued to improve and ran on nicely to score.
Pushed forward and raced on the rail, contested for lead until assumed it outright at 700M, kept on until caught by winner inside final 50M.
Travelled in front of midfield, 4-3/4L off 2 wide, kept on going nicely to the line.
No early speed and raced at the rear, 12-3/4L behind 3 wide with cover, improved nicely and ran on well to take 4th.
Slow to jump and raced at the rear, 13-3/4L behind along the rail, made good ground from 250M and kept on strongly.
Sent forward and raced prominently, 2-3/4L off 2 wide, kept on until 200m and found no extra.
Travelled at the tail end, 12-3/4L behind 2 wide with cover, made ground steadily but did not threaten.
Sent forward and sat 1 horse off the rail, shared and contested for lead until 700M, kept on until 250M flattened.
Raced in midfield, 6-3/4L behind along the fence, kept on one paced home.
Settled to race just behind midfield, 8L behind along the rail, made no progress in the Straight.
Travelled towards the rear, 11-3/4L behind along the fence, made minor ground early, then kept on one paced.
Eased and raced towards the tail, 11-1/2L behind 3 wide with cover, didn't make any ground in the Straight.
Raced in midfield, 6-1/2L behind 2 wide, found nothing in the Straight.
Raced just front of midfield, 5-3/4L behind 3 wide without cover, weakened badly rounding turn, not competitive.
Hard ridden to lead on settling but kept away from fence by inside runner. Kicked 1L clear on straightening and then kept finding under pressure for narrow win.
Broke well but unable to match early pace, dropping towards rear in one-off position. Began forward move passing 500m, swung widest into straight, finished strongly only to lose narrowly.
Hard ridden from an outside draw to share early pace but 3-wide before settling in one-off position 2L from leader. Pressed forward on straightening but unable to close gap despite vigorous riding.

Steadied shortly after start, dropping to last pair along fence. Switched out 500m to improve position but held behind horses, switched in top of straight before switching out again to get clear run, finished strongly.
Began fairly, then bumped, before pressing forward 3L from leader in one-off position. Had clear run on straightening, ran on steadily without looking dangerous.

Bumped, unbalanced start, dropping to rear. Ridden to make up ground settling midfield along fence 4L from leader. Unable to get run in straight despite shifting position, then hung out and difficult to ride final stages.
Pressed forward from an outside draw, settling in midfield but 3-wide without cover. Urged forward turning for home, swung wide into straight, boxed on fairly under hard riding.
Jumped OK, rolled forward, settling behind midfield in one-off position. Swung a little wide, switched out wider in straight, but only one-paced.
Began fairly, no early pace, settling along fence behind midfield. Kept on fairly in straight though had to shift out 100m to get clear running.
Hard ridden to hold fence, a half length inside leader to straight. Under pressure passing 300m and gave ground steadily.
Began awkwardly, losing ground, then shifted across behind runners settling in last pair. Fung little when asked on straightening.
Pressed forward from widest draw, racing behind midfield but wide. Came under pressure turning for home and dropped out in straight.
Moderately away from gate 10, raced wide, 3 lengths back in 5th, same position on turn, finished off strongly to score.

Slightly slow out, raced 3 to 4 lengths back on rail in midfield, angled out on turn, no daylight early in straight and checked near 300M, taken widest thereafter and closed off very strongly to get 2nd.
Began well, raced 3 to 4 lengths back in midfield, improved from 600M, widest turning in, finished off well, lost 2nd last stride. (Lame left front leg next day morning.)
Jumped well, positioned 2 to 3 lengths back on rail in 4th, easy run to turn, kept on evenly in straight to make frame without threatening.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide, 6 lengths back at rear, there to turn, made good progress in straight without threatening the first few.
Began well from a tricky gate, sent forward to race prominently, 2nd on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 200M, stayed on one-paced.
Slowly away, recovered to race in 3rd, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight and weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began very awkwardly, recovered, took the lead after 900M, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 200M, headed and weakened thereafter.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, raced at rear, still 5 lengths or so back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, still well back on turn, failed to close off, never a threat.
Away with them, raced wide behind midfield, weakened on turn, emptied early in straight, finished tailed out, unacceptable performance.

Jumped fairly, well placed behind the leader on rails, commenced run after straightening, hit the front 200 metres out, won readily.
Soon took up running setting a sound pace, kicked over 1.5L clear after straightening but unable to sustain effort and overhauled inside final 200 metres.
Settled in last few, took closer rounding home bend, ran on to gain distant 3rd over 250 metres out, made no further impression.
Raced keenly early stages, shuffled back to midfield before home bend, in similar position on rails entering home straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Taken back from the widest gate, trailed the field to straight, ran on past well-beaten horses inside final 200 metres. (Jockey questioned)
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, settled in last few, shifted out for a run entering straight, kept on same pace without quickening.
Wide in midfield early stages, improved to close-up 2nd before home bend, dropped out early in straight.
Broke well, prominent early stages, just over 2L back in 5th rounding home bend, found nil in straight. (Questioned for disappointing performance) (Lame next day)
Ridden along out wide in midfield early stages, picked up to prominent 3rd coming onto home bend, dropped out of contention in straight.
Sluggish at start, settled within 3L of pace and wide in 6th, soon found no extra after straightening.
Soon dropped behind midfield, baulked for a run in similar position early in straight, weakened.
Soon dropped towards the rear on rails, folded up quickly after straightening.
At back, 2 wide, struggled to keep up with the field in middle stages, suited by the fast tempo, lack room 400M, progressed steadily when clear.
Eased back, trapped 3-4 wide, benefited by the fast pace, made steady ground 400M for 2nd.
Settled just behind midfield, 3 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 400M for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward to take rail and lead, clocked very fast sectionals, hung on well until 150M flattened.
Hard ridden forward, box seat, not suited by the fast sectionals, ran on until 200M flattened.
In front of midfield along the fence, raced keenly in a more prominent spot, lack turn of foot in straight.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, lack room 4-2, just held ground when clear.
Eased to rear, took rail, favoured by the fast pace, held up 4-2, made steady ground when clear.
Hard ridden forward, harmed by the fast pace, emptied 350M.
At rear, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, ran on ok in straight.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, checked 1200M, favoured by the fast tempo, lack room 400M, no progress when clear.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, suited by the fast pace, ran on fairly.
Eased back, never a factor.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide, not suited by the fast pace, dropped off quickly 400M.
Tracked behind the leader nicely along the outer fence, ran on well to score comfortably by 2Ls.
Pushed forward to settle 2Ls behind the leader, ran on gradually for 2nd.
Sent forward to take the lead, kept on steadily until final 250M headed by the winner, hung on for 3rd.
At rear, travelled 3Ls behind the leader, ran on steadily for 4th without any serious threats to the placegetters.
Tracked 1.5Ls behind the leader, found nothing when placed under pressure.
Rolled forward, however, under heavy pressure near the course proper, weakened 300M.
Broke ok & bustled forward from wide gate to slot 1 off with cover 4th, shifted 3 wide turning in, driven 400m, quickened to lead 180m, soon peaked but boxed on to wire.
Taken behind from wide & niggled at tail, progress to 2nd last turning in & driven 400m, switched widest 300m & quickened, hung in & bumped rival 150m, closed late.
Fast start & bustled to lead, soon to rail, cuddled into home straight, 1L up when shaken up 350m, all out & headed 180m, game but tapered & lost 2nd late.
Speedy break, eased from vanguard to 3rd 1 back on rail, driven 430m & shifted 1 off, kept on evenly under hard drive.
Broke ok but soon outpaced & niggled midfield 3 deep with cover, driven into stretch, stayed on evenly until tapered closing stage.
Awkward start & hung in, bustled forward from rear to settle midfield 1 off with cover, driven & shifted out turning in, plugged on for gradual inroads.
Snagged back at start to race 3 wide with cover near rear, swung wide into stretch & shaken up 380m, plugging on one pace when bumped 150m, no extra.
Speed wide & bustled on to press early lead, sat 2nd 1 off, 1L down & driven 400m, outkicked & soon all out, faded in run home.
Slow start, raced rail back of midfield, driven 400m, out-kicked, kept on tepidly.
Slow start & bumped, raced near rear 1 off, crowded & snatched off heels 1100m, niggled along 600m & soon under pump, 3rd last at turn, found nil, faded.
Smart break, niggled along midfield on rail, under pump 550m, outpaced & hard-ridden 350m, found nil & eased.
Moderate break & bustled wide midfield initially, snagged from 1000m to slot 2nd last 1 off at 700m, ridden 500m, found nil & eased.
Jumped fast, natural speed to lead on rail, awkward action & overracing 800m, clicked up 400m, green but found enough.
Began well, into handy position, raced fore of midfield on rail, ridden along 450m, switched over heels 320m, chased solidly but always safely held.
Even dispatch, into midfield spot 1 off and travelling strongly, pushed 3 deep with cover 750m, ridden 500m, finished solidly.
Jumped OK, squeezed out shortly afterwards and back to last, improved to settle near rear on rail, overracing 800m, ridden 500m, changed course 300m, found line solidly.
Away with them, driven vigorously to push forward, moved up to just outside lead 800m, settled 2nd 1 off, held together until 380m, moved up to leader but didn't pass, weakened last 50m.
Slightly slow, ridden to go forward, up to 2nd 1 off 1100m but relegated to 4th 900m, ridden 450m, one-paced in straight.
Slightly awkward break, eased to near rear, settled beyond midfield 1 off and overracing slightly, ridden along 500m, limited room 300m and again 180m, found line OK.
Even jump, lack of natural speed and restrained to near rear, keen 970m, settled near tail 1 off, 3 deep 700m and ridden soon after, never in it.
Even break, eased in search of a spot but unable to get in, pushed forward 1000m, settled 3rd 3 deep no cover, ridden 660m, hung out entering straight & green, outpaced.
Slow to break on inside, ridden along to push forward, settled just fore of midfield but overracing slightly, back to midfield 1 off an pulling 700m, ridden 430m, faded.
Broke on terms, outpaced early, settled beyond midfield 3 deep, overracing 800m, ridden 4 deep 600m, widest into straight, never in it.
Among the best to begin, restrained right back to last 1020m, slightly keen at back on rail, ridden 500m, quickly weakened, eased from 100m.
Eased and raced towards the rear, 6-1/2L behind along the rail, found extra at 200M and ran on strongly to score.
Raced just in front of midfield, 3-1/2L behind along the rail, ran on gamely to finish 2nd.
Travelled in just behind midfield, 5L behind along the rail, closed off nicely to take 3rd once cleared from 300M.
Slotted into box-seat, sat 2L off the lead, ran on well but couldn't hold off the place-getters.
No early speed and raced in midfield, 4-1/2L behind 2 wide, continued to make ground in the Straight.
Failed to muster and raced towards the rear, 6L behind 2 wide, showed good dash at 150M and made ground late.
Raced in midfield, 4L behind 3 wide with cover, kept on one paced to the line only.
Travelled in worse than midfield, 5-3/4L behind 3 wide with cover, kept on but passed tiring runners only.
Crowded after the jump, settled in one-off one-back position 2-1/2L off, found no extra passing 300M.
Pushed forward and sat outside the lead about 1L off, kept on until 250M when weakened.
Eased and raced at the rear, 7-1/2L behind 2 wide, found nothing in the Straight.
Settled to race prominently, 2L off but 3 wide without cover, weakened passing 300M, not competitive.
Sent forward to take the rail and led by 1L, dropped off gradually from 350M out.
At the rear and finished tailed out. Not a factor.
Began OK then ridden to find cover, settling behind midfield in one-off position. Lost position approaching turn, swung very wide into straight, stormed down centre track to win close home.
Began well but allowed to slide back, settling one-out about 4L from leader. Improved position around turn, taken wide in straight, hit front 300m, kept finding when challenged but run down 50m out.
Broke well but restrained and shifted across behind runners, settling at rear in one-off position. Taken to centre field on straightening and finished strongly to grab minor placing.
One of the first into stride before settling between horses 2L from leader. Took home turn 4-wide, loomed alongside leaders approaching 300m, kept on gamely to line.

Vigorously ridden from an outside draw to share early lead but trapped 3-wide a half length behind leader. Rolled forward turning for home to share lead passing 400m. Kept on gamely until flattened 50m.
Broke well, sharing early pace before settling in box seat 2L from leader. Blocked for run early in straight, got clear 250m, kept on fairly.

Began fairly, then hard ridden but failed to muster, dropping behind midfield along fence. Improved position around turn but held up in traffic early in straight. Finished off nicely when clear final 100m.
Outpaced and last on settling. Trailed field to straight, shifted out passing 300m to get clear passage and ran home nicely.
Jumped well, sharing early pace before bumped 1100m, settling one-off 2L from leader. Stayed behind the pace till straightening, not much room early in straight but only one-paced when clear 300m.
Slow into stride, taken to fence and urged forward, settling behind midfield 6L from leader. Not much room top of straight but only one-paced when clear.
Slow into stride, taken to fence settling at rear. Shaken up turning for home but found little under hard riding.
Hard ridden to lead on settling before being passed by inside runner 1100m. Stayed a neck behind till retaking lead 400m, but overtaken passing 250m before running on empty final 100m.
Hard ridden to hold fence inside early leader before taking over passing 1100m. Overtaken shortly after straitening, crowded and unbalanced 350m, gave ground quickly.

Pressed forward from widest draw, racing 3-wide 2.5L from leader on settling. Lost position passing 1000m dropping behind midfield but still 3-wide. Gave ground turning for home and finished tailed out.
Chased pace, caught 3-wide no cover first half, raced up to hit the front inside 300M, kept on strongly for a dominant win.
With leaders early, eased back to sit ahead of midfield, tracked the path of eventual winner turning home, tried hard to the finish but couldn't bridge gap.
Began awkwardly, settled down 2-wide in midfield 4-5Ls off the good pace, inclined to lay in early straight, responded well from 300M putting on a late spurt to get in for 3rd.
Jumped well, settled down 3Ls behind leader in 4th, stayed on mildly over final 300M but not making progress on winner.
Rushed forward to track leader, pace good, ran on well early straight and briefly took on winner inside 250M, turned one pace final stages, beaten to 5th near finish.
Eased back from wide draw and taken across to rail, towards the rear 5-6Ls off the pace at 800M, took time to pick up on straightening, switched out 150M and best work final stages.
Began only fairly from draw 1, 4Ls back in mid-division along rail, held ground only in straight and never going the pace to challenge leaders.
Began awkwardly losing ground, ended up in rear pair 8Ls off the good pace, got past a few beaten runners in straight, never threatening.
Restrained in midfield, wide no cover from 700M, ran on same pace passing 400M, weakened final stages.
Bustled along to find the lead, led from 1100M and set good pace under 7lb claimer, couldn't fend off rivals near 250M though and weakened rapidly towards finish.
Raced keenly on debut, pushed wide 950M then restrained to a rearward position for cover, failed to quicken entering straight, checked 100M and eased.
Eased back to the rear 8Ls adrift of the leader, didn't respond to urging passing 550M, soon left behind.

Began fairly, shifted across behind horses, settling towards rear in one-off position. Turned behind a wall of horses, got close to heels 250m before bursting through between horses to win on the line.
Began fairly, taken back to find cover, settling behind midfield in one-off position. Began forward move passing 700m, very wide into straight, hit front 50m out but nosed out on the line.
Began well but eased back, settling along rail behind midfield but only 4L from leader. Stayed on rail on straightening, rolled forward strongly only to fail narrowly.

Hard ridden to lead on settling but kept away from fence by inside runner. Kicked 2L clear at the turn and kept on strongly under pressure in the straight. Still in front passing 100m before laying out and swamped close to line.

Began well, ridden along to hold forward position, settling 2L from leader along rail. Stayed on rail around turn, held for run early in straight, then raced tight passing 300m, but kept on strongly to line.

Lost ground on turning head at start, hard ridden but didn't muster, settling at rear. Last into straight, kept shifting ground to find clear running, surged forward when clear but tightened final stages and not ridden out.
Began well, hard ridden to hold fence inside early leader before easing back and taking box seat 800m. Battled on strongly in straight, holding position until swamped final strides.
Outpaced early, dropping to last pair. Well back entering straight, forced to shift out 250m to get clear passage, finished strongly doing best work final stages.
Jumped OK, staying close to pacemakers before being eased back approaching home turn. Taken to centre track on straightening and ran on steadily under the whip to be closest at finish.
Jumped with field, sharing early pace before being eased to find cover. However trapped 3-wide without cover and fred to race wide from 900m. Boxed on fairly in straight.
Pressed forward from an outside draw to race 4L from leader in one-off position on settling. Battled on fairly in straight without looking dangerous.
Jumped well, shared early pace before settling 2L from leader in one-off position. Rolled forward on straightening, looked a chance passing 200m before running out of steam final 100m.
Outpaced and soon at rear but kept away from fence. Taken very wide on straightening but only one-paced.
Broke well but unable match early speed, dropping 5L back passing 800m. Lost more ground around turn, hard ridden to hold position in straight but tired quickly after passing 200m and faded.
Cruised forward from the low draw to sit midfield. Forced a run through at 350m, and ran strongly to lead at 100m. Pushed out to the line, and held off challengers late.
Took the entire back straight to ease across to sit behind the leader. Hit go from the 300m, and lead by 200m. Lost lead at 75m, and couldn't match the motor of the winner late.

Crowded on jumping and dropped back soon after to be worse than midfield, 3 wide. Widest on the turn, and ran strongly in the straight. Progressed well last 100m, and was rapidly running down 1st two.
Eased back early to sit worse than midfield, 1 off the fence. Ran strongly early in the straight, but ran out of steam 100m and didn't progress from there.
Cruised forward early, settling around midfield on the fence. Came in off heels 400m. Stayed on solidly in the straight without ever threatening.
Pressed hard to be a clear leader in the back straight. No petrol left in the tank for the run home.
Cruised across to be midfield, 3 wide no cover. Plugged away, but no threat in the straight.
Dropped back early and settled worse than midfield, 1 off the fence. Checked and lost ground and momentum 350m. Only fair to the line late.
Taken forward from the wide draw to be handily placed 2nd/3rd. Battled on 1 paced in the straight, and was eased late.
Crowded on jumping and dropped back to sit in the last pair, 3L off the main group. Wide on the turn, and still last at the 250m. Plodded along and picked up a couple of slower ones late.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, before dropping back to settle a clear last early. Plugged away fairly in the straight.
Taken up early before settling midfield, 1 off the fence. Hampered at 350 but had nothing in the straight, and dawdled to the line late.
Settled forward of midfield, 1 off the fence. Lay out on the turn. No kick in the straight, and eased out from the 150m.
Fairly away, but recovered to go forward and be handily placed in 4th. Gave ground rapidly from the 350m, and eased out. Unacceptable performance. Vet  Lame Off fore leg.
Moderately away from a tricky gate, raced 2 wide in midfield, improved from near 900M, 3 wide on turn, finished off strongly to score.
Jumped well from a wide draw, positioned 2 wide in 2nd, same position on turn, kept on well in straight but couldn't hold off the winner final 50M, stayed on for 2nd.
Bumped start, raced at rear on rail, similar position on turn, kept to inside after straightening, made good progress until checked near final 100M to get 3rd.

Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, 3rd on turn, improved from near 600M, kept on well after turning in, peaked near 250M, just stayed on evenly thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slightly slow out, raced 4 lengths back on rail in midfield, there to turn, in traffic early in straight, made some progress when clear thereafter. (Lost right hind plate after the 500M.)
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths or so back on rail, easy run throughout, angled out after turning in, finished off evenly without threatening.
Away with them, raced 2 wide 4 lengths or so back in midfield, improved from 750M, wider turning in, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 9 lengths back at rear, still 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off evenly.
Began well, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back in 5th, similar position on turn, finished off one-paced.
Moderately away from a wide draw, taken back to race 8 lengths back at rear, improved after 900M, 3 wide with cover in midfield turning, taken wide in straight and finished off one-paced.
Began fairly, raced behind midfield throughout, no daylight and checked early in straight, showed no progress when clear thereafter.
Bumped start, raced at rear, still well back on turn, taken widest in straight, showed no response, eased final 100M.
Raced at tail throughout, never a threat.
Slowly away, recovered to take the lead, peaked and headed on turn, emptied early in straight, finished tailed out. (See Racing Incidents.)

Well placed off the pace on rails, quickened well under pressure to take charge over 150 metres out, won cozily.

Broke well from the widest gate, pressed forward to travel 2-wide just off the leader at the Rock, sustained run to join the lead briefly turning for home, drifted out under pressure early in straight and soon headed.
Settled in midfield, commenced move leaving the Rock, just over 2L back in 5th turning into straight but baulked early on, fought on steadily inside final 200 metres.
Moderate start, travelled mainly in 5th within 3L of pace, fought on steadily in straight.
Jumped fairly, settled in rear of midfield, produced good late impression inside final 200 metres.
Ridden to hold prominent position early stages, dropped to rear of leading pack in 7th coming out of back straight, produced late impression in the run to line. (Blood in trachea)
Shared pace early, taken 2L back in 4th shortly afterwards, found nothing under pressure from a similar position into straight.
Moderate start, worked his way forward to assume lead on rails at the Rock, saved ground turning for home, unable to sustain effort and overhauled inside final 200 metres. (Lame next day)
Broke well, quickly taken back towards the rear, remained in similar position to straight, kept on steadily without quickening.
Never a danger.
Began awkwardly losing considerable ground, never seen with a chance.
Lacked early pace, soon dropped towards the rear, never a factor.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M to score.
At rear, trapped 3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 250M for 2nd.
Hard ridden to obtain the box seat, not suited by the fast pace, lack room 300M, ran on well when clear.
Hard ridden to share the lead and clock fast sectionals, hung on until 150M flattened.
At back along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M, held up and checked 150M.
Pressed forward, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the fast sectionals, flattened 200M.
Midfield, 2 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, checked 450M, made some ground 200M.
Pushed forward to share the lead, 2 wide, clocked fast sectionals, soon emptied 250M.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 2 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, flattened in straight.
Hard ridden to keep up at rear, suited by the fast pace, lack room 4-2, made minor ground when clear.
Failed to muster, trapped 3-4 wide, never a factor.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide, dropped off 300M.
Taken back from a wide draw, 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, gradually improved around the field from 700M, ran on strongly to score by a short head.
At rear, 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, under heavy pressure when the pace quickened 700M, improved nicely rounding the Home Turn, ran on strongly for 2nd, missed by a short head.
Pushed forward to take the fence and led alone at slow sectionals, challenged 600M, kept on gamely until weakened latter stages, hung on for 3rd.
Raced midfield, 3Ls behind the leader 3 wide without cover, improved around the field along the back straight to take the lead, battled on strongly until weakened final stages, hung on for 4th.
Raced midfield, 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, under heavy pressure when the pace quickened 700M, ran on gradually.
Ridden forward to occupy the box seat, under heavy pressure when the pace quickened 700M, kept on one pace to the line without threatening.
Sent forward to park outside the leader, unable to find extra when the pace quickened 700M, dropped off rounding the Home Turn.
At rear, improved around the field from 800M 4 wide without cover, weakened rounding the Home Turn.
Raced midfield, 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, gradually improved around the field from 700M, weakened soon after straightening.
Prominent early, dropped off badly from 700M when the pace quickened.
Sharp break, immediately snagged to back of midfield 1 off with cover, shuffled to last trio 600m, shifted 4 deep for progress 450m & driven, very wide home turn, quickened to lead 130m.
Pace from gate, soon eased to race midfield on rail, shuffled back 600m, in pocket on turn, driven in pursuit 300m quickened to press lead 130m, held.
Awkward start & outpaced, raced last 1 off, shifted out 800m & advanced 4 deep to 3rd 500m, hard-ridden 400m, all out to vie for 2nd 250m, tapered, held 3rd.
Started ok, restrained to midfield 1 off with cover, shuffled back 600m, shifted out & driven 300m, kept on for minor late gains.
Slow start & taken behind near rear, overraced 1 off with cover near rear, 3 wide for progress 700m, ridden 650m, boxed on evenly under drive.
Tardy from gate, raced last pair on rail, shuffled to last 750m, switched 3 deep 600m & bustled forward a spot, forced 4 deep 500m, very wide on turn, last & hard-driven 300m, stayed on late.
Rousted at break, advanced to vie for lead 1 off 1420m, led outright 1200m & to rail 1080m, 2L up & driven 300m, soon emptied & headed 130m, faded.
Broke ok, lacked toe & raced rail near rear, shuffled to last trio 600m, plugged on dourly.
Broke ok, parked 1 back 1 off, niggled 650m, shuffled back & bustled 520m, driven into stretch, plugged on tamely.
Driven from gate & contested lead 3 deep into 1st turn, settled 2nd 1 off no cover, under pump 500m, hard-ridden & emptied 200m.
Speed to lead, crossed to rail, eased & shared lead until headed 1200m, shuffled to 1 back on fence, ridden at turn, found nil & weakened.
Even break, ridden to get into forward spot, settled fore of midfield 1 off, baulked 600m, travelled into race strongly, clicked up 400m, hit lead 150m, just held on.
Jumped OK, outpaced early, settled beyond midfield 1 off, pushed on 500m, into clear 250m, finished willingly, just missed.
First to break, ridden to hold lead on rail, led at solid sectionals, ridden 350m, claimed 150m, battled on well.
On back foot at start, settled beyond midfield on rail, ridden 550m, held up 420m, hanging on turn, stayed on.
Broke on terms, pushed to go forward but unable to match early speed, settled midfield 1 off, ridden 380m, switched over heels 220m, one-paced to line.
Very awkward jump, quickly clear last, stayed off rail, held together until 270m, charged home.
Slightly slow to begin, ridden along to get into a forward spot, settled just fore of midfield on rail, niggled 600m, hard ridden 400m, weakened late.
OK beginning, eased to near rear on rail, held together on turn, railed through, ridden 300m, limited room 200m, never a threat.
Jumped well, bustled to press forward, settled 2nd 1 off, pulling slightly, ridden 370m, faded meekly.
Broke strongly, pushed but unable to cross, settled fore of midfield 3 deep, ridden 440m, effort short-lived.
Away well, ridden vigorously to press forward, up to 3rd 4 deep 850m, ridden along 600m, widest on turn, dropped out.
Jumped well, bustled & near speed 6 deep 1000m, eased shortly afterwards but trapped 5 deep, eased for cover 700m, under riding 500m, dropped out quickly.
Slow to jump, settled to race in behind midfield, 3L behind long the rail, kept on strongly and secured the win in final strides.
Raced in midfield, 1-3/4L off along the rail, ran on fairly well but couldn't hold off winner inside 50M and settled for 2nd.
Raced towards the rear, 5L behind 2 wide, made ground steadily and kept on nicely for 3rd.
Rolled forward but trapped wide, allowed to improve and led at 800M, headed passing 100M but ran on.
Niggled forward and settled in one-off one-back position, sat 1-1/4L off, kept on one paced to the line.
Travelled in midfield, 2-3/4L behind 2 wide, slight dashed early then kept on one paced to the line.
Raced at the rear, 5L behind the lead along the fence, improved slightly and kept on to the line.
Eased and raced at the rear, 6-1/4L behind 2 wide, made minor ground in the Straight and ran on.
In worse than midfield, 4-1/4L behind 3 wide without cover, made ground until bumped at 150M, one paced thereafter.
Pushed forward and settled to race in box-seat, sat about 1L off, ridden from 700M, weakened badly at 250M.
In midfield and 2 wide initially but failed to maintain and dropped to behind midfield at 800M, found nothing in the Straight.
Ridden forward and sat outside the lead, dropped off gradually in the Straight.

Bumped and unbalanced shortly after start, then outpaced, dropping to rear along fence. Steadied passing 880m, well back entering straight before surging through between horses to win in final strides.
Began fairly, outpaced, dropping to rear but kept away from fence. Started forward move approaching 800m, took home turn 4-wide, kicked forward to lead 100m before run down on wire.

Jumped with field then ridden to find cover but trapped 3-wide in midfield. Pushed forward passing 700m, 3-wide outside leader turning into straight, joint leader from 250m before run down close home.
Began OK, allowed to stride forward, settling in midfield. Switched out turning for home, taken very wide in straight, loomed alongside leaders passing 200m but no extra close home.
Began well, shared early pace before settling in box seat 2L from leader. Kept tabs to 400m but unable to get clear running until 200m, then awkwardly placed 100m before finishing well.
Restrained shortly after start and taken in behind horses, settling behind midfield in one-off position. Vigorously ridden from 500m to go forward, widest into straight, boxed on gamely.
Crowded out on jumping and shortly after crowded out again, dropping to last. Tailed field to straight, switched out to centre track passing 200m, finished off strongly.
Jumped well, sliding forward gradually before settling one-out, one-back. Well held till home turn when put under pressure, no clear run top of straight, switched out 180m and ran on steadily.
Broke well, ridden to hold forward position settling outside hindquarters of leader. Put under pressure from 500m, hit front 300m but unable maintain momentum and swamped close home.
Bumped and badly unbalanced shortly after start, then taken to fence, settling behind midfield. Hard ridden from 500m but ran into tight space passing 200m and steadied. One-paced after that.
Jumped well but not pushed, settling along fence 4L from leader. Got shuffled back approaching final turn then badly held for run from 450m to 150m. Ridden hands and heels final 50m.
Allowed to stride forward from widest draw, taking lead passing 1600m before crossing to fence 1450m. Travelled keenly in the lead setting fast tempo. Ran out of fuel passing 300m and faded.
Began fairly, sent forward to race prominently, shared lead turning in, kept on well in straight to score by a nose.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, shared lead turning in, kept on well in straight but just beaten by narrow margin.
Began awkwardly, positioned on rail behind midfield, there to turn, made good progress in straight to get 3rd.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, similar position on turn, angled out in straight and finished off well to make frame.
Began well, positioned a length or so back on rail, saved ground throughout, kept to inside after straightening, finished off evenly.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, taken wide turning in, made some headway in straight.
Away well, raced 2 wide in 5th, there to turn, kept on well until peaked near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail to turn, made some headway in straight.
Jumped well, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with no cover in 3rd, peaked on turn, finished off one-paced.
Slightly slow out from gate 10, raced at rear throughout, failed to close off in straight, never a threat.
Moderately away from a tricky gate, raced 2 wide, 6 lengths back at rear, wider on turn, emptied early in straight and eased.
Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in early, raced 3 wide in midfield, weakened gradually from 500M, emptied early in straight and eased.
