Settled in rear of midfield on rails, commenced move on top of home bend, switched out for a run entering straight, ran on under pressure to assert authority inside final 100 metres.
Settled inside the leader on rails in back straight, shared the pace rounding home bend and hit the front turning for home, unable to sustain effort and headed inside final 200 metres.

Amongst leaders early, taken back to settle just off the pace in 4th on rails, switched out to challenge entering home straight, held every chance over 200 metres out but unable to sustain effort closing stages.
Settled in last few, saved ground on rails entering home straight, angled out for a run shortly after straightening but unable to make any impression inside final 200 metres.

Prominent early, carried backward on rails early in back straight, recovered to forward of midfield approaching home bend and sustained headway to reach 4th some 2L back turning in, found no extra inside final 200 metres. (Bled)
Taken back to 3-wide in last few from a wide gate, unable to quicken under pressure in straight.
Slow into stride, settled in last few on rails, saved ground turning for home, forced to steady 300 metres out, one-paced.
Settled in 5th within 3L of pace, shifted out wide for a run entering home straight, fought nothing.
Ridden positively from the widest gate, circled the field on stables bend before taken in for one-out-one-back position 1100 metres out, dropped out tamely from approaching 400 metres.
Settled in last spot from a wide gate, trailed the field to straight, went past well-beaten runners.
Mainly in midfield to straight, raced keenly early in far side, folded up quickly.
Moderate start from a wide gate, raced wide in midfield around first bend and most of way down back straight, dropped out of contention from home bend.
Pressed forward from a wide gate to gain narrow lead upon turning into back straight, joined rounding home bend before dropped away quickly in home straight. (Blood in trachea)
Jumped fairly from a wide gate, raced wide mainly in midfield far side, dropped away quickly from approaching home straight.
Took rail and lead easily, clocked advantageous slow sectionals, drifted away 300M to score.
Hard ridden forward, sat just off the leader 2 wide, favoured by the slow tempo, just held ground for 2nd.
Settled in box seat, benefited by the slow sectionals, ran on well for 3rd.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, little dash 200M.
Pushed to keep up in midfield along the fence, not suited by the slow pace, dashed well 250M.
Eased at start, took rail at back, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Behind midfield, 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, ran on fairly.
Walked out of barriers, detached, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 150M.
At back, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, no turn of foot.
Eased back, took rail, not suited by the slow pace, no dash.
Trapped 3 wide in midfield, harmed by the slow pace, never nearer.
At rear, trapped wide, never a factor.
Jumped well, settled off the speed, angled out on straightening, challenged strongly at 200m and gained control final 50m.
Jumped smartly and ridden along to lead, travelled comfortably mid-race, under strong hold home turn, let down strongly but overpowered final 50m.
Pushed along to settle behind leaders, asked for effort at 400m and battled strongly to the line.
Pushed hard early from wide gate to settle outside leader, issued challenge passing 400m, tried hard before weakening late.
Ridden along early to race on speed, attempted to challenge on straightening but one paced to the line.
Jumped well, settled midfield, took time to get balanced early straight before finishing strongly.
Bumped and unbalanced at start, pushed early, wide without cover from the 900m, one paced in straight.
Slow to begin, settled at rear, made some ground along rail in straight.
Settled midfield and travelled keenly mid-race, one paced in straight.
Began fairly, settled midfield, pushed along home turn but unable to quicken.
Eased back from wide gate, bumped at 700m and 300m, one pace to the line.
Fractious in gates, jumped awkwardly, raced keenly midrace, bumped at 700m and 300m, did not run on, Rider question re performance.
Began awkwardly, taken back, crowded 1150m and the raced keenly, made no impression in straight.
Taken back at start, widest on straightening, did not run on.
Pushed on to lead & to rail 1050m, raced 1.5L clear, extended to 2L up & driven turning in, kicked on & stretched away, pushed out right to wire, in command.
Smart start, eased back to midfield 1 off with cover, caught in traffic on bend, ridden turning in & shifted centre track, strong headway to 2nd 120m, closed but no threat.
Pace to vie for initial lead, to rail 1150m, settled 1 back 4th & niggled 700m, 3rd & ridden 400m, progress to 2nd 210m, all out & lost a place closing stages.
Fair start, raced rail midfield, driven into stretch, kept on evenly.
Broke ok, mid-rank early & trapped wide no cover, rolled on to 2nd 1 off no cover 1050m, niggled 600m, driven turning in, vied for minors until emptied 150m & tapered.
Started well, taken back near rear 1 off with cover, niggled 850m, driven 430m, some progress & edged centre, stayed on for moderate headway.
Broke in front rank, eased to fore of midfield 1 off with cover, niggled 500m, driven turning in, found little, plugged on.
Slow start & bustled to race rail near rear, ridden turning in, kept on one pace.
Snagged back at start to rail last pair, niggled 550m,driven into stretch, plugged home past beaten rivals.
Taken back to last pair 1 off, ridden final turn, boxed on past beaten horses.
Started ok, caught wide & advanced 3 deep no cover to 3rd 900m, under pressure 5th & driven 400m, outpaced & faded.
Taken back from wide gate, 3 wide with cover back of midfield, a touch keen, switched widest 550m, driven turning in, plodded tamely.
Steadied start to near tail 3 wide with cover, niggled 700m, widest into stretch & driven, weak effort centre track.

Placing: UR
Comment: Outpaced early, raced 3 wide midfield, lost action 400m, eased down & unseated rider.

Very awkward start, natural speed to get into forward spot, settled fore of midfield 1 off, niggled 900m, short of room 600m, hampered 450m, sprinted strongly soon after, hit lead 240m, challenged but fought gamely to score.

Jumped in at start, up into 3rd on rail early, shuffled back into midfield position on fence by 1500m, pushed off rail 580m, hampered slightly 400m, chased willingly, almost on terms 120m, never quite passed.
Even break, eased to near rear, at tail on inside from 1880m, nudged 970m, driven strongly shortly afterwards, stuck to inside on straightening, made steady ground to just grab 3rd late.
Jumped well, natural speed to cross and lead, passed 1700m, settled 3rd on rail, clicked up 500m, checked 400m, back to rail 250m, even finish.

Pinged the gates, initially 2nd 1 off but keen & allowed to stride, hit lead 1700m but still slightly keen, passed 860m but quickly retained equal lead, held together until 350m, headed 240m, battled to line.
Bumped and then checked out of gates, eased, hampered slightly 1800m, keen soon after, settled near rear 1 off, pulled 3 wide & improved 1050m, ridden 4 deep 500m, sprinted well, one-paced last 200m.

Bumped at start, eased, got head up 2000m & again 1900m, eventually settled beyond midfield on rail, back to 2nd last 900m and ridden, pushed along 400m despite limited room, checked badly 300m, struggled to pick up again.
Slow to begin, stuck 3 wide no cover midfield at 1st turn, strode forward into 2nd 1 off, hit lead 800m but joined again soon after, ridden 440m but quickly beaten off.
Squeezed out badly at start, back to beyond midfield on rail, overracing slightly, near rear 1 off for majority, 3 deep & improving 950m, ridden 500m, widest into straight, couldn't go on last 200m.
Eased from gates, back to clear last, pulled into midfield position 3 deep no cover by 1550m, keen throughout, up into 3rd 970m, ridden 650m, faded tamely.
Bumped significantly at start, fired up and hard to settle thereafter, settled just beyond midfield 1 off, ridden along 1150m, asked for effort 400m, no response.
Raced in worse than midfield, sat 4L behind a long the fence, closed off strongly once cleared at 200M and scored.
Travelled in front of midfield, sat 3L off 2 wide, progressed steadily and hit the line well to take 2nd.
Rolled into box-seat, sat 1-1/2L off the lead, ran on well but unable to hold off first two.
Pushed forward to take the rail and led by 1/2L, kept on going until caught passing inside 50M.
Raced in worse than midfield, sat 5-3/4L behind 2 wide, continued to improve and finished off well.
Travelled in midfield, sat 3-1/2L behind along the fence, kept improving and hit the line well.
Slotted into midfield, travelled 4-1/2L behind the lead 2 wide, improved steadily in the Straight.
Ridden forward, trapped 3 wide until cleared and shifted in to race outside the lead near 700M, emptied near 100M.
Eased and travelled at tail end, 6-3/4L behind 3 wide and without cover, failed to make any ground.
Sent forward, settled to race in one-off one-back position and sat 2L off, dropped off gradually in the Straight.
Slow to jump, race at the rear 5-1/2L behind along the fence, continued to make ground until checked after 100M.
Always at the rear, never competitive.
Jumped fairly but had the natural speed to roll forward, settling less than 2L from leader. Burst through between horses passing 400m, took lead 300m, then held off late challenge for narrow win.

Broke well, ridden to hold forward position settling 2.5L from leader along outer fence. Switched in passing 400m to get clear running, threw out strong challenge final 200m before going down narrowly.
Jumped with field but unable handle early pace, dropping to behind midfield along outer fence. Picked up momentum 400m after a couple of reminders and finished strongly to grab minor placing.
Quickly into stride, holding outside rail position while sharing early lead before settling a half length behind leader. Pushed forward to lead passing 400m, overtaken 300m but kept on gamely.

Jumped OK, ridden to obtain forward position while edging closer to outer fence, settling 1L behind and inside leader. Battled on gamely while laying out under pressure from 400m before turning one-paced final 100m.
Broke well but unable handle early pace, dropping to behind midfield one-away from outer fence. Boxed on fairly under hard riding final 400m.
Broke well, surged forward to lead narrowly on settling but kept away from outer fence by another runner. Set good pace to 400m when overtaken and gave ground gradually.
Got off OK, pressed forward between horses, settling 4L from leader. Kept tabs on pacemakers but only one-paced when put under pressure final 400m.
Stumbled shortly after start, dropping to rear. Remained at the rear till running past tired horses final 200m.
Bumped start, pushed forward, settling between horses 4L from leader. Kept on fairly before giving ground final 200m. Lame left front leg.
Broke OK, ridden along to hold midfield position while edging closer to outer fence. Put under pressure passing 400m but only one-paced.
Crowded for room on jumping then outpaced, dropping towards rear. Found little when put under pressure final 400m.
Began fairly, outpaced, dropping towards rear along outer fence. Remained at rear and never competitive.
Began OK but soon outpaced and last on settling. Trailed field thereafter and finished tailed out.
Sat behind midfield early stages, taken to 3-wide back straight, move up to be 2Ls off the pace 400M, quickened to lead 250M, well on top final 100M.
Reserved near the rear early and middle stages, crept closer home turn to be 5Ls off the pace 400M, stayed on well between runners, got up 2nd near line.
Positively ridden, 3-wide no cover chasing leaders 1st turn then eased back for cover, within striking distance 350M, kept finding the line well but couldn't peg back winner, lost 2nd near line.
Outpaced by rivals early stages, settled down behind midfield 4-5Ls back, ran on well down outside early straight but peaked on its run 200M and held ground over final stages.
Jumped well from draw 1 to be tracking leaders along the fence, lacked room inside 300M-200M, ran on mildly towards the line.
Along the inside 3-4Ls back in midfield, held up for clear running until 200M but lacked the needed response when clear, held by leaders to on the run home.
Taken across from wide draw, held up in rear early stages, moved closer passing 1000M, brought wide to challenge in straight, ran on moderately and well held by leaders.
Urged forward, sat just off the pace, kept on same speed in straight, faded 100M.
Settled down behind midfield 5Ls back, soon ran into traffic on straightening, had no clear run until closing stages, not properly tested.
Held up in midfield 4Ls behind leader, not quickened when placed under pressure inside 350M, never threatened.
Lacked early speed, travelled further back than usual, detached in last from 1000M and only got past a couple of beaten horses in straight. (Jockey: didn't travel well at any stage.)
Soon emerged as leader, set steady pace to straight, headed 250M, weakened noticeably thereafter. (Lame RF)
From draw 12 caught wide no cover throughout the race, chased leaders to straight, weakened badly 250M.
Began fairly before striding forward to grab box seat 2L from leader 1300m. Got split 400m out before grinding forward under hard riding to share victory on the line.
Broke well, pressed forward to lead on settling, crossing to fence 1350m. Kicked ahead on straightening, kept finding under intense pressure final 300m to dead-heat for first place.
Outpaced soon after jump, settling towards the rear but away from fence. Switched wide around turn, taken even wider in straight, ran on strongly to grab minor placing.
Began well, taken to fence, settling 4L from leader. Stayed on rail around turn, took inside run in straight, boxed on steadily to finish closest at line.
Jumped with field, taken in for cover, settling along fence behind midfield. Checked passing 900m but stayed on fence, edging forward in straight despite racing in restricted room.
Got off OK, ridden along to hold midfield position between horses. Taken wide on entering straight and ran on fairly.
Outpaced early, dropping to rear but away from fence. Taken to centre track on straightening and ran on steadily without looking dangerous.
Jumped well, pressed forward, settling one-out, one-back. Not much room top of straight but only one-paced when clear final 300m.
Steadied soon after start to find cover but last on settling. Trailed field to straight, switched wide, and ran on fairly.
Jumped well, rolled forward settling 1L behind and outside leader. Took closer order around home turn but under pressure soon after straightening and gave ground gradually.
Pressed forward from an outside draw to get forward position, settling 3-wide without cover 2L from leader. Urged forward turning for home, stayed in contention to 200m before tiring.
Steadied soon after start and shifted across behind runners, settling at rear but wide. Swung wide into straight but only one-paced under hard riding.
Slow into stride, dropping towards rear along rail. Remained well back to straight, plodded home.
Pushed forward from widest draw to get midfield position but 3-wide 4L from leader. Remained wide around home turn and spent force soon after straightening.
Cruised forward to be handily placed 4th, on the fence. Loomed up 300m, and pulled away at 200m. Needed no urging from that point, cruised to the line and eased late.
Eased out to sit midfield, on the fence. Kicked clear of the main group and had no threats for 2nd, making slight ground on winner late as he eased.
Eased forward early, settling worse than midfield, one off the fence. Wider on the turn. Looked gone 200m, but showed good turn of foot late to get 3rd on the line.
Eased back early, settling 3rd last on the fence. Battled on steadily in the straight, and just run over for 3rd late.
Cruised up early, midfield and 1 off the fence. Wider on the turn and ran solidly in the straight, just missing a place.
Taken out and early leader, before being crossed 900m. Plugged on fairly in the straight, and swamped late.
Fractious in the barrier, reared on jumping and lost plenty of ground. Lost all hope from there, and did well to end up midfield.
Wide no cover early, before pushing to lead at 1000m. Led early in the straight, but peaked at the 200m, and faded out from that point.
Dropped back from the wide draw early to sit at the rear of the field, 2-3 wide. Plugged on fairly and picked up a couple of slower ones late.
Pressed forward early, eventually settling 3rd, 1 off the fence. Faded under the stick early in the straight, and only went to the line under minimal urging late.
Slow to begin and settled worse than midfield, on the fence. Never responded to the stick, and plugged to the line without ever threatening in the straight.
Pressed to sit midfield. Unsettled on heels for a considerable distance from the 1100m. Widest on the turn, but didn't have a lot left in the tank and was eased late.
Sat midfield, 3-4 wide, and taken wider without cover 1000m. Did respond to pressure early in the straight and only pushed hands and heels, before easing late.
Stuck 4-5 wide with no cover in midfield early, before eventually getting a spot forward of midfield, 3wd with no cover at 900m. Never pushed out, and eased a long way from home.

Ridden after moderate start, settled in forward of midfield in 5th on rails about 3L off the pace, angled out for a run entering straight, ran on under pressure to just get up on line.
Worked forward from the widest gate to take up running on rails at the 1000 metres, kicked over 2L clear on straightening, soon flattered and caught in the shadow of the post.
Jumped well, ridden before settling one back behind leader in 3rd on rails while racing keenly down back straight, similar position turning in, ran home one-paced.
Jumped well, settled one off the rails in 4th just over 2L back, one-paced from a similar position into straight.
Ridden early before settling in midfield in 6th 2-wide, ran home one-paced.
Lacked speed, settled in rear of midfield 2-wide, made no impression in straight.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, steadily recovered to reach rear of midfield on rails 800 metres out, met minor interference coming onto home bend, found nothing in the straight.
Jumped fairly, improved steadily to join the leader at the 800 metres, unable to sustain effort in straight.
Jumped awkwardly and crowded losing ground, trailed the field most of way, only went past well-beaten horses inside final 200 metres.
Always well behind, never seen with a chance.
Slightly slow out, always well behind, found nil in straight.
Moderate start from a wide draw, settled wide in rear of midfield, swung widest into home straight, soon faded.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2-3 wide, pace good, progressed steadily 400M to score.
Hard ridden to occupy a midfield spot, 2 wide, pace good, made steady ground 300M for 2nd.
Settled in prominent spot, 2 wide, pace good, ran on well for 3rd.
Eased back, 2 wide, pace good, progressed steadily 300M but without threats.
Pushed to obtain box seat, pace good, flattened 250M.
Pushed to keep up in midfield along the fence, pace good, held up and checked 250M, made some ground when clear.
Took rail and lead easily, hung on until 200M weakened.
At back along the fence, pace good, no dash.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, pace good, lack turn of foot in straight.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, pace good, never improved.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, pace good, emptied 300M.
Trapped 3-4 wide in midfield throughout, dropped off 500M.
Jumped well, settled off pace, tracked up behind leaders at home turn, challenged strongly at 300m, held off all challengers.
Slow to jump and settled at rear, made ground home turn, raced greenly in straight when finishing strongly.
Crowded at start and settled behind leaders, ridden along home turn to issue challenge, battled strongly to the line.
Jumped well, pushed to lead and travelled comfortably, challenged at 200m but no match, weakened late.
Settled midfield relaxing nicely, improved along inside home turn, finished well, awkward on heels late.
Taken back shortly after start to obtain cover, pushed along passing 500m, awkward home turn and ran home well, hampered at 200m.
Settled at rear, commenced wide run passing 450m, closed steadily in straight.
Settled off pace, steadied at 900m, pushed along 500m but failed to run on in straight.
Fast out to share lead, brief challenge on straightening, weakened out of it from 200m.
Taken back at start, always rearward and made no impression in straight.
Pushed to go forward, lay out 1000m when racing greenly, continued hanging out when racing wide without cover  must trial.

Placing: TNP
Comment: Reared as start was effected dislodging rider, took no part.
Lacked early toe & bustled, sat midfield 1 off with cover, shifted 3 deep 700m & bustled forward to lead 570m, 2L clear home turn, driven to wire, in command.
Started well, vied for early lead, relented to 2nd 1 off no cover 1400m, shuffled back & ridden 550m, chased centre track in stretch, battled to 2nd close home.
Awkward but speed at break to lead, headed 1500m & trapped handy 3 wide no cover, rolled to lead 1060m, to rail 1000m, headed 570m, shifted out home turn, fought on, tapered late.
Slow start, restrained to rail near tail, progress & shaken up turning in, quickened & stormed late to share 3rd.
Smart start, raced handy 4th with cover, shuffled back & niggled 600m, ridden on turn, kept on evenly.
Broke well, eased back to 1 off with cover near rear, advanced a spot 1000m, bumped to 3 deep 850m, wide forward move 700m to 4th 500m, scrubbed & no extra, tapered in run.
Broke well, soon outpaced & bustled on rail to race 1 back, shuffled back a spot 1000m, overraced 880m, shuffled to midfield & under pump 550m, kept on one pace.
Slow start & crowded, dropped to rail & bustled early, sat back of midfield, checked off heels to 1 off & bumped rival 850m, 3 wide advance from 630m, wide home turn, plugged one pace.
Snagged back at start, midfield on fence & overraced 1200m, checked off heels 850m & shuffled back, under pump 500m, swung widest into stretch, boxed on evenly.
Taken behind from wide to race near tail , 2nd last & uner pump 500m, outpaced plugged on tepidly.
Broke ok, won pace battle to lead 1400m & to rail, steadied & headed 1060m, raced 1 back, driven into stretch, faded in run.
Restrained from widest to race at tail, ridden 430m, found little.
Jumped OK, eased from wide gate, settled 3rd from last 1 off, ridden 400m, widest entering straight, charged home to score.
Even break, natural speed to settle handy, niggled 750m, settled 4th on rail, asked for full effort 310m, hit lead 120m, just run down late.
Pinged gates, pushed through to lead, sat 2nd on rail, pushed 320m, hit lead 250m, grabbed 120m, weakened late.
Broke evenly, unable to muster, settled just fore of midfield 1 off, nudged 350m, stayed on to line.
Squeezed out at start and unable to muster, quickly back to 2nd last & outpaced, hard ridden from 800m, stuck to inside in straight, finished willingly.
Jumped evenly, on heels 970m, back to beyond midfield 1 off, clicked up 450m, switched to outside 200m, found line evenly.
Slightly slow to break, eased to beyond midfield, travelled comfortably throughout, into clear 250m, checked again 210m, one-paced to line.
Jumped well, nudged forward but unable to match other speed, settled fore of midfield 1 off, pushed 350m, no extra.
Broke well, eased across, settled 3rd 1 off, pushed from 350m, faded.
Very fast jump, pushed on to lead, 0.5L lead 700m 1 off, fast sectionals, under riding 320m, weakened badly from 200m.
Slow to break & quickly outpaced, long last by 700m & niggled, ridden entering straight but never a factor.
Missed start slightly, ridden along to push through, settled midfield on rail, ridden along 350m, switched inside, faded.
Raced in front of midfield, sat 2-1/2L off the lead 2 wide, ran on strongly to take the prize.
Slotted into box-seat, sat 1-3/4L behind the lead, ran on nicely but couldn't hold off winner in the final strides.
Ridden forward to take the rail and led by 3/4L, headed passing 100M but ran on to take 3rd.
Awkward start, settled to race in midfield, 3-3/4L behind 2 wide, made marginal ground without threatening.
Raced in midfield, 3-1/2L off along the rail, kept on one paced to the line.
Pushed forward to race outside the lead, sat 3/4L off, kept on until emptied passing 150M.
Travelled at the rear, 6-1/2L behind 3 wide with cover, made slight ground in the Straight.
Eased and raced in worse than midfield, 5-1/4L behind 2 wide, made minor progress.
Raced slightly in front of midfield, 3-3/4L off 3 wide without cover, not quickened to challenge, did not threaten.
Crowded start, then taken back to race behind midfield, 5-1/2L behind along the fence, kept on one paced to the line.
Raced at the rear, 7-1/2L behind 2 wide, not a factor.
Ridden early then eased to race in behind midfield, 6L behind 3 wide with cover, found nothing in the Straight.

Began well, pressed forward, settling 4L from leader in one-off position. Took closer order approaching home turn, urged forward passing 550m, 3-wide into straight, kicked ahead 200m and went to the post unchallenged.
Jumped with field, ridden to hold rail inside early leaders before settling in box seat 2L from leader. Got clear rails run on straightening and kept on strongly to the line.

Bumped shortly after start, allowed to stride forward at own pace, settling behind midfield in one-off position. Urged forward passing 500m, swung wide entering straight, ran on strongly to grab minor placing.
Jumped OK, sliding forward one-out to midfield position at first turn. Improved around home turn, ran on steadily in straight to be closest at finish.
Steadied soon after start and taken to rail, settling towards the rear. Left fence 500m, swung wide into straight, ran on steadily down centre track to finish just behind place-getters.
Began well but restrained to find cover, dropping to last. Improved position slightly along back stretch, put under pressure from 500m, finished off nicely down centre rack.
Pressed forward from an outside draw to lead passing 1500m before crossing to fence 1250m. Set good pace to straight when overtaken, but kept on gamely to 100m before being swamped.

Began well, ridden to hold forward position settling 2L behind leader at first turn. Urged forward from 600m to eyeball leader, hit front 400m, overtaken 300m, kept on gamely until swamped final 100m.
Steadied soon after jumping and taken in for cover, settling towards rear in one-off position. Put under pressure turning for home but only one-paced in straight.
Jumped well, ridden to hold rail, settling 5L from leader. Travelled comfortably to home turn when lost position, then one-paced in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, taken to fence, settling midfield. Came under pressure and lost position home turn, took inside run in straight but found little under hard riding.
Steadied soon after start and shifted across behind horses, settling at rear. Given reminder passing 600m before being eased out of race from 500m. Bled from both nostrils.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths or so back, same position on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to score.
Moderately away from a tricky gate, taken back to race 6 lengths back on rail at rear, there to turn, made very good progress in straight to get 2nd.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, positioned in 4th, taken wide after turning in and made good progress early in straight, peaked and headed final 50M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 6 to 7 lengths back at rear, improved on turn, taken wide in straight and made good progress to make frame.
Bumped start, positioned a length or so back on rail, easy run on turn, finished off evenly in straight without threatening.
Bumped start, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 6 lengths back at rear, same margin back on turn, made minor progress in straight, never a threat to the first few.
Average to begin, raced 3 lengths back in midfield, taken wide after turning in, finished off evenly in straight.
Slowly away, recovered to race 2 to 3 lengths back on rail in 5th, saved ground on turn, finished off one-paced.
Crowded out start, raced at tail, checked near 500M, made minor progress after turning in, in traffic near final 100M, not tested thereafter.
Away with them, raced prominently, travelled keenly in the middle stages, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 200M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well, unable to slot in early, sent forward to take the lead near 850M, headed final 200M, dropped off tamely thereafter. (Blood in trachea.) (See Racing Incidents.)

Taken back from a wide gate for inside run, soon picked up to midfield along rails, obtained a clear run shortly after straightening, quickened well to assert authority 200 metres out.
Jumped fairly, with leaders 3-wide most of way to straight, fought on dourly closing stages to claim 2nd.
Began from a wide gate, travelled very wide in midfield, quickened well in straight while shifting in, just failed to reach 2nd.
Driven along from the one draw, settled in 2L 5th on rails, baulked for a run early in straight, made no impression in the closing stages.
Attempted to make all, kicked over 1L clear early in straight, unable to sustain effort and swamped inside final 200 metres. (Bled)
Settled in forward of midfield in 6th, gained nearer the pace rounding home bend, shifted wide for a run entering straight, kept on same pace without quickening.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, soon dropped further back to just worse than midfield, saved ground on inside turning for home, kept on at the one pace.
Moderate start, soon recovered to midfield 3-wide, kept on under pressure early in straight but could find no extra closing stages.
Soon taken back from the widest gate travelling 3-wide, kept on steadily without quickening in straight.
Ridden along from a wide gate travelling wide behind midfield, made short-lived effort into straight, made no impression closing stages.
Began well from a wide gate, raced in prominent 4th and wide most of way before swinging wider at the home turn, folded up quickly in straight.
Soon came to join the leaders, dropped out tamely after straightening.
Slowly away losing a lot of ground at the start, remained well behind throughout.
Soon dropped to last few, never seen with a chance.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, closed off strongly 400M to score.
At back, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
Hard ridden forward, took rail, led at fast sectionals, hung on well until 200M overhauled, ran on for 3rd.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 350M.
Eased to sit in midfield along the rails, benefited by the fast pace, made ground 350M.
At back, 3 wide, suited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M.
Eased to rear, 3 wide, benefited by the fast pace, made steady ground 300M run ended 100M.
Pushed early, behind midfield, 3 wide, suited by the fast pace, lack room 4-2, ran on ok when clear.
Eased to rear, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, no dash.
Behind midfield along the fence, favoured by the fast tempo, no progress.
Pushed to obtain box seat, not suited by the fast pace, ran on well until 200M emptied.
Pressed forward, sat 2 wide, not suited by the fast pace, out of fuel 350M.
At rear, never competitive.
Jumped well, pushed along to lead, relaxed nicely mid-race, held off all challengers in straight for tough win.
Settled behind leaders, pushed to improve along inside making home turn, challenged strongly at 400m but unable to get past the winner.
Eased back early to settle towards rear, commenced to move closer passing 800m, urged to challenge making home turn, fought hard entire straight, weakened late.
Jumped smartly and settle behind leader, improved to join leader on straightening and fought gamely to the line.
Settled at rear, commenced forward move around runners passing 600m and issued challenge on straightening, battled gamely but commenced to weaken on run passing 200m.
Sharp start, crossed to race 3 from rail, rolled to lead 450m, hard-driven 250m & drew 1L clear, kept on under pressure.
Fast start, stalked speed, niggled along & under pump 400m, closed off to 2nd late, held at wire.
Speed break, raced close u in 2nd, niggled along, edged out to 3rd 500m, driven & regained 2nd 300m, out-kicked & to 3rd 50m, kept on evenly.
Broke ok, to rail & niggled along near rear, raced greenly, driven 350m, switched in 250m & quickened, kept on soundly without threat.
Awkward start, niggled near rear 1 off stands fence, bustled for progress 400m, hard-ridden 300m, kept on evenly.
Sluggish start & raced at rear near outside fence, shifted in & advanced a spot 520m, under pump 450m stayed on for moderate headway.
Started with others, raced mid rank, niggled along 700m, driven 500m, boxed on one pace for pressure until tapered closing stages.
Missed break, rolled forward to back of midfield 500m, shifted in 500m, driven 400m, one-paced centre track.
Quick to stride, soon led on rail, under pressure & headed 450m, weakened thereafter.
Good break, raced midfield, niggled 500m & forced inward, fund nil for pressure & faded.
Smart start, settled midfield centre track, ridden under pressure 500m, found nil & struggled in weakening run.
Broke well, parked midfield, ridden 550m, soon emptied & faded.
Slow break, recovered to fore of midfield centre track, shaken up 500m, found nil & faded weakly.
Tardy start, soon rousted & to tail 520m, centre track & eased 300m when no extra.
Slightly awkward break, settled just beyond midfield 1 off, improved between runners 700m, into clear 400m, sprinted strongly, hit lead 150m, ran right through line.
Jumped well, eased from outside gate, settled near tail 3 wide no cover, ridden 1200m, improved shortly afterwards, driven 500m, widest into straight, unleashed strong sprint but no match late.
Away OK, eased to near tail, settled near rear 1 off, back to last 830m, ridden 480m, on heels 350m, sprinted hard shortly afterwards but couldn't get there.
Alert at jump, natural speed to press forward, settled just behind leaders on rail, railed through strongly from 600m, ridden 450m, kicked away, run down 150m, battled on.
Broke OK, eased to near rear, settled beyond midfield on rail, saved ground into straight, short of room 400m, sprinted OK when clear.
Slow to muster, ridden into beyond midfield position 1 off, ridden 800m, back near tail 500m & pushed, one-paced to line.
OK break, eased to settle midfield on rail, slightly keen, into clear 420m, almost on terms with leader 230m but never quite passed, faded.
Missed break, straight back to last on inside, passed a runner 830m, hugged rail, clicked up 400m, finished evenly.
First to jump, stuck 3 deep & pressed on, settled 3rd 3 wide by 900m, clicked up 520m, faded, hampered 250m, eased down.
Good start, pushed to get into handy spot, settled just behind speed 1 off, niggled 900m, driven 780m, lost place, battled away until eased down last 100m.
Jumped on terms, natural speed to press forward, settled midfield 1 off, niggled 900m, driven 650m, improved out wide, badly hampered 320m, dropped out.
Quick into stride, couldn't muster sufficient early speed, stuck 4 deep early and eased, settled midfield 3 deep, niggled 900m, lost place 750m, last on straightening, eased from 250m.
Good break, kicked up to lead by 1200m on inside, 0.75L lead by 800m, drifted out on corner, ridden 600m, joined & headed 460m, dropped out.
Jumped well, pushed towards lead, settled 2nd 1 off, pushed deeper on track by inside horse 650m, under riding 480m, faded quickly.
Sent forward to take the rail and led by 3/4L, ran on nicely and held on to score by 1/2L.
Travelled just in front of midfield, 4-1/4L off 2 wide, ran on gamely and hit the line well.
Settled in one-off on-back position, sat 2-3/4L off, one paced in the Straight but ran on for 3rd.
Eased and taken to the rail in behind midfield 6-1/4L off, improved steadily and finished off well inside final 150M.
Rolled forward and took up box-seat, sat 2-1/2L off the lead, kept on one paced going to the line.
Bounded at start and lost ground, at rear 9-1/2L behind 2 wide, awkward to heels at 400M, made good ground and closed off strongly.
Jumped slowly, raced at the rear, 9-3/4L behind 2-3 wide with cover, made good ground in the Straight.
Travelled in front of midfield, 4L off 3 wide with cover, remained one paced in the run home.
Raced behind midfield, 5-3/4L behind 2 wide, kept on one paced going to the line.
Eased and raced near the tail, sat 8-1/4L behind 3 wide with cover, made slight ground.
Sent forward and raced outside the lead, sat 3/4L off, one paced and then faded gradually near 200M.
Rolled into midfield 4-1/2L off along the rail, showed slight dash after 300M, but emptied approaching 150M.
Raced slightly behind midfield, 5-1/2L behind 3 wide with cover, showed nothing in the Straight.
Pushed and raced prominently, but trapped wide and without cover, gave ground before entering the Straight.
Quickly into stride before being eased to sit along fence 4L behind leader. Not asked for an effort until passing 500m, surging forward along the rail to hit the front 50m out and drawing clear.
Pressed forward to lead on settling, drawing 2L clear at first turn and then setting good pace. Kicked further ahead on straightening and kept finding under pressure before being caught 50m out.
Broke well, taken to fence and settled 6L from leader. Travelled comfortably to home turn, swung wide entering straight, ran on steadily to finish only 1L from winner.
Jumped OK then shifted across behind horses from an outside draw to settle at rear in one-off position. Taken very wide on straightening and ran on strongly down centre track.
Restrained shortly after jump and shifted in to fence behind runners, settling towards rear. Shaken up on turning for home, ran into a tight space 350m, switched in and ran on steadily.
Began well, allowed to stride forward settling one-out in midfield. Switched out entering straight and ran home steadily.
Allowed to stride forward at own pace, dropping behind midfield in one-out position. Taken wide on entering straight and ran home fairly.
Pushed forward from an outside draw to hold midfield position but trapped wide without cover. Put under pressure turning for home but only one-paced in straight.
Slow into stride, trailing field to first turn before improving position along fence, settling behind midfield. Took closer order turning for home but only one-paced in straight.
Shifted across behind runners soon after start, dropping to last around first turn. Improved position around home turn but only one-paced in straight. Lame left front leg.
Restrained shortly after jumping and shifted across behind runners, settling towards rear in one-out position. Switched out turning for home, taken to centre field on straight but only one-paced.
Jumped well, pressed forward taking box seat 2L from leader. Set off after leader on straightening but ran out of steam 200m out and faded.
Ridden to obtain forward position, settling one-out 2L from leader. Came under pressure turning for home and gave ground steadily in straight.
Jumped well, ridden forward, settling 4L from leader in one-out position. Hard ridden from final turn but found little and faded.
Began well to be 4th, never far, moved strongly into contention 450M, soon led entering straight, pressed by runner-up 150M but found extra in reserve. First horse to complete the 4YO Classic Series.
Taken across behind runners, sat last over 10Ls off the pace early stages, ran on well final 400M between runners, pressed winner final 150M but always held.
In mid-pack, caught 3-wide first turn before improving into a 2-wide position passing 1150M, tried hard but not finishing pace of first 2 inside 200M, kept on to hold 3rd.
Tracked leaders early, shuffled back to midfield in middle stages, saved ground on the inside throughout, finished off honestly but comfortably held by first 2 over final 200M.

From draw 14 taken across behind runners, given a waiting ride towards the rear, 3-wide home turn, last at 400M and no clear run until 300M, stayed on well to go 5th near line without threatening top 4.
Dropped back to near the rear 9Ls off the pace early, brought widest 600M and rousted, stayed on without troubling first few.
Slow to begin but soon improved to a midfield position along the rail, shuffled back to near the rear 900M, got past a few over final 400M but at no stage a threat to leaders.
Restrained in midfield along the 2-path, difficult to settle 1400M, in touch turning home but kept on same pace only, soon out of contention.
Overcame wide draw with ease, raced outside the pace in first half, remained close up turning in but couldn't go on passing 250M.
Behind midfield, switched to 3-wide entering back straight, bustled along 500M but not quickened, crowded for room 350M and ended up last, passed some tired runners late. (Lame next day.)
Held up in midfield early stages, shifted out 3-wide 1100M and moved up to join leader 800M, no extra 300M and dropped away.
Soon led, took them along slowly early stages, pressed by rival 1300M, tracked leaders home turn, gave way 350M.
Slow to begin, restrained behind midfield, proved difficult to settle, 9th at 400M, failed to quicken when driven.
Awkwardly away, chased leaders 3-wide without cover, injected pace and took up the lead from 1300M, run ended passing 250M, weakened to last.
Broke well to lead on settling and crossing to fence. Headed passing 800m but retook lead 400m, kicked 2L clear passing 200m, then kept finding to hold off late challenge.

Restrained on jumping and shifted across behind horses, settling at rear in one-out position. Stayed at rear until straightening for home, taken to centre field and ran on strongly while laying in to miss narrowly.
Began fairly, then ridden to hold fence behind midfield. Got close to heels turning for home, took inside run in straight and ran on strongly between horses to grab minor placing.
Began OK then ridden to hold one-out position in midfield. Switched out to issue challenge on straightening and ran on strongly to just miss a placing.
Pressed forward from an outside draw, racing wide without cover before taking lead passing 800m. Headed passing 400m but stayed in contention until swamped final stages.
Bumped and unbalanced on jumping, then ridden to make up ground, racing wide without cover 1L from leader. Stayed in contention up the straight before being swamped final stages.

Sat down in starting gate before start. Unbalanced on jumping but grabbed box seat on settling. Stayed behind pace to straight but unable close gap. Had graze on left hind cannon, small cut outside left hind heel.
Began well, pressed forward, settling one-out 1.5L from leader. Put under pressure turning for home but only one-paced in straight.
Shifted in shortly after start to find cover but trapped 3-wide behind midfield on settling. Lost position around home turn and boxed on one-paced in straight.
Hard ridden from widest draw to get forward position before finding cover but 3-wide in midfield. Given reminders on straightening but raced greenly and one-paced final 200m.
Outpaced and last on settling. Stayed at rear until 200m before running past beaten horses.
Bumped and unbalanced on jumping then hard ridden to get forward position, settling 1/2L from leader in one-off position. Kept battling in straight until running out of fuel final 200m and fading.
Began awkwardly, bumped and lost considerable ground before pushing forward between horses behind midfield. Taken wide in straight but found little under hard riding.
Slow into stride, settling at rear along rail. Improved position around home turn but run ended on straightening and faded.
Fairly away and settled midfield, 1 off the fence. Clear run in the straight, and lead at 200m. Pushed all the way to the line, but easily in.
Sat forward of midfield, 5th/6th and 3 wide no cover. Wider in the straight and ran strongly to the line, closing margin on winner late.
Worse than midfield, 3-4 wide with limited cover. Wider on turn, and stayed well early in the straight. Good turn of foot last 100m to nab 3rd.
Settled worse than midfield, 3 wide. Battled strongly in the straight and finished well.
Pushed up to be well placed 3rd, on the fence. Stayed on solidly in the straight, just peaking late.
Dropped back early to sit in the last pair. Widest on turn, and ran home solidly without threatening a place.
Pressed forward to sit 2nd, 1 off the fence. Only 1 paced in the straight.
Eased out and settled towards the rear of the field, 1 off the fence. Stayed on fairly, but never a threat.
Pushed up to be handily placed 4th, 1 off the fence. Led briefly 300m, before peaking and eased late.
Checked on jumping and got back. Only fair to the line and made no impact.
Settled forward of midfield, on the fence. Lay in from the 600m. Only fair in the straight, and not pushed out last 200m.
Dropped back early to sit last. Fading when striking interference at 200m. Only plodded on late. Jockey questioned.
Settled forward of midfield, 1 off the fence. Faded quickly in the straight, and eased late.
Pushed out early to lead. Dropped back quickly from 300m, and eased out late.

Settled in rear, circled the field rounding home bend, widest turning in, ran on well down the centre of the track to snatch victory final strides.
Soon took up running, obtained rails run coming onto stables bend setting a healthy early pace, kicked over 1L clear turning into home straight only to be collared nearing finish.

Pressed forward from a wide gate, settled 2-wide within 3L of pace in 3rd or 4th, similar distance from leader when 7th on top of home bend, saved ground turning in and ran on steadily under pressure.
Settled some 3L back in 4th on rails, gained closer on pace 600 metres out, soon came to challenge after straightening, fought on steadily without threatening.

Moderate start, travelled in rear of midfield, tightened briefly 600 metres out, commenced move rounding home bend, came within 3L of pace in midfield entering straight, ran on steadily without threatening.

Worked his way forward from a wide gate to reach 2nd spot after the first 500 metres, swamped past by quickening runners coming out of back straight, just over 2L back in 6th coming onto home turn, one-paced while hanging in.
Moderate start, travelled towards the rear on rails, switched out for a run entering straight, produced good late impression.
Waited with, given reminders 400 metres out, ran on well down the centre of the straight.

Travelled in 5th in forward of midfield racing keenly early in back straight, took off approaching the Rock to join the leader around home bend, unable to sustain effort and folded up quickly after straightening.
Raced wide in midfield, took closer order leaving the 700 metres, prominent 3-wide rounding home bend, found nil in straight.
Towards the rear, short-lived effort rounding home bend, found nothing in straight.
Settled in midfield on rails, tightened coming onto stables bend, gave ground at home bend.
Hard ridden to occupy box seat, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Pushed forward, just off the leaders 2 wide, ran on well for 2nd.
Hard ridden to obtain a midfield spot, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, made steady ground 300M for 3rd.
At back, 2-3 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M.
Pushed to take rail and led at fast sectionals, hung on until 200M flattened.
Behind midfield, 2 wide, favoured by fast pace, made minor ground 200M.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, suited by the fast tempo, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden early, behind midfield, checked badly 800M, ran on fairly in straight.
Hard ridden early but not muster, at back on the rails, never improved.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, not suited by the fast pace, out of fuel 250M.
Hard ridden throughout to keep up with the field, one paced in straight.
Never a factor at rear.
Jumped fairly, settled nicely off pace, took some time to wind up in straight but finished powerfully final 100m.
Pushed along early from wide gate to settle outside leader, quickened nicely at 300m to take lead, overpowered late.
Jumped fairly, settled behind leaders, issued challenged on straightening and fought strongly to the line.
Taken back early to settle towards rear, travelled nicely mid race, ran on strongly in straight.
Bumped at start, settled midfield, wide without cover from 700m, tried hard in straight.
Settled towards rear, ran on fairly in straight.
Taken back at start, wide on straightening and worked home strongly.
Bumped heavily at the start, pushed along to take lead early stages, under pressure on straightening and weakened final 200m.
Heavy bump at start, settled behind midfield, finished fairly.
Settled leaders back, under pressure home turn and weakened final 200m.
Began awkwardly and settled at rear, awkwardly placed at 500m, made no impression in straight.
Settled midfield, hampered near 500m, one paced in straight.
Even break, eased to beyond midfield on rail, held together until 380m, railed through, pulled off inside 280m, picked up strongly last 150m, comfortable win.
Broke well, handy & to rail 1570m,raced 1 back, niggled & edged 1 off 450m, ridden & closed on turn, led 250m, kicked on, emptied 50m & headed close home.
Awkward jump, eased to beyond midfield 1 off, shuffled back 600m, pulled 3 deep and ridden 450m, found line strongly late.
Started ok, restrained to midfield 3 wide no cover, under pump 500m, hard ridden wide on turn, boxed on centre track for minor inroads.
Broke ok, sat rail midfield, 4th & driven turning in, outkicked & no extra when lost action late.
Started ok, overraced midfield 1 off with cover, niggled 650m, shuffled back on turn, driven 300m, plugged on one pace.
Moderate break & bustled mid pack, soon advanced to 2nd 1 off no cover 1250m, niggled 800m, under pump 550m, pushed 3 deep 450m, all out turning in, tapered tamely.
Hopped up at start, straight down to rail, settled last on inside & slightly keen, clicked up 320m, stayed on, short of room near line.
Awkward start, speed to grab easy lead, to rail 1250m & set tempo under restraint, nudged 1.5L clear 450m, driven turning in, all out & headed 250m, faded.
Fast break & front rank, soon settled 1 off 1 back, niggled 520m, soon in retreat, found nil in home stretch, eased when beaten.
Away on terms, eased to near rear 1 off & keen, under a drive 650m and pulled deep, improved to 4th 500m, widest into straight, eased from 250m.
Sluggish start, raced last trio three wide with cover, advanced 1050m to back of midfield 750m, ridden along 450m, last & widest into stretch, outpaced.
Smartly away, eased into trailing position on inside, clicked up 320m, short of room shortly afterwards, pushed into clear 250m, sprinted strongly, hit lead final few strides.
Jumped fast, driven hard, led 1000m 1 off, clicked up 400m, fought on strongly, just caught.
Broke well, settled 3rd 1 off & keen, ridden 320m, stayed on.
Fast break, straight on lead, settled 2nd on rail, railed through to joint lead into straight, ridden 280m, boxed on.
Awkward start, niggled, natural pace into midfield spot on rail, pulled off rail 280m & ridden, still green but stayed on well.
On back foot at start, ridden into fore of midfield position 1 off, ridden 450m, one-paced to line.
Fast getaway, eased to beyond midfield 1 off, under riding 370m but blocked soon after, switched over heels 250m, found line very late.
Slightly slow start, back beyond midfield but trapped 3 deep, improved quickly 500m & under a ride soon after, widest into straight, faded late.
Very awkward start, quickly into beyond midfield spot, slightly keen, ridden 500m, sprinted through on inside, one-paced.
Awkward break, quickly back to last, quite keen, pulled wide & ridden 320m, never a threat.
Eased from gates, back to near rear 3 wide, then 1 off, improved 500m, under riding 400m, never in it.
Started well, lost forward position quickly, back to 3rd last on rail 800m, gave ground 550m, weakened.
Niggled forward and sat in front of midfield, 2-1/2L off 2 wide, pulled away at 100M to score comfortably by 1-1/2L.
Raced just behind midfield, 5-1/4L behind 2 wide, continued to improve and finished off gamely to take 2nd.
Eased to the rear, sat 7-1/4L behind along the rail, hampered at 400M, made nice ground, finished off strongly.
Travelled in front of midfield, 4L off 2 wide, kept on going and closed off well for 4th.
Slotted in behind midfield, 6-3/4L behind 2 wide, made good ground and finished off nicely to the line.
Travelled in one-off one-back position, sat 1L off the lead, kept on one paced going to the line.
Raced just front of midfield, 2-3/4L off along the rail, took charge of rider at 500M and continued to be awkward, closed off well when balanced from 200M.
Sent forward and led by 1/2L in a 2 wide position, kept on until approaching 100M when emptied and headed.
Slow to jump, checked at 1000M, remained at the rear along the rail 10L behind, kept on one paced home.
Pushed at start, in behind midfield initially but wide, taken to rear of the field before turn, did not improve.
Awkward start, raced in midfield 5-1/4L off along the fence, checked at 400M, showed nothing. (Heart irregularity)
Pushed hard, settled to race inside the lead along the rail, dropped off badly in the Straight. (Heart irregularity)

Broke well but eased to find cover, settling along rail towards rear. Unhappy with pace and set off passing 1000m, circling field to take over 650m out, increasing lead with every stride to win by wide margin.

Began a little awkwardly, ridden to find cover, settling behind midfield between horses. Checked off heels 1000m, losing position. Began forward move passing 600m, 4th into straight, boxed on gamely for quinella spot.
Jumped OK, not pushed, settling one-out 6L from leader. Got shuffled back along back stretch to near last entering straight before running on strongly to grab minor placing on the line.
Pressed forward from outside draw to lead initially before easing back 2L from leader at first turn. Shaken up 650m to give chase to new leader and kept on gamely before being swamped final 100m.
Vigorously ridden from jump but didn't muster, settling 3-wide in midfield. Lost position approaching final turn before running on steadily in straight to finish behind place-getters.

Ridden to obtain forward position settling on rails 3L from leader. Got shuffled back as rivals moved forward approaching turn, stayed on rail in straight and ran on steadily without looking dangerous.
Restrained on jumping and shifted across behind horses, settling at rear. Trailed field to 800m when urged to go forward. Swung wide into straight and boxed on one-paced.
Jumped OK, ridden to hold rail position, settling ahead of midfield. Lost position turning for home, taken to centre field on straightening, boxed on fairly.
Away nicely, shared early pace before settling 2L behind leader at first turn. Kept tabs on leaders to home turn when came under pressure and gave ground gradually

Pressed forward from widest draw, sharing early pace before taking lead passing 1400m, crossing to fence 1150m and slowing pace. Overtaken passing 650m but kept on gamely to 200m before running out of steam.
Began fairly, outpaced, dropping towards rear along fence. Switched out turning for home, take very wide in straight, found little under pressure.

Steadied on jumping and shifted across behind runners, settling at rear. Began forward move 1000m, racing 3-wide without cover, getting to within 3L of leader at 500m when run ended. Eased down final stages.
Began well from a wide draw, raced prominently, took the lead near 600M, kept on well after turning in and scored.
Fast into stride, positioned 1-2 lengths back on rail, easy run to turn, angled out near 400M, finished off well to get 2nd.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, improved from near 700M, 2nd on turn, difficult to ride in straight, not able to test properly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, similar position on turn, kept to inside after straightening, made some progress to make frame without threatening.
Bumped start, positioned on rail in midfield in the early stages, kept 4 lengths or so back on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Moderately away from the widest gate, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, made minor progress in straight.
Away with them, positioned on rail behind midfield in the early stages, angled out from 1000M and improved gradually thereafter, 4 wide no cover on turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Taken back to race at rear, severely hampered near 800M, slightly improved in the middle stages, 4 wide turning, made some progress in straight. (Lost left front plate.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, slightly improved from 800M, 3 wide on turn, taken widest in straight and finished evenly. (Horse hit on nose by rival's whip near 50M.)
Bumped start, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Moderately away, raced behind midfield early, carried wide with no cover from near 1000M, difficult to settle thereafter, 4 wide on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away from a tricky gate, sent forward to take the lead, headed near 600M, weakened gradually thereafter, emptied early in straight, eased final 150M. (Disappointing performance.)

Jumped fairly, restrained behind the slow pace in 3rd or 4th on rails, soon came under pressure to challenge after straightening, fought on dourly to assert authority near the finish.

Taken back from the widest gate, took closer order to wide in midfield down the back straight, held similar position rounding home bend before quickening from 5-wide into straight to hit the front briefly over 200 out, soon headed.
Settled well behind, commenced run wide rounding home bend, ran on to hold some chance over 200 metres out, unable to sustain effort close to home.

Moderate start, soon recovered to forward of midfield while difficult to settle in the slow pace, drifted further back towards the rear rounding home bend, briefly baulked early in straight, fought on under pressure without threatening.
Held up in midfield on rails, shuffled back rounding home bend, baulked for a run after straightening, finished off race nicely.
Wide behind midfield early, improved steadily down far side to join the slow pace-setter passing the 1200 metres, unable to sustain effort in straight.

Sent forward from a wide draw to join the lead in slow early pace, shifted back to about 2L off halfway out, renewed effort amongst the leaders upon straightening, unable to sustain run and faded inside the final 200 metres.
Travelled towards the rear on rails, did not find much room most of way in straight.
Broke well from a wide draw, settled wide in better than midfield, 4-wide amongst the leaders entering the straight, unable to sustain effort inside final 200 metres.
Soon took up running on the rails setting a slow early pace, quickened up pace briefly approaching the halfway mark, folded up quickly shortly after straightening.
Moderate beginning, settled in last few, became last rounding home bend, weakened after straightening.
Very slow away, pushed to obtain a midfield spot 2 wide, dashed strongly 250M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Settled in midfield along the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, blocked 400M, dashed strongly when clear.
Pushed to take rail and led at advantages slow sectionals, soon overhauled 400M, ran on well for 3rd.
At back, 2 wide, unleashed strong finishing efforts 300M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide just off the leader, enjoyed the slow sectionals, led 400M, flattened 150M.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, benefited by the slow sectionals, just held ground in straight.
Settled in midfield along the rails, harmed by the slow tempo, held up most straight, dashed strongly to the line.
Settled in more prominent spot, 2 wide, just held ground in straight.
Eased to rear, 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 300M, lack room 150M.
Very slow away, at back along the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, little dash 200M.
Checked at start, 3-4 wide at rear, harmed by the slow tempo, lack turn of foot.
Eased to rear, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 300M, eased down 150M.
Eased back, trapped 3-4 wide, not suited by the slow pace, never improved.
Trapped 3 wide in midfield throughout, emptied 400M.
Jumped well, pushed along to settle off pace, worked home strongly final 300m to hold off all challengers.
Allowed to find midfield position, urged to improve passing 500, got going final 150m and finished strongly.
Jumped smartly, sent forward to settle behind leader, ridden along to challenge passing 450m, hit the front at 100m before being overpowered late.
Fast out and lead easily, challenged at 200m, fought on well.
Crowded at start and settled worse than midfield, commenced to improve passing 400m, checked near 150m when making ground, balanced up to finish nicely.
Jumped fairly and settled towards rear, ran home nicely down middle of track.
Jumped well and pushed to hold position forward of mid, ridden along to improve passing 500m, checked at 150m when challenging strongly and then easy to the line.
Jumped well and settled worse than mid, commenced to improve passing 400m, hampered at 150m.
Settled midfield, ridden along passing 500m and quickly under pressure, one paced to the line.
No early pace and settled at rear, pushed along passing 600m and finished off fairly.
Settled midfield, awkwardly placed passing 400m, did not run on.
Settled worse than mid, failed to run on.
Slow to begin, settled towards rear and failed to run on.
Fast out and settled on speed, under pressure 500m and steadily gave ground.
Broke well, soon nudged along 4 wide no cover fore of midfield, worked to join lead 3 wide at 680m, soon eased to 3rd, driven turning in, gradual progress to lead at line.
Fast start, buffeted, rousted to lead & to rail 1020m, kicked on turning in & soon 2L clear, emptied final 100m, pipped last stride.
Ducked right & bumped rival but speed at break, raced handy 1 off with cover, ridden turning in, kept on evenly to nick 3rd at wire.
Speedy break & bustled to sit 2nd 1 off no cover, pressed leader 700m, outpaced & 1L back turning in, soon 2L back , one-paced in run, lost 3rd on nod.
Bumped start & nudged along, recovered to sit 1 back on rail, niggled 500m, hard-driven 350m, kept on same speed until tapered final 100m.
Sluggish & bumped at start, soon improved to midfield on rail, overraced 900m to 600m, ridden 350m, shifted out 200m, stayed on moderately.
Slow start, raced near rear on rail, ridden 400m stayed on for moderate headway.
Tardy break & bustled to race midfield 3 wide with cover, under pump 500m, one-paced in tepid stretch run.
Slow start & bumped rival, driven at tail, soon 2/3L detached, some headway home turn & shifted out in stretch, stayed on past beaten rivals.
Sharp start, restrained to midfield 1 off with cover, niggled 500m & outpaced, hard-driven turning in, found nothing in tame run home.
Moderate break, soon niggled & raced midfield 3 wide with cover, outpaced turning in & driven, struggled in run home.
Broke well, taken back from wide gate to race near rear 1 off, shifted wide & driven 450m, found nil, plodded on centre track.
Broke on top, ridden to lead on rail, travelled strongly on speed, 1.5L lead 600m, held together into straight, ridden 350m, kicked clear.
Slightly slow break, vigorously driven into forward spot, settled 3rd on rail, ridden 600m, stayed on.
On back foot at start, under heavy drive to push forward, settled midfield on rail, under pressure 500m, on heels 200m, ran on strongly again late.
Began well, stumbled shortly after start, back to beyond midfield on rail, clicked up 400m, found line powerfully but too late.
Fast to begin, couldn't match early speed, settled fore of midfield 1 off, ridden 500m, short of room & badly hampered 320m, checked again 140m, found line again late.
Slightly slow start, ridden through to midfield spot 1 off, shifted 3 deep 600m, improved quickly, ridden 350m, hanging left shortly afterwards, weakened.
Away well, eased to beyond midfield spot 3 deep, ridden 750m, under vigorous drive 500m, made ground very late.
Awkward start, eased to near rear 3 deep, under drive 600m, made some ground in straight, died on run 100m.
Outpaced from gates, back to distant last, railed through and ridden 350m, making ground when on heels 150m, severely checked, eased.
Broke on terms, eased to beyond midfield 1 off, driven 500m, outpaced.
Quick jump, early natural speed to gain forward spot, ridden along from 1070m, settled fore of midfield 3 deep, improved into 3rd 600m, ridden 380m, dropped out.
Even break, ridden to press forward, settled 2nd 1 off, under pressure 400m, faded meekly.
Settled to race in box-seat, sat 3L off the lead, took lead passing 150M, held off a late challenge to score by a short-head.
Travelled in behind midfield before the turn, 8L behind 3 wide with cover, improved position when rounding turn, made good ground and finished off gamely for 2nd.
Pushed forward to take the rail and led by a nose, maintained lead until headed at 150M but ran on for 3rd.
At the rear throughout, raced 9-1/2L behind the lead 2-3 wide, made impressive ground and kept on going to the line.
Settled in fore of midfield, sat 3-1/4L off the lead 2 wide, kept on going and finished off well to the line.
Raced at the rear, 8-1/4L behind 2 wide, made nice ground and kept on gamely to the line.
Travelled just in behind midfield, 5-3/4L behind along the rail, continued to make ground steadily, ran on well to the line.
Very awkward start and shifted out, settled to race in one-off one-behind position 2L off, slight dash before 200M then flattened.
Sent forward and settled to race outside the lead after being trapped wide initially, found no extra passing 200M.
Pushed early but showed no speed, slotted in just behind midfield, 6-3/4L off 3 wide with cover, kept on early and then flattened after 200M.
Began only fairly, raced at the rear, 8-1/4L behind along the rail, kept on only one paced to the line.
Checked at start, then taken closer to the rail from the wide draw, in behind midfield, 6-1/4L behind 2 wide, kept on until flattened at 250M.
Rolled forward into a prominent spot early, dropped to midfield when bumped at 1000M, 6-1/4L behind but wide, not competitive.
In midfield, 5-1/4L behind 2 wide, checked at 1000M, awkward to heels at 600M, showed nothing and finished tailed out.
Hard ridden to lead on settling before crossing to fence 800m and slowing pace. Kicked 2L clear passing 300m and kept finding under pressure to hold off late challenge.
Broke well, restrained and taken in for cover, settling at rear in one-out position. Taken to centre track on straightening for home and finished strongly.
Eased shortly after start and shifted across behind runners, dropping to last. Not much room top of straight, shifted out 200m to get clear running and finished strongly.
Broke well, ridden to hold rail before checked 800m but holding box seat. Set off after leader on straightening but only one-paced final 200m.
Jumped OK, held, settling behind midfield in one-out position. Switched out turning for home and boxed on fairly without looking dangerous.
Began well, sharing early pace before being taken 3-wide without cover passing 800m, 3L from leader. Pressed on to get within 2L of leader on entering straight before turning one-paced.
Ridden to get forward position, settling along rail 3L from leader. Switched out turning for home, looked chance passing 200m before run ended.
Bumped and unbalanced start before pushed forward to race one-back, one-out. Kept tabs on leader to straight when came under pressure and faded.
Got off with field but not pushed, settling behind midfield along rail. Switched out turning for home to get clear running but found little under pressure.
Tracked leader 2-wide, took over 350M, fought on strongly in the lead and courageously held off persistent challenge of rival overs final 250M.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, ended up near the rear in a steadily run race, 4Ls to make up 400M, closed off strongly to be nearest at the line.
Never far off behind the steady pace, loomed 300M, closed off well but couldn't run down winner, lost 2nd just before line.
Soon took rail position tracking leader, had every chance passing 350M, battled on well to hold 4th.
In 5th place 3Ls behind leaders, in touch with main rivals turning in, kept on steadily to the line but was always held.
Restrained in midfield, 3-wide and left with no cover from 1200M, tried hard but couldn't get closer to leaders over final 300M.
Slow to begin, settled down behind midfield 5Ls behind leader in a steadily run race, kept on one pace final 400M, well held by leaders.
Switched off to the rear after the start, given a waiting ride along the rail, failed to make appreciable ground passing 400M, no threat to leaders.
Taken back to the rear, 7Ls off the pace middle stages, made no real progress turning in, still last 200M and only went past some weakening rivals late stages.
Towards the rear 3-wide, travelled only fairly and had to be shaken up 900M, 5Ls back and widest of all turning, failed to improve and never featured as a threat.
Held up behind midfield 4Ls off the steady pace, kept on fairly 400M-200M, no extra late stages.
Allowed uncontested lead, set steady pace to straight, fought on briefly when challenged 350M but weakened badly from 200M. (Jockey : unable to offer explanation for disappointing performance.)

Broke well, taken in for cover, settling between horses towards the rear. Patiently ridden to straight, turned in behind horses. Got split clear run passing 200m and accelerated strongly to win drawing away.
Jumped with field, pressed forward but kept wide 3L from leader. Took home turn 4-wide, rolled forward on straightening to look a chance 200m but unable match winner closing stages.

Quickly away, leading field on settling before crossing to fence 1100m. Set good pace to straight, kicked 2L clear passing 300m. Started to shorten stride 100m but managed to hold on for minor placing.
Began fairly, not pushed, settling behind midfield in one-out position. Improved position approaching turn before finishing strongly between horses to be closest at finish.
Jumped OK, restrained and shifted across behind horses, settling at rear but away from fence. Made some progress around home turn before finishing strongly down centre track.
Began fairly, taken to fence, settling towards rear. Not asked for an effort until passing 400m, ran on gamely between horses up the straight.
Jumped with field, pressed forward but away from fence 2L from leader. Got shuffled back turning for home but kept on gamely in straight without looking dangerous.
Pressed forward from an outside draw, racing wide without cover 2L from leader. Continued to race wide around home turn, kept on gamely to 200m before tiring.
Ridden along early to look for cover but kept 4-wide mostly, covering extra ground around turn. Boxed on one-paced in straight.
Crowded and badly unbalanced on jumping before pushed forward to hold rail 3L from leader. Improved position around turn, kept on gamely to 200m before tiring.
Began OK but not pushed, striding along at own pace to hold rail behind midfield. Took rails run on straightening and made some headway until running out of steam passing 100m.
Hampered start, pushed forward, grabbing rail 4L from leader. Lost position around home turn, one-paced on straight.
Began awkwardly, losing ground and dropping to last. Trailed field thereafter and never competitive.
Jumped well, pressed forward to race outside leader on settling. Gave ground abruptly soon after straightening for home and eased down final 200m.
Handily placed 4th, 4L off the leaders early. Smoked the pipe until 300m before beginning a run. Tackled leader at 200m and kicked clear late, easily in under full riding late.
Midfield, on the fence early. Wider on the turn looking for a run. Came home solidly. Ran strongly from 150m, nabbing 2nd in the last 20m.
Pushed forward early to set pace in a group of 3 horses, 4L clear of the rest. Tackled by winner 200m. Paddling late, but had just enough in the tank to hold 3rd by the barest margin.
Began well, but eased back early and eventually settled worse than midfield. Wider on the turn, and produced a strong run to the line late.
Towards the rear of the field early, on the fence. Ran well in the straight, and picked off plenty of horses in the run home.
Cruised forward and settled around midfield, 1 off the fence. Ran solidly, but slightly 1 paced in the straight and swamped late.
Cruised across from the wide draw to settle midfield, 2-3 wide. 1 paced in straight, and no threat.
Dropped back early to sit at the tail of the field. Checked and badly off heels when horse in front broke down 750m. Ran solidly without threatening in the straight.
Taken up early and raced forward with breakaway group, slightly keen. Didn't have much left in the tank in the straight, and faded out from 350m.
Dropped back early to sit in the last couple at the back. Only fair in the straight.
Bounded on jumping, jockey lost iron and got back to tail of the field. Never involved.
Taken forward early, to sit with breakaway leaders, 3 wide no cover. Only settled to a trailing position at 900m. Use up, and had nothing left in the straight. Jockey questioned.
Stumbled on jumping and got back worse than midfield, 3-4 wide limited cover. Never in it. Vet  Roarer.

Placing: PU
Comment: Broke down at 750m.
