Held up towards the rear early stages when slowly run, took off upon straightening onto far side to assume lead passing the 800 metres, just held off fast-finishing second to claim the race.
Settled in last few, commenced move entering home straight, finished off race strongly down the centre of the track.
Slightly slow out, settled well behind and waited with, switched out to challenge entering straight, ran on well down the centre of the track to be nearest at finish.
Restrained alongside slow pace-setter, still held 2nd when pace quickened passing the 800 metres, one-paced under pressure in straight and swamped for minor placing late.
Jumped well from the one draw, set slow early until headed and became 3rd halfway out, one-paced in the run to the line. (Tactic questioned)
Held up on heels of leader in 3rd on rails, hampered and shuffled back to midfield 600 metres out, saved ground turning for home, fought on steadily without threatening.
Began well from the wide-ish draw, restrained in midfield of slowly run race, quickened under pressure with the pace to maintain position around home bend, sustained headway in the run to the finish.
Restrained behind midfield early stages, made swift progress around slowly-run field from the 900 metres to reach 3L 4th on the bend, made no impression in home straight.
Broke well, settled just off the slow pace 2L back in 4th, quickened with pace when 5th leaving the Rock, found nothing under pressure in straight.
Soon taken well behind, took closer order to 9th out wide in back straight, circled the field to reach 6th on top of home bend, found nothing under pressure in straight. (Lame)

Moderate start, soon recovered to better than midfield in 5th and then 6th in the slow first half of the race, shuffled back to behind midfield when pace quickened approaching the Rock, found nothing in the run home.
Moderate start, travelled in rear of midfield on rails, dropped towards the rear when pace quickened approaching the Rock, no further impression.
Took rail and lead easily, drifted away 300M, ran on well to score.
Midfield along the fence, dashed strongly 300M for 2nd.
At back, trapped 3wide, unleashed strong finishing efforts 300M despite negative racing situations.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, just held ground in final stages.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 2-3 wide, held ground in straight.
Slow away, behind midfield on the rails, little dash 200M.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, 2 wide, dashed well 200M.
Eased back, took rail, lack room 300M, dashed well when clear.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, ran on until 200M weakened.
Awkward away, pushed to keep up in midfield, trapped 3 wide throughout, emptied 250M.
At back, 2 wide, no progress.
At rear along the fence, hung out badly and checked at bends, never a factor.
Jumped well and lead easily, travelled well and kicked strongly on straightening to win easily.
Settled leaders back, pushed along home turn, tried hard but no match for winner.
Raced on speed, pushed along home turn, tried hard but no match for winner.
Settled midfield, travelled nicely home turn, ran home fairly.
Jumped well, settled behind midfield, widest on straightening and finished strongly.
Settled midfield, asked for effort on straightening, one paced to the line.
Commenced awkwardly and unbalanced, hampered at 1000m and settled at rear, urged along home turn and ran home well.
Settled behind midfield, ran one paced.
Check at start and lost ground, one paced in straight.
Pushed early to settle off pace handy, asked for effort on straightening but no response.
Unbalanced at start and settled at rear, failed to run on in straight.
Settled midfield, under pressure at 600m and gradually faded.
Tardy start, bustled to settle back in pack 1 off with cover, switched wide & stoked up 500m, very wide progress to lead 160m, kicked clear, eased down last strides.
Good break, led 1350m & crossed to rail, soon 1.5L clear & keen, joined on turn & driven into stretch, all out & headed 160m, tapered but held on to 2nd.
Smart start, parked 1 back on rail, driven turning in & boxed on dourly to hold 3rd.
Snagged back from widest & soon detached 15L off lead, bustled to tag onto to pack 700m, driven 1 off 600m, widest into stretch, ran on to press for minors.
Started well, settled midfield on rail, shifted out & driven turning in, fought on dourly to press for minors.
Started well, slotted 1 back 1 off, niggled 500m, shifted 3 deep & driven 400m, wide into stretch, kept on evenly.
Broke ok but lacked toe & raced back of midfield 1 off with cover, shifted 4 deep 600m & bustled forward, very wide into stretch, plugged on evenly.
Broke well & bustled, prominent but soon settled midfield 1 off with cover, ridden 400m, swung out centre track, kept on one pace.
Lacked early toe, raced back of midfield on rail, ridden along 400m, hard driven 300m, plodded one pace.
Broke ok, soon rolled to lead, headed 1350m, moved upsides leader turning in, shaken up 300m, emptied 220m & faded tamely.
Broke wide & bustled on outer to 1st turn, trapped 3 wide no cover midfield, nudged along, under pump 500m, emptied turning in & weakened out.
Taken back, soon driven along 2nd last, worked to join pack 700m, last 450m & adrift turning in, eased down.
First to break, initially urged but then restrained into box-seat spot on rail, ridden 450m, pulled off heels entering straight, hit lead 150m, raced clear.
Jumped well, urged to lead, joined 1000m but booted up on rail to take 1L lead by 750m, held together until 350m, joined 150m, no match.
Jumped well, eased to settle midfield 1 off, pushed along 520m, changed course 150m, finished solidly.
Away on terms, eased to settle beyond midfield 1 off, niggled 850m, ridden again 450m, found line strongly late.
On back foot slightly at start, ridden to get into midfield spot, settled midfield on rail, slightly keen throughout, ridden 370m, stuck to inside, couldn't pick up.
Slightly slow to break, nudged into forward spot, settled 4th 1 off, slightly keen 700m, driven 350m & pulled centre track, one-paced.
Driven from gates, unable to muster & stuck midfield 4 deep early, into fore of midfield spot 3 deep by 900m, improved quickly 700m into 2nd, under pressure 400m, weakened.
Jumped evenly, restrained to settle well beyond midfield 1 off, clicked up 400m, pulled widest, wayward in straight, never nearer.
Broke strongly, restrained to settle beyond midfield on inside, under riding 380m, never in contention.
Eased from start to settle at rear 1 off, improving between runners 600m when squeezed out, made very late headway.
Hard-ridden from wide gate to cross, led 1000m but restrained shortly afterwards, settled 2nd 1 off, under pressure 500m, weakened.
Very slow start, ridden to settle near rear on rail, nudged 450m, faded tamely.
Sent forward and led by 1/2L in a 2 wide position, kept on going and scored comfortably by 1-1/4L.
Eased and shifted to the rail, in worse than midfield 4-3/4L behind, swung widest at 400M, ran on strongly for 2nd.
Rolled forward and settled into box-seat, sat 1-1/2L off the lead, kept on well to take 3rd.
Settled in one-off one-back position, about 2-1/2L off the pace, ran on fairly to be closest at the finish.
Raced in front of midfield, 2-3/4L off but 3 wide without cover throughout, kept on one paced going to the line.
Sent forward and raced inside the lead along the fence, sat about 1/2L behind, emptied inside final 100M.
Settled to race in midfield, 3-1/2L behind along the fence, kept on one paced in the run home.
Bumped start and travelled at the rear, 5-3/4L behind along the rail, continued to make ground steadily in the run home.
Raced in midfield, 3-1/2L behind 3 wide with cover, made little impression in the Straight.
Travelled in midfield, 3L behind 2 wide, steadied and was galloped on passing 700M, never ran on.
Settled in behind midfield, 3-3/4L behind 2 wide, blundered and lost ground at 700M, did not feature in the Straight.
Always at the rear, never in contention.
Jumped fairly, hard ridden to lead approaching first turn and then made every post a winner. Started to shorten stride final 50m but managed to hold on for narrow win.

Vigorously ridden after jumping well but didn't muster enough speed, dropping towards rear between horses. Bumped and unbalanced 600m, rolled forward from 500m, wide into straight before finishing strongly to just miss.
Broke well, shared early pace before easing back to midfield. Put under pressure 600m out, swung wide into straight, battled on gamely to snatch minor placing on post.

Hard ridden to get forward position, racing 4-wide until settling 1L behind leader in one-off position at first turn. Put under pressure to chase leader 400m out but unable to close gap and then swamped final strides.
Began awkwardly then crowded out, dropping to last along rail. Improved position rounding home turn and ran on fairly in straight to be closest at finish.
Jumped OK, outpaced, dropping towards rear along fence. Attempted to lay out turning for home but stayed on inside rack in straight and boxed on gamely.
Broke well, pressed forward snatching box seat 2L from leader at first turn. Under pressure turning for home, kept on fairly to 200m before giving ground.
Steadied on jumping and shifted across behind runners, settling one-out at rear. Dropped to last approaching home turn, taken wide in straight but only one-paced.
Pressed forward on jumping but caught wide without cover entering first turn, but only 2L from leader. Came under pressure from home turn and one-paced in straight.
Jumped OK but steadied before first turn, settling behind midfield in one-out position. Lay out home turn and gave ground quickly in straight, finishing tailed out. Unacceptable performance.
Jumped well, ridden forward, staying behind pacemakers to back stretch. Started to give ground turning for home and faded in straight, finishing tailed out. Unacceptable performance.

Hard ridden from widest gate but unable to get forward position and held wide behind midfield at first turn. Hung out from 600m losing considerable ground and eased down from home turn. Had irregular heart rhythm.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned a length or so back on rail, easy run throughout, finished off well in straight to score.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, reluctant to improve near 800M, angled out after 400M, finished off well to get 2nd.
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kept on well after turning in, headed near 100M, stayed on for 3rd.
Bumped start, no early speed, raced 5 lengths or so back at rear, bumped running rail and unbalanced near 600M, similar position on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame.

Taken back to race at rear, positioned 2 wide behind midfield, slightly improved on turn, taken wide in straight and made good progress, just missed frame. (Sustained a wound to the right hind leg.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide throughout, peaked early in straight and weakened gradually thereafter.
Moderately away from the widest draw, unable to slot in early, sent forward near 850M, 3 wide with no cover throughout, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back to race at tail, 7 lengths back, still well back on turn, set too much to do and could only pass a few tired ones.
Bumped start, positioned on rail in midfield, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, similar position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Away with them, raced 3 wide in midfield, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away from a tricky gate, unable to slot in, raced wide with no cover throughout, weakened on turn, finished last.

Crowded at start losing ground, recovered steadily on rail to be just worse than midfield home bend, obtained a run 300 metres out and ran on well to take charge nearing finish.
Made narrow running before joined shortly after straightening, kicked 1L clear under pressure passing the 200 metres but only to be collared close to home.
Began fairly from the widest gate, settled wide in worse than midfield, ran on well inside the final 300 metres, did best work late.
Well there, disputed lead into straight but unable to sustain effort from 250 metres out.
Jumped fairly, settled within 3L of pace in 5th on rail, in similar position turning in, one-paced under pressure.
Soon in rear, finished off race well down the centre of the home straight.
Jumped fairly from a wide-ish draw, gradually shifted in for cover in rear of midfield, kept on well down in the run home.
Settled in midfield on rail, saved ground turning in, found nothing in straight.
Settled in midfield, one-paced under pressure.
Settled just off the pace in 3rd on rail, came under pressure upon straightening, soon weakened.
Not far off, tendency to hang in early in straight, hampered by the winner 300 metres out, hampered again when beaten over 150 metres out.
Never in the hunt.
Niggled along in last few, saved ground on rail turning in, made no impression in straight.
Began well from a wide draw, soon dropped to midfield despite coming under pressure, went wide into straight, weakened. (Lame)
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, suited by the slow tempo, closed off strongly and drifted away 300M to score.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, benefited by the slow sectionals, ran on well for 2nd.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, dashed well 400M for 3rd.
Very slow away, at back, dashed strongly 400M despite not suited by the slow pace.
At back, 2 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, lack room 400M, dashed well when clear.
Eased to sit behind midfield, trapped 2-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden to sit in front of midfield, not suited by the slow tempo, lack room 400M, no progress when clear.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, harmed by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 200M.
Very slow away, hard ridden to keep up at back, 2-3 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, ran on fairly.
Eased back, took rail, harmed by the slow pace, no turn of foot.
Very slow away, hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, flattened 300M, checked 150M.
Eased back, 2 wide, never a factor.
Hard ridden forward, shared the lead 2 wide at slow sectionals, out of fuel 350M.
Hard ridden forward, took rail and shared the lead at slow pace, soon emptied 350.
Jumped well, pushed along to lead, kicked clear on straightening to win easily.
Settled behind midfield, angled out on straightening and worked home strongly.
Settled off speed wide without cover, tried hard entire straight.
Bumped and unbalance at start, settled off pace, loomed to challenge Home Turn but quickly under pressure and became unbalanced in action. Must trial.
Pushed along early to race on speed, unable to quicken at 300m and battled one paced to the line.
Settled midfield, tried to issue challenge on straightening but unable to quicken.
Began fairly, settled leaders back, one paced in straight.
Settled behind midfield, made no impression in straight.
Settled midfield and travelled nicely, under pressure at 300m and gradually weakened.
Taken back at start, one pace throughout.
Always well back and did not run on.
Always well back and did not run on.
Always well back and did not run on.
Always well back and did not run on.
Smart break, bustled initially & soon midfield 3 deep with cover, advanced a spot 850m, shifted 4 deep 550m & driven 300m, grinding effort to lead close home.
Bumped at break, dropped-in back of midfield 3 wide with cover, advanced a place 780m, shifted very wide home turn for progress & driven 350m, chased winner to wire, just held.
Sharp start & bustled, lacked toe & raced mid rank 4 wide no cover, advanced to 3rd 3 deep 980m, driven into stretch & led 380m, all out & headed close home.
Speed to lead, headed 1250m & raced 1 off 1 back, checked off heels turning in & crowded, close-up & driven 400m, every chance, emptied 150m & tapered.
Tardy break &bumped, near rear initially, 3 wide & rolled forward a spot 750m, wide & driven turning in, kept on for minor headway.
Tardy start, settled midfield 1 off with cover, driven into stretch, plugged on evenly.
Broke ok but lacked toe & bustled, raced rail midfield, edged out final turn, soon driven & checked 350m, staying on for minor headway when checked again 100m.
Bumped at break, taken back to rail near tail, last pair from 750m, edged wide home turn, widest & driven 400m, some headway but one-paced in closing stages.
Taken back from wide gate to tail, soon detached 3L, closed gradually to join pack 1 off at 850m, forced widest home turn, switched in 400m & driven, modest inroads.
Broke well, prominent on rail, settled 1 back 1100m, shaken up turning in, shifted out & bumped rival 390m, hard-ridden but plodded one pace.
Pushed forward from widest to lead 1250m, crossed to rail 1100m, joined at 950m & vied for lead, driven turning in & headed 380m, weakened out.
Restrained at break to back of midfield 1 off with cover, niggled 550m, shifted out in stretch & hard-ridden 350m, found nil in tame run home.
Tardy break & bumped, soon recovered & raced handy 3 wide no cover, nudged on to press leader 950m & vied for lead, driven home turn, soon emptied, faded tamely.
Slow start & bumped, to rail back of midfield, under pump 500m, hard-ridden 400m, no response, eased when beaten 200m.
Jumped quick, natural speed to settle handy 1 off, niggled 550m, on scene quickly entering straight, hit lead 250m, sprinted strongly to score.
Quick to jump, eased to settle beyond midfield 3 deep 1st turn, ridden 550m, widest into straight, charged home, couldn't quite get there.
Even break, nudged to push forward, green on 1st turn, checked 870m, back to fore of midfield spot 1 off, ridden 600m, sprinted well but never quite on terms, boxed on late.
Away OK, eased to beyond midfield spot 1 off, nudged 1000m, driven 550m, switched back inside in straight, made very strong ground late, 4th on wire.
Flew the gates, niggled to hold lead on inside, headed 1000m but kicked up to rejoin equal lead on inside 750m, clicked up 460m, kicked strongly, claimed 250m, fought to line.
Strong start, keen early, eased into midfield spot on rail, driven 500m, not quite clear 400m, in clear 300m, stayed on.
Broke fast, driven to lead 1000m, slightly keen, joint lead 1 off 750m, ridden 450m, weakened.
Even dispatch, settled fore of midfield 3 deep, niggled 600m, ridden entering straight, weakened noticeably, bled.
Slightly awkward start, quickly up into box seat spot, settled 4th on rail, under pressure 500m, weakened quickly.
Hopped in air at start, back to near rear of main pack on rail, keen 850m, ridden 450m, never a factor.
Eased from gates, settled near rear 1 off, outpaced 800m and ridden, awkward in straight, not in it.
Jumped on terms, settled midfield 1 off before easing to get spot slightly worse than midfield on rail, held together until 400m, green in straight, faded tamely.
Slow to begin and unable to keep up early, ridden hard to tack on, outpaced early & again 600m, never in it.
On back foot out of gates, shunted along to push up into midfield spot on rail, lost ground 850m & hard-ridden soon after, faded meekly.
Rolled forward and took up racing in the box-seat, sat 1-3/4L off, kept on going and took the prize in the final strides.
Sent forward to take the rail and led by 3/4L, maintained lead and only headed inside final 50M, held on for 2nd.
Raced in front of midfield, 2L off the lead 2 wide, hampered at 1100M, found extra passing 250M, ran on well for 3rd.
Raced in behind midfield, 5L behind the lead 2 wide, ran home well once cleared at 200M.
Taken back and travelled at the rear, 7L behind 3 wide with cover, made impressive ground and ran home strongly.
Pushed forward and stayed prominent, sat 1-1/4L off but 3 wide without cover, kept on one paced home.
Slotted in just behind midfield, 4-1/4L behind 3 wide with cover, made slight ground in the run home.
Ridden out of the barrier, settled to race in front of midfield, 2-3/4L off 3 wide with cover, finished off only one paced.
Settled to race in midfield, 3-1/4L behind along the rail, kept on one paced in the run home.
Settled to race in midfield, 3-1/4L behind 2 wide, checked near 1100M, slight dash at 350M, one paced thereafter.
Pushed and raced prominently, wide until improved to race outside the lead at 1100M, weakened passing 250M.
Slow to jump, then eased back and raced towards the rear, 5-3/4L behind along the rail, not competitive.
Slightly crowded at start, race towards the rear, 5-3/4L behind 3 wide with cover, found nothing in the Straight.
Slightly crowded at start, remained at the rear throughout, never a factor.
Pushed forward to lead on settling and set steady pace to straight. Kept finding when put under intense pressure and though shortening stride in final stages managed to hold on for narrow win.
Missed the start slightly, taken to rail and hunted forward to get within 3L of leader at home turn. Blocked for inside run top of straight, switched out 300m and closed with a rush to just miss.
Broke well, pushed forward to grab box seat, then kept tabs on leader to turn when left fence to make challenge. Battled on gamely in straight only to fail narrowly.

Jumped with field, shared early pace to 1100m when steadied and travelled keenly before settling midfield but 3-wide with cover. Swung wide into straight and closed off nicely to finish just behind place-getters.
Unable handle early pace and settled towards the rear along fence. Made some progress around home turn and kept on steadily in straight without looking dangerous.
Jumped OK but not much speed and dropped towards rear in one-out position. Remained at rear till straightening for home and ran on fairly between horses.
Ridden to hold forward position but stranded wide without cover, racing 3-deep 2L from leader on settling. Swung wide into straight and boxed on one-paced.
Pressed forward from a wide draw before being eased back to find cover, settling at rear but 3-wide. Taken to centre field on straightening and found little despite several reminders.

Shifted across behind runners shortly after start, dropping to last pair but kept away from fence. Remained at the rear till well into the straight before running past tired horses. Lame left front and left hind legs.
Got off well, pressed forward 3-wide before settling 3-parts of a length behind leader approaching turn. Swung a little wide into straight, boxed on fairly to 200m when ran out of fuel and faded.
Hard ridden but unable to match early pace, being shuffled back gradually to behind midfield. Lost more ground around home turn, taken wide in straight but only one-paced.

Vigorously ridden from the jump to get forward position but couldn't muster sufficient speed, dropping to behind midfield but wide. Taken to centre field on straightening but found little under hard riding.

Given a couple of slaps at the start to get moving, racing outside early leader before being eased one-back, one-out approaching home turn. Given reminders top of straight but found nothing and drifted back.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw and last on settling. Trailed field to straight and never competitive.
Chased leaders 2-wide, quickened up nicely early straight, led nearing 200M, stuck to task well at the front and fended off a late challenge to keep unbeaten record intact.
Began awkwardly, recovered to race in midfield, 5th at 400M 3Ls behind leader, tracked path of eventual winner turning in, kept finding to make it close at the finish.
Reserved near the rear early and middle stages, did best work final 250M, weaved through horses to get up for 3rd late.
Restrained in midfield early, shifted out to 3-wide 700M, pushed wider 550M, kept up with the pursuit to 150M, flattened late stages. (Jockey questioned)
Taken back from wide draw, near last 10Ls off the pace early stages, worked home well from the rear down the outside, made good impression on debut.
Chased leader, checked 950M, got out of pocket 300M, tried hard but couldn't reel in leader, flat final 100M.
Sent forward from wide draw, sat outside leader from 900M, kept on evenly early straight, outpaced by pursuing rivals 150M.
Held up behind midfield, 4Ls to make up on leader at 400M, kept on evenly without threat.
Never far off the pace, 3Ls behind leader at 400M, going one pace in the run home, steadied 100M and eased off.
In midfield, made the turn awkwardly 900M and ended up 3-wide no cover, kept on moderately in straight, not reach contention.
Rushed forward, led along the rail from 1000M, pace slow, headed nearing 200m and faded out of contention thereafter.
Dropped back to last from 13, 10Ls off the pace middle stages, took time to muster speed turning in, commenced to finish off passing 200M but unable to obtain clear running over final stages.
Settled down 8Ls back near the rear, brought widest 400M but offered little.
Behind midfield, 5Ls off the pace at 400M but couldn't sprint with them, eased 150M when no chance.
Lunged at start losing ground, then hunted forward, settling midfield approaching turn. Pocketed top of straight but got split 300m and powered forward along fence to win close home.
Quickly into stride from an outside draw, leading field but wide until 1150m when overtaken. Chased leader to straight, retook lead 300m out, looked winner before being run down close to line.
Jumped well, pressed forward, settling 3L from leader in one-off position. Urged forward on straightening, looked chance 200m, one-paced final strides.
Outpaced early, dropping to rear along fence. Stayed at rear till home straight when taken wide and finished off nicely.
Jumped OK, ridden along but unable to find cover, settling wide in midfield. Kept wide around turn and boxed on gamely in straight to finish just behind place-getters.
Began fairly then stumbled before recovering, settling behind midfield. Lost some ground around home turn, taken to centre field on straightening and ran home fairly.
Jumped with field but then restrained and shifted across behind runners to find cover, settling towards rear. Remained well back to straight and ran past tiring rivals.
Broke well, ridden to hold fence, surging forward to lead passing 1150m. Skipped 2L clear turning for home but collared 300m out. Boxed on gamely to 100m before giving ground gradually.

Away quickly, pressed forward, racing wide to 1000m when got cover 3L behind leader. Came off the bridle passing 500m and failed to respond to hard riding in straight, giving ground rapidly final 200m.
Pushed forward from inside draw, hugging rail 4L from leader on settling. Stayed on rail around turn but ran out of steam halfway up the straight and faded.
Slow into stride and last on settling. Trailed field thereafter, losing touch with rivals in straight.
Eased out and settled worse than midfield. Held up until 300m, and switched in towards the rail for clear running. Great turn of foot from 150m and easy to the line late under hand and heels.

Dropped back early and settled towards the rear of the field, 3 wide. Widest on the turn, and ran strongly to lead at 150m. Couldn't match winners turn of foot, but strong to the line for a clear 2nd.
Settled midfield, on the rail. Raced tight at 300m and again at 150m when taking runs. Finished solidly, and easily held 3rd.
Bumped on jumping and eased back to sit worse than midfield. Solid early in the straight, and finished strongly over the last 100m.
Dropped back early to sit at the tail of the field. Last on turn, and came widest in the straight. Stayed on OK in the straight, but never threatened a place.
Pressed forward and handily placed 4th, 1 off the fence. Off heels 900m and went 3 wide no cover. Steadied off heels 300m and lost momentum 300m. Stayed on fairly after that.
Handily placed 3rd/4th early. Ran on OK early in the straight, but 1 paced from the 250m.
Taken up to midfield, 1 off the fence. Steadied early in the straight, but only fair when clear and made no impact.
Fairly away and dropped back to last early. Plugged away solidly in the straight without ever threatening.
Taken up to share lead early, before dropping back to sit 2nd at 1100m. Dropped out quickly from 200m.
Taken up from the wide draw to sit just forward of midfield, 1 off the fence. Only fair in the straight and eased out late.
Bumped on jumping and got back. Never in it.
Very keen early and taken up to lead. Race was run by the 250m, and faded out quickly from there.
Wide no cover at the rear of the field early, before pushing to sit forward of midfield at 800m. Gave nothing in the straight, and eased a long way from home.

Settled at the back from a wide gate, waited with well behind, switched wide for a run early in straight, finished off race strongly to snatch victory final stride.
Jumped well from the widest gate, gradually moved in to track the leader around home bend, hit the front under pressure 150 metres out, only to be caught close to home.
Raced wide throughout, prominent early, drifted back to midfield rounding home bend, ran on well to be nearest at finish.
Ridden in first few early, settled in 5th in forward of midfield, fought on dourly to narrowly miss the place-getters.
Jumped fairly from a wide draw, ridden along to take up running passing the 900 metres, obtained run on the rail coming onto home bend, led the field until headed 150 metres out.
Led early stages, taken 2.5L back to 4th coming onto home bend, came under pressure to challenge when 3rd into straight but failed to quicken to threaten.
Towards the rear, made modest progress in straight, never nearer.
Moderate start, towards the rear on the rail, baulked for a stride upon straightening, kept on at the one pace. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Jumped fairly niggling along, settled 2.5L back mainly in 3rd around home bend, kept on early in straight before fading inside the final 200 metres.
Moderate start, settled in rear of midfield, jostled between runners and lost position approaching home bend, one-paced before fading inside final 200 metres.
Detached early, never seen with a chance except for short-lived effort to reach the tail-end of the field briefly around home bend.
Jumped fairly, quickly picked up to midfield on the rail, hampered and lost position coming onto home bend, dropped out under pressure shortly after straightening. (Lame next day)
Detached early, made it move from 600M around the field in 3 wide, suited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 300M and scored.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in front of midfield, closed off strongly 300M, just beaten by a narrow margin in 2nd.
Eased back, took rail, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 400M for 3rd.
Pressed forward, settled in box seat, not suited by the fast pace, ran on strongly until 150M overhauled.
Pushed forward, 2-3 wide, rider dropped the reins for some distance in straight, ran on well until 150M run ended.
At back, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, just held ground in straight.
Checked start, hard ridden forward to lead at fast sectionals, emptied 300M.
Eased back, trapped 3-4 wide, favoured by the fast pace, no progress.
Pushed early, suited by the fast tempo, behind midfield along the fence, never improved.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide, harmed by the fast pace, dropped off rapidly 400M.
Jumped well, settled off pace, moved up to challenge home turn, let down nicely to win easily.
Checked shortly after start and settled towards rear, commenced to improve passing 600m, ran home strongly.
Jumped fairly before speeding through to lead easily, tendency to over-race, fought on well.
Jumped smartly, settled off pace, issued challenge on straightening and ran home well.
Allowed to settle towards rear, improved along rail home turn and battled solidly to the line.
Jumped smartly and settled behind leader, tried hard to challenge at 300m before weakening late.
Raced ungenerously early and settled at rear, ran on fairly.
Crowded at start, settled midfield, ridden along400m, one paced to finish.
Settled behind midfield, widest on straightening, one paced to finish.
Hampered shortly after start, made some ground along rail home turn before weakening in straight.
Taken back at start, raced ungenerously and hung out throughout, never in it.

Placing: PU
Comment: Rider concerned with action near 1300m, commenced to ease down but travelling strongly, eased down in straight.
Broke ok, rolled forward to outside leader, keen & allowed to lead 1150m, clear & to rail 1030m, joined home turn, shaken up 350m & kicked clear, driven out.
Started well & bustled forward to park 1 off 1 back, forced 3 wide no cover 850m, niggled 600m, 3rd & driven turning in, fought on dourly to nick 2nd.
Fast start & urged to lead, to rail 1400m, headed 1150m & shifted 1 off no cover 850m, niggled on turn to close, driven 400m but outkicked, boxed on one pace.
Fast start, soon restrained to 1 back on rail, 4th & driven 350m, kept on evenly down fence to maintain position.
Broke ok, steadied from widest gate & trapped on outer 1st turn, snagged 1250m & taken to tail 1150m, soon 2L adrift, reminders 550m & progress, switched widest in stretch, stormed late.
Awkward start & bustled up rail from rear to park midfield, driven & shifted out 450m, closed steadily centre track.
Broke ok, niggled to midfield 3 deep no cover, gained brief cover 850m, under pump 650m & soon hard ridden, accidentally struck in face 350m, kept on for minor late headway.
Taken back to race midfield on rail, shuffled back a spot 850m, shifted out on turn & driven into stretch, kept on for moderate inroads.
Started ok, settled mid-pack 1 off with cover, ridden along 500m, kept on evenly in stretch.
Taken back at break & trapped 4 wide no cover until slotted 3 deep near rear 950m, under pump 650m, driven home evenly.
Broke well, sat midfield 1 off with cover, bustled 600m, driven 450m, outpaced in stretch run, checked close home.
Steadied & wide near tail 1st turn, settled 3 wide with cover, niggled forward a spot 750m, driven on turn & very wide into stretch, plugged on one pace.
Held up at start, overraced behind midfield 1400m, shuffled near tail & checked 720m, driven 350m but crowded turning in, plugged on tepidly.
Taken to tail, improved to 2nd last 1150m, under pump to maintain position 1100m, checked off heels 700m, retreated to last 500m, no extra & tailed off.
Broke well, eased to settle at rear 3 deep by 1st turn, clicked up 450m, took time to wind up, hit top gear last 100m, just prevailed.
Slightly slow to begin, settled beyond midfield 1 off, shifted 3 deep 800m, travelled well throughout, ridden 430m, unleashed strong sprint, reached lead 50m but overhauled quickly .
First to jump, outpaced & stuck midfield 4 deep early, eventually into 4th 3 deep, ridden 400m, sprinted solidly, just outgunned late.
Slightly awkward start & ridden, stuck beyond midfield 4 deep, edged forward from 650m but always wide, stayed on well.
Broke OK, natural speed to get into spot just behind speed, settled 3rd on rail, pulled off leader's back & ridden 400m, strode up to lead 350m, kicked clear, worn down final strides.
Got away well, eased at first but then nudged into midfield spot1 off, clicked up 470m, sprinted well between runners, on heels 100m, not ridden out.
Eased from widest gate, quickly clear last, niggled 1050m, passed another horse 700m, hard ridden 500m, shifted off rail 250m, short of room 100m, not fully tested.
Started well, allowed to find his feet beyond midfield 3 & 4 deep, nudged 600m, near rear entering straight & ridden, never in contention.
Even break, driven hard to lead on rail, 1L lead 700m, placed under pressure 360m, quickly passed, faded tamely.
Slowest to break, railed through to beyond midfield spot, shifted to 1 off 800m, scrubbed 600m, back to last entering straight, no threat.
Driven vigorously out of gates, unable to muster & settled midfield on rail, under pressure & lost spot 800m, under riding remainder of race, dropped right out.
Head up at start, hard pressed to push forward, settled 2nd 1 off, didn't handle turn & hung badly off track under riding, dropped away.
Settled to race in the box-seat, sat 2-3/4L off the pace, kept on going nicely and scored by 3/4L.
Raced in worse than midfield, 6-1/4L behind along the rail, made good ground, hit the line strongly, missed by 3/4L.
Raced just front of midfield, 4L off 2 wide, checked at 350M, ran on thereafter and hit the line well to take 3rd.
Pushed and raced in front of midfield, 3-1/2L off but trapped wide throughout, kept on well to take 4th.
Slow to jump and raced at the rear, 9-1/2L behind along the rail, improved steadily, ran on well.
Travelled towards the tail end, 7-1/2L behind 2-3 wide, made ground steadily, finished off well.
Pushed forward to take the rail and led by 1-1/2L, emptied and headed passing 200M.
Eased back and raced at the rear, 9L behind 2 wide, continued to make ground in the Straight, kept on well.
Rolled forward and sat outside the lead, about 1-1/2L off, kept on until approaching 150M and weakened.
Settled in one-off one-back position, about 3L off the pace, emptied approaching 250M.
Raced in worse than midfield, 5-1/2L behind 2 wide until 700M when taken wider, found nothing in the Straight.
Bumped start then failed to muster, lost ground when hung out badly at turn, did not recover.
Broke well, ridden to hold rail, settling 3L from leader. Took closer order around turn, set off after leader on straightening, hit front 180m, pulled clear under hands and heels riding.
Pressed forward from an outside draw, racing wide 2L from leader then left without cover from 900m. Swung wide into straight before finishing strongly to grab quinella spot.
Quickly into stride, holding rail a half-length inside leader. Shared lead around turn, kicked 2L clear top of straight but caught 180m out. Boxed on to hold minor placing.
Crowded out at start, then hard ridden but slow to muster, falling behind midfield 4L from leader. Stayed on rail around turn and ran on fairly in straight.
Jumped with field, ridden to hold forward position, settling midfield in one-out position. Lost position around turn but boxed on fairly in straight without looking dangerous.
Got off OK, settling in midfield 4L from leader. Got shuffled back around turn, swung wide, boxed on fairly in straight while laying in.
Quickly into stride, leading for a few strides before settling one-out, one-back. Taken wide entering straight, boxed on fairly to 200m before turning one-paced.
Jumped fairly, outpaced, dropping to last. Improved position approaching home turn but only one-paced in straight.
Jumped OK but beaten for early pace, dropping to last pair. Made up some ground around home turn but only one-paced in straight.
Broke with field, racing wide before being steadied 900m after which raced keenly. Taken 4-wide without cover passing 700m, losing ground around turn. Found nothing in straight.
Broke well, pushed to lead on settling before joined up front by inside runner. Under pressure on straightening, kept on fairly to 200m before fading.
Jumped OK but unable handle early pace, dropping to rear. Under pressure on straightening and dropped to last 200m out.
Jumped well, raced prominently early, 2 wide in midfield in the middle stages, there to turn, angled out in straight and finished off well to score.
Slowly away, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, similar position on turn, improved from 500M, finished off very strongly in straight to get 2nd.
Crowded out start, positioned 2 wide behind midfield, steadied near 1400M and 900M, 3 wide with cover on turn, closed off well, just missed 2nd.
Began well from a middle draw, raced 2 wide in 4th, similar position on turn, kept on evenly to the line.
Moderately away from gate 1, showed no early speed, raced 7 lengths or so back at rear, improved from 600M, very wide turning in, ran home very strongly to be nearest on line.
Moderately away from a wide draw, positioned wide in midfield, no cover after 900M, peaked early in straight, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, recovered, took the lead near 1250M, easy lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 150M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in early, sent forward near 1300M, raced in 2nd in the middle stages, peaked on turn, one-paced in straight.
Taken back to race 5 lengths or so back at rear, saved ground throughout, kept to inside after straightening and made minor progress.
Away with them, positioned on rail in midfield, there to turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off one-paced.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced wide with cover at rear, bumped near 800M, very wide turning in, one-paced in straight.
Began well, positioned a length or so back on rail, easy run throughout, showed no response after turning in, eased final 100M.
Began fairly from a tricky gate, positioned 2 wide in midfield, weakened on turn, emptied in straight and eased.
Bumped start, raced at tail throughout, never competitive.

Travelled just off the pace near stands rail, shifted in off the rail for a run 500 metres out, responded well inside final 150 metres to just get up on line.
Took slender lead from the middle draw, obtained run on stands rail approaching the course proper, kicked over 2L clear 250 metres out only to be caught near the finish.
Well there on stands rail, kept on without quickening under pressure inside final 300 metres. (Saddle shifted)
Moderate start, well behind early, soon picked up to midfield, kept on steadily without threatening.
Well there, came under pressure coming onto course proper, folded up quickly inside final 300 metres.
Taken back from the lowest draw, gained closer towards midfield over halfway out, one-paced under pressure in the run home.
Soon dropped to last few, one-paced.
Well behind, one-paced.
Jumped well, prominent early stages, gave ground from approaching the 500 metres.
Not far off early stages, shuffled back to behind midfield approaching the course proper, never recovered.
Settled just better than midfield, jostled between runners about 600 metres out, no further impression.
Moderate start, soon dropped to last few on stands rail, never a danger.
Jumped fairly, settled just better than midfield, struggling from halfway out.
Lacked pace, never in the hunt.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, not suited by the slow pace, dashed strongly 350M and scored.
Pushed forward, sat outside the leader, benefited by the slow sectionals, ran on strongly in the lead until 150M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide, ran on well to the line for 3rd.
Slow away, behind midfield, trapped 4 wide, unleashed strong finishing efforts 300M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Trapped 4 wide in midfield without cover, harmed by the slow pace, dashed strongly 400M despite all negative racing situations.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in the lead, suited by the slow tempo, out of fuel 200M.
Rolled forward, trapped 3 wide without cover, ran on until 200M flattened.
Eased to rear, trapped 2-3 wide, dashed strongly 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
At rear, took cover, harmed by the slow tempo, dashed well 200M.
Pressed forward early, stayed 2 wide, shuffled back to midfield, harmed by the slow pace, made ground early straight, however blocked and checked 200M.
Eased to sit in midfield, raced keenly, 3 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, little dash 200M.
At back along the fence, not suited by the slow pace, lack turn of foot in straight.
Slow away, eased back, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, emptied in straight, checked 200M.
Never competitive at rear.
Jumped well and settled on pace, ridden along from 1100m to hold position, improved to challenge strongly home turn, took control at 300m to win easily.
Settled outside leader, travelled well home turn, tried hard but no match for winner.
Settled at rear, commenced to improve around field 550m, ran home strongly without threatening.
Raced midfield, urged along home turn, tried hard to challenge in straight but one paced to the finish.
Settled midfield, travelling well home turn, tried hard to challenge in straight but one paced to the line.
Sent forward to lead, ridden along home turn, gradually weakened in straight.
Settled towards rear, raced ungenerously passing 1450m, held up 150m when making steady ground.
Settled at rear and ran home fairly.
Began awkwardly and failed to muster speed early stages, one paced in straight.
Crowded at start and failed to muster speed, checked when racing keenly at 1400m, one paced in straight.
Raced behind leaders, under pressure home turn and weakened out of it in straight.
Settled midfield, under pressure home turn and did not run on.
Settled behind midfield, under pressure home turn and did not run on.
Settled forward of midfield and gradually gave ground from 700m.
Speedy break to dispute initial lead, went on from 1000m & set tempo, shaken up 400m & bounded 2L clear, emptied close home & just held on.
Fast start wide, pushed to vie for lead until crossed at 1000m & settled 2nd 1 off no cover, ridden into home turn, outkicked & boxed on for closing 2nd.
Broke ok, bustled initially to race rail 1 back, niggled 550m, hard-ridden into stretch & shifted centre track, kept on for gradual inroads.
Broke well & rousted, not pace of leaders & settled handy 1 off with cover, driven into stretch, gradual closer, just missed frame.
Broke well but quickly outpaced & rousted, settled rail near rear, shifted out & ridden 520m, wide into stretch, rattled centre track for late gains.
Sluggish start, taken behind to race near rear 3 wide with cover, over-raced 800m, progress on turn, ridden 350m & ran on for minor inroads.
Broke well, eased 1000m & settled midfield on rail, niggled at 500m, driven into stretch, plodded on one pace.
Broke well, raced 4 wide no cover in 3rd, slotted 3 wide 900m, niggled along 550m, driven into stretch, no extra & faded.
Restrained at start, rolled on to midfield 1 off with cover, driven home turn, outpaced & plodded on tepidly.
Shifted in at break, good pace to track front rank 3 wide, snagged back a spot 950m, niggled 550m, hard-ridden into stretch, faded tamely.
Tardy start & soon bustled near rear on rail, to tail 900m, driven 400m, found little & eased late.
Slow break, rolled from tail to 2nd last 900m, bustled 3 deep 550m, widest into stretch, checked 400m, found nil in tame run home.
Vigorously ridden from gates, into 2nd 1 off but niggled throughout, ridden hard 360m, hit lead final strides, just scored.
Pinged the gates, natural speed to lead early, crossed to outside rail by 700m, clicked up 350m, 1L lead 200m, claimed final strides.
First to begin, ridden to hold fore of midfield spot on outside rail, under drive 370m, not clearest of runs, stayed on well.
Away evenly, settled midfield 4 deep & niggled, 5 deep 500m, under riding 420m, strode up well but peaked on run last 100m.
Awkward start, outpaced & back to beyond midfield 3 deep, driven from 650m, pulled centre track, finished well.
Jumped OK but squeezed out shortly after start, back to near rear 1 off, ridden 650m, took long time to wind up but finished well.
Away OK, pushed to get into 3rd 3 deep, ridden 400m, weakened last 150m.
Slightly awkward start, outpaced early, settled midfield 1 off, hard ridden from 600m, one-paced to line.
Began well, eased to beyond midfield spot 4 deep, ridden 550m, outpaced.
Bumped at start, pushed to hold spot fore of midfield 3 deep, ridden 500m, pulled wider on track, eased down last 50m.
Green from gates, settled near rear 4 deep, pressed hard 600m, out to centre track 350m, never in it.
Awkward start, outpaced, settled last 3 deep, eased out to centre track, pushed 350m, battled away.
Outpaced early, beyond midfield on outside rail, ridden 350m but limited response.
Even jump, natural speed to get up towards lead, settled just off speed 4 deep, under pressure 450m, dropped right out.
Niggled forward and eventually took the rail and led by 1-1/4L, ran on nicely to score by 1L.
Settled to race in box-seat, sat 1-3/4L off the pace, kept on and pushed the winner to the line.
Eased back and raced towards the rear, 7L behind 2 wide, covered nice ground, and finished off strongly.
Hampered at start, raced in midfield, 4-1/4L behind 2 wide, made good ground and found the line fairly well.
Travelled just in front of midfield, 3-1/2L off along the fence, made no ground but kept on fairly.
Hampered at start, settled in midfield, 5L behind along the rail, kept on one paced in the run home.
Awkward start, raced just behind midfield, 5-1/2L behind 2 wide, made good ground from 200M.
Rolled forward but trapped wide, improved to race outside the lead at 800M, sat 1-1/4L off, dropped off gradually.
Awkward start and eased to race near the rear, 6-3/4L behind along the rail, ran on one paced.
Rolled forward and travelled keenly in one-off one-back position, sat 3L off the pace, weakened at 250M.
Raced at the rear as per usual, 8-3/4L behind 2 wide, swung widest after turn, did not make ground.
In midfield, about 4L behind 3 wide throughout, raced ungenerously, one paced until flattened passing 200M.
Raced just behind midfield, 5-1/4L behind but 3 wide throughout, did not improve.
Reluctant to race and was eased down by rider at 900M.
Moderately away, no pace, dropping to last. Taken to rail, made up ground around turn, worked way forward along rail, hit front 100m out, pulled clear.
Quickly in front, set good pace, well clear entering straight, caught 100m out, boxed on gamely.
Began well, hampered 1000m, dropping behind midfield. Caught behind traffic early in straight, steadied and shifted out for run 200m, finished off nicely.
Began fairly, hampered 1000m, hard ridden to occupy box seat 800m. Raced in restricted room top of straight before finishing off nicely.
Pressed forward on jumping but left without cover after 700m. Covered extra ground turn, wide into straight, finished off well to grab 3rd placing. Demoted on protest.
Pressed forward from start, hampered 1000m, settling one-out, one-back. Remained in contention up the straight before emptying 100m.
Hard ridden from an outside draw to race outside leader to straight. Kept on gamely to 200m before tiring.
Pushed forward from wide gate, steadied 900m to get cover and shuffled back to rear. Made no impression in straight.
Began fairly, ridden to take forward position, steadied 1000m to obtain cover. Dropped out of contention rounding turn and finished tailed out. (Unacceptable performance).
Moderately away, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, travelled well throughout, improved from 600M, finished off very well in straight to score.
Slightly slow out, raced 3 to 4 lengths back in 6th, same position on turn, finished off very strongly in straight to get 2nd.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 2 to 3 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, crowded for room near 300M, made some progress to get 3rd without threatening the first two.
Slightly slow out, raced 4 to 5 lengths back, raced tight near 550M, made some headway in straight to make frame without threatening.
Moderately away from a wide draw, positioned 2nd to turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped well, showed good speed to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead to turn, peaked early in straight, headed near 250M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back to race 6 lengths back at rear, there to turn, made minor progress in straight, never a threat to the first few.
Raced at rear, slightly improved on turn, widest in straight, showed no progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced wide in midfield, no cover from 1100M, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Broke well, positioned behind the pace and waited. Shaken up 750m, rolled forward 3-wide into straight, worked home strongly to win on the post.
Got off well, steadied passing 2000m to get cover, dropping to rear. Began forward move 1050m, circling field to lead 500m out. Given reminders passing 200m but run down on line.
Jumped fairly, looked for cover, positioning behind midfield. Blundered and unbalanced 900m when bumped, urged forward from 750m, 4-wide into straight, worked home strongly. (Rider dropped rein 50m).
Out quickly but pulled out of pace battle, settling behind midfield. Given reminder passing 550m, hard ridden in straight, finished off strongly to just miss a placing.
Broke well, restrained and taken in for cover, settling towards rear in one-off position. Took off passing 900m, 4-wide around home turn, made progress to 50m when emptied.
No early pace, settling at rear along rail. Made progress around home turn, switch out in straight and ran on well.
Hard ridden to lead on settling, crossing to fence 2000m. Kicked 2L clear entering back stretch, under pressure from 750m and overtaken 500m. Kept on gamely to 200m before tiring.
Worked way forward, positioning behind the pace 4L from leader. Got shuffled back 900m when several rivals moved forward, under pressure home turn, one-paced in straight.
Began moderately, restrained, shifted across behind runners, dropping to last. Trailed field to straight before running past tired horses.
Pushed forward between horses to race outside leader at first turn. Followed leader back stretch, urged forward passing 500m but ran out of steam 300m and plodded home.
Pressed forward from wide gate before steadied first turn 3L from leader. Became difficult to handle and left wide without cover until 1200m. Lay in rounding home turn, one-paced in straight.
Jumped OK, ridden to hold rail, settling 4L from leader. Stayed in contention till entering straight when showed no response to rider's urgings.
Pressed forward from an outside draw, racing wide without cover some 4L from leader. Under pressure turning for home, one-paced in straight.
Began fairly, eased off heels shortly after, dropping to rear between horses. Shaken up turning for home, made no impression in straight.

Eased up early to be handily placed 6th, 3L off the leader. Had to be worked all the way down the straight before nosing in front at 200m. Pushed all the way home, and just held off the late challenger.
Began well, and then eased early to sit midfield. Ran solidly in the straight, before beginning a run at 200m. Strong to the line and catching winner, but just missed late.
Pushed hard early, and eventually assumed the lead at 1000m. Battled hard before losing the lead at 200m. Stayed on OK, but peaked late and just held off fast finishers for 3rd.
Eased forward from the wide draw to sit forward of midfield. Came wider on the turn, and ran strongly under the stick late.
Bumped on jumping, and then dropped back from the wide draw to sit last. Battled on well down the extreme outside in the straight, and finished last 150m strongly.
Tried to go push up early, but was stuck forward of midfield, 3 wide and without cover from 900m. Prominent early in the straight, but slightly 1 paced and never ran on late.
Taken up early to be well placed 4th/5th on the fence. Held up early in the straight, but had clear run from 300m and only plugged away 1 paced to the line.
Bumped on jumping and dropped back early to sit toward the rear of the field. Plugged away in the straight, without threatening.
Slow away, then crowded on jumping. Sat worse than midfield on the fence. Wider on the turn. Only battled on fairly late.
Cruised forward early and settled midfield. On heels early in the straight and only fully clear at 250m. Ground away steadily without threatening, before coming off heels and easing last 50m.
Cruised out early, and settled towards the rear of the field. Travelled keenly early/mid race and became unbalanced 1000m. Plugged away late under minimal urging.
Slow to begin and got back to the rear of the field. Made no impact late.
Pushed out early to sit 2nd. Had nothing left in the straight, and was eased out early.
Easily worked forward early to be well placed 2nd/3rd. Didn't respond to urging early in the straight, and eased out from 200. Jockey questioned.

Took up running after the first 200 metres, just held on to the line.
Unable to slot in from the widest draw, raced without cover in midfield before improving to 2L back in 4th around home bend, ran on in straight to be nearest on line.
With leaders 3-wide, taken 2L back to 5th approaching home bend, renewed effort after straightening, kept on steadily without threatening.
Travelled wide without cover in 4th some 2L off on far side, gained 2 wide position in 2nd coming onto home bend, kept on without threatening in the run home, lost quinella placing late.
Ridden along towards the rear, gained slightly closer coming off the Rock, produced good late impression under hard driving in the run home.

Moderate start, responded to reminders for closer order 800 metres out, tightened on rail coming onto home bend, saved ground in better than midfield turning in, did not find much room most of way in straight. (Blood in trachea)
Lost many lengths for slowly away, remained one from last entering straight, switched out for a run shortly after, finished off race nicely.
Failed to respond to riding at the start, 2L back and wide in 5th before carried backward to 3L 8th on top of the Rock, fought on steadily in straight, never nearer.
Advantaged by the one draw, taken one back to 3rd on rail at the 600 metres, in similar position turning in, swamped under pressure close to home.
Ridden early stages but never better than midfield, saved ground on rail turning in, never nearer.
Broke well, being taken back when hampered and badly stumbled shortly after the start dropping to the tail-end, never recovered.
Moderate start, gradually dropped towards the rear, never a danger.
Pushed to take the rail and lead, closed off strongly to score.
Hard ridden forward, sat outside the leader, ran on well for 2nd.
Eased at start, took rail, progressed along the fence, lack room 300M, dashed strongly for 3rd.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield along the fence, lack room 300M, dashed well when clear.
Hard ridden forward, box seat, emptied 200M.
Midfield, 2-3 wide, flattened 250M.
Eased back, on heels early, trapped 2-3 wide, held ground in straight.
At back, 2 wide, no dash in final stages.
Eased back, trapped 3-4 wide, checked 500M, lack turn of foot in straight.
Eased back, trapped 3-4 wide, no progress.
Never a factor.
Midfield, trapped 4 wide, hung out badly, tailed out.
Jumped well and sent forward to race speed, challenged strongly home turn, quickened nicely to win easily.
Jumped well, settled leaders back, pushed along home turn to improve, worked home solidly.
Taken back at start to settle at rear, commenced forward move around runners passing 600m, ran home strongly.
Settled midfield, made steady ground in straight, awkward late.
Settled in front, urged along 500m, battled on one paced.
Jumped awkwardly, rider unbalanced and crowded, settled towards rear, steadied at 500m when attempting tight run, held up 250m and ran on fairly.
Settle off pace, under pressure to improve home turn, battled fairly in straight.
Raced tight shortly after start, settled midfield, shuffled back passing 600m, kept battling to the finish.
Settled towards rear, commenced forward move passing 900m, hard ridden home turn and weakened in straight.
Settled towards rear, ridden along to improve near 600m, under pressure home turn, weakened in straight.
Settled worse than midfield, awkward on heels at 650m, failed to run on.
Settled at rear, forward move passing 700m, asked for effort on straightening but failed to respond and gave ground in straight.
Outpaced from gates, settled beyond midfield, striding awkwardly, eased off rail 600m, ridden 350m, hit top gear final 150m centre track, struck lead final strides.
Speedy start & rousted to lead 3 deep, joined 1000m, shifted 1 off & settled close 2nd 700m, driven into stretch, led 200m under drive, headed 130m, rallied to claim 2nd.
Moderate start, rolled to handy 1 off with cover, flat-footed & lost 1L 650m, niggled 550m, shifted wide & driven on turn, ran on to lead 140m, faltered & headed close home, lost 2nd last stride.
Slightly slow break, eased to settle well back 1 off, ridden 450m, sprinted strongly down centre, nearest finish.
Fast break but soon outpaced, drifted back to midfield 1 off with cover, driven wide final turn, ran on for minor headway without threatening.
Broke well, nudged along 1 back on rail, driven 300m but trapped in pocked & steadied, hemmed in & checked off heels 200m, found gap 70m & driven, too late to challenge.
Started well & vied for lead 1000m, snagged to 1 back 1 off 750m, switched out & driven 300m, boxed on evenly.
Prominent at break, 4 deep & snagged 1000m to 3deep 1 back, lost cover 750m & rolled to close 3rd, pressed home turn, driven 300m, soon all out, tapered closing stages.
Broke well, on rail & pressed lead 1000m, narrow lead 700m, driven 300m, all out & headed 200m, faded.
Reared at start & almost dislodged rider, allowed to tack on at own speed, settled back on rail, clicked up 320m, unable to make headway.
Eased from gates, settled rear 1 off & outpaced, niggled 650m, hard-ridden 400m, widest into straight, couldn't come on.
Started ok, lacked toe & nudged along to midfield on rail, niggled 660m, driven into stretch, found nil & faded tamely.
Jumped fast, natural speed to settle 3rd on rail, box-seat run, clicked up 550m, pushed off rail 400m, challenged 3 deep, hit lead final strides.
First to break, urged forward to lead, crossed to rail for 1L lead 1000m, pressured & joined 500m, ridden entering straight, kicked clear, grabbed final strides.
Away OK, eased, settled near rear 1 off, ridden 500m, charged home, nearest at finish.
Jumped well, eased into midfield spot on rail, keen early, ridden 400m, had his chance, outgunned late.
Slightly slow jump, checked shortly afterwards, straight to rail, settled beyond midfield, ridden 420m, railed through, short of room 220m, finished solidly.
Slightly awkward start, allowed to stride into 4th 1 off, niggled 550m, driven soon after, stayed on one-paced.
Eased from wide gate, back to last by 850m, ridden 500m, found line nicely between runners.
Broke on terms, eased to beyond midfield spot 1 off, held together until 350m, found little when asked.
Slightly slow to muster, posted 3 deep no cover beyond midfield, up to midfield spot 500m, widest into straight & ridden, no threat.
Broke on terms, stranded 3 deep just beyond midfield 1st turn, eased soon after, settled beyond midfield 3 wide, hard ridden 500m, weakened.
Slightly awkward start, last early, settled near rear on rail, nudged 450m, never likely.
Jumped well, ridden to settle handy, initially 2nd 1 off, pulling slightly, joint lead 500m, under pressure 350m, quickly faded, eased down.
Towards the rear, about 5-3/4L behind 3 wide with cover, ran on strongly and held off challenge to score by a neck.
At the rear throughout, about 7-1/2L behind the lead, widest at turn and in the Straight, ran on gamely but couldn't pass the winner.
Sat outside the lead until the field improved near 800M, remained prominent, steadied at 100M but ran on for 3rd.
In front of midfield and improved to race outside the lead near 800M, kept on but was no match to the placegetters.
Raced in the one-off one-back position, improved and assumed the lead at 750M, emptied passing 100M.
Travelled in worse than midfield, about 5-1/4L behind along the rail, finished off one paced in the run home.
In worse than midfield, about 4-1/2L behind but wide, improved to race prominently at 600M, weakened noticeably approaching 150M.
Raced in midfield along the rail, about 3-3/4L behind, away from rail at 800M, checked at 400M, ran on slightly late.
Raced just behind midfield until improved slightly to race in midfield at 800M, not competitive in the Straight.
Travelled in midfield but mostly trapped 3 wide and without cover, dropped off when rounding Home Turn.
Slotted into the box-seat when making the first turn, shifted out to maintain its position at 800M, not competitive.
Rolled forward and led on the fence until 800M, gave ground thereafter and never recovered.
Soon took up running, setting steady pace under a hold. Kicked 2L clear top of the straight and sprinted strongly to the line without being threatened.
Bumped start but recovered quickly and pushed forward to occupy box seat 2L from leader. Had clear running on straightening for home, kept on strongly but unable close gap to leader.
Broke well but soon outpaced, dropping to rear along fence. Swung wide into straight, taken to centre track and ran on well, picking up strongly final 200m.
Jumped well, strode forward at own pace, settling behind midfield along rail. Switched out for clear running in the straight and finished off nicely.
Away well, driven forward to settle one-out, one-back. Looked a chance turning for home but only one-paced in straight.
Began fairly, then restrained and shifted across behind runners, settling at rear. Taken to centre track on straightening for home and ran on fairly.
Pressed forward from widest draw, settling one-off in midfield, 4L from leader. Covered extra ground around turn and made no impression in straight.
Began fairly, then driven forward, settling along rail 4L from leader. Stayed on rail around turn but only one-paced in straight.
Slow into stride, shifted across behind runners and last on settling. Made some headway around turn but only one-paced in straight.
Jumped OK, ridden along in midfield but away from fence. Checked approaching 1000m, swung wide into straight, found little when asked
Broke well, pressed forward to race outside leader. Lay out after 800m and made turn awkwardly. Spent force on straightening and faded.
No early speed, settling at rear. Shuffled back to last around home turn and found nothing in straight despite hard riding.
Jumped well from a tricky gate, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, kicked clear after turning in, scored easily.
Began well, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, kept on well in straight to get 2nd without posing any threat to the winner.
Taken back to race at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, same position on turn, angled out in straight and made good progress to get 3rd.
Taken back to settle worse than midfield, improved from near 600M, made some progress early in straight, peaked final 100M, stayed on for 4th.

Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 5 lengths or so back on rail, same position on turn, no clear running near 250M, made minor progress when clear thereafter. (Lost right front plate after the 900M.)
Bumped start, positioned 3 lengths or so back on rail, there to turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Bumped start, no early speed, raced 6 lengths or so back at rear, improved from near 500M, taken wide in straight and made minor progress. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail for the majority of the race, kept to inside after straightening and made minor progress.
Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Began fairly, raced wide behind midfield, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight and eased.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide in 4th, slightly improved from 600M, peaked near 400M, emptied in straight. (Left front tendon injury reported following day.)
Began fairly, raced in midfield, improved from near 600M, very wide on turn, emptied early in straight, finished tailed out. (Lame right front leg.)
