Well there, hit the front 600 metres out, laying in off the stands rail when headed at the 400 metres, fought on dourly to assert authority final strides.
In front early, narrowly headed approaching the course proper, renewed effort to re-gain advantage over 250 metres out, only to be caught close to home.
Well there, hit the front under pressure at the 400 metres briefly, faded inside the final 200 metres.
Well there, weakened under pressure from the 600 metres.
Soon tailed-off despite given reminders, never a factor.
With leaders briefly, dropped away quickly from over half-way out.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Pressed forward, box seat, not suited by the fast tempo, closed off strongly 400M, led 150M, just beaten in last few strides.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 2 wide, ran on well to the line for 3rd.
Hard ridden to take the rail and led at fast sectionals, ran on strongly until 150M overhauled, checked 50M.
Eased back, took rail, benefited by the fast pace, made steady ground 300M.
Pushed to obtain a more prominent spot in front of midfield, trapped 3 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, flattened 200M.
Pushed early but not muster, 2 wide, at back, favoured by the fast tempo, made minor ground 200M.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast pace, emptied 300M.
Bumped start, at rear, 2 wide, benefited by the fast sectionals, ran on fairly in straight.
At back, trapped 3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, no dash.
Checked start, took rail at rear, benefited by the fast pace, no progress.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, trapped 3 wide, never improved.
Suited by the fast tempo, never competitive at rear.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the fast pace, soon dropped off 600M.
Settled midfield, eased off rail home turn to improve, challenged strongly at 300m, sprinted clear 150m for impressive win.
Bumped at start, settled off pace, asked for effort at 400m, ran home strongly in straight.
Sent forward and raced on pace, tried hard entire straight but no match for winner.
Led easily, travelling well home turn and asked to quicken on straightening, fought on okay.
Tightened shortly after the start and settled at the rear, crept closer midrace along rail, pushed along home turn and ran home steadily.
Settled behind midfield, forward move passing 1200m, moved up to challenge home turn but failed to quicken and one paced to the finish.
Settled midfield, awkward at 1400m, steadied at 900m, urged along home turn, battled fairly to the line.
Taken back at the start, widest on straightening, ran home fairly.
Settled towards rear, one paced in straight.
Bumped at start, settled behind leaders and raced keenly, made no impression in straight.
Settled behind midfield and travelled wide without cover, one paced in straight.
Sent forward to settle outside leader, travelling okay home turn, quickly under pressure in straight and gradually gave ground.
Bounded at start and lost ground to settle at rear, never in it.
Pushed forward from an outside gate to lead passing 950m, pulling 3L clear turning for home. Kept on strongly in the straight for an easy win without being challenged.
First into stride but overtaken passing 950m. Thereafter chased leader without being able to narrow the gap.
Broke well then restrained to find cover, settling one-out in midfield position. Turned a little wide, ran on steadily to grab third placing.
Ridden early to obtain forward position but kept 3-wide without cover 4L from leader on settling. Boxed on gamely in straight losing third spot close to line.
Steadied soon after start and shifted across behind runners, settling at rear. Forced wide turning into straight by fallen horse and ran on fairly down centre track.
Slow into stride, ridden to make up ground, settling behind midfield. Blundered 450m when inconvenienced by fallen horse, one-paced in straight.
Ridden early to find cover but still 3-wide behind midfield on setting. Wide around home turn and one-paced in straight.
Hampered shortly after start but pushed forward to hold rail 6L from leader. Steadied off heels passing 600m, then severely checked 450m because of fallen horse. Faded.
Began fairly, no pace, dropping towards rear. Under pressure turning for home and finished tailed out.

Placing: UR
Comment: Checked shortly after start, pushed forward to midfield and settled. Severely checked 450m to avoid fallen horse dislodging rider. Found to be a "roarer."

Placing: FE
Comment: Broke well, ridden to hold forward position, settling one-out, one-back. Shaken up turning for home but broke left front leg 450m and fell. Put down humanely.

Placing: UR
Comment: Began awkwardly, losing ground and dropping to rear. Blundered when taking evasive action from fallen horse and dislodged rider.
Bumped, unbalanced start, then pressed forward but kept wide by riderless horses. Urged forward turning for home, 4-wide into straight, hit front 400m, kept finding under pressure.
Pressed forward from outside gate to hold forward position but left without cover after 900m. Took closer order around turn to look chance 400m but unable to close gap on winner final 200m.
Broke OK, ridden along between horses, settling in midfield 3L from leader. Made progress around turn and kept on gamely in straight.
Very slow, losing considerable ground and settling at rear. Taken to centre track on entering straight and finished off gamely.
Began awkwardly, bumped and unbalanced, dropping to rear. Shifted ground several times and checked 500m when difficult to manage. Ran on steadily in straight. Racing manners unacceptable.
Not much early pace, settling behind midfield along rail. Took closer order around turn, ran on fairly between horses in straight.
Began OK but hampered by riderless horse near 1250m, dropping to behind midfield. Taken wide entering straight and boxed on fairly.
Pressed forward from outside gate but kept wide by riderless horses before racing outside leader. Looked chance passing 400m, kept on gamely to 200m before tiring.
Began awkwardly, pushed forward, racing one-off 2L from leader. Under pressure turning for home and gave ground steadily in straight.
Bumped start, pressed forward to hold rail 3L from leader. Stayed on rail around turn but spent force on straightening and faded.
Fractious in gate, reared at start and lost considerable ground. Trailed field to straight, ran past beaten horses.
Ridden early but forced to race wide in midfield. Turned wide and faded in straight.
Hard ridden to lead on settling, holding narrow lead to turn. Gave ground soon after straightening for home and finished tailed out. Unacceptable performance.

Placing: UR
Comment: Bumped and unbalanced at start, then crowded out, blundered and dislodged rider.
Sent forward to take the fence and led by 3/4L, kept on and held off late challenges to score by 1/2L.
Settled in midfield, 3L behind along the rail, slightly held up after 250M, ran on nicely thereafter.
Crowded at start, pushed to be fore of midfield, 2-3/4L off but wide and without cover, kept on well to take 3rd.
Pushed forward, checked and lost running when being crossed at 900M, sat 3/4L off thereafter, ran on one paced.
Bumped start, raced towards the rear, 6L behind 2 wide, made good ground and ran on gamely to the line.
Awkward start, ridden and settled in worse than midfield, 4-1/4L behind 3 wide with cover, improved slightly.
In behind midfield, 4L behind along the rail, awkward to heels at 350M and was then held up, made slight ground once cleared.
Raced in midfield, sat 3L behind the lead 2 wide, kept on one paced going to the line.
Bumped start, raced at the rear, checked when crowded near 900M, made minimal ground only.
Travelled in front of midfield, sat 2L off along the fence, kept on until 200M and weakened.
Taken back and raced at the rear, saved some ground late only.
Raced prominently, sat about 2-3/4L off but trapped wide and without cover, dropped off badly at 300M.
Broke well, ridden to find cover, settling midfield in one-off position. Swung wide into straight. Picked up momentum, hit front 150m, pulled clear.
Lunged at start and slow into stride. Taken to fence and vigorously ridden to make up ground, though still well back. Swung wide into straight and finished off strongly.
No early speed, dropping to rear. Last around turn and into straight, switched out and finished strongly down centre track.
Began fairly, ridden to make up ground, settling behind midfield along rail. Stayed on rail around turn, held for run top of straight before finishing off nicely between runners.
Bumped start, pressed forward holding rail 3L from leader. Checked turning into straight, blocked for run 200m and not tested until after passing 150m, kept on fairly.
Hard ridden from outside gate to get forward position, settling one-out, one-back. Made progress around turn, hit the front with 250m to go before run ended.
Broke well, allowed to slide forward but bumped and unbalanced passing 900m, settling 5L from leader. Took closer order around turn, looked chance 200m before running out of steam.
Ridden along early to hold rail, settling 6L from leader at midfield. Switched out turning for home, kept on fairly to 200m before tiring.
First out but soon joined by another, the pair pulling well clear on settling. Bumped and unbalanced rounding turn, kept on fairly in straight until flattened 100m.
Steadied shortly after jump and shifted across behind runners, settling towards the rear. Lay out turning for home, one-paced in straight.
Jumped OK, steadied, shifted across behind runners and last on settling. Stayed at rear around turn and failed to respond to rider's urging in straight.
Hard ridden to take narrow lead on settling but kept away from rail by inside runner. Under pressure early straight gave ground from 300m. Unacceptable performance.
Led early stages, sat back behind leader entering home turn, finished strong up the rail through the final 300M, wrestled the lead 100M out and held firm to the line for 4 consecutive wins.
Held up 2-wide in mid-division but never far off from the pace, into clear 350M, ran on well to go 2nd near line but unable to reel in winner.
Behind midfield, shifted wide 600M, had every chance on straightening, kept going solidly to the line under 10 lb claiming rider, got up for 3rd last stride.

From wide draw caught 3-wide no cover for majority of the race, moved to a prominent spot outside leaders 500M, led narrowly 300M out, fought hard to the line, caught nearing 100M and edged out to 4th late.
Taken back from wide barrier, in the rear 5-6Ls off the pace middle stages, held up until 300M, worked home well down outside over final 200M but always held by leaders.
Urged along to take the lead passing 900M, lay out home turn, headed inside 300M, faded over final 150M.
Towards the rear and no closer than 3-wide throughout, brought widest on straightening, ran on fairly to the line.
Dropped back to the rear 5-6Ls off the pace, responded fairly passing 400M and never troubled the leaders.
Held up midfield along the fence, couldn't go on passing 250M, kept on same pace to the finish.
Towards the rear, inclined to lay out home turn, pushed wider by rival passing 600M, failed to finish off.
Always close up, tracked leader 2-wide, couldn't sustain run passing 250M and weakened to last. Ran well below par.
Jumped OK, ridden but slow to muster, dropping to last before improving slightly in one-off position. Swung wide into straight and finished strongly down centre track to win close home.
Crowded out start, pushed forward, settling behind midfield 6L from leader. Swung wide into straight, taken to centre track and finished off strongly.
Broke well, ridden along between horses before finding rail 4L from leader. Stayed on rail around turn, blocked for run top of straight, switched out 300m and finished strongly.
Off nicely, pressed forward, settling one-out, one-back. Improved position around turn, hit front 400m, well clear passing 200m, run down final strides.
Ridden to find cover, positioning ahead of midfield in one-out position. Urged forward turning for home, looked a chance 200m before turning one-paced.
Hampered start, restrained, shifted across behind runners, last on settling. Made progress turning for home, kept on fairly in straight.
Jumped OK but no pace, dropping to rear. Dropped to last around home turn, taken to centre track on straightening, ran on steadily.
First out but unable cross to fence and settled outside rival 1400m. Retook lead 1000m but still unable to cross to fence. Overtaken 400m, kept on fairly before tiring final 200m.
Jumped well, pressed forward, settling in box seat 2L from leader. Came off fence to pass tiring runner 400m, then switched in again, kept on fairly to 200m before tiring.
Ridden along early to hold fence in midfield, steadied 1400m when crowded, lost position around turn, one-paced in straight.
Fractious in gate, slow to jump, dropping to rear but wide. Allowed to improve passing 1200m, circling field to within 2L of leader at 400m before tiring and dropping back.
Jumped well, ridden to find cover but stuck 4-wide until 700m. Made some progress around turn but spent force in straight.
Began fairly, ridden along, positioning behind midfield away from fence. Got shuffled back around turn, found nothing under pressure in straight.
Broke well from wide gate, hard ridden to clear inside runners to get to rail 1300m. Overtaken 1000m but stayed a half-length inside leader to straight before tiring.
Cruised out early to settle around midfield. Widest on the turn, and ran strongly over the last 200m. Got in front last 50m, and no had no threats late.
Began well, but dropped back soon after to sit worse than midfield. Switched inside at the top of the straight for clear run, and lead by 150m. Peaked last 50m, and just beaten for 2nd.
Eased forward early and settled forward of midfield, 1 off the fence. Wider on the turn, and progressed solidly in the straight.
Only cruised forward early, and settled towards the rear of the field. Held the rail in the straight, and stayed on solidly late.
Eased back early and settled at the rear of the field. Wide on the turn and progressed solidly to the line without threatening a place.
Pressed forward from the inside draw to settled 3rd, on the fence. Stayed on OK early in the straight, but peaked at 100m and dropped out from there.
Taken up to be forward of midfield early, 1 off the fence. Crowded and taken out at 350m. Battled on fairly after that, without threatening.
Pushed hard early to be clear leader in the back straight. No kick in the straight and dropped out from the 200m.
Dropped back early from the wider draw to sit at the rear of the field. Went searching for a run early in the straight, but only ran on fairly when clear in the straight.
Taken up to be handily placed 4th/5th, 3 wide with no cover. Lay out from 500m. Prominent early in the straight, but 1 paced from there and eased out late.
Cruised forward early, settling midfield. Steadied off heels 1250m. Clipped heels and almost brought down at the 350m. Recovered, but race was effectively over from that point.
Pressed forward early, eventually settling 4th/5th, 1 off the fence. Checked and lost run 350m, and not pushed to the line from that point.
Pushed from the wide draw to sit 2nd. Never responded in the straight and was eased from the 150m.
Bounded on jumping, unbalanced and lost many lengths on jumping. Played no effective part in the race.

Never far off in 5th, checked on final turn, fought on under pressure to assert authority inside the 100 metres.
Waited with towards the rear on rails, switched 3-wide approaching the Rock, made swift progress rounding home bend but steadied before straightening, ran on well but winner too good.
Settled in midfield, hugged rails turning for home, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled at the back from the widest gate, commenced move from the 500 metres, swung widest turning in, quickened well to hold every chance 100 metres but unable to sustain effort final stages.

Held up behind midfield, allowed to gain closer 3-wide going up the Rock, sustained progress 4-wide rounding home bend to lead on straightening, had no more to give when headed inside the final 100 metres.
Driven to lead early, ceded advantage passing the 1600 metres settling one back in 3rd or 4th on rails, awkwardly placed and steadied turning in, ran home one-paced.
In last few to straight, saved ground turning for home, baulked for a run early in straight, kept on well to finish.
Broke well, soon shifted back to behind midfield, drifted to last on final bend, produced good late impression inside the final 150 metres.
Given early reminders, close up in 4th before gradually taken back to midfield half-way out, kept on at the one pace despite hampered early in straight.

Began well, settled 3-wide without cover in midfield, took closer order rounding stables bend reaching 3rd into back straight, came under pressure turning for home when jostled between runners, soon dropped out.
Drawn wide, worked on the first bend to take up running passing the 1600 metres, held running until swamped inside the final 300 metres.
Prominent, found no extra after the final turn.
Eased at start, took rail, harmed by the slow pace, made its run around the field 3-4 wide, unleashed strong finishing efforts 300M to score.
Pushed early, trapped 2-3 wide in midfield, made early move 800M, closed off strongly 300M for 2nd.
Hard ridden to keep up in front of midfield, 2 wide, held up 300M, dashed well when clear.
Pushed to hold the rail in front of midfield, dashed strongly 300M.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, 2-3 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, dashed well 300M run ended 100M.
Box seat, benefited by the slow pace, no turn of foot in straight.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, suited by the slow tempo, flattened 200M.
Took rail easily and led at slow sectionals, out of fuel 250M.
Eased back, took rail, harmed by the slow tempo, dashed only fairly.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, no progress.
Eased back, never a factor.
Never competitive, tailed out.
Jumped well, settled midfield, travelling well home turn, eased out to challenge on straightening, quickened nicely for strong win.
Fast out and allowed to settle behind leaders, inside run on straightening to challenge on strongly, no match for winner final 50m.
Bumped at start, pushed along to race on speed, challenged strongly at 200m and fought on solidly to the line.
Bumped at start, quickly gathered pace to lead, asked for effort on straightening and battled solidly to the line, weakened final 50m.
Nice early speed to settle outside leader, travelling okay home turn but unable to quicken and battled fairly to the line.
Taken back at start, commenced to improve along rail mid race, ran home fairly in straight.
Pushed along early to settle better than midfield, urged along 350m to make forward move, one paced in straight.
Settled behind midfield, tightened at 1000m, commence wide run at 400m and ran home fairly.
Taken back early, crowded at 1000m, hard ridden passing 500m, one paced in straight.
Settled midfield, made no impression in straight.
Taken back at start and always rearward.
Taken back at start to settle behind midfield, under pressure 500m and gradually gave ground.
Quickly away but forced to race one-off till finding rail 700m. Under constant pressure from eventual runner-up but kept finding up the straight for narrow win.
Jumped well, pressed forward to race a half length outside leader. Challenged strongly in the straight but just failed.
Got off OK, ridden to find cover, settling one-off 4L from leader. Swung wide turning for home and finished off strongly.
One of the first into stride before electing to take box seat, stalking pace 2L from leader. Put under pressure on straightening but unable close gap.
Broke well from widest draw but kept wide without cover losing ground. Shifted across behind runners passing 700m, made progress around turn and finished off gamely.
Off OK, pressed forward, settling one-out, one-back. Put under pressure turning for home but only one-paced. Had small overreach wound to left front heel.
Beaten for early pace, dropping to rear in one-off position. Still well back on straightening before finishing off fairly down centre track.
Began well, ridden but slow to muster, dropping to rear. Began forward move passing 500m, taken wide in straight, boxed on fairly.
Jumped well but unable handle early pace, dropping back gradually and last into turn. Kept on one-paced in straight.
Quickly into stride but unable sustain effort and raced wide mostly. Lay out turning for home, made no impression in straight.
Began awkwardly losing ground. Pressed forward along rail improving to midfield around turn. Kept on fairly to 150m before tiring.
Began awkwardly then crowded for room before pressing forward but wide 3L from leader. Kept wide around turn, taken wider in straight, found nothing. Rider reported saddle shifted at start.
Away well then slotted 2L behind leader on settling. Pushed forward on straightening, gradually narrowing the gap to win on the line.
Pressed forward from wide gate to lead on settling before crossing to fence passing 1300m. Kicked 2L clear along back stretch, kept on strongly in straight but run down on line.
Began well, not pushed, settling ahead of midfield along fence. Swung wide into straight, picked up momentum, doing best work final 150m.
Jumped well, ridden forward to grab one-out, one-back position 3L from leader. Put under pressure turning for home but unable close gap, finishing one-paced.
Away nicely, taken to fence, stalking pace 4L from leader. Stayed on fence around turn, made some headway early in straight before turning one-pace final 200m.
Off OK, pressed forward before checked at first turn, settling in midfield but wide. Taken wider on straightening for home but only one-paced.
Jumped with field but allowed to find feet, dropping to rear despite slow early pace. Still well back on straightening and only one-paced in straight.
Crowded and lost ground at start, taken to rail while drifting back towards rear. Made some progress around turn but only one-paced in straight.
Off Ok, no pace, dropping to rear between horses. Remained well back to straight, under pressure 500m out but showed little.
Pressed forward from widest draw but raced ungenerously when taken in for cover passing 1300m. Failed to respond to rider's urgings in straight and eased down when beaten.
Began fairly, no pace, dropping to rear but 3-wide. Kept wide along back stretch and made no impression in straight.
Jumped OK but restrained and shifted across behind runners, settling last but 3-wide. Clear last along back stretch and never in the hunt.
Pushed forward and took rail near 600M to lead, kept on going and held on to score by 3/4L.
Failed to muster and settled in midfield, 3L behind 2 wide, showed good dash after 300M, kept on going to take 2nd.
Settled to race in worse than midfield, 4-3/4L behind 2 wide, covered nice ground and hit the line strongly.
Travelled in front of midfield along the rail initially, taken to 2 wide to improve near 600M, stayed on.
Raced towards the rear, 4L behind along the rail, made good ground and ran on well to the line.
In front of midfield, 1-1/2L off pushed to 3 wide and without cover near 600M, kept on one paced home.
Eased and raced at the rear, sat 6-3/4L behind 2 wide, made ground steadily and ran on to the line.
Pushed forward settled to race in box-seat, in touch until 100M, found nothing thereafter. (Lame right front leg)
Travelled in midfield, 3-1/4L behind but trapped wide and without cover until 600M, one paced home.
Settled to race in midfield, 3-1/2L behind along the rail, found nothing in the Straight.
Ridden to obtain forward position but held 3-wide in midfield until crossing to fence 600m. Shifted out turning for home, finished strongly between horses to win on the line.
Away nicely, grabbing rail and keeping leaders racing wide. Stayed on rail in straight and finished strongly to just fail.
Restrained on jumping from wide barrier, shifted across behind runners and last on settling. Last into straight before finishing strongly between horses to fail narrowly.
Away well, pressed forward, settling one-out 3L from leader. Four-wide into straight, surged forward to lead 100m, swamped close to line.
Began fairly, no pace, settling at rear. Lost ground 1000m when shifted out abruptly, taken to centre field on straightening, finished strongly to just miss the frame.
Away OK but not pushed, holding fence 6L from leader. Made some progress home turn but blocked twice in straight before switching out and finishing nicely.
Pressed forward from outside gate to lead but kept 3-wide by inside runners until kicking clear 600m. Kept on well to 100m when flattened.
Jumped well, hard ridden to stay inside leader in one-off position, keeping within a half length till 500m. Kept chasing till squeezed out 150m.
Began fairly, ridden along but stuck 3-wide behind midfield. Kept wide along back stretch, widest into straight, ran past beaten horses final 200m.
Had head turned when gates opened and slow into stride, then inconvenienced 1000m, dropping to rear. Took inside run in straight closing off nicely till blocked 100m and eased.
Got off with field then raced behind midfield in one-off position to straight. One-paced final 200m. Rider dropped whip passing 200m.
Hard ridden to hold forward position but stuck wide without cover 4L from leader. Spent forced on straightening and gave ground quickly final 200m.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 3 lengths back on rail, easy run throughout, improved along the rail on turn, angled out in straight and finished off very strongly to score narrowly.
Began well from a wide draw, positioned nicely in 3rd, improved from 600M, took the lead on turn, kicked clear early in straight but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Steadied start to back of midfield 1 off with cover, slightly improved on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to be nearest on line.
Away with them, positioned 2 wide in 4th, carried wider near 650M, got no cover thereafter, kept on evenly after turning in, just lost 3rd late.
Jumped well from a tricky gate, unable to slot in early, sent forward to race prominently, same position to near 500M, 2 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly in straight.
Average to begin, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide without cover behind midfield, slightly improved in the middle stages, finished off evenly in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 7 lengths back on rail, still 6 lengths or so back on turn, closed off moderately, had to switch lane near 100M, passed a few late. (Lame left front leg.)
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, one-paced in straight.
Began only fairly and crowded losing ground, raced 4 to 5 lengths back on rail behind midfield, kept to inside after turning in, finished off one-paced.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, still well back on turn, made little progress in straight.
Jumped with them, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead in the middle stages, headed near 500M, emptied early in straight, dropped off tamely. (Lost right front plate.)
Away with them, unable to slot in early, taken back to race 3 wide at rear, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight, never a threat.

Jumped fairly, settled not far off on rail, soon came to challenge after straightening, responded well to hit the front inside the 100 metres, won going away.
Moderate start, led or disputed lead to straight, gained narrow advantage on straightening but swept past by fast-finishing winner inside the final 100 metres.
Ridden and given a reminder after the first 200 metres, gained slender advantage over 800 metres out, narrowly headed into straight, kept on steadily without quickening.
Settled in midfield on rail, saved ground turning for home, baulked for a run 200 metres out, kept on steadily without quickening.

Average to begin, positioned 4 lengths or so back on rail, same margin back on turn, no daylight early in straight, made some headway when clear final 200M. (Lost left front plate shortly after the start.)
Jumped well but soon taken 2L back 2-wide in 5th, switched out for a run turning for home, one-paced.
Slow to muster, niggled along and wide behind midfield, did not find much room at about 200 metres, kept on same pace to finish.
Pressed forward from a wide gate to hold 3rd 3-wide without cover, similar position turning into straight but soon dropped out.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, remained well behind to straight, ran past well-beaten horses inside final 200 metres.
Raced wide throughout, hard ridden to hold prominent position early, hampered and lost ground 600 metres out, one-paced in home straight.
Soon dropped to the rear, shifted wide turning into straight, found nothing under pressure.
Soon dropped well behind, never seen with a chance.
Shared the lead easily, pace good, hung on strongly to score.
Hard ridden forward to share the lead, pace good, closed off strongly, just beaten in 2nd.
Award away, pressed forward to share the lead, pace good, ran on for 3rd.
At back, pace good, progressed steadily 250M.
Shared lead easily, pace good, ran on until 150M flattened.
Slow away, at back, pace good, made some ground 200M.
Hard ridden forward, pace good, ran on until 200M weakened.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, pace good, ran on ok.
Midfield, pace good, ran on fairly.
Slow away, at rear, pace good, no dash in final stages.
Slow away, at rear, pace good, never improved.
Behind midfield, pace good, no progress.
Never competitive at back.
Slow away, never a factor.
Pushed along early to hold midfield position, urged along to improve passing 700m, finished strongly to gain upper and final stages.
Taken back from wide gate to settle at rear, crept closer midrace along rail, eased out on straightening for clear running and finished strongly to just miss.
Jumped smartly and took lead, travelled nicely in running, kicked strongly on straightening, overpowered late.
Crowded at start, settled towards rear, improved along rail passing 700m, pushed along early straight and ran home well.
Settled on pace, urged along home turn but one paced in straight.
Jumped well, raced in midfield position wide without cover, forward move near 800m, and issued strong challenge in straight before weakening late.
Taken back from wide gate to settle at rear, improved along rail home turn and ran home fairly.
Taken back at start, widest on straightening and finished fairly.
Settled forward of midfield, under pressure home turn, one paced in straight.
Crowded at start and settled towards rear, pushed along home turn, one paced in straight.
Jumped awkwardly and bumped, pushed along to settle outside leader, raced keenly middle stages, quickly under pressure on straightening and gave ground. Must Trial
Ridden along early to settle forward of midfield, under pressure 800m and gradually gave ground.
Pushed along early before easing back to settle at rear and remained there throughout.
Bumped at start, settled midfield and commenced to give ground from 600m.
Broke well, rolled forward to race three-quarter length outside leader. Shaken up top of straight and gradually wore down leader to win on the post.
Away nicely and soon in box seat keeping tabs on leaders. Switched out on straightening and finished off strongly doing best work final 200m.
Quickly away, strode forward to lead passing 1450m then set slow pace to straight. Picked up speed when put under pressure 400m, kept on strongly but run down in final stride.
Began fairly, then driven forward to hold rail 3L from leader. Stayed on rail around turn and ran on gamely in straight.
Slow into stride and then severely checked approaching first turn, dropping to rear. Well back turning for home, taken to centre track and finished off nicely.
Jumped OK but checked before first turn and dropped to rear in one-out position. Took closer order back stretch, boxed on one-paced in straight. Rider said came off bridle 700m from home.
Broke well, ridden forward before seeking cover 1400m, slotting behind midfield though still wide. Swung wide into straight and boxed on fairly.
Away OK, ridden along in midfield but wide. Made up some ground around home turn but one-paced in straight.
Jumped with field, ridden along settling midfield along rail. Stayed on rail around turn and into straight but only one-paced.
Began awkwardly, driven forward, settling 3L from leader in one-off position. Got shuffled back turning for home, one-paced in straight.
Pressed forward from outside draw, racing wide without cover 2L from leader. Continued to race wide around home turn, kept on fairly to 200m before tiring.
Restrained on jumping and shifted across behind runners from outside draw but bumped and unbalanced 1400m dropping to rear. Shaken up turning for home but found little.
Away OK but severely checked approaching first turn, dropping behind midfield. Shuffled back to last around home turn. No closing kick.
Broke well, grabbing box seat 2L from leader. Kept tabs to straight, then hard ridden, wearing down rivals to get nose in front on line.
Began awkwardly, crowded, then worked way forward to lead 1300m before giving away 1150m and tailing leader. Retook lead 300m, kept on strongly but nosed out on line.
Pressed forward from outside draw, settling one-out, one-back 3L from leader. Closed in around turn and boxed on strongly in straight only to lose narrowly.
Jumped with field, not pressed, settling behind midfield close to rail. Swung wide entering straight and finished off strongly to finished a half length from winner.
Bumped and unbalanced at start, dropping to rear. Taken 3-wide wide around home turn and to centre track on straightening but finished off only fairly.
Jumped OK, not pushed, dropping to rear along rail. Started to race fiercely after being checked 1100m, swung very wide into straight, boxed on fairly.
Steadied soon after start and shifted across behind runners, settling along fence at the rear. Put under pressure 400m, disappointed for run passing 300m, boxed on one-paced when clear.
First into stride but unable handle early pace, dropping to midfield. Shuffled back to last around home turn and found nothing when asked in the straight.
Jumped well, pushed forward to lead 1150m. Pulled 2L clear back stretch but overtaken 300m and faded quickly.
Raced at the rear, about 5-3/4L behind along the rail, made nice ground on outer track, ran on strongly to score by 1/2.
Rolled forward and settled into box-seat, sat 2L off, improved gradually but couldn't hold off the winner's effort.
Rolled forward along the fence and took outright lead near 650M, kept on but couldn't find extra near 100M.
Settled to race just in front of midfield, 2L off 2 wide, showed good dash near 200M, ran on nicely.
Raced in front of midfield, 1-1/2L off 3 wide with cover, improved steadily until 150M, then one paced to the line.
Pushed forward and shared lead in a 2 wide position until 650M, kept on one paced going to the line.
Sent forward and raced prominently in a wide 3 position without cover, one paced in the Straight.
Hard ridden forward but settled to race in worse than midfield, 3-1/2L behind and wide, dropped to last rounding turn, made some ground in the Straight.
Raced in behind midfield, 3-3/4L behind along the fence, held up early in the Straight, kept on going to the line.
Travelled slightly behind midfield, 3-1/4L behind 2 wide, slight dash near 300M, one paced thereafter.
Ridden forward, stayed prominent but trapped very wide, dropped off gradually in the Straight.
Always at the rear, never a factor.
Quickly into stride to lead on settling. Joined up front passing 800m but kicked ahead 400m, pulling away to easy victory.
Lifted front feet as gates opened and began only fairly. Pushed forward along outer fence to settle 3L from leader. Finished strongly final 400m to grab 2nd placing.
Bumped and steadied at start, dropping to behind midfield 5L from leader. Switched in approaching course proper and finished strongly.
Broke well, not pushed, settling 2L off the pace. Put under pressure 400m but started to hang badly, forcing jockey to stop riding momentarily 150m. Boxed on gamely.
Began fairly, bumped, dropping to rear. Lay out and proved difficult to ride when put under pressure 500m and raced ungenerously when making ground final stages. Had superficial abrasion on the nose.
Began well, shifted out to position 1L behind leaders passing 800m. Made some ground when put under pressure 400m but only one-paced final 200m.
Began well, pressed forward, settling a half length inside leader close to outer fence. Failed to close off when put under pressure 400m and faded.
Broke well from inside draw and ridden to obtain forward position, settling 2L from leaders 800m. Stayed in contention to 200m before tiring.
Bumped start, no pace, settling behind midfield two-away from outside fence. Hard ridden final 400m but raced greenly, shifting ground several times in straight.
Bounced OK but no pace and last on settling. Trailed field to straight where ran past beaten rivals.
Broke well, pressed forward to join leader passing 800m. Under pressure from 400m and gave ground gradually.
Jumped OK, no speed, dropping to rear. Dropped to last on entering course proper and found nothing under hard riding.
Sent forward on jumping from draw 1, maintained steady lead to straight under 10 lb claimer, strongly pressed by rival from 250M, held on gamely.
3Ls back in midfield early stages, bustled along to go closer to leaders home turn, surged home over final 200M, just missed.
Urged along to sit outside the pace under 7lb claimer, worked home well and strongly pressed leader from 200M, held in the run home and lost 2nd last strides.
Reserved behind midfield 5Ls off the pace, stayed on well enough but not reached top three.
Settled 3-wide in mid-division, driven out nearing 400M, fought on without making progress on leaders.
Taken back from wide barrier, 5Ls towards the rear, held up for a while passing 500M, couldn't accelerate enough over final 400M.
Unable to cross from draw 11, caught 3 wide no cover chasing leader, kept on one pace on straightening, faded 150M.
Failed to muster speed despite ridden along, raced back in the field, no closer than 3-wide and lay out home turn, never going pace to reach leaders in straight.
Settled down 2-wide in midfield, 5-6Ls to make up 400M but unable to quicken on straightening, never near contention.
Taken back from wide barrier, 8Ls off the pace in rear, gave limited response when driven 500M, didn't factor.
4th chasing leaders early stages, shuffled back over home turn, weakened away inside 400M.
Missed the jump losing a considerable amount of ground, in rear pair 8Ls off the pace, left behind on straightening.
Jumped OK, ridden along, racing one-off in midfield. Began forward move 600m, 4-wide into straight, finished strongly to hit the front 100m and pulling clear.
Broke well, pressed forward but wide to take lead 1600m, crossing to fence 1350m. Joined up front 1200m, headed entering final turn, retook lead 400m and kicked ahead but run down close to line.
Jumped well, pressed forward but wide from outside draw, before settling outside leader 1200m. Took narrow lead around home turn, boxed on gamely in straight before flattened close home.
No pace and last on settling. Made up some ground approaching and around home turn and finished off gamely in straight.
Steadied on jumping and shifted across behind rivals, settling towards rear in one-off position. Still well back on entering straight before finishing off fairly.
Broke well, pressed forward grabbing box seat 2L from leader. Kept tabs to 200m before tiring.
Jumped OK, no pace, dropping behind midfield in one-off position. Got shuffled back turning for home, taken to centre track on straightening, finished off fairly.
Jumped with field, ridden to hold rail position 3L from leader. Became unbalanced when brushed rail approaching 700m but stayed in the hunt before tiring and giving ground final 200m.
Began well, ridden to hold forward position, settling one-out 3L from leader. Raced tightly turning for home, swung wide into straight but unable to make headway.
Pressed forward from outside draw, racing wide till slotting in one-out, one-back 2L from leader at first turn. Came under pressure to hold position from 600m and gave ground quickly.
Began fairly, allowed to stride at own pace, settling behind midfield. Switched out to make run entering straight but found little when asked.
Ridden along from widest gate, taking first turn 4-wide. Kept 4-wide without cover 2L from leader along back stretch and spent force in straight, giving ground gradually.
Jumped OK, no pace, dropping to rear along fence. Put under pressure turning for home but made no impression. Rider reported never travelled on bridle during the race.
Bumped start, shifted in looking for cover, dropping to rear. Clear last approaching final turn and finished tailed out. Unacceptable performance.
Began well, raced 2 wide in 3rd, there to turn, kicked clear early in straight, won easily.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear, slightly improved on turn, angled out early in straight and made good progress to get 2nd.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, similar position on turn, no daylight early in straight, closed off well to get 3rd when clear thereafter.
Slightly slow out, steadied early, recovered to race 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, made some headway early in straight, peaked near 200M, stayed on for 4th.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail at rear, still there on turn, no clear running early until near final 150M, made some progress thereafter.
Away with them, sent forward to race 2 to 3 lengths back on rail, easy run on turn, made minor progress early in straight, peaked near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began very awkwardly from gate 12, raced at rear, improved from near 500M, taken widest in straight and finished off evenly.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, same position on turn, finished off one-paced.
Taken back from a tricky gate, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.

Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in early, sent forward after 1100M to race prominently, 2nd on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter and eased. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began fairly, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced wide in midfield, no cover on turn, emptied in straight and dropped off gradually.
Jumped well, showed early speed to take the lead, easy lead on turn, emptied early in straight.
Crowded out start, raced at tail throughout, detached on turn, finished tailed out, unacceptable performance. (See Racing Incidents.)

Jumped well, settled in midfield on the rail, switched out to challenge upon straightening, responded well inside the final 200 metres to just get up on line.

Ridden positively from a wide draw, settled just off the heels of leader turning into back straight, came under pressure to tackle the leader upon straightening, held every chance but pipped final strides.

Hard ridden, raced keenly in the front rounding stables bend, fought on to resist challenges in straight but unable to sustain effort close to home. (Jockey reprimanded for not riding out to the line.)
Settled mainly in forward of midfield, ran on steadily under pressure to narrowly miss the place-getters.
Settled in last pair, commenced move rounding home bend, made moderate progress inside the final 200 metres.

Worked his way forward from the widest gate, forced 3-wide in midfield before going forward for 2.5L 4th turning into back straight, came under pressure to hold place rounding home bend, yielded ground quickly inside the final 200m.
Settled just better than midfield on the rail, came under pressure upon straightening, found nothing.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, raced keenly early in last few, behind turning in, ran past well-beaten horses.
Jumped well from the one draw, taken back to 2L 3rd on the rail, remained same to straight, soon faded out of contention. (Lame next day)
Began from a wide gate, settled in midfield or slightly worse, came under pressure rounding home bend, faded in straight.
Lacked pace and soon dropped to last few, came under pressure rounding home bend, saved ground on the rail turning in, folded up quickly in straight.
Checked at the start, always struggling at the back. (Lame next day)
Eased at start, took rail, favoured by the fast pace, progress steadily from 600M around the field in 4 wide, dominated from 300M.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily around the field in 4 wide from 400M for 2nd.
Pushed forward, took rail, not suited by the fast tempo, held up 4-2, made some ground when clear.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, not suited by the fast pace, held up 5-3, ran on ok until 150M run ended.
Pushed to take the rail and led at fast sectionals, took box seat middle stages, out of fuel 400M.
Checked badly first bend, at back on the fence, on heels again 600m, made ground 500M around the field in 3 wide.
Took rail and lead, clocked fast sectionals whilst being pressured, out of fuel 250M.
At back, 2 wide, moved forward 900M in 3 wide, soon weakened 400M, checked badly just prior to straightening.
Hard ridden early, midfield 2 wide, moved forward 900M to sit outside leader, emptied 300M.
At back, never improved, tailed out.
Jumped smartly and settled on pace, travelled well, inside run on straightening, quickened nicely to hold off all.
Commenced fairly and settled towards rear, travelling nicely mid-race, forward move passing 500m, widest on straightening and finished strongly.
Jumped well but caught wide without cover in forward position, moved up to issue challenge home turn and tried hard in straight.
Settled towards rear, ran home solidly without threatening.
Crowded at start and lost ground, race back in field, urged along to improve passing 500m, made steady ground between runners in straight, hampered at 100m.
Tightened shortly after start and settled at rear, held up near 200m, ran home well late.
Pushed along early to settle midfield, checked near 100m when finishing nicely. Ride questioned.
Ridden along early to settle leaders back, moved up to challenge home turn but quickly under pressure and weakened out of it.
Taken back to settle at rear, ran home nicely late.
Settled midfield, one paced in straight.
Fast out and ridden along to lead, asked for effort on straightening, no response and gave ground.
Settled handy position, one paced in straight, hampered 100m, awkward late.
Jumped well from wide gate, cut to rail first turn, 2L from leader. Swung wide entering straight, made ground gradually, led passing 120m and then held off late challenge.
Began OK, then taken to fence 3L from leader. Not asked for effort until home stretch when took inside run and finished strongly to miss narrowly.
Jumped with field, then raced in midfield in one-off position. Taken to centre track on straightening and finished off strongly.
Steadied soon after start and shifted in for cover, dropping to rear along fence. Switched out wide entering straight and finished off gamely, doing best work final 200m.
Began awkwardly, losing ground, then ridden to hold position behind midfield. Stayed on rail around turn and ran home steadily in straight to be closest at finish.
Quickly into stride, holding rail, but switched out passing 900m to go past leader at 800, pulling 3L clear approaching 500m. Kept on well in straight until flattened 120m and faded.
Pressed forward to lead on settling, crossing to fence. Overtaken passing 800m, kept on gamely to 200m before tiring.

Began fairly, ridden but didn't muster, occupying trailing position but away from fence. Shifted ground several times approaching and rounding home turn, one-paced in straight. Rider reported travelled greenly.
Restrained shortly after start and shifted across behind runners, dropping to last at first turn. Stayed on rail back stretch and home turn and boxed on fairly in straight.
Jumped OK, ridden to find cover but stuck 3-wide entering back stretch. Remained wide around turn and only one-paced in straight.
Began well, pressed forward, settling one-out, one-back entering back stretch. Shaken up passing 600m to hold position, kept on gamely to 200m before tiring.

Pressed forward 4-wide from outside gate until getting cover 900m when started to race keenly. Under pressure early in straight and eased down final stages. Lame right front leg with stiff and restricted action.
Broke well, quickly in front, setting steady pace. Kicked 3L clear on straightening for home and went to the post unchallenged.
Off fairly, ridden but slow to muster, dropping to rear between horses. Raced keenly passing 900m when checked off heels, taken to centre track on straightening and finished strongly.
Jumped well, ridden to hold rail position before grabbing box sear 2L from leader at first turn. Shaken up 500m to chase leader, kept on strongly but swamped near line.
Began OK, no speed, dropping towards rear along fence. Stayed on fence around home turn and ran on steadily between horses in straight to just miss a placing. Lost left front plate before first turn.
Quickly away, striding forward to hold position one-out, one back around first turn. Swung 4-wide turning for home and boxed on one-paced in straight.
Bumped start, then raced in midfield in one-off position to turn when steadied of heels. Wide into straight, boxed on one-paced.
Restrained on jumping, shifted across behind runners and last on settling. Swung wide into straight and ran on fairly.
Bumped start, no pace, dropping to rear in one-out position. Put under pressure turning for home but only one-paced.
Bumped start, ridden to hold forward position, brushing rail 1000m before settling 4L from leader. Put under pressure turning for home but found little.
Bumped start, pushed forward but 3-wide without cover entering back stretch. Continued to race wide around home turn, given reminder 300m but one-paced.
Pressed forward from outside draw to race outside leader on settling. Kept tabs to straight when ran out of fuel and faded. Eased down when beaten final stages.
Allowed to stride forward from outside draw, racing 4-wide behind midfield before finding cover back stretch. Shuffled back to last around home turn and made no impression in straight.
Pushed and always sat outside the lead, kept going and held off challenges to score by a nose in a photo finish.
Raced in midfield, 2-3/4L behind 2 wide, made move at 800M when others improved, rounded turn 4 wide, kept on and just missed by a nose.
Crowded at start and settled at the rear until entering the Back Straight, ridden to improve and assumed lead along the rail near 700M, ran on to take 3rd in a blanket finish.
Travelled in front of midfield 2 wide until near 700M and made move when others improved, rounded turn 3 wide, ran on okay despite laying in mostly.
Eased back and raced at the rear, 7L behind along the rail, steadied when ran into tight running at 150M, nonetheless improved steadily to be closest at the finish.
Raced in midfield mostly, about 4L behind along the rail, improved slightly near 700M, in touch until disappointed for run near 250M, ran on to the line thereafter.
Settled to race in front of midfield, 2-3/4L off along the rail, dropped to behind midfield when others improved near 700M, ran home one paced.
Slow to jump and at the rear until entering the Back Straight, improved to be front of midfield but made turn very wide, ran on fairly to the line.
Travelled in behind midfield, 4-1/4L behind 2 wide, ridden and improved slightly near 700M, one paced and weakened in the latter stages.
In behind midfield, 5-1/2L behind along the rail, dropped to the rear near 700M, closed off only one paced.
Sent forward, prominent but trapped wide initially, improved to lead from 1200M to 700M, box-seat thereafter, battled on until eased down at 200M.
Ridden forward and raced in box-seat from 1200M, dropped off gradually when rounding turn.
Off well, pressed forward to sit in one-off position 2L from leader. Took closer order around turn, surged through gap along rail to lead passing 300m, kept on strongly to line.
Quickly into stride before electing to drop back along rail 3L from leader. Switched out on straightening and finished off strongly.
Jumped OK, not pushed, racing in midfield in one-out position. Swung wide into straight and finished off nicely to grab minor placing.
Lifted front feet at start and slow into stride. Ridden to make up ground before racing along rail behind midfield. Made turn awkwardly, pressed forward but blocked 200m. Raced tight final 100m.
Jumped OK but no early speed, dropping towards rear close to rail. Made some progress around turn, taken wide in straight, boxed on fairly.
Away nicely, pressed forward to hold position between horses three-quarter length from leader. Improved to race outside leader home turn, hit front 300m, kept on well to 100m before tiring.
Broke well, pressed forward to race 3-wide outside leader. Eased to 4th 2L from leader home turn, battled on gamely in straight until hanging out under pressure final 100m and fading.
Steadied on jumping from outside gate, shifted across behind horses and last on settling. Last into straight before running past tired rivals.
Pressed forward from wide gate, settling 3L from leader but 3-wide. Kept in contention around turn and early in straight before tiring final 200m.
Began fairly, no speed, dropping to rear in one-out position. Taken wide in straight but made little impression though inconvenienced near 250m.
Quickly into stride to lead on settling. Set steady pace to straight but spent force passing 300m and faded.
Jumped OK but beaten for pace, dropping to rear along fence. Stayed on rail around turn but found nothing when put under pressure in straight.
Jumped well, positioned 1-1/2 length behind the leader on rail, easy run throughout, finished off well to score by a neck.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, checked near 600M, still 5 lengths or back on turn, finished off very strongly to be nearest on line, narrowly beaten.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide at rear, severely affected by the broken horse near 600M, well back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to get 3rd late.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, uncontested on turn, kept on well early in straight, headed final 100M, lost 3rd on line.
Began well from a tricky gate, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back in 4th, there to turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked near 150M, stayed on evenly.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, slightly improved on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground throughout, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly.
Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Began fairly, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths back in midfield, improved after 450M, 4 wide turning home, peaked early in straight and weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back to race at rear, slightly improved on turn, failed to close off in straight, never a threat.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield early, carried wide and without cover after 700M, peaked on turn, one-paced in straight.

Placing: PU
Comment: Slightly slow out, raced in midfield, broke down near 600M.

Moderate start, soon recovered along the rail to forward of midfield, came to challenge upon straightening, responded well to take charge over 150 metres out.
Waited with in rear, ran on well down the inner of the straight to snatch 2nd final strides. (Bled)
Ridden early, settled just better than midfield in 5th, moved forward to over 2L back in 3rd on the bend, ran on to hit the front briefly over 200 metres out, swamped close to home.
Settled just better than midfield in 4th or 5th on the rail, switched out for a run entering straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Ridden early but soon dropped behind midfield, saved ground turning in, made modest progress closing stages.
Given a reminder early, shared pace on the rail before ceding advantage 1000 metres out, chased the leader into straight, weakened.
Towards the rear, saved ground turning in, made short-lived effort early in straight.
Over 4L back in 3rd far side, similar distance from the leader but back to 4th rounding home bend, gradually weakened out of contention in straight.
Never better than midfield, ran home one-paced.
Ridden for pace early, took up running on the rail 1000 metres out, led until finding no extra 250 metres out.
Settled at the back, ran past well-beaten horses in the straight.
Taken back to wide in midfield from a poor gate, drifted further back coming onto home bend, no further impression.
Midfield, folded up quickly in straight.
Taken back from the widest gate, never a factor.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, pace good, progress steadily 400M to score.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, pace good, failed to accelerated until 250M, closed off well.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide, pace good, checked 400M, led 300M, hung on well until 100M overhauled.
Behind midfield, pace good, 2-4 wide, progressed steadily 300M, run ended 50M.
Hard ridden forward, took rail, box seat, pace good, ran on until 150M flattened.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, trapped 3-4 wide, pace good, closed off well 200M.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide in the lead, pace good, out of fuel 250M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail behind midfield, pace good, made ground 200M.
Eased to rear, took rail, pace good, progressed steadily 200M.
Slow away, trapped 4-5 wide at back, raced greenly, pace good, made some ground 200M.
Checked at start, struggled to keep up at rear, pace good, raced flat until 150M made ground.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, 3 wide, pace good, ran on ok.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at good pace, hung out badly, emptied 300M.
At back, 2-3 wide, pace good, no progress.
Jumped well, settled forward of midfield, travelling easy home turn, challenged strongly at 300m, gained control at 100m for strong win.
Fast out and pushed along to settle outside leader, pushed along home turn and fought on strongly entire straight.
Settled midfield, taken wide on straightening to challenge and finished strongly.
Bumped at start and settled midfield, looking for a run home turn, pushed along 350m, picked up near 200m and finished strongly.
Steadied shortly after start and settled at rear, commenced to run on in straight, steadied 200m and finished strongly, awkward late.
Slow to begin and settled at rear, bumped at 200m when finishing well along rail.
Settled towards rear, looking for a run on straightening, bumped at 200m and made steady ground to the line.
Pushed along early to obtain lead, quickly under pressure on straightening and one pace to the finish.
Began awkwardly and settled towards rear, widest on straightening and ran on nicely.
Raced on pace, awkward on heels 400m, tried to challenge but faded final 100m.
Settled on pace, shifted out near 700m to improve, loomed to challenge on straightening but found nothing and faded.
Urged along early to hold position forward of midfield, hard ridden 900m and gradually weakened in straight.
Bumped and unbalanced at start and settled worse than midfield, failed to run on.
Raced forward of midfield but wide without cover, weakened in straight.
Hard ridden to lead on settling, then set steady pace to straight. Kicked clear passing 350m and kept finding when strongly challenged final stages to win narrowly.
Broke well, ridden to hold rail 3L from leader at settling. Switched out to make challenge on straightening and finished strongly final 150m to just miss.
Beaten for early pace, settling towards rear but wide. Covered extra ground around home turn, taken wide in straight, finished strongly to grab minor placing.
Bumped start, steadied 1100m losing ground and then raced freely. Made progress around home turn, took inside run in straight, finished strongly to just miss a placing.
Ridden to hold rail before taking sit on leaders on settling. Moved up at the turn-in to look a strong chance but unable close gap to winner.
Ridden along early but wide before getting cover approaching turn, though still wide. Steadied at turn-in, taken to centre track and finished strongly.
Pressed forward from outside gate to race outside leader on settling. Continued to chase leader in straight but swamped close home.
Steadied on jumping and shifted across behind rivals, dropping to rear. Made some progress around home turn, took inside run in straight and ran on well to finish just behind place-getters.
Ridden forward but wide before finding cover, settling one-off at midfield. Switched out on straightening to make challenge but only one paced.
Shifted across behind rivals soon after jump and last on settling. Trailed field to straight and finished off fairly along rail.
Jumped OK, shifted in for cover, dropping to rear but away from fence. Made some headway in straight when put under pressure.
Ridden to get forward position but held 3-wide and without cover 2L from leader passing 1050m. Under pressure in straight and gave ground gradually.
Bumped start, pressed forward, racing between horses 3L from leader at turn. Took inside run in straight but made no impression.
Lifted front feet at start and began only fairly. Hustled along to make up ground before settling worse than midfield. Under pressure turning for home and dropped out in straight.
Broke well but eased to midfield under a tight hold. Came off fence turning for home, finished strongly to win close home.
Jumped OK, taken to rail, 3L from leader. No run early in straight, switched out 300m, surged forward to lead momentarily passing 200m, lay out under pressure and run down close to line.
Bounced well, pressed forward to race one-off 1L from leader. Rolled forward top of straight, joint leader passing 200m, battled strongly but run down close to line.
Jumped OK, shifted in for cover, settling one-off towards rear. Switched out turning for home and finished strongly to just miss a placing.
Crowded out on jumping, no pace, dropping to rear along fence. Made some progress home turn, switched out in straight and ran on well to finish just behind place-getters.
Broke well, grabbing box seat on settling 2L from leader. Closed in turning for home to look a chance but one-paced final 200m.
Hard ridden to lead passing 1450m, cutting to fence and slowing pace. Joined up front passing 200m before flattened passing 150m.
Jumped with field, quickly finding cover in one-out position 4L from leader. Shaken up top of straight but only one-paced.
Broke best but snagged back, dropping to rear in one-out position. Three-wide around home turn, switched out in straight, boxed on fairly.
Outpaced, dropping to rear along fence. Got close to heels around turn, boxed on fairly in straight under hard riding.
Taken out soon after start, then hard ridden but didn't muster, dropping to last. Ran past beaten rivals in straight.
Pressed forward from outside gate, racing wide without cover 2L from leader. Under pressure turning for home and gave ground in straight.
Began awkwardly, switched out to go forward but held 4-wide till getting cover approaching turn. Niggled at to hold position around turn, widest in straight, faded.

Began fairly, pressed forward to race between horses 3L from leader. Under pressure from turn-in and faded. Had blood in trachea and small wound to right front fetlock. Rider said not comfortable in action.
Travelled in behind midfield, about 5-1/2L behind along the rail, ran on nicely and held off challenge to score by 3/4L.
Raced towards the rear, about 7-1/2L behind along the rail, kept on in a tight battle until the final stages, settled for 2nd.
Eased and raced at the back, about 8-1/4L off, shifted to centre track at 300M, ran on strongly to take 3rd.
Raced in midfield, sat about 4L off 2 wide, ran on until the final stages, couldn't hold off 3rd placegetter.
Travelled in behind midfield, 5-1/2L behind 2 wide, swung widest, ran home one paced only.
Raced towards the rear, 6-3/4L behind 2 wide, made slight ground early then passed beaten runners only.
Race at the rear initially, took off and settled to race outside the lead in Back Straight, ran on until 250M only.
Rolled forward and raced in box sea, sat about 2L behind, raced keenly throughout, ran on until 250M and weakened.
Sent forward to take the rail and led by about 3/4L, weakened and headed passing 300M.
Travelled in front of midfield, 3-3/4L behind along the rail, ran on until 200M when found no extra, finished tailed out.
Found no early speed, in behind midfield then gradually improved in Back Straight, wide all along and tailed out.
Always prominent, sat 2-1/2L off 2 wide, dropped to 6th when others improved near 1000M, dropped off at Home Turn.
Rolled forward, prominent but trapped wide, improved to be outside the lead from 1400M until 1000M, gave ground when rounding Home Turn.
Hard ridden from widest gate to lead, crossing to fence 1100m. Put under pressure 400m when strongly challenged but kept finding to score by half a length.
Pressed forward from an outside gate to race outside leader. Shaken up 400m to challenge but unable to run down leader.
Began OK, ridden to hold rail in midfield 4L from leader. Held in traffic top of straight, switched in 350m to improve, ran into tight space 150m and unable stretch out final stages.
Steadied on jumping, shifted across behind rivals and last on settling. Still well back at the turn-in, switched out in straight and finished strongly to just miss a placing.
Began well, rolled forward, settling one-out in midfield 4L from leader. Blocked for run early in straight, switched out 350m, finished strongly to just miss a placing.
Jumped with field, steadied and shifted in for cover, finding the rail towards rear. Switched out turning for home, then finished strongly between rivals, racing tight final stages.

Jumped out at start, restrained and taken in, finding cover but three-wide at rear. Continued to race 3-wide around turn, taken to centre field on straightening and ran on well, making good late ground.
Began fairly, allowed to slide forward at own pace, settling worse than midfield in one-out position. Swung wide into straight, given reminders, boxed on gamely.
No early pace and soon at rear along rail. Last into straight, switched out to make run and finished off nicely.
Began fairly, dropping to rear, then taken to rail, making up some ground to race behind midfield. Switched out top of straight but blocked for run, shifted in to rail 350m and finished off fairly.
Away nicely and soon in box seat 2L from leader. Caught flat-footed 400m when leading pair kicked but kept chasing until swamped close home.
Jumped with field, ridden to get forward position, settling 3L from leader in one-off position. Turned a little wide and one-paced in straight.

Got off well, shifted in for cover, settling worse than midfield but wide. Lost some ground turning for home, taken wide in straight but found little, plodding to line. (Had left front leg over barrier before start)
Jumped well, allowed to slide forward but wide without cover 2L from leader. Kept on well to 300m when tired and dropped out.

Travelled keenly early stages in a very slowly run race, shifted out 1050M and allowed to improve into the lead, led the sprint home from 500M, was strongly challenged final 100M but held sway at the finish.

Raced keenly in a slowly run race, restrained to sit just behind leader early stages, shuffled back to midfield when pace quickened 1000M, 3Ls down at 400M, ran on strongly in the sprint home, line just came too soon.
Settled 2-3Ls back in 4th, pace slow early and middle stages, always within striking distance, sprinted well in the run home but just couldn't reel in the leader. (Blood in trachea.)
Always prominent, tracked eventual winner into straight, fought on honestly but unable to get any closer, outsprinted by 2nd and 3rd final 150M.
Took lead from 1800M, led very slowly and being taken over from 1000M, tried hard to keep up as they sprinted home from 500M, one pace and out of contention mid-straight.
Held up 2nd last in a slowly run race, 4Ls to make up 400M, couldn't reach leaders in the sprint home.
Slow to begin, held up midfield, left flat footed when they sprinted home 500M, never involved.
At the rear 8Ls off the very slow pace, couldn't muster the speed when driven out home turn, soon left behind.
Hard ridden to lead on settling, crossing to fence 1000m and pulling 1.5L clear at turn. Kicked further ahead on straightening and won pulling clear final stages.
Pressed forward from wide gate to race outside leader initially, before dropping 1.5L back at the turn. Left flat-footed 400m when leader kicked, then took up the chase but unable to close gap.
Broke well then ridden to hold rail 4L from leader. Checked off heels around home turn, blocked for run top of straight, shifted in 300m and ran on steadily, hanging on for minor placing.
Slow into stride and last on settling. Switched out turning for home, and ran on steadily down centre track without looking dangerous.
Jumped OK, allowed to find feet, settling worse then midfield in one-out position. Swung wide into straight and ran on fairly while laying in under pressure.
Pressed forward from outside gate, settling one-out, one-back 3L from leader. Rolled forward turning for home to sit outside leader but under pressure final 200m and swamped close home.
Jumped fairly, restrained, dropping to rear in one-out position. Given reminders top of straight and ran on steadily. Had blood at mouth.
Allowed to stride forward from outside gate to race three-wide in midfield. Allowed to stride forward turning for home to get within 2L of leader before turning one-paced and tiring close home.
Jumped with field, taken to fence, settling midfield 5L from leader. Switched out turning for home but only one-paced.
Hard ridden to go forward from an outside gate, racing wide before getting cover 4L from leader at turn. Found little when put under pressure 300m and faded.
Slow into stride, then ridden to hold rail settling worse than midfield. Stayed on rail around turn but made no impression in straight.
Outpaced, steadied passing 900m, dropping towards rear. Hard ridden at turn-in but only one-paced. Had substantial amount of blood in trachea.
Lifted front feet at start and slow into stride, then taken to fence settling towards rear. Shuffled back to last turning for home and found nothing in straight.
Began fairly, ridden along 3-wide but no pace, dropping towards rear. Made no impression in straight.
Pressed forward early to sit clear 3rd, just behind the 2 early leaders. Came round to lead at 300m. Ran strongly from that point. Peaked late, but was just far enough ahead to hold on.
Began well, and cruised forward to be placed forward of midfield, 4th/5th on the fence. Given a clear run to the line in the straight. Ran strongly, and almost mowed down the winner late.
Fairly away and then taken up to sit midfield, 1 off the fence. Looked to be battling early in the straight. Came out across heels at 150m, and ran strongly to the line, gaining on first 2.
Dropped back early from the wide draw for a share of last place. Widest on the turn, and still last at the 200m. Showed a massive turn of foot late to run down the outside and take 4th.
Pressed forward early to sit forward of midfield, 1 off the fence. Ran solidly in the straight without threatening a place.
Pushed hard from the wide draw to ensure he had a share of the lead. Battled on 1 paced in the straight.
Eased forward early to settle midfield, but stuck 3-4 wide with no cover. Stayed on fairly in the straight, without ever threatening.
Dropped back early from the wide draw to share last place. Progressed fairly in the run home and picked up a few of the slower ones late.
Eased out early to settle worse than midfield, 1 off the fence. Battled on fairly in the straight, with little progression.
Bumped early and dropped back to sit towards the rear of the field, 3 wide with limited cover. Wider on the turn, but only plugged away to the line fairly.
Eased out early, eventually settling worse than midfield. Never responded to urging early in the straight, and not pushed to the line late.
Eased out early and settled worse than midfield, on the fence. Didn't respond to the stick, and was eased out late.
Eased out early to settle midfield, on the fence. Never responded to riding in the straight, and dropped out quickly.
Pushed hard early to share the lead. Race was run by the 300m, and dropped out quickly from that point.
