Held up in 5th on the rail within striking distance, soon came to challenge in the straight, responded well to take charge over 100 metres out, won readily.
Ridden along, took up running in back straight obtaining rails run at the Rock, led until overshadowed by the cosy winner inside the final 100 metres.
Broke well, settled towards the rear, came wide for a run entering straight, finished off race well down the centre of the track.
Ridden early, settled just better than midfield in 6th within 3L of pace, similar turning for home, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled in 4th one-out-one-back, soon came under pressure to challenge after straightening but found no response.
Ridden to the front before settling just off the speed in 3rd on the rail, kept on in straight before finding no extra inside the final 200 metres.
Given reminders in last few, checked and lost position at the 1000 metres, remained virtually last to the straight, produced good late impression inside the final 200 metres.
Moderate start, ridden along in 7th in midfield, in similar position on the rail turning for home, found nothing.
Driven forward from the widest gate to eventually reach 2nd outside the leader at the Rock, unable to sustain effort and tired noticeably in the run home.
Lacked speed, always well behind.
Always in last few.
Jumped fairly, hampered and badly stumbled at the 1000 metres, never recovered.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, not suited by the fast sectionals, drifted away 250M to score.
Pushed forward, trapped 3 wide early, improved and sat outside the leader 600M, not suited by the fast tempo, ran on for 2nd.
Trapped 3wide throughout in midfield, closed off strongly 200M for 3rd.
At back, on the rails, benefited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 300M.
Hard ridden early, 2-3 wide just behind midfield, suited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 200M.
Pushed forward, 2 wide in front of midfield, just held ground in straight.
Pushed to take rail and led at fast sectionals, soon emptied 250M.
Midfield, on the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, ran on ok in straight.
Pushed to occupy box seat, ran on until 200M flattened.
Hard ridden early, at rear along the fence, favoured by the fast pace, ran on fairly.
Pushed early but not muster, took cover at rear, 2 wide, suited by the fast tempo, never improved.
Behind midfield, 2 wide, suited by the fast tempo, no progress.
Settled worse than midfield, commenced to improve 500m, strong run in straight when laying in, gained upper hand final 50m.
Fast out and allowed to settle off pace, eased out to challenge on straightening and ran home strongly to just go down.
Crowded at start, awkwardly placed shortly after start and settled towards rear, pushed along home turn to improve, widest on straightening, ran on strongly.
Bumped and unbalanced at start, showed pace and settled behind leader, awkward 850m, tight running at 300m, held position to the line.
Settled behind midfield, inside run on straightening, shifted in 200m, held up 150m and finished fairly.
Shortly after start bumped and unbalanced, push hard to race on pace, tried hard to challenge on straightening but gradually faded.
Crowded on jumping and hampered shortly after, settled at rear, in need of run home turn, checked and lost ground when making run at 200m.
Good early pace to lead, asked for effort on straightening but quickly under pressure and faded.
Crowded at start, checked and lost ground, settled last, unable to obtain clear running final 200m.
Began awkwardly, settled midfield, under pressure home turn, one paced in straight, checked passing 200m
Settled midfield, one paced in straight, inconvenienced near 200m.
Pushed along early to race on pace, under pressure 600m and gradually gave ground.
Jumped well, pressed forward 3-wide outside early leader. Took over lead passing 700m, kicked 1L clear at the turn, came under pressure when challenged 400m but kept finding to win comfortably.
Broke well, hard ridden to hold fence inside early leader. Moved up around turn to challenge new leader but unable to close gap.
Jumped with field, striding forward to settle one-out behind early pace. Swung wide into straight and ran on steadily to grab minor placing.
Hard ridden early to obtain forward position before finding cover 800m along rail behind midfield. Stayed on fence around turn and ran on steadily in straight.
Jumped OK, raced behind midfield in one-out position. Switched out on straightening and ran home fairly.
Began awkwardly, losing ground, then steadied and shifted across behind rivals, dropping to last pair in one-out position. Taken to centre field on straightening and ran on fairly.
Allowed to stride forward from widest draw before shifting in 800m and finding rail 4L from leader. Took inside run in straight and boxed on fairly.
Jumped well, ridden to hold rail 2L behind the pace. Looked a chance turning for home but only one-paced in straight.
Away nicely, ridden to find cover, gradually losing ground until settling near rear in one-out position. Swung wide into straight and kept on fairly though awkwardly placed closing stages.
Hard ridden to lead narrowly between two rivals before being passed 700m and taking the sit. Dropped to fourth entering straight and then one-paced.
Beaten for early pace, dropping behind midfield along rail. Stayed on rail around turn but found nothing in straight when popped the question.
Had head turned when gates opened, losing considerable ground and last on settling. Never in the hunt.
Ridden to get forward position, racing 3-wide in midfield 4L from leader. Covered extra ground turn, swung wide into straight, finished strongly final 200m to win close home.
Began well, pressed forward, settling between horses 3L from leader. Took closer order around home turn, hit front 200m, run down close home.
Got off OK, ridden to find cover, settling behind horses worse than midfield. Not asked for an effort until straightening for home, finished off nicely though raced right final 100m.
Jumped well, pressed forward but wide before settling behind pace 1250m. Made long forward move from 900m, raced alongside leader home turn, led 350m out before tiring close home.
Bumped start, restrained, shifted across behind rivals and last on settling. Made progress around turn, caught in traffic top of straight, switched wide, finished off nicely.
Jumped with field, pressed forward to hold rail, settling 2L from leader. Closed in around home turn, stayed on rail in straight, boxed on gamely.
No early pace, dropping towards rear but away from fence. Well back turning for home, taken to centre field in straight, but only one-pace. Had substantial amount of blood in trachea.
Outpaced and soon at rear. Shuffled to last turning for home, ran past beaten rivals in straight.
Pressed forward from outside gate, taking first turn 3-wide before settling outside hind-quarters of leader 1250m. Dropped to 3rd when another rival moved forward 650m, one-paced in straight.
Ridden to hold forward position, taking first turn wide and then held without cover 2L from leader at 800m. Lost position around home turn and plodded home in straight.
Jumped OK, taken to rail behind midfield but raced keenly approaching first turn. Travelled fairly after that but made no impression in straight.
Broke well, surged forward to lead on settling, crossing to fence at first turn. Led narrowly to turn-in when spent force and faded.
Settled to race in box-seat, sat 1-1/2L off, pulled away passing 200M and scored impressively by 3-1/2L.
Pushed and raced front of midfield, 3-1/2L off but trapped 3 wide throughout, still ran on strongly to take 2nd.
Ridden forward and raced in front of midfield, 3-3/4L off along the rail, ran on well to the line to take 3rd.
Bumped start, ridden forward to take the lead in a 2 wide position, kept on going to the line.
Found no early speed and took cover, raced just behind midfield 5-1/2L behind 2 wide, made ground steadily.
Rolled forward from the inside draw, sat inside the lead along the rail, kept on until 150M and then flattened.
Raced just behind midfield, 5-3/4L behind along the rail, ran on one paced, held up and not tested in final strides.
Pushed and settled in worse than midfield, 7-1/4L behind along the rail, swung widest and one paced to the line.
Settled to race just front of midfield, 4-3/4L behind 2 wide, crowded at 600M, found nothing in the Straight.
Bumped start, raced towards the rear, about 9L behind 2 wide, made minor ground early and ran on.
At the rear throughout, not competitive.
Always at the rear, never a factor.
Broke well, grabbing box seat 2L from leader on settling. Urged forward on straightening, making ground steadily to hit front 150m before holding off late challenge.
Away quickly, not pushed, settling one-out 3L from leader. Turned behind horses, switched out 280m to get clear running, finished strongly to fail narrowly.
Jumped well, pressed forward to race outside hind quarters of leader. Lost position approaching home turn but found second wind in straight and finished off strongly.
First from the gates, taken to rail and set steady pace to home turn. Put under pressure nearing 600m, kicked clear on straightening but caught 150m and passed by two others close home.
Lifted front feet at start, losing ground, taken to rail and made progress to midfield. Kept improving position around home turn and ran on steadily in straight to finish just behind place-getters.
Pressed forward from outside gate, taking first turn 4-wide buy only 2L from leader. Urged forward passing 700m to race outside leader from 600m to straight before giving ground gradually.
Got off nicely, ridden to hold forward position and kept wide without cover 2L from leader. Kept tabs to 200m before turning one-paced.
Steadied on jumping, shifted across behind rivals and last on settling. Taken wide in straight and ran past tiring rivals.
Steadied soon after start and shifted in for cover, settling one-out towards rear. Turned in behind horses, shifted out to make progress, then shifted in 100m when blocked. One-paced.
Pressed forward on jumping, racing 4-wide mostly 4L from leader. Covered extra ground home turn, very wide in straight, one-paced.
Steadied on jumping, shifted in for cover, dropping to rear. Raced ungenerously back stretch, dropped to last around turn, found nothing in straight.
Ridden forward before racing ungenerously 1000m when steadied to find cover behind midfield. Boxed on one-paced in straight before checked 150m and faded. Had substantial amount of blood in trachea.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, still 7 lengths or so back on turn, taken widest in straight and finished off very strongly to score narrowly.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to race outside the leader, similar position on turn, kept on very well in straight but couldn't hold off the winner, just missed.
Began awkwardly, recovered to race 2 wide in midfield, slightly improved on turn, kept on very well to the line, missed narrowly in a 4-horse pipeline at finish.

Began well from gate 1, positioned 1-2L back on rail, saved ground to turn, kept to inside after straightening, checked near 200M, made good late progress thereafter to be nearest on line. (Finished 5th but promoted to 4th on protest.)
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kept on well after turning in, shifted in near 200M, finished 4th, demoted to 5th.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, there to turn, angled out in straight and finished off evenly, never a threat to the first few.
Jumped well from a tricky gate, showed early speed to race in 3rd, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back to race 5 lengths or so back on rail at rear, there to turn, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Raced 4 lengths back on rail in midfield, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, still 6 lengths or so back on turn, one-paced in straight.

Taken back from a wide draw, raced 6 lengths back at rear, difficult to settle in the middle stages, same position on turn, no clear running early in straight, showed no progress when clear thereafter.
Away with them, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover after 1200M, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight when hard run took effect.

Settled in midfield on the rail, commenced move approaching the home turn and obtained a clear run shortly after straightening, ran on well inside the final 250 metres to assert authority close to home.
Settled one back in 3rd on the rail, hit the front from tiring pacemaker over 350 metres out, soon flattered and headed close to home.
Jumped well, settled towards the rear, came under pressure on the outside turning for home, made modest progress without threatening.
Ridden to just better than midfield in 6th about 3L off the pace, briefly baulked after straightening, fought on well late.
Settled in rear of midfield, produced good late impression inside the final 200 metres.
Settled wide in midfield from a wide gate, made headway approaching the home turn, faded out of contention inside the final 200 metres.
Travelled wide behind midfield, made some headway on outside around home bend, ran home one-paced.
Moderate start, settled mainly in forward of midfield on the rail, kept on steadily without threatening.
Settled well behind, chased the field into the straight, ran on past well-beaten horses.
Taken back from a wide gate, remained well behind most of way, widest runner turning in, one-paced in straight.
Niggled at in last few, remained in third last on the rail entering straight, found nothing.
Pressed on from a wide gate to join the leader after the first 400 metres, well there until weakened under pressure inside the final 250 metres.
Ridden to 4th about 2L off the pace, folded up quickly inside the final 250 metres.
Soon took up running from the widest gate, led until tiring badly over 350 metres out.
Pushed to take rail and led at fast sectionals, hung on strongly to win.
Eased to rear, settled along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steady 300M for 2nd.
Pressed forward, sat outside the leader, harmed by the fast pace, held ground for 3rd.
Pushed early, at back, 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast pace, made steady ground 600M, run ended 150M.
Eased to rear, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 300M.
Behind midfield, took rail, benefited by the fast pace, never improved.
Pushed to obtain a midfield sport, trapped 3 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, weakened 250M.
Midfield, raced keenly, 2-3 wide, out of fuel in straight.
Pushed to occupy box seat, not suited by the fast pace, soon emptied 300M.
Fractious in gates, good early speed to settle on pace, pushed along home turn, raced greenly in straight and shifted ground, knuckled down to gain control late.
Fractious in gates, began awkwardly, ridden along to settle midfield, urged along to challenge 350m, took time to get going and worked to the line strongly.
Jumped well and settled behind leaders, cruised up to challenge 350m, looked the winner 100m, claimed late.
Pushed along early to race outside leader, fought on gamely in straight, weakened final 150m.
Bumped at start, settled midfield but wide without cover, tried hard entire straight.
Urged along to lead, travelling nicely home turn, asked for effort 350m but unable to quicken and weakened late.
Taken back at start, keen mid-race, closed of strongly.
Hard ridden early but no pace, settled worse than midfield, widest on straightening, one paced in straight.
Settled midfield, ridden along midrace to maintain position, one paced in straight.
Bumped at start and crowded shortly after, settled midfield, one paced in straight.
Settled at rear, ridden along to improve home turn, did not run on.
Slow to begin, steadied 1000m, always rearward.
Settled at rear and never in it.
Fast break wide, soon led & crossed to rail 1320m, maintained solid gallop, wound it up off final turn & driven 3L clear 300m, all out final 100m, held on.
Smart start, stalked 1 back on fence, 2.5L back & nudged to close 850m, driven 400m, outkicked & boxed on in closing pursuit, held at wire.
Tardy start, settled back of midfield 1 off with cover, shifted out 550m & ridden along, stayed on centre track to take 3rd.
Fast break, soon snagged to fore of midfield 1 off with cover, niggled 900m, shifted wide home turn & driven, stayed on centre track without threat.
Snagged at start to rail midfield, niggled 800m, driven 550m, shifted out 400m, boxed on evenly.
Moderate start, raced rail near tail, niggled 800m for minor advance, driven turning in & shifted out, ran on for dour headway.
Broke well to rail fore of midfield, hard ridden 500m, plugged on at one pace, tapered final 100m.
Bustled from gate, raced midfield 1 off with cover, niggled along, under pump 800m & lost ground, hard driven 9th 550m, kept on moderately in straight.
Impeded at start, parked rail back of midfield, niggled 750m, driven 650m & shifted out, one-paced in run.
Speedy start, bustled to settle 1 back 1 off, niggled along in 4th, driven centre track 350m, emptied 200m & tapered.
Tardy & crowded start, raced last pair on rail, minor progress & shifted out 600m, driven home turn, plodded on tepidly.
Taken behind at start, last pair 1 off & niggled along, last & bustled 600m, found nil in turn for home.
Broke ok, taken back to near rear 1 off with cover, niggled 850m, 3rd last & driven 700m, 2nd last turning in, found nil.
Shifted out & impeded rivals at start, raced 2nd 3 wide no cover, edged 1 off 900m, 1.5L down & under pump 800m hard ridden to hold spot, emptied & eased down final 300m.
Began strongly but couldn't muster, back to near rear on rail 1st turn, travelled strongly throughout, clicked up 600m, took time to wind up between runners, sprinted powerfully late to score.
Slightly awkward break, across into fore of midfield spot on rail by 1650m, niggled 1000m, pushed 420m, sprinted strongly to hit lead 100m, just grabbed final strides.
Ridden along from start, settled midfield 1 off, pulled 3 & 4 deep 550m, ridden along soon after, bold bid to lead 200m, joined 100m, swamped late.
Away fairly, held midfield position on rail, lost place steadily, under heavy riding from 1000m, short of room 350m, found line very late but never a threat.
First to break, joint lead from 1700m before taking solo lead on rail 1500m, headed 1100m, ridden 750m, clicked up 460m, hit lead again 250m, swamped but stuck on gamely.
Eased from gates, settled clear last, under a drive 900m to latch onto main body of field, made steady ground to line.
Broke fast, eased out of speed battle, settled just behind speed 1 off, niggled 800m, ridden approaching 500m, in contention 300m, couldn't keep on from 150m.
Started OK, eased to settle near rear 1 off, nudged 800m, made deep run on turn, widest on straightening, ridden 500m, closed off evenly.
Began smartly, eased to midfield spot 3 deep 1st turn, settled just beyond midfield 1 off, overracing slightly at times, ridden 450m but crowded, checked 120m, still stuck on.
Slightly slow to break, settled beyond midfield 1 off before pushing to rail 1600m, keen at times, niggled 900m, ridden 650m, pulled wide on straightening, couldn't sustain run.
Broke well, pushed hard to cross from outside gate, 4 deep on speed 1st turn, settled 3rd 3 deep, set alight to lead 1100m at speedy fractions, clicked up 500m, grabbed 250m, weakened.
Away evenly, settled just behind speed on rail, pushed along 480m, stuck to inside, couldn't pick up, eased 100m.
Eased from gates, trapped deep 1st turn, settled beyond midfield 1 off, scrubbed along 900m, lost place & back to 2nd last 600m, last on straightening, never in it.
Broke on terms, pressed forward under own steam, joint lead to 1500m, settled 2nd 1 off, back to 3rd 1100m, nudged 600m, under riding 460m, dropped out meekly, eased 150m.
Prominent throughout, raced 1 line behind the pace, about 1-1/4L off, ran on nicely to score by 1/2L.
Sent forward to lead by 3/4L on the outside rail, kept on going, only to be headed by the winner passing final 50M.
Travelled in front of midfield, about 2-1/4L off on the outside rail, mostly held up from 400M to final 50M, not fully tested.
Settled towards the rear, 3-1/2L behind on the outside rail, improved gradually through tight runs, hit the line strongly.
Travelled in front of midfield, sat 2-1/2L off on centre track, one paced but ran on the line.
Bumped start, raced at the rear, 3-1/4L behind stand side, slight dash at 200M, kept on until checked close to the line.
Sent forward, sat 3/4L behind the pace on the outside rail, in touch until 100M, found no extra thereafter.
Detached early, raced 7-1/2L behind on the outside rail, made ground gradually and closed off well.
Settled to race in midfield, sat 3L behind stand side, steadied when crowded at 250M, did not run on.
Pushed and raced 1 line behind the lead, 1-1/2L off stand side, kept on until checked at 150M.
Hard ridden, in behind midfield about 4-1/2L behind stand side, did not improve.
In midfield, about 3-1/4L off on centre track, flattened at 150M.
Awkward start, stayed at the rear, not competitive.
Slow to jump, remained at rear, not a factor.
First out, led field to 900m, then took slipstream when overtaken. Retook lead 300m but immediately challenged and passed, found extra close home to win narrowly.

Jumped with field, not pushed, settling along rail 3L from leader. Took closer order around home turn, no run early in straight, finished strongly but unable catch winner. Objection against winner overruled.
Began OK, allowed to find feet, dropping towards rear but only 4L from winner. Shifted out 650m to improve, swung wide into straight, hit front momentarily before peaking 200m.
Away nicely, pressed forward settling 3L from leader in one-out position. Urged forward around home turn to look a chance on straightening, kept on gamely before tiring close home.
Jumped OK but travelled keenly early stages and unable find cover, dropping to rear. Allowed to improve from 1100m, circling field to lead passing 900m. Overtaken 300m and faded.
Broke well but no early pace and then travelled keenly, dropping to rear. Trailed field from 800m and never in the hunt.

Placing: PU
Comment: Began fairly, ridden to make up ground but broke pelvis passing 800m and pulled up.
Tracked leaders along the inside, poised to strike passing 400M, hit top gear 200M under strong urging, got up 50M and fended off a late charge to register first G1 success.
Not hurried early stages, reserved towards the rear along the inside, found clear running 250M but hung out under pressure and proved difficult to ride, got together and charged home late, just held.
Travelled smoothly in 3rd, loomed a strong threat top of straight, responded well to lead briefly inside 150M but not pace of first 2 late stages.
Held up midfield, 3Ls off the pace 400M, crowded for room 200M, ran on steadily to go 4th late stages, creditable effort.
Set steady pace, all out passing 400M, fought on well early straight, run ended nearing 100M and swamped by pursuing rivals.
Taken back from wide barrier, held up towards rear 4Ls back, responded well early straight and looked one of the possibles at 200M, couldn't go on nearing 100M, one pace towards the finish.
Sent forward to track leader in a steadily run race, kept up with leaders until no extra inside 150M.
Taken back from wide barrier, settled last 6Ls off the pace, lacked a strong turn of foot but stayed on steadily to the finish.
Settled down 2-wide in midfield, 3Ls off at 400M, not pace to challenge leaders, crowded for room 200M, no threat thereon.
Taken back from wide barrier, sat 5Ls off the pace in 2nd last, ran on only fairly down outside on straightening, never a threat to leaders.
Away nicely, then taken to fence 3L from leading pair. Closed in around home turn, got inside run in straight, hit front 200m and pulled clear.
Broke well, ridden to hold forward position 4L from leading pair. Urged forward 3-wide around home turn, finished off strongly to grab quinella placing.

Jumped OK but no early speed, dropping towards rear between runners. Switched out around home turn to get clear running, taken to centre track on straightening and finished strongly to grab minor placing.

Pressed forward from an outside gate, racing wide until settling 2L from leading pair in one-out position. Urged forward top of straight to look a chance 300m but peaked on run and swamped final stages.
Ridden along to find fence, settling ahead of midfield 4L from leaders. Stayed on fence around turn and ran on steadily in straight without looking dangerous.
No early pace and soon at rear along fence. Made some progress around home turn, taken wide in straight and ran on fairly.
Began awkwardly, vigorously ridden to go forward from outside gate but slow to muster and held 3-wide behind midfield. Taken wide in straight, bumped and unbalanced 150m, boxed on.
Off OK, then raced in midfield in one-out position. Switched out in straight but bumped several times midway, finishing one-paced.
Steadied shortly after jumping, shifted across behind rivals and last on settling. Last into straight, taken to centre track and ran past beaten rivals.
Hard ridden from outside gate to go forward, crossing to rail and racing a half length inside leader. Left in front 350m but had little left in the tank and gave ground gradually.
Jumped with field, not pushed and taken to rail behind midfield. Switched out turning for home, made some headway early in straight before running out of steam 200m and fading.
Beaten for early pace and soon at rear along fence. Never in the hunt.
Jumped OK, steadied to find cover, settling at rear but wide. Lay out around turn, shaken up 300m but failed to respond.
Hard ridden from widest gate to lead passing 900m but kept away from fence by inside runner. Travelled keenly around turn and spent force passing 350m.
Taken forward early to sit on leaders flank, 2L clear of 3rd. Nosed in front at top of straight, pulling clear from 200m. Pushed most of the way to the line, but in very easy.
Eased back from the wide draw to settle towards the rear of the field, 1 off the fence. Ran strongly down the outside in the straight to take 2nd, but no chance of catching the winner.
Settled midfield, 3-4 wide with limited cover. Rode into a cul-de-sac at the top of the straight, and unable to get clear until the last 100m. Ran strongly from that point. Jockey questioned.
Pushed forward early to lead. Battled on fairly in the straight, and only just lost a place on the line.
Taken forward early, but dropped back 1100m to settle midfield. Stayed on OK in the straight, before peaking late.
Eased forward early and settled midfield, on the fence. No run early in the straight and awkward on heels 250m. Lay in late and bumped 100m. Off heels 50m, but stayed on OK late.
Went to go forward early, then dropped back to forward of midfield and stuck 3 wide no cover. 1 paced in the straight.
Taken forward early to be handily placed in 3rd. Still prominent at 100m, but peaked from there and dropped back quickly.
Dropped back early to sit at the rear of the field. Only got clear running in the last 100m, and was never able to fully stretch out.
Only eased forward and settle worse than midfield, on the fence. Tight mid straight, and came off heels 100m, but never threatening.
Began awkwardly and lost ground. Recovered to push forward and be handily placed in 4th, on the fence. Never responded to pressure in the straight, and not pushed hard to the line late.
Settled midfield initially. Under pressure before the turn and was a beaten horse early in the straight, before going limply to the line late.
Dropped back early to sit at the rear of the field, 3-4 wide with limited cover. Never kicked in the straight. Vet-Lame.
Began awkwardly, and quickly lost contact with the field. Played no part in the race.

Ridden early, settled mainly in 4th about 2L off the pace, fought on well to gain upper hand final strides.
Soon driven to the lead attempting to make all, fought hard to gain 1L advantage briefly 100 metres out, caught close home.
Hard ridden to hold place outside the leader, disputed lead into the straight, unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.
Slowly away, gradually recovered to just worse than midfield on the rail approaching the Rock, saved ground turning in, ran on well from 3L 6th into straight to be nearest at finish.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, finished off the race strongly down the centre of the track.
Settled mainly in 5th about 2L off the pace on the rail, similar turning in, failed to quicken under pressure.
Soon dropped to last few on the rail, saved ground turning for home, produced good late impression closing stages.
Raced wide in first few after beginning from the widest gate, 3-wide and 2L back in 3rd rounding home bend, faded in straight.
Jumped fairly, soon dropped to midfield 4-wide in back straight, one-paced under pressure in the run home.
Taken back to last from a wide draw, trailed 3L behind the field into straight, finished off race well past beaten horses.
Never better than midfield, found nothing in straight.
Moderate start, ridden to midfield 3-wide in 6th, became 7th in similar position into the straight, gradually weakened.
Pushed to take rail, led easily at fast sectionals, drifted away 250M to score.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, favoured by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300 for 2nd.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, held ground in straight for 3rd.
Eased at start, raced 3-5 wide, suited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 300M.
Behind midfield, 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, ran on ok.
At back, took rail, benefited by the fast pace, ran on fairly in straight.
Behind midfield, trapped 3-4 wide, suited by the fast pace, no progress in straight.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2-3 wide, faded 400M.
Hard ridden forward, 2-3 wide, harmed by the fast tempo, soon out of fuel 300M.
Pushed forward, sat outside the leader, not suited by the fast tempo, emptied 200M.
Never competitive at rear.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3-4 wide, harmed by the fast pace, dropped off 500M.
Jumped smartly and settled behind leader, travelling easily home turn, challenged strongly at 200m, easy win.
Bumped at start, settled midfield, pushed along at 500m, inside run on straightening and ran home strongly.
Urged along early to race off pace, asked for effort at 300m and worked home solidly.
Bumped at start, settled midfield, pushed along to improve home turn and ran on fairly in straight.
Raced in handy position, urged along home turn to challenge, finished fairly.
Fast out to lead, travelling well home turn, asked to quicken at 200m but no response and battled fairly to the line.
Hampered at start and taken back to settle at rear, eased out on straightening for clear running and finished strongly.
Settled behind midfield, unbalanced and checked at 900m, ran home fairly.
Settled behind midfield, proved difficult to settle mid-race, severe check at 600m and unable to finish race off due to racing manners.
Taken back to settle at rear and did not run on.
Taken back at start and failed to run on.
Raced wide without cover throughout and gave ground in straight.
Smart start, raced rail fore of midfield, shaken up 300m & shifted 1 off, quickened to press leader 150m, edged ahead 75m, pressed but held on.
Prominent at break, restrained to fore of midfield 1 off with cover, niggled 420m, driven wide home turn, quickened to lead 170m, headed 75m, rallied, just failed.
Bustled forward from widest gate, 4 deep 1st turn, to 2nd 1 off 1240m, eased to lead 400m, driven 1L clear 300m, soon all out, headed 170m, tapered.
Broke ok, snagged back to slot 1 off with cover midfield, nudged along 450m, widest turning in & hard-ridden, ran on for minor inroads.
Slow break, taken behind to rail & scooted forward to sit midfield, shifted wide home turn & driven 300m, kept on soundly.
Broke well, restrained to 1 back on rail, overraced 1100m, shifted 1 off 380m & driven, boxed on one pace.
Taken back to race rail near rear, niggled along, driven final turn, boxed on evenly.
Speed early, snagged to park 1 off 1 back, ridden 430m, forced 3 wide on turn, found little in tepid run home.
Restrained at start & parked 2nd last, niggled 500m, driven home turn, one-paced in run.
Taken back from wide to race at tail, niggled on & off, hard-ridden home turn, kept on moderately past fading rivals.
Broke ok, taken back to 1 off near rear, bustled along 700m, reminders 450m & driven, wide into stretch, tame effort.
Awkward start, speed to lead 1st turn & to rail 1250m, set sharp tempo, headed 400m & immediately under pressure, faded out.
Restrained from gates, down to last on inside early, settled near tail on rail, travelling well but limited room 450m, weaved a passage in straight, sprinted powerfully on rail, pulled clear.
Jumped well, natural speed to go forward 1 off, settled 3rd, travelled strongly throughout, nudged 550m, grabbed lead 200m & kicked clear, headed on inside 50m.
Away evenly, settled near rear 1 off, ridden 500m, sprinted well, held on to 3rd late.
Broke smartly, ridden to press forward, stuck 4 deep into 1st turn & eased into 3-wide line, settled fore of midfield 1 off, under riding 600m, took an age to wind up but hit line solidly.
Eased from gates, stuck 3 deep into 1st turn & ridden to settle closer, positioned midfield 1 off, clicked up 600m, widest on straightening, made solid ground.
Jumped on terms, natural pace to settle handy on rails, positioned 4th on inside, pushed 450m, switched over heels on straightening, couldn't quicken.
Slow into stride & then bumped heavily, nudged along at 1st turn, settled beyond midfield 1 off, hard ridden 600m, pulled wide in straight, couldn't get into it.
Broke well, ridden to lead, in front on rail 1st turn, joined 1200m & passed soon after, raced at head of main pack, ridden 700m, joined in on straightening, effort short-lived, one-paced.
Hopped at start, under heavy drive to press forward, 3 deep 1st turn, pressed on to lead 1150m, quickly opened up 6L lead at fast splits, under riding 320m, grabbed 200m, weakened.
Jumped OK, eased, settled last on rail, pulled 3 wide & ridden 650m, never able to get into it.
Very awkward out of gates but fast to muster, settled fore of midfield of main bunch on rail, hard-ridden 500m, stuck to inside on straightening, weakened.
Slightly slow start, pushed to get to rail, settled just beyond midfield of main bunch on inside, niggled 700m, railed through into straight, checked badly 150m, eased.
Sent forward and sat outside the lead, about 1L off, took lead passing 100M, ran on nicely to score by 1/2L.
Travelled in front of midfield, sat 3-3/4L off along the rail, kept on and hit the line strongly to finish 2nd.
Rolled forward and settled to race in box-seat, sat 2L off the lead, ran on well to the line to take 3rd.
Sent forward to take the rail and led by 1L, headed passing 100M, kept on to take 4th but was no match to the others.
Bumped start, travelled in midfield, 5L behind 2 wide, continued to make ground and kept on well to the line.
Crowded at start, raced towards the rear, 7-1/4L behind 3 wide with cover, made ground steadily on outer Straight.
Fractious and was slow to jump, settled in behind midfield, 6L behind along the rail, kept on one paced to the line.
Bumped start, raced in front of midfield 3-1/2L off 2 wide, swung wide and found nothing in the Straight.
Awkward start, settled to race in behind midfield, 6-1/4L behind 2 wide, made ground slowly in the Straight.
Slow to jump, at the rear throughout, 7-3/4L behind along the rail, did not improve.
Raced at the rear, 8-1/2L behind 2 wide, never improved, not a factor.
Sat just behind midfield, 5-1/2L behind 3 wide without cover, dropped off rounding turn, not competitive.
Away quickly, then pressured forward to race a length behind leader on settling. Shaken up 400m when tempo increased, hit front 250m, battled on gamely to hold off late challenge.
Away nicely and soon in box seat trailing leaders. Switched out top of straight to make run, finished strongly to grab quinella placing.
Away well, allowed to slide forward under a tight hold, racing one-out in midfield, Swung wide into straight, got clear passage 250m, then lunged forward only to fail narrowly.
Bumped and unbalanced start, driven forward but steadied approaching first turn, settling along fence 4L from leader. Shaken up top of straight and battled on gamely without looking dangerous.
Hard ridden from outside draw to lead on settling, crossing to fence 1300m. Under pressure turning for home, caught passing 150m but kept finding until swamped final strides.
Bumped start, no early speed, dropping behind midfield along fence. Urged forward turning for home and ran on steadily in straight.
Outpaced and soon at rear in one-out position. Well back entering straight before picking up momentum 250m to finish close behind place-getters.
Away nicely, pressed forward, settling one-back, one-out. Boxed on fairly in straight while laying in final 200m.
No early speed and soon at rear, racing wide but with cover. Taken to centre track on straightening but only one-paced. Lost right hind plate 1300m.

Bumped start, hard ridden to go forward but didn't muster and trapped 3-wide in midfield without cover back stretch. Tired soon after straightening and faded. Rider dropped whip at entrance to straight.
Bumped start, no speed, settling between horses at the rear. Took inside run in straight but only one-paced.
Steadied shortly after start, shifted across behind runners and last on settling. Trailed field thereafter and never competitive.
Never far off in 5th, 2Ls off leader on the turn, worked home well from top of straight, took lead near 50M and held sway at the finish.
Began fairly, settled down in midfield 4Ls off the good pace, shifted lane 300M to obtain clear running, stayed on well to make it close at the finish.
Quickly away, restrained to track leader passing 1000M, loomed mid-straight and took lead inside 200M, fought on well only to go down in the concluding stages. Gap to 4th.
Chased leader along the 2-path, stayed close with front runners but couldn't go on final 100M.
Jumped well, held back to race in midfield 4Ls off the pace, brought wide 400M, made some progress without threatening first 3.
Crossed to the lead passing 1000M, led at good pace, battled away early straight, lost lead inside 200M and weakened towards the line.
Not hurried early stages, dropped back towards the rear of the main group, 4Ls to make up top of straight but couldn't accelerate enough to challenge leaders.
Commenced to race fiercely after being crossed by rival 1100M, held 4th spot and wide no cover making the turn, kept on same pace on straightening.
Restrained to a rearward position after the jump, proved difficult to settle, 5-6Ls to make up 400M but failed to improve.
From widest draw made some use early to obtain a midfield position, driven out 400M but didn't close off the race.
Taken back on jumping from wide barrier, 6Ls off the good pace middle stages, switched wide approaching home straight, got too far back and never in the hunt. (Jockey lost whip 200M.)
Began only fairly, hard ridden forward but failed to muster speed and detached from field 600M, never in the picture. (Jockey : horse did not show interest in the race / Lame next day.)

Made all, pushed clear inside final 200 metres.
Raced just inside the leader near the stands rail, failed to match the eventual winner's turn of foot in the final 200 metres.
Soon dropped to 5th within 3L of pace, shaken up coming onto course proper, fought on steadily closing stages to reach 3rd late.
Soon crossed to stands side and came within 2L of pace in 3rd, failed to quicken under pressure coming onto course proper, lost 3rd late.
Close up in 3rd, taken back for cover just behind the leaders inside the 600 metres, found nothing under pressure in the run home.
In last few, one-paced under pressure.
Jumped fairly, soon dropped to 6th some 4L back on rails, dropped out of contention from over half-way out.
Always struggling.
Jumped awkwardly, tailed-off throughout.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, pace good, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Hard ridden forward, sat outside the leader, pace good, ran on well for 2nd.
Eased back, took rail, pace good, lack room 400M, progressed steadily when clear.
Pressed forward, 2 wide, pace good, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden forward, took rail and led at good pace, hung on until 200M flattened.
Pushed to obtain box seat, pace good, ran on until 150M flattened.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, pace good, ran on ok.
Eased back, took rail, pace good, made some ground 200M.
Sat in midfield, trapped 3 wide, pace good, flattened 200M.
Hard ridden early but not muster, trapped 4 wide throughout at back, pace good, ran on fairly.
At back, 2 wide, pace good, never improved.
Never competitive at rear.
Pushed early, midfield 2 wide, raced very keen, pace good, emptied in straight.
Jumped fairly and pushed along to take lead, travelling well home turn, quickened nicely 300m, held off all for strong win.
No early speed and settled at rear, widest on straightening and ran home strongly.
Jumped well, settled behind midfield, shifted out around home turn to issue challenge and stayed on without threatening.
Taken back shortly after start, settled behind midfield, held up near 400m, ran home fairly.
Began fairly, pushed along to settle behind leaders, asked for effort on straightening but unable to quicken, one paced to the line.
Jumped well and good speed to settle outside leader, quickly under pressure 400m and gradually gave ground.
Jumped well, settled behind leader, one paced in straight.
Broke ok, parked 1 back on fence, easy advance to close on lead final turn & edged 1 off, shaken up to lead 340m, kicked 2L clear, kept on under drive.
Lacked early toe, raced rail midfield, stalking when crowded & bumped home turn, driven 430m, shifted 1 off & closed to wire, always held.
Sluggish start, nudged along initially to race midfield 1 off, popped 3 deep no cover 900m, ridden for progress 600m, 4th & driven into stretch, boxed on dourly.
Snagged at start to race rail back of midfield, driven 400m, shifted out in stretch, kept on for minor headway.
Bustled forward initially, 4 wide & prominent 1st turn, slotted handy 1 off with cover 1350m, niggled 600m, crowded home turn, boxed on evenly centre track.
Slow start & bustled at tail, advanced 1100m to race 3rd last 1 off, niggled 650m & shifted wide for progress, plugged on evenly.
Bustled from gate, mid-pack & checked off heels 1st turn, edged 3 deep & overraced, restrained to near rear, angled wide on turn, kept on for moderate inroads.
Slow start, outpaced & bustled near rear, checked off heels 1080m & shuffled to 2nd last, under pump at tail 500m, hard ridden to pass beaten rivals.
Smart start & led 1st turn, restrained & headed 1130m, 1L 2nd & shifted 1 off 750m, 3 wide & driven home turn, out-paced, emptied 250m & faded.
Broke well, taken back to race last pair on outer, last at 1060m, under pump 900m & advanced a spot, hard ridden 550m, plodded home tamely.
Tardy break, bustled to race handy 3 deep 1st turn, slotted midfield 1 off with cover 950m, niggled 850m, soon under pump, shifted wide home turn, found nil.
Good start & bustled to press lead 1 off, shuffled to 3rd 1 back 1050m, niggled 850m, soon under pump, faded home turn.
Broke well, bustled to press lead 3 wide, rolled on to lead 1130m & berthed 1 off, 1L clear &to rail 750m, driven turning in, all out & headed 340m, faded out.
Quick break, natural early speed but allowed to find feet midfield centre track, clicked up 500m, took time to wind up, sprinted very strongly from 150m to score on line.
On back foot slightly at start, mustered into joint lead 750m 1 off, ridden along 450m & went clear, just collared late.
Jumped OK, hanging out throughout, settled handy 1 off, driven 450m, switched over heels 250m, sprinted well but clearly 3rd best.
Hopped slightly at start, driven hard to press towards front, just behind leaders 3 off 750m, strode to joint lead 600m, stuck on solidly but no match.
Very awkward start, shifted to 3-off spot & allowed to stride into position behind leaders at 600m, niggled 450m, stayed on without threatening.
Jumped out at start, settled beyond midfield centre track, scrubbed along 600m, never in contention but stayed on.
Very awkwardly away, shifted behind runners, outpaced & ridden 800m, settled near rear 1 off, niggled throughout, made ground but never a threat.
Broke sharply, ridden into lead on outside rail, joined 750m, pushed 600m, weakened.
Away OK, outsped early, settled near rear 2 off, ridden 600m, back to last 350m, short of room 150m, made ground late.
Broke evenly, eased to last, outpaced early, clicked up 550m, never in it.
Began on terms, quickly outpaced & ridden along, settled beyond midfield 3 off, driven 600m, outpaced to line.
Slightly slow, ridden along to press forward, settled handy 2 off, ridden 500m, switched towards centre, unable to pick up.
Jumped well, ridden to go forward, joint lead 750m 2 off, under pressure 500m & quickly beaten off.
Began well, niggled to settle midpack on outside rail, already under pressure 650m, dropped out quickly.
Settled to race in midfield, 4-1/4L behind 2 wide, continued to find extra and ran on nicely to score by a short head.
Eased and raced at the rear, 10-1/4L behind 2 wide, taken widest in the Straight, and closed off strongly to take 2nd.
Pushed forward and raced outside the lead, sat 1-1/4L off, ran on well and locked in a tight battle to the line to take 3rd.
Ridden forward to take the rail and led by 1-1/4L, headed passing 300M, in touch until passing 100M and flattened.
Sent forward and obtained one-off one-back position, sat 2-3/4L off, kept on one paced to the line.
Travelled in behind midfield, 5-3/4L behind 2 wide, kept on one paced going to the line.
Pushed forward and settled to race in box-seat, sat 2-1/4L off, in touch until 200M and then faded gradually.
Eased and raced at the rear, 8-3/4L behind 2 wide, made minor ground in the Straight.
Shifted abruptly at start, settled to race towards the rear, 7-3/4L behind along the rail, kept on one paced.
Settled to race just fore of midfield, 3-3/4L off along the rail, kept on until faded near 200M.
Raced in worse than midfield, 7-1/4L behind 2 wide, did not improve in the Straight.
Crowded start, raced just behind midfield, 5-1/2L off on the rail, one paced and flattened half way down the Straight.
Niggled along, fore of midfield and dropped to midfield rounding turn, wide and without cover, not a factor.
Jumped well, allowed to slide forward down centre track, about 1L inside pacemakers. Hit the front passing 250m while shifting out and pulled clear under hands and heels riding.
Broke well, hard ridden to hold forward position inside the pace. Took over lead passing 400m, overtaken 250m, battled on gamely to hold second placing.
Off with field, pressed forward, settling 3L behind pacemakers. Shifted in passing 350m to improve, then shifted in again 200m to get clear running, finished off nicely.
Jumped well, hard ridden to hold outside rail while sharing early pace. Looked chance when urged forward 400m but unable match place-getters final stages.
Bumped on jumping, pressed forward inside leaders and rolled forward 400m to share lead. Came under pressure 250m, shifted out under pressure, then one-paced.
Bounced well, pressed forward settling 3L behind the pace one-away from outer fence. Shaken up passing 400m but only one-paced.
Bumped start but recovered quickly, pressing forward to share early pace one-away from outer fence. Slightly inconvenienced passing 200m before giving ground gradually.
Began OK, shifted out but no early pace, dropping towards rear. Boxed on gamely final 400m without looking dangerous.
Outpaced and soon at rear. Made progress in the middle stages but one-paced final 200m.
Broke well, pressed forward to lead on settling close to outer rail. Joined up front by several rivals approaching 400m when failed to respond to hard riding and faded.
Away nicely, racing in midfield behind pace and close to outer fence. Came under pressure final 400m and faded.
No early pace and soon at rear 3-away from outer fence. Under pressure passing 500m and never competitive.
Jumped well, pressed forward, racing alone down centre track 3L from leading pack. Under pressure passing 400m and dropped out.
Bumped shortly after start, outpaced and soon at rear. Never in the hunt.
Ridden forward, emerged as leader nearing 1200M, set good pace and opened up 3Ls lead 300M out, stuck to task well and holding off a late challenge for first win since arrival.
Began awkwardly, severely checked 1500M, settled down midfield along the fence and shuffled further back hone turn, picked up strongly from 300M, closing on winner late just ran out of ground.
Towards the rear, shifted out to 3-wide spot down the back straight, swung wide for home, stayed on well for 3rd but couldn't trouble winner.
Began only fairly, held up towards the rear, ran on moderately for non-threatening 4th.
Not far off form leaders, driven out 500M, went 2nd 250M but couldn't get closer to leader, flattened final 150M.
Caught wide no cover on jumping from draw 9, chased pace, fought on early straight but not gaining ground on leader, weakened late stages.
Caught wide from draw 14, made some use to take up a forward position just outside leader, couldn't keep up passing 400M, weakened 250M and out of contention for minor placings.
Unable to slot in from wide barrier, 3-wide in midfield 4Ls off the good pace, kept on same pace on straightening, never seriously threatened.
Held up 2-wide in midfield 5Ls back, driven along middle of the turn, couldn't go on passing 300M, made no impression on AWT debut.
Taken back from wide barrier, held up 2nd last 8Ls behind leader, bustled along 600M, couldn't accelerate enough to challenge leaders.
Quickly guided to the fence, sat 3Ls off leader ahead of mid-division, pushed along middle of home turn, couldn't pick up turning home, eased when no chance.
Switched off to last, settled 9-10Ls off the pace, couldn't pick up turning home, never in the picture.
Fractious in stalls, urged forward after the jump, chased leaders down the back straight, gave ground from 700M and finished tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Chased leaders, came under serious pressure 600M, dropped out sharply turning in, eased and finished tailed out on AWT debut. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Broke well, hard ridden to hold rail, settling 4L from leader passing 1200m. Hampered passing 500m, badly blocked for run top of straight, got split 330m, powered home final 200m to win on line.

Hard ridden from outside draw but failed to muster, dropping to rear. Allowed to roll forward from 900m, entered straight 4-wide, took over lead 300m and looked the winner until run down final strides.

Jumped well, then ridden to hold midfield position close to rail. Got shuffled back passing 800m, crowded for room 500m, switched out 300m to pass tiring rival, finished strongly only to fail narrowly.

Began fairly, shifted in for cover, settling one-out towards rear. Raced tight passing 1000m, swung wide entering straight, taken to centre track, finished strongly under the whip to just miss a placing.

Jumped OK, pressed forward inside pacemakers to hold rail before slipping into slipstream of leader passing 900m. Rolled forward top of straight to look a chance 300m but swamped by several rivals final 50m.
First out, pressed forward to share pace before settling one-out 2L from leader 900m. Three-wide into straight, rolled forward to lead momentarily 300m, battled on gamely final 200m.
Away nicely, not pushed, racing one-out in midfield 4L from leader. Hampered 500m, switched out turning for home, made some progress to 200m before turning one-paced.
Slow into stride and distant last on settling. Closed in around home turn and ran on fairly in straight.
Jumped OK, taken in for cover, dropping to rear along rail. Made up some ground around home turn but only one-paced in straight.
Began awkwardly, ridden to obtain forward position but held 3-wide without cover 3L from leader. Covered extra ground around turn, kept on fairly to 200m before tiring.
Hard ridden to hold forward position before taking lead passing 1200m and crossing to fence 900m. Unbalanced passing 400m, overtaken 350m, faded.
No early speed and soon 3-wide at rear but with cover. Travelled well to straight when came under pressure and weakened. Stewards ruled performance unacceptable.

Jumped with field, hard ridden to stay with pace but kept wide. Allowed to slide forward from midfield to race outside leader from 800m but spent force on straightening and dropped out quickly. Unacceptable performance.
Pushed forward early to ensure he had a share of the lead, on the fence. Ran strongly in the straight, without kicking clear. Started to fade last 50m, but just enough in the tank to hold on.

Taken up from the wide draw to sit forward of midfield. Unsettled and checked off heels 1100m. Well placed at the front at the top of the straight. Dropped off slightly 200m, but strong late and was catching winner.
Dropped back early from the wide draw to sit towards the rear of the field, 3 wide. Ran strongly in the straight and made up a lot of ground.
Began awkwardly, but recovered to push forward and lead. Faded out from the 150m, but still held 4th. Found to have bled.
Cruised forward early and settled behind midfield. Had to come wide in the straight to get clear running, eventually kicking at 200m. Ran very strongly from that point.
Crowded and then steadied on jumping. Taken forward to sit midfield, on the fence. Progressed solidly in the straight, without threatening a place.
Taken up to settle forward of midfield. Off heels for a run at the top of the straight, but only 1 paced to the line.
Pushed forward from the inside draw to settle just behind the leaders, on the fence. Dropped back quickly from the 250m.
Taken up early to be handily placed 3rd/4th, 1 off the fence. Lost a run 550m. Plugged on fairly early in the straight. Awkwardly placed on heels at 200m, but already fading out by then.
Settled towards the rear of the field. Widest on the turn, but only plugged away fairly in the straight.
Taken up early to sit midfield. Unsettled from the 1200m, and started throwing his head around at 1000m. Didn't kick in the run home.
Dropped back early to get cover and settled at the rear of the field. Wider on the turn, but never responded to pressure in the straight.
Sat around midfield, but was being pressed forward throughout and raced wide for the trip. Prominent on the turn, but dropped out quickly soon after.
Stumbled out of the barriers and dropped back early. At the back of the pack, and played no part in the race.

Ridden early, settled one back in 2nd on the rail, tracked leader into straight, asserted authority 100 metres out.
Soon led, ridden along, obtains rail run over 700 metres out, held 1L break into straight, unable to sustain effort and headed 100 metres out.
Settled just behind midfield on the rail, switched out to challenge entering the straight, ran on to snatch 3rd late.
Taken back from the widest gate, saved a lot of ground on the rail turning in, ran on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Began from a wide gate, disputed 2nd, one-paced in straight.
Ridden along, gradually improved to 4L back in 5th on the rail, ran home one-paced.
Began from a wide gate, settled towards the rear, produced some late impression under pressure closing stages.
Settled in midfield, lost position turning into straight, ran home one-paced.
Ran wide without cover in midfield, lost position when the widest runner into straight, ran home one-paced.
Travelled 3-wide without cover in forward of midfield, improved to 3L 4th approaching the Rock, faded under pressure after straightening.
Moderate start, trailed the field to straight.
Moderate start, always in last few.
Hard ridden to sit in midfield, 2 wide, made early move 1200M to take advantages of the slow pace, ran on strongly 300M to score.
Pushed forward, 1 out 1 back, benefited by the slow pace, closed off strongly for 2nd.
Hard ridden to be in front of midfield, 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, unleashed strong finishing efforts 300M and got 3rd.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2-3 wide, dashed well 250M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased to sit in midfield early, however raced too keen, took lead 1600M, clocked slow sectionals, overhauled 300M, ran on fairly,
Eased back early, trapped 3 wide throughout, harmed by the slow pace, moved forward 1200M, ran on well until 150M flattened.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, no progress in straight.
Eased back, sat 2 wide, on heels early, not suited by the slow tempo, little dash 300M.
Eased back, took rail, held up and checked 5-3, harmed by the slow pace, dashed fairly when clear.
At back, 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, no dash.
Eased at start, too cover at rear, harmed by the slow pace, attempted to improve around the field in 3-4 wide, however no progress.
Hard ridden forward along the fence, shuffled back from 1600M, emptied 400M.
Settled midfield, ridden along passing 600m to improve, shifted out on straightening and issued strong challenge, gained control final 100m.
Jumped well and soon led, travelling well home turn, quickened nicely and fought on strongly to the finish.
Settled off pace, urged along home turn, hampered at 300m, worked home solidly.
Settled towards rear, pushed to improve near 400m, inside run on straightening and ran home well.
Raced on speed, awkward at 1500m, keen at 1000m, tried hard to challenge home turn but could not quicken and battled fairly to the line.
Raced in rearward position, pushed to improve passing 500m and ran home fairly.
Taken back at start to settle at rear, hard ridden at 350m and one paced in straight.
Settled on pace, hampered at 1000m, asked to improve at 500m but quickly under pressure and gave ground in straight.
Settled forward of midfield, hampered winning post first time and then hung out, raced ungenerously and race wide without cover , gave ground from 500m.
Sharp break, soon led & to rail 1150m, headed 800m & tracked 1 back, ridden on turn & quickened to lead 140m, pressured late but held on.
Broke well, snagged to park midfield 1 off, shuffled back a spot 800m, niggled 500m, under pump turning in, driven & progress to 2nd close home, no extra final strides.
Snagged back to 2nd last on rail, to tail 1150m, 1L adrift & nudged along, driven wide into stretch, charged home late, just failed.
Restrained start to tail, soon advanced to 2nd last 1 off, niggled 500m, shifted 3 deep 400m & driven widest into stretch, closed for late gains.
Tardy start & raced near rear on rail, shifted wide & bustled to lead 750m, driven & headed 560m, pushed to lead again 400m, kicked 1.5L clear, peaked & headed 140m.
Impeded start & raced 1 off near rear, wide advance 900m, raced midfield 3 deep no cover, driven wide home turn, kept on for minor inroads.
Led at break on rail, headed 1250m & raced 1 back, shuffled back to midfield 800m & bustled, shifted out & driven 400m, boxed on evenly.
Awkward start & restrained initially, rolled to midfield first turn & to rail 1200m, checked off heels 900m & lost ground, 3rd last & niggled 700m, driven home turn, one paced.
Lacked toe at start & bustled to 5th on rail, checked off heels 1030m & shuffled to back of midfield, driven home turn, found little in tame stretch run.
Broke ok, raced midfield 1 off with cover, bustled to hold spot 700m, wide on turn & shuffled back, outpaced, driven 220m, tepid run home.
Awkward start & bumped, raced handy 3 wide no cover, rolled to edge lead 800m, soon headed & under pressure 1 back 1 off, wide on turn & no extra.
Bumped start, close up 2nd no cover & overraced 1000m, bustled to vie for lead 780m, led 500m, all out & headed 400m, emptied 250m & eased.
Slightly awkward start, into spot just behind leaders 1 off, switched over heels 350m & clicked up, sprinted powerfully, hit lead 120m, raced clear.
Jumped well, eased, settled beyond midfield 1 off, clicked up 500m, short of room soon after, into clear on straightening, finished strongly but no match.
Slightly slow to jump, pushed along to go forward along rail, in front from 900m, travelled comfortably throughout, ridden 350m, kicked solidly, joined 120m, stayed on.
Broke on terms, pushed to press forward, narrow lead 1000m, headed on inside 900m, settled 2nd 1 off, ridden 360m, boxed on.
Away OK, ridden to lead early, stuck 4 deep & eased into midfield spot 3 deep, niggled 550m, stuck on OK.
Fastest to break, eased & quickly beyond midfield, ridden up rail 1000m, settled box seat, pushed along 350m up inside, faded late.
On back foot slightly at start, sped through to handy position 3 deep 900m, strode up to joint lead 400m, ridden soon after, weakened.
Jumped well, settled handy but stuck 5 deep, back to midfield 800m, ridden into joint lead 600m, weakened from 550m.
Very slow start, settled 2nd last on inside, switched to 1 off spot, ridden 450m, short of room near 100m, never a threat.
On back foot at start, settled well back on rail, niggled at times throughout, never a threat.
Ridden hard from gates but couldn't muster sufficient speed to cross, stranded 5 deep in midfield, ridden 800m, up into 3rd briefly but weakened from 600m.
Slightly slow, eased right back to tail, outpaced & struggling 800m, never got back into it, eased right down from 200m.
In midfield, 3-3/4L behind 2 wide, made ground in clear running on centre track, kept on nicely to score by 1/2L.
Raced at the rear, 6-3/4L behind along the rail, made good ground, shifted in at 100M and ran on nicely to the line.
Hard ridden forward to cross and took the rail, led by 1-1/4L, headed near 50M but ran on well to the line.
Sent forward and raced outside the lead, sat 1-1/2L off, remained in touch until 200M, one paced in the Straight.
Pushed early, settled in one-off one-back position, sat 2-1/4L off, finished off one paced.
Settled in front of midfield, 2-1/2L off along the rail, raced keenly, kept on one paced to the line.
Raced in worse than midfield, 5L behind 3 wide at turn, shifted widest on straightening, kept on one paced.
Pushed forward and settled to race in box-seat, sat 1-1/4L off, flattened and found no extra passing 200M.
Settled to race towards the rear, 6-1/4L behind 2 wide, made minimal ground only but ran on.
Raced in midfield, 3-3/4L behind along the rail, inconvenienced at 300M, remained one paced thereafter.
Travelled in behind midfield, 5L behind along the rail, made no progress. (Scoped blood in trachea)
Slow to jump, at last and travelled detached throughout.

Bumped on jumping, eased to behind midfield in one-out position and switched off. Switched out turning for home, taken to centre field in straightening, finished powerfully to win close home, laying-in final strides.
Ridden early to hold forward position before getting cover in midfield, one away from fence. Got clear run in straight and finished off strongly to grab quinella placing close home.
Broke well, then pushed forward to track leader in one-out position. Nudged forward from 500m to join leader 300m, broke clear 150m but run down final strides.
Began fairly, then hard ridden to hold rail 6L from leader. Closed in around turn, surged forward along fence to look a chance 200m but no extra close home.
Crowded for room on jumping, settling towards rear in one-out position. Put under pressure turning for home, took inside run in straight and finished off nicely, doing best work final 150m.
Crowded out on jumping, ridden to find cover but held 3-wide behind midfield. Swung wide into straight and ran on steadily without looking dangerous.
Hard ridden from outside gate to lead, crossing to fence 1000m and setting good pace. Joined up front passing 300m, kept on gamely to 150m before giving ground gradually.
Hard ridden on jumping but failed to muster, dropping to last. Well back entering straight, taken very wide and finished off fairly.

Began awkwardly, bumped, ridden to make up ground and taken to rail behind midfield. Raced in restricted room around turn, had clear rail run in straight but failed to respond when popped the question.
Jumped well, pressed forwards from widest gate, racing 4-wide before finding cover between horses 3L from leader passing 1000m. Under pressure turning for home and faded.
No early speed, dropping to rear along rail. Stayed on rail around turn and in straight but found nothing when put under pressure.

Began well, pressed forward but trapped 3-wide without cover 2L from leader. Under pressure turning for home and dropped out quickly in straight. Lost left front plate after 1000m. Bled from both nostrils.
Jumped well, took the lead easily, uncontested throughout, kept on well in straight to score.
Began well, raced 2 wide in 2nd throughout, kept on well in straight to get 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Began fairly, no early speed, raced 4 lengths or so back on rail, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight to get 3rd.
Slightly slow out from gate 1, raced 3 lengths or so back on rail in midfield, similar position on turn, made minor progress early in straight, peaked near 100M, just stayed on for 4th.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail to turn, taken widest in straight and made very good progress to be nearest on line.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide at rear, slightly improved from 600M, taken wide in straight and made some progress.
Jumped well, positioned 1-1/2L back on rail, same margin back on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 100M, weakened thereafter.
Began awkwardly from a wide draw, raced 6 to 7 lengths back at rear, similar position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well from a tricky gate, unable to slot in early, taken back to race 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Shifted out at start, difficult to settle early, raced 5 lengths or so back at rear, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, unable to slot in, travelled wide and without cover throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in 4th, improved on turn, peaked early in straight and weakened thereafter, eased final 200M. (See Racing Incidents.) (Sustained a cut to the right hock.)
