Ridden positively from the widest gate, led on the rail after the first 200 metres, kept on similar pace but extended the margin after straightening when prominent runners faded, won unchallenged.
Waited with in rear, finished off race well to reach 2nd late.
Broke well, ridden along before settling outside the leader, unable to sustain effort after straightening.

Slow to muster despite ridden along, picked up along the rail to just worse than midfield passing the 1000 metres, shuffled back to second last entering straight, produced good late impression in the run to the line.

Settled towards rear, awkwardly placed briefly in crowding approaching the home bend, over 5L back in 7th turning into straight, produced good late impression closing stages off the centre of the straight nearer the stands side.

Moderate start, gradually improved to prominent position but forced 4-wide onto home bend, allowed to stride forward to 2L 3rd but remained 3-wide rounding the bend, weakened under pressure after straightening.

Raced wide in midfield early from a wide gate before settling towards the rear, commenced move out wide rounding home bend, produced good late impression in the straight off the centre of the straight nearer the stands side.

Prominent early, raced awkwardly after crossed by the leader and dropped slightly backward to 2L 4th approaching home bend, renewed effort rounding the bend but had no more to give upon straightening.
Slowly away and dropped to tail-end, trailed the field to the 300 metres, ran past only well-beaten horses.
Settled wide in midfield, commenced move approaching the home turn to reach 4L 5th briefly, gradually weakened under pressure in the straight.
Moderate start, settled in midfield, awkwardly placed in general crowding coming onto home bend, held similar midfield position when some 4L back in 6th turning for home, soon weakened.
Broke well from the one draw, settled in forward of midfield before hampered and shuffled slightly backward approaching the home bend, dropped away quickly after straightening. (Bled)
Took rail easily, led at fast sectionals, drifted away 400M to score impressively.
Hard ridden to keep up with the pace in midfield, 2 wide, ran on well for 2nd.
Hard ridden early, struggled to keep up at back, 2 wide, suited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M for 3rd.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden early, at rear 2 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, made steady ground 250M.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast pace, ran on until 200M flattened.
At back along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, made steady ground 400M, lack room 200M.
Hard ridden early, 3 wide at back, suited by the fast tempo, ran on fairly.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, not suited by the fast pace, out of fuel 200M.
Hard ridden early but not muster, trapped 3-4 wide, emptied in straight.
Hard ridden and trapped 4-5 wide throughout, never nearer.
Checked start, at rear, never competitive.
Fast out and sent straight to lead, kicked strongly at 400m and easily held off all.
Bumped at start, went forward to settle outside leader, urged to challenge home turn and tried hard entire straight but no match for winner.
Eased back early to settle behind midfield, shifted out on straightening to issue challenge and ran home strongly without threatening.
Settled behind midfield, bumped and unbalanced at 900m, commenced to improve passing 700m, ran home solidly in straight.
Bumped at start, settled midfield and raced keenly, in need of run at 500m, bumped on straightening, held up near 200m and finished fairly once clear.
Jumped well and settled off pace, pushed to challenge home turn, bumped at 400m and stayed on in straight.
Settled behind midfield, bumped and unbalanced at 900m, one paced in straight.
Jumped nicely, settled leaders back, pushed along 500m and quickly under pressure and gradually weakened.
Settled in midfield position, under pressure 500m and one paced in straight.
Began awkwardly and bumped, settled forward of midfield wide without cover, under pressure home turn and weakened out of it.
Inconvenienced at start, settled at rear and remained there throughout.
Jumped fairly, settled near rear and remained there throughout.
Broke ok, bustled initially & soon settled midfield 1 off with cover, 3 deep 900m & driven 4 deep 550m for progress, quickened to lead 320m, all out to hold on.
Taken back of midfield 1 off with cover, niggled for progress 800m, steadied on turn until driven wide 500m, hung in & bumped 430m, quickened to 2nd but continued to lug in.
Good start & led, to rail 1450m & soon joined on front end, headed 1200m & shuffled 1 back, overraced 900m, driven turning in, shifted 1 off, boxed on for 3rd.
Broke ok widest, rolled to lead 1200m & to rail 960m, pressed on turn, shaken up 400m, all out & headed 320m, game but tapered.
Awkward start, pace to race handily, steadied 1500m to track pace, off heels 950m & shuffled back a spot, driven into stretch, stayed on evenly.
Snagged to tail at break, soon settled rail 2nd last, advanced a spot 900m & shifted out, brushed rival 430m & not clear ground, checked off heels 280m, driven & kept on for minor gains.
Broke well, pace to post 1 off in front rank, shuffled back to 3rd & niggled 1200m, urged to press lead 900m, ridden into home turn, plugged on one pace.
Moderate start, raced rail midfield, steadied off heels & shuffled back 940m, shifted 1 off 800m, wide into stretch, crowded & bumped, stayed on moderately.
Slow start & raced 1 off near tail, advanced a spot 1250m, shifted wide into home turn & driven, ran home evenly.
Taken back at start to rail back of midfield, shifted out home turn and driven, kept on moderately.
Snagged back from wide gate, settled at tail 1 off, slightly keen 800m, ridden along 550m, shifted centre track, plugged away but never a threat.
Bustled from gate & soon prominent, settled behind speed 1 off with cover, driven turning in, outpaced in tame run home.
Sluggish start, raced last trio 1 off, 2nd last & niggled 800m, bustled wide 750m, hard-driven home turn, found nil.
Broke well enough but lacked toe & soon rowed along mid rank, advanced 3 deep from 950m, 1L down turning in, out-paced when heavily impeded 380m, faded.
Slightly slow to begin, mustered quickly into handy position, settled fore of midfield 1 off, keen at times, ridden 550m, pulled to centre track, strode up strongly, hit lead 150m, dogged to line.
Fastest to break, pushed along to lead, crossed to rail at 1000m, 2.5L lead 800m, pushed 480m, joined 250m, kicked on strongly.
On back foot at break, hard ridden to press forward, settled fore of midfield on rail, clicked up 520m, into clear on straightening, never quite on top, fought on solidly.
Began smartly, pushed hard to get into forward spot, settled 2nd on rail, pushed along 450m, joint lead 250m but couldn't break clear, boxed on.
Slightly slow break, initially ridden to go forward but then eased into midfield spot on rail, held together into straight, took time to wind up, strong late.
No speed from gates, settled last under hard riding, pushed along at times throughout, tacked on from 700m, under a drive 500m, found line very late.
Began on terms, eased into midfield spot 1 off, raced keenly throughout, ridden 500m, wayward in straight, couldn't pick up.
Eased from gates, settled near rear on rail, keen 600m, ridden 450m, never a threat.
Jumped OK, eased right back to beyond midfield 1 off, ridden 550m, pulled widest into straight, couldn't come on.
Couldn't muster out of gates, settled beyond midfield on rail, niggled at times throughout, hard ridden 600m, never in it.
Jumped well, natural speed to settle 3rd 1 off, slightly keen, niggled 550m, dropped out from 300m, eased down.
Ridden forward, took rail and led by 1-1/4L at 800M, pushed to the line and held on to score by 1/2L.
Sent forward and raced outside the lead, 1-1/4L off, kept going nicely and pushed the winner to the line.
Pushed and settled to race in box-seat, sat 1-1/4L off, kept going but was no match to the first two.
Settled in behind midfield, 6L behind along the rail, severely checked at 800M, improved steadily and kept on.
Settled to race in behind midfield, 5-1/2L behind 2 wide, checked at 800M, kept on one paced to the line.
At rear, 7L behind 2 wide, checked at 800M, awkward to heels at 400M and then held up, improved steadily thereafter.
Take in at start, shifted to rail, raced in midfield 4L behind, one paced in the Straight but ran on.
At start was bumped, in worse than midfield, 6L behind 3 wide, hung out at turn and in the Straight, one paced.
Bumped start, in behind midfield, 4-1/4L behind and wide, taken wider after 800M, one paced and never threatened.
Pushed but settled front of midfield only, 2-1/2L off wide and without cover, weakened passing 300M.
Raced in front of midfield, 2-1/2L off along the rail, checked at 800M, flattened half way down the Straight.
Travelled in front of midfield, 2-1/2L off 2 wide, hampered near 800M, did not keep up in the Straight, not competitive.
Settled to race in midfield, 3-3/4L behind 2 wide, found nothing in the Straight.
Began fairly only and remained at the rear throughout.
No early pace, dropping to rear but 3-wide on settling. Covered extra ground turning for home, pressed forward on straightening to hit the front 150m before pulling clear.
Fractious in gate, lifted feet at start losing considerably ground. Trailed field to straight before finishing on strongly down centre track.
Hard ridden to get forward position, settling in box seat 2L from leader. Put under pressure in straight but raced ungenerously while inclined to lay in, boxing on for minor placing.
Had head turned at start and lost ground. Taken to rail at rear and settled. Switched out turning for home and finished off nicely.
Hard ridden to lead on settling, crossing to rail 1000m and setting good pace. Kicked ahead on straightening but collared passing 150m and then swamped by several other rivals in final strides.
Jumped well, ridden along in midfield but kept wide. Made some progress early in straight to look a chance 200m before turning one-paced.
Not pushed early, settling between horses behind midfield. Put under pressure turning for home but only one-paced.
Pressed forward on jumping, racing wide 3L from leader. Shifted out turning for home, kept on gamely to 200m before tiring.
Hampered and taken out soon after start, dropping to rear. Well back turning for home, took inside run in straight but no clear passage final 150m and not properly tested.
Broke OK, then hugged rail behind midfield to straight. Made progress from 400m to 200m before run ended. Lost right hind plate after 900m.
Broke well, pressed forward to race 1L outside leader. Under pressure soon after straightening and gave ground gradually.
Began well, pressed forward from outside gate but unable find cover and raced 3-wide without cover 2L from leader. Under pressure prior to straightening and faded.
Chased leaders in 3rd, came through narrow passage to take lead 100M then drew away towards the line for 4th win of the season.
Led early stages, tracked leader from 1000M, quickened to recapture lead 250M, outsprinted and headed by winner 100M.
Crossed to the lead passing 1000M, led to 250M, couldn't match strides with first 2 but held on for 3rd well.
Dropped back to a rail position behind midfield, 4Ls to make up 400M, took a while to find clear running top of straight, stayed on over final 250M for non-threatening 4th.
About 3Ls back, in midfield, raced ungenerously from 900M, in 4th place turning in, kept battling away on same pace, couldn't trouble leaders.
Sat behind midfield 4Ls off the pace, tried hard over final 300M but couldn't quicken enough under top weight to be closer to leaders.
Taken back from wide barrier, 8Ls off the pace at the tail of main group middle stages, made some progress up the fence passing 400M, hampered 150M but not making material difference to the results.
Held up behind midfield, 5Ls off the pace top of straight, fought on one pace, no threat to leaders.
Put his head down at the start and lost ground, recovered to race in midfield, keenly from 700M, couldn't go on passing 250M, faded towards the line.
Taken back from wide barrier, 7Ls towards the rear, not quickened passing 400M and failed to come into contention.
Refused to jump with the field and blew the start, detached from the field throughout, never in the picture.
Not far off from leaders early stages, made the home turn awkwardly on his debut, gave ground from 500M, weakened to last.
Jumped well, hard ridden along rail to lead passing 1200m, then set steady pace to straight where kept finding to hold off all challenges.
No early pace and last on settling. Last into straight, taken to centre track and finished powerfully only to fail narrowly.

Away nicely from inside gate and soon in box seat tracking leader. Moved up alongside leader on straightening and battled on strongly without being able to close gap. Lost right front plate after 300m.

Began awkwardly, allowed to stride forward while looking for cover, settling 3-wide 2L from leader. Swung wide into straight, boxed on fairly under whip to finish in the frame. Had small overreach wound to inside right front heel.
Hard ridden from outside gate to race 1L outside leader back stretch. Swung wide entering straight, boxed on gamely without closing gap.
Outpaced and soon at rear but kept away from fence. Not asked for effort until straightening for home when taken to centre track and finished off nicely.
Steadied on jumping and shifted across behind runners, settling along fence towards rear. Improved position around turn, kept on fairly in straight.
Jumped OK before racing between horses in midfield. Lost position turning for home, boxed on one-paced in straight.
Rolled forward from an outside gate, but stranded 4-wide without cover and allowed to stride forward approaching turn. Effort took its toll and beaten horse soon after straightening.
Jumped awkwardly then crowded for room before taken to fence and improving position to midfield before the turn. One-paced in straight.
Broke well, pressed forward, settling between horses 4L from leader. Lost position turning for home, shifted out several times in straight to get clear running but only one-paced despite reminders.
Hard ridden to lead but kept away from fence by inside runner. Overtaken passing 1200m, got shuffled back turning for home, spent force in straight and eased down.
No early pace, dropping towards rear. Got shuffled back turning for home and found nothing when popped the question in the straight. Confirmed to be a "roarer".
Jumped OK, not pushed, settling towards rear but wide. Continued to race wide around turn before dropping out quickly in straight.

Dropped back early from the wide draw to sit at the back of the field. 2nd last on the turn, and came widest in the straight. Ran steadily, before showing enormous turn of foot last 150m to get in cozily.

Taken up early to be well placed 4th, on the fence. Clear run in the straight, and was running well without pressure early in the straight. Increased the tempo under the stick from 200m, and only beaten by a big run late.
Pushed from the wide draw to go to the lead on a front runners track. Taken on in the straight and went stride for stride with challenger. Peaked in the last 20m.
Eased forward early to sit midfield. Came off heels 500m and lost ground. Ran very strongly when given a chance over the last 100m.
Went to press forward early, but was stuck forward of midfield, 3 wide with no cover. Stayed on well in the straight and was gaining on the placegetters late.
Sat around midfield, 3-4 wide with limited cover. Stayed on solidly in the straight and was making up ground. Lay in late, and came off heels close to the line.
Bumped and unbalance on jumping. Recovered well enough to push up to midfield, on the fence. Ran solidly, without threatening a place in the straight.
Pressed forward from the inside draw to settle just forward of midfield. Had a clear run home in the straight, but only battled to the line 1 paced.

Dropped back early to settle at the rear of the field. Ran on steadily early in the straight, and switched inside, off heels, after missing a run at 200m. Only plugged to the line steadily after that.
Taken up early to sit 2nd, on the fence. No clear run early in the straight, coming across heels to be clear at 300m. Only ran on 1 paced and eased up near the line.
Dropped back early to sit towards the rear of the field. Plugged along and never threatened in the straight.
Pressed forward early to be handily placed 2nd/3rd, 1 off the fence. Dropped out quickly from the 200m.
Began awkwardly, and dropped back to sit last. Never improved.
Crowded and unbalanced on jumping. Didn't muster early and dropped back to the rear of the field. Off heels and lost ground 1400m. Gave nothing in the straight and eased out early.

Driven to join the leader early, took up narrow running on the rail passing the 1000 metres, driven clear inside the final 200 metres.
Ridden early, settled one back in 3rd on the rail, became 4th one out passing the 1000 metres, commenced move to reach 2nd entering straight, unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.
Settled in last few, commenced move out wide rounding home bend, ran on steadily without threatening.
Ridden positively from a wide gate, settled in forward of midfield 2-wide approaching the 1000 metre bend, switched onto the rail for a run early in straight, failed to quicken under pressure.

Broke well from a poor draw, led briefly on the rail coming onto stables bend, ceded advantage for cover in 3rd turning into back straight, gradually faded under pressure from a similar position into home straight.
Taken back from a wide gate, circled the field rounding home bend, widest runner turning in, fought on dourly under pressure down the centre of the track.
Broke well, held up in rear of midfield, dropped slightly back when pace quickened around home bend, made up some late ground under pressure closing stages.

Moderate start, ridden before taken back for cover in vain early stages, improved to midfield without cover back straight, made short-lived effort on home bend, still very wide into home straight, soon faded.
Settled at the back, trailed the field to the 400 metres, ran on past beaten horses closing stages.
Given early reminders before settling in midfield on the rail, slightly worse when pace quickened approaching the home turn, found nothing in the straight.
Began fairly, improved steadily 3-wide around stables bend to reach 2nd turning into back straight, dropped away quickly inside the final 400 metres.
Restrained for cover early, hampered and dropped to last few on the rail coming onto stables bend, dropped further back to the tail-end entering home straight, no further impression.
Jumped best, pushed to further secure the lead, clocked slow sectionals, drifted away 300M to score.
Very slow away, took rail at back, dashed strongly 300M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Hard ridden forward, took rail, just off the leaders, held ground in straight.
Settled in box seat, benefited by the slow sectionals, ran on until 100M flattened.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, not suited by the slow tempo, lack room most straight, dashed well.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, harmed by the slow pace, blocked whole straight, ran on well to the line.
In front of midfield, 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, no progress.
Hard ridden forward, just off the leader, 2-3 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, emptied 150M.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, ran on fairly.
Bumped start, pushed to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, no dash.
Eased back, trapped 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Hard ridden throughout, trapped 4-5 wide, never responded.
Began awkwardly, settled forward of midfield, loomed to challenge home turn and finished strongly.
Began fairly, settled midfield and gradually improved to be handy at 700m, fought on gamely in straight.
Jumped well, settled midfield, commenced wide run from 400m and ran home strongly.
Jumped nicely to settle midfield, finished fairly along rail.
Bumped at start, settled midfield, ran home fairly. Lame left fore, blood trachea.
Settled behind midfield, asked for effort at home turn and made up nice late ground.
Jumped nicely, soon in lead, limited response on straightening and gradually weakened. Lame right fore.
Taken back at start, shifted out away from heels at 200m and made some late ground.
Jumped fairly, settled midfield wide without cover, one paced in straight.
Bumped at start and taken back, asked for effort home turn but no response and finished one paced.
Settled leaders back. Under pressure on straightening and gradually weakened.
Began fairly and failed to muster early speed to settle at rear, finished fairly in straight.
Speed to lead, to rail 1300m, urged on when pressed 500m, 1.5L up & driven turning in, maintained advantage to wire.
Smart start, sat 1 back on rail, ridden along 500m, driven into stretch & advanced to 2nd 200m, no extra & held.
Broke well & settled handy 1 off with cover, overraced 1150m, shaken up & wide turning in, hard driven to close, 3rd & hung in through final 100m, no extra.
Sharp start, 2nd but 3wide no cover 1st turn, edged to 1 off outside leader 1100m, bustled up for pressure 550m, driven 400m, boxed on in pursuit but no threat.
Taken back at start to 2nd last 1 off with cover, nudged forward 600m & soon under pump, very wide final turn, ran on for minor headway.
Broke well, soon bustled & settled rail fore of midfield, shuffled back & ridden 600m, 6th turning in & driven, shifted out & edged back to rail through even run home.
Moderate start, settled back of midfield 1 of with cover, bustled forward a spot 700m, hard driven 500m, one-paced in run home.
Slow start & raced at tail on rail, niggled along 600m, minor progress until briefly steadied in traffic turning in, driven 250m, stayed on for modest gains.
Snagged back at start to near rear 1 off with cover, bustled forward 650m for 3 wide advance, wide home turn, plugged on evenly.
Smart break but then lacked toe, niggled back of midfield on rail, under pump 600m, rear rank & hard driven 400m, plugged on tamely.
Good break, steadied to midfield 1 off with cover, overraced 1100m, bustled for 3 deep advance 700m to share 2nd 500m, all out turning in, emptied 250m & retreated.
Tardy start & niggled, raced near rear on rail, nudged along 650m, shifted 1 off 550m & soon under pump, no impression & last turning in, plugged on same speed.
Pushed from gates, settled into box seat 3rd on rail, niggled 570m, hard ridden soon after, switched over heels into straight, joined in strongly, went to narrow lead 200m, raced clear.
Broke smartly, ridden to lead early but then restrained behind leaders, settled 4th 1 off, pushed along 500m, raced up solidly, no match late but stayed on.
Restrained from gates, head up early stages, settled near tail 1 off, pushed along 400m, switched over heels 120m, ran home strongly.
Jumped well, driven hard to hold lead on rail, keen at times, 1.5L lead 1000m, joined 430m & clicked up soon after, kicked strongly, succumbed 100m, fought on.
Started well, natural speed to press forward, into midfield spot 1 off, ridden 550m, pulled widest into straight, couldn't sustain run, boxed on.
Jumped inwards at start, eased behind leaders, keen & into midfield spot on rail, clicked up 550m, slow to pick up, green on bend & in straight, short of room 100m, went to line hard-held.
Threw head in air at start, ridden to press forward, settled 2nd 1 off, joint lead 430m, ridden into straight, faded from 150m.
Broke fast, natural speed to press forward, stuck wide & eased into 1st turn, settled beyond midfield 1 off, niggled 550m, driven soon after, pulled to centre track, never made an impact.
Ridden hard from gates, on heels 1300m, settled beyond midfield on inside, keen at times, ridden 470m, unable to pick up, eased from 100m.
Slightly slow break, back to last & ridden along, settled at rear & niggled at times throughout, hard ridden 500m, quickly dropped after.
Always in midfield, about 2-1/4L behind 2 wide, ran on steadily before closing off well to score by 1/2L.
In behind midfield, moved after 800M to take up the lead, pressured from 300M, headed by winner at 50M, ran on.
Pushed forward and raced in box-seat, sat 1-1/4L off, one paced until dashed slightly near 100M, finished off well.
Eased back to race at the tail, 4L behind 2 wide, made nice ground, ran on well to the line. (Rider lost whip at 75M)
Raced in midfield, 3L behind along the rail, dropped to rear near 700M, made good ground and closed off nicely.
Taken back after start, raced at the rear but moved closer to midfield after 700M, made ground gradually and kept on.
Rolled forward to race prominently, sat 3/4L off and outside the lead at 800M, ran on one paced in the Straight.
Ridden forward to cross and took rail, remained in the lead until 600M, kept on until 250M when weakened.
Settled in behind midfield initially but trapped wide, ridden to sit outside the lead at 900M, dropped off rounding turn.
Towards the rear, taken to 3 wide at 850M, remained very wide thereafter, faded soon after straightening.
Hard ridden to lead on settling, crossing to fence 700m and setting good pace. Joined up front 300m, kicked ahead passing 150m, pulled clear final stages.
Broke well, taken to fence but unable prevent leader from crossing. Moved up to race outside leader at turn, pulled level 300m but unable match strides when winner kicked clear final stages.
Jumped well from inside draw, taking box seat 2L from leader. Chased winner all the way without being able to narrow the gap.
Bumped and unbalanced start but recovered quickly, settling one-out, one-back. Got shuffled back turning for home but ran on fairly in the straight without looking dangerous.
Got off well, not pushed, racing one-off before shifted to the fence at the turn 4L from leader. Swung wide into straight and boxed on fairly.
Lifted front feet and began only fairly, then shuffled back, settling one-out towards rear. Taken on centre track on straightening and finished off fairly.
Began awkwardly, losing ground, dropping to rear. Taken to rail turning for home but only one-paced in straight.
Crowded out at start, no pace, settling at rear. Never in the hunt though ran past tiring rivals in straight.
Steadied on jumping and taken in but unable find cover and forced to race 3-wide, 3L from leader. Under whip on straightening but failed to respond and eased down final 100m.
Pressed forward from an outside gate and raced in midfield but 4-wide to turn. Spent force soon after entering straight and faded.

Placing: UR
Comment: Reared abruptly at start dislodging rider and left barriers riderless.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader, easy run on turn, finished off strongly in straight, scored easily.
Taken back to race 4 lengths or so back on rail, saved ground throughout, kept to inside after straightening and made good progress to get 2nd without threatening the winner.
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, kept on well after turning in, headed final 150M and weakened thereafter, stayed on for 3rd.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, similar position on turn, finished off evenly to make frame.
Began very awkwardly and lost ground, recovered to race in midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly without threatening.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 2 wide, 3 to 4 lengths back in midfield, taken wide in straight and finished off evenly.
Began well from a middle gate, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with no cover throughout, peaked on turn, bumped early in straight and weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 5 lengths or so back at rear, there to turn, finished off one-paced.
Taken back to race at tail, 6 to 7 lengths back, still last on turn, finished off one-paced in straight, never a threat.
Fast into stride, positioned in 2nd, peaked on turn, bumped near 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began fairly from the widest gate, raced 3 wide with cover, 4 lengths or so back, carried wider near 350M, failed to close off in straight.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight.

Settled just off the pace on the rail, came to challenge entering home straight and led passing the 400 metres, won cozily.
Given reminders early, settled well behind midfield in 6th about 5L off the pace, ran on inside the final 300 metres, did best work late.
Settled 3L back on the rail in 4th, moved slightly closer to the pace coming onto home bend, came under pressure upon straightening, produced good late impression closing stages.
Soon took up running attempting to make all, led the field until narrowly headed by the winner at the 400 metres, swamped for a placing final stages.
Midfield throughout, kept on at the one pace under pressure.
Broke well from a wide-ish gate, settled 2L back in 3rd, became 4th coming onto home bend, commenced run from the 650 metres, soon faded after straightening.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, remained in rear to straight, found nothing.
Always well behind, found nothing under pressure.
Hard ridden throughout to keep up with the pace, ran on well to the line and scored.
Eased to sit just off the leaders, led 300M, ran on strongly, just beaten in last few strides.
Pressed forward, shared the lead at fast sectionals, hung on until 200M overhauled, ran on for 3rd.
At back, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M.
Pushed to share the lead, clocked fast sectionals, ran on until 200M flattened.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, benefited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 300M.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, favoured by the fast pace, just held ground in final stages.
Very slow away, at rear, suited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 250M.
Failed to muster, at back, benefited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 200M.
Very slow away, at rear, favoured by the fast pace, made some late ground 100M.
At back, suited by the fast pace, ran on fairly.
At rear, favoured by the fast tempo, no dash.
Pushed forward, not suited by the fast pace, emptied 250M.
Never a factor.
Pushed along early to settle on speed, travelling well 600m, challenged strongly at 300m and pulled away for strong win.
Jumped smartly and settled on speed, eased out to issue challenge on straightening and ran home strongly without threatening.
Pushed along early to lead, relaxed nicely midrace and fought on gamely in straight.
Settled midfield, pushed along passing 600m to improve, ran on fairly in straight making nice late ground.
Eased back early to settle behind midfield, raced keenly near 1000m, hung inwards in straight when running on strongly.
Settled towards rear, ran home nicely in straight, tight for room final 100m
Began awkwardly, settled handy steadied at 1100m, drifted back midrace, asked for effort on straightening and ran home fairly.
Settled behind midfield, hard ridden to improve passing 600m, worked home solidly in straight.
Settled midfield wide without cover, under pressure 500m, one paced in straight.
Taken back at start from wide gate, one paced in straight.
Taken back at start, widest on straightening, never threatened in straight.
Taken back at start, failed to run on.
Settled forward of midfield, over-raced and checked at 1100m and then left wide without cover, under pressure home turn and faded in straight.
Settled behind midfield, under pressure 600m and weakened.
Broke well, parked midfield on fence, travelled strongly, steadied turning in & switched to clear ground 380m, driven in pursuit 350m, gradual gains to lead 50m.
Awkward but speedy break for narrow lead 1 off, rolled on 1L clear 850m, shaken up 400m & kicked on, all out 150m, no extra & headed 50m.
Awkward start & bumped, raced at tail on rail, over-raced 700m & shifted out, driven wide into stretch & rattled home centre track for closing 3rd.
Broke well & prominent, soon settled 1 off 1 back, driven on turn& progress to brief 2nd at 250m, out-paced, edged out of frame close home.
Good break, soon taken back from wide to race midfield 3 wide with cover, wide home turn & driven into stretch, boxed on evenly.
Slow start & niggled to race near rear 1 of, shifted wide turning in & driven for minor headway.
Broke ok but soon outpaced, settled rail near rear, driven 400m & shifted out, hard ridden for moderate inroads.
Broke well, close 2nd on rail initially, soon restrained to 1 back, driven turning in, plugged on one pace.
Broke ok widest, dropped in to midfield 1 off with cover, shaken up & shifted out 450m, soon driven, found little in tame run home.
Smart start, raced handy 3 wide no cover, kicked up to close 2nd 1 off at 700m, niggled 500m & driven off home turn, emptied 250m & weakened.
Tardy start & bustled to sit 3 wide with cover near rear, ridden 450m, widest on turn, found nil.
Broke well, handy but trapped 4 wide no cover, 3 deep & eased off a touch 700m, weakened on turn & found nil in stretch.
Broke quickly, hard ridden to get into forward position, settled 2nd 1 off, back to 3rd 950m, strode through to joint lead 600m, ridden 450m, outright lead 320m, driven out for easy success.
Started strongly, couldn't match early speed, settled just fore of midfield 1 off, searching for clear room 550m, ridden 450m, finished solidly.
Among fastest to begin, eased to settle just behind speed on rail, ridden 450m, boxed on.
Jumped well, initially eased, pushed 1200m, settled beyond midfield 3 deep with cover, ridden 700m, widest into straight, closed off resolutely.
Began OK, ridden through to lead on rail, 0.5L lead 1050m, joined 800m, clicked up 420m, lost lead soon after, fought on but no match.
On back foot at start, strode into beyond midfield position on rail, clicked up 530m, switched over heels 300m, plugged on one-paced.
Very awkward break, 6L last early, tacked on by 1000m, settled at rear on inside, keen at times, limited room 400m, one-paced to line.
Eased from gates, settled near rear 1 off, ridden along 500m, pulled centre track and in bumping duel 400m, couldn't go on from 150m.
Away fairly, allowed to find spot just behind lead between runners, keen at times, settled fore of midfield 3 deep with cover, pulled centre track & ridden 450m, little response.
Slightly slow to begin, settled beyond midfield between runners, ridden 470m, couldn't pick up.
Slightly slow to muster, ridden, pressed leaders 3 deep, joint lead 800m, ridden 460m, dropped off tamely, eased.
Raced in midfield, 5-1/4L behind along the rail, kept on going nicely and held off late challenge to score by 1/2L.
In behind midfield, 6-1/4L off, made the Home Turn wide, saved good ground and ran on gamely to the line.
Travelled in behind midfield, 6-3/4L behind 2 wide, made good ground, closed off nicely.
Raced in front of midfield, 3-1/2L off 2 wide, remained in touch until after 100M, kept on going to the line.
Settled to race in front of midfield, 3-1/2L off along the rail, kept on one paced to the line.
In behind midfield, 6-1/2L off along the rail, no clear running early, ran on well once cleared passing 200M.
Travelled at the rear, 8L behind 3 wide with cover, made ground steadily and kept on well to the line.
Settled to race in midfield, 5L behind 2 wide, kept on nicely whilst laying in, brushed at 200M, one paced thereafter.
At the rear, 9-1/4L behind along the rail, made the Home Turn wide, covered good ground on outer straight, ran on fairly.
Raced in one-off one-back position, sat 1-3/4L off, displayed good dash early but flattened near 150M.
Settled to race in box-seat, sat 2-1/4L off, showed no turn of foot to be competitive.
Raced in behind midfield, 6-1/2L behind but wide, found nothing in the straight.
Ridden forward and sat outside the lead, faded approaching 300M, never a factor. (Lame left front)
Pushed forward, took rail and led, weakened passing 350M, not competitive.

Broke well, tracked leader to first turn, then settled 3rd 4L back entering back stretch. Peeled out home turn to go forward, 3-wide into straight, hit front halfway up the straight and pulled clear for easy win.
Away nicely, then tracked leader to straight. Hit the front momentarily 350m, then battled strongly to line though no match for winner.
Snagged back after jumping from widest gate and shifted across behind runners, dropping to last. Made up some ground back stretch, moved closer turning for home, finished off strongly.
Bumped and unbalanced start, ridden along to find cover, settling one-out towards rear. Dropped back to last approaching home turn before running on fairly in straight while shifting ground.
Got off well, settling one-back, one out. Inclined to lay out around home turn and only one-paced when put under pressure in straight.
Shifted across behind horses from an outside gate soon after jumping and taken to fence at the rear. Never in the hunt and plodded home one-paced.
Jumped straight to the front and then set good pace, pulling 3L clear entering back stretch. Increased tempo turning for home but caught 350m and faded.
Bustled along after the jump, sat outside leader in a slowly run race, hit lead inside 150M, battled on well to line and kept pursuers at bay.
Began only fairly, raced keenly 1000M, in midfield 2-3Ls back home turn, worked home steadily to go 2nd near line.
Towards the rear in a slowly run race, pushed to a 3-wide spot making the turn, closed off fastest down outside, got up for 3rd just before line.
Jumped well, sat just off the pace along the rail, kept up the chase on winner passing 300M, missed 3rd narrowly.

Held up behind midfield in a slowly run race, just over 2Ls away at 400M, responded well over final 300M, held by winner but remained in contention for minor placing, narrowly missed in a close finish.
Never far off from leaders, 3-wide home turn and moved into contention 500M, tried hard on straightening but always held by winner, peaked on its run 100M, beaten into 6th in photo.
Crossed to the lead 900M, led slowly, fought on well up the inner, faded final 100M.
Dropped back to the rear, pace slow, 3-4Ls behind leader at 400M, responded mildly under top weight, inclined to lay out under pressure and couldn't go on passing 150M.
Began only fairly, taken back to the rear in a slowly run race, couldn't make up ground on leaders passing 400M and never threatened.
Niggled along early stages to keep up with rivals, raced without cover throughout, made 4-wide move home turn to be closer to leaders, soon under pressure 450M and weakened.
Away well, grabbed box seat and tracked leaders to straight. Took over running passing 250m and pulled clear for easy win.
No early pace, dropping towards rear along fence. Made up good ground turning for home, took inside run in straight and finished off strongly.
Stood flat-footed at start and lost considerable ground. Ridden to make up ground but kept wide, then crowded for room turning for home. Taken wide in straight and finished strongly.
Began OK before racing between horses in midfield. Lost position turning for home, second last into straight, taken wide and finished off nicely to just miss a placing.
Unable find cover after jumping from an outside gate and trapped wide without cover towards the rear. Kept wide around home turn before running on fairly in the straight.
Broke with field, ridden to hold fence, settling 4L from leader. Stayed in contention to straight but only one-paced when put under pressure.
Outpaced and last on settling. Made good ground along rail turning for home to get within range passing 200m before tiring.
Lifted front feet at start and began awkwardly before being bumped, dropping to rear. Dropped to last turning for home, ran on fairly in the straight.
Away nicely, pressed forward, settling one-out 4L from leader. Travelled smoothly to straight when soon under pressure, giving ground gradually.
Hard ridden from widest draw to race a half length outside leader. Moved up turning for home, took over lead passing 400m but run ended 250m and faded. Had substantial amount of blood in trachea.
Began OK then ridden along one-out in midfield to straight. Switched out to make run but only one-paced.
Ridden along early to find cover but raced keenly to turn then left wide without cover to straight. One-paced thereafter.
Pushed forward from an outside gate, grabbing good position one-back and one-out. Under pressure soon after straightening and faded quickly final 200m.
Pressed forward from outside gate to lead on settling, crossing to fence 1000m. Set good pace to 400m when collared, kept on fairly to 100m when flattened.
Pushed hard to ensure he was the clear leader by 900m. Ran strongly in the straight, before starting to weaken over last 100m. Had just enough in the tank to hold the win late.
Pushed forward early to be handily placed 4th/5th, 3 wide no cover. Battled on strongly in the straight, and was running down the winner late.
Eased back early from the wide draw to sit worse than midfield, 1 off the fence. Only got a clear run after the 200m, but ran on strongly from that point, and was rapidly catching first 2.
Eased out to settle midfield, 1 off the fence. Battled on solidly under the stick from 200m, peaking just near the line.
Taken up early to be handily placed 4th/5th, 1 off the fence. Battled on solidly without threatening in the straight.
Began well, but dropped back early to settle at the rear of the field, 3 wide with limited cover. Came widest in the straight and battled on solidly without threatening.
Cruised forward to settle midfield, on the fence. Battled on fairly under the stick, but never a threat.
Began awkwardly, and eased back to settle worse than midfield, on the fence. Brushed rail and unbalanced 700m.Only plugged away fairly in the straight, picking up a few slower ones late.
Eased out early and settled at the rear of the field. Still at the rear turning for home, and only battled away under hands and heels late.
Dropped back from the wide draw to sit a clear last, 2L behind the next horse. Still last at the 200m. Stayed on OK, but only picking up the slower ones late.
Bumped and unbalanced on jumping but recovered to be well placed, 3rd on the fence. Dropped out from the 200m, and eased late. Vet- Cardiac Arrhythmia.
Pushed forward early to settle 2nd/3rd, 1 off the fence. Under pressure at 300m, and began to drop back quickly from there. Eased down last 100m.
Settled forward of midfield, on the fence. Went looking on turn, and had clear running from 300m. Never responded to riding and was eased out late. Jockey questioned.
Dropped back early to sit at the rear of the field. Never progressed, and eased late.

Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths or so back on rail, raced tight near 750M, slightly improved on turn, kept on well in straight to score. (Dropped whip near 250M.)
Bumped start, raced in midfield, improved from near 500M, kept on well in straight to get 2nd.
Crowded out start, raced 6 to 7 lengths back at rear, slightly improved on turn, taken wide in straight and made good progress to get 3rd.

Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide without cover in the early stages, took the lead near 1100M, there to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 200M, stayed on for 4th.

Bumped start and unbalanced, positioned 5-6 lengths back on rail, slightly improved along the rail in the middle stages, angled out after turning in, finished off evenly. (Had a small wound to the outside of the right hind cannon.)
Taken back from gate 9, raced at tail early, slightly improved after 1000M but still 3 wide at rear, same position on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off evenly.

Slightly slow out, sent forward to take the early lead, headed near 1100M, sat on the leader's back, there to turn, no response to riding in straight. (Lame right front leg with a sore fetlock next day.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide at rear, ridden in the middle stages, showed no response, emptied early in straight and eased.
Moderately away, raced prominently, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight, finished tailed out. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, carried wide on turn and peaked, emptied near 400M, finished tailed out, unacceptable performance.
Pushed to occupy box seat, pace good, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Took rail at rear, pace good, lack room 400M, dashed strongly when clear and ran 2nd.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, 2-3 wide, pace good, led 300M, hung on well until 100M overhauled, ran on for 3rd.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, pace good, made the move around the field in 4-5 wide, unleashed strong finishing efforts 250M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in front of midfield, pace good, made steady ground 300M.
Hard ridden forward, led at good pace, soon flattened 250M.
Eased back, trapped 2-4 wide, pace good, ran on ok in straight.
At back along the fence, pace good, ran on fairly.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, pace good, no dash in straight.
Pressed forward, 2 wide, pace good, emptied 400M.
At rear, 2-4 wide, pace good, never progressed.
Hard ridden early but not muster, 2-3 wide at back, no progress.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide throughout, pace good, never improved.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, pace good, dropped off rapidly 400M.
Settled midfield, gradually improved position passing 300M, shifted out for challenges on straightening, ran home strongly and held off all challengers to win.
Pushed at start to settle midfield, raced wide without cover, ran home strongly.
Moderate start, settled behind leader on rail, pushed along to improve near 500M and fought on strongly in straight.
Urged at start before eased back to settle behind midfield, travelled wide without cover, gradually made ground in straight.
Hard ridden early stages to eventually settle outside leader near the 700M, tried hard early straight before weakening final 150M.
Jumped OK, settled towards rear, worked home fairly in straight.
Jumped nicely, settled forward of midfield, under pressure 500M and failed to quickened in straight. Blood trachea after race.
Pushed along early to take lead, asked for effort home turn but no response and weakened in straight.
Taken back at start, failed to run on in straight.
Began fairly and steadied, settled towards rear, one-paced in straight.
Settled behind midfield, under pressure at 700M and gave ground thereafter. Lame left fore.
Began fairly and hung out throughout race, never in it. Must trial.

Fast jump, ridden to maintain handy spot on rail, settled in box seat 3rd on rail, keen throughout, no clear run until 340m when switched over leader's heels, took time to pick up, hit lead final strides.
Quick to muster, trapped 3 wide in handy spot early, pushed towards lead 1000m, up to 2nd but still 3 deep, ridden 600m, claimed lead 200m, just caught final strides, game.
Moderate jump, hard ridden to find lead, awkward on 1st bend, 2L lead on rail by 1300m but keen, hard to settle throughout, ridden 440m, claimed 200m, battled on.
Broke well, ridden into midfield spot on rail, niggled 800m, ridden 600m to rail through, stuck on strongly.
Jumped OK, pushed through to handy position, settled 2nd 1 off, back to 3rd 970m, ridden 500m, whacked away one-paced.
Eased from gates, at tail early on rail, travelled strongly throughout, held together until 400m, finished strongly without threatening.
Slow to muster, driven hard early stages, settled well back on rail, 1 off from 1100m, 3 deep 650m, ridden soon after, pulled centre track in straight, closed off OK.
Awkward at start, ridden into midfield position but trapped deep 1st turn, settled midfield 3 deep with cover, pushed forward 1000m but back to midfield 800m, ridden 500m, faded.
Jumped fairly, back towards tail 1 off, ridden 500m, widest into straight, made ground very late.
Slightly awkward start, beyond midfield 1 off, 3 deep from 1100m with cover at times, ridden along 620m, couldn't get into it.
Slightly slow, allowed to stride forward naturally, settled fore of midfield between runners, clicked up 500m, couldn't pick up.
Jumped OK, settled beyond midfield on rail, hampered 1050m, niggled 850m, under drive 550m, dropped out.
Began speedily, eased to just beyond midfield spot 1 off, began overracing 700m, on heels 450m, ridden 320m, making ground when unbalanced of own accord at 100m, eased down.
On back foot at start, settled near tail on rail, pulled out 580m & urged, ridden 350m, made up plenty of ground, hit lead 20m and pulled away.
Among fastest to start, eased into handy position 3 deep, ridden 570m, raced up to join lead 300m, broke clear, grabbed near line.
Began evenly, natural speed to lead on rail, joined 650m, ridden 400m, joint lead soon after but never quite on top again, stayed on well.
Broke well, outpaced early & back to spot just fore of midfield on rail, niggled at times throughout, ridden 400m, making solid ground when short of room 160m, finished resolutely.
Began well, not rushed to press forward, 3rd early but deep on track, joint lead 3 deep 650m, ridden 450m, claimed 300m, stayed on.
Jumped OK, into handy position early, settled just behind lead 1 off, driven 620m, bumped 250m, struggled to pick up, found line again very late.
Moderate start, eased behind runners, settled beyond midfield 1 off, keen at times, ridden 600m, pulled widest into straight, couldn't come into it.
Even break, ridden vigorously early to go forward but couldn't muster & back to midfield, 4 deep into turn & pushed forward, 1L off lead into straight & ridden, weakened steadily.
On back foot slightly at start, ridden through to sit outside lead 1 off, back to 3rd 700m & niggled, ridden 450m, one-paced to line.
Hard ridden early but couldn't muster & back to tail 1 off, niggled 700m, driven 500m, never a factor.
Even start, settled midfield 1 off, to rail 700m, ridden along soon after, dropped out.
Began smartly, couldn't muster, back to beyond midfield spot 3 deep, hard ridden 650m & back to last, right out of it.
Sent forward, raced inside the lead initially before taking it outright near 600M, pulled away gradually and kept on to score by 2-1/2L.
Pushed and settled in box-seat, sat 1-1/4L off, checked at 700M, kept on but never threatened the winner.
Raced in behind midfield, 3L behind along the rail, ran on well to the line but was no match to the first two.
Pushed then crowded shortly after the start, settled front of midfield, 2L off but wide, kept on one paced to the line.
At the rear, 4-1/4L behind 2 wide, improved slightly along the inside rail early in the straight, one paced in the latter.
Settled to race in worse than midfield, 3L behind 2 wide, kept on one paced in the straight.
Raced at the rear, 4-3/4L behind 3 wide with cover, only passed tired runners.
Travelled in front of midfield, sat 1-1/2L off 2 wide, lost ground at home turn, made no progress thereafter.
In worse than midfield, 2-3/4L behind 3 wide with cover, swung widest and found nothing in the straight.
Sent forward and raced inside the lead, dropped off when rounding home turn not a factor.
Pushed and raced prominently but trapped wide, hung in throughout, not competitive.
A little slow to move, hard ridden to go forward inside leaders, edging to the front passing 1000m. Kicked 2L clear turning for home, kicked further ahead 300m, went to the post unchallenged.
Restrained shortly after start and shifted in for cover, settling towards rear in one-out position. Swung wide entering straight, taken to centre track and finished off nicely.
Steadied on jumping, shifted in towards rail, settling behind midfield. Switched out in straight to get clear running and ran on steadily to grab minor placing.
Broke well, not pushed, settling in box seat 2L from leader entering back stretch. Took up the chase on entering straight but unable close gap and swamped by two other rivals close home.
Hard ridden on jumping but didn't muster, dropping towards rear along fence. Stayed on rail around home turn and ran home fairly in straight.
Outpaced and distant last on settling. Tagged on to field turning for home and ran past beaten rivals in straight.
Pressed forward from outside gate, taking first turn 5-wide before getting cover entering back stretch 2L from leader. Under pressure turning for home and faded gradually in straight.
Taken in for cover soon after start, settling towards rear, mostly in one-out position. Switched out to centre track soon after straightening but only one-paced. Lame left front leg.
Hard ridden between horses to lead soon after jumping before being passed by inside runner 1000m. Dropped back to 3rd approaching home turn, dropped out quickly in straight.
Jumped nicely then ridden along one-out in midfield. Lost position turning for home and faded in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, showed early speed to take the lead, easy lead on turn, kept on very well in straight and scored.
Crowded out start, raced at tail, still 7 to 8 lengths back on turn, angled out in straight and finished off very strongly to be nearest on line.
Began well, difficult to settle the 1st turn, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, there to turn, kept on well in straight, just missed 2nd on line.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, kept on well in straight to make frame.

Bumped start and unbalanced, unable to slot in, travelled wide and without cover in midfield, sent forward to sit outside the leader in the middle stages, kept on well after turning in, just missed frame late.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, there to turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off evenly. (Lame right hind leg next day morning.)
Slowly away from a wide draw, raced at rear, still well back on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made some progress.
Slightly slow out, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, similar position on turn, made some progress in straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, peaked on turn, kept on one-paced to the line.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, improved on turn, peaked early in straight and weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide at rear, still 8 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back to race at rear, 5 lengths or so back on rail, taken wide after turning in, showed no progress.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, peaked on turn, failed to close off in straight, never competitive.
Slightly slow out, raced 4 wide and without cover behind midfield, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight, never competitive. (The whip broke shortly after the start.)

Jumped well, took the lead easily, travelled well throughout, kicked clear after turning in, easily scored.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 lengths or so back at rear, improved from 550M, made reasonable progress to get 2nd, never a threat to the winner.
Taken back to race at rear, improved from 600M, taken wide after turning in and made minor progress to get 3rd.

Began fairly, raced outside the leader in 2nd, difficult to settle when being steadied in the early stages, same position on turn, peaked near 250M, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slightly slow out from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, a length or so back in midfield, peaked after turning in, weakened thereafter, finished tailed out.
Pushed forward, box seat, held up 4-2, dashed strongly and drifted away when clear.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, benefited by the slow sectionals, ran on well for 2nd.
Pushed forward, took rail and led at slow sectionals, hung on until 150M overhauled, ran on for 3rd.
At rear, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, held up 400M, dashed strongly when clear.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, raced keenly, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Hard ridden to hold the rail at back, harmed by the slow pace, no turn of foot.
Eased to sit in midfield, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, no dash.
Pushed to keep up in midfield along the fence, not suited by the slow pace, never improved.
Bumped start, at back, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Slow away, never competitive.
Pushed along early to lead, travelling nicely midrace, kicked clear at 400m and held off all for comfortable win.
Jumped fairly, settled off pace, tracked leader into straight, tried hard to challenge but no match.
Slow to begin and settled midfield, rails run on straightening and finished strongly.
Began fairly and bumped, settled midfield wide and without cover, kept coming in straight.
Settled towards rear, urged along to improve passing 600m, made up some ground in straight.
Settled behind midfield, drifted back to rearward position passing 900m, pushed along to improve passing 600m and made up some ground in straight.
Sent forward to race outside leader, under pressure on straightening and gradually weakened.
Failed to must speed and settle behind midfield, keen and awkward on heels near 1000m, ran on fairly in straight.
No early speed and settled and settled towards rear, worked home fairly in straight.
Jumped well, settled midfield, under pressure in straight, held up at 250m, one pace thereafter.
Sent forward to settle on pace, under pressure home turn and gradually gave ground.
Began fairly and then crowded, settled behind midfield under pressure at 600m, one paced to the line.
Bumped at start and settled at rear, under pressure at 600m and made no impression in straight.
Jumped nicely and settled in handy position, faded on straight.
Started ok, bustled to soon settle midfield on rail, overraced 800m, edged 1 off 500m, shifted out & shaken up 400m, sustained strong progress to lead at line.
Speedy break, settled 1 back on fence 950m, shifted out & driven 400m, quickened up final 250m to edge lead 50m, overhauled at line.
Speed to lead & pushed on to snare rail 950m, driven into stretch under pressure, headed 400m but rallied to regain narrow advantage 120m, no extra & headed 50m.
Shifted in at break & bumped rival, bustled forward wide, raced handy 3 deep no cover, driven 430m, fought on dourly without threatening.
Awkward & slow at break, settled rail near rear, 5L back & driven into stretch, closed off for late gains.
Speedy break but bumped, rolled forward to park close 2nd outside leader, shaken up to edge lead 400m, tight duel, all out & headed 120m, tapered.
Bumped start, keen in mid rank wide without cover, taken back near rear 1 off with cover, niggled 500m, driven into stretch, switched out 400m, kept on evenly.
Impeded start & taken back to race 2nd last 1 off, edged out on turn, stayed on for minor headway.
Smart start, tracked 1 back 1 off, niggled 550m & soon under pump to hold position, weakened.
Moderate start, soon rolled to midfield 1 off with cover, shifted 3 deep on turn & niggled, driven turning in, outpaced & plugged home tamely.
Smart start, snagged to midfield 3 wide with cover, outpaced & ridden along 800m, 3rd last at top of stretch, plodded on same speed.
Taken back to tail from widest gate, to rail 800m, checked off heels 750m, switched 1 off 600m, forced widest home turn, tepid run home.
Jumped fast, natural speed to settle just behind leaders 3rd, keen at times, held together until 500m, switched out 420m, hit lead 300m, raced right away.
Began well, ridden hard to go forward, 1L lead on rail by 1700m, well-rated in front, joined 600m, ridden along shortly afterwards, no match for winner but stuck on solidly.
Couldn't muster early, back to beyond midfield 1 off, shifted 3 deep 800m & whipped around field soon after, joint lead 600m 3 out, kept on but no match.
In front at post 1st time, eased to sit 2nd 1 off, poked through to make line of 3 on speed at 520m, never quite on top, fought on well.
Eased from gates, settled beyond midfield 1 off, switched 3 deep 650m, travelled into race strongly, clicked up 420m, one-paced to line.
Restrained from barriers, settled last 1 off, slightly keen at times, ridden 600m, took an age to wind up but got going very late.
Away OK, eased to beyond midfield spot on rail, shifted off rail 650m, ridden 500m, erratic at times in straight, one-paced late.
Slightly slow to begin, back to rear early, settled near tail on inside, back to last again 680m, ridden 500m, short of room on straightening, never a factor.
Began on terms, ridden to get into handy spot, settled 4th 1 off, ridden 700m, under pressure soon after, weakened out.
Raced in behind midfield, 4-3/4L behind along the rail, showed good dash early before closing off strongly near 150M to score.
Pushed forward to take rail and led by 3/4L, pulled away on straightening, kept on nicely until caught by winner approaching 50M. (Trainer questioned)
In midfield, 4L behind 2 wide, awkward to heels when rounding turn, kept on well to the line to take 3rd.
Eased and raced towards the rear, 7L behind 2 wide, covered good ground and ran home well.
Sent forward and raced prominently, sat 2L off but wide and without cover, kept on one paced to the line.
At the rear, 8-1/4L behind 2 wide, started move passing 600M, made nice ground on outer straight, ran on.
Pushed forward and settled to race outside the lead, sat 3/4L off, kept on until near 150M and then flattened.
Rolled forward and settled in one-off one-back position, sat 2-1/2L off, one paced and weakened after 150M.
Settled to race in midfield, 3-1/2L behind 3 wide with cover, finished off only one paced.
Travelled towards the rear, 6-3/4L behind along the rail, showed slight dash after 200M but mostly one paced.
Ridden but showed no early speed, settled in behind midfield, 5-1/2L behind 3 wide with cover, showed some response after 200M.
Rolled forward to race in box-seat, sat 1-1/2L off, stayed on until 300M and flattened.
Settled to race in midfield, 3L behind along the rail, slightly crowded at 1000M, found nothing in the straight.
Broke well, snagged back, settling one-out towards rear. Swung wide entering straight, surged forward to hit the front 150m, pulling clear at the line.
Began well, pressed forward, grabbing box seat 2L from leader on settling. Urged forward turning for home, looked chance 200m, unable match finishing burst of winner.
Jumped well, taken to rail in midfield and switched off. Urged forward turning for home, 4-wide into straight, hit the front 250m, flattened final strides.
Snagged back soon after start and last on settling. Last into straight, switched out widest and finished off strongly to just miss a placing.
Began OK, no early pace, dropping to rear along rail. Shaken up turning for home but only one-paced.
Hard ridden along rail to go forward, taking over lead passing 1200m. Set good pace to 250m when overtaken and faded.
Jumped best, led to 1200m when overtaken. Tracked leader to straight, under pressure passing 200m and faded.

Hard driven from draw 12, crossed to the lead 900M and steadied the pace, opened up 2L lead at 300M, battled on well under 10lb claimer, dug deep late stages to just hold off the strong finishing 2nd.

Prominent early, track leaders from 900M, raced tight 700M and lost ground, 2Ls to make up on the leader and eventual winner at top of straight, closed fast final 150M but drifted out under pressure late stages and was just denied.
Jumped well but had to be bustled along to hold a position ahead of midfield, moved up along rails to be 2nd at 400M, continued to chase on straightening but couldn't get near to first two.
Began well from inside draw, not pace of leaders early stages, 7th on settling, saved ground on inside, stayed on mildly over final 350M, no threat to first two.
Held up 2-wide in midfield 4Ls off the pace, switched wider 650M, picked up well early straight but run ended 150M and no extra over final stages.
Dropped back to near the rear after the start, 10th on turn, made limited progress over final 300M.
Jumped on terms, 2-wide in midpack and 3Ls off the pace middle stages, tried hard over final 300M but couldn't sprint enough to get closer to leaders.
Pushed along to hold its position behind leaders, 3-wide no cover home turn, one paced in the run home out of contention 200M.
Pushed forward from wide barrier and settled 2nd outside leader, faded away from 350M.
Taken back to last on debut, over 10Ls off the pace early stages, moved closer to be 6L down approaching top of straight, couldn't accelerate enough and never a threat to leaders.
Placed near the rear, 2nd last well off the pace early stages, couldn't quicken turning in, never in the picture.
Got into a position behind mid-division, 6Ls off the pace home turn, couldn't quicken passing 400M, wilted final 200M.
Settled down behind midfield, couldn't keep up passing 350M, dropped away from there.
Jumped with field but unable handle early pace, dropping 3L back in one-out position. Began forward move passing 500m, got run between horses 200m, surged through to win narrowly.
Jumped well, hard ridden to stay within a half length of pacemakers, one-away from outer fence. Joint leader passing 400m, hit the front narrowly 200m, run down close home.
Away nicely, pressed forward, settling a half length inside leading pack. Lay out from 800m, forced to shift in 300m for clear running, battled only gamely, tiring only in final strides.
Off OK, taken to outer rail, settling 1L behind pacemakers. Shaken up passing 400m and kept on gamely to just miss a placing.
Jumped OK but unable handle early pace, dropping back towards rear along outer fence. Shifted in passing 600m to get clear running and finished off strongly.
Crowded out at start, dropping towards rear. Allow to stride out at own pace behind midfield one-away from outer fence. Boxed on steadily final 400m without looking dangerous.
Jumped best, switched out but held in centre track, settling 1L behind the pace. Kept on well to 200m before running out of steam, giving ground gradually.
Began well, hard ridden to stay with pace, joint leader passing 500m. Under pressure 300m, kept on gamely to 150m before giving ground.
Steadied soon after start and shifted out to obtain cover, settling behind midfield 3-away from outer fence. Made steady progress midway through the race but only one-paced final 200m.
Beaten for early pace, then raced behind midfield close to outer fence. Put under pressure 400m but only one-paced.
Broke well, pressed forward to take narrow lead 3-away from outer fence. Joined up front 500m but kept battling to 300m when started to shorten stride, dropping back.
Beaten for early pace and soon at rear. Never competitive.
Began well, taken to centre field, settling 3L behind the pace. Put under pressure passing 400m, kept on fairly to 200m before tiring.
Slow into stride and distant last on settling. Never in the hunt and finished tailed out.

Bumped on jumping and dropped back from the wide draw to sit towards the rear of the field. Came wide in the straight to ensure a clear run. Let down from 200m and ran very strongly from that point, easing late.
Cruised forward early to sit around midfield, 1 off the fence. Ran strongly in the straight, showing good turn off foot in last 200m, but couldn't match winner.
Showed good gate speed and pushed out to be clear leader. Still in front at 150m, but started to fade slightly from there, and was just beaten for 2nd on the line.
Cruised forward early to sit forward of midfield, on the fence. Ran solidly down the fence in the straight, but didn't threaten a place.
Taken up from the inside draw to be handily placed 4th, on the fence. Drifted off the fence at 200m, and plugged along fairly to the line.
Pushed forward early, before easing off at 1200 and settling forward of midfield. Battled on fairly in the straight, without ever threatening.
Dropped back early to sit in the last pair. Battled on steadily in the straight, and picked up a few runners on the way to the line.

Pushed forward from the wide draw and looking for cover early. Stuck 3 wide outside the leader until dropping back to get cover at 800m. 1 paced in the straight, and not pushed hard after bump at 200m. Vet-Lame off fore.
Pushed forward early to be well placed 2nd/3rd, 1 off the fence. Battled on only fairly early in the straight, before being crowded at 200m and not pushed hard to the line late.
Bumped on jumping and dropped back from the wide draw to be last. Plugged away fairly in the straight and picked up a few slower ones late.
Fairly away, easing forward to sit worse than midfield. Widest on the turn, and only went fairly to the line.
Dropped back early to sit towards the rear of the field. Struggled to get going in straight and was eased late.
Fractious before the jump and only fairly away, before settling around midfield. Taken wider at 600m. Never kicked in the straight and went meekly to the line.
Bounded on jumping and slow to begin. Recovered to sit midfield, on the rail. Dropped out quickly from the 300m, and eased a long way from home.
