Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, slightly improved from 650M, finished off strongly to score.
Crowded out start, raced 5 to 6 lengths back at rear on rail, improved on turn, ran on well in straight while laying in under pressure.
Taken back to race at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, sent forward from 550M, very wide on turn, kept on well in straight, just missed 2nd on line.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths back, slightly improved near 700M, 2nd on turn, kept on well early in straight, headed 150M and weakened thereafter.
Slightly slow out from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths or so back in 5th, raced tight near 550M, finished off evenly in straight without threatening.
Jumped well from gate 8, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, similar position to near 600M, improved on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Slowly away, no early speed, raced at tail, still well back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Jumped well, raced prominently, bumped near 1050M, took the lead thereafter, peaked near 200M and headed, weakened thereafter.
Began awkwardly, checked near 1450M, positioned on rail in midfield, steadied near 550M, made no progress in straight.
Jumped well from the widest draw, took the lead early, bumped near 1050M and unbalanced, headed thereafter, sat behind the leader to turn, emptied early in straight.
Bumped start from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover, 2 lengths or so back, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight and eased. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, travelled wide and without cover throughout, emptied on turn, finished tailed out.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Eased back, took cover, 2 wide, favoured by the fast pace, lack room 4-2, dashed well when clear.
Pushed to obtain box seat, ran on well for 3rd.
Eased at start, 2-3 wide at back, benefited by the fast pace, made steady ground 250M.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, out of fuel 150M.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3-4 wide throughout, harmed by the fast pace, flattened 150M.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at fast sectionals, hung on until 150M weakened.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, favoured by the fast pace, however held up most straight, ran on ok.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, benefited by the fast pace, ran on only fairly in straight.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, soon emptied 250M.
Slow away, at back, 2-3 wide, suited by the fast tempo, however never improved.
Eased at start, never competitive.
After start pushed along to take lead, kicked out after Home Turn, fought on strongly in straight for narrow win.
Fast out, settled at handy position, quickened and challenged strongly passing 150M, just missed by a neck.
Urged from wide barrier till settle forward of midfield, asked effort at home turn, travelled solid in the straight.
Jumped well, raced behind midfield, travelled wide in early straight, worked home well.
Hard ridden till 800M to settle outside leader, pushed at home turn, lost ground passing 150M, finished fairly.
Settled midfield, travelled 3 wide without cover, tried hard in the straight, came home only fairly.
Jumped smartly then eased to settle in midfield, one-paced in the straight.
Normal start, gradually eased to race at rear, ran fairly in the straight.
Began slowly, settled at rear on rail, under pressure but only one-paced.
Settled behind midfield on rail, pushed hard in early straight but failed to run on.
Taken back at start and settled at tail, weakened in the straight and failed to run on.
Began awkwardly, ridden along to obtain forward position, severely checked at 850M, finished tail. Lame left front leg, OVE.
Broke well & worked forward from wide gate to lead 1st turn, to rail 1200m & steadied tempo, wound it up out of back stretch, shaken up turning in & kicked 1.5L clear, held on.
Smart start & taken back to settle 1 off with cover near rear, niggled 750m, under pump 650m, steadied on turn, switched out & bumped 300m, balanced up 200m, closed to 2nd late.
Moderate start, soon near rear & bustled on rail, rolled to midfield 1050m, driven & shifted out on turn, stayed on dourly to 3rd close home.
Broke ok, raced handy 1 off with cover, 5th & niggled 600m, driven for progress 450m, vied for minors, battled on evenly.
Broke ok, handy on rail initially, shifted 1 off 1100m to race 2nd without cover, bustled 520m & soon driven, one paced in run home.
Broke well, taken back to 1 off behind midfield, off heels 1100m & to rail, 1 off & advanced a spot 750m, driven 400m, plugged on one pace.
Sharp start but soon outpaced & niggled midfield on rail, closed to handy 1 back 1000m, niggled to hold spot 600m, hard driven 400m, tapered in run home.
Smart break, soon nudged along & settled midfield 1 off with cover, shifted 3 deep with cover 850m & advanced a spot, driven 4 deep 450m, one-paced.
Tardy break & niggled, trapped wide 1st turn, settled second last on inner, driven home turn, edged centre track in run, plodded home without threat.
Slow start & bustled, soon 1L detached at tail & ridden to maintain contact, plugged on tepidly past beaten rivals.
Speed & led 1500m, soon headed & parked 3rd 1 off with cover, forced 3 wide 1100m, niggled 550m, unable to hold position & wide into stretch, beaten when bumped 250m, faded.
Awkward start & rousted initially, raced 3 wide with cover midfield, overraced 850m, under pump 600m, 2nd last & empty turning in.
Even dispatch, back to 2nd last on rail, shifted off rail 950m, ridden to improve 450m, pulled centre track, strode up powerfully, joined 150m, pulled clear late.
Very awkward jump, recovered to settle midfield on rail, overracing slightly, niggled 600m, railed through before pushing into clear 300m, raced to lead 150m but joined quickly, outgunned late

Broke strongly, pushed towards lead, keen at post 1st time between runners, settled just behind lead 1 off & overracing to 950m, back to midfield 750m & niggled, switched 3 deep to improve soon after, boxed on.
Snagged from outside gate to sit at rear, ridden 500m, railed through, made solid ground into 4th.
Fast jump, ridden early to be amongst leaders, settled behind speed 1 off before midfield from 1000m, losing ground & under heavy drive 550m, picked up again very late.
Jumped well, among leaders early, narrow lead post 1st time on rail, slightly keen, headed 960m, urged along with leader, regained front 550m, ridden 360m, joined 150m, one-paced.
Away evenly, 3 deep early, pushed wider 1300m & eased, settled beyond midfield 1 off & keen, 3 deep from 900m, under riding 700m, back to 2nd last 450m, widest into straight, one-paced.
Hard-ridden from gates, outpaced early, joined lead 3 deep just past post 1st time, settled 2nd 1 off until passed 960m, outsped & back behind leaders, losing ground 500m, no threat.
Attempted to ease from wide gate but keen, settled beyond midfield 1 off early but racing erratically, allowed to stride forward 1100m, in front 960m, rejoined 550m, ridden 350m, quickly weakened.
Hampered shortly after the start, back to beyond midfield & niggled, clicked up 500m, short of room 400m, checked 300m, couldn't pick up.
Slightly slow break, recovered to lead momentarily, settled just behind speed on rail, overracing slightly, niggled 750m, ridden soon after, short of room 300m, eased from 150m.
Eased from gates, settled near tail 1 off early, shifted 3 deep 1050m & ridden to go forward, up to 3rd 3 deep 750m & ridden hard, checked 300m when weakening, eased right down.
Sent forward, took rail and led by about 1/2L, ran on gamely, held off challenge to score by 3/4L.
Raced in the box-seat, sat 1-1/4L off, ran on very nicely but couldn't catch the winner.
Settled in one-off one-back position, sat 2L off the lead, kept on nicely to the line.
Travelled in worse than midfield, 4-3/4L behind 3 wide with cover, improved steadily and hit the line well.
Raced just behind midfield, 3-1/2L behind 2 wide, showed slight dash near 200M, one paced mostly.
Pushed and sat outside the lead, sat about 1/2L off, kept on until flattened passing 150M.
Initially in behind midfield, dropped to the rear when racing ungenerously, 2 wide at turn, one paced.
At the tail end, 4-3/4L behind along the fence, made slight ground early, ran on the line.
Eased back and raced at the rear, 5-3/4L behind along the rail, one paced.
Raced in midfield, 3-1/4L behind along the rail, gave ground passing 200M.
Settled in midfield 3L behind, wide and without cover throughout, weakened at 250M.
Awkward start and became detached throughout, never a factor.
Broke well, shared early pace before settling in box seat 2L from leader. Switched out top of straight to make run, gradually overhauling leader to win close home.
Away nicely, raced 3-wide initially before setting one-out, one back. Took a few strides to gain momentum in straight, finished strongly final 200m to grab second placing.
Jumped well, hard ridden to lead on settling, then set good pace to straight. Joined up front 100m out and swamped by two rivals close home.

Off nicely, quickly taken in for cover, dropping one-out towards rear. Under pressure turning for home, given reminders early in straight, picked up strongly final stages to finish on heels of place-getters.
Began OK, then ridden to hold rail behind midfield. Made up ground around home turn, stayed on rail in straight and ran on steadily.
Began well, ridden to obtain forward position but unable find cover and raced mostly 3-wide in midfield. Swung wide into straight and boxed on fairly.
Jumped fairly, then ridden to make up ground before settling one-out in midfield. Made some ground around home turn, shifted out 400m to go forward but didn't finish off.
Steadied shortly after start and shifted in for cover, dropping to last. Stayed at rear until straightening before making up some ground in straight.
Out quickly, sharing early pace before settling one-out 1L from leader. Threw out challenge top of straight, battled on gamely to 200m before tiring.
Beaten for early pace and soon at rear but wide. Kept wide around turn, one-paced in straight.
Hampered on jumping, losing ground, dropping to rear along fence. Put under pressure turning for home but only one-paced.
Pressed forward from outside gate, racing 4-wide 4L from leader entering back stretch. Under pressure turning for home, losing ground steadily, before tiring badly in straight.
Held up in 8th 4Ls off the pace, made early move 550M out, hit top gear mid-straight sweeping to the lead 100M out, kept on well to hold off a late challenge.
Taken across behind runners, given a waiting ride in last, peeled off the fence 400M, mounted a strong challenge outside the winner, ran his usual honest race, just held.
Settled down 2nd last, 5Ls off the pace 600M, moved closer over the home turn, tried hard to the line for minor honours but well held by first 2 over final stages.
Pressed forward and obtained the rail spot soon after the start, always prominent, led them into the straight, kept grinding when challenged, lost lead 100M, faded towards the line.
Towards the rear, quickly moved up along the fence passing 400M, held ground and lacked the winning dash over final 200M.
Settled down in midfield, ran on moderately on straightening, severely checked close home to avoid a fallen jockey and might have been 4th.
Chased leaders, awkwardly placed behind a weakening rival 400M and was steadied, failed to make an impression on straightening.
Chased leaders along the 3-path, no cover after 600M, responded briefly turning in, weakened 200M.
Close up behind leaders in a strongly run race, struggled to keep up home turn, couldn't get back to it and left behind by rivals passing 300M.
Pressed forward from wide draw, caught wide without cover until 600M, weakened passing 400M to finish tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance.)

Placing: UR
Comment: Never far off from leaders, improved to 2nd inside 300M, tried hard in the run home but broke down 25M out and dislodged rider.

Jumped awkwardly but soon placed in 3rd behind the leading pair, came to challenge under pressure inside the final 200 metres, just got up.
Ridden forward to share the pace on stands rails, gained narrow advantage coming onto course proper, only to be pipped at post.
Held slender lead to the 600 metres when headed narrowly, remained close up to the line, lost 2nd late.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, raced keenly in midfield one off the stands rails, finishing off race nicely when hampered and stumbled 50 metres out.
Ridden along in forward of midfield, produced good late impression closing stages.
Ridden to 4th about 3L off the pace, unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.
Settled behind midfield from the one draw down the centre of the track, kept on same pace without quickening.
Jumped fairly, ridden along the stands rails in midfield, found nothing under pressure inside the final 400 metres.
Jostled between runners at the start, soon dropped towards the rear, kept on past well-beaten horses closing stages.
Crowded at start, soon dropped to last few, made short-lived effort coming onto course proper, weakened.
Tailed-off early, ran on past well-beaten horses inside the final 300 metres.
Never better than midfield.
Settled in midfield, faded out of contention from half-way out.
Never better than midfield.
Hard ridden to take the rail and lead, clocked fast sectionals, drifted away 400M to score.
Hard ridden to keep up with the fast pace in front of midfield, closed off strongly for 2nd.
At back, along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M for 3rd.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 2 wide, ran on until 100M flattened.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast sectionals, ran on until 150M flattened.
Bumped start, at rear along the fence, favoured by the fast pace, made steady ground 300M, on heels 50M.
Hard ridden early, trapped 3 wide in front of midfield, ran on fairly in straight.
At rear, raced 3-4 wide, benefited by the fast pace, ran on ok in final furlong.
At back, raced 3-4 wide, suited by the fast tempo, however never improved.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the fast tempo, emptied 250M.
Never competitive at rear.
Pushed forward, harmed by the fast pace, dropped off 400M.
Jumped well, settled behind midfield, rails run on straightening, gained control final 100m for strong win.
Ridden along early to hold midfield position, pushed along passing 600m, improved along rail home turn, strong challenge at 250m, overpowered inside 100m.
Settled worse than midfield, commenced to improve passing 500m, made strong steady ground in straight.
Ridden along early to race on pace, moved up to challenge at 350m and fought on solidly to the line.
Allowed to settle at rear, ridden along to improve near 500m, got going final 150m to make up good ground.
Fast out and settled on pace, eased out to improve near 500m and issue challenge on straightening, run ended at 100m and awkward late when weakening.
Jumped smartly and settled midfield wide without cover, tight at 500m, ridden along to challenge in straight, unable to quicken and one paced to finish.
Hampered at start and settled at rear, ran on fairly in straight.
Hard ridden early stages to eventually lead at 800m, travelling okay home turn, overpowered passing 250m and gave ground.
Blundered at start and then failed to muster, settled at rear, under pressure to improve at 600m. Made no impression in straight.
Hard ridden to go forward and settle on pace, under pressure at 600m and lay out home turn, weakened.
Began fairly and settled at rear, made no impression
Slow break & soon at tail, 3-deep advance 1500m to mid pack at halfway, gradual progress to 2nd 1 off 880m, shaken up 430m, driven to lead 250m, drew well clear, eased close home.
Awkward start, midfield 3 deep 1st turn, advanced 1250m & led 980m, to rail 880m, driven 430m, kicked but pressured, all out & headed 250m, just held 2nd.
Pace to lead 1800m, soon to rail, headed 1400m & shuffled back to midfield 900m, shifted out & driven 650m, bumped 400m & crowded 300m, stayed on late to 3rd.
Started ok, sat handy 1 off with cover, shuffled back 1200m, shaken up 4 wide into stretch, stayed on evenly.
Broke ok, prominent & soon pushed on to 2nd 1 off, shuffled to 1 back 1 off 880m & niggled, driven into stretch, boxed on until tapered final 100m.
Missed break, raced 2nd last on rail, to tail 1450m & raced last pair 1 off, advanced 1150m, driven forward 900m & switched 3 deep, 4 wide into stretch, stayed on until emptied 100m.
Started ok but soon out-paced, niggled to settle back of midfield on rail, shuffled to 2nd last 1000m, niggled 600m, driven 430m, ran on for minor gains.
Broke well, settled midfield on rail, shifted 1 off 950m & niggled, ridden wide home turn, driven into stretch, kept on moderately.
Slow start, raced rail near rear, over-raced & restrained to tail by 1200m, shifted 1 off 1050m, shifted inside for clear run 400m, driven home one pace.
Bumped start, pace to lead 1st turn on rail, soon headed to sit 1 back, shuffled back 1200m, niggled 900m, 1 off & ridden 600m, crowded & bumped 300m, no extra.
Driven at break, soon settled midfield 1 off with cover, over-raced 1120m & shifted 3 wide for progress, hard-ridden 4th 600m, found nil in stretch & faded.
Tardy break & niggled to 1 off near rear, bustled for progress 3 wide 1100m, lacked toe & forced 4 deep, hard driven 800m, wide into stretch, struggled in run home.
Started ok widest & rousted forward, four-wide in front rank 1st turn, worked 3 deep to lead 1400m, to rail 1200m, headed 980m & niggled, under pump 750m, faded tamely.
Began well, up into box-seat position quickly, travelled strongly throughout, stuck to rail on straightening, ridden 450m, knuckled down willingly, joint lead 100m, got the bob.
Broke fast, ridden to press forward, led early, 1L lead 900m, clicked up 500m, kicked grimly, joined 100m, fought back doggedly but outbobbed.
Quick jump, natural speed to press towards lead but keen at times, settled 2nd 1 off, ridden 500m, never quite on top, boxed on.
Good break, ridden into forward spot 1 off, pushed along 600m, one-paced in straight, came again very late.
Even break, settled into spot just fore of midfield on rail, pushed off fence 620m, ridden 420m, tight of room 350m, one-paced to line.
Broke OK, eased to settle midfield 1 off, pulling at times, held together until 450m, pulled centre track, made good ground late.
Slightly slow start, eased to settle near rear on rail, improved along inside 1000m, clicked up 550m, stayed on same pace.
Away on terms, settled fore of midfield 1 off, niggled 600m, pulled 3 deep & driven soon after, weakened in straight.
Fair jump, stuck beyond midfield on rail & ridden 1350m, up to midfield by 1000m, ridden 800m, niggled along to 500m, couldn't pick up.
Struggled to muster early, settled beyond midfield 1 off, niggled at times throughout, widest into straight, struggled to pick up.
Very awkward jump, settled last, niggled throughout, improved along rail 950m, driven 600m, never in contention.
Away on terms, eased right back initially, into just beyond midfield spot 3 deep, overracing, pulled back to 2nd last 800m, ridden 600m, never a threat.
Slightly awkward start, eased towards tail, settled at rear 1 off, overracing from 1200m, back to last 950m, ridden 580m, no chance.
Raced one-off one-back, 1-1/2L off, progressed steadily to catch 2nd placegetter inside final 50M, scored by a neck.
Sent forward and take the rail and led by 3/4L, ran on nicely until caught by winner inside final 50M.
Eased and taken back, raced 4-1/4L behind along the rail, showed good dash near 250M, ran on well for 3rd.
Settled to race in the box-seat, sat 1-1/2L off the lead, kept on well to the line for 4th.
Pushed and settled to race outside the lead, sat 3/4L off, out of steam passing 150M.
Travelled keenly early, settled in midfield 2-3/4L behind along the rail, kept on one paced home.
Break slowly, raced at the rear, 6-1/4L behind along the rail, kept on one paced to the line.
In behind midfield, 4-1/4L behind 2-3 wide with cover, one paced and only passed tired runners.
Travelled in midfield, 2-1/2L behind 2 wide, one paced until flattened passing 200M.
Raced in midfield, but trapped very wide and without cover, hung in at turn, found nothing in the straight.
Settled in midfield, 3 wide without cover, faded gradually in the straight.
Broke well, taken in but unable find cover and held 3-wide 2L from leader on settling. Nudged forward approaching straight, hit front 300m, finished off strongly.
Jumped OK, shifted across behind runners but difficult to settle and dropped back to rear. Taken 3-wide turning for home and finished off strongly in straight while rolling in against the whip.
Bounced well, hard ridden to get forward position, settling one-out 1L from leader. Got shuffled back entering straight but fought on gamely in straight to hold minor placing despite shifting ground.
Quickly into stride, taking lead on settling and setting good pace to straight. Collared passing 300m but kept battling to finish in the frame.
Away nicely and soon in box seat 3L from leader. Came off fence to make challenge 400m but unable close gap despite hard riding.
Allowed to slide forward at own pace, settling one-out 3L from leader. Lost position turning for home but kept on gamely in straight to finish just behind place-getters.
Ridden to find cover, settling one-out behind midfield. Made some progress around home turn, blocked for run early in straight, shifted out 350m and finished off fairly. Rider dropped whip 100m.
Restrained shortly after start and shifted across behind horses from wide draw, settling at rear. Taken wide entering straight and ran past beaten rivals.
Slow into stride, pushed along fence to make up ground but difficult to settle and checked off heels 1200m. Improved position around turn but only one-paced in straight.

Bounced well, pressed forward but wide before getting cover though 3-wide in midfield turning for home. Wide in straight, boxed on fairly before eased down final stages. Had superficial abrasions both hocks.
Began fairly, ridden to hold rail but badly checked 1200m, dropping towards rear. Made up some ground around turn but only one-paced in straight.

Pressed forward from an outside gate, racing wide in midfield before clipping heels and blundering 1150m, dropping back. Lost further ground home turn and finished tailed out. Unacceptable performance.

Caught wide no cover from draw 12, improved to the lead entering home turn but still wide, continued on well in straight under 10lb claimer and built up enough of a margin to hold off the fast finishing 2nd.
Given a waiting ride at the rear, 8Ls off the good pace entering the turn, found clear passage nearing 200M hit the line hard to finish just 0.5L behind winner.
Tracked the leading trio in a strongly run race, had every chance turning in but lacked the winning dash, well held by leader in the run home.
Chased the pace in 5th, 3Ls to make up 400M, fought on steadily on the inside but couldn't sprint enough to be closer.
Not hurried early stages, dropped back to a position behind midfield, 6-7Ls off the good pace at 400M, ran on mildly to line, no serious threat.
Began fairly, hard driven to the fore under 10lb claimer, taken on by rivals passing 700M, continued the chase on leader until weakening over final 150M.
Held up in midfield 5Ls off leader in a strongly run race, kept on one pace over final 300M and not gaining on leaders.
Taken back to the rear 7-8Ls off the good pace, driven along 550M, stayed on only fairly, no threat to leaders. (Jockey : his mount appeared reluctant to stretch out whilst resenting the kickback.)
Outpaced by leaders despite driven along, fell back to a midfield position middle stages, remained one pace turning home and outsprinted by rivals passing 250M.
Prominently ridden, chased leader along the 2-path, pace strong, weakened noticeably passing 300M.
Had trouble keeping up with rivals in a strongly run race, last of 12 making the home turn, 12Ls off leader at 400M, made no real progress in straight, never in the picture.
Began awkwardly, towards the rear, never travelled, unbalanced 500M when reluctant to maintain its position, well beaten top of straight and finished tailed out on debut. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Began well, ridden to hold rail, grabbing box seat 3L from leader after avoiding fallen horse 1050m. Rolled forward top of straight, hit front 350m and kept on strongly to win.
Ridden along but wide from an outside gate while seeking cover but severely checked 1050m and left 3-wide behind midfield. Kept wide entering straight before finishing strongly.
Pressed forward from outside gate but hampered 1050m and settled in midfield. Severely hampered by riderless horse 750m and taken wider, before finishing off strongly to grab minor placing.
Restrained shortly after start and shifted across behind runners but severely checked 1050m, dropping towards rear. Switched out top of straight and finished off nicely.
Bumped shortly after start but pressed forward, settling one-out 3L from leader. Shaken-up top of straight but severely checked passing 400m dropping back sharply. Finished off fairly.
Shifted across from wide gate shortly after start but severely checked 1050m, dropping to rear. Well back turning for home, taken to centre track on straightening and finished off fairly.

Jumped well, sharing early pace before settling outside leader 1100m after interference caused by fallen horse. Swung wide into straight before being struck by riderless horse, dropping back. Finished off one-paced.

Jumped OK, ridden along but wide before severely checked 1050m by fallen horse, dropping to behind midfield. Checked again turning for home, shifted out in straight to get clear run but only one-paced.
Hard ridden to hold forward position then left in front when leader struck rail 1050m and fell. Overtaken shortly after straightening and gave ground gradually.
Ridden along from inside gate to go forward but severely checked by fallen horse 1050m, dropping to midfield. Made progress turning for home but severely checked passing 400m, dropping back abruptly.

Broke well, ridden forward but inconvenienced 1050m when rivals shifted out, settling one-out 3L from leader. Steadied from heels of riderless horse passing 400m and collided with rival, dropping back.

Placing: UR
Comment: Restrained on jumping and shifted across to rail behind horses before striking fallen horse 1050m dislodging rider. Finished the race riderless. Lame left front leg.

Placing: FE
Comment: Bounced well, allowed to slide forward in search of the lead and crossing in 1200m before heavily striking running rail 1050m and falling, dislodging rider. Lame right front leg, wounds to right front and hind legs.

Pushed forward early to eventually settle 4th/5th, 1 off the fence. Held up early in the straight, before forcing a run at 350m. Tight at the 150m. Strong to the line, and just held out fast finishing 2nd in a head bobber late.
Eased back early to sit 3rd last, 1 off the fence. Wide on the turn, and ran strongly from the 350m. Showed great turn of foot late, and just missed the win in a head bobber on the line.
Looked to push forward early, but was beaten to the punch and was stuck 3 wide no cover towards the front of the field. Stayed on very well in the straight, and only peaked slightly late.
Tracked wide in the back straight when pushing forward to eventually lead passing the 1000m. Still in charge at the 200m, but peaked soon after, and was fading quickly in the last 50m.
Cruised forward from the inside draw to settle midfield, on the fence. Stayed on well in the straight and finished off strongly, without threatening a place.
Pushed forward to be the early leader, before being taken on in front at 1000m. Stayed on solidly in the straight, but never kicked and went to the line 1 paced late.
Slowest out and had to be pushed early to find a spot around midfield, 1 off the fence. Pushed on steadily in the straight, without ever threatening.
Began awkwardly and dropped back early to sit 2nd last. Stayed on OK in the straight, and picked up a few slower ones late.
Bumped on jumping, but recovered to settle forward of midfield. Never kicked and went to the line 1 paced.
Dropped back from the wide draw to sit a clear last. Widest on the turn, but only stayed on steadily in the straight.
Dropped back early to sit towards the rear of the field, 3 wide with limited cover. Widest on the turn and only plugged away fairly under minimal urging.
Bumped on jumping, then pushed forward to be handily placed, 4th/5th on the fence. Struggled for a run at the top of the straight, and not pushed out in the run to the line. Jockey questioned.
Eased forward early to settle around midfield. Never responded to riding in the straight, and was eased out late.
Slow to begin, dropped to the rear of the field and played no part in the race. Unacceptable performance.

Moderate start, settled just off the pace in 3rd on the rail, switched out to challenge upon straightening, gained upper hand near the line.
Began well from the one draw, setting a smart pace to virtually make all, only to be caught in the final strides.
Settled in midfield in 5th on the rail, saved ground turning for home, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled 2L back in 4th, fought on steadily in straight without threatening.
Niggled at early before steadied back in 6th in rear of midfield, came under pressure rounding home bend, finished off the race well.
Settled towards the rear from a middle draw, made good impression in the straight.
Settled behind midfield on the rail from a middle draw, saved ground turning for home, fought on steadily without threatening.
Taken back from the widest gate, trailed the field most of the way to straight, produced good late impression closing stages.
Settled well back, produced good late impression closing stages.
Ridden forward from a wide gate, chased the leader to straight, dropped away quickly.
Hard ridden to take rail and lead, ran on well to the line and scored.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2-3 wide, dashed strongly 300M, just beaten by a narrow margin in 2nd.
Eased to sit in midfield 2 wide, made early move 900M, led 300M, ran on well for 3rd.
Settled in box seat, just held ground in straight.
Pushed early, behind midfield, dashed well 250M.
Eased back, took rail, held up and checked 500M, dashed strongly 200M.
Eased back, took rail, made early move around the field in 3 wide from 900M, ran on until 200M emptied.
Eased back, 2 wide, dashed well 200M.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, attempted early move 900M but failed, dashed well 200M, on heels 50M.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, soon under pressure 400M.
Began awkwardly and hampered, hard ridden to settle outside of leader, pushed passing 400M, gained control for final 100M to hit the line.
Jumped out well, travelled wide without cover until settled at handy position near 600M, improved at home turn, finished strongly.
Bumped and became unbalanced start, raced at handy position on rail, fought solid in the straight.
Failed to muster speed despite been aggressively ridden, raced midfield, commenced to improve at home turn, gradually gained ground passing 200M, came home well.
Jumped smartly, travelled front of midfield, tried hard in the straight, finished OK.
Began fairly, settled behind midfield, awkward on heels at 400M, ran home fairly.
Settled behind midfield, became unbalanced and brushed rail near 550M, raced in restricted room at home turn, one-paced.
Raced midfield, widest on straightening, tried to improve but one-paced.
Pushed hard to take lead after start, hold the lead until weakened at 200M, faded out after passing 100M.
Taken back from outside barrier, travelled at rear, under pressure in the straight but only one-paced.
Jumped OK, settled 3 wide at handy position, gradually moved to midfield at midrace, weakened in the straight and failed to run on.
Taken back from wide draw, settled at tail, never in it.
Slow start, raced 3.5L adrift of main pack with one other, bustled along & advanced to join tail of group turning in, driven 300m & rattled home to nick win.
Fast break & ridden to dispute initial lead 3 wide, snagged 750m to slot 1 back 1 off 550m, niggled 400m, hard ridden into stretch, battled to nose ahead 50m, mugged at wire.
Broke well & bustled forward on rail, edged lead 620m & rolled 1L clear, driven 300m, boxing run but headed close home.
Started ok but rousted to hold mid rank position 3 wide with cover, checked off heels 520m & lost ground, driven wide into stretch, closed for late gains.
Smart start widest, raced wide no cover & driven into stretch, hard ridden 300m to press for minors, brushed by passing rival 90m, kept on evenly.
Speed to dispute lead 1 off, headed 620m & settled 1L back, niggled 450m, ridden into stretch, one-paced in run.
Tardy break & bustled with one other 3L adrift of main pack, driven turning in, kept on past beaten rivals.
Broke with others, ridden forward on rail to park 1 back, shifted out & driven turning in, outpaced & tapered late.
Broke ok & bustled along 1 off in midfield, overraced 550m & shifted to rail 450m, driven into stretch, found nil in tepid run home.
Sluggish start, soon well adrift at tail, never a factor.
Slow to muster from stalls, settled just beyond midfield 1 off, pulled widest into straight, ridden 320m, unleashed powerful run, just got up on line.
Fast break, eased to settle 4th 1 off, niggled 470m, sprinted strongly, got on top near line but overhauled last stride.
Started well, ridden to cross to rail, settled 3rd on inside, clicked up 350m, stuck to inside, hit lead 230m, just nabbed late.
Ridden from gates, unable to match early speed, settled midfield on rail, ridden 420m, stuck on one-paced.
Eased from barriers, settled near rear 1 off, keen at times, ridden along 370m, picked up very late.
Slow into stride, hard ridden last early, settled beyond midfield on rail, niggled 700m & again 550m, driven 300m & switched to rail, even finish.
Jumped OK, scrubbed early, settled midfield 1 off, ridden 370m, stuck on fairly.
Away well, eased into midfield spot but stuck 3 deep 1st turn, settled midfield 3 wide, niggled 400m, effort short-lived.
Jumped quickly, ridden to hold early lead, settled 2nd on rail, slightly keen, pushed off rail 400m, ridden soon after, weakened last 75m.
Restrained right back from gates, settled clear last, niggled 700m, driven 500m, shifted inside in straight, battled.
Away on terms, stuck wide early, ridden to lead from 900m, 2L lead on rail 600m, ridden 350m, joined 230m, weakened.
Slightly slow start, settled near tail on inside, driven 350m, never in contention.
Raced in midfield until falling back slightly near 700M, progressed and kept on nicely to score by 1-1/2L.
Travelled in worse than midfield, dropped to the rear near 800M, made ground and ran on strongly to the line.
Taken back initially, moved near 800M and assumed lead, headed passing 150M, ran on to the line.
Eased back and remained at the rear, moved near 800M to assume position outside lead, stayed on well to the line.
Raced outside the lead until crossed at 1000M, taken to 3 wide before turn, kept on until flattened passing 100M.
In front of midfield initially, dropped to midfield near 700M, raced 2 wide throughout, made slight ground early, ran on.
Eased and raced towards the rear, 4-1/2L behind 2 wide, moved early near 700M, made the turn wide, one paced.
Awkward start, in box-seat before dropping to midfield passing 700M, slight dash on straightening only.
Failed to muster, sat just behind midfield, 2 wide initially but wide after 950M in an ungenerous run, not competitive.
Prominent but trapped wide, settled outside the lead at 1000M, dropped to midfield near 700M, found nothing.
Raced in the lead until passing 700M when others moved, did not look likely thereafter.
Quickly in front, taken to rail and set steady sections. Kicked 2L clear on straightening and then kept finding, going to the post unchallenged.
Jumped awkwardly, rolled forward to share early pace before sliding into box seat approaching first turn. Niggled at turning for home, switched out 400m to give chase but unable to run down winner.
Jumped with field, not pressed, dropping behind midfield in one-off position. Not pressured till straightening for home when finished off steadily to grab minor placing.
Bounced well, taken to rail, settling behind midfield 5L from leader. Stayed on rail throughout, running home steadily up the straight.
Crowded out at start, not pushed, dropping to rear in one-out position. Well back turning for home, switched wide in straight to make run, boxed on fairly.

Pressed forward from outside gate, racing down centre track and taking first turn 4-wide before settling 1L behind and outside leader 1000m. Moved closer turning for home but ran out of puff 200m and faded.
Outpaced and soon at rear. Trailed field to straight and ran past tired rivals.
Jumped well, ridden to hold fence, settling 4L from leader. Switched out home turn to get run, boxed on gamely to 200m before tiring.
Crowded out start, pushed forward, settling midfield but wide. Taken to centre track on straightening but only one-paced.
Steadied soon after start and shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling at rear. One-paced in straight when asked for an effort.
Away nicely, pressed forward, settling one-out and one-back. Travelled fairly to home turn when came under pressure and dropped back gradually. Rider reported may be better suited to AWT.

Vigorously ridden to obtain forward position, racing 3-wide outside leader, but unable get cover and dropped to midfield. Under pressure from 600m and eased down in straight. Unacceptable performance.
Travelled well in midfield, 3Ls to make up 400M, quickened up strongly in straight took the lead near 50M, powered away.
Tracked leaders in 3rd, quickened up along fence to grab lead 200M, kept on well but caught by winner 50M out.
Settled down 6Ls off the good pace, headway passing 400M, ran on soundly for 3rd.
Vied for lead on the outside, pace strong, continued the chase to 200M, weakened towards the finish.
Taken back from wide bar, 3-wide at the back, 7Ls to make up 400M and brought widest home, closed off steadily without reaching leaders.
Pressed by rival in the lead, pace strong, headed 200M, run ended and faded towards the line.
Taken back from wide bar, near last making the home turn, pulled wide and stayed on without troubling leaders, tight for room 100M.
Quickly away from wide draw settled ahead of mid-division, battled on one pace only, could not reach contention.
Settled towards the rear 6Ls behind leader, couldn't finish off passing 350M, no threat to leaders.
Slowly away, travelled at the rear 8Ls off the pace, made no progress turning home.
Held up midfield, driven along 500M, never going the pace to challenge crowded for room 100M but made no difference to the result.
Saddle shifted near 1050M resulting in jockey losing the use of irons, unable to ride out for the remainder of the race.

Made all, won easily.
Well there, outclassed by the winner inside the final 300 metres.
Settled about 2L off the pace near the centre of the track, failed to quicken under pressure after coming onto course proper, soon weakened.
Well there to the 400 metres, weakened.
With leaders on the stands rail, taken one back 600 metres out, soon weakened.
Tailed-off throughout.
Settled in midfield along the fence, dashed strongly and drifted away 300M to score.
Hard ridden to secure box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, held ground for 2nd.
Hard ridden to sit in front of midfield, ran on well to the line for 3rd.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, overhauled 200M, ran on ok.
Eased back, took rail, harmed by the slow tempo, dashed well 300M.
Bumped start, at back, dashed well 250M despite not suited by the slow tempo.
Eased to rear and took rail, harmed by the slow pace, improved around the field in 5-6 wide, dashed well 200M.
Eased back, 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, little dash 250M.
Eased to rear, raced 4-5 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Pushed forward, sat outside the leader, benefited by the slow sectionals, out of fuel 300M.
Pushed to sit in midfield, trapped 3 wide, raced keenly, emptied 400M.
Pushed forward, 2-3 wide, dropped off quickly 600M.
Behind midfield, not suited by the slow tempo, never improved.
Trapped 3 wide in midfield, harmed by the slow pace, never a factor.
Jumped smartly, ridden along to take lead, kicked in early straight and held off to win.
Travelled front of midfield on rail, pushed along passing 500M, quickened after 200M, came home strongly.
Start OK, settled midfield on rail, asked effort at home turn, fought solid in the straight.
Crowded after start, no early speed and settled at rear, improved at home turn, ran on and battled well in the straight.
Jumped nicely, urged along and sat at box position, under pressure in the straight, finished OK.
Moderate start, race midfield, wide on straightening, tried hard in final stage but finished fairly.
Taken back at start, settled at tail, hung out and proved difficult to ride, finished only fairly. Unacceptable racing manners, rider questioned and must series trials.
Taken back at start, settled towards rear, bumped and unbalanced in the early straight, one-paced.
Settled midfield on rail, asked for effort passing 600M, tried hard but only one-paced.
Jumped well, ridden along after start to settle outside of leader, gradually fade out passing 300M and failed to run on in the final stages.
Raced behind midfield, failed to make any impression, only one-paced in the straight.
Slow began, settled behind midfield, tried but failed to run on.
Travelled wide without cover in midfield, out of fuel after 300M, failed to run on.
Fractious in the barrier, began only fairly, settled midfield, never in it. Must trial.
Awkward start & rousted to 1st turn, settled rail fore of midfield, shifted 1 off 550m & quickened to 2nd turning in, driven to lead 250m, raced clear.
Slow break and punched along to settle near rear 3 wide with cover, advanced wide form 700m, mid rank & progressing turning in, closed centre track to 2nd late.
Speed to lead, soon to rail & set tempo, 2L clear & shaken up 450m, soon all out & headed 250m, no extra, lost 2nd late.
Tardy & crowded start, bustled to settle near rear 1 off, to rail 800m, driven 550m & progress turning in, kept on for minor headway.
Lacked toe & bustled along to rail midfield, driven 550m, shifted out wide into stretch, driven home for even headway.
Sluggish start, raced last pair 1 off, niggled 900m, last &ridden 680m, hard driven turning in & switched out, stayed on under drive centre track.
Sharp start, to rail 1 back & overraced 1300m, 1.5L 2nd 680m & hard ridden 500m, 3rd turning in, tapered in run.
Tardy start, rolled forward to park fore of midfield 1 off with cover, keen in backstretch, shifted 3 deep for progress 600m, 4th & driven turning in, weakened in run home.
Broke ok, raced midfield 3 deep with cover, niggled 700m, to 1 off 650m & under pump 550m, plodded on tepidly.
Broke ok, soon outpaced & slotted midfield 1 off with cover, niggled 750m & shuffled back, 3rd last & driven into stretch, weak run home.
Missed break, rousted initially to race last pair on rail, niggled 900m, hard driven 550m, plugged on same speed.
Broke well, handy but trapped 3 wide no cover, pushed on 1050m to press lead, short-lived & soon retreated, faded out tamely.
Taken back, trapped 4 wide no cover back of midfield, shuffled to near tail 700m, 2nd last & driven 500m, soon to last, not a factor.
Fast break, bustled to park 2nd 1 off, niggled 1050m & shuffled to 1 of 1 back, 3 deep no cover 850m & under pressure, mid rank & hard-ridden wide on turn, faded out.
Began well, eased to midfield spot, stayed 1 off, niggled 550m, stuck to inside, hampered 350m, switched over heels 300m, sprinted strongly, hit lead 120m, comfortable win.
First to break, outsped early, settled just fore of midfield on rail, clicked up 520m, no real run on straightening, into clear 150m, closed solidly.
Slightly slow, eased to settled beyond midfield 1 out, ridden 500m, took time to wind up, strong last 100m.
Began OK, ridden to lead, 0.5L lead on rail 800m, pushed 420m, hard driven soon after, strong kick, claimed 120m.
Clearly slowest to begin, settled at rear on inside, pushed along 650m between runners, never a threat but stayed on.
Away on terms , pushed into handy spot, settled fore of midfield 1 off, ridden 460m, one-paced to line.
Jumped fast, hard-ridden to press across & sit outside lead, settled 2nd 1 off, niggled 500m, driven soon after, couldn't stay on.
On back foot slightly at start, nudged to settled fore of midfield but stuck 3 deep & pulling 900m, driven 550m, laying in & green, eased.
Broke evenly, outsped & back to near rear 1 off, hunted along to hold spot, under riding 650m, struggled to pick up.
Good jump, natural speed to get into handy spot, settled 3rd but stayed 1 off, pulled 3 deep & ridden 500m, effort short-lived.
Away only fairly, used to settle beyond midfield on rail, niggled 800m, driven 580m, lost ground & couldn't recover.
Eased from gates, settled near rear 2 off, very keen, back to last 750m, under pressure 550m, tailed out.
Travelled at the rear, 5L behind 2 wide, shifted widest and made good ground in straight, closed off strongly to score.
Sent forward to take rail and led by about 1L, always looked likely until caught late by winner in the final strides.
Raced just in front of midfield, 2-1/2L off 2 wide, shifted out to make early move at 700M, checked at 50M but kept on going to the line. (Rider questioned)
Crowded start, in worse than midfield, 4L behind along the rail, found extra passing 200M, ran on well to the line.
Jumped awkwardly, settled to race in box-seat, sat 1-3/4L off, kept on mostly one paced to the line.
Travelled in about a midfield position, 3-3/4L behind 2 wide, kept on until about 250M and then flattened.
Bumped start, eased and raced at the rear, 6L behind along the rail, under pressure near 700M, never a factor.
Raced outside the lead, sat about 1L off, weakened badly approaching 300M.
Bumped start, eased and settled towards the rear, 4-3/4L behind 3 wide without cover, showed nothing.
Jumped well, taken in for cover towards rear first turn before switching out wide back stretch. Switched in home turn, blocked 400m, switched out 300m, finished strongly to win eased down.
Hard ridden to share early pace, taking first turn 3-wide before being eased back 1L passing 1000m. Swung very wide entering straight but kept on strongly to hold down quinella spot.
Jumped well, tightened before first turn, then settled in box seat behind hot pace. Switch out 4-wide top of straight, surged forward to lead 350m, then boxed on gamely the overtaken 110m.
Jumped well then eased off hot pace, dropping back. Raced one-out behind midfield to straight, taken to centre track on straightening and finished off gamely.
Pressed forward from outside gate, taking first turn 4-wide. Hard ridden from 1000m to race outside leading duo but still held 3-wide. Kept on gamely early in straight before tiring close home.
Broke well, hard ridden to lead on the rail but harassed by outside runner. Pulled narrowly ahead on straightening but soon under pressure and tired passing 200.
Hard ridden from outside gate to go forward, taking first turn 5-wide, before settling 3-wide in midfield back stretch. Taken to centre track on straightening but found little when asked.
Hard ridden to hold forward position, eye-balling leader from first turn to straight. Boxed on gamely under pressure in straight to 200m before tiring.
Began fairly, tightened, then taken to fence towards rear. Switched out turning for home but only one-paced in straight. (Lost right front plate after 800m).
Shifted across behind runners from widest gate and last on settling. Hard ridden from 600m to go forward but only minor gain till running past beaten rivals in straight.
Beaten for pace early pace then lay out approaching first turn, dropping back towards rear. Dropped to last turning for home, one-paced.
Bounced well, hard ridden to stay forward but unable match pace and dropped 4L passing 1000m. Dropped back further approaching home turn, boxed on fairly till running on empty 100m.
Crossed to the lead passing 1000M, taken on by rivals in the fore, quickened up strongly when asked 300M and soon opened up an unassailable lead, coasted home final 50M.
Quickly away from draw 1, took cover behind eventual winner, shifted out from the box seat nearing 300M, tried hard but couldn't get closer to winner, held 2nd comfortably though.
Not hurried after the jump and eased back to near the rear, 5Ls off leader at 400M, stayed on mildly for non-threatening 3rd.
Began well, dropped back to mid-division before the turn, kept on steadily for remote 4th, no impression on first 2.
Jumped fairly to be about 5th on settling, 3-wide over home turn but always within striking distance, fought on same pace only in straight, no threat from 200M.
Chased leaders along the 2-path, couldn't accelerate enough passing 400M, out of contention mid-straight.
Ridden forward, up with pace along the 2-path, couldn't sustain run and faded passing 350M.
Began fairly, ridden along early stages trying to improve its position but became difficult to settle making the turn at 900M, towards the rear turning in, couldn't pick up and eased late stages.
Caught wide early, taken across behind runners before the turn, 6Ls off the pace and last turning in, couldn't quicken from the rear, never involved.
Began fairly, sat back in a 3-wide position towards the rear, found nothing under pressure passing 400M, eased when no chance.
Unable to cross from widest draw, caught 3 wide no cover outside the pace, weakened rapidly passing 400M, finished tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Jumped OK, not pushed, settling on rail towards rear. Stayed on rail turning for home, switched out 300m to issue challenge, hit the front 100m and pulled clear.
Out quickly, battled for early lead before settling in box seat 2L from leader. Bumped turning for home, urged forward top of straight, hit front 350m, run down 100m, boxed on.
Broke well, hard ridden to lead but kept away from rail by inside runner. Dropped back 1000m to take sit on leader, boxed on gamely in straight to hold down minor placing.
Shifted across behind runners soon after start and taken to rail, settling last. Taken out turning for home, switched to centre track in straight, and finished off gamely.
Pressed forward from an outside gate and forced to race wide without cover 2.5L from leader. Dropped back slightly turning for home but kept on gamely in the straight.
Shifted across behind runners shortly after start, settling at rear but away from fence. Swung wide entering straight, ran on gamely, doing best work final stages.
Out quickly but restrained and taken to fence 4L from leader. Came off fence in straight to make challenge but only one-paced.
Hard ridden from jump to hold fence, gradually edging forward to lead passing 1000m and slowing the pace. Overtaken passing 350m and faded gradually.
Away nicely, pressed forward but wide before settling ahead of midfield in one-out position. Kept on fairly early in straight before tiring passing 200m.
Jumped well, ridden early to go forward before settling behind midfield in one-out position. Dropped back steadily around turn before plodding home in the straight.
Bounced OK, not pushed, dropping to rear in one-out position. Taken wide entering straight, given reminders before eased down final stages when beaten.
Pushed forward from the wide draw to ensure he led at all costs. Ran strongly and pulled away mid straight. Despite fading late, held well on the line.
Only jumped fairly, but taken forward early to sit 5th on the fence. Steady for the majority of the straight, before switching on and running strongly to consolidate 2nd over the last 100m.

Taken up early to be handily placed, before being crowded at 900m and settling forward of midfield. Tended to drift out under the stick late, but still managed to sneak into 3rd under hands and heels late.
Taken forward early from the inside draw to settle 3rd, on the fence. Slightly 1 paced in the straight, and faded out in the last 100m.
Eased back early to settle second last. Came widest on the turn and stayed on strongly and was still gaining on the line.
Pushed forward to be prominent early, before being steadied when crossed at 900m and settling 4th. 1 paced in the straight, and never a threat.
Pushed forward to the front of the field early. Struck heels and unbalanced 850m when crossed. Plugged on to the line fairly, under minimal urging.
Cruised forward early to settle around midfield. Never a threat and plugged away to the line under minimal urging.
Fractious in the barrier, threw his head back and was very slow to begin. Was a distant last for the majority of the race. Picked up a couple easing late, but was never in the race.
Settled just forward of midfield, wide with no cover. Only responded meekly to urgings in the straight, and eased out last 100m.
Dropped back early from the wide draw to sit near last. Never kicked, and was eased late.
Eased back from the wide draw to sit towards the rear of the field. Didn't respond to riding in the straight, and quickly eased.

Settled in midfield gaining to 3L 5th coming onto home bend, quickened well inside the final 200 metres, did best work late. (Finished 2nd, placed 1st.)

Driven from the widest gate to take up running on the rail after the first 300M, narrowly headed entering straight, endured a tight run inside the first-past-the-post in final 100M. (Finished 3rd, placed 2nd.)

Began well from the one draw, settled just off the pace on the rail, switched out for a run and hit the front turning into the straight, maintained narrow advantage throughout closing stages while laying in. (Finished 1st, placed 3rd.)
Began from a wide gate, settled wide in prominent 4th never far off, fought on steadily without threatening in the straight.
Settled in rear of midfield on the rail, switched out to challenge entering the straight, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Settled in midfield, came under strong pressure upon straightening, ran on without threatening.
Close up on the rail, kept on same pace without quickening in the straight.
Taken back from a wide gate settling wide behind midfield, came under pressure rounding home bend and remained wide entering the straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Ridden along in 6th in forward of midfield on the rail, saved ground turning for home, kept on same pace without quickening.
Slowly away, settled towards the rear on the rail, tightened over 500 metres out, made steady headway in the straight.
Tightened at start settling one from last, in similar position to the straight, made no show.
Lacked pace and soon dropped to tail-end, never seen with a chance.
Took rail in midfield, not suited by the slow tempo, made a quick move 500M around the field in 3 wide, drifted away 300M to score.
Hard ridden forward, sat 1 out 1 back, just held ground in straight.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 2-3 wide, dashed well 250M, just missed 2nd.
Pushed early but failed to cross in front, soon eased back and took rail, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow tempo.
Midfield along the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, little dash 200M.
Hard ridden forward, sat outside the leader, out of fuel 250M.
Eased to rear, took rail, not suited by the slow tempo, ran on fairly in straight.
Eased back, 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, lack turn of foot.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, emptied 250M.
Hard ridden early but not muster, 2 wide at back, not suited by the slow tempo, no dash.
At rear, 2-3 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, no progress.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at slow sectionals, however soon dropped off 300M.
Moderate start, pushed along to settle behind leaders from a wide barrier, taken out to challenge at home turn, tried hard entire straight
Jumped smartly, pushed along to take lead, lay in under pressure in the straight, battled well.
Fast out, urged hard to settle outside the leader from a wide barrier, commenced to improve passing 400M, battled hard to the line.
Jumped OK, travelled midfield, tried hard in the straight, finished OK.
Raced behind midfield, tried to improve in the final stages, finished fairly.
Travelled midfield, asked for effort at home turn but only limited response, one-pace in straight.
Slow start, raced at rear, tried to improve at home turn, one-paced.
Settled behind midfield, under pressure to improve passing 550M, never threatened in straight.
Taken back at start and settled at tail, under pressure near 400M, failed to run on.
Jumped OK, drifted back and settled at rear, widest on straightening, failed to run on and to make any impression.
Taken back at start, settled at rear and travelled wide without cover, tried to improve at 700M and made some ground at home turn, weakened in the straight and failed to run on.

Placing: DISQ
Comment: Jumped well, pushed to sit in box seat, asked for effort in early straight and responded strongly to win.
Moderate break, driven to park 2nd 1 off, shuffled to 3rd & niggled 800m, under pump 400m, hard-ridden into stretch, boxing run to lead close home.
Impeded start, raced rail near rear, overraced 1000m, bustled forward 850m to mid rank, hard-ridden into stretch, switched out & rattled home final 150m, just failed.
Shifted into rival at break, handy on rail until popped 1 off 1 back 1000m, 3 deep & bustled to press lead 800m, hard-ridden 350m, battled to lead 130m, headed close home.
Fast start & soon led on rail, pressed 800m but rallied to hold narrow advantage, shaken up turning in, headed 130m, fought on but held.
Fast start widest & prominent, steadied 1600m, settled 1 back on rail, 4th & under pump 800m to hold position, driven into stretch, one-paced in run.
Awkward start, 3 wide near rear 1st turn, settled 1 off & niggled 850m, under pump & to rail 650m, hard-ridden turning in, boxed on for dour inroads.
Started ok, bustled along to midfield on rail, overraced 1500m & 950m, switched 1 off 880m & advanced a spot, under pump 550m, driven turning in, one-paced.
Taken behind at start to rail, raced last pair, niggled 820m, driven for progress on turn, stayed on for moderate gains.
Started ok & handy 1 off into 1st turn, settled midfield & pushed 3 deep 950m, niggled 850m, under pump 500m, hard ridden & all out turning in, plugged tamely.
Restrained near tail initially, 4 wide 1st turn & rolled to midfield without cover, niggled 700m, outpaced & driven on turn, found nil in run home.
Tardy break, driven to settle last pair 1 off, niggled at tail 800m, soon driven & detached last, plodded on past easing rival.
Broke ok, raced back of midfield 1 off with cover, niggled 800m, outpaced & soon under pump, near rear & crowded when eased down 400m.
Strong start, ridden to track leader on rail, clicked up 400m, responded strongly, raced to lead 250m, broke clear, dying on run late but held a comfortable margin.
Away on terms, eased to beyond midfield spot 1 off, head up at times, pulled deep & ridden 320m, unleashed powerful sprint to charge home.
Eased from gates, settled 2nd last 1 off, pushed along 380m, switched back to inside, sprinted well.
Fastest to begin, natural speed to lead comfortably, 2L lead & keen 800m, held together until 300m, headed 250m, stayed on.
Away OK, slow to muster, settled beyond midfield 3 deep, back to 2nd last 650m, ridden 350m, made good late ground.
Even break, eased to settle just fore of midfield between runners, keen at times, ridden 370m, making ground when on heels near line.
Ridden from gates, settled 3rd 1 off, ridden 370m, one-paced, eased near line.
Fair break, pushed along to get into midfield spot on rail, niggled at times throughout, under a drive 440m, weakened.
Snagged from widest gate, settled last on rail, slightly keen, held together until 330m, nearest at finish.
Slightly slow start, settled near rear on rail, improved along rail until ridden 450m, effort short-lived.
Began well, showed speed to settle fore of midfield but stuck 3 deep, niggled 430m, driven soon after, dropped out meekly.
On back foot slightly at start, ridden into midfield spot but 3 deep with cover, shuffled back to beyond midfield, under pressure 360m, dropped out.
Raced towards the rear, 10L behind 2 wide, made good ground and kept on strongly to score by 2-1/2L.
Sent forward, raced prominently in a 2 wide position, 3-3/4L off the lead, kept on going nicely to the line.
Bumped start, settled in midfield, 6-1/2L behind 2 wide, maintained run and finished off well to the line.
Slow to jump, in behind midfield, 8-3/4L off along the rail, good dash before crowded at 250M, ran on well.
Rolled forward to race in box-seat, sat 5-1/4L off, kept on until 150M when couldn't find extra.
Sent forward to lead but raced unkindly, established a margin of 3-3/4L at 800M, flattened passing 150M.
Eased and settled towards the rear, 10-1/4L behind along the rail, saved ground and kept on going to the line.
Very awkward start, settled at the rear 12-1/4L behind, along the rail until 400M, made ground and ran on okay.
Settled in midfield, 8-1/2L behind 2 wide, showed little in the straight, not a factor.
Eased back, raced at the rear, 11-3/4L behind 2 wide, kept on but did not improve.
Rolled forward, settled in one-off one-back position, 5-1/4L behind, dropped off badly rounding turn. (Heart irregularity and lame left front leg)

Placing: PU
Comment: Began awkwardly and then ridden forward, pulled up near 1500M as jockey was concerned about the horse's action.
First out and soon dictating pace. Pulled 2L clear around home turn and kept finding in the straight when strongly challenged final 100m.
Jumped well, pulled out of pace battle and taken to fence 3L from leader. Kept tabs to straight, threw out strong challenge from 300m but failed narrowly.
Broke with field then ridden along one-out, one-back. Dropped back slightly around home turn but rolled forward again between horses in straight to grab minor placing.
Jumped awkwardly, bumped, took first turn 4-wide before settling 3-deep 2L from leader 800m. Dropped back slightly turning for home but boxed on gamely in straight to finish in the frame.
Bounced well, pressed forward, racing outside but 1L behind leader back straight. Swung a little wide into straight, boxed on fairly before turning one-paced final stages.
Got off OK, not pushed, racing just ahead of midfield in one-out position. Shaken up top of straight but only one-paced.
Slow into stride, dropping to last pair along rail. Made up some ground turning for home, took inside run in straight and ran on steadily though slightly inconvenienced final stages.
Hard ridden from widest gate, taking first turn 5-wide before shifting in and finding cover 3-wide behind midfield. Made some progress in straight but tightened close home and not fully tested.
Bounced well, not pressed, dropping behind midfield along fence. Made some progress around home turn, took inside run in straight but only one-paced.
Bounded in air at the start, was bumped and unbalanced then shifted in, dropping to rear but wide. Continued to race wide around home turn and spent force in straight.
Jumped fairly, shifted across behind runners from a wide gate dropping to rear in one-off position. Trailed field to straight without ever looking competitive.
Jumped OK, ridden forward, settling ahead of midfield but wide. Lost position steadily around home turn and dropped out in straight.
Away with them, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back in midfield, bumped and unbalanced near 600M, finished off strongly in straight and scored by a neck.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths back in midfield, improved from 450M, took the lead near 150M, but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, kept on well in straight to get 3rd.
Began well, sat 2 wide in 4th, similar position to turn, shifted in near 300M, finished off evenly to make frame without threatening.
Jumped well, raced in 2nd, shared lead on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line. (Lame right front leg.)
Average to begin, taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, still 6 lengths or so back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off evenly.
Slowly away, raced 6 to 7 lengths back on rail, bumped near 600M, similar position on turn, finished off one-paced.
Slowly away, showed no early speed, raced at tail, still well back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Away with them, positioned 3 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 9 lengths back at rear, same margin back on turn, emptied early in straight.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, led uncontested to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter, eased final 50M.
Slow to begin, raced at rear throughout, finished tailed off, never competitive.
