Settled behind midfield, baulked for a run after straightening, quickened well inside the final 300 metres to assert authority close to home.
Well there, tightened and dropped to two back on the rail coming onto home bend, came to challenge inside the final 300 metres but found winner too strong.
Moderate start, ridden forward to just better than midfield on the rail, switched out for a run upon straightening, ran on quite well without threatening inside the final 300 metres.

Driven forward to join the leaders on the rail, shifted one back rounding home bend, angled out to hit the front upon straightening, unable to sustain effort and overhauled inside the final 100 metres.
Jumped well niggling along from a poor draw, settled wide without cover in midfield to straight, made steady headway without threatening.
Taken back from a wide gate, remained in last few to straight, baulked for a run before finishing off race nicely inside the final 200 metres.
Taken back to wide in midfield from the widest gate, dropped towards the rear rounding home bend, widest runner turning for home, made modest progress without threatening.
Settled in last few, saved ground turning for home, kept on steadily past well-beaten horses.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, trailed the field to the straight, kept on past well-beaten horses.
Raced wide in prominent position early, shifted back for cover 2L off the pace rounding home bend, made no impression in the straight.
Moderate start, settled in midfield, made no impression in straight. (Lame next day and questioned for disappointing performance)
Driven along to lead over 1000 metres out, held clear advantage to the straight but soon found no extra after straightening.
Given reminders after beginning from a wide gate, ridden along and travelled prominently and wide without cover to the straight, weakened.
Led briefly, dropped away quickly after straightening.
Pushed forward, pace good, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Pushed forward, shared the lead at good pace, hung on until 200M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Shared lead easily at good pace, ran on well for 3rd.
Pushed forward, pace good, just held ground.
Very slow away, hard ridden to keep up in midfield, pace good, just held ground in final stages.
Eased back, pace good, made some ground 250M.
Hard ridden to keep up at back, pace good, ran on ok.
Behind midfield, pace good, ran on ok.
Very slow away, at back, made steady ground 200M.
At back, pace good, made some ground 200M.
Hard ridden forward, pace good, soon dropped off 500M.
Very slow away, at rear, pace good, no progress.
Never better than midfield.
Never a factor.
Started OK, settled in box seat, shifted in to obtain clear run in the early straight and finished strongly once clear.
Jumped well, took lead after start, lay out rounding home turn, asked for effort in the early straight, rider dropped whip 200M, fought on solidly.
Settled behind runners, passing 700M commenced forward move to issue strong challenge on straightening, fought hard entire straight.
Jumped smartly, settled outside the leader, commenced to improve passing 600M to challenge on straightening, quickly under pressure and weakened in the straight.
Began slowly, settled at tail, refused to race near 1600M, series barrier trials.
Sharp start, raced 1 off 1 back until forced out 1000m & checked back to 3 wide midfield, shifted out home turn & driven 430m, rattled mid track to lead 75m.
Moderate start & bustled to rail midfield, ridden 500m & shifted off fence final turn, switched out for daylight 300m & hard driven, ran on to 2nd close home.
Started ok, lacked toe & niggled along 3rd last, bustled & improved a spot 900m, under pump 600m, rattled home for late gains to 3rd.
Moderate break, bustled forward to 1 back 1 off & light up, overraced 1000m to 800m, shuffled back to 5th, niggled 650m, driven turning in but one-paced, kept on dourly.
Sharp start & soon led, crossed to rail 1050m, 1L clear turning in & shaken up 400m, hard driven & edged out under pressure, empty & swamped 75m, faded.
Started ok, soon niggled mid rank 1 off with cover, ridden home turn, kept on for even progress.
Broke ok, lacked speed initially & sat midfield on rail, advanced to 3rd 1 back 800m, driven turning in & 2nd 220m, no extra & swamped final 100m.
Fast break, bustled wide & crossed to park 2nd 1 off 1050m, driven into stretch, one-paced in run home.
Broke well, trapped wide & snatched off heels 960m, raced last trio 3 wide with cover, driven widest into stretch, plugged one pace.
Tardy break, recovered quickly to park midfield 3 wide, checked off heels 1000m & shuffled back of midfield, swung wide into stretch & driven 400m, outpaced in tame run home.
Sluggish start, to tail & continued to race keenly, ridden turning in, plodded on tamely.
Slow start. Checked 1190m, raced rail near tail, niggled 600m, driven 500m, found nil in tepid run home.
Moderate start, 3 wide no cover & rolled to 4th 800m, soon niggled, under pressure home turn, emptied 350m & faded.
On back foot at start, ridden through to settle 3rd on rail, niggled 500m, sprinted strongly to hit lead 280m, raced clear.
Away well, back to midfield 3 deep no cover, ridden 480m, finished strongly but couldn't pick up winner.
Jumped well, pushed up into 2nd 1 off, joint lead 450m, ridden entering straight, headed 280m, no match but stuck on well.
Stumbled slightly start, restrained to near tail, pulling & improved 800m, ridden 480m, widest into straight, closed off late.
Began smartly, quickly outsped, settled midfield on rail, shuffled back from 650m, ridden 450m, closed resolutely but no threat.
Away on terms, eased to settle midfield between runners, slightly keen, ridden 500m, one-paced in straight.
Back to last, bustled at times throughout, ridden along 450m, switched to inside, made some ground but never figured.
Only fair to jump, niggled but outpaced, settled near rear on rail, clicked up 460m, finished OK.
Hopped at start, eased to settle well back 3 deep, lost ground 650m, pushed along 500m, never in mix.
Sharp jump, forward early, back to fore of midfield spot on inside, driven 600m, couldn't come on.
First to break, natural speed from outside gate to cross to 1.5L lead 800m on rail, joined 450m & ridden, succumbed 300m, weakened.
Slightly slow jump, pushed through to settle fore of midfield 1 off, under drive 620m, faded.
Pushed to take the rail and led by 3/4L, made the home turn awkwardly, kept on nicely to score by 1/2L.
Rolled forward, settled to race in box-seat, sat 1-1/2L off, inconvenienced passing 400M, ran on gamely to take 2nd.
Sent forward and settled to race outside the lead, sat 3/4L off, ran on nicely to the finish.
Awkward start before settling to race in midfield, 5L behind 2 wide, fought on well to the line.
Sent forward and settled in one-off one-back position, sat 2L off the lead, kept on going to the line.
Raced in worse than midfield, 6-1/2L behind 2 wide, travelled unkindly near 700M, improved steadily and kept on strongly inside final 100M.
Pushed but found no speed, took cover passing 1200M to race in front of midfield, 3-1/4L off 2 wide, fought on until passing 200M when flattened. (Rider questioned)
Settled in worse than midfield, 6-3/4L behind along the rail, made steady ground, ran on okay to the line.
Jumped awkwardly, settled in midfield 5-1/4L behind along the rail, held up passing 150M then crowded close to the line, nonetheless mostly one paced in the straight.
Raced in front of midfield, 3L off along the rail, shifted out to improve at 300M, remained one paced, couldn't match the others.
Steadied and taken back, raced 10-3/4L behind along the rail, made steady headway in the straight.
Slow to jump, raced at the rear, 9-1/4L behind 2 wide, shifted wide at 600M when running onto heels, kept on but did not threaten.
Steadied after start, raced towards the tail, 7-3/4L behind 2 wide, checked and lost ground at 700M, one paced in the straight and made no show.
Crowded start, then raced towards the rear 8-3/4L behind along the rail, left no impression.
Snagged back soon after start, dropping to last. Tailed field to straight, taken to centre track and ran past the field to win easily.
Pressed forward to hold box seat 4L from leader 1000m before racing fiercely passing 900m and dropping back slightly. Got clear run 400m, hit front 300m, overtaken 200m, boxed on.
Began fairly, picked up pace to behind midfield in one-out position. Got close to heels 800m, swung wide entering straight, ran on well to snatch minor placing.
Jumped on terms, not pushed holding rail in midfield. Closed passing 850m, blocked for run top of straight, switched in 200m to get clear, tightened 150m, boxed on.
Allowed to stride at own pace in midfield before shifting out 1000m and left without cover. Closed in on leader turning for home but only one-paced in straight.
Snagged back soon after start and taken to rail towards the rear. Swung wide entering straight, given reminders but little response.
Hard ridden, settling 2L behind leader at 1100m. Edged forward when pace slowed to race outside leader turning for home. Boxed on gamely to 200m before tiring.
Out quickly, pulling 2L clear passing 1100m, then put under a hold and slowed pace. Collared passing 350m and emptied soon after.
Never far off from the pace, 4th making the turn under a good hold, quickened up strongly passing 400M, lead near 150M and pulled clear for a dominant win with blinkers fitted first time.
Fractious in stalls, began very awkwardly and lost about 5L at the start, got back to the rear of the field 1300M, 7Ls off the pace 400M, closed off well to go 2nd near line but not reaching winner.

Held up in midfield, 6Ls off the pace halfway, headway along inside passing 500M, kept on steadily down the straight, couldn't get closer to winner. Briefly went 2nd inside 50M until overhauled in the shadows.
Settled down in about 8th place 6-7Ls off the pace, made ground nicely down the center over final 300M albeit never getting to the winner, missed 3rd spot just.

Began awkwardly, proved very difficult to settle and unable to be restrained by jockey, caught wide no cover before taking the lead reluctantly passing 900M, caught by winner nearing 150M, faded to 5th final stages.
Led slowly from the start and attempted to dictate the race, taken on by rival passing 900M, sat 2nd entering home turn, kept grinding to the line but lacked the winning dash, well held by rivals.
Taken back from wide barrier, waited with near the rear, shifted out nearing 400M for clear run, stayed on without threatening.
Slotted into a 2-wide spot in mid-division before the turn, 5Ls to make up 400M but closed off only fairly, didn't bother the leaders.
Settled ahead of mid-division 3-4Ls behind leader, had every chance passing 400M but was only holding ground, no extra final stages.
Began awkwardly, restrained to race near the rear, swung widest for home and 7Ls off leader 400M, made limited progress in the run home.
Held up 2-wide behind mid-division, pushed along 600M out, couldn't finish off, well beaten from 150M.
Raced on pace outside leader early stages, sat 3rd making the turn but failed to hold its position from 500M, soon weakened in straight.
Began fairly, picked up quickly, racing one-out behind midfield. Turned in behind horses, got clear run halfway up the straight, powered home final 200m to win pulling clear.
Pressed forward from outside gate, racing 3-wide before settling one-out 1.5L from leader 900m. Hard ridden in straight to catch leader, hit front momentarily but caught final strides.
Bumped start, pressed forward inside leader before easing into box seat 850m. Brushed rail 700m, kept on well in straight though raced in restricted room 100m.
Raced along fence in midfield before edging forward under hard riding in straight, doing best work final 100m.
Quickly in front but unable to cross to fence until passing 700m. Kept on strongly in straight before swamped close to line.
Ridden to stay with pace, racing wide without cover 3L from leader. Dropped back slightly around turn but boxed on gamely in straight.
Pressed forward, racing one-out 2L from leader on settling. Left flat-footed top of straight when pace quickened, finishing one-paced.
Outpaced, dropping towards rear along fence. Well back entering straight before making up some ground final stages.
Snagged back soon after start and shifted across behind runners to rail at the rear. Shifted out turning for home, one-paced in straight.
Shifted across behind runners soon after start, dropping to last. Tailed field to straight and never in the hunt.
Began awkwardly, then bustled along to race behind midfield but wide. Under pressure turning for home and dropped out in straight.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back, improved from 550M, finished off very strongly in straight to score by a neck.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in 5th, carried wider near 800M, no cover thereafter, kept on well after turning in, took the lead final 200M but couldn't hold off the winner late. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began awkwardly, raced at rear, travelled along the fence to turn, taken wide in straight and made good progress to get 3rd. (See Racing Incidents.)

Began well from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths or so back in 4th, angled out near 850M and slightly improved on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 200M, stayed on evenly thereafter, just missed 3rd on line.
Began fairly from a wide draw, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Jumped well from the widest gate, took the lead easily, travelled well throughout, kept on well early in straight, headed near 200M, stayed on evenly.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced prominently, steadied near 1000M, sat right behind the leader on turn, no daylight until after final 200M, finished off evenly thereafter.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced prominently, 2nd on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, raced at tail to turn, widest in straight, made minor progress.
Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide in midfield, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Slowly away, raced 2 wide at rear, difficult to settle near 900M, same position to turn, made no progress in straight.
Away with them, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Raced at rear, difficult to settle near 1100M, 7 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Slowly away and checked, recovered to race 5 lengths back on rail, travelled along the rail on turn, emptied early in straight and eased.

Settled just worse than midfield, quickened well upon straightening, took command over 100 metres out.
Settled in rear of midfield, made rapid progress up the Rock to be one-out-one-back in 3rd onto home bend, sustained progress under pressure to claim 2nd close to finish.
Caught wide in forward of midfield, allowed to take up running passing the winning post the first time, led until challenged around home bend, swamped under pressure inside the final 200 metres.
Settled well behind, commenced move at the 700 metres, switched for rails run entering home straight, ran on steadily under pressure.
Settled just off the pace on the rail, came under strong pressure early in straight, one-paced.
Midfield most of way, with short-lived impression early in home straight.
Raced wide throughout, pressed forward to midfield from a wide gate, improved to 3L 5th passing the winning post the first time, one-paced in the run home. (Tactic questioned)

Led or disputed lead early, ceded advantage passing the winning post the first time, ridden to re-gain lead coming onto final turn, unable to sustain effort and overhauled inside the final 200 metres.
Never seen with a chance.
Driven to slender lead early, taken 2L back passing the winning post the first time, came under pressure approaching the home bend, dropped out after straightening.
Never seen with a chance.
Prominent early, drifted back to midfield on stables bend, dropped out under pressure from the Rock.
Pushed forward to take rail and lead at good pace, made all.
Settled in box seat, pace good, closed off well for 2nd.
Eased back, took rail, on heels early, pace good, progressed steadily 250M for 3rd.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, pace good, ran on until 100M flattened.
Hard ridden to hold the rail just behind midfield, pace good, progressed steadily 200M.
Slow away, took rail at rear, on heels early, pace good, made steady ground 200M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, pace good, just held ground in straight.
Behind midfield, 2 wide, pace good, bumped 300M, ran on ok in straight.
Hard ridden forward, sat outside the leader, pace good, out of fuel 200M.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, pace good, blocked whole straight, never tested.
Eased at start, took rail, checked early, pace good, ran on fairly in straight.
At rear, shortly after the start became very unbalanced in its action and attempted to buck for some distance, pace good, never improved.
Taken back at start, settled at rear, urged for speed in early straight, quickened passing final 100M, came home strongly.
Moderate start, settled at handy position, drifted back to midfield passing 1000M, issued challenge passing 550M and widest on straightening, fought hard entire straight.
Soon after start became unbalanced, settled behind midfield, commence to improve passing 500M, shifted out for clear running in early straight, worked home solidly.
Pushed to settle outside the leader after start, drifted back to front of midfield after 800M, taken out to improve at home turn, finished satisfactorily.
Pushed after start and shifted in to settle in midfield, commenced to improve passing 450M, fought hard in the straight and finished fairly.
Taken back at start and settled at tail, tried to improve passing 500M, made some ground after 150, finished fairly.
Steadied to obtain cover after start, soon was crowed for room and became unbalanced, settle behind midfield, in early straight was held up for clear running until passing 250M, one-paced.
Settled at handy position, was hampered when held up for clear running in early straight, not fully tested.
Started OK, hard ridden along to take lead passing 1100M, shifted in on rail passing 800M, commenced to tire passing 200M.
Jumped nicely, pushed to take lead and passing 1100M drifted back to box seat, asked effort passing 400M, in the early straight was bumped and became unbalanced, failed to run on.
Jumped well, travelled wide and without cover until 800M being ridden along to settle outside the leader, in the early straight was bumped and became unbalanced, finished disappointing.
Speed to lead, headed 1020m & settled close 2nd 1 off, nudged along 500m to press lead, driven ahead turning in, kicked clear centre track.
Taken back to rail near rear, progress on turn & driven 300m, ran on to nick 2nd late.
Restrained at start to rail at tail, niggled 400m, driven 300m & shifted out, kept on well to take 3rd late.
Broke well, soon taken back to sit midfield on rail, shaken up 300m, ran on for solid headway.
Broke with others, urged on 3 wide no cover, trapped out until slotted 1 off 1 back 800m, ridden in 3rd 400m, swung wide on turn, boxed on evenly.
Fast break, bustled to lead on rail 1020m, pressed & niggled final turn & headed into stretch, outkicked & plugged on evenly until emptied & swamped 50m.
Started with others, midfield 3 deep when overraced 1100m & shuffled to back of mid rank 1 off with cover, on & off bridle, hard-ridden 420m, wide in stretch, stayed on for late gains.
Broke with others, raced midfield 1 off with cover, snatched off heels 780m, bustled 500m, driven centre track, plugged on evenly.
Pushed to midfield initially but wide no cover & overraced 1100m, restrained to near rear 3 wide with cover, niggled along, under pump 500m, driven widest in run, struggled.
Taken back at break to last pair 1 off, niggled 650m, driven turning in, one-paced in tame effort.
Broke ok & raced 3 wide with cover midfield until exposed 800m, niggled 550m, driven wide home turn, found nil & tapered.
Broke well, bustled to sit 1 back on rail, niggled 550m, under pump in 4th 450m, weakened out in run home.
Away fairly, niggled early, assumed front 1080m & down to rail, joined & headed narrowly 750m, held together until 350m, reclaimed lead soon after, clearly headed 170m, fought back & got bob.
Among fastest to begin, pushed early but couldn't cross to lead, eased to settle fore of midfield 3 deep & overracing, ridden 600m, came into race strongly at 250m, narrow lead 170m, just outbobbed.
Broke well, eased to settle midfield but stuck 4 deep no cover, pushed along 520m, driven hard on straightening, kept coming, charged into 3rd on line.
Jumped quickly, ridden through to be up near the speed, eased to settle in box seat on inside, clicked up 370m, stuck to inside, almost on terms 200m, boxed on.
Fast to begin, among leaders early, restrained to sit 2nd outside leader until 800m when back to 3rd, clicked up 350m, crowded 200m, stuck on OK.
Even break, niggled early to settle midfield on rail, off the bit and niggled throughout, laying out towards heels and awkwardly placed 400m, one-paced early in straight, picked up late.
On back foot at start, quickly into midfield spot 1 off, pushed through to settle fore of midfield, slightly keen, niggled 620m, driven 350m, pulled centre track, couldn't come on.
Fair break, eased to settle last, outpaced from 1000m, niggled 850m to tack on, ridden 440m, never in contention but made good late ground.
Awkward start, down to rail and ridden to pick up ground, settled beyond midfield on inside, ridden 600m, switched off heels 400m, never in contention.
Slightly slow break, trapped very wide on course, pushed on 4 deep towards the speed, took narrow lead 750m 1 off, ridden 360m, joined shortly afterwards, weakened quickly.
Away well, steadied towards the rear early, stuck 3 deep until 800m, settled 2nd last 1 off, outpaced and ridden 500m, back to inside on straightening, made no impression.
Just fair to begin, hampered soon after start, settled beyond midfield 1 off, keen at times, niggled 600m, lost position 450m, never a threat.
Settled to race in front of midfield, sat 3L off 2 wide, kept on and closed off nicely to score by a neck.
Travelled in midfield, 4-1/2L behind 2 wide, shifted wide on straightening, kept on but couldn't match winner's effort inside final 100M.
Pushed and settled to race outside the lead, sat 1L off, kept on going but couldn't hold off the first two.
Jumped slowly, raced at the rear, 7-3/4L behind 2 wide, made good ground and finished off well.
Settled to race in midfield, 5L behind along the rail, improved steadily and ran on well to the line.
Rolled into position just front of midfield, 3-1/2L behind along the rail, remained one paced to the line.
Slow to jump, settled to race in worse than midfield, 6-1/2L behind along the rail, made minor ground.
Taken back and raced at the rear, 8-1/4L behind along the rail, showed good dash approaching 150M to save ground.
Pushed and crossed runners to take rail and led by 1L, kept on until 250M and faded gradually.
Eased and settled to race in worse than midfield, 6-1/4L behind 2 wide, did not improve.
Sent forward and stayed prominent, sat 2-1/2L off but trapped wide and without cover, not competitive in straight.
Settled to race in box-seat, sat 1-1/2L off, under pressure when rounding turn, found nothing and was disappointing.
Hard ridden to lead before first turn, then set good pace to straight. Kicked 1.5L clear passing 350m and went to the post unchallenged.
Ridden to hold forward position, settling one-out 1L from leader. Took closer order turning for home but had no answer when leader kicked 350m. Boxed on gamely.
Restrained soon after start and shifted in for cover, dropping one-out towards the rear. Kept on a strong hold to straight, ran on steadily to snatch minor placing.
Shifted across behind horses from widest gate, dropping to last. Tailed field to straight, taken wide and finished off steadily.
Pressed forward to stay with the pace, racing wide without cover 3L from leader. Covered extra ground home turn and finished off one-paced.
Not pushed early, settling along rail behind midfield. Got shuffled back turning for home, stayed on rail in straight and ran on fairly, doing best work final stages.
Jumped nicely, not pushed, settling along rail 3L from leader. Switched out top of straight to issue challenge but only one-paced.
Shifted across behind runners soon after start, settling at rear. Held up behind horses entering straight, then checked approaching 200m. Boxed on.
Away nicely, sharing early pace before easing into box seat 1.5L from leader. Looked a chance turning for home but found little when asked and swamped close home.
Ridden early to stay with pace, settling one-out 2.5L from leader. Kept tabs to straight when under pressure and gave ground gradually.
Hampered soon after start, then ridden to hold one-out position behind midfield. Found little in straight but awkwardly placed close to heels final stages.
Raced behind midfield but wide, then covered extra ground home turn, before dropping out in straight. Lame right hind leg.

Slightly slow out, positioned 4 lengths or so back on rail, got its head up when awkwardly placed on heels near 700M, slightly improved on turn, no daylight early in straight, finished off well when clear final 150M to score narrowly.
Jumped well, positioned 3 lengths or so back on rail, there to turn, angled out in straight and finished off well, just missed.
Moderately away from a tricky draw, unable to slot in early, sent forward near 700M to race outside the leader, kept on well in straight, but couldn't hold off the first two late.
Crowded out start, raced 5 lengths or so back at rear, difficult to settle near 650M, 2 wide on turn, no clear running until final 100M, made good progress late to make frame.
Crowded out start, raced 7 lengths or so back at rear, last turning in, made good progress early in straight, in traffic final 100M, not able to test properly.
Taken back from gate 8, raced at tail, slightly improved along the rail on turn, unable to obtain clear running in straight, not able to test properly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 6 lengths back at rear, carried wider near 650M, same margin back on turn, took widest in straight and made reasonable progress.
Bumped shortly after the start, raced 2 wide in 5th, same position on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off one-paced.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, shared lead on turn, peaked near 150M, weakened thereafter.
Away with them, positioned 1 out 1 back, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from the widest gate, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths back in midfield, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Average to begin, sent forward to race prominently, unbalanced near 700M, saved ground on turn, showed no response in straight and eased. (See Racing Incidents.)

Jumped well from the one draw, led or disputed lead early stages, ceded advantage rounding home bend, renewed effort and hit the front over 300 metres out, hung on well.
Jumped fairly, close up early stages, took up running passing the 800 metres, held 1L advantage entering straight but soon collared over 200 metres out.
Niggled along in midfield, saved ground on inside rounding home bend, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Given reminders after beginning from the widest gate, travelled wide in midfield to straight, ran on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Slowly away, trailed the field to straight, saved ground making home turn, finished off race well.

Ridden in prominent position early before shifted over 2L back in 6th, slightly worse turning for home and baulked for a run early in straight, produced good late impression inside the final 200 metres.
Broke well, amongst leaders early before shifting to one-out-one-back position in 3rd, similar turning for home, one-paced under pressure. (Mucus in trachea)

Ridden along towards the rear, improving under pressure to midfield when steadied approaching home bend, suffered further interferences rounding home bend, fought on steadily under pressure, nearest at finish.
Moderate beginning, recovered steadily from midfield along the rail to be 2L back in 4th at home bend, unable to sustain effort in the run home. (Tactic questioned)
Wide throughout, midfield early, taken back towards the rear rounding home bend, widest runner entering straight, kept on steadily without quickening.
Very wide in midfield early, taken back to rear for cover coming out of back straight, hugged the rail making home bend, switched out for a run on straightening, fought on steadily.
Raced wide mainly in midfield, further behind entering home straight, made no impression. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Awkward when taken back early, badly checked when driven forward on the rail 1000 metres out, hampered again 550 metres out, saved ground turning in but soon dropped out under pressure.
Vied for lead out wide early, taken back to just better than midfield rounding home bend, folded up quickly after straightening.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, dashed well 300M to score.
Pushed to take rail and led at good pace, hung on well until 100M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, pace good, lack room 4-2, progressed steadily when clear.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, trapped 3 wide, pace good, just held ground in straight.
Eased back, 2 wide, pace good, progressed steadily 300M.
Eased to rear, 2 wide, pace good, blocked 400M, dashed well when clear.
Took rail behind midfield, bumped 900M, pace good, lack room 4-2, made steady ground when clear.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, pace good, flattened 250M.
At back along the fence, pace good, ran on fairly.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide outside leader, pace good, out of fuel 200M.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, pace good, ran on fairly.
Hard ridden to take box seat, pace good, soon emptied 300M.
Trapped 3 wide, never better than midfield.
Urged along and took lead passing first turn, travelled strongly in the straight to win.
Started smartly, settled towards midfield, rider dropped right rein in the early straight, issued strong challenge final 100M, finished solidly.
Jumped well, pushed along to settle in box seat, commenced to improve passing 500M, fought hard entire straight.
Ridden hard at start, settled in midfield, asked for effort at home turn, battled well in the straight.
Taken back at start from wide barrier, settled at tail, hard ridden passing 500M, made some ground passing 200M, finished OK.
Moderate start, settled behind midfield, tried to improve passing 600M, widest on straightening, worked home OK.
Taken back at start, settled midfield on rail, drifted back behind midfield near 800M, asked for effort approaching 500M, finished fairly.
Taken back at start, settled at rear, tried hard entire straight, finished fairly.
Urged along after start, travelled wide at first turn, kept moving to settle outside the leader near 1100M, under pressure at home turn, weakened in the straight. Blood trachea.
At the start bounded in the air and began awkwardly, settled at rear on rail, under pressure and one-paced in the straight.
Taken back at start, settled at rear, one-paced in the straight.

Hard ridden after start, steadied for cover passing first wining post, travelled very wide without cover at rear, made move to handy position passing 1000M, under pressure at home turn, failed to run on.
Jumped smartly, settled wide midfield, tried hard at home turn, failed to run on.
Settled towards midfield on rail, never in it.
Speed early to front rank, 4 deep 1st turn, rolled to lead 1550m, clear & to rail 1350m, clear & shaken up 400m, kicked on gamely, all out but just held on.
Broke ok & slotted 5th 1 off with cover, advanced to 4th 1250m, shuffled back on turn & pocketed, switched out 420 & driven, rattled home centre track, just failed.
Front rank on rail 1st turn, soon shuffled to midfield on fence, retreated to rear rank, niggled 700m, last trio turning in, driven & closed strongly.
Sluggish start & niggled initially to race near rear on rail, shifted 1 off 1100m & raced last trio, shifted wide for progress 650m, ran on centre track for solid inroads.
Front rank 3 wide 1st turn, led & to rail 1650m, soon headed & 1 back on fence, overraced 1250m & shuffled back, 7th & not clear run turning in, driven 300m, stayed on dourly.
Broke well, settled 3rd 1 off 1 back, lost cover 1350m & overraced to 2nd, shuffled to 3rd on fence 950m, driven for pressure 550m & vied for 2nd turning in, one-paced in run.
Restrained at break to 2nd last 1 off, shifted 3 wide last trio 1150m, progress from 1000m to 4th at 600m, driven turning in to share 2nd, peaked 250m & tapered.
Slow start, nudged on to midfield on rail, overraced in backstretch & shuffled back, checked off heels & to tail 980m, switched 3 deep 600m, driven 500m, plugged on moderately.
Tardy start, nudged along initially to park back of midfield 1 off with cover, overraced 1150m, shuffled to rear rank and driven turning in, struggled thereafter.
Slow start & soon detached at tail, advanced 3 wide from 1350m to sit 2nd 1 off at 950m, niggled 650m, hard ridden turning in, found nil & faded out.
Away on terms, ridden early to take a handy spot, settled just behind speed 1 off, slightly keen & eased 800m, switched out 500m, held together until 350m, hit lead 50m, comfortable at end.
Broke well, driven to push towards speed, got to lead on rail 900m, 1.5L lead 700m, hanging slightly on bend, ridden 420m, fought on gamely, grabbed 50m.
On back foot at start, ridden along to get into handy position on rail, up to 3rd by 800m, keen on turn, given his head at 400m, loomed up to challenge but never got by, stayed on well.
Slow to begin, mustered through to settle just beyond midfield on rail, stuck to inside on turn, ridden along 440m, stuck on solidly.
Slightly slow to muster, eventually got through to settle midfield of main bunch 1 off, down to rail 800m, ridden 500m, made steady headway without threatening.
Eased from gates to settle near rear, clicked up 500m near inside, green but motored home when wound up.
Fastest to begin, ridden to hold lead, passed 1050m, settled just fore of midfield, 3 deep at first before getting into 2-wide line, niggled 520m, pulled centre track in straight, couldn't quicken.
Hopped slightly at start, ridden through to settle midfield 1 off, ridden 520m, wayward early in straight, never a threat.
Restrained from outside gate but quickly outpaced, 3L from 2nd last runner 1000m and driven along, travelling better 750m, niggled 570m, made late ground but never a threat.
OK jump, eased to settle beyond midfield, 3 deep at first but then to 1 off spot, ridden 500m, pulled to centre of track, one-paced.
Hard driven from gates to push towards leaders, slight lead 1000m, passed 900m, settled 2nd 1 off, nudged along from 700m, under pressure soon after, eased down from 200m .
Eased from gates, settled beyond midfield on inside, ridden 350m, couldn't pick up.
Even break, natural speed to be up near pace, trapped 3 deep no cover throughout, ridden 550m, weakened, eased right down from 150m.
Speedy beginning, taken back to beyond midfield & trapped 3 deep throughout, ridden along 500m, no response, eased out of race from 320m.
Travelled in front of midfield, sat 3-1/2L behind along the rail, produced good kick at 200M and scored impressively.
Sent forward to take the rail and led by 3/4L, kept on only to be caught by an impressive winner near 100M.
Race in behind midfield, sat 6L behind 3 wide without cover, continued to improve and fought on to the line.
Settled to race just behind midfield, 6L behind 2 wide, made good ground in the straight to take 4th.
Pushed forward to race outside the lead, sat about 2L off, galloped on at 700M, hard ridden but no change of gear.
Travelled just in front of midfield, sat about 2-3/4L off 3 wide and left without cover near 800M, kept on to the line.
In midfield, sat 4-1/2L behind the lead 2 wide, improved until shifted away from heels 150M, one paced thereafter.
Raced in midfield, sat about 5L behind along the fence, showed slight dash passing 300M, and again near 200M.
Eased and raced detached in the early and middle stages, made minor ground despite being slightly held up at 150M.
Bumped star, one-off one-back until dropped a slot behind at 700M then struck heels, one paced in the straight.
Pushed forward and sat 3/4L off, wide and without cover until near 700M, weakened upon straightening.
Settled to race in midfield, 4-1/2L behind 3 wide with cover, found nothing in the straight.
Rolled forward, settled to race in box-seat, sat 2L off the pace, weakened badly near 250M, disappointing.
Eased from start, remained at the rear and finished tailed out, not competitive.
Jumped well but eased back settling along fence 3L from leader. Closed in turning for home, surged forward soon after straightening, hit front 250m, pulled clear.
Bumped start, outpaced, dropping one-out towards rear. Switched to centre track on straightening and finished strongly to grab second spot.
Slow into stride, dropping to last on settling. Stayed at rear until turning in when taken wide and ran on steadily.
Raced along fence in midfield, took inside run in straight and ran on well to finish in the frame.
Bumped start, pressed forward to midfield, then raced fiercely to turn. Hung in badly under pressure and proved difficult to ride out in straight. Racing manners unacceptable.
Away nicely, then taken to box seat. Closed in steadily around turn, hit the front 300m but soon overtaken and faded.
Began fairly, outpaced, dropped back between horses at the rear. Took inside run in straight and finished off fairly.
Jumped OK, then taken in for cover, dropping behind midfield but 3-wide. Continued to race 3-wide throughout and only one-paced in straight.
Hard ridden to stay with hot early pace before being eased one-back, one-out 1000m. Swung wide into straight, kept on well to 200m before fading.
Hard ridden along rail to lead on settling, then travelled keenly setting strong pace to 300m when ran out of fuel and faded.
One of the first into stride, pressed forward but wide, before settling 3-wide 2L from leader. Came under pressure turning for home and faded in straight.
Shifted across behind runners from outside draw, dropping back. Became detached from field approaching turn and never in the hunt.
Began fairly, outpaced, dropping towards rear along fence. No response when shaken up top of straight.
Pressed forward to stay one-out 1L from leader. Lost position home turn, dropped out in straight, finishing tailed out. Unacceptable performance. Had small amount of blood at left nostril.
Positively ridden to take the lead from 1350M, ensured a good pace up front, kept on well turning in under light weight and a 7 lb. claim, showed no signs of weakening leading all the way home.
Restrained to race in mid-division, 3Ls off the leader and eventual winner at 400M, tried hard to the line but couldn't run down leader.
Chased the pace 2-wide, well poised to strike turning in, lacked winning dash and couldn't get closer to leader, kept on evenly for 3rd.
Prominently ridden from the start, sat outside leader 1300M, kept up the chase until passing 150M, faded over final stages and lost 3rd near the line.
Began only fairly, quietly ridden in a position behind midfield, 5Ls off the pace at 600M, took time to get going despite ridden along 500M out, pinched some ground late.
Settled down behind midfield 5-6Ls off leader, stayed on only mildly final 400M, no impression on leaders.
Held up towards the rear, 7Ls off the pace making the turn for home, ran past beaten horses only, no threat.
Taken back from wide barrier, given a waiting ride at the rear, 7Ls to make up 400M, raced tight and was steadied inside 300M, didn't find much when clear.
Driven along from draw 1, settled just off the pace, came under pressure 500M out, dropped away tamely from 300M.

Taken back from wide barrier, near the rear first half then made 3-wide move passing 800M, run ended 250M and nothing left in tank. (Jockey : his mount may not have handled the AWT at its first time of asking.)
Unable to slot in from wide barrier, caught wide no cover throughout in midfield, gave ground passing 550M and well beaten top of straight, finished tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Allowed to stride own pace early, racing behind midfield. Improved position home turn, switched wide in straight and finished strongly to win close home. Had wound to right front pastern.
Jumped well then settled 4L from leader along fence. Edged closer turning for home, threw out challenge top of straight, hit front momentarily before being run down 50m out.
Outpaced, dropping towards rear along fence. Stayed on fence around turn, took inside run in straight and finished strongly.
Hard ridden to hold forward position, edging forward approaching 900m to race outside hind-quarters of leader. Hit front halfway up the straight but emptied close home.
Pressed forward from widest gate, racing wide till taking over lead 1100m and crossing to fence. Kept on strongly in straight to 220m when overtaken and then swamped final stages.
Shared early pace before being eased back, racing one-out in midfield to straight. Switched to centre track and ran on steadily.
Pressed forward from outside gate, racing outside early leader before settling one-back, one-out. Under pressure top of straight, boxed on well to 200m before tiring.
Raced 3-wide behind midfield, covered extra ground home turn, very wide in straight, but only one-paced.
Quickly into stride, leading field to 1100m before slipping into box seat. Under pressure home turn and gave ground steadily in straight.
Pressed forward from outside gate, racing wide before being steadied and shifted across behind runners, dropping to rear. Last into straight, one-paced.
Hard ridden to obtain forward position but slow to muster and then trapped wide in midfield without cover. Under pressure on straightening and faded gradually.
Began fairly, vigorously ridden but didn't respond and became detached from field. Remained at rear throughout and one-paced in straight.
No early pace, then difficult to settle when pressed 1300m dropping towards rear. Continued to race fiercely approaching home turn and never competitive. Racing manners unacceptable.
Outpaced, racing at rear but away from fence. Well back turning for home and dropped out in straight, finishing tailed out. Unacceptable performance.

Pushed out early to ensure he led. Set a decent chase at the top of the straight and was 3L clear at the 200m. Started to fade quickly in the straight, but just had enough in the tank to hold on by barest margin late.
Cruised forward early to be handily placed in 4th, 1 off the fence. Ran solidly early in the straight, before showing good turn off foot last 150m, almost catching winner on the line.
Cruised forward early to settle around midfield, 1 off the fence. Came wider in the straight, and progressed solidly. Ran well late and held of late challenge for 3rd.
Dropped back from the wide draw to sit worse than midfield. Awkward on heels 900m. Wider on the turn, ran home solidly late and was rapidly catching 3rd.
Broke well, Then eased out to settle forward of midfield, on the fence. Maintained momentum in the straight and finished well late under minimal urging.
Slightly tardy in the jump, but pressed hard early to sit 2nd, 3/4L off the leader. Plugged on 1 paced in the straight, and easily overtaken late.
Looked to press forward early before settling midfield, 3 wide with no cover. Well positioned at the top of the straight, but only ran on 1 paced and not pushed hard to the line late.
Only fairly away and dropped back to settle 3rd last, on the fence. Wider on the turn. Stayed on OK late, and picked up a few slower ones late.

Dropped back early to sit toward the rear of the field, never closer than 4 wide in the back straight. Got head up when keen at running onto heels 900m. Checked 700m. Plugged on fairly under minimal urging in the straight.
Steadied off heels early and cruised back to sit towards the rear of the field, 1 off the fence. Only responded fairly to pressure, and was gradually eased late.
Eased forward early to settle around midfield, on the fence. Made no impression in the straight, and not pushed hard to the line.
Drifted back early, before being badly checked at 1000m, losing ground and settling 2nd last. Wanted to drift under the stick in the straight. Didn't improve and not persevered with late.
Stared well and taken up to be handily placed in 3rd. Gave nothing in the straight, and eased a long way from home.
Slow away and then bumped on jumping, before dropping to the rear of the field. Never improved from there.

Soon dropped to the rear, ridden along on the rail, commenced move rounding home bend, switched out into the clear on straightening, ran on well down the centre of the track to take charge 70 metres out, won cozily.
Never far off, hit the front from the weakening leader at the 300 metres only to be overshadowed final stages.
Ridden along on the rail before settling just off the pace from the 800 metres, briefly baulked early in straight, kept on at the same pace without quickening.
Towards the rear early, improved on the rail to midfield coming onto home bend, baulked for a run until the 200 metres, fought on late.
Jumped well from a middle draw, settled not far off in joint 5th, kept on steadily without quickening under pressure in straight. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Settled in midfield off the rail, came under pressure to challenge from the 500 metres, kept on at the same pace without quickening.
Raced wide in midfield without cover on the far side, taken slightly backward for cover rounding home bend, dropped to last few when wide turning in, produced moderate late impression closing stages.
Made narrow running to the 300 metres, weakened under pressure.
Not far off on the rail in joint 5th, switched out to challenge on straightening but soon weakened.
Always in last few and never seen with a chance.
Settled at the back from the widest gate, trailed the field most of the way.
Driven up to dispute the lead from the 1000 metres, found no extra and folded up quickly after straightening.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, made all.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, dashed strongly 300M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pushed to hold the rail in front of midfield, not suited by the slow tempo, little dash 300M.
Hard ridden forward, sat just off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the slow pace, ran on until 100M flattened.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Eased back, 2 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, unleashed strong finishing efforts 200M.
Midfield, on the fence, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 200M.
Box seat, benefited by the slow sectionals, just held ground in straight.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Hard ridden early, at back, 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, little dash 200M.
At back along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 150M.
Hard ridden to sit in midfield, trapped 3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, emptied 300M.
At back, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, never improved.
Never a factor.
Settled towards midfield, commenced to improve after passing 600M, gained control of the 200M and held off all to win.
Jumped OK, settled midfield, asked for effort in the early straight, quickened final 150M and finished strongly.
At the start bumped and became unbalanced, after that was buffeted for some distance, raced behind midfield, after 800M commenced to improved and travelled wide and without cover, finished solidly.
Settled midfield, battled hard in the straight and made some ground final 100M, worked home well.
Jumped smartly, raced outside the leader, fought hard entire straight, finished OK.
Jumped out well, travelled wide and without cover, improved to midfield at home turn, widest on straightening, came home fairly. Lame right front next day.
Urged hard after start to take lead, asked for effort in the straight, one-paced.
Taken back at start and settled at tail, tried to improve at home turn, only one-paced.
Started OK, took the box seat, under pressure and weakened passing 200M.
Taken back at start and settled at rear on rail, under pressure and failed to improve in the straight.
Raced midfield, under pressure in the straight and then failed to run on.
Settled at rear, never in it, lame right front leg.
Settled at rear, failed to make impression, irregular heart and blood trachea, must trial.
Began only fairly, settled towards midfield on rail, faded-out in the straight.
Speed to settle 1 back on rail, shifted out & driven 360m, quickened to lead 220m & extended, pressed late, held on.
Started ok, soon bustled midfield on rail, minor progress 600m, shifted out & shaken up turning in, grinding progress to press lead, always held.
Tardy break & rousted, worked forward to midfield 1 off with cover 800m, outpaced & lost ground 600m, driven turning in but lacked toe, grinding run centre to nick 3rd.
Smart start, restrained wide at break but trapped handy 3 deep no cover, ridden 500m, stayed on evenly to challenge for minors, pipped for 3rd at wire.
Broke well, raced keenly to 2nd 1 off no cover, pressed leader on turn, 2nd & hard-ridden 320m, found little & plodded on one pace.
Speed wide to lead, to rail 850m, joined for lead on turn, shaken up 370m & held narrow advantage, all out when headed 220m, tapered.
Smart start, early speed to sit handy 3 deep no cover, snagged 860-m to slot 1 back 1off, soon under pressure & retreated, under pump 6th turning in, no headway.
Slow start, bustled 4 deep behind mid rank when snatched off heels 920m, back of mid 3 deep & niggled 700m, hard driven 500m, plodded tepidly.
Broke ok, rolled forward wide no cover, trapped handy 4 deep & niggled 800m, lost ground on turn & driven into stretch, weak run home.
Outpaced from wide gate & soon at tail, niggled along 700m, hard-ridden centre track, plugged on to pass weakening rivals.
Missed break & raced rail near rear, niggled 600m, found nil in weak stretch run.
Moderate break, lacked toe & near rear when checked 920m, 2nd last & niggled 750m, driven turning in, found nothing in tame run to finish.
Bumped at start, ridden to get into handy spot 4 deep, among leaders 500m, driven 350m, raced to narrow lead 170m, green but pulled away late.
Strong start, quickly up near lead 3 deep, ridden along 400m, narrow lead 200m, claimed soon after but fought on.
Awkwardly away, bumped soon after, settled beyond midfield 4 deep, niggled 750m, ridden 480m, bumped 250m, stayed on well.
Good jump, natural speed to settle near lead 1 off, held together until hit lead 450m, ridden soon after, joined 220m, stuck on OK.
Bustled from gates, settled just behind speed 3 deep, pushed along 420m, bumped 250m, tight for room late.
Bumped soon after start, outpaced early, settled near rear on outside rail, clicked up 550m, found line nicely late.
Away OK, settled well back, ridden from 750m, never truly travelling, found line very late centre track.
Away on terms, eased to midfield spot 6 deep, ridden 450m, one-paced to line.
Hopped in air at start, back to last on outside fence, hampered slightly 850m, ridden from 500m, pulled towards centre 200m, weakened late.
Very fast break, ridden to maintain forward spot, narrow lead 800m on outside rail, clicked up 520m, quickly beaten off.
Jumped cleanly, eased to settle well back & deep, ridden from 650m, last 500m, never a threat.
Began well, eased to sit just behind speed centre track, dropped out from 600m.
Ridden along from inside gate, up near speed but stranded 6 deep, ridden 450m, weakened.
Slightly awkward start, ridden to press towards lead but stuck 5 deep, driven 600m, no response.
Raced in midfield, 3-3/4L behind 2 wide making the first turn, finished off strongly inside 150M to score.
Taken back and raced in behind midfield, 4-3/4L behind 3 wide, closed off nicely to take 2nd.
Settled to race in front of midfield, sat 2-1/2L off 2 wide, ran on well to take 3rd.
Pushed and raced inside the lead along the rail, sat 3/4L off, ran on but couldn't' hold off the others inside final 50M.
Eased and raced towards the rear, 5-1/2L behind 2 wide, made good ground inside 250M and closed off strongly.
Rolled forward and raced in box-seat, sat 2-1/4L off, remained one paced in the straight.
Sent forward and led by 3/4L in a 2 wide position, weakened gradually passing 200M.
Pushed and settled in one-off one-back position, sat 1L off, flattened passing 250M.
Pushed and slotted into midfield, sat 3-1/4L behind along the rail, lost ground rounding turn, did not threaten.
Raced at the rear, 6-3/4L behind along the rail, not competitive.
Crowded start and remained at the rear throughout, 6-3/4L behind 3 wide with cover, never a factor.
Pushed and settled to race in midfield, 3-3/4L behind 2 wide, pushed from home turn, found nothing.
Began fairly, pushed forward, racing one-out in midfield. Swung wide into straight before finishing strong down centre track to win pulling clear final 150m.
Bumped, unbalanced start, then ridden positively but unable match pace and left wide 1500m before seeking cover at the rear. Taken to centre track on straightening and finished strongly.
Pushed forward on jumping to race outside hindquarters of leader. Edged forward turning for home, took over lead 400m, overtaken 150m, emptied close home.
Pressed forward from outside draw racing 3-wide before getting cover 2L from leader passing 1300m. Looked a chance top of straight but only one-paced final 200m.
Shifted across behind runners shortly after start settling along rail at the rear. Shifted out at entrance to straight, bumped, but boxed on gamely to be closest at finish.
Ridden along early but unable match pace and held 3-wide behind midfield. Taken wide entering straight and ran on fairly.
Strolled forward on jumping, then eased into box seat 2L from leader. Kept tabs to 200m before turning one-paced.
Slow into stride, outpaced, dropping towards rear along rail. Put under pressure turning for home but only one-paced in straight.
Jumped awkwardly then hard ridden along rail to lead on settling. Set quick tempo to 400m when overtaken and faded.
Pressed forward sharing early pace before settling 3-wide 1L from leader. Under pressure at the turn in and faded gradually.
Jumped OK, hard ridden to go forward but slow to muster, settling in midfield along rail 4L from leader. Shaken up turning for home but only one-paced in straight.
Pressed forward on jumping, sharing early pace before settling one-out 2L from leader. Kept tabs to straight when ran out of stamina and faded.
Outpaced, then raced tight 1300m, dropping towards rear. Swung wide entering straight but found little when asked. Lame left front leg.
Shifted across behind runners from widest gate and last on settling. Made forward move top of straight but blocked for run 200m. Plodded home.

Heavily restrained behind the pace, raced keenly middle stages, improved to outside leader 250M, knuckled down with determination, gained upper hand 100M, held sway to the line fending off a late challenge.
Given a waiting ride 5Ls off the pace, closed off strongly down outside, held by diminishing neck.
Restrained in a 2-wide spot in mid-division, held up 300M-150M behind leaders, let down well when clear and went 3rd before line. Unlucky.
Settled down in midfield along the 3-path, found the line well on his AWT debut, nearest finish.
Strode forward to race just outside leader, gained narrow lead inside 350M, soon pressed by eventual winner, fought on to 100M, no extra and weakened to 5th late.
Never far off the pace but caught wide no cover from draw 12, within striking distance passing 350M but failed to make ground on leaders, well held over final 150M.
Quickly crossed to the rail, always prominent, difficult to settle when crossed by rival 700M, couldn't find another gear turning in, no clear run final 100M but already out of contention.
Positively ridden from the beginning, crossed to the lead 700M, outsprinted by rivals passing 300M, weakened noticeably final stages.
Recovered from a slow start to race behind mid-division, failed to make progress on his AWT debut over inadequate trip.
Dropped back to near the rear, ran on steadily when driven 400M, had no clear run final 100M and could have been closer.
Sluggish away, well off the pace early stages, last of 12 turning in but couldn't kick away, never likely.
Crossed to a 3-wide spot behind midfield, swung widest into straight but couldn't pick up pace on his AWT debut.
Began awkwardly, then crowded and before settling on rail 5L from leader. Turned in behind wall of horses, got split 350m before forcing way between horses to win close home.
Away well, racing one-out 3L from leader. Closed in around home turn, looked winner when hit front 250m, bumped and unbalanced 100m, overtaken final strides.
Taken in for cover soon after start, dropping one-out towards rear. Taken wide in straight and pressed forward but hung in badly and not fully tested. Racing manners unacceptable.
Began well, ridden along to hold rail 3L from leader. Dropped back slightly back stretch, edged forward around home turn, took inside run in straight and finished off strongly.
Raced behind midfield early stages before edging closer along rail back stretch. Shifted out at turn in to challenge but blocked several times when improving and not fully tested.
Jumped well, sharing early pace before settling in box seat. Threw out challenge at turn in but joined by several rivals 200m and raced in restricted room final stages. Not fully tested.
Hard ridden from an outside draw to lead, crossing to fence 1700m. Started to race keenly when challenged up front 1400m, setting hot pace to 200m when emptied.
Raced one-out ahead of midfield mostly to straight when put under pressure, making some progress to 200m before turning one-paced.
Bumped heavily shortly after start and then checked, dropping one-out behind midfield. Fund little when put under pressure in straight, finishing one-paced.
Slow to move, outpaced, dropping to last pair but away from fence. Remained at rear to straight where one-paced.
Outpaced, dropping to rear along fence. Last turning for home and little response when put under pressure in straight. Lost right hind plate near 450m.
Bumped, unbalanced shortly after start, pressed forward 3-wide to race outside leader 1450m before easing back slightly. Under pressure at turn in and dropped out. Unacceptable performance.

Cruised forward early to settle midfield, 3 wide with limited cover. Started his run before the turn, and ran strongly in the straight. Nosed in front at the 200m, and had enough in the tank to hold on late.

Cruised forward early and settle just behind midfield. Off heels at 1100m. Ran solidly early in the straight, before taking the bit between his teeth and finishing last 200m strongly. Was gaining on the winner at the finish.
Eased back early to sit around midfield, on the fence. Ridden for luck at the top of the straight, and got a clear passage in the straight. Ran solidly late and only peaked near the line.
Pushed forward early and settled 2nd/3rd, 1 off the fence. Battled on solidly in the straight, and just lost a place in the last 50m.

Crowded on jumping, but recovered quickly to push forward and settle forward of midfield. Held up for a run at the top of the straight, and came off heels 300m. Ran solidly in the straight, and unlucky to run onto heels at 100m.
Dropped back early from the wide draw to settle 2nd last. At the back of the pack turning for home, but ran solidly in the straight and gaining momentum late.
Pressed forward early to eventually take the lead. Peaked on his run at the 200m, and not pushed hard to the line from that point. Jockey questioned.
Dropped back from the wide draw to sit last. Stayed on solidly in the straight, without threatening.
Pushed forward from the inside draw to be early leader, before being crossed at 1000m, and settling 3rd/4th. Hampered when missing a run at 200m, and went to the line 1 paced late.
Pressed forward from the wide draw to sit 2nd/3rd, but stuck 3 wide with no cover. Nothing left in the straight, and dropped back quickly from the 250m.
Bumped and unbalanced on jumping before settling midfield, 1 off the fence. Never responded in the straight, and went to the line meekly under minimal urging.
Cruised forward early and settled just forward of midfield. Made no impression in the straight, and was eased out late.
Slowly away, and settled towards the rear of the field. Never competitive. Unacceptable performance.
Got head up early when being steadied back from the wide draw. Settled worse than midfield, wide with limited cover. Dropped out quickly in the straight. Unacceptable performance.

Fair start racing wide in prominent 3rd, became 2nd coming onto home bend, hit the front upon straightening, just held on to the line.
Broke well from the one gate, settled in 4th on the rail just over 2L back, similar turning in, angled off the rail to challenge over 200 metres out, finished off race strongly.
Slow to begin, soon picked up to just worse than midfield, made headway under pressure rounding home bend, sustained progress from midfield into the straight, nearest at finish.
Made running, crossed to the rail passing the 800 metres, headed under pressure shortly after straightening, no extra.
Broke well from a wide gate, settled just better than midfield 3L back in 5th, one-paced under pressure from 4th into the straight.
Settled in midfield, hung out and lost position rounding home bend, produced good late impression inside the final 200 metres.
Began awkwardly losing ground, travelled in midfield on the rail, ran home one-paced.
Hampered at start, raced greenly at the back early and middle stages, ran on past beaten horses inside final 250 metres.
Jumped fairly, niggled long inside the leader on the rail, tightened when drifted back to 1.5L 3rd coming onto home bend, soon weakened after straightening. (Mucus in trachea)
Reluctant to stride out early, recovered to rear end of field 700 metres out, made no impression for remainder of the race, green.
Jumped fairly, soon dropped to midfield despite ridden along, hampered, carried wide and lost position rounding home bend, weakened after straightening.
Taken back to last few from the widest gate, widest runner turning in, made no impression in the straight.
Just behind midfield, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 400M to score.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, suited by the fast pace, made steady ground 400M for 2nd.
Took rail at back, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M whilst racing in restricted room between runners, on heels just prior to the line.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, made ground 250M.
Box seat, not suited by the fast tempo, ran on well to the line.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide, not suited by the fast pace, ran on ok.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, lack turn of foot in straight.
Pushed forward, not suited by the fast sectionals, flattened 200M.
Eased to rear, took rail, favoured by the fast pace, made some ground 200M.
At back along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, ran on fairly in straight.
Eased back, 2 wide, suited by the fast pace, no progress.
Hard ridden to take rail and lead, clocked fast sectionals, soon dropped off 350M.
Began awkwardly, settled behind midfield on rail, commenced to improve passing 400M, wide on straightening, quickened passing final 150M, held off all to win.
Began fairly, raced behind midfield on rail, held up for clearing run in the early straight, shifted out at 250M and asked for effort, travelled strongly in the concluding stages.
Moderate start, travelled midfield, pushed after home turn, lay out under pressure final 150M, worked home solidly.
Travelled at handy position, urged at home turn, fought hard entire straight, finished well.
Jumped OK, took box seat, tried to improve at home turn, under pressure in the straight, finished OK.
Settled behind midfield, tried to improve passing 500M, under pressure in the straight, one-paced.
Taken back at start and settled at rear on rail, one-paced.
Urged along to take lead, commenced to improve at home turn, weakened passing 150M.
Taken back at start and raced at tail, widest on straightening, asked for effort but only limited response.
Ridden along after start, travelled wide and without cover at front position throughout the race, under pressure and lost ground in the straight.
Raced midfield on rail, held up for clearing run in the early straight, failed to run on.
Raced outside the leader, became unbalanced in the early straight and fade-out abruptly. Failed to make impression, must trial.
Taken back at start to sit 3rd last 1 off, nudged along 500m, shaken up 400m & shifted widest into stretch, gathered & driven 200m, roared to lead close home.
Smart start, settled 1 back on fence, shaken up behind front rank 300m, quickened to edge lead 80m, all out & headed close home.
Speed to lead at break, restrained & headed 1130m to race 1 back 1 off, niggled 720m, under pump 520m & shifted 3 wide 480m for progress, edged lead 200m but peaked & headed 80m.
Slow break, raced rail back of midfield, niggled 550m, driven 400m, stayed on for grinding gains in stretch.
Started ok & bustled initially to race midfield 3 wide no cover, advanced 700m to join front rank 4 deep, bumped turning in, boxed on evenly, no extra when checked last strides.
Moderate break & sat 1 off with cover behind midfield, niggled 500m, driven very wide home turn, stayed on for minor headway.
Taken back at break, niggled along 2nd last, under pump 500m, plugging on but still only 1 behind at 100m, maintained momentum for late progress.
Sharp break widest, pushed on to park 2nd 1 off no cover, pressed lead home turn, led on straightening, all out & headed 200m, tapered thereafter.
Started ok, driven initially to park midfield 1 off with cover, overraced 780m, shifted 3 deep for progress 550m & under pump, hard ridden 300m, outpaced in run home.
Broke ok but rousted to settle midfield on rail, shifted out 380m, driven 300m, found little in tame run to wire.
Broke well, pushed 3 deep to lead 1130m, to rail 1020m, bowled along keenly, driven under pressure & headed turning in, faded in run.
Slow start, raced at tail, detached & under drive turning in, found nil.
Quick start, outpaced early, settled midfield on rail, niggled 750m, ridden 400m, railed through, burst between runners to hit lead 75m, strong win.
First to jump, scrubbed early to get to lead, assumed front 880m, 2.5L lead 600m, set blistering fractions, clicked up 350m, kicked strongly, claimed 75m, fought to line.
Even break, into spot just beyond midfield but keen, ridden 330m, never a threat but found line late.
On back foot at start, eased to well beyond midfield spot on rail, off rail 400m, ridden 320m, laying in, knuckled down late.
Smart jump, natural speed to get into handy position on rail, ridden 350m, boxed on.
Bounced fairly, settled beyond midfield on rail, ridden 320m, made ground late.
Broke quickly, led early, settled 2nd 1 off, held together until 300m, found little when asked, one-paced to line.
Eased at jump, settled at rear on rail, stuck towards inside on straightening and ridden 330m, drifted out further in straight, made a little ground over closing stages.
Away fast, ridden to maintain forward spot, settled 4th 1 off, slightly keen at times, ridden upon straightening, one-paced.
Broke well enough, natural speed to settle fore of midfield 1 off, back to midfield 550m, niggled 300m, couldn't come on.
Eased from gates to settle near rear 1 off, ridden 350m, never in contention although OK very late.
Out the back from start, settled at rear 1 off, pulled widest into straight, held together until 300m, couldn't make any impact.
Travelled in behind midfield throughout, 4L behind 2 wide, closed off solidly inside 100M to score by a short-head.
Raced just in front of midfield, 1-1/2L off along the rail, kept on going nicely to take 2nd in a blanket finish.
Jumped fairly only then crowded, in behind midfield 3-1/4L off along the rail, finished off nicely inside 150M for 3rd.
Settled to race in midfield, 2-1/4L behind 2 wide, kept on and worked home well to take 4th.
Niggled after start, stayed in one-off one-back position, sat about 3/4L off, ran on fairly to the wire.
Rolled forward along the rail, stayed on the first line until near 600M to race in box-seat, kept on okay to the line.
Jumped well then eased to race at the rear, 5-1/2L behind along the rail, made ground in the straight.
Steadied after start, raced at the rear 5-1/4L behind 2 wide, saved ground in the straight.
Niggled to be prominent, trapped wide until assumed lead near 600M, caught when couldn't find extra passing 100M.
Pushed and settled to race in about midfield, lost ground gradually after 700M, not likely thereafter.
Sent forward and led until 700M, always in a 2 wide position, kept on till 200M and weakened out.
Prominent until dropping to midfield near 600M, wide throughout, faded gradually from rounding turn.
Got away OK, then raced along rail behind midfield to home turn. Swung wide at turn-in, cruised forward to hit front 100m before pulling clear.
First out, pressed forward from outside gate before taking sit one-out 1L from leader. Surged forward at turn in, hit front 250m, run down final 100m.
Hard ridden along the rail to lead approaching first turn, then put under a hold to straight. Shaken up passing 350m, joined up front 250m, kept on gamely.
Jumped shadow approaching first turn, then slid into box seat back stretch, 2L from leader. Boxed on well early in straight before emptying close home.
Outpaced early, settling behind midfield 6L from leader. Made some progress around home turn but only one-paced in straight.
Away well, shared early pace before steadied 1300m, settling one-out, one-back. Made forward move 3-wide at turn in, kept on well to 200m before tiring.
Away well, then raced ahead of midfield before losing position first turn and dropping back 6L from leader. Shaken up home turn but only one-paced.
Shifted across behind runners soon after start, then checked 1200m, dropping to last. Made some progress around home turn but one-paced in straight.
Crowded out on jumping, restrained and shifted across behind runners to rail in last place before improving to behind midfield. Found little in straight when asked.
Broke well, shared early pace to first turn, before easing 3L back in one-out position. Spent force soon after straightening.
Outpaced, racing towards rear to straight. Never in the hunt.
Pressed forward from outside draw before shifting in for cover behind midfield approaching first turn. Held position to straight before tiring.
Jumped well from the widest draw, slotted in midfield spot easily, travelled well to turn, angled out early in straight and finished off very strongly to score.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 9 lengths or so back at rear, same margin back on turn, ran home strongly to get 2nd.
Away with them, positioned right behind the leader, ideal run to turn, took the lead near 150M, but couldn't hold off the first two late.
Average to begin, positioned on rail in 5th, 3 lengths or so back, easy run on turn, kept on well in straight to make frame.
Began fairly from gate 1, raced 7 to 8 lengths back on rail, same position on turn, made reasonable progress in straight without threatening.
Jumped well from a tricky gate, sent forward to race prominently, shared lead on turn, peaked near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began well, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back in 4th, there to turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped with them, taken back to race 8 lengths back at rear, same position on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out near 350M, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well, took the lead easily, travelled nicely throughout, headed near 150M, weakened thereafter.
Moderately away from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with no cover throughout, failed to close off in straight.
Slowly away, raced at tail throughout, never a threat.
