Broke well from a low draw, settled just off the pace on the rail, angled out for a run entering straight, fought on steadily to just prevail in a four-way finish.
Began well from a wide gate, prominent and wide before racing one-out-one-back in joint 3rd around home bend, fought on steadily down the straight, lost in bob.
Moderate start, improving on the rail when inconvenienced passing the 800 metres, ran on alongside first two holding every chance but unable to peg them back.

Ridden from the widest gate to lead on the rail, held narrow running round the bend and into straight, broke over half a length clear early in straight but unable to sustain effort and swamped inside the final 150 metres.
Settled just worse than midfield, shuffled further back when wide around home bend, widest runner turning in, produced good impression down the centre of the straight, did best work late.
Settled at the back from a wide gate, saved ground on the rail turning for home, did not find much room behind runners early in straight, kept on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Settled in midfield, kept on steadily down the centre of the track, never threatening.
Moderate start, improved steadily to join the leader rounding home bend, unable to sustain effort and faded inside the final 300 metres.
Lacked early pace, travelled in last few before creeping up on the rail rounding home bend, one-paced in straight.
Always in last few, baulked for a run early in straight, kept on at the same pace. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Raced wide in last few after beginning from a wide gate, lost position and dropped to last coming onto home bend, failed to quicken under pressure but kept on same pace to the line.
Prominent far side, gave ground steadily from half-way out.
At back, pace good, progressed steadily 400M to score.
At back, pace good, made the move around the field, dashed well 300M, just missed by a narrow margin.
Slow away, at back, raced keenly, on heels early, pace good, lack room 4-2, made steady ground when clear.
Midfield, trapped wide throughout, pace good, closed off strongly.
Pushed forward, pace good, out of fuel 300M.
Pushed to occupy a more prominent spot, pace good, flattened 200M.
Pushed forward, pace good, soon emptied 300M.
At back, pace good, made minor ground 200M.
At back, pace good, ran on ok in straight.
At back, trapped wide, pace good, never improved.
Very slow away, at rear, no progress.
Midfield, never a factor.
Pushed forward to lead at good pace, dropped off 400M.
Started well, settled midfield on rail, improved passing 500M, quickened at 150M, came home strongly to win.
Moderate start, race midfield, commenced to improve at home turn, fought hard entire straight and finished solidly.
Slow start, settled behind midfield on rail, badly held up passing 150M, worked to the line well.
Started well and took box seat, asked for effort in the early straight, finished well.
Settled midfield, tried to improve passing 500M, under pressure and made some ground in final 100M, finished OK.
Jumped OK, pushed along to take lead, asked for effort in the early straight, lost ground passing final 50M, finished fairly.
Urged along to settle outside the leader, under pressure in the straight, one paced.
Settled behind midfield, tried to improve at home turn, one paced.
Jumped well, settled at handy position, under pressure and weakened in the straight, failed to make impression.
Taken back at start and settled at rear, no response in the straight.
Began only fairly, travelled at rear on rail, never improved.
Taken back at start and raced at tail, never in it.
Moderate start, settled rail midfield, shaken up 400m, shifted 1 off & battling run to lead 80m, maintained momentum through line.
Slow start, raced rail behind midfield, shifted out & shaken up 400m, switched back in & driven in close quarters 300m, ran on to 2nd close home.
Speed to lead, driven to snare rail, relaxed to race 1.5L clear, shaken up 400m, all out & under pressure 150m, headed 80m, clung on to 3rd.
Broke well, niggled along 1 back on rail, driven home turn, shifted 1 off to challenge 400m & soon 2nd, stayed on to press lead 100m but peaked & tapered.
Broke ok, taken back from wide gate to race 3 deep with cover behind midfield, widest & driven home turn, stayed on dourly centre track for minor gains.
Good start, raced 1 back 1 off, shifted out & driven final turn, boxed on dourly centre track.
Started well, taken back to slot midfield 1 off with cover, ridden along 500m, hard driven centre track, plodded on tepidly.
Slow break, raced rail near rear, 3rd last & driven into stretch, stayed on for minor headway, flashed tail repeatedly in stretch.
Fast break wide & pushed on to park 2nd 1 off, 1.5L back & ridden turning in, soon all out & faded in run home.
Lacked toe & raced 1 off with cover behind midfield, niggled 700m & lost ground, driven widest home turn, stayed on past fading rivals.
Broke well & bustled to race handy 3 wide no cover, niggled 650m, driven 430m but outpaced, struggled in fading run home.
Started ok from wide gate, snagged & taken behind, soon detached at tail & niggled to latch on 700m, 2nd last & driven turning in, plodded on weakly.
Modest break, raced midfield 3 wide with cover, niggled 650m, under pump 550m, shifted wide turning in, found nil & faded weakly.
Tardy start, raced 3 wide with cover near rear, niggled 650m, under pump at tail 500m, found nil & eased.
Jumped well, natural pace to settle just behind speed on rail, stuck to inside throughout, pushed along 450m, hit lead 250m, powered clear.
Away on terms, allowed to find midfield spot 1 off, asked for an effort 400m, short of room 350m to 150m, sprinted well when clear.
No gate speed, eventually mustered into midfield spot on rail, no clear run upon straightening, into clear 200m, knuckled down late.
Driven hard from gates, got into forward position but trapped 3 deep, niggled 550m, never quite on top but fought on well.
Started OK, outpaced early & settled beyond midfield 1 off, travelled strongly throughout, pulled 3 deep 700m, ridden 550m, loomed as major threat 300m, peaked on run 150m.
Fair beginning, niggled early, settled beyond midfield 1 off, clicked up 570m, plugged away.
Began evenly, clicked up to get to lead on rail by 1650m, slightly keen at times, 0.5L lead 1000m, held together until 380m, claimed 250m, one-paced to line.
Away fairly, hard ridden to get into spot just behind the speed 1 off, ridden 450m, sprinted well but only momentarily, weakened from 180m.
On back foot slightly at start, settled beyond midfield 1 off, pushed at times, ridden 520m, short of room soon after, into clear 350m, struggled to come into it.
No gate speed, back to a clear last & ridden 1600m, niggled 800m, driven 550m, widest into straight, OK very late.
Broke fairly, settled near rear 1 off, niggled 1200m, ridden 550m, short spurt but weakened from 200m.
Ridden early from outside gate, eased to settle fore of midfield 3 deep with cover, niggled 700m, under pressure 500m, weakened.
Very slow to jump, ridden into spot near rear on rail, never really travelling and niggled throughout, under pressure 600m, never a factor.
Fastest into stride, ridden along to maintain handy position, sat 2nd 1 off, ridden 450m, weakened soon after.
Sent forward, took fence and led by 3/4L, pulled away gradually from 250M, kept on nicely to score by 1-3/4L.
Travelled in worse than midfield, sat 5-3/4L behind 2 wide, covered nice ground inside 300M, closed off well.
Awkward start, raced in behind midfield, 5L behind 3 wide with cover, made good ground and ran on well to the line.
Stumbled at start, then pushed to race outside the lead, sat 3/4L off, showed little response, remained one paced.
Raced towards the tail, 6-1/2L behind 3 wide with cover, made ground and finished off fairly.
Hard ridden after start, took up racing in box-seat, sat about 1-3/4L off, remained one paced to the line.
In midfield, 4L behind 2 wide, badly unbalanced when bumped at 550M, no run at 300M, one paced thereafter.
Travelled in midfield, sat about 3-1/4L behind the lead, wide and without cover throughout, never threatened.
Pushed and settled in one-off one-back position, sat about 2-1/2L off, out of steam when approaching 200M.
Race in midfield, sat 4L behind but trapped wide and without cover throughout, not competitive in the straight.
Eased back, sat 7-1/2L behind 2 wide, remained at the rear throughout, never in it.
Taken back and shifted to rail, settled to race behind midfield about 7-1/2L behind, kept up until 250M only.
Fractious prior to start, raced in front of midfield along the rail sat about 3L off, hard ridden to 250M, tailed out.
Pushed forward from outside draw to race one-back, one-out. Threw out strong challenge from 400m but held until edging ahead closing stages.
Away nicely, easily finding lead and steadying pace. Kicked ahead on straightening, then kept finding when strongly challenged final 300m, only to lose narrowly.
Shifted across behind horses from outside draw and last on settling. Improved position turning for home, taken very wide in straight, ran on well but no match for first two.
Outpaced and raced at rear to straight. Taken to centre track and ran on steadily to make the frame.
Nicely positioned along rail in box seat to turn. Boxed on gamely in straight before emptying close home.
Slow into stride, taken to rail and improved to behind midfield. Put under pressure on straightening but only one-paced.
Not pushed early, racing one-out behind midfield. Swung wide into straight but only one-paced.
Jumped OK then ridden one-out in midfield before being steadied 1000m and losing position. One-paced in straight.
Ridden to hold forward position, settling one-out 3L from leader. Checked off heels approaching 1000m but held position to straight when one-paced.
Ridden to hold fence in midfield 5L from leader. Kept on steadily in straight before tiring final 200m.
Hard ridden early but failed to muster and held towards rear. Put under pressure turning for home, wide in straight, found little. (Lost left front plate after 1400m).
Pressed forward from an outside gate to race behind the pace before moving forward outside leader around turn. Kept on fairly to 200m before flattened.
Pressed forward early but held 3-wide without cover 3L from leader. Kept wide around turn and faded in straight.
Shifted across behind runners to find cover, then hard ridden but failed to muster. Taken wide 500m to get clear passage but failed to respond and eased out. Unacceptable performance.
Emerged as leader 1300M, allowed an easy lead middle stages, kicked home strongly passing 400M and no danger 150M out winning by comfortable margin.
Dropped back to the rear 5-6Ls off leader, waited with till 400M, closed off well to go 2nd near 80M, kept chasing winner but unable to close the gap.
Restrained behind leaders on this first attempt over 1600M, close enough turning in, tried hard to close the gap on leader passing 400M, held ground over final 150M, lost 2nd 80M out.
Chased leaders along the inside, pace slow 2nd and 3rd quarter, kept on evenly turning home, lacked winning dash.
Tracked leader in 2nd, pace slow middle stages, left flat footed when tempo quickened 450M, failed to make any impression for the remainder of the event.
Held up in the rear pair, 6Ls off leader 400M but couldn't muster the speed to be closer, never likely.
Settled down in 6th place 3-4Ls off the pace, kept on same pace turning in, no threat to leaders.
Held up 4Ls off the pace in 5th, beaten off early straight, eased final 150M when no chance. (Lame next day.)
Came out running, clear leader on settling, then put under a hold. Kicked ahead soon after straightening and went to the post unchallenged.
Away nicely then raced one-out behind midfield. Swung wide entering straight, finished strongly while hanging in under pressure near 250m.
Began fairly, taken to fence behind midfield. Made up some ground approaching final turn, ran on well between horses to grab minor placing.
Pressed forward 3-wide to race behind leader passing 1000m before dropping back to third approaching home turn. Taken wide entering straight to make challenge but only one-paced.
No early pace, racing behind midfield along fence. Switched out home turn to get clear passage and ran on fairly to just miss the frame.
Began awkwardly, ridden but held wide without cover towards rear. Hampered approaching 1000m, lay in straight and not ridden out fully. (Rider fined).
Ridden early to get midfield position but wide, then pushed forward to race alongside leader approaching home turn. Kept on fairly early in straight before emptying 200m.
Hard ridden to hold forward position before seeking cover one-out in midfield approaching turn. One-paced in straight. Lame right front leg.
Travelled strongly early stages one-out behind pace to home turn when put under pressure but found little and faded.
Slow into stride, dropping to rear and taken to fence. Made some headway early in straight before turning one-paced final 200m. Lame right front leg.
Badly hampered at start, dropping one-out towards rear. Made up some ground early in straight before tiring.
Outpaced, dropping to rear. Clear last approaching turn and never in hunt.
Away fairly, pressed forward, settling along rail 4L from leader. Under pressure turning for home and dropped out in straight.

Placing: UR
Comment: Fractious in gate, lunged, dislodged rider and left gate riderless.

Went to press forward early, before being steadied off heels soon after jumping and settled forward of midfield, 1 off the fence. Ran on from the 300m. Nosed in front at 100m, and just held out challenger.
Jumped well and allowed to roll forward to be handily place 3rd/4th, 3 wide no cover. Clear run in the straight, and was running on strongly. Never weakened and was closing in on winner late.
Taken forward early, and settled just behind the early leader. Pushed up to grab lead at the 300m. Battled on OK, but 1 paced late and was overtaken in the last 100m.
Dropped back from the wide draw to sit at the rear of the field. Came off heels at 150m, and was strong to the line from that point.
Started well and taken up early to be placed 3rd/4th, on the fence. Never improved his position and faded last 100m.
Didn't muster early, and settled in midfield. Wider on the turn, and stayed on fairly late.
Push to lead early. Not much in the tank in the straight, and eased out late.
Leapt out of the barrier, missed the kick and settled at the rear of the field. Plugged away steadily under hands and heels in the straight, without ever threatening.
Inconvenienced soon after jumping and dropped back to sit worse than midfield, 1 off the fence. Never kicked in the straight.
Awkward on heels on jumping, but recovered to settle midfield, on the fence. Only plugged away early in the straight, before dropping out quickly late.
Slow into stride and eased forward to sit towards the rear of the field, 3 wide with limited cover. Widest on the turn, but made no impression and was packed up late.
OK away, but eased back to settle worse than midfield. Gave nothing in the straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to race outside leader, shared lead on turn, kept on very well in straight to score.
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, slightly improved from 600M, finished off strongly to get 2nd.
Slow to begin, recovered to race 5 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, made very good progress to get 3rd.
Away with them, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 150M, missed 3rd late.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide at rear, there to turn, finished off well in straight to be nearest on line.
Jumped well from gate 8, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths or so back at rear, same position on turn, angled out in straight and made reasonable progress.
Bumped start, raced 8 lengths or so back at rear, still well back on turn, taken wide after straightening and made minor progress.
Jumped well, positioned a length or so back on rail, awkwardly placed near 550M, no daylight early in straight, bumped near 150M, one-paced thereafter.
Began well from a wide draw, positioned 1 out 1 back, improved from 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced at rear, difficult to settle in the early stages, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away from a middle gate, unable to slot in, travelled wide with no cover for the majority of the race, peaked on turn, finished off one-paced.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, recovered to race 3 lengths back on rail in 6th, similar position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, improved from 600M, 4 wide turning in, peaked early in straight and weakened gradually thereafter, eased final 100M.
Bumped start, raced at tail throughout, finished tailed out, unacceptable performance. (See Racing Incidents.)

Shared early pace on stands rails, gained clear lead coming onto course proper, won comfortably.
Began well to dispute the lead early stages, shaken up coming onto course proper but unable to quicken under pressure.
Jumped fairly, settled just off the pace on stands rails, came under pressure coming onto course proper, kept on same pace without quickening.
Bumped jumping out, unbalanced and shuffled back to rear of midfield about 3L off the speed, shaken up half-way out, kept on same pace without quickening.
Began well from the one draw, not far off the pace without cover near the centre of the track, gave ground under pressure inside final 300 metres.
Gradually picked up from a low draw to a handy position over half-way out, unable to sustain effort and gave ground steadily inside final 300 metres. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Settled just off the pace early stages, baulked for a run approaching the course proper, faded inside final 300 metres.
Jumped awkwardly and crowded, travelled towards the rear near the centre of the track, found nothing in the run home.
Checked at start and dropped well behind, never a danger.
Checked at start and dropped well behind, never seen with a chance.
Hard ridden to obtain a midfield spot, 2 wide, lack room 400M, dashed well when clear and scored.
Settled just off and outside the leader, led 300M, hung on well until 150M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Hard ridden throughout to keep up with the field, trapped 3 wide, made steady ground 400M for 3rd.
Hard ridden early but not muster, at back along the fence, lack room early part of straight, dashed strongly 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pressed forward, sat 2 wide, just held ground in straight.
Took rail and lead easily, overhauled 300M, flattened 150M.
Pushed to occupy box seat, ran on until 200M flattened.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, made steady ground 250M.
Eased back, raced 3-4 wide, ran on only fairly in straight.
At back along the fence, lack room 400M, no progress.
Pushed forward, raced keenly, 2 wide, lack room 400M, checked badly 200M, emptied.
Began fairly, settled at tail on rail, improved at Home turn, quickened in the straight, finished unchallenged.
Jumped well, settled midfield, commenced to improve after 400M, worked home strongly.
Took lead after start, asked for effort passing 350M, fought hard in the straight, finished solidly.
Settled behind midfield, made ground in the straight, worked home well.
Taken back at start, settled at tail, asked for effort at Home turn but only one-paced in the straight.
Pushed to take box seat, under pressure in the straight, failed to make impression.
Settled behind midfield, never in it.
Speared to the front on jumping, pulling 2L clear 1000m before slowing pace. Kicked ahead on straightening, pulling away final 200m.
Jumped well but not pushed, settling on rail 3L from leader. Shifted out turning for home, got clear run 320m, finished strongly.
No early pace, racing 3-wide towards rear entering back stretch. Kept wide home turn, ran on steadily down centre track to grab minor placing.
Jumped well, ridden to hold box seat 2L from leader. Kept tabs to straight, boxed on gamely but only one-paced.
Jumped OK, shifted in from outside gate, settling 3-wide at rear. Kept wide throughout before running on fairly in the straight.
Ridden early to hold position behind pace, one-away from fence. Shaken up turning for home but only one-paced, laying in final 300m.
Shifted across behind horses from outside draw, settling one-out at rear. Under pressure home turn, held for run 200m, then raced in restricted room to line.
Began awkwardly, crowded, then shifted across to rail, dropping to last. Checked 800m losing more ground, ran past tiring rivals in straight.
Pressed forward from outside gate to race outside leader on settling. Stayed alongside leader to 400m when put under pressure and faded.
Pressed forward, settling one-out, one-back. Urged forward 400m to look a chance before fading abruptly. (Lost right front plate 600m, substantial amount of blood in trachea)
Beaten for early pace, settling between horses towards the rear. Crowded out turning for home, one-paced in straight.
Slow into stride, ridden to make up ground along rail to behind midfield before racing awkwardly home turn. Faded in straight.
Ridden to hold forward position but kept 3-wide mostly. Taken even wider home turn before running out of steam in straight and fading.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 to 3 lengths back on rail in midfield, travelled well throughout, angled out near 550M, finished off very well in straight and scored easily.
Jumped well, positioned a length or so back in 4th, similar position on turn, made good progress early in straight but couldn't hold off the winner final 100M.
Taken back from a tricky gate, 7 lengths back at tail, there to turn, made very good progress in straight to get 3rd, nearest on line.
Began well, taken back to race 2 wide, 5 lengths or so back at rear, angled out from 500M, finished off very strongly in straight to make frame, nearest on line.
Moderately away from gate 8, unable to slot in early, raced 3 wide in midfield, wider on turn, finished off evenly in straight, just missed frame.
Jumped well from a middle draw, raced 3 wide in 5th, bumped near 900M, no cover thereafter, improved to 2nd on turn, kept on well until near 150M, slightly weakened in the concluding stages.
Slightly slow out, raced 6 lengths back at rear, gradually improved on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Began fairly from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, headed near 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned a length or so back on rail, no clear running early in straight, angled out near 200M, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 10, raced 3 wide, 5 lengths back in 9th, improved on turn, peaked early in straight, stayed on one-paced.
Jumped well, raced prominently, 2 wide, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back, angled out near 500M, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Sat just behind midfield, 5-1/2L off 2 wide, closed off strongly in the straight to take the prize by a short-head.
Raced in front of midfield, sat 2-1/4L off 2 wide, looked likely until headed by the winner just before going to the line.
Bumped start, settled to race in midfield, 4L behind 2 wide, fought well and worked home nicely.
Travelled towards the rear, 7L behind along the rail, made good ground and kept on well to the line.
Showed no early speed and raced in midfield, 5L behind and wide with no cover, despite that ran on okay to the line.
Taken back to be at the tail, 8-3/4L behind along the rail, made good ground in the straight and closed off nicely.
Pushed out of the gates, settled 3/4L off outside the lead, kept on to the line but was no match to the others.
Eased and raced at the back, 8-1/4L behind 2 wide, swung widest on straightening, made minor ground.
Settled to race towards the rear, sat about 6-3/4L behind 2 wide, kept on mostly one-paced in the straight.
Sent forward to cross and take rail from the outside gate, led by 3/4L, ran on until 200M and weakened. (Lame right front)
Pushed forward and occupied box-seat, about 1-1/2L off the lead, raced ungenerously in middle stages, faded at 300M.
Inconvenienced after start, raced in behind midfield, 5-1/2L off along the rail, never looked likely.
Jumped awkwardly, settled in front of midfield, 2-1/2L off along the rail, niggled early but found nothing at all. (Bled)
No early speed, dropping to rear but away from outer fence. Shaken up 500m, given reminders 350m, shifted in for clear run and raced past leaders for narrow win.
Quickly into stride, settling 1L behind pacemakers 800m. Shifted in 370m for clear run, hit front 110m, run down final strides.
Away nicely, rolled forward settling 3-away from outer fence 2L from pace. Urged forward passing 350m, joint leader 110m, run down.
Fast out, shifted across to outer fence, settling a neck behind leader 800m. Went forward to eyeball leader 600m, took lead 400m, joined up front 110m, no extra close home.
Jumped OK, then settled in midfield 3-away from outer fence. Put under pressure from 500m and ran on steadily to be closest at finish.
Jumped well but unable match pace, settling one-away from outer fence 4L from leaders. Improved position when taken to fence 400m but only one-paced final 200m.
Bumped start, ridden along, settling behind midfield. Kept on steadily final 500m without looking dangerous.
Fast out, used up to get lead crossing to outer fence 800m, then eased. Under pressure from 500m, overtaken 400m, dropped off quickly final 150m. (Unacceptable performance)
Crowded out start, dropping to rear but kept away from outer fence. Never competitive though ran past tiring horses close home.
Jumped OK but checked and unbalanced 700m. Checked again 600m losing considerable ground. Plodded home. (Racing manners unacceptable)
Bumped start, dropping to rear. Never competitive.
Away well, pushed forward, settling on fence 3L from leaders. Under pressure from 500m, dropped out quickly final 350m. (Lame left hind).
Slow to begin, settled down in 10th behind midfield, showed good acceleration and motored home well to lead 150M, shifted ground under pressure but kept up the momentum to score.
Held up in midfield 3Ls off the pace, shifted out from fence 350M to challenge, tried hard but always held by winner, held on for 2nd in a photo.
Dropped back to race near the rear, switched wide 500M, chased solidly down the outside on straightening, narrowly missed 2nd.
Caught wide no cover throughout from draw 12, chased leaders into straight, improved to lead passing 300M but couldn't hold off first 3 inside 150M.
Never far off the pace, in 5th / 6th place home turn, kept battling away on straightening, inside final 200M had to be steadied when crowded for room.
Held up midfield along the 2-path, brought wide 500M, not quicken with main rivals inside 300M, one paced final 150M.
Held up in last first 700M, 5Ls behind leader top of straight, plodded on over final 300M, never on terms with leaders.
Slow to begin from draw 1 but soon recovered to race in a position chasing the pace, fought on to near 250M, outran by leaders and weakened towards the finish.
Sent forward setting steady pace up front, couldn't hold off pursuers 250M, faded towards the line.
Caught 3-wide midfield on jumping from wide barrier, lacked acceleration, left behind by leaders 250M. (Blood in trachea.)
Failed to muster speed despite ridden, gradually fell back to the rear, soon left behind on straightening.
Pressed forward to race outside leader, couldn't hold his position passing 400M, weakened badly to last, eased.
Away well, settling on fence 5L from pace. Shifted 3-wide entering straight and surged forward, edging ahead 150m before pulling clear final strides.
Jumped well, taken to fence 3L from leader. Improved position around turned but sandwiched top of straight. Took time to accelerate finishing strongly final 100m.
Pressed forward from widest gate, settling one-out 1L from leader 900m. Shaken up top of straight, hit front 250m, tired final strides.
Quickly away, settling one-out 2L from leader. Rolled forward on straightening to look a chance but only one-paced final 200m.
Bumped start, dropping to rear on settling. Improved along rail turning for home and ran on steadily in straight to be closest at finish.
Jumped OK, settling one-out in midfield. Swung wide entering straight, pressed forward but only one-paced final 200m.
No pace, dropped to rear but three-wide. Kept wide around turn, taken to centre field in straight and ran on fairly.
First out, became unbalanced 1050m but held lead until passed 900m, sitting inside leader around home turn. Retook lead passing 400m, overtaken 250m, faded.
Jumped fairly, vigorously ridden but failed to muster, settling along rail behind midfield. Switched out turning for home and ran on fairly.
Bumped start, no pace, dropping to rear between horses. Boxed on one-paced in straight.
Steadied on jumping and shifted across behind runners, dropping to rear. Last into straight before running past tired rivals.
Began OK but checked passing 900m then raced fiercely, refusing to settle and dropping back. One-Paced in straight.
Pushed forward from outside gate, racing wide before taking lead 900m. Overtaken 400m, brushed by another runner and unbalanced 350m, dropped out.
Began awkwardly, pressed forward to midfield but left wide without cover from 900m. Wide throughout and faded in straight.
Dropped back from the wide draw to eventually settle worse than midfield. 2nd last rounding for home, but powered on under urging from 300m. Pushed out until the last stride, and was easily in.

Pushed forward initially, before easing back for cover at 1200m. Came wider soon after straightening and was slightly wayward early in the straight. Focused from the 200m, and ran strongly to the line.

Eased back early to sit around midfield. Went searching for a run at the top of the straight. Was building momentum, before being checked and coming out off heels at 200m. Stayed on well late to be clear 3rd.
Dropped back from the wide draw to sit last. Came widest on the turn and ran well in the straight, only peaking in the last 50m.
Eased back early to sit towards the rear of the field. Weaved through the field, and finished off the race gamely.
Awkwardly away, but recovered to push up to sit forward of midfield, 3 wide with limited cover. Battled on fairly, without threatening late.
Pushed hard early to eventually take the lead passing the 1000m. Couldn't maintain the pressure, and faded out from the 200m.
Pushed forward from the wide draw to initially settle forward of midfield and 3 wide. Pushed forward at 1000m to be 2nd/3rd, but still 3 wide. Nothing left late, and faded out from the 200m.
Pushed up early to be well placed in 3rd, 1 off the fence. 1 paced in the straight, and never threatened.
Taken up early from the inside draw to be well placed, forward of midfield and on the fence. Held up in the straight until 200m, and never able to run it out late.
Battled for the early lead, before accepting 2nd at the 1000m. Nothing left in the tank late, only battling on before being eased from 100m.

Pushed forward early, before electing to ease off and settle forward of midfield. Didn't respond to riding early in the straight, and was eased a long way from home. Jockey questioned. Unacceptable performance.

Held slender lead from the middle draw, ceded advantage 800 metres out, back to alongside the leader turning for home and soon hit the front, just held off runner-up's late challenge at the finish.
Ridden along from the one draw, settled just off the pace in 4th on the rail, became 3rd in similar spot 800 metres out, baulked briefly 200 metres out, fought on dourly to only fail narrowly.
Settled just worse than midfield from a poor draw racing keenly at times after the Rock, commenced move on top of the home bend, ran on under pressure from 7th into straight, nearest at finish.
Slow into stride, settled in rear of midfield on the rail, gained closer to 5th at the Rock, ran on under pressure in straight but pipped for 3rd.
Vied for lead from the widest gate before settling 2-wide 2L back in 4th, renewed effort entering straight, keeping on at the same pace when hampered and lost position close to home.

Crowded at start losing ground, in last few far side, raced ungenerously dropping further back coming onto home bend, soon given strong reminders, produced good late impression inside the final 200 metres.
Given reminders jumping out, settled 3L back in 5th far side, dropped slightly backward to 6th at the Rock, renewed effort entering home straight but only produced modest headway.
Ridden along sharing the early pace, gained half a length advantage at the 800 metres, led until headed over 200 metres out, weakened under pressure.
Moderate start, remained well back throughout.
Slowly away, soon tailed-off. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Settled in front, 2 wide outside the leader, benefited by the slow sectionals, ran on well to the line and scored.
Midfield, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, on heels 500M, again checked 300M and have to re-gather momentum, dashed strongly 150M, just missed.
Eased at start, took cover, harmed by the slow pace, worked around the field 600M in 3-4 wide, unleashed strong finishing efforts 200M.
At back, 2-3 wide, dashed well 250M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Midfield along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, on heels 400M, made steady ground in straight.
Pressed forward, box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Pushed to take rail and led at very slow sectionals, hung on until 200M flattened.
At back, 2-3 wide, made early move 900M to try to take advantages of the slow pace, however soon emptied 300M.
Moderate start, settled midfield, quickened passing 200M, finished unchallenged.
Settled midfield, hard to find clear running in the early straight, made ground final 150M, worked home solidly. Blood trachea.
Began fairly, settled behind midfield on rail, commenced to improve at Home Turn, travelled strongly in the concluding stages.
Began fairly, settled behind midfield, asked effort passing 600M, widest on straightening, finished well.
Slow to begin, raced midfield on rail, fought hard in the straight, worked home OK.
Started well, pushed along to take lead, faded out in the straight, finished fairly.
Jumped out well, urged along to take box seat, asked for effort passing 550M, one-paced in the straight.
Settled behind midfield, tried to improve passing 500M, under pressure in the straight, one-paced.
Started OK, settled front of midfield, was taken to three wide approaching 700M, made home turn awkwardly, tiring in concluding stages.
Settled at handy position, tried to improve at Home Turn, failed to run on.
Taken back at start, settled at tail, never in it.
Ridden but unable handle early pace, settling behind midfield along rail. Peeled out 350m to get clear run, finished strongly to win final strides.
Speared to the front soon after start but kept wide until crossing to fence 650m. Kicked 2L clear on straightening to look the winner but caught final strides.
Steadied soon after start, pressed on 3-wide behind midfield before getting cover approaching turn. Shaken up 350m and finished strongly.
Jumped well, kept wide,, steadied 850m and taken in at midfield. Lost position turning for home before finishing off nicely in straight.
Quickly away, holding rail inside leading pack before settling in box seat 600m. Kept tabs on leader to straight, boxed on gamely.
Ridden early to hold forward position but trapped 3-wide and left without cover from 600m. Boxed on fairly in straight.
Began fairly, no pace, dropping to rear. Stayed at rear to straight before running past tiring rivals.
Began fairly, no pace, dropping to last. Trailed field to straight before finishing fairly down centre field.
Crowded start, ridden to make up ground, settling ahead of midfield away from fence. Lost ground home turn, one-paced in straight. (Lame both front legs)
No early pace, dropping to behind midfield along fence. Made up some ground turning for home, then one-paced.
Pressed forward from widest draw to race outside leader passing 800m. Flat-footed when leader kicked 400m, boxed on to 200m, faded.
Hard ridden to hold forward position, racing one-out 3L from leader. Under pressure turning for home, giving ground quickly final 200m.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in 3rd, travelled well throughout, improved from near 500M, challenged the leader early in straight, kept on very well to score by a neck.
Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead from 800M, enjoyed the easy lead on turn, headed near 200M, stayed on strongly but always held.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 4 lengths back at rear, same margin back on turn, angled out in straight and finished off strongly to get 3rd.
Began well, positioned a length or so on rail, angled out near 450M, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Began fairly, showed no early speed, recovered to race 3 lengths back on rail in midfield, saved ground to turn, kept to inside in straight and finished off evenly.
Jumped well from the widest draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with cover, 3 lengths back in 8th, travelled keenly near 800M, improved from 450M, made some progress in straight.
Bumped start, pushed forward to take the rail, sat right behind the leader on turn, peaked early in straight and weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 3 to 4 lengths back in 9th, same position on turn, bumped near 250M, finished off one-paced.
Away with them, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with no cover in midfield, weakened gradually after turning in when hard run took toll.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, same position to turn, bumped near 250M, showed no response thereafter.
Always at rear, never competitive.
In behind midfield, 5-1/4L off 2 wide, continued to save ground and closed off strongly inside 100M to score.
Sent forward, prominent 2-1/4L off but found no cover, battled on gamely to take 2nd.
Crowded after the start, mended to sit in midfield, 4-1/4L behind on the rail, good dash inside 100M and finished well.
Eased and raced at the rear, 6-1/4L behind along the rail, made good ground and closed off well inside final 200M.
Rolled forward and sat in the box-seat, about 1-1/4L off the lead, closed gap early in the straight, ran on well.
Ridden forward to be outside the leader, sat 3/4L off, kept on one paced to the line.
Travelled in front of midfield, 2-1/2L off 2 wide, fought on till the finish.
Bumped at the start, at the rear, 6-1/4L behind 2 wide, made ground steadily in the straight.
Settled to race in midfield, 4L behind the lead 2 wide, made no ground but kept on to the finish. (Roarer)
Crowded at the start, settled in front of midfield, 2-1/4L off along the rail, ran on to the line.
Pushed forward to take rail and led by 3/4L, caught near 100M, one paced.
Taken back and remained there throughout.
Ridden early to hold forward position then settled one-out 3L from leader first turn. Stoked up passing 600m, overhauled leaders 250m, pulled clear.
Ridden to hold midfield position then taken to fence first turn 5L from leader. Checked and taken out 450m, blocked for run early straight, got split 250m, finished strongly.
Speared to the front from widest draw, crossing to fence 1450m. Set good pace until caught 250m, boxed on gamely to hold minor position.
No pace, taken to rail behind midfield and settled. Switched out turning for home, ran on well to be closest at finish.
Behind midfield on settling, one-away from fence. Shaken up turn, taken to centre track on straightening, finished off nicely.
Jumped well, pushed forward from inside draw, holding box seat 2.5L from leader. Kept tabs to straight but only one-paced when put under pressure.
Began OK, ridden along in midfield one-away from fence. Lost position home turn, boxed on fairly in straight.
Pressed forward from wide draw to race outside leader initially before dropping 2L back passing 800m. Kept on well to 200m before tiring.
Shifted across behind horses soon after start, settling one-out at rear. Taken to rail approaching home turn but only one-paced in straight.
Jumped well but caught wide at midfield first turn and allowed to stride forward to race outside leader passing 900m. Kept on well to straight before fading final stages. (Lame left front leg)
Began fairly, vigorously ridden but failed to respond, gradually becoming detached from field and finished tailed out. (Unacceptable performance)

Placing: PU
Comment: Slow into stride, hard ridden to keep up at rear before breaking down passing 750m and pulled up.
Away well enough from draw 1, sat in 5th 3Ls off the pace, shifted out near 400M and improved to challenge, hit lead 200M, fought on well to maintain upper-hand over the runner-up.
Chased leader, joined by eventual winner 200M, rallied but was held in the run home.
Held up in midfield 4-5Ls off the pace, chased hard behind first two over final 200M but not getting there.
Taken back, settled 7Ls back near the tail, waited with until 250M, sprinted home well down the outside to take 4th. (Jockey reminded he must ride with sufficient vigour and purpose.)
Caught 3-wide from widest draw until slotting in 700M, in 4th place making the turn, inside 300M couldn't quicken to challenge leaders, just kept on.
In midfield, pushed to a 3-wide spot down the back straight, swung widest into straight, kept on steadily but run ended passing 150M.
Quickly into stride, tracked leader along the rail, couldn't lift when asked, kept on same pace to line.
Ended up 3-wide towards the tail, stayed on moderately inside 350M but severely checked 200M, lost rhythm never recovered. (Lame next day.)
Settled down 2-wide towards the rear, 6Ls behind leader at 400M, kept on only fairly in straight, no threat to leaders. (Mucus.)
Behind midfield 5-6Ls off the slow pace, offered little response on straightening, awkwardly placed 150M but made little difference to the results.
Crossed to the lead passing 1000M, led slowly, couldn't fend off pursuers 200M, weakened towards finish.
Soon ended up in the rear, didn't respond to riding turning home, never involved.

Ridden positively to take up running from the widest gate, obtained rails run coming onto home bend, kicked over 2L clear under pressure inside the final 200 metres, won readily.
Held rails run about 2L off the pace, chased leader turning for home, fought on steadily in straight without threatening.
Settled 3-wide without cover just over 3L back in 5th, similar turning for home, kept on steadily without quickening.
Broke well from a wide gate, vied for lead before settled just off the pace coming onto home bend, gained closer to travel alongside the leader rounding the bend, faded steadily after straightening.
Began awkwardly, soon recovered to one-out-one-back in 4th, commenced move to be 3-wide in joint 3rd entering straight, soon faded under pressure after straightening.
Ridden early, mainly in 6th and within 4L of lead, kept on at the one pace without quickening in the run home.
Ridden but remained in 7th on the rails and within 4L of pace, similar turning for home, found nil.
Soon dropped well behind, never seen with a chance.
Jumped fairly but soon dropped to second last and detached from the main body of the field, virtually pulled up closing stages.
Hard ridden forward, pace good, drifted away 200M to score.
Hard ridden to lead at good pace, hung on until 250M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
In front, pace good, progressed steadily 300M.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, pace good, made ground 200M.
At back, pace good, on heels 450M, made some ground 200M.
Hard ridden to keep up in front, pace good, ran on fairly.
Pushed to hold a midfield spot, pace good, just held ground.
Slow away, at back, pace good, no turn of foot.
At rear, pace good, no progress.
Midfield, pace good, never progressed.
Never a factor.
Started OK, raced behind midfield on rail, badly held up from 400M to 300M, obtained clear running passing 200M, quickened in the final stages to win.
Jumped well, eased to settled midfield for cover, improved after Home Turn, travelled strongly in the straight, just missed by short-head.
Fast out, pushed along to take lead, fought hard entire straight, missed by neck.
Started well, settled midfield, asked for effort passing 500M, made ground in the straight, finished well.
Began fairly, taken back at start and raced at tail, widest on straightening, worked home OK.
Began well, raced in front of midfield, asked effort passing 600M but only limited response, finished one-paced.
Began awkwardly, raced at tail on rail, tried to improve but only one-paced in the straight.
Jumped fairly, urged to sit behind leader on rail, under pressure and faded out in the straight.
Settled midfield, travelled wide and without cover throughout the race, failed to run on.
Moderate start, settled midfield on rail, failed to run on in the straight, raced disappointingly.
No pace, racing one-out behind midfield. Switched out turning for home, taken to centre field on straightening, finished strongly to win close home.
Away nicely, moved forward settling one-out, one-back. Blocked for run on entering straight, got clear 200m, finished strongly but no match for winner final strides.
Forced to race wide early, then failed to settle when checked 1300m to obtain cover. Checked again 1100m and kept 4-wide to turn. Finished strongly to grab minor placing.
Ridden forward but kept wide, left without cover from 1100m and allowed to improve to sit 3-wide outside leader at turn in. Kept on well to 200m before tiring.
Used inside draw to hold rail at midfield but got shuffled back turn and switched out to get clear running. Finished off nicely in straight to be closest at finish.
Ridden along between horses behind early pace, keeping within striking distance to 200m before coming under pressure and tiring.
Bumped and unbalanced start, no pace, dropping one-out towards rear. Taken wide on entering straight and finished off fairly. (Had substantial amount of mucus in trachea)
Pressed forward from an outside draw to lead on settling, crossing to fence 1100m and slowing pace. Joined up front 400m, kept on gamely to 200m before tiring.
Jumped well, pushed forward, racing outside hindquarters of leader to turn. Took over running 400m, caught 200m, faded.
Jumped well, ridden to hold box seat 2L from leader. Kept tabs to 300m when came under pressure and faded.
Jumped OK, taken to rail but stranded towards rear by slow pace. Switched out turning for home and ran on fairly.
Snagged back soon after start to get cover but not suited by slow pace and shuffled back to last. Raced fiercely to turn, plodded home in straight.
Steadied soon after start and shifted in for cover, dropping towards rear along rail. Improved position slightly turning for home but one-paced in straight.
Away well, grabbed rail 3L from leader, before over-racing. Came under pressure turning for home before fading in straight.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced 2 wide in midfield, same position on turn, finished off strongly in straight to score narrowly.
Average to begin, sent forward to sit outside the leader, there to turn, kept on very well in straight but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Away with them, taken back to race 2 wide in 7th, angled out near 500M, made very good progress in straight to get 3rd.
Jumped well, took the lead easily, travelled well throughout, headed early in straight, stayed on evenly.
Began well from gate 1, positioned a length or so back on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight and finished off evenly without threatening.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 6 lengths or so back at rear, slightly improved on turn, taken widest in straight and made some progress.
Began fairly, positioned 3 lengths or so back on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off one-paced.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths back in 4th, emptied early in straight.
Taken back from gate 9, difficult to settle early, raced at tail to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Crowded out start, positioned on rail at rear, well back on turn, emptied early in straight and eased, finished tailed out, unacceptable performance.
Raced in the box-seat, sat 1-3/4L off, held up until 300M, found extra at 150M and closed off gamely to score by 2L.
Sat just off the leaders, 3/4L behind but wide and without cover, kept on going to the finish.
Sent forward and shared lead by 3/4L in a 2 wide position, fought on but had to be straightened at 200M.
Pushed forward and shared lead by 3/4L along the rail, battled on but was no match.
Jumped well and sat fore of midfield, 1-1/4L off 2 wide, ran on fairly to the line.
Settled to race in midfield, 1-3/4L off 3 wide with cover, under whip at 600M, closed off only one paced.
Raced at the rear, 3-1/4L behind and wide, pushed to keep up from 600M, failed to make ground. (Lame left front leg)
Slow to jump, settled in behind midfield, 2-3/4L behind 2 wide, uncompetitive in the straight.
Lifted feet off at start and lost ground, stayed back, never in it. (Heart irregularity)
Away well, settling one-out 3L from leader 800m. Moved up 3-wide turning for home, finished strongly to hit front close home, pulling clear.
Began awkwardly, punched forward to sit 1L behind leader 800m. Rolled forward home turn to lead passing 400m, strongly challenged from 200m, beaten final strides.
Steadied and shifted in for cover soon after start, settling one-out towards rear. Taken wide entering straight and finished off strongly under big weight.
Ridden early to hold forward position, settling in box seat 2L from leader. Closed in turning form home, boxed on gamely in straight without looking dangerous.
Ridden early but failed to muster, settling along rail 4L from leader. Got clear run entering straight, made some headway before turning one-paced final 200m.
Found early pace too hot, dropping to rear along rail. Stayed on rail entering straight but only one-paced.
Used early to lead on settling, then slowed pace passing 800m. Under pressure when joined up front turning for home, faded from 400m.
Unable to handle pace despite being niggled at, trailing field throughout. Never competitive.
Not hurried early stages, sat towards the rear 5Ls off a slow pace, bustled along 500M, closed off strongly final 200M to lead in the shadow of the post.
Travelled smoothly just behind leaders, on straightening chased strongly, improved to the lead 150M, couldn't hold off fast finishing winner late.
Awkwardly away, held up behind midfield 3-4Ls off a slow pace, improved along the 3-path from 600M, kept coming to the line for close 3rd.
Raced prominently outside leader, pace slow for the first half, took over 500M leading the sprint home, headed 150M, faded to 4th.
Chased leaders in a slowly run race, kept up the chase to 150M when crowded for room and lost a bit of momentum, could be closer.
Dropped back to the rear from the outside gate, checked near 800M and raced ungenerously for some distance, took a while to get going inside 400M, boxed on well late.
Held up near the rear, not helped by the slow tempo middle stages, didn't quite finish off when driven out in straight.
Crossed to the lead passing 1100M, slowed down the pace once in front, lost lead inside 500M, tired mid-straight and weakened towards the line.
In mid-division 3Ls off the pace in 5th, inconvenienced when pace slackened 900M, couldn't keep up with rivals inside 300M. Never a threat.
Settled at the rear of the field, checked 850M, off the bridle and didn't travel comfortably from this point thereon, detached top of straight and eased over final 300M. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Began fairly, pressed forward to sit in slipstream of leader to turn. Switched out on straightening, given reminders, hit front 150m, pulled clear.
Speared to the front, quickly cross to fence 2L clear on settling. Set good pace to straight, collared passing 150m, battled on strongly.
Jumped well, not pressed, settling one-out behind midfield 5L from leader. Turned wide, finished strongly down centre track to grab minor placing. (Small wound above inside left hock)
Away OK, not pushed, settling along rail 5L from leader. Switched out turning for home, finished off nicely to just miss a placing.
Ridden to hold forward position, racing one-out 2L from leader. Had clear running entering straight but only one-paced, tiring final strides.
Began fairly, no pace, dropped towards rear along rail. Improved slightly around home turn, kept on fairly in straight.
Began well, taken to box seat 3L from leader. Kept tabs to straight when found nothing under pressure and faded.
Began fairly, ridden along but wide towards rear. Severely checked and taken wider to avoid mishap 550m, boxed on down centre track.
Inconvenienced start, hampered 850m when racing at rear. Severely checked 550m to avoid mishap, found nothing when asked in straight.
Began well, pushed forward but steadied 1050m to obtain cover 4L from leader. Lost position turning for home, faded in straight.
Steadied on jumping and shifted in, dropping to rear. Checked 650m, severely checked 550m to avoid mishap, after which eased down, finished tailed out.

Placing: UR
Comment: Steadied on jumping and shifted in, racing one-out behind midfield. Dislodged rider 550m and finished riderless. (Small wounds inside right front cannon and right hock)

Broke well and pushed forward before electing to drop back to find cover in midfield. Pressed forward from the top of the straight and ran strongly to the line. Grabbed the lead 20m out and still pulling away on line.
Pushed out early to make sure he led. Cleared out in the straight, but ran out of petrol late and was nabbed near the finish.

Dropped back early to sit midfield. Drifted towards the rear of the field around the 600m. Wide on the turn and sat in the last couple. Showed great turn of foot in the straight and was only one making ground on the winner late.
Hampered on jumping and dropped back to sit last. Held the rail on the run home and stayed on solidly late.
Took usual position at the back of the field early. Raced keenly in middle stages and was checked off heels at 800 and 700m. Came wider on the turn, and ran solidly to the line.
Cruised forward early to sit around midfield. Progressed steadily early in the straight, but ran flat late.
Pressed forward from the inside draw to sit just behind the early leader, on the fence. 1 paced in the straight, and not pushed out late.

Slowly away and dropped back to sit towards the rear of the field. Keen in back straight and came wide when awkward on heels 650m. Widest on turn. One paced in the straight, and picked up some slower ones late.
Fairly away, but recovered well enough to settle just forward of midfield. Awkward on heels 500m. Hampered and lost run at 300m, and didn't press on from there.
Pressed forward early and was stuck 3-4 wide in the back straight. Bumped at 500m. Started to fade at the top of the straight, and made no impact in the run home. Vet- Blood in trachea.
Pressed forward early to sit just behind the leaders, 3rd/4th with cover. Never responded to riding in the straight, and dropped back through the field quickly. Jockey questioned.
Pushed hard early from the wide draw, sitting wide with no cover, to eventually share the lead at 600m. Had nothing left in the run home and faded out quickly.

Jumped well, settled in 4th 2-wide within 3L of pace, commenced move entering straight, hit the front under pressure inside the 200 metres, won readily.
Settled in rear of midfield in 5th on the rail, shifted out for a run upon straightening, made moderate headway under pressure without threatening the winner.
Moderate start, trailed the field most of way to the home bend, ran on quite well down the centre of the straight but without threatening.
Began fairly, settled one back in 3rd on the rail, went off the rail turning in but soon shifted back in and faded gradually under pressure.
Well back, widest into the straight, fought on steadily in the centre of the track.
Broke well from the widest gate to quickly take up running on the rail passing the 1000 metres, led the field until weakened under pressure inside the final 200 metres.
Pressed forward from a middle gate, settled just off the lead, weakened under pressure upon straightening.
Settled behind midfield in 6th, in similar position entering home straight, found nothing.
Hard ridden forward, just off the leader, benefited by the slow sectionals, led 300M, ran on well to score.
Hard ridden early, midfield 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 200M for 2nd.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, suited by the slow pace but was taken to 3 wide after 600M, ran on well to the line for 3rd.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, favoured by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Bumped start, took rail at back, harmed by the slow pace, blocked most straight, dashed well.
Eased back, 2 wide, lack room 4-2, dashed well despite not suited by the slow pace.
At back along the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, little dash in straight.
Hard ridden forward, took rail and led at slow sectionals, however soon emptied 300M.
Started well, pushed along to take handy position, asked for effort in the early straight, came home strongly, dead-heats winner.
Taken back at start, raced behind midfield, commenced to improve passing 500M, widest on straightening, quickened passing 100M, dead-heats winner.
Began fairly, settled behind midfield on rail, approaching 1400M and 700M checked, improved passing 400M, fought hard in the straight, worked home solidly.
Settled behind midfield, commenced to improve passing 650M, battled hard entire straight, finished well.
Pushed to settle in front of midfield on rail, tried to improve at Home Turn, finished OK.
Moderate start, travelled well to take lead, under pressure but one-paced in the straight.
Raced midfield on rail, asked for effort passing 500M, one-paced.
Settled midfield, moved forward to improve passing 900M, no response in the straight.
Taken back at start, settled at tail, faded out passing 600M, must trial.
Taken back at start, settled at tail, never in it, must trial.

Placing: PU
Comment: Jumped well, took box seat, approaching 700M gave ground abruptly, pulled up. Bled and irregular heart rhythm.
Quickly away, got close to heels before settling in box seat 700m. Switched out top of straight to get clear running and powered home, pulling clear final 150m.
Vigorously ridden to lead from the jump, pulling 2L clear 700m before easing pace. Kicked ahead top of straight but caught 150m out. Boxed on gamely.
Out OK, then ridden to hold midfield position, one away from fence. Taken wide in straight and finished strongly to grab minor placing on line.
Restrained and shifted in soon after start to find cover, racing one-out towards rear. Taken to centre track on straightening and finished off nicely.
Hard ridden early to hold one-back, one-out position, then niggled at to stay with pace around turn. Battled on gamely in straight.
Jumped well, pressed forward, racing one-out 2L from leader. Surged forward top of straight to look a chance but only one-paced final 200m.
Away nicely, taken to rail 3L from leader and settled. Stayed on rail throughout and kept on fairly in straight.
Shifted across behind runners from an outside draw, dropping to last pair on settling. Put under pressure turning for home but only one-paced in straight.
Got off OK but unable match early pace, dropping behind midfield along rail. Shaken up top of straight but limited response.
Shifted across behind runners from a wide draw and last on settling. Remained at the rear throughout and never in the hunt.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, slightly improved on turn, finished off very strongly in straight to score.

Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail in the early stages, improved from 900M, took the lead near 650M, travelled well on turn, kept on very well in straight but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Taken back from gate 7, raced 2 wide at rear, slightly improved near 800M, 4 lengths or so back on turn, made good progress in straight to get 3rd.
Began well from the widest gate, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide throughout, peaked shortly after turning in, stayed on evenly to the line.
Jumped well from barrier 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, positioned a length or so back on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, ridden in the middle stages, but only showed limited response, failed to close off in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced 5 to 6 lengths back on rail at rear, kept to inside after turning in, failed to close off.
Began well, took the lead easily, enjoyed the easy lead in the early stages, headed near 700M, unbalanced near 600M, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Raced at rear throughout, weakened from 550M, finished tailed off.
In behind midfield initially, moved after 900M and took outright lead at 600M, pulled away upon straightening, held on to score by 1-3/4L.
Eased and raced at the rear, 5L behind along the rail, made nice ground and ran on strongly to the line.
Raced in worse than midfield, 4-1/2L behind 2 wide, made good ground and fought on well.
Settled to race in behind midfield, 3-1/2L behind along the fence, saved ground and kept on fairly to the line.
Raced in about midfield, sat 3L behind 2 wide, finished off mostly one paced in the straight.
At the rear initially in a 2 wide, improved after 900M and raced prominently, finished off one paced.
Sent forward and sat outside the lead, sat 1/2L off, niggled to maintain position after 550M, one paced home.
Settled one-off one-back, 1-3/4L off, dropped to midfield after 700M, taken in and was unbalanced near 550M, one paced.
Rolled forward into the lead, led by 1/2L along the rail, crossed after 600M, flattened out after 200M.
Raced in box-seat, sat 1-1/2L off, dropped when others improved at 700M, checked at 500M, never recovered.
Jumped OK, hard ridden to hold rail inside leader before putting head in front 1000m. Narrowly headed 800m to 350m, retook lead, strongly challenged final 200m, just held.
Away well, racing between horses at front before easing 1L back around home turn. Entered straight 3-wide and finished strongly to just miss out.
Steadied on jumping and taken in for cover in midfield but failed to settle and over-raced. Swung wide into straight, taken to centre track and finished strongly to grab minor placing.
Hard ridden from outside draw, racing 3-wide outside early leader before poking head in front passing 800m. Kept wide around turn, overtaken 350m, but kept battling to line.
Beaten for early pace, dropping behind midfield but away from fence. Swung wide into straight and finished off nicely to be closest at finish.
Ridden early to stay close to pace, one-away from fence. Taken wide entering straight, bumped and unbalanced 200m, kept on gamely.
Jumped OK, ridden early to hold position before taken to rail behind midfield 800m. Turned in behind horses, shifted out for run, kept on fairly.
Shifted across behind runners from outside draw and last on settling but away from fence. Taken to centre track in straight and finished off nicely.
Jumped well, taken to fence, settling 2L from leader. Brushed rail and unbalanced 600m but maintained position. Got close to heels final stages and not ridden out.
Unable handle early pace, dropping to rear but away from fence. Had to be ridden 500m to hold position, got close to heels in straight, kept on fairly.
Bumped, no pace, dropping to rear along fence. Stayed on rail throughout, made up some ground early straight but not tested close home.
Pressed forward from an outside draw, settling one-out 2L from leader back stretch. Urged forward 4-wide turning for home but run out of puff 200m and faded.
Travelled smoothly in midfield, saved ground, brought out to challenge 300M, under gradual acceleration got up near the finish.
Tracked leader on the outside, raced up to the lead at 250M, kept on gamely to line, caught late.
Guided to a position ahead of midfield, gave a good kick final 300M, came very close and was just held.
Reserved in midfield about 6Ls behind leader, brought wide to challenge 400M, ran on well to be nearest at the finish.
From draw 12 slotted into a 2-wide spot just behind leaders, pushed along 450M, went 2nd 200M and kept chasing leader, swamped by pursuers late.
Away well enough from inside draw, sat behind leaders, moved out to challenge nearing 400M, kept on evenly on straightening, run ended 150M.
Began awkwardly, held up near last 8-9Ls off the moderate pace, made some ground at the finish without threatening.
Bumped by rival after the jump, guided to the fence and settled near the rear 9Ls off the pace, passed a few in straight without threatening.
Taken back from wide draw, settled at the rear over 10Ls off the moderate pace, still last 300M, stayed on only fairly to line but awkwardly placed 100M and not properly tested late.
Led steadily along the rail, headed nearing 200M, weakened rapidly towards the finish. (Sore hindlimb action next day.)
Held up behind mid-division, in 8th place 7-8Ls off the pace, made no ground in the home run, weakened away 200M.
Not hurried after the start, settled down in 9th place 8Ls off the pace, couldn't go on 400M, dropped out.
