Ridden to lead, made all, soon drew clear after straightening.
Unbalanced at start, inconvenienced at the 1100 metres, towards the rear rounding home bend, fought on steadily in straight to claim 2nd final strides.
Settled just off the pace on the rail, raced awkwardly behind the leader rounding home bend, failed to quicken to threaten and lost 2nd final strides.
Travelled wide in midfield, drifted slightly backward to 6th coming onto home bend, fought on steadily in straight to narrowly miss the place-getters.

Moderate start, taken back from a wide gate, towards the rear on the rail when checked and lost position 850m out, trailed the field on home bend, shifted out for a run 250m out, produced good late impression under pressure.
Broke well, taken back to just better than midfield, remained without cover most of the way, kept on before fading under pressure inside the final 200 metres.
Jumped fairly, soon picked up to a prominent 2-wide position just off the pace, faded steadily under pressure in the straight.
Crowded at the start and inconvenienced coming onto home bend, remained in last few most of the way, never nearer.
Taken back from a wide gate, raced wide without cover well behind far side, made short-lived effort rounding home bend, no further impression.
Crowded at start, soon recovered to midfield position on the rail, dropped away quickly inside the final 300 metres.
Hard ridden to keep up at back, suited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 400M and scored.
Pressed forward to share the lead, harmed by the fast pace, led 450M, hung on until 150M overhauled.
At back, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M for 3rd.
Settled just off the leaders in midfield, just held ground in final stages.
Pushed to keep up with the leaders, not suited by the fast tempo, held ground.
Hard ridden to keep up with the field at back, favoured by the fast pace, ran on ok.
Pushed early, midfield, not suited by the fast tempo, ran on fairly.
Shared the lead easily, not suited by the fast sectionals, out of fuel 200M.
Hard ridden to share the lead at fast sectionals, ran on until 200M emptied.
Never a factor, tailed out.
Started well, settled midfield, drifted back passing 900M, improved approaching 700M, widest on straightening, quickened in the straight, finished strongly.
Pushed after start, raced midfield, after 900M was left racing wide and without cover, commenced to improve approaching 700M, made ground in the straight, came home solidly.
Travelled well to take lead, asked effort in the early straight, battled hard in the final stages.
Urged along after start, settled behind midfield, made ground passing 200M, fought well in the concluding stages.
Taken back at start, settled behind midfield on rail, commenced to improve at Home turn, worked home well.
Began only fairly, raced midfield on rail, tried to improve passing 700M, under pressure in the straight, finished fairly.
After start ridden along but failed to muster speed, settled at tail, one-paced in the straight.
Slow to muster speed after start, travelled wide and without cover till passing 1000M, then raced behind leaders, weakened at Home Turn, failed to run on.
After start hard ridden but failed to muster speed, raced wide and without cover till 900M, then raced outside leader, faded out in the early straight.
Gave ground passing 1000M, no response despite been ridden along, must trial.
Jumped well but outpaced, dropping one-out towards rear. Niggled at home turn, given reminder 400m, switched to centre track 280m, finished strongly to win close home.
Lifted leg at start losing ground and dropping to rear. Improved position home turn, raced tight early straight, shifted in 200m for clear run, looked winner 100, run down.
Jumped OK, not pushed, racing one-out behind midfield. Pumped up turning for home, swung wide entering straight, finished off strongly.
Pressed forward, crossing to rail 1000m, then hard ridden to hold position a half-length inside leader to straight. Hit front 250m, collared 100m, swamped final strides.
Jumped well, taken to rail, settling 4L from leader. Switched out turning for home, steadied 300m, taken wide in straight, finished off nicely.
Outpaced, dropping to behind midfield along rail. Stayed on rail around turn and in straight, ran on steadily.
Shifted in for cover soon after start, dropping to last. Trailed field to straight, ran on fairly.
Began awkwardly, pressed forward inside leading pack before being eased 2L back along rail 1000m. Switched out 400m, kept on well to 200m before tiring.
Hard ridden from outside draw to lead on settling, but forced to race wide to straight. Spent force soon after straightening and faded.
Bounced well, pressed forward, settling one-out, one-back. Under pressure turning for home, hard ridden to hold position to 200m, faded.
Away OK, ridden along one-out at midfield to turn. Hard ridden in straight but ran to of stamina 200m and faded.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back, improved from near 600M, finished off strongly to score.
Jumped well from the widest gate, showed early speed to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead to turn, kept on well in straight but couldn't hold off the winner in the final stages.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 6 to 7 lengths back at rear, slightly improved on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to get 3rd.
Began well, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths back, same margin back on turn, steadied near 450M, no daylight early in straight, made good progress when clear thereafter, just missed 3rd.
Average to begin, unable to slot in early, sent forward to race in 2nd, same position on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and bumped near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 1 to 2 lengths back on rail, easy run to turn, angled out near 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Taken back to race on rail behind midfield, angled out and slightly improved on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, raced at tail, 7 lengths or so back, gave very limited response when asked for efforts on turn, failed to make up any ground in straight.
Slowly away, recovered to race 3 to 4 lengths back on rail in midfield, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away from a middle draw, unable to slot in early, taken back to race 2 wide, 6 lengths back, carried wider on turn, emptied early in straight.
Rolled forward to race in box-seat, sat 1-1/2L off, kept on going and found extra near 100M to close off for the win.
Jumped well and race outside the lead, about 1L off, led from 250M until caught by winner at 150M, ran on well.
Raced in behind midfield, 5L behind along the rail, closed off nicely inside 150M to take 3rd.
Fractious in barriers, settled in midfield 3-1/2L behind along the rail, kept on going and finished off well for 4th.
Sent forward and led the field by about 1L, lay out throughout, weakened and caught near 250M.
Settled to race in midfield, 4-1/2L behind 2 wide, kept on going to the line.
Steadied after start, raced in behind midfield, 5-3/4L behind 2 wide, made minor ground and finished off okay.
Eased and raced towards the rear, 6-1/2L behind 2 wide, finished off only one paced.
Pushed and settled in one-off one-back position, about 2-1/2L off, flattened passing 200M.
Settled in about midfield, 4-1/4L behind but wide, found nothing in the straight.
Always at the rear, never a factor.
First out, set good pace along outer fence under a hold. Shaken up passing 300m and pulled clear to win comfortably.
Away well but unable to cross to outer fence, settling behind midfield. Popped the question passing 400m, picked up momentum and finished strongly to grab 2nd close home.
Ridden early to hold midfield position, two-away from outer fence. Switched out passing 400m for clear run, finishing strongly to snatch minor placing.
Began well, pressed forward, racing three-away from outer fence 2L from leader. Set off after leader from 400m to look a chance but ran out of steam close home.
Quickly out, matching strides with leader before settling a half-length back passing 800m. Under pressure to hold position final 400m and tired close home.
Restless in starting gate and slow into stride, dropping well back. Taken to centre track half way up the straight and ran on steadily to be closest at finish.
Away well, pressed forward 3-away from outer fence, 2L from leader. Hard ridden from 400m to hold position before tiring close home.
Outpaced, racing behind midfield to course proper when lost position and shifted in. Ran on fairly down centre track.
Ridden to hold forward positon, settling along outer rail 4L from leader. Under pressure from half-way mark but only one-paced.
Crowded out start, then ridden along between horses behind midfield to 400m, boxed on one-paced.
Began well, pressed forward, 4L from leader but kept away from outer fence. Under pressure final 400m and faded.
Jumped well, crossed over towards outer fence, settling 4L from leader. Under pressure from 500m and faded gradually despite hard riding.
Lifted feet at the start and began only fairly, dropping to last on settling. Never in the hunt.
Outpaced and soon struggling at the rear, never competitive.
Always prominent, chased leader along 2-path, dueled with the leader passing 250M, kept coming and eventually gained upper hand late stages.
Urged along from draw 11 and crossed to the lead passing 900M, driven out 300M, went head to head with rival, drifted out under pressure, gave way late stages.
Dropped back to near the rear, came 3-wide home turn, closed off willingly to claim 3rd near line but couldn't get closer to front pair.
Held up 2-wide in midfield, moved closer home turn to be 2L off the pace at 400M, kept on solidly to the finish but well held by first 2, lost 3rd late.
Restrained behind mid-division, 4Ls off the pace turning in, stayed on mildly for respectable 5th.
Taken back behind runners from wide draw, settled at the rear 6-7Ls off the pace middle stages, brought widest into straight, made steady ground but no impression on the front runners.
Never far off from leaders but couldn't come on inside 300M, only battled away.
From draw 12 caught 3-wide no cover just off the pace, couldn't quicken to challenge leaders despite clear running inside 400M, out of contention mid-straight.
Away well enough, sat back in midfield along the rail, just didn't let down on straightening, never going pace to challenge.
Slow to begin, settled at the rear 7Ls off the pace early stages, couldn't quicken on straightening, never a threat.
Dropped back towards the rear, 2nd last turning in and didn't run on. Never a factor.
Went forward, sat behind leader along rail, couldn't keep up passing 300M, weakened to last.
Quickly away, switched out, settling 2L from leader but 3-away from outer fence. Niggled at passing 450m, set off after leader, poking nose in front at the line.
Jumped well, taken to outer fence and set good pace. Put under pressure 600m when strongly challenged and kept finding until nosed out final stride.
Got off OK, pressed forward between horses, settling 4L from leader. Hard ridden final 400m to grab minor placing on line.
Outpaced, dropping well back along outer fence. Disappointed for run halfway up the straight, shifted in 300m to get clear, ran on well. (Lost right front plate near 500m).
No pace, dropping well back. Picked up momentum halfway up the straight and ran on steadily down centre track to be closest at finish.
Began fairly, pressed forward between horses to join leaders passing 600m. Kept tabs to 200m when ran out of steam and faded.
Began awkwardly, then ridden to hold midfield position one-away from outer fence. Kept tabs to 400m but only one-paced when put under pressure.
Hard ridden to stay with early pace, 3L from leader one-away from outer fence. Kept tabs to 400m when one-paced.
Quickly out, shared early pace before dropping 1L back, one-way from outer fence 800m. Moved up to share lead passing 600m but tired quickly final 400m and faded.
Jumped OK, unable to cross to outer fence and held on centre track behind midfield. Put under pressure final 400m but only one-paced.
Bumped and unbalanced start, pressed forward along outer rail 1L from leader. Unable quicken when pace increased final 500m, faded 200m while laying-in.
No early pace and held between horses behind midfield. One-paced in straight.
Outpaced and became detached from field halfway up the straight. Plodded home.
Jumped OK but reluctant to stride out and soon detached from field. Eased down after 400m and finished tailed out.
Began awkwardly and lost ground. Recovered to push to midfield. Wider on the turn. Battled hard in the straight and just held on to the win late.
Eased back early to settle worse than midfield. Came wider on the turn for a clear run. Ran strongly in the straight, and showed good turn off foot in the last 100m to get 2nd late.
Eased out early to sit forward of midfield, 1 off the fence. Had to come in off heels at 350m for clear running. Strong run to the line, and just lost 2nd in the shadows of the post.
Dropped back early to sit at the rear of the field. Came down the extreme outside in the straight, and ran steadily to the line. Finished well late.
Taken forward early to settle 2nd/3rd, on the fence. Ran well early in the straight and lead until the 100m. Peaked soon after and dropped back late.
Eased out early and dropped back to sit at the rear of the field, on the fence. Angled off heels at the 150, and stayed on solidly late.
Taken up early to settle forward of midfield, 3 wide with limited cover. Battled on 1 paced, without ever really threatening a place.
Cruised forward early to settle midfield, on the rail. Went to the line 1 paced and made no real impact.

Taken up early to settle forward of midfield, on the fence. Held up early in the straight and unbalanced when bumped at 300m. Stayed on steadily in the straight without threatening and accepted things late.
Steadied off heels on jumping and dropped back to sit last. Plugged on in the straight and went past some of the slower ones.
Dropped back early to sit towards the rear of the field, pushing to worse than midfield at 1000m. Came wider on the turn, but made very little inroads in the straight.
Pressed forward early and settled 3rd/4th, 1 off the fence. Dropped out quickly from the 250m.
Pushed forward from the wide draw to lead. Nothing in the tank late and dropped out rapidly from the 250m mark.
Bounded out and pushed forward from the wide draw to sit 2nd, but stuck wide no cover. Had nothing left in the straight and dropped out quickly.

Settled in last few, commenced move rounding home bend, widest runner turning for home, ran on well down the centre of the track, asserted authority close to home.
Settled just off the pace on the rail, niggled along from far side, chased the leader in 2nd into straight, hit the front from tiring leader passing the 50 metres only to be headed close to home.

Moderate start, towards the rear when steadied at the 950 metres, remained in last few on the rail to the home straight, switched out for a run 250 metres out, ran on near the centre of the track to be nearest at finish.
Taken back from a wide gate, finished off race well inside the 300 metres down the centre of the track.
Settled at the back, saved ground on the rail turning in, ran on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Broke well to hold slender lead, went over 1L clear coming onto home bend, unable to sustain effort and overhauled inside the final 100 metres.
Ridden early from the middle draw, settled in midfield on the rail, saved ground turning for home, kept on steadily without quickening in the straight.
Inconvenienced approaching the 1000-metre bend, travelled just worse than midfield on the rail to the straight, saved ground turning for home, fought on steadily under pressure.
Jumped well from a wide gate and raced 3-wide, taken back to 6th about 3L off the pace, came under pressure after straightening but baulked for a run from the 250 metres to 150 metres.
Disputed lead, drifted one back rounding home bend, folded up quickly after straightening.

Jumped awkwardly losing ground, soon recovered to prominent position within 2L of the pace, 3-wide back in 4th when coming under pressure approaching the home turn, soon found no extra. (Lame next day)
Drawn wide and remained wide throughout, hard ridden to join the leaders briefly 800 metres out, yielded ground under pressure from approaching the home bend.
At back, 2-3 wide, pace good, made steady ground 300M to score.
Eased back, 2 wide, pace good, progressed steadily 300M, just missed by a narrow margin in 2nd.
Pushed to take rail and early lead, pace good, ran on well for 3rd.
Eased back, took rail, pace good, made early move 900M, led 600M, hung on until 200M flattened.
Hard ridden forward, took rail, pace good, no dash in straight.
Eased back, 2 wide, pace good, made the move around the field in 4 wide from 600M, checked 200M, flattened.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, pace good, flattened 300M.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, pace good, emptied 600M.
Trapped 3 wide throughout, moved forward 800M, dropped off quickly 500M.
Ridden along after start, travelled outside the leader, improved at Home Turn, closed off strongly.
Travelled well to take box seat, quickened passing 200M, worked home solidly, missed by neck.
Jumped OK, settled midfield, tried to improve in mid race, fought hard in the straight, came home strongly.
After start tight for room and settled behind midfield, commenced to improve after 700M, made ground passing 50M, finished satisfactorily.
Eased back and raced back on rail in early stages, moved forward passing 700M, made up nice late ground, finished well.
Jumped well, settled midfield, tried to improve passing 500M, finished OK.
Raced midfield on rail, asked for effort at Home Turn, one-paced in the straight.
Taken back at start, settled at tail, under pressure in the straight, one-paced.
At the start became unbalanced, raced behind midfield on rail, raced tight approaching 1200M, weakened passing 100M.
Settled behind midfield, saddle shifted and after 1350M travelled wide and without cover, failed to run on.
Started well to take lead, tiring badly after passing 200M, failed to close off.
Pressed forward from widest draw to lead on settling but kept away from fence until 1100m when crossed in. Kicked ahead top of straight and kept on strongly to the line.
Snagged back after start, dropping towards rear. Began forward move passing 600m, circled field 5-wide, finished strongly down centre track to grab quinella spot.
Away well, shared early pace before dropping 1L behind leader back stretch. Hard ridden on straightening but unable catch leader.
Scrubbed up inside leading pack to hold rail at first turn, then raced in slipstream when leader crossed over 1100m. Chased leader on straight though raced tight closing stages.
Jumped well, ridden but didn't muster, settling between horses behind midfield. Under pressure turning for home and ran on steadily without looking dangerous.
Bumped after start, then ridden to hold rail in midfield. Lost position home turn, ran on steadily in straight, shifting in 75m when tightened for room.
Pushed forward to hold rail soon after start but not enough speed, settling 3L from leader back stretch. Ran on fairly in straight though raced tight closing stages.
Ridden forward, settling one-back, one-out to straight. Boxed on gamely before checked 200m, losing position.
Pressed forwards from an outside draw but held wide 4L from leader on settling. Covered extra ground throughout and tired close home.
Began OK but outpaced, dropping towards rear, then raced keenly around first turn. Never in the hunt.
Restrained after jump and shifted across behind runners, settling at rear. Last on entering straight and finished tailed out. (Unacceptable performance).
Began well, raced 3 lengths or so back on rail, saved ground to turn, finished off strongly in straight to score narrowly.

Jumped well from a wide draw, showed good speed to take the early lead, settled in 2nd in the middle stages, kept on very well after turning in, took the lead near final 100M, but couldn't hold off the winner on line.
Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, easy lead in the middle stages, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near final 100M, stayed on for 3rd.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back in 3rd, same position on turn, finished off evenly in straight without threatening.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 8 to 9 lengths back at rear, gradually improved in the middle stages, made some headway in straight without threatening the first few.
Crowded out start, raced on rail in midfield, 6 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Bumped start, unable to slot in early, taken back to race 2 wide, 6 to 7 lengths back, same position on turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Began only fairly from gate 1, race at tail, crowded near 1050M and checked near 850M, still well back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Crowded out start, positioned on rail behind midfield, bumped near 600M, still 9 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide in midfield, peaked on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide at rear, still 9 lengths back on turn, emptied early in straight.
Slightly slow out, positioned on rail at rear, there to turn, emptied early in straight, never a threat. (Lost left hind plate after the 800M.)
Eased and raced towards the tail, moved closer to midfield passing 800M, closed off strongly to score by 1-1/2L.
In front of midfield, sat 2-1/4L off along the rail until taken to 2 wide at 1000M, ran on well but no match to winner.
Pushed forward, took rail and led by about 1L from 1200M, kept on going but couldn't hold off the winner passing 50M.
Settled to race outside the lead and sat 1L off, kept going and finished off well to the line.
In worse than midfield, 4-3/4L behind along the rail, improved slightly until run was interrupted from near 150M.
Sent forward, settled for cover behind the lead, sat about 2L off, steadied at 100M although mostly one paced.
Rolled forward, prominent until checked prior to 1400M, in midfield thereafter, 3-1/2L off along the rail, one paced.
Bumped start then remained at the tail, 7L behind along the rail, swung wide and was one paced in the straight.
Began only fairly, settled in midfield 4L behind 2 wide, tightened at 300M, slight dash before flattening at 150M.
Taken back and raced at the rear, did not improve.
In midfield before taken to 3 wide without cover at 1000M, ridden along in the back straight, gave ground from 500M.
Began fairly, ridden to hold rail, settling 4L from leader. Niggled at home turn, slipped through opening on rail 240m and finished strongly for comfortable win.
No early pace, travelling one-out towards rear to home turn. Taken to centre track on straightening and finished strongly to grab 2nd spot.
Began awkwardly then crowded, dropping back along rail. Kept well back to straight before closing off strongly despite having to shift in 100m to avoid tightening.
Jumped well, surged forward to open 2L lead on settling. Set steady pace to straight, strongly challenged from 250m, but kept on gamely while drifting out until swamped close home.
Quickly away, pressed forward, settling one-out 2L from leader. Rolled forward on straightening to look a chance, kept on gamely till running out of steam close home.
Ridden forward from an outside draw but not much pace and held three wide behind midfield. Boxed on gamely in straight but met interference close home and not ridden out.
Ridden to hold forward position, settling between horses 3L from leader. Stayed in contention in straight but bumped and unbalanced 100m losing position.
Ridden to hold midfield positon 5L from leader. Swung wide entering straight, ran on steadily before meeting interference close home. Not ridden out.
Jumped well, pressed forward to hold box seat 2L from leader. Hard ridden in straight to hold position but ran out of steam close home and faded.
Pressed forward from an outside draw and forced to race 3-wide mostly, 2L from leader. Boxed on well in straight but checked 100m and tightened 50m while tiring.
Steadied after start and shifted across behind runners, settling one-out in last pair. Remained at rear throughout and one-paced in straight.
Steadied on jumping and shifted in to hold rail, dropping to last. Trailed field throughout and never in contention.
Began awkwardly, recovered to race in 4th within striking distance from leader, chased hard just got up in the shadows of the post.
Dropped back from draw 12, raced keenly towards the rear, 5Ls off the pace home turn, restricted room 200M, fought on strong to line, just denied.
Crossed to the lead 1000M, took then along steadily, responded well to riding on straightening, only caught final 2 strides.
Tracked leader in a steadily run race, kept finding the line well, came close to win only edged out to 4th in bunch finish.
Reserved in midfield along the 3-path, worked home steadily down the outside but couldn't reel in leaders.
Held up midfield along the fence, 3-4Ls off leader home turn, worked home well under hands and heels riding and not clear run concluding stages. (Jockey questioned re his riding over final 100M.)
Began well from draw 1, travelled keenly behind leader, kept on inside 300M, outsprinted by pursuers final 100M.
Restrained near the rear along the inside, 5Ls off the pace turning home, made some ground from 300M until out of room late stages and not ridden out.
Began awkwardly, travelled in midfield along the 2-path, battled on only fairly turning home, no threat from 200M.
Caught wide no cover from draw 10, never far off from leaders, couldn't muster the speed to challenge inside 300M, didn't threaten.
Jumped on terms before easing back to last, 6-7Ls off the pace rounding home turn, didn't respond to riding.
Not hurried after the jump, settled down towards the rear 3-wide, failed to finish off when brought wide to challenge in straight.

Settled in the midfield of the small field, commenced move entering the straight, quickened well to take charge inside the final 200 metres, won readily.
Well there, soon took up running at the centre of the back straight, crossed to the rail passing the 1100 metres, led until overhauled by the winner inside the final 200 metres. (Mucus in trachea)
Well there, settled just off the pace mainly in 3rd, came under pressure after straightening, produced good late impression inside the final 200 metres to snatch 3rd late.
Settled in the midfield of the small field on the rail, saved ground turning for home, fought on steadily inside the final 250 metres but without threatening.
Settled towards the rear on the rail, made modest progress under pressure without threatening.
Hard ridden early, chased the leader to the straight, faded.
Slightly slow out, niggled at early stages, settled in 6th towards the rear, switched wide for a run entering straight, failed to make any impression in the run home.
Always well behind, made brief effort out wide rounding home bend, never a factor. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Pushed to occupy box seat, not suited by the fast tempo, drifted away 250M to score.
Pushed to take rail and lead, clocked fast sectionals, hung on well until 250M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Pushed early, took rail at back, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M.
Pushed forward, trapped 3 wide, not suited by the fast pace, ran on well until 100M flattened.
Failed to muster, took back for cover, 3 wide, suited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 250M.
Hard ridden early, trapped 4 wide throughout in midfield, hung in early straight, made steady ground 200M.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, emptied 200M.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, out of fuel 250M.
Hard ridden to keep up at rear, favoured by the fast tempo, made minor ground 250M.
At rear along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, ran on fairly.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, suited by the fast tempo, made ground 400M, emptied 200M.
Pushed forward, harmed by the fast pace, dropped off rapidly 350M.
Urged along to settled forward midfield on rail, improve approaching 400M, quickened passing 150M, finished unchallenged.
Raced behind midfield on rail, commenced to improve in the early straight, quickened passing 100M, finished strongly.
Settled at back on rail, fought hard entire straight, made up nice late ground, worked home solidly.
Pushed hard to take box seat, shifted out for clear running passing 350m, finished solidly.
Started well, took lead passing 1000M, travelled keenly mid race, gave ground passing 200M.
Travelled forward midfield, moved forward passing 700M, tried to improve passing Home Turn, gradually gave ground in the straight, finished OK.
Taken back at start, settled at tail on rail, made ground in the straight, came home well.
Moderate start, settled behind midfield, throughout the race travelled wide and without cover, one-paced in the straight.
Taken back at start, widest on straightening, tried hard but only one-paced in the straight.
Taken back at start, under pressure in the straight, one-paced.
Settled midfield, lay in throughout the race, weakened in the concluding stages, failed to run on.
Settled midfield on rail, under pressure in the straight, faded-out passing 150M, failed to run on.
Settled midfield, never in it.
Began awkwardly, never in it.
Steadied on jumping, shifted across behind runners, settling one-out at rear. Waited until straightening, taken to centre track, finished strongly to win on line.
Punched forward to take lead passing 950m, kicked clear entering straight, looked winner 100m, run down on line.
Steadied on jumping, shifted across behind runners, last on settling. Shifted out at turn in, finished strongly to grab minor placing.
Jumped OK, ridden but not pushed, settling one-out behind midfield. Lost position home turn, picked up momentum in straight and finished off nicely.
Began well, shared early pace, checked 900m and over-raced to turn but kept within 2L of leader. Boxed on gamely in straight despite getting close to heels 200m.
Quickly in front but not pushed, giving up lead passing 950m, settling one-out 1L behind. Left flatfooted top straight when leader kicked, boxed on gamely to line.
Began awkwardly, losing ground, pressed forward to midfield approaching 800m but lost position turn. Ran on fairly in straight.
Slow, taken to rail and improved to behind midfield 800m. Stayed on rail in straight and kept on steadily until blocked 200m. Not fully tested.
Away nicely, ridden to hold midfield position but left wide 900m and allowed to stride forward 3-deep to within 3L on leader at turn. One-paced in straight.
Soon in box seat, trailing leader. Kept tabs to straight, got clear running but faded quickly after passing 200m.
Ridden forward 3-wide to get within 3L of leader approaching turn. Under pressure on straightening and gave ground from 200m.
Ridden one-out in midfield to straight when put under pressure but failed to respond, dropping back gradually.
Ridden to hold rail, settling 4L from leader. Lost position around turn and one-paced in straight.
No early pace, dropping to rear and taken to fence. Shuffled back to last on entering straight, plodded home.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield, travelled well to turn, finished off strongly and scored with a little spare.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 6 to 7 lengths back at rear, bumped rounding home bend, finished off very strongly in straight to get 2nd.
Began fairly, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground throughout, angled out in straight and made some progress to take 3rd.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced 2 wide, 6 lengths or so back, there to turn, made minor progress in straight.

Slightly slow out from a wide draw, recovered to race prominently, got its head up when being shifted across towards the rail near 1000M, easy lead on turn, peaked and headed near 200M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incident)
Bumped start, positioned on rail at rear, saved ground on turn, made minor progress in straight without threatening.
Jumped well, raced 3 lengths or so back on rail, easy run to turn, kept to inside after straightening and made some progress, peaked near final 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began well, showed early speed to take the rail, sat a length behind the leader, easy run on turn, made no progress in straight, just stayed on one-paced.
Slightly slow out from a wide draw, recovered to race 2 wide in 3rd, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, stayed on one-paced thereafter.
Taken back to race at tail, 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with no cover at rear, similar positon on turn, bumped near 450M, failed to close off in straight.
Raced in behind midfield, 5-3/4L behind 2-3 wide with cover, covered nice ground and closed off strongly to score.
Settled to race prominently, sat 1-1/4L off 3 wide and no cover, lay out at turn but kept going and finished off gamely.
Eased and raced at the rear, 7L behind 3 wide with cover, made good ground and finished off well to the line.
Sent forward to take the rail and led by about 3/4L, headed just passing 100M but kept on.
Settled to race in front of midfield, 2-1/4L behind 3 wide with cover, saved ground and ran on fairly.
Pushed and settled to race prominently, sat 1-1/2L off 2 wide, kept on one paced to the line.
Sent forward and sat outside the lead, about 3/4L off, remained one paced in the straight.
Travelled in about midfield, 3L behind 2 wide, remained only one paced to the line.
Raced towards the rear, 6-1/2L behind 2 wide, continued to make ground before awkward to heels going to the line.
Eased back, at the rear 7-1/2L behind along the rail, only past beaten runners.
Sat just behind midfield, 3-1/2L behind 3 wide with cover, showed little and eased from 150M.
In box-seat, ridden from prior to 600M, finished tailed out.
Pushed forward along rail settling 3L from leader. Took closer order around turn, stayed on rail in straight, hit front passing 200m, drew clear.
Ridden along 3-wide in midfield, steadied approaching turn, swung wide in straight, finished strongly to grab 2nd close home,
Away well, pressed forward, settling one-out 3L from leader. Niggled at top of straight and boxed on well to hold minor placing.
Away well but restrained and taken back, settling at rear. Stoked up turning for home, very wide in straight, finished strongly to just miss a placing.
Pressed forward from outside draw, racing without cover 2L from leader. Kept on well in straight.
Punched forward on jumping, shared early pace before settling a half-length outside leader from 1000m Took lead soon on straightening but only one-paced from 200m. (Rider dropped whip 150m)
Shifted across soon after start, dropping to rear, then hard ridden from turn to hold position. Shifted in to get run halfway up straight and finished off nicely.
Ridden along between horses behind midfield to straight. Given reminders and boxed on fairly.
Shifted across behind runners soon after start, dropping to rear. Blundered around home turn, boxed on fairly in straight.
Quickly out, shared early pace until settling 3-wide 3L from leader approaching turn. Kept tabs to 200m when came under pressure and faded.
Away OK, taken to rail, settling behind midfield. Improved position home turn but only one-paced in straight.
Ridden to hold forward position but didn't settle and kept wide 3L from leader. Swung wide into straight, one-paced.
Hard ridden to lead on settling, hugging rail and setting steady pace. Overtaken on turning in and faded gradually.
Vigorously ridden but failed to muster dropping to last. Trailed field throughout. (Had substantial amount of blood in trachea)
Bustled along from draw 12, crossed to 2-wide tracking leader before home turn, kept chasing from 400M, ran in hard and finished well to wrap it up late stages.
Soon led and set steady pace, pressed by rival from 550M, quickened up again passing 300M but couldn't shake off its nearest rival, outgunned late but easily accounted for the rest. (Bled.)
Held up 2-wide in midfield, 5Ls off leader 400M, kept grinding to the line, went 3rd 100M but not reach first two.
Taken back from wide draw, settled down near last 8Ls off the pace middle stages, ran on steadily from off the pace, got up for 4th late but no threat to the runaway first two.
Began fairly, held up towards the rear, 7Ls to make up 400M, made some progress but never a threat to first two.
Restrained to sit behind mid-division, lay out home turn, battled away final 300M without threating first two.
Held up in mid-division about 6Ls behind leader, never going the pace to challenge but stayed on.
From draw 11 unable to find cover, caught 3-wide towards the rear, 9Ls off the pace at 400M, only ran past a few in straight.
Began fairly, held up 2-wide towards the rear, pushed along to improve position home turn, effort levelled off 200M, weakened towards the line.
Tracked leader in a steadily run race, raced keenly from 800M, shifted out 3-wide to challenge 450M, soon couldn't go on with leaders, weakened badly final 200M.
Taken back from wide draw, waited with in last place, over 10Ls to make up 400M, made no real progress, never involved.
Settled down in 4th 3-4L behind leaders, found little when asked 400M, soon in retreat.
Away well, racing close to pace but wide. Got close to heels 1000m, dropping back 3-wide at midfield. Taken to centre track on straightening and finished strongly to win close home.
Began OK, taken to fence at midfield and settled. Improved position approaching and around turn, rolled forward on straightening, took lead 200m, run down near line.
Steadied on jumping, shifted across behind runners, settling at rear. Improved to midfield around turn, and finished off nicely in straight.
Jumped with field, settling one-out ahead of midfield. Closed in steadily around turn and boxed on gamely in straight.
Jumped OK, hard ridden along fence to lead 1050m, set good pace to straight. Overtaken 200m and swamped final 100m.
No early pace, taken to rail behind midfield and improved position gradually. Kept on steadily in straight without looking dangerous.
Steadied and shifted in for cover, settling towards rear. Raced ungenerously approaching turn, one-paced in straight.
Jumped well, pressed forward, led from 1150 to 1050m before taking sit on leader. Under pressure on straightening and gave ground close home.
Began fairly, outpaced, dropping to last. Trailed field to straight before finishing off nicely.
Hard ridden on jumping but slow to muster, making ground to midfield but wide. Shuffled back turn, one-paced in straight.
Ridden along from outside draw but no pace and held three-wide towards rear. Kept wide around turn, one-paced in straight.
Jumped well, held in midfield but soon under pressure, and ridden hold position, losing ground steadily. Found nothing when asked in straight.
Jumped well, led initially before being eased 2L back, one-away from fence. Bumped and unbalanced 800m and 600m, weakened at turn-in, eased down 300m. (Unacceptable performance)

Crowded on jumping, off heels and dropped back, before recovering quickly to push to midfield. Went searching in the straight and found room from 200m. Good turn of foot, grabbed leader at 50m and was comfortable late.
Pushed forward early to lead, and set a slow tempo. Stayed on strongly in the straight. Faded late, and just held onto 2nd.
Dropped back from the wide draw to sit worse than midfield. Had a clear run in the straight. Ran well in the last 150m, and was the only one gaining on the winner late.
Pushed out from the wide draw to sit around midfield. Prominent in the straight and ran well to the line. Jockey lost left rein at 50m, and horse peaked late.
Taken up to be handily placed 4th/5th. Ran strongly in the early part of the straight, before running out of steam in the final 200m.
Pressed forward early to settle 2nd. 1 paced in the straight, and couldn't hold off the late chargers in the last 150m.
Eased back early to be worse than midfield. No options early in the straight, but had clear running from 300m. Stayed on solidly in the straight, without threatening.
OK away and settled forward of midfield. Steadied off heels at 200m, but wasn't progressing and 1 paced to the line late.
Dropped back from the wide draw to sit last, 2L off the nearest runner. Widest on the turn and stayed on 1 paced to the line.
Settled around midfield early. Keen and checked off heels 900m. Only fair in the straight under hands and heels.
Slowly away and dropped back to the rear of the field. Awkward on heels 800m. Held up from 350m until steadied off heels at 200m for clear run. Only ran fairly when clear.
Crowded on jumping and dropped back to the rear of the field. Plugged away in the straight and made little impression.
Pressed forward to sit 2nd/3rd, 3 wide with no cover. Dropped out rapidly from the 250m.
Eased forward early to sit around midfield. Over raced and checked off heels from 1000m to 700m. Gave ground quickly in the straight. Jockey questioned. Vet reported cardiac arrhythmia.

Settled well behind and waited with, commenced move switching wide into straight, made significant progress inside the final 200 metres to assert authority close to home.
Settled in last few and waited with on the rail, saved ground turning in, ran on well between runners to just fail to get up on line.
Broke well in the front early stages, taken back just off the pace in 3rd on the rail approaching the home bend, fought on gamely under pressure without threatening in the run home.
Broke well, close up early, steadied to just better than midfield in 6th early in back straight, wide turning for home, fought on steadily without threatening.
Driven along after beginning from a wide gate, settled just off the pace in 2nd, hit the front briefly passing the 200 metres but unable to sustain effort and swamped closing stages.
Settled in last few from a wide gate, produced good late impression inside the final 200 metres.
Prominent when clipped heels and lost position rounding the 1000-metre bend, travelled just worse than midfield to straight, kept on same pace without threatening.

Settled just off the pace in 5th on the rail, about 3L off the speed at the Rock and slightly further back when pace quickened on the bend, saved ground turning in when coming under pressure, made no impression in closing stages.
Close up in 4th 2-wide, came under pressure rounding home bend, one-paced in the straight.
Pressed forward from the widest gate, obtained rails run going up the Rock and led to the 200 metres, folded up quickly.
Vying for lead early when checked and dropped back sharply, remained in rear of field and widest into straight, no further impression.
Slowly away, soon recovered on the rail to rear of midfield, weakened after straightening.
Eased back, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 200M to score with some in hands.
Hard ridden to occupy box seat, benefited by the slow pace, ran on well for 2nd.
Midfield, 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, dashed well 300M, run ended 50M.
Pushed to take the rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on well until 100M overhauled.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, lack room in straight, little dash.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, dashed strongly 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, not suited by the slow pace, just held ground in straight.
Eased to sit in midfield, trapped 3 wide throughout, harmed by the slow tempo, held ground in straight despite all negative racing situations.
Pushed forward, sat outside the leader, benefited by the slow sectionals, out of fuel 150M.
Eased at start, took rail at back, not suited by the slow tempo, lack turn of foot.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide throughout, harmed by the slow pace, ran on ok.
Never a factor.
Settled midfield on rail, improved passing 350M, quickened passing 50M, finished strongly.
Jumped OK, pushed along to settle forward midfield, issued a challenge in the straight, just missed by head.
Jumped nicely, raced midfield, improved passing 550M, made up nice late ground, finished solidly.
Fast out to take box seat, commenced to improve at Home Turn, fought hard entire straight, finished well.
Ridden along to take lead, asked for effort at Home Turn, gave ground passing 150M, worked home OK.
Moderate start, travelled midfield, made some ground passing 200M, finished OK.
Settled at back, checked approaching 700M, tried to improve passing 450M, made ground in the final stages, came home OK.
Travelled behind midfield on rail, asked effort passing 500M, finished fairly.
Taken back at start, raced behind midfield on rail, one-paced in the straight.
Raced forward midfield on rail, weakened passing 100M, failed to run on.
Raced behind midfield, widest on straightening, showed no response and finished disappointingly.
Taken back at start, raced at tail, never in it.
Pressed forward from outside draw to contest early lead before taking sit 4L back. Threw out strong challenge on straightening, making up ground gradually to win close home.
Hard ridden from outside draw to lead on settling, pulling 4L clear passing 1000m. Still well clear entering straight but started to feel the pinch 200m and run down final stages.
Ridden along in midfield between horses to 1300m when checked and started to over-race. Settled better back stretch, given reminders at turn-in, finished strongly down centre track.
Slow, then snagged back and taken to rail, settling towards rear. Checked off heels 1000m, swung 3-wide entering straight, finished off nicely between horses.
Began awkwardly, taken to fence at midfield and settled. Got clear inside run in straight, making ground steadily until racing tight concluding stages.
Ridden to hold rail, settling 5L back when leaders sprinted. Closed in slightly turning for home, Ran on steadily in straight under vigorous riding.
Away quickly but unable match early pace, settling one-out 5L from leader. Closed in around home turn but only one-paced from 200m.
Outpaced, dropping to last at first turn. Made up some ground around home turn and finished off fairly.
Outpaced, nestling one-out behind midfield. Taken to centre track on straightening but only one-paced under hard riding.
Outpaced, dropping to last pair but away from fence. Remained at rear to straight where failed to respond to hard riding.
Began well, racing close to pace but three-wide. Kept wide throughout, swung wider at turn-in, spent force passing 200m and eased down final stages.
Ridden to hold midfield position but held 3-wide mostly. Lost position abruptly home turn and finished tailed out. (Had irregular heart rhythm)
Slightly slow out, raced 3 to 4 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out in straight and finished off well to score.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, taken wide after turning in, made very good progress in straight to get 2nd.
Slightly slow out, positioned 2 to 3 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, made reasonable headway in straight to get 3rd.
Began fairly, raced 5 lengths or so back at rear, same margin back on turn, no daylight early in straight, made good progress when clear thereafter to be nearest on line.
Jumped well from a tricky gate, unable to slot in, travelled 3 wide in midfield, there to turn, made some progress before hampered in the closing stages, just missed frame.
Began well from the widest gate, raced prominently, 3 wide turning, hung out when placed under pressure in straight, weakened from final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from a wide draw, showed early speed to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed final 100M, weakened thereafter.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back in midfield, no daylight in straight, not able to test properly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away, taken back to race at rear, still 5 lengths or so back on turn, bumped and unbalanced near 300M, finished off evenly.
Began well, positioned 2 wide in 4th, same positioned on turn, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began only fairly from gate 1, sat right behind the leader on rail, saved ground to near 500M, peaked early in straight and weakened thereafter.
Slowly away, raced at tail throughout, never a threat.
Raced in front of midfield, 3-1/2L behind 2 wide, found nice kick after 150M, stormed home to score comfortably by 2L.
Settled in one-off one-back position, sat 1-1/2L off, kept battling and finished off well for 2nd.
Sent forward, shared lead by about 1L in a 2 wide position, kept on going to the line to take 3rd but was no match.
Awkward start, settled in midfield, 4-3/4L behind along the rail, taken wide in straight, kept on fairly to the line.
Rolled forward and raced in the box-seat, sat 1L off the lead, kept on one paced to the line.
Sent forward and shared lead along the rail, kept on until 150M and found no more.
Hampered at start, settled in worse than midfield, 6-1/4L behind along the rail, one paced but ran on late.
Crowded at start, sat just behind midfield, 5-1/2L behind 2 wide, made minor ground.
Hampered at start, settled in behind midfield, 7L behind 2 wide, one paced.
Raced near the tail, 7-3/4L behind along the rail, did not improve.
Settled in midfield, 4-1/2L behind 2 wide, didn't improve and flattened passing 200M.
Taken back and raced at the rear, never in it.
Away well, shared pace before settling in box seat 1L from leader. Rolled forward top of straight, hit front 200m, held off late challenge.
Jumped well, raced close to pace before hampered and unbalanced near 1000m when one-out at midfield. Got inside run in straight and finished strongly only to fail narrowly.
Crowded and lost ground start, dropping behind midfield but holding rail. Stayed at rear to turn, took rails run in straight and finished strongly to grab minor placing.
Outpaced, racing towards rear between horses. Well back entering straight, took inside run and finished off nicely to be closest at finish.
Ridden early to find cover before slotting in passing 1300m but still three-wide behind midfield. Turned wide and boxed on fairly in straight.
Used early to share lead at first turn before inching ahead 1200m, cutting to rail 1000m. Set steady pace to straight, overtaken 150m, faded.
Shifted across behind runners soon after start, dropping to last pair. Began to over-race first turn and awkwardly placed passing 1000m. Took rails run in straight and ran on steadily.
Ridden early but unable find cover and shifted across behind runners, dropping to last pair. Stayed at rear to straight before running past tired rivals.
Began awkwardly, pressed forward, shared pace first turn before settling one-out 1L back. Shaken up 450m but under pressure from 250m and faded.
Away well, pressed forward holding rail 3L from leader. Kept tabs to straight when came under pressure and faded.
Crowded and lost ground start, then pushed forward, settling one-out 2L from leader. Stayed in contention to straight when ran out of steam and faded.
Bumped and unbalanced start, pressed forward, racing wide 4L from leader. Hampered turning into straight and faded gradually.
Utilized his inside draw, soon led at good pace, kept finding under pressure in straight and fended off challenges from both side to score.
Settled down behind midfield, 4Ls off the pace home turn, driven wide to challenge and closed off strongly despite hanging, rattled home late and only a few strides short of catching the winner.
Had a ground saving run along the fence and remained close up behind leaders throughout, every chance over final 300M, just couldn't reel in the leader, lost 2nd late.
Jumped midfield to be 8th on the inside 4Ls on settling, ran on steadily when placed under full pressure and got up for 4th late. Honest effort.
Urged forward from draw 9, caught 3-wide early before improving to a position outside leader, kept on evenly in straight, outsprinted by rivals final 150M.
Taken back from wide draw, settled 2nd last 5Ls off the pace, switched widest passing 300M, worked home well without threatening.
Taken back from wide draw, settled last 6-7Ls off the pace, made some ground final 300M but couldn't get close enough.
Began moderately, held up 2-wide in mid-division, kept battling away honestly without threatening in straight.
Jumped well to be 3rd chasing leaders, kept on same pace turning home, no impression on leaders from 200M.
Slow out, pressed on to chase leaders along the 3-path, couldn't muster enough speed to be closer over final 300M.
Up with early pace, dropped back to midfield entering back-straight but remained in touch with leaders, driven out 300M but struggled to make headway to the line.
Away with them then taken back to a rearward position 4-5Ls off the pace, brought wide for challenge early straight but got held up, checked again 200M and not ridden out to the finish.

Average to begin, raced 2 lengths or so back on rail, easy run on turn, angled out early in straight, bumped near 350M, finished off strongly in straight to score.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, slightly improved on turn, bumped early in straight, kept on well in straight to get 2nd.
Jumped well from a tricky gate, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 200M, stayed on for 3rd.
Began fairly, raced 7 lengths back at rear, travelled well on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening the first few.
Moderately away, raced at rear, steadied near 1000m, slightly improved on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Slowly away, no early speed, raced at tail, still well back on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made minor progress.
Jumped well, showed early speed to race prominently, sat next to the leader turning in, kept on fairly early in straight, peaked final 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began fairly from the widest draw, unable to slot in, travelled wide with no cover throughout, peaked after turning in, weakened gradually in straight. (Lame left front leg.)
Began well, raced 2 wide in 4th, same position on turn, severely checked and unbalanced near 350M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Slowly away, raced 3 to 4 lengths back on rail, there to turn, showed no response in straight and eased.
Settled in box seat, progressed steadily 400M, hung in badly 300M, ran on well to win.
Eased to rear, took cover, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 400M for 2nd.
Pushed early, behind midfield 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, made steady ground 300M.
Pushed forward, 2-3 wide, ran on until 200M flattened.
Slow away, at back along the fence, suited by the fast pace, however held up and checked 300M, made minor ground 100M.
Pressed forward, sat just off the leader, not suited by the fast tempo, emptied 250M.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at fast sectionals, soon dropped off 400M.
Eased back, never a factor.
Slow out, settled at back on rail, commenced to improve in the early straight, quickened passing 100M, finished strongly.
Jumped well then taken back, widest on straightening, asked for effort approaching 350M, made up nice late ground, finished solidly.
Moderate start, pushed along to take lead, ridden along on rail in the straight, worked home solidly.
Settled behind midfield, improved passing 600M, fought hard entire straight, came home well.
Fast out, took box seat, tried to improve passing Home Turn, finished OK.
Raced midfield on rail, inconvenienced passing 100M, one-paced.
Jumped well, throughout the race travelled wide and without cover, weakened passing 200M, one-paced in the straight.
Started OK, urged to settle outside the leader, weakened passing 300M, failed to run on.
Settled midfield, raced ungenerously at middle stages, failed to run on in the final stages.
Away nicely, settling one-back, one-out 2L from leader. Moved up at turn-in, given reminder, hit front 100m and pulled clear.
Hard ridden to lead on settling, cutting to fence 1100m and slowing pace to a crawl. Kicked ahead on straightening, kept finding when challenged, run down final 100m.
Jumped well, shared pace till settling 1L behind leader passing 1100m. Edged forward top of straight to look a chance but no match for winner final 100m.
Quickly into stride, holding box seat 2L from leader. Raced greenly when put under pressure top of straight but battled on gamely to line.
Began awkwardly, bumped and lost ground, dropping to last. Trailed field to field, surged forward on straightening to look a chance but run ended 200m. One-paced.
Slow into stride, ridden to hold midfield position but raced ungenerously when pace slackened. Shaken up top of straight but only one-paced.
Allowed to settle early, racing one-out towards the rear. Stoked up passing 600m but little response. One-paced in straight.
Taken back on jumping, dropping to last pair but away from fence. Stayed at rear mostly and never in the hunt.
Ridden early to hold midfield position but soon under pressure, dropping back approaching home turn. Did not respond to hard riding in straight and eased down.
Began well from gate 1, positioned a length or so back on rail, easy run on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off well to score.
Slightly slow out, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground to near 600M, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line. (Horse hit on nose by rival's whip near 200m.)
Taken back to race 6 lengths back at rear, slightly improved along the rail, angled out near 600M, finished off well in straight to get 3rd.
Bumped start, raced wide with no cover at rear, improved in the middle stages, 5 wide turning in, kept on well until peaked near final 150M, just missed 3rd on line.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, raced 7 lengths back at tail, still last turning in, no daylight early in straight, made some headway when clear thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 5 to 6 lengths back at rear, taken very wide turning in, bumped and unbalanced early in straight, finished off evenly thereafter. (Lame right front leg.)
Began well, raced 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, angled out near 600M, peaked early in straight and finished off evenly thereafter. (Lame left front leg.)
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, improved from 600M, 4 wide turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Fast into stride, took the lead easily, headed shortly after turning in and gradually dropped away.
Began well, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, taken very wide turning in, bumped and unbalanced near 400M, showed no progress thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to race prominently, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight.
Travelled in front of midfield, 2L off 2 wide with cover, drifted away after 150M, ran on nicely to score.
Rolled forward and raced just in front of midfield, 2-3/4L off 3 wide with cover, ran on gamely to the line.
Settled in front of midfield, 2-1/4L off along the fence, found daylight after 300M, progressed well from thereon.
Raced in behind midfield, 5L behind 2 wide, raced ungenerously throughout, made ground steadily, ran on okay.
Pushed and raced prominently, sat about 1L behind 3 wide with cover, ran on fairly to the line.
Sent forward and kept up with the pace, sat 3 wide without cover, ran on well until headed at 150M.
Travelled in midfield, 3-3/4L behind 2 wide, kept on going to the finish.
Sent forward and sat outside the lead, 1/2L behind 2 wide, kept on until weakened approaching 200M.
Settled behind midfield, 4L behind but 4 wide without cover, remained one paced home.
Raced in behind midfield, 5L behind 3 wide with cover, kept on one paced to the line.
Slow to jump and settled towards the rear, 7-1/4L behind 2 wide, swung widest and made minor ground only.
Pushed forward, shared lead along the rail, headed and found no extra near 250M.
In midfield, 3-3/4L behind along the rail, one paced.
Slow out and raced at the back, not a factor.
Crowded out start, pressed forward, racing 3L behind leader to 350m when given reminder. Switched in 200m to get clear run and surged forward under hard riding to win close home.
Away OK, pressed forward, racing 3L from leader 4-away from outer fence. Got clear run 300m, poked head in front 100m, battled strongly to line.
Jumped fairly, ridden to hold forward position 1L from leader at halfway mark. Edged forward to share 4-way lead 200m but unable match first two closing stages.
Jumped smartly, ridden along down centre track 3L from leader. Shaken up passing 200m and battled on gamely to line.
Quickly into stride, speared to the front 4-away from outer fence. Joined up front 200m, boxed on gamely but swamped close home.
Fast out, taken to outer fence and settled 1L from leader. Edged forward passing 400m, joined leaders 200m, no extra close home.
Ridden early down centre track to hold midfield position before edging closer to outer fence 4L from leader passing 400m. Boxed on one-paced in straight.
No early pace, racing along outer fence towards rear. Well back to straight, made late surge final 100m.
Away well, taken to outer fence 1L from leader. Edged forward passing 400m to share 4-way lead 200m before tiring and dropping back. (Lost right front plate shortly after start)
Bumped starting gate on jumping losing ground. Trailed field thereafter and finished well back. (Had substantial amount of blood in trachea)
Ridden forward from widest draw, crossed to lead uncontested from 1000M setting slow pace, drifted out under pressure in straight but continued on strongly to line, well in control final 100M.
Not hurried early stages, guided to the fence and improved to a midfield spot near 1000M, stuck to the inside on straightening, ran on well to go 2nd inside 100M but well held by winner.

Began well from draw 2, elected to sit behind leaders, hung in and reluctant to shift out early straight, stuck on well final 200M and got up for 3rd final stages. (Jockey and Trainer questioned re riding tactics.)
Sat outside leader in a slowly run race, kept up the chase turning in, run peaked 150M, caught by rivals and lost 2nd place inside 100M. (Jockey and Trainer questioned re riding tactics.)
Given a waiting ride near the rear, 5Ls to make up 400M, brought widest and worked home steadily.
Began only fairly, held up towards the rear 4-5Ls off the pace, saved ground on inner, ran on moderately, couldn't sprint enough to challenge leaders.
Unable to slot in from draw 11, caught 4-wide no cover in midfield, stayed on mildly without threat on straightening.
Began only fairly, held up in 8th 3-4Ls off the slow pace, raced keenly middle stages, only made limited progress final 300M. (Jockey reported his mount was not suited to how the race was run.)
Jumped well from draw 12, restrained back to midfield but no closer than 3-wide throughout, only battled away in straight, no threat.
Jumped well enough, dropped back to a 3-wide position behind midfield, never going the pace to challenge inside 400M.
Up with early pace then restrained behind leaders passing 1200M, 3Ls off the pace turning in, couldn't lift under pressure, faded 200M.
Never far off the pace, settled 3rd passing 800M 3-wide no cover, kept on same pace and weakened out from 200M.
Outpaced early stages soon dropped back to the rear, still last to the turn 6Ls off the pace, couldn't come on.
Away nicely, settling one-out 3L from leader. Not asked for effort until straightening, barged through between horses 300m, hit front 100m, held off late challenge.
Steadied soon after start and shifted in for cover, dropping out-out towards rear. Stayed well back to straight, taken to centre track and finished strongly to miss narrowly.
Ridden to hold forward position but held 3-wide with cover 3L from leader. Boxed on strongly in straight to grab minor placing. (Lost right hind plate 1100m)
Jumped well, shared early pace while holding rail, before easing 3L back at turn. Left fence on straightening and battled on strongly to finish in the frame.
Hard ridden to lead, crossing to fence 1000m. Kept finding in straight when strongly challenged only to be swamped final stages.
Pressed forward from an outside draw to race outside hindquarters of leader on settling. Urged forward on straightening, joint leader 200m, swamped closing stages.
Began awkwardly, then held between horses towards rear to turn. Swung wide into straight, finished off nicely though disappointed for run close home.
Ridden along early to hold midfield position but held three-wide with cover. Taken to centre track on straightening but only one-paced.
Outpaced, dropping towards rear along fence. Swung wide into straight, checked 200m, one-paced.
Jumped OK, taken to fence, settling behind midfield. Lost position approaching home turn, stayed on rail in straight but only one-paced under pressure.
Broke well, shared early pace before settling in box seat 2L from leader. Kept tabs to 200m when ran on out steam and faded.
Used from outside draw to stay with early pace, racing 3-wide without cover 2L from leader. Under pressure on straightening and faded gradually.
Steadied soon after start and shifted across for cover, settling at rear along fence. Under pressure throughout but unable to improve position.
Began fairly, ridden and given reminders but didn't respond, becoming detached from field and retired from race.

Pressed forward to lead early, before settling 3rd/4th and 1 off the fence. Loomed up to lead at 200m, where jockey lost the whip. Stayed on strongly under jockey power and just held off fast finishing 2nd.
Dropped back from the wide draw to sit behind midfield, 1 off the fence. Ran well in the straight. Very strong late, and was rapidly closing on the winner.
Dropped back early from the wide barrier to sit at the rear of the field. Last at the 350m. Produced a massive turn of foot in the straight and grabbed 3rd place on the line.
Cruised forward early to sit midfield. Stuck 3 wide with no cover from 800m. Stayed on solidly in the straight, but just lost 3rd in the shadows of the post.
Taken forward early to sit 3rd/4th, on the fence. Restricted room at 850m. Momentarily nosed in front at the 250m, but was 1 paced in the straight and swamped late.

Eased back early and settled towards the rear of the field, on the fence. Keen in the middle stages. Not pushed hard early in the straight, and got whip caught in reins at 200m. Stayed on well when finally pushed to the line late.
Eased forward and settled forward of midfield, on the fence. Plugged away early in the straight. Stayed on OK over the last 100m, but never threatened.
Taken up early. Checked at 850m and eventually settled 5th, 1 off the fence. Stayed on fairly under hands and heels, and never threatened.
Pressed forward from the wide draw to eventually sit 2nd, on the shoulder of the leader. Had no kick and faded out quickly from the 200m.
Cruised up to sit midfield, 1 off the fence. Only fair in the straight and not pushed out to the line.
Bumped early and then dropped back to sit at the rear of the field. Only battled on fairly under the stick, and made no real impression.
Pushed forward to be the eventual leader. Still in front at 250m, but gave no response to pressure in the straight and dropped out quickly.
Initially pushed forward, before easing back to sit just behind midfield. Plugged along the rails, without ever picking up speed in the straight.
Dropped back from the wide draw and sat at the rear of the field. Needs at least 600m further, and played no part in the race.
