Jumped well from a tricky gate, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths back in 5th, improved from near 600M, 3 wide turning in, finished off well in straight to score.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out near 400M, made very good progress in straight to get 2nd.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back in 4th, awkwardly placed near 500M, made good progress in straight to take 3rd.
Away with them, raced 4 lengths back on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out after 400M and finished off evenly to make frame.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 7 lengths back at rear, there to turn, taken widest in straight and made good progress to be nearest on line.
Began awkwardly, raced 6 to 7 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out near 200M and made some progress thereafter.

Taken back from the widest draw, travelled 3 wide and without cover at rear, improved from near 800M, bumped and unbalanced near 550M, 4 wide turning in, bumped again early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well, showed early speed to take the lead, travelled well throughout, peaked early in straight, headed near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from gate 11, raced at tail, slightly improved turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run throughout, kept to inside after straightening, peaked near 200M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to race in 2nd, difficult to settle early, same position to turn, steadied early in straight, showed no response and faded thereafter.
Began only fairly, failed to muster speed, raced at rear throughout, finished tailed off.
Pushed to take rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, drifted away 300M to score.
Very slow away, pushed to obtain box seat, benefited by the slow sectionals, ran on well for 2nd.
Eased back, took rail, harmed by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 250M for 3rd.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide in the lead, benefited by the slow tempo, flattened 100M.
Midfield, 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Eased back, took rail, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Behind midfield, 2 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, lack room 300M, dashed well when clear.
Very slow away, checked 900M, at rear 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, little dash 100M.
Eased to sit in midfield, raced 3 wide throughout, harmed by the slow tempo, no dash.
Raced 3-4 wide throughout ungenerously, harmed by the slow pace, ran on ok in straight.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide, suited by the slow tempo, emptied 250M, checked 150M.
Very slow away, harmed by the slow pace, never competitive.
At the start bumped and became unbalanced, settled midfield, improved passing 500M, gradually made ground from Home Turn, finished strongly.
Taken back at start and settled at tail on rail, commenced to improve passing 500M, widest on straightening, issued a strong challenge passing 200M, finished solidly, missed by head.
Taken back at start and settled on rail, asked for effort passing 500M, made up good late ground, worked home solidly.
Settled outside the leader, passing 800M moved to lead, asked for effort at Home Turn, came home well.
Raced at handy position, tried to improve approaching 750M, worked home OK.
Urged along to take lead, passing 800M drifted back to box seat, asked for effort at Home Turn, finished fairly.
Began only fairly and settled behind midfield on rail, tried to improve passing 800M, one-paced.
Jumped well, raced midfield on rail, asked for effort passing 650M, ran on well until weakened passing 100M, failed to finish off.
Raced behind midfield, ridden hard but only limited response at Home Turn, failed to run on.
Ridden along after start and settled midfield, asked for effort but no response passing 700M, gave noticeably ground at Home Turn, finished disappointing. Must trial.
Raced box seat until 800M, pushed along at Home Turn but no response, under pressure and faded out in the straight.
Bumped, unbalanced start but recovered quickly and taken to fence 3L from leader. Ran on strongly in straight to hit front 50m and then held off late challenge.
Beaten for early pace, settling between horses behind midfield to turn. Taken to centre track on straightening and finished strongly.
Shot to the front soon after start but kept one-out till kicking clear 500m and crossing to fence. Kept on strongly in straight but run down close home.
Steadied shortly after start and taken in for cover, settling one-out at rear. Took inside run in straight and finished off nicely while weaving between horses.
Comfortably placed one-out in midfield to turn. Put under pressure top of straight and boxed on fairly.
Fast out, racing wide without cover outside leading pack until settling behind leader 700m. Lost ground at turn-in and one-paced in straight.
Steadied shortly after start, dropping to last pair. Clear last entering straight before picking up momentum, blocked for run from 100m to 50m, finished off well.
Ridden along from widest draw, racing 3-wide mostly towards the rear. Covered extra ground turn and kept wide in straight. One-paced.
Fast out, grabbing rail a half-length inside leader until 500m when crossed. Under pressure soon after straightening and faded. (Lame right front leg)
Began awkwardly and bumped, dropping to rear along rail. Took inside run in straight but held behind horses from 150m to 50m and not properly tested.
Pressed forward, settling one-out 2L from leader. Lost position turning for home and faded gradually in straight. (Bled from both nostrils)
Began awkwardly, then pushed forward to midfield along rail. Lost ground around home turn and one-paced in straight.
Away with them, sat a length behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, finished off very well in straight to score.

Bumped start, positioned on rail in midfield, 2 to 3 lengths back, saved ground to near 450M, no daylight early in straight, shifted in thereafter but caught in traffic again, finished off strongly when clear final 100M.
Began well, positioned 2 wide in 4th, improved from near 500M, finished off well to take 3rd. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from a tricky gate, sent forward to race prominently, same position on turn, fought on steadily to the line.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced ungenerously at tail in the early and middle stages, still well back on turn, finished off very strongly to be nearest on line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 6 lengths back at rear, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slowly away, positioned on rail at rear, slightly improved along the rail on turn, kept to inside after straightening, no clear running near 100M, made minor progress when clear thereafter.
Away with them, raced 3 wide at rear, awkwardly placed near 1000M, improved from 400M, taken widest in straight, but finished off only one-paced.
Jumped well from gate 1, took the lead easily, enjoyed the uncontested lead on turn, kicked clear early in straight, peaked and headed near 100M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths back behind midfield, there to turn, finished off one-paced, never a threat.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, same position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Slowly away from a wide draw, caught 3 wide with no cover in midfield, emptied early in straight and eased.
Rolled forward to take up the box-seat, sat 1-1/2L off the lead, ran on well and held off challenges to score.
In midfield, 5-1/2L behind 2 wide, got going but was impeded at 150M, resumed but had to settle for 2nd.
Slow to jump, settled in behind midfield, 7L behind 2 wide, made good ground and kept on to the line.
Eased and then raced towards the rear, 8-1/4L behind 2 wide, covered nice ground and ran on well to the line.
Sent forward and sat outside the lead, sat 1/2L off, headed passing 150M, kept on going to the line.
Travelled in front of midfield, 3-1/2L off along the fence, kept on until passing 150M and flattened.
Taken back, raced at the rear, 10L behind along the rail, continued to make ground steadily.
Raced in front of midfield, 2-3/4L off 2 wide, kept on one paced to the line.
Settled just in front of midfield, travelled keenly in the middle stages, wide from 600M turn, hardly improved.
Raced in worse than midfield, 6L behind along rail, never threatened.
Pushed and raced prominently, but trapped wide throughout, found nothing.
Sent forward to take rail and led, showed little in the straight, not a factor.
Jumped well, holding rail inside leader to turn. Clipped heels and blundered 350m, recovered and surged forward to lead 150m, then kept finding to hold off late challenge.
Raced comfortably one-out in midfield to turn, taken to centre track on straightening and finished strongly to just miss.
Away well, racing one-out 3L from leader. Swung wide entering straight and finished off nicely.
Jumped straight to the front, racing one-out before crossing to fence home turn. Joined up front 150m and faded close home.
Ridden 4-wide at rear before getting cover entering turn. Took inside run in straight but forced to switch out 200m to get run, then closed off nicely.
Raced one-out behind midfield to turn. Boxed on gamely in straight to finish on heels of placegetters.
Steadied and shifted in for cover soon after start, settling one-out behind midfield. Taken wide in straight and ran on fairly.
Ridden to hold rail, settling 3L from leader before home turn. Kept tabs to straight but only one-paced under pressure.
Steadied soon after start and shifted in for cover, dropping to last. Checked off heels home turn, taken wide in straight, one-paced.
Quickly away, racing one-out 1L from leader to straight. Under pressure passing 200m and faded.
Began OK, then taken to rail behind midfield. Crowded and lost ground home turn, faded in straight.

Taken across behind runners and guided to the fence 5-6Ls back in midfield, saved ground waiting for an opening on the inside, kicked on well to lead near 100M and fought hard to hold off a late challenge.
Switched off to race towards the rear, travelled well and gradually moved closer to the pace passing 600M, hit the line strongly on straightening to just miss.
Held a rail position from draw 1 and always within striking distance, loomed a chance 250M out, hit the line well to be beaten not far at the finish.
Sent forward as expected, crossed to the lead 1200M setting even pace, travelled well into straight, tried hard to the wire but couldn't fend off pursuers nearing 100M, edged out to 4th at the line.
Jumped evenly to be 5th on settling, within 3Ls of leader making the home turn, worked home steadily over final 300M but couldn't get closer to the leaders.
Reserved near rear early stages, made mid-race move 800M to be 3-wide outside the pace home turn, kept grinding on straightening but was well held by leaders final 200M.
Began only fairly, restrained to sit behind midfield, pushed along 600M swinging wide into straight, stayed on only fairly and not reached contention.
Sent forward to be 3rd tracking leaders, had to be urged along rounding the home turn, run ended passing 200M and faded.
Held up in mid-division 4-5Ls off the pace, on straightening blocked for run until final stages, not properly tested.
Slow to begin, sat in rear over 10Ls off the pace at early stages, pushed along 600M and tried to improve position but not quickened. Never a threat.
Set early pace, proved difficult to settle when restrained to allow rival to cross passing 1200M, couldn't sprint with them inside 300M, weakened away.

Settled down 2-wide in midfield, pushed wide 700M then came under pressure, didn't respond to riding and dropped away early straight. (Jockey and Trainer unable to offer any reason for the disappointing run.)

Showed good speed to race prominently, travelled well throughout, kicked clear from near 400M and scored easily, impressive winning debut.
Began well, positioned a length behind the leader near to the stands rail, improved from near 400M, finished off well to get 2nd without threatening the winner.
Began awkwardly, recovered to race prominently on the stands' rail, kept on well until peaked near 300M, slightly weakened thereafter.
Began fairly, positioned a length or so back in midfield, 1 away from the stands rail, finished off evenly.
Slightly slow out, positioned behind midfield, 2 to 3 lengths back, finished off evenly, never a threat to the first few.
Jumped well from the gate 10, positioned on rail behind midfield, made no impression final 400M.
Began fairly from gate 1, raced in midfield nearer to the middle of the track, showed no progress in the final stages.
Jumped well from gate 2, sent forward to race prominently, 2 away from the stands rail, no response to riding near 450M, weakened in the concluding stages.
Raced at rear throughout, never competitive.
Slightly slow out, no early speed, raced at rear, peaked near 500M and dropped away tamely thereafter.
Hard ridden to take rail, led at advantageous slow sectionals, kicked away 500M, just made all.
At back, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed strongly 300M, just missed by narrow margin in 2nd.
At back, 2 wide, unleashed strong finishing efforts 250M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Midfield, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, lack room 4-2, dashed well when clear.
At rear, 2-3 wide, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased to rear, took rail, harmed by the slow pace, made early move 700M around the field in 4 wide, dashed well until 150M run ended.
Midfield, 2-3 wide, made early move 600M, held ground in straight. (saddle shifted)
Eased back, raced 3-4 wide throughout, harmed by the slow pace, emptied 200M.
Pushed forward, benefited by the slow pace, lack room 400M, flattened 200M.
Midfield along the fence, not suited by the slow pace, flattened 300M.
Hard ridden to occupy box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, out of fuel 400M.
Eased back early, however trapped very wide, moved forward 1600M into the lead, emptied 400M.
Moderate start, settled at box seat, improved in the early straight, made up good late ground, finished strongly to win.
Began awkwardly and was hampered, raced wide behind midfield, passing 700M lay out and proved difficult to settle, quickened passing 200M, just missed by head.
Started well to take lead, asked for effort in the early straight, fought hard in concluding stages, finished solidly.
Settled midfield on rail, held up for clear running in the early straight, finished nicely.
Taken back and raced behind midfield, widest on straightening, made ground passing 200M, worked home well.
Taken back and settled at tail, asked for effort at Home Turn, passing 300M held up for clear running, finished well.
Settled midfield, asked for effort passing Home Turn, made some ground in the concluding stages, finished OK.
Hard ridden and settled at handy position, weakened passing 150M, came home fairly.
Started OK, raced in front of midfield, under pressure in the straight, one-paced.
Raced midfield, after 900M travelled wide and without cover, one-paced in the straight.
Slow to begin and raced behind midfield on rail, never in it.
Jumped well and urged along to settle outside leader, weakened in the straight, failed to make impression.
Ridden along 4-wide before cutting to fence 1000m, settling 5L from leader. Stoked up passing 500m, switched out 300m for run, hit front 200m, pulled clear.
Bounced well, ridden to hold fence 3L from leader. Came off fence turning for home and finished strongly between runners to grab second close home.
Pressed forward from outside draw, settling one-out 3L from leader at turn. Swung wide into straight and finished off nicely down centre track.
Away well, grabbing box seat 2L from leader. Tightened approaching home turn, closed in at turn-in, hit front momentarily halfway up the straight, tired close home.
Shifted across behind runners after start, dropping one-out towards rear. Remained well back to straight, no run till after 300m, finished off nicely. (Rider dropped right rein 150m)
Outpaced, dropping to rear along rail. Last of main bunch into straight, taken to centre track and ran on steadily.
Shifted across behind runners after start, dropping to rear but away from fence. Well back to straight, taken to centre track and ran on fairly.
Crowded out start, dropping to behind midfield along fence. Stayed on fence around turn, made ground early in straight, turning one-paced final 200m.
Jumped awkwardly, ridden but didn't stretch out and became detached from field. Picked up bit passing 600m and made up considerable ground in straight.
Raced one-out behind midfield mostly. Shaken up top of straight but only one-paced.
First out, then took sit behind leader before forging forward 700m. Took narrow lead around home turn, overtaken soon after straightening, faded.
Hard ridden to lead on settling, cutting to fence 1000m. Joined up front 700m, headed at turn-in, faded. (Had small cut outside right front fetlock)
Bumped start, pressed forward to sit behind pace but kept wide without cover mostly. Kept tabs to 200m before tiring.
Jumped well, ridden forward, settling one-out 2L from leader. Under pressure turning for home and gave ground steadily in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, improved from 600M, finished off strongly to score.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, same position on turn, angled out near 550M, finished off well to get 2nd.
Away with them, raced 3 wide in midfield, carried wider after 600M, but still able to make good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Began well, took the lead easily, travelled well throughout, kept on well early in straight, headed near 200M, stayed on evenly for 4th.
Taken back from a middle draw, raced 2 wide, 6 lengths back at rear, angled out after turning in, made reasonable progress without threatening the first few.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 5 lengths or so back at rear, slightly improved along the rail on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned a length or so back on rail, easy run on turn, no daylight early in straight, finished off evenly when clear thereafter.
Away with them, positioned 2 wide behind midfield, same position on turn, finished off evenly.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, there to turn, taken very wide in straight, failed to make any progress.
Taken back to race at tail, still 6 lengths back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Bumped start, unable to slot in from the widest gate, raced 3 wide with no cover in front, peaked after turning in, weakened gradually thereafter when hard run took toll. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slowly away, positioned on rail in midfield, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced prominently, travelled keenly and difficult to settle for some distance after 1100M, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight, eased final furlong.
Taken back to race at rear, showed no response on turn, eased early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Raced in about a midfield position, 4-1/4L behind 2 wide, closed off strongly inside 200M to score.
Jumped well, rolled forward but failed to find cover initially, improved to sit outside lead, closed off well for 2nd.
Pushed and settled to race in the box-seat, sat 2-1/2L off, ran on well, overtook by 2nd just on the line.
Settled in about midfield, 5-1/4L behind along the rail, showed good dash inside 150M, finished off nicely.
Sent forward to take the rail and led by about 1L, out of fuel and headed passing 200M.
Rolled forward and raced prominently, 2-1/2L off and stayed 2 wide, kept on one paced.
Travelled towards the rear, 7-1/4L behind along the rail, made ground, kept on the line.
Eased and raced at the tail, 9L behind along the rail, made ground, ran on the line.
Raced towards the rear, 7-1/2L behind 2 wide, one paced mostly.
Settled in about midfield, 5-3/4L behind 2 wide, found nothing. (Irregular heart rhythm)
Away well, shared pace before crossing to rail and taking box seat. Came off fence turning for home, hit front 200m, started to shorten stride close home but just held.
Pushed back by slow pace, dropping to behind midfield back stretch. Improved around home turn, surged forward between horses in straight to just miss out.
Jumped OK, holding rail 5L from leader. Got shuffled back by slow pace back stretch, came off fence home turn, finished off nicely to grab minor placing.
Quickly out, shared pace to first turn, then settling one-out 1L from leader. Moved up around home turn, hit front 400m, caught 230m but kept battling to line.
Pressed forward from widest draw, racing 4-wide before settling one-out 4L from leader back stretch. Improved position approaching home turn, kept tabs to 200m, then one-paced.
Pressed forward from outside draw and caught wide at midfield 1100m. Allowed to improve, circling field to lead 900m, overtaken at turn-in, kept finding to 200m before tiring.
Began fairly and last on settling. Taken to rail around home turn, and ran on steadily in straight to be closest at finish.
Jumped well, ridden to hold midfield position one-away from rail. Got shuffled back when pace slowed back stretch, taken 4-wide home turn, widest into straight, finished off fairly.
Ridden but slow to muster, dropping towards rear. Held three-wide back stretch, made up some ground approaching turn but one-paced straight under hard riding.
Ridden to go forward one-out from rail but dropped to midfield when pace slowed back stretch. Under whip in straight but only one-paced.
Raced at rear mostly, dropping to last approaching home turn. One-paced in straight. (Lame right front leg, restricted action both hind legs. See also stewards' report)
Restrained at jump and taken in for cover but left three-wide at rear when pace slowed. Raced at rear mostly and limited response when asked in straight.
Ridden early to stay forward settling one-back, one-out. Got shuffled back when pace slowed back stretch. Gave ground from home turn and eased down final strides.
Hard ridden to lead before first turn, crossing to fence and then slowing pace. Overtaken passing 900m, under pressure turn, faded, finished tailed out. (Unacceptable performance).
Soon led under 7lb claimer, dictated a steady tempo from the start, travelled strongly into 400M, kept up momentum when pushed out and left rivals trailing, well in control final 150M.
Positively ridden, tracked leader in a race run at even tempo, all out passing 250M but couldn't gain ground on the winner, held on 2nd.
Guided to the fence and settled down in midfield, improved to 3rd 250M, kept working to secure the minor spot but couldn't get near to the runaway winner.
Taken back from wide draw to a position 4th last, 6Ls to make up at 400M, ran on well down outside but couldn't quite get to the first 3.
Away with them reigned back from draw 13 to sit near last 8Ls off leader, brought widest into straight, closed off well but too much to make up on leaders.
Chased leaders along the fence, couldn't keep up with first few when the race got serious passing 400M, one paced over final 200M.
Restrained in midfield, settled 7th 4Ls back, held position to the turn, kept on only fairly over final 400M, no threat to leaders.
Held up behind midfield 5-6Ls off the pace, couldn't get any closer to leaders when driven out 400M, held ground to the line.
Settled down 2-wide behind mid-division, 6Ls to make up 400M but couldn't make any headway.
Fractious in stalls and very slowly away, ended up at the back 9Ls off the pace, struggled home and failed to make any real progress.
Chased leaders 3-wide without cover, gave ground gradually passing 350M.
Rushed along to be chasing leaders, came under pressure 550M, weakened away early straight.
Slowly away, settled near last, never picked up in straight. (Bled.)
Away OK, holding rail, dropping to behind midfield back stretch. Came off fence 500m, got split 300m, surged forward to hit front 180m, pulled clear for easy win.
Pressed forward from start and got dream run in box seat when leaders fanned out first turn. Kept tabs to straight. Rolled forward to lead 250m, but unable to hold off winner.
Crowded out start, beaten for pace, dropping to rear. Made ground along rail home turn, held for run early in straight, finished off well to grab minor placing.
Crowded out start, pressed forward, holding midfield position one-out from rail. Ran on steadily in straight to finish just behind placegetters.
A little slow into stride, racing at rear before making up ground home turn. Took inside run in straight to get within range 200m before turning one-paced.
Hard ridden from inside draw to share early pace before settling one-out 1L from leader back stretch. Kept on well to 200m before tiring.
Jumped well, pressed forward but wide without cover 2L from leader. Forced to shift out top of straight for clear run, kept on well to 200m before turning one-paced.
Away nicely, racing one-out in midfield first turn and back stretch. Had clear running in straight but only one-paced when given reminders and eased final strides.
Restrained on jumping and shifted in, dropping to last first turn. Stayed at rear back stretch, made up some ground home turn, one-paced in straight.
Hard ridden to stay forward, taking first turn 4-wide, dropping to midfield back stretch. Worked way forward without cover to sit outside leaders at home turn, but spent force in straight.
Hard ridden from inside draw, charging through pack to lead at first turn. Set steady pace to straight, overtaken 300m and faded. (Had substantial amount of mucus in trachea)
Hard ridden from widest draw, taking fist turn 6-wide first turn before being shuffled to behind midfield back stretch. Stayed at rear and limited response when asked in straight.
Hard ridden to go forward from outside draw, taking first turn 5-wide. Kept very wide 2L from leader back stretch before easing back 1200m for cover. Spent force in straight.
Jumped OK, settling one-out towards the rear. Under pressure home turn, no response in straight when asked and eased down, finishing tailed out. (Unacceptable performance)

Ridden forward early to be well placed 2nd/3rd on the rail. Held up early in the straight and had to go 5 wide at the 300m searching for a run. Clear at 200m, and showed huge turn of foot. Eased late.
Crowded on jumping and dropped back to sit at the back of the field. Stayed close to the rail and finished off well from the back of the pack, but lacked the motor to match it with the winner late.
Taken forward early to be well placed 2nd/3rd, 1 off the fence. Stayed on solidly in the straight.
Bumped on jumping, but recovered well to push to a handy position 4th/5th. Awkward on heels at 1000m, and lost position. Wider on the turn and stayed on solidly in the straight.
Eased back early from the wide draw to settle at the rear of the field. Wider on the turn and stayed on solidly, without threatening in the straight.
Pressed forward early to be handily placed in 4th, but stuck 3 wide with no cover. Started to fade out at the 200m. Crowded and steadied at 100m, but wasn't making ground.
Cruised forward from the inside draw to settle midfield. Hampered at the 300m. Angled off heels at 100m, but was only staying on fairly.
Pushed hard from the wide draw to lead passing the 1000m. 1 paced in the straight.
Dropped back early for cover. Unsettled on heels in the back straight and was checked from 1200m until 800m. Last at the 300, but still had plenty in the tank and ran well to the line late.
Dropped back early, but was stuck 4 wide with no cover at the rear of the field. Plugged on fairly in the straight, without ever threatening.
Eased out early to sit around midfield, 3 wide with limited cover. Unsettled in the back straight. Didn't respond to pressure in the straight and went to the line tamely.
Settled just behind midfield. Never figured at any stage and went quietly to the line.
Crept forward early to settle around midfield, 1 off the fence. Unsettled and checked off heels from the 1000m. Shifted out off heels 900m. Badly checked at 300m, and not pushed out subsequently.
Pressed forward early, before eventually settling forward of midfield. Hampered at the 300m, and eased up soon after.

Settled in midfield, quickened well under pressure to gain upper hand final strides.
Travelled in 5th in forward of midfield, commenced move approaching the home turn, ran on under pressure but failed to peg back the winner throughout.
Soon took up running from a wide draw, led until overhauled inside the final 50 metres.
Ridden along in rear of midfield, saved ground turning for home, inconvenience passing the 200 metres, produced good late impression closing stages.
Soon dropped towards the rear despite ridden along, in similar position turning in, came to challenge early in straight, ran on near the centre of the track, did best work late. (Tactic questioned)
Settled wide without cover in 2L 4th, went wider turning for home, ran home nicely. (Jockey questioned)
Vied for lead early, settled one back in 3rd 2-wide, kept on early in straight before fading inside the final 200 metres.
Held up on rails, chased leader into straight, forced to switch for a run over 200 metres out, soon found no extra.
Soon dropped to last few, kept on past well-beaten horses in the run home, never nearer.
Moderate start, niggled along in forward of midfield along the rail, saved ground turning in, forced to switch for a run after straightening, soon faded.
Settled behind midfield wide without cover after beginning from a wide draw, widest runner turning in, found nothing.
Always behind, never seen with a chance.
Hard ridden to keep up in front of midfield on the rails, suited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast pace, however taken wide on straightening, dashed well 200M.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at fast sectionals, hung on well until 50M overhauled, ran on for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward, box seat, not suited by the fast pace, flattened 200M.
Eased to rear, 2 wide, suited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 250M.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast sectionals, flattened 250M.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast pace, made steady ground 300M.
Pushed early, failed to muster, sat in front of midfield, 2-3 wide, just held ground in straight.
Trapped 3 wide in midfield throughout, emptied in straight.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, suited by the fast pace, no dash.
At back along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, no progress.
Very slow away, never competitive.
Settled midfield on rail, issued a strongly challenge passing 100M, worked home solidly to win.
Fast out to take lead, asked for effort in the early straight, finished strongly.
Taken back at start and travelled behind midfield, made up some good late ground, finished solidly.
Jumped well, raced midfield, commenced to improve passing 400M, made ground passing 200M, came home nicely.
On jumping bounded, near 1000M checked, settled midfield on rail, fought hard entire straight, finished well.
Moderate start, raced midfield, made ground passing 100M, finished OK.
Urged along to settle outside leader, tried to improve approaching 500M, one-paced in the straight.
Settled behind midfield on rail, asked for effort at Home Turn but only limited response, came home one-paced.
Raced at handy position, widest on straightening, under pressure in the straight, failed to run on.
Hampered then taken back at start, settled at tail, never improve.
Slow to begin and raced at tail on rail, never in it.
Travelled well to take box seat, weakened badly passing 150M, failed to close off.
Steadied on jumping and taken in for cover, dropping to last. Stayed at rear to straight, taken to centre track, finished strongly under whip to win on the line.
Unbalanced start, no pace, dropping to last pair along fence. Swung wide into straight, surged forward to lead passing 50m, beaten on line.
Pressed forward from an outside draw, racing 3-wide 3L from leader first turn. Pressed forward 1300m to sit outside leader before easing 2L back. Wide in straight and finished off gamely.
Crowd out start, then held along rail in midfield. Not suited by slow pace and hard ridden from 1200m to go forward, taking lead 900m. Kept on well until overtaken 100m, boxed on.
Jumped well but snagged back for cover, settling one-out behind midfield. Not asked for effort until straightening for home and finished off nicely.
Ridden early to hold rail, settling in box seat first turn. Lost position back stretch, stoked up 500m, took inside run straight and surged forward before run ended 200m and swamped.
Away well, taking lead on settling. Moved into slipstream when rival moved forward, kept tabs on leaders to 200m before turning one-paced.
Vigorously ridden on jumping but unable to lead and settled one-out 3L from leader. Stayed close to straight, checked 250m, then unable to get clear running and not properly tested.
Away well, trailing leader first turn, then taking box seat back stretch when another moved forward. Stayed close to 300m before tiring.
Away with them, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, finished off very strongly to score by a head.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, improved from 800M, 4 wide turning in, hit the front near 200M, but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Bumped start, positioned 5 to 6 lengths back on rail early, shifted out and slightly improved in the middle stages, 3 wide turning, finished off well to get 3rd.
Taken back from gate 8, raced 2 wide behind midfield early, bumped and carried wider near 800M, 3 wide with cover on turn, made some headway in straight to make frame without threatening.
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well on turn, headed near 200M, stayed on evenly. (Blood in trachea.) (Lame left front leg next day.)

Bumped start, positioned on rail in midfield early, checked heels near 1000M, difficult to settle in the middle stages, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, no clear running early in straight, taken widest thereafter and finished off evenly.
Began well, raced 2 lengths back on rail early, checked heels near 1050M, 3 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Began well from a tricky draw, positioned 2 wide in 2nd, kept same margin back on turn, peaked near 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 7 lengths back at rear, there to turn, failed to close off in straight, never competitive.
Began fairly from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, difficult to settle near 1050M, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight and faded gradually.
Taken back from a wide barrier, raced at tail throughout, never competitive.
Began fairly from gate 1, no early speed, raced at tail early, improved gradually from near 1200M, positioned 2nd near 700M, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight and eased.
Bumped start, sat in front of midfield, 3-1/2L behind along the rail, good dash at 100M, ran on to score by a neck.
Raced prominently, sat about 2L off the lead in a 2 wide position, ran on nicely but couldn't hold off the winner.
Rolled forward and raced in box-seat, sat 1-3/4L off the lead, kept on well to the line to take 3rd.
Travelled at towards the rear, 6-1/4L behind 2 wide, continued to make ground, ran home well.
Jumped awkwardly and missed start, at the rear 8-1/4L behind, made nice ground and kept on strongly to the line.
Jumped well, obtained cover in behind midfield 4-3/4L off, made ground steadily in the straight.
Raced just in front of midfield, 3L off 2 wide, kept on one paced to the line.
In behind midfield, 5-1/4L behind along the rail, disappointed for running at 250M, made minor ground thereafter.
Crowded start, rolled forward but forced to lead by 1-3/4L, weakened near 200M.
In midfield, about 5L behind but always trapped wide, never threatened.
Jumped straight to the front, pulling 2L clear at the turn. Kicked ahead top of straight and kept on well to the post without being challenged.
Pushed along to hold forward position, settling one-out 3L from leader. Gave chase in straight, closing in steadily to finish 2nd.
Jumped well, not pushed, settling 3-wide behind midfield but with cover. Swung wide into straight and ran on steadily to grab minor placing.
Steadied soon after start and shifted across behind runners, dropping to last. Swung widest into straight and finished off nicely down centre track.
Pressed forward from an outside gate and held 3-wide without cover 3L from leader at the turn. Kept wide throughout and boxed on gamely in straight without closing gap.
Away nicely, pressed forward, settling on-out 2L from leader. Shaken up top of straight to challenge but only one-paced. (Rider reported unbalanced in action closing stages)
Beaten for early pace, dropping one-out behind midfield. Swung wide into straight but only one-paced under hard riding.
Jumped OK, ridden along in midfield, one-away from fence. Slightly hampered home turn, one-paced in straight.
Ridden along early to hold fence in midfield, before checking off heels home turn. One-paced in straight.
No pace, dropping to rear along fence. Last into straight, boxed on one-paced.
Began well, gabbing box seat and keeping tabs on leader. Lost position home turn and gave ground gradually in straight. (Lame right front leg).
Caught 3-wide no cover before improving to the lead 700M, led them slowly in middle stages, kept on well turning in, held handy margin at 150M and had enough to hold off rivals late.
Restrained in midfield, raced keenly middle stages, brought wide 500M, kept chasing on straightening to be nearest at the finish.
Never for off from leaders, battled on well final 300M to secure a minor spot in a bunched finish.
Saved ground along the fence, within striking distance always, worked home steadily turning in to claim 4th in a bunched finish.
Shifted back from wide draw, settled last 7Ls off the slow pace, ran on well up the fence final 300M but awkwardly placed late stages and not ridden out.
Taken back from draw 11, held up 2nd last 6Ls off the slow pace, swung widest home and chased well to the line.
Always prominent, 2nd turning in and holding his position to 150M, faded and swamped by rivals late.
Shaken up early to chase leaders but unable to slot in, caught wide no cover from 700M, ran on steadily turning for home but always held by leaders.
Began awkwardly, moved up to the fore, led until passing 700M, remained close up to 250M but weakened thereafter. (Lame LF.)
Taken back from wide draw, travelled keenly 900M, 4-5Ls to make up 400M, made some ground in straight without threatening.
Eased back to 3rd last 5Ls off the slow pace on settling, failed to make progress over final 300M.
Settled down in 8th, 4Ls off the slow pace in midfield, couldn't pick up in straight.

Settled in midfield about 4L off the pace, soon came to challenge after straightening and gained upper hand over 150 metres out.
Amongst leaders early before taken over 2L back in 3rd, tracked the leaders into straight, hit the front briefly over 200 metres out, soon headed.
Settled towards the rear, baulked for a run early in straight, finished off race strongly.
Settled at the back from a wide gate, commenced move rounding home bend and widest runner into straight, ran on down the centre of the track to be nearest at finish.
Settled just worse than midfield on the rail, saved ground turning in, ran on to hold some chance passing the 200 metres but unable to sustain effort closing stages.
Tailed off to the straight, ran on past well-beaten runners, never nearer.
Broke well from a wide gate, disputed lead and gradually shifted towards the rail with race leader far side, unable to sustain effort after straightening.
Soon led from a wide gate and gradually shifted across for rails run, faded under pressure soon after straightening. (Mucus in trachea)

Moderate start, soon recovered along the rail to be just better than midfield 3L back in 4th, slightly closer to pace on the bend but made no impression in the run home. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Settled 3-wide without cover in midfield in 6th, soon weakened under pressure in straight.

Placing: PU
Comment: Well back, dropped out from home bend. (Bled)
Pushed to hold the rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, ran on well to win by a narrow margin.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, benefited by the slow sectionals, closed off strongly, just missed by a narrow margin.
In front of midfield, 2 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, dashed strongly 300M for 3rd.
Eased to sit in midfield early, trapped 3 wide, moved forward 1000M to take advantages from the slow sectionals, just held ground in straight.
Pushed to obtain box seat, harmed by the slow pace, blocked whole straight, not tested.
Settled in front of midfield, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, blocked whole straight, not tested.
Pushed early, just behind midfield, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 300M.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, dashed well 250M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, harmed by the slow pace, just held ground in straight.
Eased back, trapped 2-4 wide, not suited by the slow pace, just held ground in straight.
Eased back, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, just held ground in final stages.
At rear, 2-4 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, dashed well 150M.
Slow away, at rear, 2-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no dash.
Began fairly, travelled midfield, improved at Home Turn, made good ground in the final stages, finished strongly.
Urged along and settled at handy position, fought hard entire straight, approaching 300M rider dropped whip, came home strongly.
Jumped well then ridden along to take lead, asked for effort passing 400M, kept on and finished solidly.
Settled midfield, commenced to improve at Home Turn, made up some late ground, finished solidly.
Moderate start, settled midfield, widest on straightening, made ground passing 150M, worked home well.
Jumped fairly, travelled midfield on rail, battled hard in the straight, finished well.
Urged along to settle handy position, under pressure in the straight, gave ground passing 150M, came home OK.
Started well to take box seat, shifted out for improving at Home Turn, one-paced in the straight.
Raced midfield on rail, tried to improve at Home Turn, kept on fence in the straight, one-paced.
Jumped nicely then taken back for cover, settled behind midfield, one-paced in the straight.
Slow to begin, settled behind midfield on rail, failed to run on in the final stages.
Jumped OK, ridden along to settle in front of midfield, asked for effort in the early straight but no response, faded out passing 200M.
Hampered at start then taken back, never in it.
Taken back at start, no response throughout the race, finished disappointing.
Away well, shared early pace before settling one-out 2L from leader passing 800m. Dropped to 3rd around turn, got clear run in straight, finished strongly to win on the line.
Hard ridden to lead passing 900m, pulling 2L clear at turn. Kicked ahead on straightening and kept finding when challenged in straight, only to be nosed out on the line.
Unable match early pace, dropping one-out to behind midfield. Held position to turn-in, taken wide in straight and finished off nicely to grab minor placing.
Pressed forward from outside draw, racing wide without cover in midfield. Allowed to slide forward around turn to sit outside leader entering straight. Kept on well to 200m before tiring.
Slow into stride, vigorously ridden but didn't muster, dropping towards rear along fence, Had to be ridden mid-race to hold position, switched out 300m to get run, ran on fairly.
Jumped OK, then ridden to hold one-out position 3L from leader. Unbalanced turn, boxed on gamely in straight without closing gap.
Ridden early to hold forward position 3L from leader but travelled keenly around turn when put under pressure. One-paced in straight.
Vigorously ridden on jumping but unable match early pace, dropping towards rear along fence. Shaken up turning for home but only one-paced.
Shifted across behind runners soon after start, dropping to last, then became detached from field despite hard riding. Last into straight before making up good ground final 300m.
Ridden early to hold midfield position along rail, but shuffled back around home turn. Limited response when put under pressure from 500m, finishing one-paced.
Shifted across behind runners soon after start looking for cover, dropping towards rear. Hard ridden in straight but little response.
Away well, shared early pace before dropping into slipstream of leader at turn. Under pressure on straightening and dropped out final 200m.
Away with them, positioned a length or so back on rail, easy run on turn, finished off strongly to score.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, kept on well after turning in, but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, same position on turn, taken widest in straight and finished off very strongly to be nearest on line.
Began well, positioned 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, awkwardly placed close to heels near 1300M, similar position on turn, angled out early in straight and finished off evenly.
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, slightly improved along the rail on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly. (Jockey was dislodged after the race.)
Jumped with them from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, kept on evenly to the line.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back in midfield, steadied near 1100M, bumped turning in, no daylight early in straight, one-paced when clear thereafter.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, positioned 5 to 6 lengths back on rail at rear, saved ground on turn, showed no progress in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, travelled wide and without cover at front, there to turn, peaked early in straight and weakened gradually thereafter when hard run took effect.
Crowded out start, raced 7 lengths back at rear, same margin back on turn, only passed some tired runners in straight.
Began well, raced prominently, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Jumped with them, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with cover, 5 lengths or so back, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened over the final furlong.
Moderately away from a wide draw, taken back to race 6 lengths back at rear, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start, raced at tail throughout, finished last, never competitive.
Settled in about midfield, 5-1/2L behind in a 2 wide position, produced good kick after 200M, finished off gamely to score.
At the rear, 6-1/2L behind 4 wide with cover, kept on gamely until caught by winner in final strides, just missed.
Taken back and raced at the rear, 8-1/4L behind 3 to 4 wide with cover, closed off well for 3rd after a spirited run.
Eased and settled in midfield, 4-1/4L behind but trapped very wide throughout, despite that kept on well to the line. (Whip dropped at 100M)
Pushed and settled in box-seat, detached from leaders until after 800M, ran on well to the line.
Sent forward to take rail and led by about 3/4L, headed passing 150M, one paced in the straight.
Settled in one-off one-back position but detached from leaders until after 800M, kept on one paced.
Slow to jump, settled towards the rear, 6-1/2L behind 3 wide with cover, made ground steadily.
Crowded at start, in behind midfield in initially, shuffled to the back at first turn, saved ground in the straight.
Slow to begin, raced at the rear 7-1/4L behind 2 wide, made ground on outside track.
Jumped well, pushed and sat outside the leader, about 3/4L off, faded passing 300M.
Ridden and settled in about midfield, 4-1/2L behind along the rail, not competitive.
Settled in midfield, 5L behind 3 wide with cover, gave ground from 300M. (Confirmed bleeder)
Blundered start, ridden forward but might 6-wide in midfield 1000m. Allowed to stride forward to lead passing 800m. Joined up front at turn-in, but kicked ahead 250m, pulling clear.
Pressed forward from wide draw, sharing lead before crossed 800m, taking sit one-out behind leader. Closed in at turn-in but unable match winner's finishing burst.
Began awkwardly, ridden forward looking for cover, slotting in one-out 3L from leader at turn. Kept on well in straight to grab minor placing.
Hard ridden to on jumping, then shared pace until crossed 800m, dropping into box seat. Chased leader thereafter without closing gap.
Ridden early to hold rail but shuffled to behind midfield when field bunched up approaching turn. Kept on fairly in straight.
Ridden early to look for cover but held 4-wide to turn 3L from leader. Swung very wide entering straight, only one-one-paced under pressure.
Ridden to hold forward position but held 3-wide without cover 2L from leader. Continued to travel wide to 200m before tiring.
Jumped well, ridden to hold one-out position 3L from leader to turn. One-paced on straight.
Away nicely, ridden to hold one-out position in midfield but shuffled towards rear when field bunched up entering turn. Shaken up at turn-in but only one-paced.
Bumped and unbalanced shortly after start, ridden but didn't muster, dropping 3-wide towards rear. Hung out at turn, wide into straight, limited response when asked.
Steadied on jumping and shifted across behind runners, dropping to last. Made up some ground around home turn but one-paced in straight.
Hampered soon after start, dropping towards rear along rail. Dropped to last around turn and failed to respond in straight.
Travelled along the stand's rail and never far off from leaders, moved up to 2nd 200M and kept chasing, looked set to finish 2nd until leader went miss and eased down passing 50M.
Led steadily along stand's rail, kicked clear inside 250M, looked set to win but went amiss in the left front leg passing 50M, eased down and caught near line.
Chased leaders, kept on steadily to line for 3rd, honest effort.
Slow out, ended up in last first half, no clear run until 250M, chased well to the line, got up for 4th 50M.
Chased leaders, no clear run 400M-150M, not properly tested, closed well enough when pulled to the center final 100M.
Settled just behind the pace, bustled along passing halfway, well held in the run home. (Jockey reported his horse did not feel comfortable in the race.)

From draw 1 raced alone towards the far rail, always in touch with the main group on the other side, plugged away to the line without threatening. (Jockey and Trainer questioned regarding riding tactics.)

Badly unbalanced on jumping, rushed along to go forward, up with leaders 3 off the stand's rail, one paced final 200M, steadied 100M and faded out of contention. (Jockey and Trainer questioned re riding tactics.)
From draw 2 crossed to race towards the outside of main group, couldn't quicken when placed under pressure 300M. (Jockey unable to offer any explanation for the performance.)
Not far off behind leaders but came under pressure halfway and couldn't sprint with them.
Restrained in the early stages and shifted towards the stands' rail, 3Ls off the pace 400M in 9th, couldn't kick on, just plodded home.
Positively ridden, shared lead with rivals, struggled passing 300M, no extra 150M. (Jockey reported his horse did not feel comfortable in the race.)
Near last from beginning, couldn't keep up halfway, never came on from back.
Towards the rear, struggled to make an impression in the run home. Never threatened.
A little slow from gate, pushed through along rail to sit 4L behind the pace approaching turn. Came off fence 300m, raced tight 150m, pushed through to lead 100m, pulled clear.
Jumped straight to the lead from widest gate but kept away from fence by inside runner. Passed 800m and took sit 1L behind. Rolled forward on straightening, led 250m, caught 100m, boxed on.
Hard ridden to hold forward position, settling one-out 2L from leader. Taken 3-wide turning for home to look a chance at turn-in, but no match for first two final 300m.
Ridden to hold midfield position, one-away from fence. Swung a wide into straight and boxed on gamely.
Bumped and unbalanced start, dropping to last. Made progress along rail around home turn, switched out in straight, ran on fairly.
Hard ridden to go forward, pushing through along rail to lead passing 800m. Collared shortly after straightening and gave ground final 200m.
Began awkwardly, hard ridden to hold rail but slow to muster, dropping to midfield when crossed by several rivals. Niggled at to hold position turn, one-paced in straight.
Bumped and unbalanced at start, settling towards rear. Stayed well back to turn, switched out in straight, kept on fairly.
Ridden along early to find cover before slotting in one-out behind midfield on settling. Taken very wide in straight but only one-paced.
Pressed forward from an outside draw and trapped 3-wide without cover 3L from leader. Kept tabs to 200m before tiring.
Ridden along looking for cover before settling 3-wide towards rear at turn. Taken very wide in straight but only one-paced.

Ridden early before looking for cover approaching turn, dropping three-wide towards rear. Last around turn, very wide in straight but little progress.(Lame in its right front leg with a swollen right front fetlock)
Jumped well from gate 9, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead, kicked clear after turning in and scored.
Begin well, raced 2 wide in 2nd, travelled well to turn, kept on well in straight but couldn't catch the winner. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 10, raced 9 lengths back at rear, slightly improved along the rail on turn, in traffic early in straight, finished off strongly when clear thereafter to take 3rd.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, wider on turn, kept on well in straight to make frame.

Jumped well from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, same position on turn, made some progress in straight. (Had a wound to the outside of the right front fetlock.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back to race at rear, 7 lengths back, similar position on turn, taken wide in straight and made some progress.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, no clear running early in straight and steadied near 200M, not able to test properly.
Taken back from barrier 13, raced wide with cover at rear, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped well from a middle draw, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, peaked near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 9 lengths or so back at tail, still well back on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Away with them, raced in midfield, 4 lengths back, 2 wide turning, peaked early in straight and weakened thereafter.
Jumped well, raced 3 to 4 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to sit 2 lengths behind the leader, there to turn, peaked near 250M, weakened thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 6 lengths back on rail at rear, saved ground on turn, found no daylight early in straight, emptied near 200M and eased thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)

Broke well, settled in forward of midfield, in similar position in 5th some 3L back turning in, fought on dourly in straight to just get up on line.
Broke well, tracked the leader to straight, hit the front over 100 metres out, only to be caught close to home.
Slightly slow out, made steady headway to be just worse than midfield 800 metres out, hampered and lost position leaving the Rock, finished off race well to snatch 3rd close home.
Began fairly, settled in midfield, lost position coming onto home bend, renewed effort turning into straight, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Jumped fairly, settled just worse than midfield, in similar positon on the rail turning in, produced good late impression close stages.
Broke well from the widest gate, ridden forward before settling 2L back in 3rd far side, in similar position turning in, kept on before finding no extra inside final 100 metres.
Soon took up running from the one draw, led and held over 1L advantage to straight, headed under pressure over 100 metres out.
Moderate start, settled just better than midfield in 5th on the rail about 3L off the pace, became 4th passing the Rock and saved ground for 3rd upon straightening, soon weakened.
Jumped fairly, settled wide without cover in midfield, gave ground steadily from approaching home turn.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, remained in last few to straight, found nothing.
Soon dropped to the rear, never a danger.
Soon dropped to last, never seen with a chance.
Settled in midfield, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, drifted away 200M to score.
Pushed to occupy the box seat, not suited by the fast sectionals, ran on well for 2nd.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, sat 2 wide, just held ground in straight.
Eased back, 2 wide, favoured by the fast pace, lack room 300M, progressed steadily when clear.
Bumped start, eased back, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 250M.
Hard ridden to take rail, led at fast sectionals, hung on until 150M weakened.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast sectionals, out of fuel 200M.
Behind midfield, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, ran on fairly.
Bumped start, eased back, trapped 3 wide, suited by the fast tempo, ran on just ok.
Eased to rear, raced 3-4 wide throughout, favoured by the fast pace, no dash.
At back, along the fence, checked 600M, benefited by the fast pace, no progress.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, suited by the fast tempo, emptied 300M.
Began well then took midfield position, issued a strong challenge at Home Turn, battled well to win.
Started well, raced behind leaders, asked for effort in the early straight, fought well and just missed by short head.
Urged along then took lead after passing 1200M, asked for effort in the early straight, fought hard and came home solidly.
Ridden along at start then steadied to obtain cover, settled midfield on rail, asked for effort passing 400M, made ground final 100M, finished solidly.
Jumped well then took the forward position on rail, drifted back in mid race, commenced to improve approaching 400M, worked home well.
Travelled wide without cover until passing 1200M, raced outside leader, tried to improve at Home Turn, gave ground passing 200M, finished fairly.
At the start bumped then taken back, travelled at tail, improved passing 500M, widest on straightening, finished one-paced.
Began OK, settled behind midfield, one-paced in the straight.
Ridden along to take lead, drifted back to box seat passing 1200M, weakened in the straight, failed to run on.
Crowed for room at start and drifted back, raced at tail on rail, no response in the straight.
Failed to muster speed and raced back despite being ridden along, travelled wide and without cover, failed to run on.
At the start bumped then taken back, travelled behind midfield on rail, never in it.
Jumped well, ridden forward, settling one-out, one-back 3L from leader. Rolled forward on straightening, hit front 150m, held off late challenge.
Ridden along one-out behind midfield to back stretch then put under hold. Swung wide entering straight and finished off strongly.
Taken to fence soon after start and settled 4L from leader. Stoked up passing 500m, ran on steadily along rail till hanging out final stages.
No early pace, settling along fence towards the rear. Shifted out turning for home, ran on steadily in straight to finish in the frame.
Restrained on jumping and shifted in for cover, settling at rear. Raced tight around home turn, taken very wide in straight, ran on fairly.
Hard ridden from outside draw, racing wide till taking lead passing 1500m. Pulled 2L clear 1000m before slowing pace. Led into straight, hung out from 200m, overtaken 150m, faded.
Ridden to hold midfield position, one-away from fence 4L from leader. Got close to heels at turn-in, boxed on fairly in straight.
Not pushed, racing one-out behind midfield. Taken wide entering straight but only one-paced under hard riding.
First out, shared pace before taking box seat first turn. Shaken up passing 550m, raced awkwardly home turn, gave ground in straight.
Shifted across behind runners soon after start, dropping to rear along fence. Stayed at rear mostly, one-paced in straight.
Jumped OK, pressed forward, settling behind midfield along fence. Stayed on fence throughout but limited response in straight.
Hard ridden from outside draw, racing wide before settling one-out 2L from leader back stretch. Niggled to hold position from 500m, faded. (Had substantial amount of blood in trachea).
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, travelled well on turn, finished off very well in straight and scored.
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to race outside the leader in 2nd, travelled well on turn, kept on very well in straight but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Jumped with them, raced 4 to 5 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, taken wide in straight and hit the line strongly to get 3rd.
Jumped well from gate 10, showed early speed to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 150M, just stayed on for 4th.
Began well, bumped and unbalanced near 1050M, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back in 4th, same position on turn, finished off evenly.
Began fairly, bumped and unbalanced near 1050M, sat a length behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped with them, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly, never a threat to the first few.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths or so back, same position on turn, made no progress in straight.
Jumped well from a tricky gate, taken back to race 2 wide at rear, still 7 lengths back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide barrier, raced at tail throughout, never a threat.
Taken back to race at 6 lengths back on rail, difficult to settle in the middle stages, failed to close off in straight.
Raced in behind midfield, 6-1/2L behind along the rail, swung widest and finished off strongly to score by 1/2L.
Travelled in front of midfield, 4-1/2L behind 2 wide, ran on gamely to the line to take 2nd.
Bumped start, travelled behind the leaders, 2-3/4L behind 2 wide, finished off well but couldn't hold off the first two.
Bumped start, raced in about midfield, 5L behind along the rail, kept on fairly well though laying in in the straight.
Raced in front of midfield, 3-3/4L behind along the rail, slightly eased at 50M in a good run to the line.
Pushed forward to take the rail and led by about 1L, headed passing 150M, one paced to the line.
Eased after the start, raced towards the rear, 8-1/4L behind along the rail, made ground steadily and ran on.
Jumped awkwardly, settled in behind midfield, 6L behind 2 wide, improved slightly only but ran on.
Sent forward, prominent in a 2 wide position until slotted into the box-seat at 800M, one paced.
Taken back and raced at the rear, 9-3/4L behind along the rail, covered slight ground.
Bumped start, raced towards the rear throughout, never a factor.
Pushed, prominent but wide initially, improved to sit outside lead after 800M, found nothing in the straight. (Must trial)
Jumped to the front and led along rail until passed by rival 950m. Continued to hold rail, poked head in front 550m, kicked clear on straightening and kept finding to winning post.
Bumped start, then ridden to hold midfield position one-away from fence. Dropped back slightly home turn, took inside run in straight, finished strongly.
Jumped awkwardly but taken to fence and settled 3L from leader. Shifted out at turn-in but shifted in 300m for run and finished off nicely. (Rider momentarily dropped left rein 200m).
Bumped start, pressed forward, settling one-out 3L from leader. Swung wide into straight, battled on gamely to line while lying out under pressure from 200m.
Snagged back on jumping and taken in for cover, dropping towards rear along rail. Took inside run in straight and finished off gamely.
Began well, then ridden to hold rail in midfield. Stayed on rail around home turn and boxed on gamely in straight to be closest at finish.
Shifted in for cover soon after start, dropping to last. Remained at rear to straight when taken to centre field and ran on fairly.
Pushed forward but held wide in midfield before rolling forward to take narrow lead 950m. Kept one out by inside runner, overtaken 550m, boxed on gamely till flattened close home.
No early pace, dropping one-out towards rear. Taken wide entering straight but only one-paced.
Jumped well, shared pace to 950m before being eased back one-out 1.5L from leader. Kept tabs to 200m before swamped final stages. (Lame left front leg)
Jumped OK, ridden to hold midfield position but over-raced and didn't settle until straight. One-paced.
Shifted in for cover soon after start, dropping one-out towards rear. Swung widest into straight but made no headway.
Given a waiting ride near the rear, 8Ls off the pace middle stages, kept to inside while many others swung wide turning for home, ran on steadily to get up 100M and held on from fast finishing 2nd.
Not hurried, settled towards the rear 7Ls off the pace, driven wide into straight, closed off strongly final 300M, just missed.
Jumped on terms, had rail run never far off from leader, 3Ls off 400M, worked home well down the center of track.
Began well, restrained to sit behind leader, every chance final 300M, outsprinted by rivals final 150M.
Crossed to the lead 1300M, set slow pace early before quickening up middle stages, guided to center of track turning in, couldn't hold off rivals 150M.
Restrained after the start, held up 3-wide behind midfield 5-6Ls off the pace, swung wide into straight, stayed on mildly.
Positioned 2-wide just ahead of mid-division, awkwardly placed behind a weakening runner from 700M and lost ground, kept grinding to line turning home but always held by rivals.
Taken back from wide barrier, settled last 8-9Ls away, swung widest leaving home turn, ran on well but too much to make up.
In midfield, wide no cover from 1100M, ran on same pace in straight, never a serious threat. (Lame next day.)
Jumped on terms from inside gate, eased back to a position behind midfield, checked away from a weakening rival home turn, couldn't get closer to leaders in straight.
Failed to muster speed despite ridden, ended up behind midfield along the rail, under pressure home turn but couldn't pick up pace, weakened 200M.
Caught wide first turn, improved to race just off the pace 1100M, under pressure to keep up 700M, gave ground home turn and soon out of contention.
