Jumped well from the one draw, taken back behind midfield for cover early stages, commenced move down the centre of the track coming onto course proper, fought on gamely to assert authority final strides.
Broke well from the middle draw, soon came to join the leaders and hit the front after the first 400 metres, caught final strides.
Disputed lead, unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.
Settled in last few, finished off race strongly inside the final 250 metres, did best work late.
Moderate start, held up just off the pace, unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, soon recovered to midfield, inconvenienced briefly coming onto course proper, one-paced under pressure closing stages.
Moderate start, gradually settled just better than midfield near the centre of the track, found nothing closing stages.
Given early reminders, chased behind the leaders early stages, lost position over half-way out, one-paced closing stages.
Shared the pace on the rail, weakened from over 400 metres out. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Broke well, gradually dropped to last few despite ridden along.
Tightened at start, niggled along improving to within 2L of pace coming onto course prosper but soon folded up, beaten when checked about 200 metres out.
Soon dropped to the last, trailed the field most of the way, never seen with a chance.
Ridden positively from a low draw before settling in forward of midfield near the centre of the track, yielded ground from the 300 metres.
Settled behind midfield, found nothing under pressure inside the final 400 metres.
Pushed forward, harmed by the fast sectionals, closed off strongly and drifted away 250M to score with plenty in hands.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 400M for 2nd.
Hard ridden to obtain a midfield spot, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, made steady ground 400M for 3rd.
Hard ridden to hold the rail at back, raced keenly, favoured by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M.
Midfield, 2 wide, suited by the fast tempo, lack room 400M, ran on well until 150M flattened.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, ran on ok.
Eased to rear, trapped 3-4 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, made ground 200M.
Eased back, trapped 3-4 wide, suited by the fast pace, made minor ground 200M.
Hard ridden forward, box seat, harmed by the fast tempo, flattened 200M.
Eased back, favoured by the fast tempo, no progress.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast pace, out of fuel 250M.
Pressed forward, took rail and lead, clocked fast sectionals, emptied 250M.
At rear, suited by the fast pace, never improved.
Tailed out, never competitive.
Began fairly, settled behind midfield, commenced to improve in the early straight, quickened passing 100M and came home strongly to win.
At start hampered, travelled wide and without cover, raced strongly in the straight, just missed by neck.
Fast out, ridden along to take lead, fought hard entire straight, worked home solidly.
Urged along and settled in front of midfield, commenced to improve passing Home Turn, ran on and finished solidly.
Began OK and settled midfield, moved to handy position at Home Turn, came home nicely.
Taken back at start, widest on straightening, battled hard entire straight, worked home well.
Started nicely and took box seat, tried to improve at Home Turn, gave ground passing 100M, finished fairly.
Raced behind midfield, made some ground in the final stages, came home fairly.
On jumping crowed for room and lost ground, raced behind midfield on rail, under pressure but only one-paced in the straight.
Settled midfield on rail, gave ground passing 100M, failed to run on.
Settled behind midfield, asked for effort but only limited response in the straight.
Hard ridden to settle in font of midfield, gave ground in the straight, failed to run on.
At the start lost ground and stumbled when crowded for room, travelled at tail, never in it.
Travelled midfield, weakened passing 200M and failed to finish off. Next day lame left front.
Away well, settling one-back, one-out 2L from leader. Rolled forward top of straight, hit front 300m, kept finding when strongly challenged for narrow win.
Jumped with field, holding fence in midfield 4L from leader. Kept tabs to straight, finished strongly along fence, failing narrowly.
Hard ridden but slow to muster, settling behind midfield away from fence. Kept wide without cover around turn, wide in straight, finished strongly.
Not pushed, settling one-out in midfield. Got shuffled back home turn when field bunched up, no run in straight until 200m, finished strongly.
Away nicely but tended to over-race and checked 1200m dropping to midfield. Checked again 900m. Kept on well in straight to finish close to place-getters.
Began fairly, then crowded before restrained and shifted in to rail behind midfield. No run entering straight, got close to heels 300m when improving, finished off nicely.
Ridden to hold forward position but left wide without cover 1200m. Rolled forward but wide entering straight to look a chance 200m before flattened close home.
Away well, grabbing box seat 2L from leader. Kept tabs to straight and kept battling under pressure before being swamped close home.
Jumped well, staying with pace before burrowing through along rail to lead 1150m. Set strong pace to 300m when collared, giving ground gradually.
Outpaced, racing towards rear along fence. Shifted out at turn-in to make run but only one-paced.
Steadied shortly after start and shifted in for cover, dropping one-out towards rear. Put under pressure turning for home but only one-paced in straight.
Hard ridden from wide draw to lead but kept wide by inside runner and passed 1150m, taking sit 1L behind. Under pressure at turn-in and faded. (Had substantial blood in trachea)
Slow into stride and then steadied off heels, dropping to last. Remained at rear throughout.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide, 1-2 lengths back in 3rd, checked off heels and unbalanced near 1100M, same position on turn, kept on very well in straight to score narrowly.
Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, outside to the leader, travelled well on turn, kept going well in straight, just headed last stride.
Quickly into stride, showed early speed to take the lead and set a slow tempo, kept on well after turning in, headed in the final stages, stayed on for 3rd.
Away with them, positioned 2 lengths or so back on rail, easy run on turn, kept on well in straight, but posed no threat to the first few.
Taken back from the widest draw, but still unable to slot in, raced wide at rear early, improved in the middle stages, 3rd turning in, kept on steadily without quickening in straight.
Slightly slow out, bumped and unbalanced early, raced wide in midfield, found cover in the middle stages, bumped near 200M, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Steadied on jumping, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, same position on turn, bumped near 200M, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 4 to 5 lengths back at rear, there to turn, showed no progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 4 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 6 lengths back at tail, still well back on turn, finished off one-paced.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at tail, same position on turn, made no progress in straight.
Stood flat-footed at start and lost considerable ground, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Average to begin, raced 4 to 5 lengths back on rail, showed no response to riding after turning in, emptied and eased in the final stages.
In just behind midfield, 7L behind along the rail, made good ground on the inside and ran on strongly to score by 1-1/4L.
Sent forward, 2 wide initially, took rail and raced 1-3/4L off the lead at 800M, ran on nicely to the finish.
Raced in just behind midfield, 7L behind 2 wide, kept on well to the line.
Travelled strongly and prominent early, stride along and led by 1-3/4L, flattened and caught at 150M.
Occupied the box-seat until shifted away from the rail at 800M, sat 3-1/2L off, kept on fairly well in the straight.
Eased and raced towards the rear, 9L behind along the rail, held up early and onto heels near 250M, ran on okay.
Raced in about midfield, 5-1/2L behind 2 wide, produced a good dash near 250M, one paced thereafter.
Settled to race in about midfield, 5-1/2L behind along the rail, kept on one paced to the line.
Travelled in midfield, 6L behind but 3 wide and without cover throughout, one paced.
Rolled forward and raced in one-off one-back position, sat 4L off, faded in the straight. (Lame left front)
Slow to jump, raced in behind midfield, 8-1/2L behind 2 wide, hung in in the straight, failed to make ground.
Eased and raced the rear, niggled from 800M, never a factor.
Ridden to hold midfield position, one-away from fence. Swung wide entering straight, finished strongly to hit from 75m, pulling clear final strides.
Inconvenienced start, taken to fence and settled 5L from leader to turn. Held for run top of straight, shifted in for clear running 400m, finished strongly.
Shifted in for cover soon after start, dropping to rear. Stayed at rear until straightening, shifted out for clear running and finished strongly to grab minor placing.
Ridden early to hold forward position before steadied 1100m and shifted in for cover behind midfield. Taken to centre field in straightening and finished off nicely.
Vigorously ridden to lead approaching 950m, kicking 2L clear at the turn. Kept on strongly early in straight but started to shorten stride 100m and swamped final 75m.
Pressed forward from an outside draw, racing 3-wide without cover 3L from leader. Kept on gamely to 200m before tiring.
Hard ridden to share early before stalking leader in one-out position to straight. Under pressure passing 200m and swamped close home.
First into stride before sliding in box seat approaching turn, 2L from leader. Rolled forward top of straight to look a chance before flattened final 200m.
Shifted in for cover soon after start but lost contact with field because of fast pace. Last into straight before finishing off fairly.
Got off nicely, chased leading pack, settling midfield along rail 4L from leader. Shifted out on straightening to make run but only one-paced.
Ridden to hold forward position, settling one-out 4L from leader. Kept tabs to straight but only one-paced under hard riding.
Tracked pace in a steadily run race, went forward to tackle leader 500M, gained upper hand inside 100M, fought off stiff challenge to hold on.
Began well from widest draw, settled down in 5th 4-5Ls behind leader, hit the line well over final 300M, just failed to reel in stable companion.
Tracked leaders, had every chance turning in, kept chasing hard to the line, nearest finish.
Positive ridden, led from 1500M, pressed by rival 500M and dueled all the way to 100M, faded late stages and edged out to 4th.
Held up in mid-division 5-6Ls back, ran on well down center of track, continued to challenge leaders passing 200M but always held.
Reserved behind mid-division 7Ls off the pace, bustled along 500M, made steady ground behind the leaders.
Began only fairly, settled 9th about 9Ls behind, brought wide to challenge, ran on moderately without threatening leaders. (Jockey dropped whip 150M.)
Chased leaders along the fence, kept on same pace turning in and couldn't' make any headway, faded 200M.
From wide draw dropped back to the rear last 12Ls off the pace, still plenty to do turning in, closed off final 400M fastest but had too much to make up.
Quickly guided to the fence after the start, 5Ls off the pace middle stages, couldn't lift passing 400M, never a threat to leaders.
Restrained after the start, settled near rear over 10Ls off the pace, made no real progress in straight.
Taken back from wide barrier, well off the pace early stages, moved closer home turn, couldn't muster the speed to challenge leaving the bend, no extra 200M.
Quietly ridden, towards the rear always, didn't respond to riding early straight, never involved.
Began awkwardly, then ridden to hold midfield position 3L from leader but away from fence. Improved around home turn, hard ridden on straightening, hit front 150m, pulled clear final strides.
Hard ridden from outside draw to go forward, racing one-out 1L from leader. Urged forward top of straight, hit front 300m, joined 150m, unable match winner final strides.
No early pace, racing towards rear close to fence. Took closer order around turn, got inside run in straight and finished off nicely to grab minor placing.
Not pushed early, racing between horses towards the rear. Got clear running top of straight and ran on steadily to finish in the frame.
Hard ridden early but slow to muster, eventually racing 3-wide 3L from leader home turn. Swung wide into straight and boxed on gamely.
Away well, holding rail and sharing early pace before dropping into box seat approaching turn. Kept on one-paced in straight.
Outpaced, racing one-out at rear. Taken very wide entering straight and ran on fairly to be closest at finish.
Hard ridden early but didn't muster, racing 3-wide behind midfield to turn. Kept wide around home turn, one-paced in straight.
Steadied shortly after start and shifted in to rail at midfield, 5L from leader. Stayed along rail home turn but only one-paced in straight.
No early pace, racing between horses behind midfield to turn. Made some progress early in straight before tiring final 200m.
Jumped well, pressed forward, racing one-back, one-out 2L from leader. Kept on well to 250m when crowded and blundered, dropping out.
Ridden along from widest draw, steadied 1000m and shifted across behind runners, dropping to last. Stayed at rear to straight when ran past beaten runners.
Shifted in for cover soon after start but held 3-wide at rear before getting cover entering turn. Found little in straight when pressed.
First out, then set good pace to 300m when collared. Kept on to 200m when flattened.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in 5th, travelled well throughout, took the lead easily after turning in, scored comfortably.
Steadied on jumping, raced 2 wide behind midfield, difficult to settle when checked off heels in the middle stages, angled out after turning in and made very good progress to take 2nd.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths back in midfield, there to turn, finished off well in straight but never a threat to the winner, missed 2nd on line.
Crowded out start and unbalanced, raced 6 lengths back at rear, difficult to settle near 800M, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Jumped well, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, no clear running early in straight, made some progress when clear thereafter.
Crowded on jumping and unbalanced, unable to slot in, travelled 3 wide and without cover, still 3 wide in 4th on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually in the closing stages.
Began fairly from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, in traffic early in straight, angled out near 300M and finished off evenly.
Taken back to race 5 lengths or so back on rail, slightly improved along the rail on turn, no daylight early in straight, made some progress when clear thereafter.
Away with them, taken back to race at rear, 6 lengths or so back, still well back on turn, taken widest in straight and finished off evenly.
Jumped well from the widest draw, unable to slot in early, taken back to race 3 wide with cover at rear, 5 lengths back, there to turn, taken wide in straight and finished off one-paced.
Began well, raced outside to the leader, same position on turn, peaked near 300m, weakened gradually thereafter.
Crowded on jumping and unbalanced, raced at tail throughout, never a threat.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Away with them, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead to turn, headed early in straight, weakened sharply thereafter, finished tailed out. (Bled from both nostrils.)

Jumped best, settled just off the pace in 3rd on the rail, saved ground turning for home, soon hit the front and drew clear inside the final 200 metres. (Questioned for improved performance)
Tracked the leading trio just over 2L back in 4th, ran on under pressure holding some chance at the 200 metres, found winner too good.
Settled about 6L back in 6th, baulked for a run early in straight, unable to quicken to threaten despite the clear passage inside the final 200 metres.
Settled well back in last of the 7-runner field, went widest into straight, made up good ground down the centre of the track to be nearest at finish.
Settled about 5L back in 5th, commenced run on the final bend swinging 5-wide into the straight reaching within 2L of the lead, held some chance briefly but unable to sustain effort closing stages.
Soon took up running setting a smart pace, led until dropped away quickly inside the final 200 metres. (Tactic questioned)
Settled just off the pace in 1L 2nd, folded up quickly after straightening. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Settled in midfield, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M.
Took rail easily and led at fast sectionals, hung on strongly until 50M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Pressed forward, sat 2 wide just off the leader, not suited by the fast sectionals, ran on well for 3rd.
Obtained box seat, not suited by the fast tempo, in the straight hung in and just held ground.
Pushed to hold the rail just behind midfield, favoured by the fast pace, made steady ground 300M, lack room 150M.
Sat in front of midfield, pace fast, 2 wide, just held ground in straight.
At back, took rail, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 200M.
Trapped 2-3 wide in midfield, pace fast, made ground 250M.
Eased at start, 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, made ground 250M.
Eased at start, took rail, benefited by the fast pace, lack turn of foot.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in front of midfield, flattened 200M.
Eased back, 2 wide, suited by the fast pace, never improved.
Jumped out well and took the lead, hold the position throughout the race, finished strongly to win.
Settled at handy position on rail, asked for effort at Home Turn, ran on gamely to the line to take 2nd.
Slow to begin, raced at tail on rail, commenced to improve passing 600M, made up nice late ground, finished well.
Began fairly and settled midfield on rail, drifted back approaching 600M, kept on rail at Home Turn, came home well.
Moderate start, settled behind midfield, tried to improve passing 700M, made Home Turn wide, fought hard entire straight, finished OK.
Settled at handy position, asked for effort at Home Turn but limited response, one-paced.
Raced midfield, passing 1200M improved to outside the lead, asked for effort passing 700M, gave ground passing 150M, failed to make impression.
Taken back at start and travelled at tail, widest on straightening, never in it.
Ridden along to settle outside the lead, gradually gave ground passing 800M, failed to run on.
Settled at rear, passing 800M improved to forward position, faded out in the straight.
Began fairly, then crowded out before making up ground along rail 3L from leader. Switched out on straightening and finished strongly to win close home.
Enjoyed the run of the race in box seat 2.5L from leader. Picked up momentum on straightening, surged ahead to lead 100m, run down near line.
Found early pace hot, settling one-out behind midfield. Not pushed till straightening, taken to centre track and finished strongly, doing best work final 200m.
Hard pressed from widest draw to go forward, eyeballing leader around turn before leading for a few strides passing 150m. Flattened close home.
Ridden to hold forward position 4L from leader and one-away from fence. Taken very wide in straight and finished off nicely.
Outpaced, racing towards rear close to fence. Stayed on fence in straight and ran on steadily to finish just behind place-getters.
Bounced well to lead on settling. Joined by another passing 700m, increasing tempo. Overtaken 150m and gave ground gradually.
Steadied on jumping and taken in for cover, dropping one-out towards rear. Well back entering straight before running on fairly between horses final 200m.
Shifted in for cover soon after start but found pace too strong, dropping well back. Stayed at rear to straight, finishing off fairly. (Found to be a "roarer" as previously reported).
Ridden early to get forward position but held behind midfield without cover. Wide around home turn, spent force in straight, finishing one-paced.
Away well, settling one-out, one-back 2.5L from leader at turn. Kept on gamely to 200m before tiring.
Slow into stride, dropping to last. Trailed field thereafter and never competitive.
Began well from gate 1, positioned right behind the leader early, angled out near 700M, kept on well after turning in and scored by a short head.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead on turn, kept on very well in straight but just unable to hold off the winner late.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, unbalanced and lost ground near 800M, travelled well on turn, finished off strongly in straight to be nearest on line.
Began fairly, raced 5 lengths back on rail, slightly improved along the rail on turn, angled out early in straight and made good progress until awkwardly placed on heels over the concluding stages.
Bumped start, positioned 2 lengths or so back on rail, easy run on turn, kept on well until no clear running near final 100M, not able to be ridden out near the finish.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths or so back, hampered near 750M, similar position on turn, angled out in straight and made some progress without threatening.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, steadied off heels near 800M, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 6 to 7 lengths back at rear, hampered near 750M, still 6 lengths back on turn, no clear running early in straight, made minor progress when clear thereafter.
Bumped start and stumbled, raced wide behind midfield, travelled keenly in the middle stages, finished off one-paced.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, saved ground throughout, showed no progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced wide without cover in midfield, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from gate 10, raced 3 wide at rear, last turning in, failed to close off in straight, finished last.
Raced just in front of midfield, 4-1/4L behind 2 wide, showed good kick after 200M, finished off strongly to take the prize.
Pushed, settled for the box-seat when handed up lead at 1300M, sat 2-1/4L off, closed off gamely for 2nd.
Settled in just behind midfield, 5-3/4L behind the lead 2 wide, ran on well to the line to take 3rd.
Travelled in just behind midfield, 5-3/4L behind 2 wide, closed off well in the straight whilst laying in.
Rolled forward and settled to race outside the lead, sat about 1L off, found no extra at 100M, just held onto 5th.
Raced just in front of midfield, 4L behind along the rail, did not improve but ran on fairly to the line.
Pushed and settled in one-off one-back position, sat 2-1/2L behind the lead, kept on one paced to the line.
Eased and raced at the rear, 10L behind along the rail, made ground steadily, ran on okay.
Pushed, took rail and outright lead near 1300M, led by about 1L, headed passing 200M, very one paced.
Travelled in behind midfield, 7-3/4L behind along the rail, improved steadily, ran on.
Taken back and raced in worse than midfield, 7-1/2L behind 2 wide, made ground and kept on going to the line.
Eased and raced towards the rear, 9-1/2L behind 2 wide, saved minor ground.
Pressed forward on jumping, taking first turn 4-wide before rolling forward to sit 1L behind leader passing 1200m. Hit front 250m and though tiring final strides held on for narrow win.
Steadied early and taken in for cover, dropping to rear along rail. Kept under tight hold to straight. Surged forward from 300m, forced to switch course 100m, charged forward but just failed.
Ridden to get forward position, taking first turn 4-wide. Allowed to improve 3-wide from midfield to get within range at turn-in. Kept on strongly in straight to grab minor placing.
Crowded out start, steadied, taken in for cover, dropping to rear. Remained at rear until turn-in, taken to centre track and finished off strongly.
Hard ridden from wide draw, taking first turn 4-wide, dropping to behind midfield. Pushed on from 1100m to sit 2L behind leader 900m. Boxed on well in straight but swamped final strides.
Reluctant leader on jumping, before sliding into box seat first turn. Put under pressure turning for home and boxed on one-paced in straight.
Jumped OK but not pushed, taken to rail and settled towards rear. Stayed on fence around turn, took inside run in straight, blocked for run passing 100m, boxed on.
Ridden to find cover early, settling one-out behind midfield. Stoked up passing 500m, swung wide intro straight, steadied 150m, boxed on fairly.
Jumped OK, pressed forward, poking head in front 1500m before hanging out first turn. Retook lead 1250m, kept on to 250m when overtaken and faded.
Ridden to hold forward position one-out from rail but shuffled back first turn, settling behind midfield. Stayed on rail at turn-in but found little under pressure. (Lame right hind leg)
Got off OK, pressed forward, sharing early pace before settling one-out, 2L from leader 900m. Under pressure from 500m and gave ground gradually.
Began awkwardly, pressed forward to hold rail but over-raced and checked first turn, dropping to midfield. Stayed on rail at turn-in but found nothing under pressure and faded.
Tracked leaders along the inside, travelled strongly to straight, moved up well to lead near 150M, always in control towards the finish completing a hat-trick of wins.
Never far off from leaders but no closer than 3-wide throughout the race, gave chase from 300M but couldn't reel in the odds on favourite. Easily accounted for the rest.
Held up 3-wide in midfield, 4Ls to make up 400M, swung widest leaving the bend, worked home well to claim 3rd just in time but not reached first two.
Reserved in midfield, well covered, worked home steadily without threatening first 2, just missed 3rd in a blanket finish
Led steadily, headed by winner nearing 150M, faded to 5th late stages.
In midfield hugging the rail, 3Ls off leader 400M, ran on only fairly and well held by leaders.
Taken across from wide barrier, held up last 6-7Ls off the steady pace, made some ground over final 300M without threatening.
Dropped back after the start, held up 2nd last 5-6Ls back, denied an inside early straight, closed off well switched lane, severely checked near the finish.
Eased back to a rearward spot, in 10th place 4-5Ls back, no clear until 200M, worked home well and could have finished closer.
Sent forward from draw 12, tracked leader 0.5L back, couldn't sustain run passing 200M, faded towards the line.
Jumped well to be chasing leaders passing 1000M, didn't quicken on straightening, outsprinted inside 200M.
From draw 6 ended up in a 3-wide spot without cover, close up to pace making home turn, weakened away 250M.

Rear early, made steady headway to reach 5th within 3L of pace on top of back straight, commenced move around home bend but baulked on straightening, ran on gamely to assert authority inside the 100M.
Settled towards the rear, made rapid progress approaching the 600 metres to dispute the lead rounding home bend, hit the front briefly over 200 metres out but overshadowed nearing finish.
Settled towards the rear, ran on quite well between runners in straight, did best work late.
Settled not far off the pace on the rail, chased leaders into straight, met minor inconvenience on straightening, fought on steadily without threatening.
Broke well and attempted to make all, joined by eventual runner-up approaching the final bend, soon weakened under pressure in straight.
Failed to muster and dropped to last few, trailed the field from the 1700 metres, widest runner turning for home, inconvenienced 250 metres out, fought on steadily under pressure.
Pressed forward from a wide gate before settling mostly 2L back in 4th, shuffled backward steadily from the Rock despite rails run turning for home, made no further in straight.
Slow to muster and given reminders, picked up around first bend to settle in close up 2nd, failed to keep up with pace from the 600 metres.

Close up briefly, soon dropped back to wide in midfield, came under pressure to hold place rounding final bend, wide into home straight, kept on before weakening under pressure inside final 200 metres. (Lame next day)
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, harmed by the slow tempo, unleashed strong finishing efforts 250M and scored.
Pushed to take rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on well until 50M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Eased back, trapped 3-4 wide, made early move from 600M, ran on strongly for 3rd.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, not suited by the slow tempo, lack room 300M, dashed strongly when clear.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide, favoured by the slow pace, just held ground in straight.
Pushed to obtain box seat, just held ground in straight, lack room 200M.
Very slow away, took cover at rear, 2 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, little dash 300M, lack room 200M.
At rear, 2 wide, lack room 300M, dashed well 150M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Hard ridden forward, sat outside the leader, benefited by the slow tempo, soon emptied 250M.
Pushed early, midfield 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, never improved.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Began awkwardly then pushed along to take box seat, drifted back passing 600M, commenced to improve passing 400M, in the straight fought well to win.
Settled behind midfield, issued challenge in the early straight, approaching the finishing line hung in under pressure, finished strongly. Missed by neck.
Urged along at start to settle at handy position, improved to box seat at Home Turn, kept on and finished solidly.
Travelled at tail, improved at Home Turn, made up nice late ground, worked home nicely.
Moderate start, settled midfield on rail, battled hard and made ground in the straight, finished well.
Raced midfield, asked for effort passing 500M but only limited response, finished OK.
Slow out then taken back, raced behind midfield on rail, passing 150M awkwardly placed close heels, finished fairly. Stalls test.
Taken back at start, raced behind midfield, one-paced in the straight.
Ridden along to take lead, asked for effort at Home Turn, weakened passing 150M, failed to make impression.
Travelled midfield, after 650M was left racing wide and without cover, widest on straightening, no response and failed to run on.
Began very awkwardly, travelled wide until passing 600M to raced outside the leader, weakened passing 200M and failed to run on.
Started fairly, raced at rear, never in it.
Away well, pressed forward, racing one-out 3L from leader. Swung 4-wide entering straight, surged forward to lead 100m, held off strongly challenge final strides.
Broke well, taken to rail and settle 3L from leader. Had clear rails run on straightening and finished strongly, only to fail narrowly.
Pressed forward to hold forward position but kept wide without cover 3L from leader. Moved forward home turn to hit front on straightening, but run down close home.
Began fairly, no pace, dropping one-out towards rear. Well back to straight, took inside run 300m and finished off strongly.
No early pace, racing one-out behind midfield. Taken very wide in straight and finished off nicely.
Quickly into stride, shared lead before dropping into box seat passing 900m. Kept close to 100m before tiring.
Pressed forward from widest draw, racing wide before surging to the front 1000m. Placed under pressure when joined by another home turn, overtaken 150m and faded.
Fractious in gate, slow to move, last on settling. Trailed field to straight, shifted out for clear running, finished off fairly. (Lame left front leg, substantial amount of blood in trachea)
Outpaced, dropping to behind midfield along rail. Stayed on rail home turn but only one-paced in straight.
Broke well, led for few strides before settling one-out, one-back. Kept tabs to 200m before tiring.
Steadied soon after start and taken in, settling behind midfield. Left wide without cover from 600m and only one-paced in straight.
Ridden to hold midfield position, one away from rail. Shaken up top of straight, boxed on fairly to 200m before fading.
Began well from gate 1, positioned a length or so back on rail, enjoyed the easy run throughout, finished off strongly in straight to score.
Moderately away from a tricky gate, raced 3 lengths back on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out in straight and made good progress to get 2nd.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, made good progress in straight to take 3rd.

Began well from a middle draw, unable to slot in early, sent forward from near 1200M to sit outside the leader, same position on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 150M, stayed on for 4th.
Fast into stride, took the lead easily, travelled well throughout, peaked and headed near 150M, slightly weakened thereafter.
Began fairly from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, difficult to settle near 1200M, still 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Steadied start, raced 5 lengths back on rail, saved ground throughout, finished off one-paced in straight.
Tightened at start, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back in midfield, over-raced near 1000M, 3 wide with cover thereafter, peaked on turn, finished off one-paced.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 6 lengths back at tail, still well back on turn, showed no progress in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, still well back on turn, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, showed no early speed, raced 3 wide with no cover in midfield, 3 lengths back on turn, weakened after turning in and eased. (See Racing Incidents.)
Raced in behind midfield, 3L behind 2 wide, showed good kick after 150M and closed off strongly to score.
Sent forward and always sat inside the lead along the rail, kept on going until caught by the winner near 50M.
Pushed and raced prominently early, sat about 1L off 3 wide with cover, ran on well on the outside track to take 3rd.
Rolled into a position in about midfield, sat 1-1/2L off 2 wide, ran on fairly inside the final 200M.
Settled to race towards the rear, 3L behind along the rail, made ground steadily along the inside rail.
Sent forward and raced prominently, assumed outright lead in 2 wide position after 650M, flattened approaching 100M.
Travelled in about a midfield position, 1-1/2L off along the rail, kept on until crowded passing 100M, ran on thereafter.
Awkward start, settled to race in behind midfield, 2-1/4L behind 3 wide with cover, one paced.
Niggled and raced just in front of midfield, 1-1/4L off but wide, swung widest and couldn't make ground.
Showed early speed before crowded at the first turn, then trapped wide and dropped to behind midfield, not competitive.
Sent forward, raced prominently but trapped wide throughout, weakened before entering the straight.
Taken back and remained at the rear throughout. (Irregular heart rhythm, bled and lame right front)
Snagged back after start, dropping to last pair along fence. Stayed at rear to straight, shifted out 250m to get clear running, finished strongly final 100m to score pulling clear.
Away well, pressed forward, settling one-out, one-back. Swung wide turning into straight, battled on gamely to hold second.
Jumped OK. Then ridden to hold rail in midfield. Took home turn awkwardly, battled on well in straight under whip.
Ridden along early while shifting in to grab rail behind midfield at turn. Ran on well in straight under whip to just miss a placing.
Speared to the front on jumping, pulling 2L clear at one stage. Led to 50m when swamped. (Had substantial amount of blood in trachea).
Jumped well, grabbing box seat 2L from leader. Boxed on gamely in straight before tiring close home and swamped.
Vigorously ridden from jump to get forward position, settling one-out 2L from leader. Kept chasing to 100m when ran out of stamina and faded.
Shifted across behind runners soon after start, settling one-out towards rear. Stayed at back to straight, took inside run, finished off fairly.
Ridden forward from outside draw, racing wide before getting cover one-out behind midfield approaching turn. Swung wide into straight, boxed on fairly.
Ridden to get forward position, settling one-out 4L from leader. Swung wide entering straight before running out of stamina, giving ground steadily.
Outpaced and last on settling. Dropped further back around turn, ran on fairly in straight.
Bumped and unbalanced start, then pushed forward racing 3-wide without cover 2L from leader. Spent force at turn-in and faded.
Away smoothly, held up 2-wide in midfield, moved strongly into contention 400M, responded well to hit lead 150M and always holding off the persistent runner up.
Soon crossed to the fence, settled well ahead of midfield, quickened up nicely 200M and issued a serious challenge, just failed to peg back the winner.
Reserved behind mid-division in 9th, waited with until leaving the bend, laid in early straight, closed off well when straightened up, got up for 3rd near line.
Began only fairly, rushed forward to track leader, pushed along 450M, kept on steadily to line, out kicked late stages.
Never far off from leaders, travelled well into straight and had every chance from 350M, lacked a strong response, one paced late and missed out in the scramble for 4th placing.
Went forward tracking the pace, held up 300M-200M, didn't come on when clear, only battling away steadily.
Bumped heavily at the start, raced behind midfield along the fence, 4-5Ls to make up 400M, no clear run early straight, closed off well final 200M, could have done better.
Crossed to the lead passing 1400M, led to 150M and faded towards the line. (Runner significantly disadvantaged during the race as jockey lost use of right iron shortly after the start.)
Held up 2nd last about 7Ls off the pace, couldn't quicken sufficiently passing 350M, never competitive.
Bumped heavily at the start losing ground, failed to muster and raced towards the rear 6-7Ls back, closed off only fairly turning home and never a threat to leaders.
In midfield early stages, caught wide no cover 1200M strolled closer to pace but still wide to straight, run ended 250M and weakened.
Given a waiting ride in the rear on this first attempt over 1650M, made his move out-wide from 550M, couldn't sustain effort turning in, soon beaten. (Lame next day.)
Quickly in front, grabbed rail, temporarily headed entering first turn before taking command and setting good pace to straight. Kicked ahead 250m, kept finding when strongly challenged.
Shifted in for cover soon after start, settling one-out at rear. Started forward move passing 800m, racing 3-wide to get within range at turn-in. Finished strongly final 200m only to fail narrowly.
Fast out, poked head in front for a few strides entering first turn, before settling 1L behind leader back stretch. Shaken up to challenge 400m but unable close gap.
Ridden to hold rail, taking box seat at first turn. Kept tabs on leader to straight, not much room final 200m but boxed on gamely.
Shifted across soon after start, grabbing rail 1500m, settling towards rear. Took closer order around home turn, stayed on rail in straight and kept on gamely.
Shifted across behind runners soon after start and last on settling. Made up some ground home turn, switched out in straight and finished off gamely.
Ridden to hold forward position, grabbing rail at first turn, 4L from leader. Not much room top of straight, shifted out 150m for clear run, kept on gamely.
Eased back after start to find cover but held wide at rear, taking first turn 4-wide. Allowed to stride forward from 1000m to sit one-out, one-back at 600m. Under pressure 200m and faded.
Pressed forward on jumping, sharing early pace before settling one-out, 3L from leader entering back stretch. Shaken up turning for home but only one-paced in straight.
Eased soon after start, settling one-out behind midfield. Lost position back stretch, taken 4-wide home turn, swung widest into straight, found little under pressure.
Pressed forward on jumping, settled one-out, one-back entering back stretch. Lost position home turn, under pressure on straightening, faded.
Hard ridden to go forward but not enough speed and kept 4-wide first turn. Snagged back for cover but failed to stretch out and distant last passing 800m. Found little in straight.
Taken back to race 6 to 7 lengths back at tail, same margin back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to score by a neck.

Taken back from a tricky gate, raced 6 to 7 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, got its head up when awkwardly placed close to the heels near 500M, kept to inside after straightening and finished off very strongly, just missed.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 3 lengths back on rail, saved ground to turn, made some progress in straight to take 3rd.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 4 to 5 lengths back, same position on turn, made some progress in straight to make frame.
Average to begin, positioned 5 lengths or so back on rail, there to turn, no clear running in straight, not able to test properly.
Away with them, sent forward to race in 2nd, travelled well throughout, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 150M and soon passed.
Bumped at start, positioned 2 lengths or so back on rail, easy run to turn, showed good response early in straight, peaked near 100M and weakened thereafter.
Began with rest, raced 2 wide in midfield, steadied off heels near 850M, improved from 400M, made some progress early in straight, peaked near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well from the widest draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with no cover in midfield, same position on turn, finished off one-paced.
Taken back from barrier 11, raced 3 wide at rear, still 7 lengths back on turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Moderately away from a middle draw, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead near 900M, uncontested on turn, emptied early in straight, dropped off tamely.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight and eased.

Moderate start, trailed the field, commenced move on top of home bend and went widest into home straight, made significant progress down the centre of the track to assert authority close to home.

Moderate start, ridden along and given reminders to hold midfield position 800 metres out, maintained midfield rails run turning into straight, tight run early on but fought on steadily to pinch 2nd in the bobbing of the heads.
Shared pace early, took up running passing the 900 metres, obtained rails run coming onto home turn, kicked 3L clear early in straight, unable to sustain effort and caught final stages.
Niggled along in forward of midfield travelling 3-wide without cover off far side, renewed effort after straightening and ran on to be nearest at finish.
Settled in rear, ran on steadily under pressure without threatening.

Began well from a wide gate, allowed to drift backward just behind midfield, niggled at passing the 1000M but remained in similar position, did not find much room early in straight, produced good late impression.
Broke well from a wide draw but soon taken back, settled 2-wide behind midfield, kept on steadily without threatening.
Stumbled jumping out, settled in midfield, baulked for a run early in straight, made no impression inside the final 200 metres.
Well there early, gradually settled in 4th just over 3L off the pace, faded gradually in straight.
Began fairly, ridden along in prominent position, kept on in straight before faded under pressure. (Lame next day)
Always in last few and never seen with a chance.
Ridden along the rail to share early pace, settled for 2nd over 2L back approaching the home bend, folded up quickly after straightening.
Hard ridden to take rail, led at fast sectionals, ran on well to score only by a narrow margin.
Hard ridden forward, sat outside the lead, not suited by the fast tempo, closed off strongly, just missed by a narrow margin in 2nd.
Midfield, 2 wide, suited by the fast pace, made steady ground 300M for 3rd.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, favoured by the fast pace, trapped 3 wide, progressed steadily 300M.
Hard ridden forward to keep up with the fast pace, 2 wide, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide in the lead, harmed by the fast pace, emptied 300M.
Pushed early, at back, along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in front of midfield, flattened 200M.
Hard ridden early but not muster, at back, suited by the fast pace, but never improved.
Eased at start, suited by the fast tempo, however trapped wide, no progress.
Never competitive at rear.

Placing: PU
Comment: Near the 250M went amiss in its right hind leg and was eased down.
Began well, settled midfield, asked for effort at Home Turn, issued a strong challenge passing 200M and fought well to score.
Ridden along to take lead, travelled strongly in the straight, just missed by SH.
Urged along to settle outside the lead from a wide barrier, kept on and finished well.
Jumped well, settled at handy position, battled hard entire straight, work home well.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, settled behind midfield on rail, over the concluding stages lay in under pressure, came home OK.
Started well, travelled midfield, drifted back passing 900M, fought hard entire straight, finished OK.
Taken back at start, settled at tail on rail, in the straight kept on rail and one-paced.
Ridden along to race behind leaders, under pressure but gave ground passing 150M.
Raced midfield, hung out throughout the race, limited response in the straight, failed to make impression.
Taken back at start, settled behind midfield, under pressure in the straight, failed to run on.
Failed to muster speed despite being vigorously ridden along, raced behind midfield, asked for effort approaching 500M, limited response in the straight.
Travelled behind midfield on rail, asked for effort but no response, failed to run on.
Taken back at start and raced at tail, approaching 1400M was checked and lost running, failed to run on in the straight.
Travelled midfield, widest on straightening, never in it.
Away smartly, grabbing rail and eye-balling leader. Poked head in front passing 600m, kicked clear 300m, went to the post unchallenged.
Shifted in for cover shortly after start, settling towards rear. Took close order around home turn, got rails run in straight and finished strongly to grab second.
Ridden early to hold midfield position before seeking cover one-out 4L from leader. Swung wide entering straight and boxed on gamely to snatch minor placing.
Away well, settling one-out 3L from leader. Checked passing 1000m, wide around turn, boxed on in straight while laying out under pressure.
Pressed forward from widest draw, taking up one-out, one-back position. Under pressure on straightening but only one-paced.
Ridden along one-out in midfield before losing position around home turn. One-paced in straight.
Crowded out on jumping and last on settling. Made up some ground approaching turn, took inside run in straight and boxed on fairly.
Unable handle early pace, dropping one-out behind midfield. Taken wide in straight but only one-paced.
Bumped and unbalanced at start but surged forward grabbing box seat 2L from joint leaders. Kept tabs to straight when came under pressure and faded.
Taken to rail soon after start, settling 4L from leader. Made up some ground around home turn but only one-paced in straight.
Hard ridden to lead but harassed by inside runner around turn. Spent force at turn-in and faded.
Bumped and unbalanced start, dropping towards rear. Shuffled back to last approaching home turn and never in the hunt after that.
Taken back from barrier 13, raced 7 to 8 lengths back at rear, improved on turn, finished off very strongly in straight to score.
Began well from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader in 2nd, took the lead near 400M, kept on well after turning in, but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Moderately away, positioned 2 lengths or so back in 3rd, travelled well to turn, unbalanced near 400M, kept on well in straight to get a place. (Rider had his whip knocked from his hand near 100M.)
Jumped well, raced wide in midfield, 5 lengths or so back, found cover in the middle stages, slightly improved on turn, angled out early in straight and made some headway to make frame.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths back in 4th, slightly improved on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 150M, weakened thereafter.

Began well from a middle draw, showed early speed to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked and headed near 400M, just stayed on evenly. (Jockey reported that his mount was inclined to lay out throughout the race.)
Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, travelled wide with no cover at rear, improved in the middle stages, peaked near 450M, one-paced in straight.
Away with them, raced 3 to 4 lengths back on rail in midfield, easy run throughout, kept to inside after turning in, finished off one-paced.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths or so back, still well back on turn, only passed a few tired runners in straight.
Began fairly from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover, 6 lengths or so back at rear, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, raced 2 wide behind midfield early, checked near 1000M, 7 lengths back in the middle stages, slightly improved on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start, raced at rear throughout, never competitive.
Inconvenienced start, raced 5 to 6 lengths back on rail, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight.
Bumped on jumping, raced 3 wide without cover behind midfield, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight, finished last.
Pushed and sent into the lead, led by 1-1/4L along the rail, built a good margin early in the straight, held on late to score by 3/4L.
Rolled forward and raced in the box-seat, sat 1-1/4L off, kept on nicely to the line for 2nd.
Sent forward and raced outside the lead, sat 1-1/4L off, kept on well to the line to take 3rd.
Eased and raced at the rear, 5-3/4L behind wide but with cover, made nice ground by producing a strong run home.
Pushed and settled to race in front of midfield, 2-1/4L off 3 wide without cover, ran on okay to the finish.
Jumped only fairly, travelled in around midfield, 2-3/4L behind along the rail, ran on fairly to the line.
Eased and raced towards the rear, 4-3/4L behind wide but with cover, made ground steadily.
Raced in worse than midfield, 4-1/4L behind along the rail, kept on one paced to the line.
Pushed and settled just in front of midfield, 2-1/2L off 2 wide, very one paced.
Awkward start then failed to muster, settled in around midfield 3L behind 3 wide with cover, never threatened.
Raced towards the rear, 4-3/4L behind 2 wide, found nothing in the straight.
Crowded after the start, settled in behind midfield and wide throughout, not competitive.
Ridden to hold forward position, settling one-out 2L from leader. Crowded out home turn, shaken up top of straight, making up ground gradually to score narrow win.
Ridden along but wide before shifting in for cover first turn, dropping to rear. Shifted out 3-wide home turn, taken to centre track on straightening and finished strongly only to lose narrowly.
Pressed forward on jumping to race outside hindquarters of leader. Rolled forward top of straight to join leader 200m, inched ahead passing 100m but run down near line.
Quickly in front, setting good pace along rail. Kicked ahead top of straight but joined up front 150m. Boxed on gamely till swamped final 50m.
Took first turn 3-wide before settling towards rear. Took inside run in straight and ran on strongly to finish just behind place-getters.
Shifted in for cover soon after start, dropping one-out at rear. Taken 3-wide back stretch to improve to behind midfield at turn-in. Very wide in straight, boxed on fairly.
Away nicely, ridden to hold midfield position, one-away from fence. Made forward move turning for home but effort was short-lived and one-paced in straight.
Ridden along behind midfield one away from fence. Held for clear running home turn and early straight, boxed on one-paced.
Pressed forward from outside draw, racing 3-wide without cover 2L from leader. Bumped and unbalanced home turn and taken wider. Boxed on gamely to 200m before tiring.
Jumped OK, then ridden in midfield close to fence. Kept on gamely to 200m before tiring.
Inconvenienced start, taken to rail and settled towards rear. Never in the hunt, finishing well back.
Ridden to hold forward position, taking first turn 4-wide, then settling 3-wide 3L from leader back stretch. Kept wide around home turn and faded in straight.
Shifted in for cover shortly after start, dropping to last. Remained at rear throughout and never likely.
Jumped smartly, grabbing box seat and trailing leader to straight. Found nothing when asked and faded.
Set early pace, relinquished the lead near 1200M, ridden along to chase leader 450M, hit the front again 250M and sprinted away for a wide margin victory on his AWT debut.
Held up 2-wide in mid-division, taken wide 500M to make his bid, ran on well for a clear cut 2nd without threatening the runaway winner.
Moved up to 3rd 1300M, driven along 500M, stayed on moderately to the line but never a threat to runaway winner.
In mid-division 6-7Ls off the pace, kept on fairly over final 400M to finish a remote 4th beaten almost 10L.
Ridden forward from draw 14, led 1300M and opened up 3L lead into home turn, headed 250M, weakened towards the line.
Stumbled badly after the start, settled down behind midfield 8Ls back, ran past some beaten horses in straight, but only made limited progress on the place-getters.
Had a ground saving trip along the fence, positioned ahead of midfield, 5Ls to make up 400M, closed off only fairly, no threat.
Not far off the pace early stages, shuffled back to mid-division entering back straight, driven along 450M but couldn't muster the pace to challenge.
Not hurried early stages, settled down near last 9-10Ls off the pace, plodded home final 400M, never a threat.
Caught wide no cover in midfield, pushed along to keep up 500M, no extra 200M.
Eased to the rear over 10Ls off the pace first half, plenty to do turning in but couldn't get any closer to main rivals.
Held up 2-wide behind midfield, came under pressure 600M, weakened out of contention early straight. (Unacceptable Performance.)
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, settled at the rear over 10Ls off the pace, plenty to do turning in but never looked like picking up the pace. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Positioned behind midfield along the 3-path, struggled to keep up 600M out, soon gave ground (Unacceptable Performance.)

Tracked the leader to straight, hit the front passing the 400 metres, kicked over 2L clear 200 metres out, kept on well.
Settled just off the pace on the rail, switched out for a run upon straightening, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Settled in midfield on the rail, saved ground entering straight, kept on steadily under pressure without quickening.
Broke well to lead on the rail, made running to the 300 metres, faded under pressure.
Crowded at start, recovered steadily to just worse than midfield on the rail, came under pressure from the home bend, kept on same pace without quickening.
Began awkwardly and lost considerable ground, soon recovered to rear of the field on the rail, kept on at the one pace in straight.
Jumped fairly, settled in midfield, briefly baulked early in straight, one-paced.
Settled just worse than midfield, ran home at the one pace past well-beaten horses.
Soon dropped to last few despite ridden early, remained in similar position to the straight, made no impression.
Travelled wide in midfield, improved to 5th approaching the home bend, gave ground into the straight.
Moderate start from a wide gate, ridden along wide in midfield far side before improving to 2L 3rd 3-wide without cover around home bend, soon weakened under pressure in the straight.
Taken well back from the widest gate, trailed the field to the straight, never a danger.
Pushed forward, sat 1 out 1 back, favoured by the slow pace, closed off strongly 300M to score.
At back, 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 300M for 2nd.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, benefited by the slow sectionals, ran on well for 3rd.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, blocked most straight, dashed well when clear despite not suited by the slow tempo.
Bumped start, at back, 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 300M, run ended 100M.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, lack room 400M, no dash when clear.
Pushed to take rail and led at slow sectionals, hung on until 200M weakened.
At back, took rail, harmed by the slow pace, ran on fairly.
Hard ridden early but not muster, at back on the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, no dash.
Bumped start, at rear, harmed by the slow pace, never improved.
Eased to sit in midfield, trapped 3 wide, dropped off 300M.
Very slow away, never competitive.
Started well, shared lead, asked for effort approaching 450M, finished strongly to win.
Settled midfield on outside rail, shifted in for clear running passing 300M, finished solidly.
Taken back at start, made good late ground passing 150M, worked home strongly.
Raced outside the leader, one off from outside rail, asked for effort passing 500M, finished nicely.
Settled at back from barrier 1, gradually made ground passing 300M, came home nicely.
Settled midfield and one off from outside rail, made some late ground, finished OK.
Settled midfield from barrier 3, travelled inside when tried to improve, came home fairly.
Began awkwardly, raced behind leaders, asked for effort passing 500M, finished fairly.
Raced handy position on outside rail, tried to improve approaching 400M but one-paced.
Began slowly, raced at back, under pressure and one-paced in the final stages.
Shared lead, weakened passing 150M, failed to keep on.
Raced behind leaders, raced tight passing 300M, failed to run on.
Began only fairly, settled inside the lead, weakened approaching 200M, failed to make impression, irregular heart rhythm.
Reluctant to stretch out, failed to run on.
Hard ridden from widest draw to go forward, racing wide till settling outside leader passing 800m. Joined leader soon after straightening, kicked ahead 300m, pulled clear for easy win.
Pressed forward on jumping, racing 3-wide without cover from 900m when 2L from leader. Inched forward on straightening to look a chance but unable match winner's finishing burst.
Away well, grabbing box seat 2L from leader at turn. Held for clear running top of straight but boxed on gamely to finish in the frame.
Away well, taken to fence and settled 5L from leader. Stayed on fence around turn, switched out in straight to make challenge, finished off nicely.
Jumped well, pressed forward, settling one-out, one-back. Kept tabs on leader to 200m before turning one-paced.
Ridden to hold midfield position one away from fence. Stayed in contention to straight but only one-paced under pressure.
Ridden along early but wide before seeking cover 1100m, dropping to rear but away from fence. Swung wide into straight and boxed on one-paced.
Began awkwardly, then vigorously ridden to lead, crossing to rail before turn. Joined up front soon after straightening and faded.
Travelled keenly when taken to fence soon after start, settling behind midfield. Took run between horses in straight but only one-paced.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw and last on settling. Trailed field to straight and ran past beaten horses.
Restrained on jumping and shifted in for cover, settling at rear but away from fence. Taken wide in straight but never in the hunt.
Vigorously ridden on jumping but slow to muster and trapped 3-wide behind midfield at turn. Spent force soon after turn-in and faded.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, similar position on turn, improved from near 600M, finished off very strongly in straight to score.

Jumped well from a wide draw, taken back to race 6 to 7 lengths back at rear, improved from 650M, very wide turning in, took the lead near 250M, kept on well thereafter but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Began well from a tricky gate, sent forward to sit 2 wide in 2nd, there to turn, kept on well in straight to get a place.
Fast into stride, positioned a length or so back on rail, easy run to turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly to make frame.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide in midfield early, no cover after 1200M, slightly improved in the middle stages, still 3 wide on turn, hung in and a difficult ride in the run home.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, no daylight early in straight, made some progress when clear final 200M.
Began fairly, raced 4 to 5 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, no clear running in straight, not able to test properly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, angled out on turn, finished off evenly in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from a wide draw, positioned on rail at rear, there to turn, finished off one-paced.
Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead near 1200M, travelled well on turn, headed early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Slowly away from the widest draw, raced at tail throughout, never a threat.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover, 5 lengths back, improved near 650M, 4 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, emptied in the final furlong.
Taken back from gate 12, raced 8 lengths back at rear, very wide turning in, failed to close off in straight, finished last.
Settled to race in about midfield, 3-1/2L behind 3 wide and without cover, despite that kept on well to score by 1-1/2L.
One-off one-back initially, shuffled back one slot after 800M, ran on nicely to take 2nd but was no match to the winner.
Travelled in about midfield, 5L behind 3 wide with cover, made good ground and finished off well to the line.
Raced in midfield, 3-3/4L behind along the rail, picked up before crowded near 300M, and then ran on well to the line.
Raced just in behind midfield, 5-1/4L behind along the rail, made ground and ran on okay to the line.
Travelled in behind midfield, 5-1/4L behind 2 wide, gathered run before crowded after 300M, finished off well thereafter.
Raced towards the rear, 6-1/2L behind 3 wide with cover, made ground steadily and ran on to the line.
Rolled forward to take the rail and led by a neck, couldn't find extra and headed near 150M.
Settled to race in about midfield, 3-3/4L behind 2 wide, kept on one paced to the line.
Crowded at the start, then raced at the rear, 6-3/4L behind 2 wide, saved ground and ran on.
Slow to jump and raced detached early, travelled 8-1/4L behind 2 wide, made slight ground.
Urged out of the barriers, settled to race in the box-seat, sat 2L off, bumped near 300M, did not run on thereafter.
Pushed and prominent, trapped wide until improved to sit outside the lead after 800M, got tired approaching 300M.
Sent forward and raced prominently, sat 3/4L off, faded after passing 300M.
Away nicely, ridden to stay close to pace, settling between horses 4L from leader. Swung wide into straight, got split between horses 350m, finishing strongly to win on the line.
Began fast, taken to rail sharing early pace before inching ahead passing 1400m. Kicked clear on straightening, pulled 3L ahead passing 200m but run down on the line.
Away well, taken to box seat and settled 2L from leader. Set off after leader on straightening but unable to close gap, hanging on for minor placing.
Quickly into stride, racing outside leader before being eased one-back, one-out 1300m. Swung wide into straight and boxed on gamely.
Outpaced early, dropping towards rear and racing 3-wide but with cover. Taken to centre field on straightening and ran on fairly.
No early pace, racing between horses towards the rear. Still well back on straightening, finished fairly between horses to be closest at line.
Jumped well, pressed forward from widest draw to race outside leader but 3-wide without cover. Covered extra ground turn, boxed on fairly in straight until flattened 100m.
Outpaced early, racing at rear close to rail. Came off fence turning for home but hung-in badly up the straight, finishing one-paced.
No early pace, racing at rear. Switched out on straightening but found little under pressure.
Slow into stride, before picking up momentum along rail. Made up ground steadily to get within 4L of leader at turn-in before running out of stamina and fading.
Lifted feet as gates opened and began on fairly. Pushed to make up ground, settling 3L from leader approaching turn but 3-wide. Lay out under pressure in straight and faded.
No pace, dropping to last, becoming detached from field. Ran past beaten horses in straight.
Pressed forward from an outside draw, racing 3-wide until settling outside leader passing 1400m. Under pressure at turn-in and faded.
Ridden along early from an outside draw, settling 3-wide in midfield. Lost position rounding home turn, swung wide into straight, faded.
Travelled strongly behind leaders, quickened up nicely passing 350M, led near 200M, continued on well to line albeit hung in late stages and proved difficult to ride.
Soon led, enjoyed uncontested lead to 600M, quickened up well passing 400M but couldn't match pace with winner mid-straight, dug deep late stages holding on for 2nd.
Held up behind midfield, raced keenly passing 1100M, saved ground on inside, kept chasing leaders from 350M, came one stride short of catching the 2nd.
Held up last 7Ls off the pace, kept to inside for the entire trip, stayed on mildly on straightening but couldn't bridge the gap on leaders.
Caught 3-deep in mid-division on jumping from draw 11, driven wider 500M, closed off moderately.
Steadied early stages, raced at the tail 7-8Ls off the pace, swung widest home, stayed on down outside without threat.
Restrained in midfield just over 3Ls off leader, into clear passing 400M, kept on same pace to line, no threat to leaders from 200M.
Settled down in midfield about 4Ls back, couldn't muster the pace to challenge turning home, never looked a winning threat.
Crossed to a 2-wide spot behind leaders, taken out to center of track 400M, couldn't go on 250M.
Slotted into a 3-wide spot towards the rear, took closer order passing 1000M, gave only limited response, never a factor.
Caught wide from draw 12, no cover from 1200M, moved up to join leaders 600M, run ended mid-straight, faded towards finish.
Raced keenly early stages, restrained to near the rear, 6Ls off the pace making home turn, brought wide into straight but couldn't finish off.
Tracked leader 2-wide, under pressure 550M, weakened out of contention 250M, didn't last home on this first attempt over 1800M.
Pressed forward from wide draw to race outside leader but 3-wide. Set off after leader on straightening, making up ground gradually before pulling clear final strides.
Jumped well, pressed forward holding rail inside leader. Kicked ahead on straightening, but started to shorten stride 100m and run down close to line.
Outpaced early, settling behind midfield along fence. Stayed on fence around turn and finished on gamely to grab minor placing.
Steadied and shifted in for cover shortly after start, dropping one-out towards rear. Swung wide entering straight and ran on gamely to finish in the frame.
Jumped OK, ridden for a few strides before steadied and shifted across behind runners, settling one-out at rear. Taken to centre track n straightening and finished off fairly.
Slow into stride before making up ground along fence to get within 3L of leader at turn. Threw out challenge top of straight to look a chance before running out of steam 100m.
Hampered shortly after start before settling between horses in midfield. Steadied off heels around turn, dropping back, before running on fairly in straight.
Steadied soon after start and taken to fence, settling at rear. Made up some ground around home turn and early in straight before running out of steam.
Ridden between horses to share early pace before dropping one-out 2L back approaching turn. Kept on fairly early in straight before tiring from 200m. (lame left front leg)
Away nicely staying close to early pace before losing position approaching turn. Lost more ground around turn and faded in straight.
Jumped OK, pressed forward from an outside draw, racing 3-wide in midfield. Lost ground approaching and around home turn, one-paced in straight.
Vigorously ridden from wide draw to lead on settling but held away from fence by inside runner. Spent force at turn-in and tired quickly, finishing tailed out. Unacceptable performance.

Placing: FE
Comment: Jumped well, pressed forward, 3-wide 3L from leader on settling. Lost ground rapidly around home turn and collapsed shortly after straightening, dislodging rider.
Broke well and pushed out to ensure he led. Still in front turning for home. Pressured by the 2nd horse down the straight, but maintained his strong pace and held on late.

Pushed forward from the wide draw to eventually settle 2nd, 0.5L off the leader and 1 off the fence. Never started moving until 300m and only used the stick in last 150m. Strong run to the line, but couldn't get the winner.

Cruised forward from the jump to settle midfield. Had a lap full of horse early in the straight and forced a run at 300m. Huge run from that point, despite getting whip caught at 150m, and was rapidly gaining on leading pair late.
Bumped and unbalanced on jumping, but recovered well to sit 3rd/4th on the fence. Came off heels at 250m for a run. Stayed on well late and was making up ground on the leaders late.
Slow away and eased back to get cover towards the rear of the field. Widest on the turn and stayed on fairly in the straight, without ever threatening.
Eased forward to settle just behind midfield. Raced keen and came off heels at 1100m. Held up at 350m. Stayed on solidly in the straight.
Bumped on jumping and taken up to eventually settle 3rd/4th, 3 wide with no cover. Joint leader at 200m, but had nothing left turning for home and dropped out in the straight.
Fairly away before settling comfortably, worse than midfield. Awkward on heels 800m. Did his best work late and looking for more suitable race over longer.
Cruised forward early to settle around midfield. Copped a nasty bump at 350m and awkward on heels at 100m, but was always 1 paced in the straight.
Indecisive early, before eventually finding a spot midfield, 3-4 wide with limited cover. Never kicked in the straight.
Dropped back early from the wide draw to sit at the rear of the field, and made no impact from there.
Pressed forward early to settle forward of midfield, 1 off the fence. Crowded at 350m, but was already fading out.
Eased back early to sit towards the rear of the field. Stayed there and had no impact on the race.
Drifted back through the field early to sit last. Never improved from that point.
