Settled towards the rear on the rail, commenced move rounding home bend, fought on dourly from wide in midfield into straight to assert authority inside the final 100 metres.
Hard ridden early before settling towards the rear, widest runner entering straight, ran on well under pressure down the centre of the track, did best work late.

With leaders early, taken back to nearly 3L back in 3rd on the rail behind the pace-setter far side, commenced move approaching the 400M and led the field into straight, unable to sustain effort & overhauled inside the final 100M
Settled in rear of midfield, went wide into the straight, ran on under pressure near the centre of the track, nearest at finish.
Crowded at start, settled in last few, wide into straight, ran on steadily under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Taken back from a wide gate, saved ground entering home straight, made modest progress early on but unable to sustain effort closing stages.
Began well, settled in 5th on the rail just better than midfield, checked off heels of weakening pace-setter turning into straight, made no impression in the run home.
Settled in rear of midfield on the rail, badly checked on heels turning into home straight, recovered some late ground closing stages.

Gradually worked forward from the widest gate to join the leaders 3-wide first bend, settled for joint 2nd 2L off the clear leader far side, shifted very wide when tiring turning for home. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Moderate start from a wide gate, obtained 2-wide position in distant 4th over 4L back far side, became closer to lead when pace slackened rounding home bend, soon weakened after straightening.

Prominent from the middle draw, took up running coming onto stables bend, went over 2L clear early in back straight, still 1L in front leaving the Rock, folded up quickly from approaching home straight. (Tactic questioned)
Began well from a wide gate, taken back for cover in midfield on stables bend but not for long, dropped towards the rear in back straight, became last when the widest runner turning for home.
Hard ridden to take rail and lead, clocked fast sectionals, made all.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, not suited by the fast pace, closed off strongly 200M for 2nd.
Pushed early, at back, 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast pace, dashed well 250M for 3rd.
Pushed forward to cross, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast sectionals, ran on well to the line.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, suited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 300M.
At back along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M, bumped 150M.
Box seat, not suited by the fast tempo, held ground in straight.
Pushed to sit in midfield, 2 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, favoured by the fast pace, made steady ground 300M.
At rear, took rail, benefited by the fast tempo, ran on ok in straight.
Eased back, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, no progress.
Ridden along to take forward position on rail, raced inside the leader, asked for effort in the early straight and responded well, travelled strongly to score.
Started well and urged to settle behind leaders, gradually made ground passing 150M, finished strongly.
For the majority of the race travelled wide and without cover, settled in front of midfield, fought hard entire straight and worked home solidly.
Ridden along to take lead at one-off position, fought hard entire straight, finished solidly.
Taken back at start, settled behind midfield, shifted out across heels approaching 100M, came home solidly.
Settled midfield, tried to improve at Home Turn, finished nicely. Rider questioned.
Taken back at start and raced at tail, made some late ground, finished OK.
Travelled in front of midfield on rail, asked for effort passing 350M, weakened passing 150M, failed to make impression.
Travelled midfield and wide with cover, tried to improve passing 500M, one-paced in the straight.
Slow out then taken back, under pressure in the straight, passing 50M steadied away from heels, did not run on thereafter.
Travelled at tail, widest on straightening, never threatened.
Began only fairly, lost ground passing 600M, failed to run on.
Away well, taken to rail and trailed leader. Moved closer approaching 700m, no room top of straight, surged through split 200m, held off late challenge.
Jumped well, taken to rail, settling 6L from leader back stretch. Switched out turning for home, taken to centre track on straightening and finished strongly.
Pressed forward from outside draw, racing wide till settling one-back, one-out back stretch. Moved up 3-wide home turn to challenge leader entering straight, boxed on gamely.
Began awkwardly, steadied and shifted in for cover, settling one-out towards rear. Covered extra ground turn, taken very wide in straight, finished off nicely.
Jumped well but no speed, holding rail behind midfield along back stretch. Stayed on rail home turn and ran on well in straight to finish just behind place-getters.
Began OK but held wide before ending forward 1200m to get cover. Pushed forward from 700m to race outside leader at turn-in. Took narrow lead 250m and kept on well till swamped close home.
Steadied shortly after start and taken in for cover, settling one-out at rear. Taken wide entering straight and ran on steadily to be closest at finish.
Began fairly, then crowded, dropping behind midfield but holding rail. Well back to straight before running on fairly.
Away well, taken to fence, settling 5L from leader back stretch. Left fence to challenge at turn-in but only one-paced.
Bumped and unbalanced start, then ridden along one-out to hold midfield position. Under pressure home turn and one-paced in straight.
Quickly away, surging to the front and pulling 3L clear entering back stretch. Under pressure home turn when joined up front, overtaken 250m and faded.
Shifted across behind horses soon after start, settling at rear. Became detached from field back stretch and never in the hunt.
Jumped well from barrier 11, showed early speed to take the lead easily, travelled well throughout, kicked clear after turning in to score a strong win.
Began well, positioned in midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back, same position on turn, made good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Began well from barrier 1, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, easy run throughout, kept on evenly after turning in to get a place.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, similar position on turn, made some progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Jumped well from a middle gate, raced behind midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to be nearest on line.
Slightly slow out, positioned 3 lengths back on rail, same margin back on turn, hung in and difficult to ride in straight, not able to test properly.
Bumped start and unbalanced, unable to slot in early, sent forward near 1000M to race in 2nd, there to turn, peaked early in straight and weakened gradually thereafter.
Away with them, positioned one-out-one-back, similar position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began only fairly, raced wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back on turn, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Crowded out start, raced at rear on rail, still well back on turn, showed no progress in straight.
Taken back from the tricky gate, raced at tail throughout, finished last. (Lost left front plate after the race.)
Pushed and sat outside the lead, sat 3/4L off, kept going and assumed outright lead at 150M, held off challenge to score.
Settled one-off one-back, sat 2-1/4L off, improved at 500M, headed by winner at 150M but kept challenging to the line.
Just niggled to find cover after the start, settled in front of midfield, 3-1/2L off 2 wide, kept on well to the line for 3rd.
Settled to race in about midfield, 4L behind along the rail, away from rail at 400M, finished off nicely to just get in for 4th.
Raced in midfield, 5-1/4L behind 2 wide, improved with the others near 500M, kept on nicely to the line on outside track.
Raced in behind midfield, 6L behind along the rail, made ground and kept on fairly to the line.
Settled to race in behind midfield, 6-3/4L behind 2 wide, made ground in the straight, ran on not bad.
Eased and raced near the tail, 7-1/2L behind 2 wide, exited the Home Turn wide, made ground and finished off fairly.
Taken back and raced towards the rear, 7-1/2L behind along the rail, continued to make ground to the line.
Rolled forward and raced in front of midfield, 2L off along the rail, out of steam in the final 200M.
Eased back and raced at the rear, 8-3/4L behind along the rail, eased from heels at 250M, made minor ground.
Sent forward and assumed outright lead on the rail at 1100M, headed when others moved at 500M, flattened near 150M.
Flew out of the gates from widest draw but forced to race 3-wide until settling one-out 1L from leader 1000m. Hard ridden in straight, making up ground gradually to nail leader on line.
Broke well, shared early pace before forging ahead 1000m. Set hot pace to straight, still well clear 100m, run down on line.
Quickly away, racing in midfield one-away from rail. Taken wide in straight and finished strongly to grab minor placing.
Hard ridden on jumping but failed to muster, settling behind midfield along rail. Stayed well back to straight before finishing strongly along rail to just miss a placing.
Away well, taken to rail 3L from leader and settled. Took inside run in straight and finished off nicely but got close to heels final stages and not ridden out.
Good early speed, taken to box seat and tracked leader to straight. Lay in home turn, brushing rail, boxed on gamely in straight to finish close behind place-getters.
Began awkwardly, losing ground, then shifted across behind runners, dropping to rear of main field. Remained well back to straight before running past tiring rivals.
Unbalanced start, no speed, dropping one-out towards rear. Well back at turn, taken wide entering straight, ran on fairly. (Lame left front leg).
Jumped well, pressed forward, steadied off heels 1000m before settling one-out, one-back. Moved up to challenge entering straight but only one-paced.
No early pace, racing one-out towards rear. Taken wide entering straight but only one-paced.
Began OK, ridden to hold midfield position along rail. One-paced in straight despite hard riding.
Checked on jumping, becoming unbalanced, and last on settling. Became detached from field back stretch and finished tailed out. (Unacceptable performance)
Chased leaders in 3rd, showed good acceleration for a decisive lead inside 250M, margin got reduced late but held it safely to the line.
Taken back on jumping form wide barrier, reserved in 2nd last 6Ls off the pace, brought wide challenge passing 300M, closed off strongly to be nearest at the finish. Honest effort.
Pushed along to obtain the lead, set good pace to straight, couldn't match finishing pace of winner 200M but kept on steadily to hold 3rd.
Held up 2-wide in midfield, took a while to get going on straightening, did best work late to make it close at the finish.
Chased leaders 2-wide, bustled along 400M, loomed a threat early straight but couldn't reel in leaders, lost 3rd over final 50M.
Settled down in midfield along the fence, 3Ls off the pace making the turn, closed off only fairly, held ground final 150M.
Waited with towards the rear, saved ground on the inside, ran on moderately on seasonal reappearance, held ground final 200M.
Taken back on jumping form wide barrier, held up near the rear along the 2-path, 5Ls to make up 400M, gave limited response.
Taken back on jumping form wide barrier, held up last 7Ls down at 400M, didn't run on.
Ridden along early, caught wide then steadied for cover, pushed along home turn to hold his midfield position, kept on same pace over final 300M.
Outside leader, had every chance in straight, weakened away 250M.
Caught wide no cover chasing leaders, had little left turning home, gave ground rapidly.

Pressed forward from the widest gate to lead on the rail after first 400 metres, led until narrowly headed under pressure passing the 200 metres, fought back doggedly to renew advantage 100 metres out.
Broke well, soon taken back to settle 3-wide just worse than midfield, shaken up to challenge upon straightening, ran on well to be nearest at finish.
Jumped fairly from a wide gate, travelled in a handy position without cover, quickened under pressure to gain narrow advantage momentarily 200 metres out, unable to sustain effort close to home.
Moderate start, soon dropped to last few, ran on under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Began fairly, settled just off the pace on the rail, kept on steadily without quickening under pressure.
Never far off, awkwardly placed behind heels in 5th rounding home bend, fought on steadily under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Taken back from a wide gate and waited with, commenced move inside the final 250 metres, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Ridden early before settling just off the pace, drew level with leader eventual winner early in straight, unable to sustain effort and folded up under pressure inside the final 250 metres.
Close up on the rail early, drifted back to forward of midfield approaching home bend, one-paced under pressure in straight.
Jumped well, travelled wide in 6th in forward of midfield, kept on same pace under pressure.
Niggled at but soon dropped to midfield, one-paced in straight.
Began awkwardly losing ground, niggled along in rear of midfield on the rail, awkwardly placed close to heels around home bend, made no impression in the run home.
Began awkwardly losing ground, settled towards the rear on the rail, produced some late impression closing stages.
Settled wide in last few from a wide gate, remained similar turning into straight, dropped out.
Failed to muster at back, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 250M and scored.
Shared the lead easily, not suited by the fast sectionals, ran on strongly for 2nd.
Hard ridden to keep up with the fast pace, lack room 300M, closed off strongly for 3rd.
Pushed to keep up with the fast pace, ran on well to the line.
Hard ridden to share the lead, clocked fast sectionals, hung on strongly until 100M overhauled.
Eased to sit just off the front runners, progressed steadily 300M.
Eased to sit just off the front runners, made steady ground 300M.
Pressed forward, not suited by the fast pace, flattened 200M.
Hard ridden forward, not suited by the fast tempo, flattened 250M.
At rear, benefited by the fast tempo, lack turn of foot.
At rear, suited by the fast pace, no progress.
At back, suited by the fast pace, never improved.

Placing: FE
Comment: After the 400M gave ground abruptly and collapsed.
Moderate start, settled behind leaders on rail, passing 1200M moved out to one off position, quickened passing 200M, finished strongly to score.
Raced midfield, improved passing 400M, quickened passing 100M, came home strongly.
Travelled midfield on rail, fought hard entire straight, worked home solidly.
Taken back at start, settled behind midfield, commenced to improve approaching 400M and gradually made ground, worked home solidly.
Urged along to take lead, one off the rail, lay out at Home Turn and shifted out in the straight under pressure, finished nicely.
Ridden along to take box seat, asked for effort in the early straight, gave ground passing 200M, finished fairly.
Raced outside the leader, gave ground passing 250M, finished fairly.
Settled midfield, tried to improve at Home Turn, one-paced.
Settled behind midfield on rail, asked for effort at Home Turn but only limited response, one-paced in the straight.
Ridden along after start and settled in front of midfield, for the majority of race travelled wide and after 900M without cover, one-paced in the straight.
Began fairly then raced midfield on rail, kept on rail in the straight, failed to close off.
Urged along after start, settled midfield wide with cover, asked for effort but no response, failed to run on.
Began slowly then taken back, raced at tail, never in it.
Shortly after start became detached from the field and subsequently finished tailed out. Must trial.
Taken in for cover soon after start, settling one-out in midfield. Taken wide entering straight but checked 400m and switched in for run. Hit front 150m and held off late challenge.
Shifted across behind runners soon after start, settling along fence towards the rear. Well back to straight, shifted out 300m when blocked for run, finished strongly only to fail narrowly.
Hard ridden on jumping but slow to muster, eventually settling one-out ahead of midfield. Hard ridden on straightening, making up ground gradually to snatch minor placing.
Away well, shared early pace before settling one-out, one-back. Rolled forward on straightening to share lead approaching 200m before flattened close home.
Raced under a hold early, dropping one-out behind midfield. Swung wide into straight and finished off nicely down centre track.
Vigorously ridden to hold forward position, settling outside shoulder of leader 1100m. Hit the front soon after straightening, collared 200m, but kept battling till swamped final 100m.
Ridden along early but wide behind midfield before settling one-out towards rear. Taken to centre field on straightening and finished off nicely.
Taken in for cover shortly after start, racing along fence towards rear. Made up some ground around home turn but only one-paced in straight.
Began well, shared early pace before slipping into slipstream of leader passing 900m. Shaken up top of straight but raced greenly under pressure and gave ground gradually.
Jumped OK but soon outpaced becoming detached from field despite hard riding. Made up some ground around home turn, and finished off fairly in straight.
Bumped and badly unbalanced start, then pressed forward racing wide without cover to get within 2L of leader at turn. Covered extra but kept on well to 200m before tiring. (Finished distressed)
Began well, ridden forward along rail, settling 3L from leader. Kept tabs to straight but blocked for run until 250m, eased down final stages.
Hard ridden along rail to stay with pace before inching ahead 1100m. Overtaken soon after straightening but kept on fairly to 200m before tiring.
Shifted across behind runners soon after start, dropping to rear and becoming detached from main field. Never likely.

Pressed forward from the widest gate, took the lead easily, travelled well throughout, kicked clear after turning in and scored easily, impressive debut. (Vet reported had laceration on right hind leg.)
Crowded on jumping, recovered to race in midfield, but unable to found cover, travelled 3 wide throughout, kept on very well in straight to take 2nd without threatening the winner, solid debut.
Away with them, raced 2 wide, 6 lengths or so back at rear, same margin back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to get 3rd, nearest on line, nice debut.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back in midfield, same position on turn, no daylight early in straight, made some headway when clear thereafter to make frame.
Jumped well, positioned 3 lengths back on rail in midfield, travelled keenly near 600M, no clear running early in straight, made some progress when clear thereafter.
Away with them, raced 8 lengths back at tail, awkwardly placed near 900M, still well back on turn, bumped near 400M, made good progress in straight.
Bumped start, positioned on rail at rear, saved ground on turn, no daylight early in straight, severely checked near 250M, shifted out thereafter and made minor progress.
Bumped after start, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly, never a threat to the first few.
Crowded out start, sent forward to race 2 wide in 2nd, travelled well to turn, peaked early in straight, just stayed on evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Fast into stride, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, angled out near 500M, made minor progress early in straight, peaked near 250M, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths or so back, checked off heels near 800M, similar position on turn, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Steadied start, raced at rear on rail, there to turn, showed no progress in straight.
Average to begin, positioned a length behind the leader, checked off heels and travelled keenly near 600M, peaked after turning in, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 6 lengths or so back, failed to close off in straight, finished last.
Jumped well, then obtained cover towards the rear, 7-1/2L behind 2 wide, kept on strongly, scored by a neck.
Raced in about midfield, 4-3/4L behind 2 wide, kept on going nicely to the finish to take 2nd.
Settled to race in midfield, 4-3/4L behind along the rail, produced dashes at times and ran on nicely to the line.
Taken back and raced at the rear, 8-3/4L behind 2 wide, swung widest, closed off nicely to finish 1-1/4L behind.
Crowded at the start, raced in worse than midfield, 6-3/4L behind 2 wide, improved steadily, kept on well to the line.
Sent forward and hang in, sat outside the lead about 1L off, assumed it outright at 400M, headed near 100M but kept on.
Awkward start, then eased and raced at the rear, 8-1/2L behind 3 wide, made ground steadily whilst laying in.
Raced in front of midfield, 3-1/4L off along the rail, kept on one paced to the line.
Crowded at the start, raced in behind midfield, 6-3/4L behind along the rail, made minor ground and ran on.
Sent forward to take the rail and led by about 1L, headed on straightening and gradually lost ground.
Raced just in front of midfield, 3-1/2L off 2 wide, kept on until flattened passing 200M.
Taken back and raced at the rear, 8-1/2L behind along the rail, one paced in the straight, didn't make ground.
Hampered after the start, settled to race in the box-seat, sat 1-1/4L off, weakened badly at 250M.
In front of midfield, 2-3/4L off but wide, found nothing in the straight, not competitive.
Began fairly, taken to rail at rear and made ground to midfield approaching turn. Blocked for run early straight, got clear 250m, thundered home to win on the line.
Hard ridden along rail to lead on settling, setting good pace. Kicked clear on straightening to look a winning chance but run down on the line.
Jumped OK, not pushed, settling one-out towards rear. Took home turn 3-wide, taken to centre track on straightening and finished off strongly to grab minor placing.
Pressed forward from an outside draw, but over-raced when steadied for cover passing 1100m before settling one-out, one-back. Kept on well in straight to finish behind place-getters.
Ridden along early to hold midfield position but checked 900m, losing ground, dropping to last. Taken very wide in straight and ran on steadily.
Ridden to hold midfield position one-away from fence. Swung wide entering straight and boxed on fairly.
Ridden positively early to find cover but held 3-wide in midfield, then left without cover from 900m. Covered extra ground turn, kept on fairly in straight till tiring close home.
Away smartly, grabbing box seat and trailing leader. Stayed on rail around turn and in straight but only one-paced final 200m.
Began fairly, shifted across behind runners, dropping to rear. Made up some ground around home turn but only one-paced in straight.
First into stride, leading from widest gate before settling outside hind-quarters of leader 1300m. Under pressure soon after straightening and faded.
Settled down in the 6th spot, in midfield along the 2-path, chased leader from 300M, came with a strong late run to get up on the line.
Began well, restrained to sit in 5th 3-4Ls off the pace, moved up well entering straight and led 250M, fought on well to the line only to be caught final few strides.
Jumped only fairly, settled down towards the rear 6Ls back, shifted wide to challenge turning in, rattled home late but couldn't run down first 2.
In 4th never far off the pace, eased off the rails 500M, kept chasing leader and stayed in the fight till final 50M, no extra late stages, lost 3rd near line.
Jumped evenly, settled down behind midfield 4-5Ls back, ran on steadily behind leaders. Encouraging debut.
Held up behind midfield, 4Ls to make up 400M, kept battling away without threatening.
Dropped back to last, saved ground on the inside, ran on well but couldn't reach leaders.
Caught 3-wide no cover from draw 13, 4Ls off the pace in midfield home turn, swung widest home but couldn't make much headway.
Driven forward from widest barrier, vied for the lead on outside, took over 350M, headed at 220M, found little from there.
Quietly ridden, settled down near last 8Ls off the pace early stages, took inside route 500M, stayed on but never a genuine winning chance.
Tracked leaders in 3rd, had his chance turning in, couldn't go on from 250M, weakened away.
Began fairly, 6Ls back towards the rear, on straightening failed to run on, never in the picture.
Failed to muster speed, raced back in the field, 7Ls to make up 400M, failed to improve turning in, eased when no chance final 150M.
Bustled along after the jump, pressed by rival in the lead and travelled keenly middle stages, had enough when headed at 350M, swamped. (Blood in trachea.)
Shifted in soon after start, dropping to rear. Shuffled back to last 800m, stoked up passing 600m, very wide into straight, finished strongly to win close home. (Rider dropped whip 100m)
Hard ridden to lead passing 1350m, then set slow pace to straight. Overtaken 400m but refused to give up and came again at the finish to grab quinella spot.
Pressed forward but unable get cover and held three wide in midfield before striding forward to sit 3-wide 2L from leader. Took lead 400m but flattened close home and swamped.
Hampered start, no speed, dropping to last. Not happy with slow pace and took off from 800m, circling field 5-wide to look chance entering straight. Kept on well before tiring final strides.
Away well, holding rail 3L from leader. Lost position around home turn but stayed on rail in straight and kept on well to finish just behind place-getters.
Quickly away, gabbing box seat and trailing leader. Lost position home turn but kept battling in straight before racing tight final stages and not ridden out.
Ridden along to hold midfield position but held 3-wide before being allowed to stride forward around home turn to race outside leader at turn-in. Kept on well in straight before tiring close home.
Pressed forward from wide draw before cutting in for cover at midfield 1200m. Lost position home turn but kept on gamely in straight.
Ridden to hold forward position, settling one-out 3L from leader. Swung wide entering straight but only one-paced despite hard riding.
Jumped OK but over-raced while laying out, dropping towards rear. Shifted wider 800m, then hard to settle, hanging out in straight though made up some ground.
Taken in for cover soon after start but still held wide towards rear. Swung wide entering straight but only one-paced.
Ridden early before seeking cover, dropping towards rear. Hard ridden approaching turn-in but made little headway. (Rider said horse sweated up badly before start)
Away well, shared early pace before seeking cover in midfield one-away from fence. Under pressure turning for home but failed to respond and hung out in straight.
First out, holding lead for a few strides before racing outside hindquarters of leader on settling. Lost position around home turn and faded in straight.

Crowded on jumping and eased back to settle at the rear of the field, with cover. Came wide turning for home, and had a clear run down the straight. Pulled away from the 150m and went to the line easily.

Looked to press forward from the wide draw, before electing to drop back and sit at the rear of the field. Still last turning for home. Boxed in until forcing a run at 200m. Finished very strongly late.

Crowded on jumping and then dropped back to sit last. Cut the corner on the turn to improve his position, and loomed up well in the straight. Equal leader at 150m, but didn't kick late and just held 3rd on the line.
Allowed to go forward early and settled forward of midfield, 3 wide with cover. Stayed on solidly in the straight and was catching 3rd late.
Eased forward early to settle midfield. Held up early in the straight, before getting clear running at 300m. Ran on solidly, without threatening.
Eased back from the wide draw to settle behind midfield. Ran on fairly under the stick, and picked up some of the slower ones late.
Went to push forward early from the wide draw, but was stuck 3 wide with no cover up front. Race was run by the 150m, and dropped out from there. Jockey questioned.
Allowed to press forward and take the lead. Only 1 paced in the straight, and not pushed hard late.
Slow away, but recovered quickly to push forward and settle 4th on the fence. Wider on the turn, but only went to the line 1 paced.
Pushed out early to settle forward of midfield, 1 off the fence. 1 paced in the straight and eased out late.
Pushed forward early and content to sit just behind the leader, 1 off the fence. Never let down and was disappointing in the straight. Eased late. Jockey questioned.
Cruised across from the wide draw to sit worse than midfield, 4 wide with only limited cover. Widest on the turn and only stayed on fairly in the straight.
Didn't muster early and settled midfield, 3 wide with limited cover. Never ran on in the straight, and eased out from the 150m.
Eased forward early to settle midfield, 1 off the fence. Never responded to pressure in the straight and was eased out late.

Horse No: Comments on Running is not available for this race.
Horse Name: Comments on Running is not available for this race.
Jockey: Comments on Running is not available for this race.
Gear: Comments on Running is not available for this race.
Comment: Comments on Running is not available for this race.
Soon dropped to rear of midfield despite reminders, commenced move entering the straight, ran on under pressure to prevail by a narrow margin.
Settled in rear on the rail and waited with, switched wide for a run entering straight, ran on strongly to just fail to get up on line.

Attempted to make all, pressed forward from the widest gate to lead on the rail approaching the 800 metres, broke nearly 3L clear after straightening but unable to sustain effort and swamped close to home.
Niggled in midfield on the rail, awkwardly placed behind runner coming onto home bend, finished off race well.
Broke well, settled about 3L off the pace in better than midfield, came to challenge under pressure turning for home, kept on steadily without quickening.
Settled just better than midfield on the rail, inconvenienced coming onto home bend, hampered entering the straight, switched out for a run after the 200 metres and produced some late impression.
Gradually dropped towards the rear despite ridden along, travelled wide without cover to the straight, ran home nicely near the centre of the track.
Ridden along before settling mainly in 5th within 3L of pace, shaken up upon straightening but could only keep on at the same pace without quickening.
Taken back from a wide gate, remained well behind to the straight, produced good late impression on the inside, not clear run yet did best work late.
Ridden positively from a wide gate, came within 1L of lead approaching the Rock, kept on before weakening inside the final 200 metres.
Trailed the field despite niggled along, never a factor.
Moderate start, soon settled in a prominent position in 3rd, folded up quickly shortly after straightening. (Bled) (Lame next day)
Pushed to sit in midfield, 2 wide, benefited by the fast sectionals, progressed steadily 300M to score.
At back, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, made steady ground 250M for 2nd.
Eased to rear, 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 400M for 3rd.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 2-3 wide, harmed by the fast pace, ran on ok.
Eased back, settled along the fence, suited by the fast pace, held up most straight, made ground when clear.
Eased to rear, took rail, favoured by the fast tempo, lack room 4-2, made steady ground.
Hard ridden to take rail and lead, under pressure throughout and clocked fast sectionals, hung on until 150M faded.
Pushed to obtain box seat, not suited by the fast sectionals, weakened 250M.
Hard ridden forward, sat outside the leader, harmed by the fast pace, emptied 300M.
Eased back, benefited by the fast pace, never progress.
Suited by the fast tempo, never a factor.
Pressed forward, trapped 3 wide throughout in front, harmed by the fast pace, dropped off 500M.
Hard ridden to take lead, asked for effort at Home Turn, travelled strongly in the straight, finished unchallenged.
Pushed along then raced behind leaders, improved passing 500M, fought hard entire straight, finished solidly.
Urged along to settle outside the leader, tried to improve passing 450M, battled hard and worked home solidly.
Taken back at start then raced at tail, made ground in the straight, came home nicely.
Travelled midfield on rail, asked for effort passing 350M, approaching 100M lay towards heels then shifted out, finished well.
Started well to hold box seat, under pressure in the straight and gave ground passing 50M, came home well.
Began only fairly, settled midfield on rail, shifted out at Home Turn to improve, finished fairly.
Taken back at start, travelled at tail, kept on rail in the straight, one-paced.
Travelled midfield, limited response when asked for effort at Home Turn, one-paced in the straight.
Settled behind midfield, provided difficult to settle in middle stages, widest on straightening, one-paced.
Taken back at start, settled midfield, no response when under pressure, failed to run on.
Lifted feet off the ground at start and slow to begin, settled behind midfield, weakened passing 100M, failed to run on.
Quickly into stride but over-raced before being settled along rail 5L from leader back stretch. Switched out home turn to make run, hit front 200m, pulled clear close home.
Jumped well but snagged back, settling 6L from leader along rail. Got inside run in straight and finished off strongly.
Quickly out, pressed forward, settling one-back, one-out. Swung wide entering straight, boxed on gamely to line.
Jumped well, ridden forward, grabbing rail at first turn, 2L from leader. Switched out at turn-in to challenge, boxed on well to 200m before turning one-paced.
Began awkwardly, then ridden along for some distance before shifted across behind runners, dropping to rear. Remained well back to 200m before making ground close home.
Raced in midfield mostly, one away from fence. Taken wide in straight but only one-paced under hard riding.
Pressed forward from an outside draw but stranded wide without cover in midfield. Covered extra ground throughout and only one-paced in straight.
Jumped OK but not enough speed to cross in and dropped back to behind midfield for cover. One-paced in straight.
Jumped well, shared early pace before taking lead 1350m, pulling 2L clear back stretch. Collared passing 200m and faded.
Pressed forward from an outside draw, racing wide till settling one-out 2L from leader back stretch. Shaken up at turn-in but found little and faded.
Crowded out start, taken to rail, settling towards rear. Never in contention and finished well back. Unacceptable performance.
Crowded out start and clear last on settling. Hard ridden back stretch but became detached approaching turn and finished tailed out. (Irregular heart rhythm).
Began awkwardly, raced 6 lengths back at rear, improved in the middle stages, very wide turning in, finished off very strongly in straight to score narrowly.
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back, there to turn, finished off well but couldn't hold off the winner, just missed.
Jumped well from gate 1, showed good early speed to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kicked clear after turning in, peaked and headed final 50M, stayed on for 3rd.
Began well from a wide draw, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back in midfield, similar position on turn, angled out near 200M to obtain clear running, made some progress thereafter to make frame.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, made some progress before bumped near 200M, finished off evenly thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 7 lengths back at tail, angled out turning in, made reasonable progress in straight.
Jumped well, positioned a length or so back on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Checked at start, recovered to race 3 lengths back on rail in midfield, easy run on turn, raced tight near 300M, one-paced thereafter.
Crowded out start, raced 4 lengths back on rail, same margin back on turn, finished off one-paced.
Bumped start, sent forward to race outside the leader in 2nd, peaked after turning in, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide at rear, last turning in, failed to close off in straight.

Crowded out start, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with no cover in midfield, slightly improved in the middle stages, weakened after turning in, checked near 200M, finished last. (See Racing Incidents.)
Sent forward, sat just behind the lead on the rail 1/2L off, kept on going and held off late challenge to score by a neck.
Settled to race in midfield, 2-1/2L behind 2 wide, exited the turn wide, ran home nicely for 2nd, missed by a neck.
Eased and raced behind midfield, 4-1/2L behind 2 wide, shifted widest near 150M and closed off well for 3rd.
Travelled in about midfield, 3L behind along the rail, showed good kick after 200M and ran on well to the line.
Pushed and raced close to the lead 1-1/4L off, made the turn very wide, kept on going to the line.
Sent forward and shared lead in a 2 wide position, looked flattened at 150M but found extra and kept on one paced.
Rolled forward to obtain box-seat, sat 1-3/4L off the leader, kept on one paced to the line.
Raced at the rear, 5-1/2L behind along the rail, saved ground early then eased by rider after 100M. (Rider was spoken to regarding his riding towards the end)
Sent forward and shared lead, made the turn 3 wide, hard ridden until crowded at 150M, did not run on thereafter.
Niggled along, settled behind the leaders, 1-1/2L off 2 wide, couldn't find extra approaching 100M.
Crowded at the start then raced at the rear, about 7-1/4L behind 2 wide at turn, did not threaten.
Pushed out of the barriers, settled around midfield, 3-1/2L behind but 3 wide at turn, swung widest and not competitive.
Began well, racing outside early leaders before settling one-out, one-back. Surged forward top of straight to lead passing 200m, held off late challenges.
Hampered start, then shifted across behind runners, dropping to last pair. Last into straight, taken to centre track and finished powerfully.
First out before settling in box seat and keeping tabs on leader. Got rails run in straight when leader swung wide, battled strongly to the line.
Shifted in for cover soon after start, dropping towards rear but away from fence. Taken to centre rack on straight, finished strongly final 200m.
Ridden to hold forward position, settling along rail 3L from leader. Shifted out turning for home, ran on well to finish just behind place-getters.
Ridden to hold midfield position but trapped wide without cover. Taken very wide in straight and boxed on gamely.
Jumped well, then ridden to hold midfield position one-away from fence. Swung wide at turn-in but kept on gamely to line.
Bounced OK, ridden along behind midfield but away from fence. Kept on gamely in straight to finish close behind place-getters.
Shifted out at start, becoming unbalanced, before pressing forward to race outside hind-quarters of leader. Rolled forward entering straight to share lead passing 200m before flattened close home.
Shifted across behind runners soon after start, dropping to last pair. Shaken up top of straight to challenge but blocked for run final 100m and not properly tested.
Pressed forward to lead on settling, setting slow pace to straight. Overtaken passing 200m and faded.
Not pushed early, racing along rail behind midfield. Took inside run in straight but ran out of room and forced to switch out close home. Not properly tested.
Held up behind midfield, shifted out 800M racing wide no cover, made his move passing 650M, sustained run to lead inside 50M, well on top at the line.
Chased leader, moved up to challenge from 300M, gained narrow lead 150M but couldn't hold off winner late.
From wide draw taken back in early stages, settled down in 10th 8Ls off the pace, made his bid 600M, tried hard in the run home, got up 3rd near line.
Pushed forward, travelled keenly in the lead despite efforts of its riders to restrain the horse, set fast pace middle stages, joined by rival early straight, rallied but run ended late stages.
In midfield along the inside, 5Ls off the pace home turn, chased leaders steadily over final 300M.
Travelled fore of midfield, 4Ls off the good pace halfway, kept on same pace in the run home.

From wide draw taken back in early stages, settled down towards the rear 9Ls off the good pace, stayed on moderately, no clear run 150M had to shift lane to continue but never looked like troubling leaders.
From wide draw taken back in early stages, waited with in the rear over 10Ls off the pace, brought wide for challenge 400M, ran past beaten horses only.
Not hurried early stages, settled down at the rear over 10Ls behind leaders in first half, moved closer passing 600M, plodded on in straight, never likely.
Chased leaders in 4th, got shuffled back nearing 400M, didn't quicken turning in. No threat.
Held up 2-wide in midfield, struggled to keep up 500M, soon out of contention.
Rushed forward, vied for lead on the outside, under pressure 550M, gave ground and weakened to last.

Ridden early, settled in midfield or slightly worse on the rail, commenced move on top of home bend and switched wide into straight, soon hit the front and sprinted clear inside the final 100 metres.
Gradually settled in midfield, gained closer to the lead when pace slackened far side, commenced move entering the straight, ran on steadily without threatening.

Pressed forward from a wide gate to take up running on the rail from the 1200 metres, being challenged for 200 metres before going clear approaching the home straight, unable to sustain effort and swamped inside the final 100 metres.
Travelled wide in midfield, in similar position turning for home, inconvenienced 250 metres out, kept on one pace under pressure in the straight.
Not far off, travelled keenly within 2L of pace on the far side, left flat-footed when pace quickened up around the home bend, ran home one-paced.
Soon dropped well behind, given reminders on the far side, remained some 10 lengths off the lead turning into the straight, ran on past well-beaten horses in the run home.
Well there early, carried backward to 7th about 4L off the pace early in back straight, shuffled further back on the rail coming onto home bend, ran home one-paced.
Settled in last few from a wide gate, trailed the field from the back straight, looked well-beaten turning for home, finished off race well down the centre of the track.

Hard ridden from a wide gate, circled the field around the first bend before disputing the lead for 200 metres far side, unable to sustain on home bend and soon faded under pressure. (Tactic questioned)
Recovered quickly from a moderate start to reach prominent 3rd position wide without cover on the far side, soon weakened out of contention after straightening.
Began awkwardly, soon taken backward on the rail, remained mainly towards the rear to the straight, made no further impression.
Ridden positively from the middle gate, settled just off the speed on the rail far side, lost momentum coming out of the back straight, never recovered.
Began from a wide gate, settling just worse than midfield when hampered and lost position 1200 metres out, remained wide towards the rear rounding home bend, made no further impression.
Taken back from the widest gate, improved from the 1400 metres to reach the rear of midfield when wide in back straight, unable to sustain run and dropped away after the home turn.
Pushed early, sat behind midfield, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Eased to sit just off the speed, 2 wide, not suited by the fast sectionals, ran on strongly for 2nd.
At rear, trapped 3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 250M for 3rd.
Pushed early to hold the rail in midfield, suited by the fast pace, blocked most straight, made good ground.
Hard ridden early, at back, 3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, trapped 3-4 wide, held ground in straight.
Eased back, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, lack room in straight, made steady ground.
Sat outside the leader, not suited by the fast sectionals, ran on until 200M weakened.
Pushed to take rail and lead, clocked fast sectionals, ran on until 200M out of fuel.
Pushed to obtain box seat, not suited by the fast pace, emptied 400M.
Pushed early but not muster, trapped 4-5 wide throughout at back, no dash.
Hard ridden early, suited by the fast tempo, never better than midfield.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3-4 wide throughout in the lead, harmed by the fast pace, faded 500M.
Never a factor.
Moderate start, raced midfield, improved in the early straight, travelled well and quickened passing 200M, finished strongly to score.
After the 900M was left travelled wide and without cover, improved approaching 400M, issued a challenge passing 150M, worked home strongly.
Started OK, settled midfield wide with cover, widest on straightening, made good late ground passing 100M, finished solidly.
Ridden along to take box seat, asked for effort in the early straight, made ground passing 200M, finished nicely.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, settled at tail, in the straight lay in under pressure, made some nice late ground, came home well.
Settled midfield on rail, commenced to improve passing 500M, fought hard entire straight, finished well.
Urged along to settle outside the lead, tried to improve in the early straight, gave ground passing 150M, finished OK.
Taken back at start, made the turn after 900M awkwardly, approaching 500M was inconvenienced, one-paced in the straight. (Bled)
Taken back at start, settled behind midfield, one-paced when under pressure in the straight.
Settled midfield on rail, tried to improve passing 500M, gave ground passing 150M, failed to run on.
Travelled wide without cover then after 850M moved to settle behind leaders, weakened badly passing 200M, failed to close off.
Began only fairly, raced at tail on rail, no response in the straight, failed to finish off.
Fractious in the barrier and began only fairly, travelled well in middle stages, didn't respond when asked for effort in the straight and gave ground, finished disappointing. (Blood trachea)
Hard ridden to take lead, passing 1000M moved close to the rail, kept on rail in the straight, weakened passing 200M, failed to run on.
Quickly into stride, taken to front, crossed to fence, then eased into box seat 1600m. Rolled forward top to straight, hit front 250m, kept finding when challenged.
Ridden forward, settling one-out in midfield. Shifted out 700m to make challenge, racing 4-wide outsider leaders at turn in, kept on strongly to line.
Jumped well then raced mostly in midfield close to fence. Ran into heaving traffic approaching turn-in, got clear halfway up straight, finished well.
No pace, dropped to rear, then over-raced after 1300m. Took closer order home turn, took run between horses in straight, finished strongly final 200m to just miss a placing. (Rider dropped whip 200m)
Not pushed, raced close to fence behind midfield. Switched out home turn to make run, checked 550m, raced tight at turn-in, switched out, finished off well.
Shifted in after jumping from wide barrier, settling one-out at rear. Closed in around home turn, taken wide in straight and ran on steadily.
Pressed forward on jumping, settling one-out 3L from leader. Became unbalanced 550m, moved forward to 3-wide outside leader at turn-in, kept on well until swamped close home.
Not pushed, racing one-out behind midfield. Taken wide in straight to make challenge, got within range 200m before hanging out badly and losing position.
Began fairly, no speed, dropping to rear along fence. Stayed on fence home turn and straight, made up good ground to 200m before turning one-paced.
Away well, made use of inside draw to hold rail, settling 3L from leader. Turned in behind runners, switched out to challenge but ran out of steam 200m and one-paced.
Pressed forward 3-wide before taking lead 1650m and crossing to fence. Set steady pace to 250m when overtaken and faded.
Away well, ridden forward, settling one-out, one-back. Became unbalanced just before turn-in, soon under pressure and gave ground gradually.
Hard ridden to go forward before settling one-out 1L from leader. Kept tabs to straight when ran out of stamina and faded.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw and last on settling. Remained at rear throughout and never in the hunt.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, travelled well to turn, angled out near 500M, made very good progress in straight to score.
Jumped well, positioned 2 lengths or so back on rail, easy run on turn, took the lead near 250M, kept on well thereafter but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Away with them, positioned 2 wide, 6 lengths back, improved on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Began well from a wide draw, raced 2 wide in 4th, improved from 550M, finished off evenly in straight.
Slowly away, raced 9 to 10 lengths back at tail, slightly improved on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to be nearest on line.

Jumped with them, positioned 4 lengths back on rail in midfield, steadied near 1400M, there to turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off evenly when clear thereafter. (Lost both front plates near 100M.)
Slow to begin, raced 8 lengths back at rear, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.
Began fairly from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, peaked after turning in, headed near 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well from a tricky gate, raced 2 wide in 2nd, peaked after turning in, weakened thereafter.
Slow out, raced 2 wide at rear, 8 lengths back, slightly improved on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 9 to 10 lengths back, last turning in, made no progress in straight, eased late.
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, showed no response from near 600M, eased early in straight. (Had irregular heart rhythm and bled from both nostrils.)
Settled to race in midfield in a 2 wide position, chased lead until 100M, kept going and edged to win by a neck.
Sent forward and raced behind the lead albeit 4L behind, assumed lead near 300M until caught by winner after 100M, fought on and missed by a neck.
Rolled forward, settled to race in front of midfield along the rail, worked home well to take 3rd.
Crowded start, near the tail along the rail, awkward to heels prior to exit to turn, made ground and ran on fairly.
Settled in behind midfield and always 2 wide, kept on one paced to the line.
Hard ridden for the lead, established fast pace and a 4L margin in the middle stages, couldn't keep up from 300M. (Trainer and rider questioned)
Taken out at start, settled to race in about midfield along the rail, emptied after 300M.
Crowded after start, settled to race at the rear 2 wide, saved minor ground whilst hanging in in the straight.
Shifted across from wide draw soon after start, settling 3-wide behind midfield. Took turn 3-wide but had clear running in straight, hit front 200m and pulled clear.
Jumped well, not pushed, dropping one-out towards rear. Blocked for run early in straight, got clear 300m, finished strongly.
Ridden to hold forward position, taken to fence first but then taken one-out 2L from leader approaching turn. Held for run early in straight, shifted in 300m, finished well.
Hard ridden from jump to lead, crossing to fence 900m and setting slow pace to straight. Overtaken 200m and tired close home but managed to hang on for 4th.
Began well, not pushed, dropping one-out towards rear. Taken 4-wide around home turn, widest into straight, finished off nicely.
Outpaced, dropping to rear along fence. Last into straight, ran on fairly concluding stages.
Pressed forward from outside draw, racing wide without cover until settling outside hind-quarters of leader. Kept tabs to 200m when tired and faded.
Jumped well, shared pace before sliding into box seat when crossed 900m. Tracked leader to 200m when came under pressed and faded.
First out but not willing to lead, checked 900m losing ground, Travelled keenly home turn losing more ground, then held up in traffic till concluding stages and not tested.
Ridden forward, sliding in for cover approaching turn but left 3-wide from 800m when 2L from leader. Under pressure soon after straightening and faded.
Held up behind midfield 4Ls off the steady pace, 3-wide swinging for home, chased well inside 300M and gave a kick final 200M to beat off the challengers.
Began fairly, settled down in midfield along the fence, moved sweetly into contention passing 450M, ran on strongly under 5lb penalty to lead near 100M, outgunned late.

Led early stages, restrained and sat just off the pace passing 1000M, switched out 600M and poised to strike, led narrowly inside 350M, stuck on gamely only headed by first 2 near 100M, held on 3rd just.
Waited with near the rear in steadily run race, about 5Ls to make up 400M, brought widest and closed off nicely under 5lb penalty, just missed 3rd spot.
Reserved towards the rear just over 5Ls off the steady pace, in similar position turning in, kept finding the line well to finish not far behind much higher rated rivals.
In midfield along the 3-path, no cover from 1200M, strode to outside of leader 750M, kept battling entering straight, couldn't hold off pursuers over final 100M, faded out of contention.
Tracked leaders along the inside, kept up the chase turning home, held up 200M-100M, but well held by leaders when clear final stages.
Settled down in midfield 4Ls off the steady pace, ran on moderately over final 400M but couldn't muster the speed to be closer.
Went forward from draw 11, emerged as leader 1000M, led them steadily to straight, headed 350M, fought on until no extra 100M.
With leaders early, restrained to sit at the fore of midfield, moved up 700M to a contending spot, steadied passing 300M but couldn't lift in the run home.
Dropped back from draw 10, 7Ls off the pace in rear as they settled, tried hard in straight but couldn't get closer to leaders.
Taken back from wide barrier, settled in rear pair 6-7Ls behind leader, couldn't pick up under pressure entering straight, never threatened.
Jumped OK, no speed, dropping to rear along fence. Took inside run on straightening, weaved passage between horses, got clear 160m, burst though for narrow win.
Ridden along outside early leader before settling one-out, one-back at turn. Picked up momentum top of straight, making ground gradually only to fail narrowly.
Ridden forward looking for cover but held 3-wide in midfield passing 900m and allowed to stride forward to race outside leader. Took lead passing 200m but run down close to line.
Pressed forward from outside draw to lead passing 1000m before crossing to fence at turn. Overtaken 200m but battled on gamely until swamped close home.
Crowded out start, not pushed, dropping towards rear. Made up ground between horses around turn, got clear run in straight, boxed on gamely.
Began awkwardly, losing ground, taken in for cover, settling one-out near rear. Taken to centre track on straightening and finished off nicely.
Shifted in for cover soon after start, settling one-out at rear. Remained well back until straighten when ran on steadily between horses to be closest at finish.
Broke well, pressed forward, settling 3L from leader close to fence. Got close to heels around turn, boxed on well early in straight until tiring close home.
Began well, ridden along close to pace, settling 3L from leader at turn. Boxed on well early in straight but one-paced close home.
Jumped with field, ridden to hold rail but unable hold position and shuffled to midfield around turn. Boxed on one-paced in straight.
Began awkwardly, taken to fence behind pacemakers, over-raced and taken out, taking home turn 3-wide. Taken wider in straight, ran out of steam 200m and faded.
Hard ridden from inside draw to lead on settling, before sliding into box seat when overtaken 1000m. Under pressure on straightening and gave ground gradually.
Strolled forward on jumping before seeking cover 900m at midfield. Four-wide home turn, wider into straight, tired and eased down, finishing tailed out. Unacceptable performance.

Crowded on jumping and then steadied back to settle last, and still last turning for home. Manoeuvred through & came off heels at 300m for a clear run. Pushed last 200m, caught leaders at 50m and scooted clear under minimal urging.

Awkwardly away, but recovered quickly to push forward from the wide draw to sit 2nd. Battled strongly in straight & wore down the leader 100m. Led for half stride before being quickly passed by winner and had to settle for 2nd.
Pushed out to lead early. Stayed on solidly in the straight, and kept the lead until peaking in the last 100m. Vet reported that horse was a bleeder.
Eased forward early to settle midfield. Awkward on heels 950m. Sayed on well from 250m, and was rapidly catching 3rd late.
Eased back early to be worse than midfield. Stayed on well in the straight, and only peaked towards the end of the race.
Taken across from the wide draw to sit midfield, but stuck 3 wide with no cover. Prominent at the top of the straight, but only stayed on 1 paced late.
Eased away and settled behind midfield, 1 off the fence. Wider on the turn, but only responded fairly in the straight.
Pushed forward early to be handily placed 3rd/4th on the fence. Ran onto heels and was awkwardly placed 800m. Ran flat in the straight, and not pushed hard late.
Bumped on jumping before settling midfield. Quietly ridden, then held up at the top of the straight. Clear last 200m and stayed on fairly. Jockey questioned.
Taken up early to settle handy 3rd/4th, 1 off the fence. Well placed on the turn, but never responded to pressure and only went hands and heels to the line.
Eased back early to sit towards the rear of the field. Awkwardly placed on heels rounding the home turn, the badly held up until 250m. Finally clear at 200m, but wasn't pushed to the line.
Eased back early to settle towards the rear of the field. Widest on the turn, but never a factor in the straight.
Taken up early to sit around midfield, on the fence. Came off heels at 700m. Didn't respond to any pressure and not pushed out in the straight.
Dropped back early for cover, but was stuck 3-4 wide at the rear, with no cover. Pushed forward at 800m to midfield, but still stuck wide. Dropped out in the straight. Vet-Roarer.

With leaders early stages, steadied to 5th within 3L of pace, quickened well to assert authority passing the 200 metres, won readily.
Jumped well, settled mainly 3L off the pace in 6th on the rail, similar turning into home straight when tight between runners early on, fought on steadily to claim 2nd late.
Began well from the one draw, with leaders early stages, taken 2L back in 4th on the rail, switched out for a run upon straightening but could only run home one-paced.

Moderate start, settled towards the rear on the rail, saved ground on the inside turning in, soon came to challenge upon straightening but baulked for a run, finished off race nicely inside the final 150 metres.
Moderate start, soon ridden to midfield about 4L off the speed in back straight, came under pressure from rounding home bend, kept on same pace without quickening.
Ridden early among leaders, obtained lead on the rail after first 300 metres, led most of way to passing the 200 metres, weakened under pressure.

Slowly away, pushed along before settling one from last on the rail, commenced move home bend but did not find much room early in straight, made no further impression in the run to the line. (Jockey explanation accepted)
Began from a wide gate, with leaders early stages, taken back just off the pace half-way down back straight, in similar position turning for home but soon dropped out of contention.

Moderate start off the widest gate, soon given reminders and travelled wide towards the rear in back straight, wide home turn, hung in behind runners early in straight, produced good late impression closing stages.

Ridden positively from a wide gate to keep up with the leaders early, travelled wide without cover back straight, pushed forward to hit the front briefly onto home bend, weakened noticeably under pressure inside the final 250M.
Raced wide throughout, taken back from a wide gate to midfield, lost position rounding the home bend, made no impression in straight.
Soon tailed-off, never a factor.
Eased to rear for cover, pace good, dashed strongly 300M to score.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide early, pace good, made early move 800M, led 500M, hung on until 100M overhauled.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, pace good, progressed steadily 600M.
Pushed forward, 2-3 wide, pace good, made early move 800M, ran on well.
Pushed early but not muster, behind midfield on the rails, pace good, made steady ground 200M.
Midfield, 2 wide, pace good, ran on just ok in straight.
Took rail at rear, pace good, made minor ground 200M.
At back, 2 wide, pace good, blocked most straight, not properly tested.
Pushed early to hold the rail in midfield, pace good, lack turn of foot.
Pushed to obtain box seat, pace good, flattened 200M.
Trapped 3 wide in midfield early, moved forward 1200M to sit in 2 wide, out of fuel 300M.
Pushed forward to take rail and lead, soon emptied 400M.
Fast out, ridden along to hold leading position on rail, fought well in the straight, quickened passing final 50M to score.
Taken back at start, travelled wide with cover in midfield, approaching 600M moved in one off, wide on straightening, issued a strong challenge passing 50M, missed by neck.
Settled midfield on rail, shifted in for clear running in the early straight, kept improving on the rail, finished solidly.
Began slowly, raced behind midfield, approaching 600M commenced to improve, made up some nice late ground, finished well.
Taken back at start, settled midfield, moved to rail at 600M, gradually made ground in the straight, worked home well.
For the majority of race travelled wide and without cover, raced at handy position, under pressure in the straight, finished fairly.
Settled at back on rail, asked for effort to catch up main group in the early and middle stages, only one-paced in the straight.
At the start was bumped and became unbalanced when buffeted between runners, settled behind midfield on rail, from 200M until after 100M was unable to find clear running, not fully tested.
Hard ridden to race wide outside the leaders, passing 800M rolled forward to take lead at one off position, asked for effort but limited response in the straight, weakened passing 50M.
Settled behind leaders, asked for effort passing 400M, awkwardly placed in the early straight, one-paced after.
Urged along to settle outside the leader, passing 700M drifted back to handy position, tiring badly passing 150M and failed to run on.
Taken back at start, raced at tail, never in it.
Ridden to get forward position, settling one-out, one-back. Swung wide into straight, picked up momentum, finished strongly doing best work final 150m.
Away well, taken to rail and settled 5L from leader. Got run between horses on straightening and finished off well.
Travelled comfortably in midfield, one-away from fence. Swung wide into straight and worked home strongly to grab minor placing.
Found early pace hot, settling behind midfield between horses. Remained well back to straight, switched out for clear run, finished off nicely to just miss a placing.
Hard ridden from widest gate, sharing lead before easing 1L back passing 900m. Set off after leader on straightening and kept on gamely to line.
Steadied soon after jump and taken in for cover, settling one-out towards rear. Taken to centre field on straightening and ran on steadily.
Ridden to get forward position but not enough speed and held three-wide without cover in midfield. Kept wide throughout but still kept on fairly in straight.
Began fairly, not pushed, dropping to rear close to fence. Remained well back to straight before making ground final 100m.
Crowded out start, then checked, dropping to last. Remained well back to straight before running past beaten rivals.
Pressed forward from wide gate, sharing early lead before pulling ahead 900m. Kicked 3L clear on straightening but emptied 100m and faded.
Checked shortly after start, dropping to behind midfield along fence. Shaken up turning for home but only one-paced in straight.
Ridden early to hold box seat, keeping tabs on leading pair. Hard ridden from 500m to hold position, under pump in straight before giving ground quickly final 100m. Unacceptable performance.
Fast into stride, showed early speed to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kept on well after turning in, scored by a neck.
Away with them, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths back in midfield, same position on turn, finished off strongly in straight to be nearest on line.
Bumped jumping out and unbalanced, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening, tried hard but always held.
Slowly away, raced 6 lengths back on rail at rear, saved ground to near 400M, taken wide thereafter, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 2 to 3 lengths back on rail, same position to near 400M, angled out for a run turning in, finished off evenly without threatening.
Steadied shortly after start and shifted in for cover, raced 4 to 5 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, showed no progress when clear thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 7 to 8 lengths back, still well back on turn, taken widest in straight and made reasonable headway to be nearest on line.
Bumped start, raced 6 lengths back at rear, slightly improved from 600M, 3 wide on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off evenly.

Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, difficult to settle near 1300M, raced tight near 600M and around home turn, finished off one-paced in straight. (See Racing Incidents.) (Epiglottic entrapment.)
Began only fairly from a tricky draw, unable to slot in early, sent forward near 1300M to race outside the leader, peaked after turning in, weakened gradually thereafter.
Crowded out start and unbalanced, unable to slot in early, raced 3 wide with no cover in 4th, found cover near 1000M, peaked on turn and bumped near 400M, weakened gradually in straight.

Taken back from the widest draw, raced 4 to 5 lengths back, left racing wide and without cover near 1000M, slightly improved in the middle stages, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight, finished last.
Settled to race in midfield, 3L behind the lead 2 wide, bumped and unbalanced at 200M, ran on nicely to the line.
Eased and raced towards the rear, 7-1/4L behind 2 wide, made nice ground and fought on to finish 2nd.
Settled to race in one-off one-back position, sat 1-3/4L off the lead, kept on going to the line to take 3rd.
In around midfield, 3L behind along the rail, awkward on heels at 200M, then shifted out and worked home well for 4th.
Eased and settled to race worse than midfield, 4-3/4L behind 2 wide, swung widest and made steady ground to the line.
In behind midfield, 4-3/4L behind along the rail, commenced to make ground until checked after 200M.
Pushed forward and led in a 2 wide position, steadied at 600M, kept on until checked at 200M.
Sent forward, prominent but trapped wide initially, improved to lead on rail at 550M, weakened gradually near 200M.
Niggled to obtain box-seat, sat 1-1/2L off the pace, run ended when hampered passing 300M.
Eased back and remained at the rear, never improved.
Pushed forward, sat outside the lead, dropped off from 500M and tailed out, must trial.
Ridden to hold midfield position, one-away from fence. Swung wide turning for home, picked up strongly final 200m to win close home.
Away well, stayed close to pace in one-out position. Had clear running top of straight, loomed boldly 100m but unable to hold off winner final strides.
Jumped well, taken to fence 900m but tended to over-race and checked 650m, settling 5L from leader. Took inside run in straight, weaving between horses to grab minor placing.
Hard ridden from widest draw to lead passing 950m, cutting to fence 800m. Kept up good pace before running on empty 50m and swamped.
Steadied shortly after start and taken in for cover, settling behind midfield one-away from fence. Taken very wide in straight and finished off fairly.
Jumped well, pressed forward, settling one-out 2L from leader. Shaken up turning for home but did not improve and finished one-paced.
Ridden along to hold rail 4L from leader. Stayed on rail around turn but failed to improve when asked 300m and plodded to line.
Hampered start and last on settling. Trailed field to straight before running on fairly final 200m.
Bounded in air at start losing ground, taken to fence, and settled towards rear. Stayed on fence around turn, one-paced in straight.
Away well, pressed forward inside pace before taking box seat 2L from leader. Shifted out 400m to challenge, loomed 200m before dropping off sharply 100m. Bled both nostrils.
No pace, dropping to last pair soon after start. Remained at rear throughout and never in contention.
Shared early pace before settling 3L back but 3-wide without cover. Swung wide into straight and soon under pressure, dropping out final 150m. (Lost left hind plate 1150m)
Guided to the fence soon after the jump, settled 3-4Ls off the pace in midfield, challenged on the inside passing 300M, quickened up smartly to lead 200M and pulled away for a commanding win.
Away quickly to be 5th on settling, remained in touch final turn, kept finding the line well but couldn't reel in winner.
Failed to muster speed despite ridden along, settled down in 10th 4-5Ls behind leader, brought wide passing 400M, chased steadily to go 3rd near line but never threatened the winner.
Eased back on jumping from draw 12, raced as the back-marker 6Ls off the pace, stayed on well between runners for 4th.
Dropped back on jumping from wide draw, held up in 2nd last, had rails run, chased solidly without posing threat to the winner, narrowly missed out in the scramble for 3rd placing.
Began fairly, chased leaders on the inside, well placed to strike 350M, kept on evenly, unbalanced when making heavy contact with rival 150M, outsprinted towards the finish.
Chased leaders but caught 3-wide no cover during the race, boxed on over final 300M but lacked the needed kick.
Restrained in midfield just over 3Ls off leader, shifted out to 3-wide middle stages, kept grinding away entire straight, no threat inside 150M.
Jumped well from draw 1, led reluctantly, appeared to travel well into straight but run ended 200M and weakened noticeably.
Not hurried on jumping from wide draw, settled down behind midfield, just over 3Ls behind leader at 400M, couldn't come on.
Rushed forward from draw 9, parked outside leader, under pressure 450M, soon weakened away.
In midfield, caught wide the whole trip, widest straightening and couldn't find any when asked.
