Settled just off the pace, commenced move shifting towards the stands rail passing the 400 metres, hit the front under pressure just inside the 200 metres, held on well.
Sluggish start, soon recovered to within 3L of pace, commenced move inside the 300 metres, ran on under pressure but never threatening.
Settled within 3L of the pace on the stands rail, ran on under pressure to claim 3rd close to home.
Settled within 2L of the pace, faded gradually inside the final 200 metres.
Began from the one draw, settled about 3L off the pace near the centre of the track, ran home one-paced under pressure.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, soon dropped to last few about 4L back, kept on one pace under pressure.
Trailed the field to the 300 metres, ran on past well-beaten runners closing stages.
Began from the two draw, settled not far off the pace near the centre of the track, faded under pressure inside the final 200 metres.
Jumped fairly, soon dropped to last few, ran past well-beaten horses closing stages.
Showed natural speed to establish a 1L break early stages, led the field until headed by the winner inside the 200 metres, dropped out under pressure close to home.
Settled within 3L of the pace near the centre of the track, weakened under pressure inside the final 200 metres.
Not far off, weakened under pressure inside the final 200 metres.
Settled just off the pace, gradually faded after coming onto the course proper.
Soon dropped to last few, never seen with a chance.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 350M to score.
Pushed forward and shared early lead, not suited by the fast sectionals, ran on strongly 300M for 2nd.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, ran on well to the line despite hanging out away from the whip.
Hard ridden to take the rails and to keep up in midfield, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M.
Very slow away, detached early, suited by the fast tempo, dashed strongly 200M.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, 2-3 wide, assisted by the fast pace, made steady ground 250M.
Hard ridden to share the lead in 2 wide, harmed by the fast pace, weakened 200M.
Eased back, 2 wide, on heels early, suited by the fast tempo, ran on fairly.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast pace, no dash.
Box seat, not suited by the fast tempo, emptied 250M.
At rear, on the rails, benefited by the fast tempo, never improved.
At back along the fence, on heels early, suited by the fast pace, no progress.
Began only fairly, settled box seat, improved passing 400M, in the final stages travelled strongly, finished unchallenged.
Started OK, settled midfield, asked for effort passing 400M, made up some nice late ground, worked home solidly.
Began well and settled outside the lead, asked for effort passing 400M, battled hard in the straight and finished solidly.
Urged along after start, raced behind midfield, lay in when under pressure in the straight, not fully tested.
Travelled behind midfield, commenced to improve at Home Turn, made ground passing 100M, finished nicely.
Fast out and took the lead, fought hard entire straight and passing 100M gave ground, finished fairly.
Began only fairly then raced back, tried to improve at Home Turn, worked home fairly.
Moderate start, ridden passing 900M but failed to improve, one-paced in the straight when under pressure.
Urged along and settled behind leaders, asked for effort approaching 500M, weakened passing 150M, failed to close off.
Ridden along at start then taken back for cover, settled midfield, no response in the straight, failed to run on.
Travelled at back, always ridden along but no response at any stages, failed to make impression, rider and trainer questioned, must trial.
Taken back at start then travelled wide and without cover, in the straight gave ground. Bled.
Jumped badly losing ground, taken to rail and settled in last pair. Shifted out in straight to get clear running before powering home, doing best work final 200m.
Shifted in for cover shortly after start, settling one-out towards rear. Improved position home turn but 4-wide, finished strongly.
Taken to fence and settled 3L from leader. Turned in behind horses, got clear passage 200m, finished strongly final 50m to snatch minor placing.
Well there early but kept 3-wide. Swung wide entering straight and kept on gamely to line.
Pressed forward between horses to get within 2L of leader. Tended to over-raced approaching home turn and checked off heels. Loomed 200m but swamped close home.
Settled one-out towards rear, then raced ungenerously when stoked up passing 800m. Turned wide, boxed on gamely.
Ridden to hold midfield position but trapped wide, then left without cover 800m. Allowed to stride forward circling field to lead into straight. Kept on strongly until swamped final stages.
Ridden positively to hold box seat, keeping tabs on leaders. Stayed on rail in straight, kept on well until flattened final 50m.
Began fairly, not pushed, settling one-out towards rear. Taken to centre field on straightening but only one-paced.
First out, led narrowly to 1000m before racing outside early leader to turn. Edged ahead at turn-in, kept on fairly before tiring close home.
Hard ridden along rail inside early leader before taking over 1000 and slowing pace. Overtaken entering straight, kept on fairly until emptied 200m.
Began fairly, settling one-out behind midfield. Got shuffled back at turn and only one-paced in straight.
Jumped well, hard ridden to get within 1L of leader but held 3-wide without cover. Started to feel the pinch turning for home and faded in straight.
Shifted in for cover soon after start, settling in last pair. Remained at rear throughout and never in contention.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off strongly in straight and scored by a neck.
Away with them, sent forward to race prominently, 3 wide throughout, took the lead after turning in, kept on well but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Moderately away from a tricky draw, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths back, similar position on turn, angled out early in straight and made some progress to take 3rd.
Began well, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide throughout, shared lead on turn, peaked and headed early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 4 lengths back at rear, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Slightly slow out, positioned 3 lengths back on rail, save ground on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped well from gate 1, raced prominently, shared lead on turn, peaked early in straight, finished off one-paced thereafter.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 3 wide at rear, 3 to 4 lengths back, wider on turn, finished off one-paced.
Began only fairly, positioned 2 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, but finished off only one-paced.
Steadied on jumping, no early speed, raced at tail, still last turning in, one-paced in straight.
Jumped well from a middle draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 to 4 wide, found cover on turn, emptied early in straight.
Jumped well from the widest draw, unable to slot in, travelled wide with no cover throughout, emptied early in straight when hard run took effect.
Rolled forward and settled one-off one-back, sat 2-1/2L off, away gradually from 200M, ran on nicely to score by 1/2L.
Jumped in then raced at the rear, 7L behind 2 wide, swung widest to make nice ground, kept on strongly and missed by 1/2L.
Rolled into a spot just in front of midfield, sat 3-1/2L behind along the rail, kept on well but was no match.
Raced in behind midfield, 5L behind along the rail, improved slightly and kept on going to the line.
Sent forward and raced in the box-seat, sat 1-1/2L off the lead, ran on fairly well once cleared after 300M.
Crowded start, raced towards the rear, 6L behind 2 wide, made ground and ran on nicely inside final 200M.
Settled to race just in front of midfield, 4-1/4L behind 2 wide, crowded at 900M, one paced in the straight.
Niggled then took rail and led by 1L, headed when couldn't keep up at 300M, only one paced to the line.
Pushed forward from a wide barrier, sat 1L off and outside the lead, gradually faded after 250M.
Ridden after start then raced tight, in just behind midfield, 5-1/2L behind 3 wide rounding turn, showed nothing.
Crowded out start, recovered, pushed forward to race a half-length behind leader 400m. Hit the front 200m and held off late challenge.
Slow, shifted out towards outer fence while making ground. Unable get clear run until 250m but then forced to race tight. Broke through final 50m but just missed.
Jumped well, taken to centre field and settled 3L from leader. Urged forward passing 400m, finished well to grab minor placing.
First out, taken to outer fence and set strong pace. Under the pump passing 200m but battled on strongly till run down final strides.
No early pace, shifted out but kept 3-away from outer fence. Under the pump from 400m and kept on gamely to finished just behind place-getters.
No pace, shifted out from inside draw, settling towards rear. Shaken up passing 500m and ran on steadily.
Settled along outer rail behind midfield. Started to improve from 600m, finishing close behind place-getters.
Away well, shifted out to race inside leader passing 800m. Looked chance 300m when joint leader but ran out of steam 100m and faded.
Away well, then taken to outer rail in midfield. Held position to 400m when one-paced.
Hard ridden to stay with pace, settling one-away from outer fence 3L from leader. Put under pressure passing 400m but only one-paced.
Stumbled start but recovered quickly and pressed forward to within 3L of leader. No response when popped the question 400m and faded.
Slow into stride, and soon detached from field. Never in contention.

Began well to take a up a prominent spot behind leaders in a slowly run race, into clear 400M, quickened up smartly to lead 200M, dug deep with strong determination to hold off challengers both sides.
Held up in midfield, raced keenly in a slowly run race, into clear 300M and chased well, went 2nd near line but couldn't reel in winner. Strong debut.
Away well enough, gradually moved up to track leaders along the rail, responded well when asked on straightening, laid down a strong challenge, pushed winner to the line, lost 2nd concluding stages.
Pushed along, moved to the lead 1150M them led them slowly, headed inside 250M, battled on to hold 4th.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, bustled along to sit outside leader in a slowly run race, fought on well early straight, run ended 150M and faded towards the finish.
Dropped back from a wide draw, travelled keenly at the back 5Ls off the slow pace, made his move 700M looping the field, lacked the finishing kick but kept on steadily to the line.
In midfield along the fence, raced keenly 800M due to slackening pace, 3Ls off leader turning in, tried but couldn't get closer to leaders in the run home.
Taken back to the rear, not helped by slackening pace middle stages and raced keenly, switched wide 650M, unable to give a kick when let down on straightening, not reached contention.
Settled down in 5th 2-3Ls off leaders, hampered by the slackening pace middle stages, kept on same pace in straight couldn't get closer to main rivals.
Towards the rear, inconvenienced by slackening pace middle stages and shuffled back to last on the turn, had to pull widest for clear run in straight, couldn't lift.
No closer than 3-wide in mid-division, couldn't lift after a tough run, weakened away 250M.
Held up near the rear along the 2-path, raced keenly middle stages when pace slackened, ridden 400M and no response, soon out of contention. (Blood in trachea.)
Bumped and unbalanced start, pressed forward to race one-out 3L from leader. Shifted out turn to get clear running, finished strongly to hit the front 200m, holding off late challenge.
Began OK but tended to over-race, settling one-out behind midfield. Held up in traffic top of straight, got clear 300m, finished strongly.
No early pace, racing along fence towards rear. Stayed on fence around home turn, got clear running from 300m, finished strongly final 100m.
Hard ridden too hold fence in midfield. Stayed on fence around turn and in straight, making ground steadily to finish behind place-getters.
Hampered start, pushed forward from an outside draw to race one-back, one-out. Loomed as a chance 250m but only one-paced close home.
Hampered start, dropping to last pair but away from fence. Last into straight, switched wide, ran on fairly.
Hit stall on jumping, losing ground, dropping to last pair. Switched wide entering straight and ran on fairly.
Hard ridden to hold narrow lead along fence before pulling clear 1050m. Kept steady pace to 200m when emptied and faded.
Hampered start, pushed forward to midfield but held 3-wide. Bumped 500m and taken wider, made up some ground early in straight before running out of puff 200m.
Hard ridden early to hold box seat 2L from leader. Blocked for run early straight, but only one-paced when clear final stages.
No pace, racing 3-wide behind midfield mostly. Made up some ground early in straight but wide before tiring 200m and fading.
Hard ridden from widest draw, racing wide until settling outside hind-quarters of leader passing 1050m. Felt the pinch at turn-in and gave ground steadily in straight.
Early leader before being crossed at 1000m.Loomed up to lead at top of the straight. Only worked on him from 250m, where he pulled away and won easily under hands and heels late.
Began well before electing to drop back and sit midfield. Clear run in the straight and ran strongly. Grabbed 2nd in the last 25m, but no hope of catching the winner.
Pushed forward early to be early 2nd. Came off heels and lost some ground at 1100m, then stuck 3wd. Well placed on turn, and ran into 2nd from 200m. Starting to run out of puff late.
Pushed forward from the wide draw to eventually lead passing 1100m. Stayed on well in the straight, before peaking in the last 100m and losing a place.
Bumped and unbalanced on jumping, and dropped back to settle worse than midfield. Stayed on well in the straight but ran into a cul-de-sac late, and not tested in the last 50m.
Dropped back early from the wide draw to sit worse than midfield, 3 wide with cover. Wider on the turn. Stayed on solidly in the straight, without ever threatening.
Dropped back from the wide draw to be a clear last. Came widest on the turn and battled away solidly in the straight.
Eased forward early to be forward of midfield. Struggled for a clear run early in the straight, and ran flat when clear.
Dropped back early from the outside draw to sit at the rear of the field. Stayed close to the rail in the straight and plugged away to the line.
Bumped on jumping and eased back early to sit worse than midfield. No clear run early in the straight, and had to switch off heels at 200m. Only stayed on fairly late.
Bumped on jumping and eased forward but was stuck around midfield, 4 wide with no cover. Didn't have a lot left in the tank in the straight and was eased out late.
Eased across early to settle midfield, 1 off the fence. Never kicked under pressure in the straight and was eased late.
Bumped and badly unbalanced on jumping and initially got back before pushing forward to settle midfield at 1200m. No run early in the straight, but gave nothing when clear and eased late.
Pressed forward early to be handily placed 3rd/4th on the fence. Gave nothing in the straight.

Began from a wide gate, improved steadily before settled just outside the leader in sedate pace, quickened passing 500M to keep fast-approaching eventual 2nd from hitting the front, kicked 2L clear 200M out, just held on to the line.

Tight early before settled in midfield, made rapid progress through the pedestrian-paced field to eyeball the leader briefly coming onto home bend, fought on under pressure from 1L back into the straight to fail narrowly.

Settled towards the rear, steadied in slow pace early in back straight, let down to make rapid progress leaving the Rock to be 4th rounding home bend and into the straight, continued to make ground to be nearest at finish.
Broke well, settled in midfield or slightly better in 5th or 6th far side, shuffled backward coming onto home bend, fought on steadily in the straight without threatening.
Prominent from a difficult draw, crossed to the rail in front passing the 1200 metres setting a sedate pace far side, headed on top of home bend and swamped after straightening.
Ridden to be close up early, restrained to one back in 2L 4th coming onto stables bend, left flat-footed rounding the home bend, inconvenienced after straightening and failed to quicken when asked.

Settled just better than midfield on the rail, shuffled backward coming onto home bend, re-gained positon about 2L off the pace turning into home straight, kept on same pace under pressure in the run to the line.
Soon taken back to the rail from a wide gate, commenced move rounding home bend and wide into the straight, produced good late impression nearing the finish.
Held up just behind the pace, shuffled back from 3rd off the Rock to 2 back into home straight, found nothing under pressure.
Began well, settled in rear of midfield on the rail, shuffled further back coming onto home bend, produced good late impression past well-beaten horses.
Broke well from a wide gate, settled towards the rear, made short-lived effort passing the 600 metres to reach midfield on top of home bend, soon weakened.
Never seen with a chance.
Settled in box seat, pace good, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Eased to sit just off the leaders, 2-3 wide, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
At back along the fence, pace good, made steady ground 250M for 3rd.
Midfield, pace good, progressed steadily 300M.
Very slow away, pushed to obtain midfield spot along the fence, pace good, flattened 200M.
Pushed early, 2-3 wide in midfield, pace good, just held ground.
Behind midfield, 2 wide, pace good, ran on ok in straight.
Pushed to take rail and led at good pace, emptied 250M.
Eased at start, trapped 3 wide throughout, pace good, ran on fairly.
Eased to rear for cover, 2 wide, pace good, no turn of foot.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, pace good, no progress.
Hard ridden forward, pace good, hung out around the bend, hung in severely in straight whilst weakening.
Moderate start, raced behind midfield on rail, near 1100M checked away from heels, commenced to improve approaching 600M, quickened passing 100M, finished strongly to score.
Jumped well and settled behind leaders, ridden along to keep position passing 1000M then improved to lead passing 600M, travelled strongly on rail in the straight, just missed by nose.
Taken back at start, always stayed at tail until commenced to improve near 500M, fought well in the straight and came home solidly.
Settled behind midfield on rail, moved out to one off near 1000M, improved approaching 500M, widest on straightening, made up some nice late ground, finished nicely.
Raced midfield on rail, moved out to one off near 1000M, improved near 600M, batted hard entire straight, worked home nicely.
Gradually moved forward to settle outside the leader near 1500M, drifted back passing 600M, asked for effort approaching 400M, passing 100M checked away from heels, finished fairly.
Slow to begin, settled midfield, mid race moved forward near 1000M then ridden along to race outside the leader approaching 600M, kept asking for effort after but just one-paced in the straight.
Ridden to take box seat, gave ground passing 800M, limited response at Home Turn, failed to run on.
Fast out then settled behind leaders, tried to improve near 500M, weakened passing 150M, failed to run on.
Settled behind midfield, no response throughout the race.

Approaching 1800M checked away from heels when travelled keenly, settled midfield, mid race moved to take lead passing 1000M, asked for effort near 700M but gradually gave ground, tiring badly in the early straight, must trial.
Jumped OK and took lead, drifted back passing 1000M, faded out quickly after entering the straight, must trial.
Slow into stride, taken in for cover, settling midfield. Switched out turning for home, bumped several times passing 200m before picking up momentum and surging ahead to win close home.
Enjoyed a lovely trail on the back of the speed to straight. Loomed alongside leader passing 100m but run down close home.
Hard ridden along rail to take lead passing 950m. Kicked ahead on straightening but under pressure final 100m and swamped close home.
Raced mostly in midfield but away from rail. Swung wide entering straight, bumped several times while making ground 200m, kept on gamely to line.
Bumped start, not pushed, settling along rail behind midfield. Took closer order turning for home, kept on well in straight before turning one-paced final stages.
Outpaced, racing towards rear but away from fence. Taken wide in straight and ran on fairly.
Shifted in for cover soon after start, dropping to rear along rail. Stayed on rail around turn, switched out 300m to make run but only one-paced.
Hard ridden to obtain forward position but trapped wide without cover 2L from leader. Covered extra ground turn, kept on gamely to 200m before tiring.
Shifted across behind runners soon after start and last on settling. Became detached from field around turn before making up late ground.
Away well, pressed forward, racing one-out 3L from leader. Stayed in chasing pack to 200m before shortening stride.
Away well, sharing early lead before racing outside leader approaching and around turn. Kept on well to 200m before giving ground abruptly. Unacceptable performance.
Bumped start, pushed forward, settling midfield but wide. Came under pressure passing 600m, losing ground steadily. Finished tailed out.
Jumped well, sent forward to race in 2nd, easy run throughout, closed off well to score comfortably.
Bumped start and hampered early, raced 2 wide in midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back, improved from near 400M, made good progress in straight to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Began well from a tricky draw, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3 lengths on turn, kept on well early in straight, headed near final 100M, just stayed on for a place. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, hampered near 1150M, positioned 4 to 5 lengths back on rail, same position on turn, finished off evenly to make frame without threatening.
Average to begin, positioned on rail, 6 to 7 lengths back, there to turn, angled out near 350M, finished off evenly.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide behind midfield, same 9 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Bumped start, recovered to race 2 wide in 3rd, 5 lengths or so back on turn, peaked early in straight and weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide without cover at rear, 10 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide at rear, 9 lengths back on turn, one-paced in straight. (Blood in trachea.)
Bumped start, raced 10 lengths back at rear, still well back on turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Crowded on jumping, raced at tail throughout, never looked likely.
Crowded out start, positioned on rail at rear, peaked on turn, weakened in straight, finished last.
Travelled in front of midfield, 2-1/2L behind 2 wide, maintained in neck-a-neck duel to the line to score by 1/2L.
Raced in the one-off one-back, sat about 1L off the lead, pushed the winner all the way to the line, missed by 1/2L.
Bumped start, settled to race in midfield, 4L behind 2 wide, kept on fairly well to the line to take 3rd.
Crowded after the start, in behind midfield, 6-1/4L behind 2 wide, made good ground and finished well to the line.
Hampered after the start, settled in about midfield, 5-1/4L behind 2 wide, swung wide and ran on only one paced.
Ridden to take the rail and led by about 1L, found no extra and headed passing 150M.
Pushed forward, trapped wide at 1000M turn, improved to sit outside the lead, sat 1-1/4L off, flattened at 150M. (To trial for barrier manner)
Taken back and raced at the rear, 9L behind 2 wide, made ground and ran on fairly to the line.
Niggled along and raced in front of midfield, 2-3/4L off, shifted to the rail on straightening, held up from 200M to 100M, closed off fairly. (Rider warned for choice of running)
Hampered after the start, settled in behind midfield, 6-1/2L behind along the rail, made slight ground only.
Taken back and raced near the tail, 7-3/4L behind along the rail, did not improve.

Placing: PU
Comment: Went amiss after 1000M, retired from the race.
Jumped well, pushed forward, taking lead 1100m and crossing to fence. Kicked ahead on straightening and kept on strongly to line.
Quickly into stride, shared lead before slipping into box seat 1100m. Came off fence to challenge 300m but unable catch leader.
Away nicely and soon in ideal spot one-back, one-out. Swung wide entering straight and boxed on gamely to line.
Made use of inside draw to hold rail 3L from leader. Stayed on rail around turn and in straight, kept on well without threatening.
Raced mostly in midfield, one away from fence. Stoked up turning for home but only one-paced in straight.
Settled towards rear along rail and allowed to travel at own speed. Took inside run in straight but only one-paced.
Steadied soon after start and shifted in for cover, dropping to last. Looked well beaten entering straight though made up some ground between horses closing stages,
Began fairly, dropping towards rear along rail. Stayed well back to straight before running past beaten rivals.
Hard ridden to go forward but unable find cover and held wide in midfield. Over-raced badly approaching turn and lost position. Faded in straight. Had substantial amount of blood in trachea.
Steadied soon after start and taken in for cover, settling one-out behind midfield, swung very wide entering straight but only one-paced.
Pressed forward from wide draw to race outside hind-quarters of leader. Under pressure soon after straightening and faded.
Ridden early to hold midfield position. Lost ground around home turn, dropping to last soon after straightening.
Prominent from the start, chased leaders along the 2-path as they settled, raced on strongly turning in, led 150M and dug deep to hold on.
Settled down behind midfield, held position along the rail, switched out 250M and laid down a strong challenge, held by a diminishing half length.
Settled down in 5th 3Ls off the pace in mid-stages, had a ground saving run along the fence, battled on steadily inside 300M, held by winner final 150M, lost 2nd late.
Held up towards the rear early stages, took closer order back-straight, driven wide into straight, made steady headway in the run home, was nearest at the finish and just missed 3rd.
Moved up gradually to race outside leader 1200M, remained in same position to straight, took over inside 300M, fought hard but couldn't fend off pursuers final 150M.
Reserved in a 2-wide spot behind midfield 6Ls off the slow pace, 10th at 400M, stayed on well down the outside.
Jumped well to take early lead, sat behind leaders near 1200M, loomed a threat 300M out, chased hard but held ground over final 150M.
Reserved in a 2nd last, 7Ls off the pace making the turn for home, hit the line well but left with too much to do.
Couldn't get closer than 3-wide in mid-division, no cover for majority of race, kept on same pace in the straight without threatening the front runners.
Switched off after jumping from 12, always at rear, 9Ls to make up 400M, made some progress to the line but never threatened.(Jockey questioned re his riding.)
Held up 2-wide in mid-division, couldn't make any headway inside 300M, never looked to threaten.
Sent forward, crossed to lead passing 1300M, led them along slowly, couldn't kick on turning in, brushed the running rail 200M and unbalanced, dropped away.

Hard ridden early, travelled handily in 3rd, hit the front under pressure over 300 metres out, held on to the line.
Ridden along in midfield racing wide throughout, commenced move home bend, quickened well inside the final 300 metres despite rider lost whip, just failed to get up on line.
Broke well from the widest gate, settled wide in last few, made significant progress in straight.
Ridden along early stages, settled about 3L off the speed, lost position coming onto home bend, renewed effort entering home straight but unable to sustain run close to home.
Moderate start and slow to muster, settled in rear of midfield on the rail, gained closer rounding home bend, kept on same pace without quickening from 2L back into straight.
Broke well from a wide gate, settled towards the rear on the rail, finished off the race nicely.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, trailed the field to the straight, made steady progress near the centre of the straight. (Jockey warned for poor start execution)

Began very awkwardly losing ground, soon recovered to rear of midfield before hampered and lost position again coming onto home bend, given reminders approaching home turn, kept on steadily without threatening.
Jumped well, ridden along handily, joined the leader coming onto home bend, folded up quickly after straightening.
Ridden positively from a wide gate, obtained rails run after the first 250 metres, led or shared lead to the 300 metres and weakened under pressure.

Ridden at the start, niggled along in forward of midfield on the rail, became 4th some 3L back coming onto home bend and on heels of the leader turning in, no day light the length of the straight and not tested.
Settled at the back from a wide gate, given reminders on the bend, never seen with a chance.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide just off the leaders, not suited by the fast pace, closed off strongly to score on debut.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, suited by the fast pace, made steady ground 400M for 2nd.
Hard ridden early, behind midfield on the rails, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 400M for 3rd.
Blundered badly at start, pushed to keep up in midfield along the fence, made steady ground 250M.
Pushed to hold the rail in front of midfield, not suited by the fast pace, ran on fairly in straight.
Hard ridden early but failed to muster, trapped wide at rear, severely hampered round the home turn when being taken out to 6-7 wide, ran on well in straight.
Hard ridden to hold the rail, shared the lead at fast sectionals, ran on until 200M weakened.
At back, 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast pace, no progress.
At rear, benefited by the fast tempo, never improved.
Pushed forward, shared the lead at fast sectionals, out of fuel 250M.
Hard ridden forward, hung out badly at home turns, flattened in straight.
Pushed early but failed to muster, trapped 4 wide in midfield, badly hampered round the home bend, emptied in straight.
Fast out and take lead without asking for much effort, kept improving on the rail in the straight, finished strongly to score.
Began well and ridden along to settle outside the lead, fought hard entire straight, worked home solidly, just missed by head.
Settled box seat, in the early part of straight had difficulty obtaining clear running, from approaching 100M to 50M held up for run, not fully tested.
Ridden after start, settled in front of midfield, always niggling, commenced to improve at Home Turn, kept on to the line.
Settled midfield, asked for effort at Home Turn, battled hard in the straight, worked home well. Next day lame left front.
Travelled behind midfield, approaching 1200M was steadied away from heels, limited response in the straight, finished fairly.
Raced midfield, tried to improve at Home Turn, one-paced in the straight.
Settled outside the leaders, throughout race travelled wide and without cover, under pressure and gradually gave ground in the straight.
Travelled at tail on rail, kept on rail at Home Turn to save ground, one-pace in the straight.
Began only fairly, raced midfield on rail, one-paced.
Settled behind midfield on rail, no response in the straight, failed to run on.
Raced at tail, widest on straightening, no response in the straight, failed to run on.
Taken back at start, no response in the straight.
Throughout race travelled wide and without cover, faded out after 300M.
Hard ridden from outside gate to settle one-out, one-back at first turn. Not asked for effort until turn-in, surged forward to hit front 180m, pulled clear.
Hard ridden to lead soon after the start, crossing to fence 1500m. Travelled comfortably to straight, kept on well despite being overtaken 180m.
Ridden to hold forward position, settling one-out 3L from leader. Boxed on gamely in straight to grab minor placing.
Taken in shortly after start, settling one-out behind midfield. Travelled keenly approaching home turn, swung very wide into straight, finished off nicely.
Jumped well, stayed with early pace, then taken to fence at first turn 3L from leader. Switched out at turn-in to make challenge and kept on fairly.
Shifted across behind horses shortly after start but still held 3-wide towards the rear. Swung wide into straight and ran on fairly.
No early pace, racing along fence towards rear. Remained on fence around home turn and ran on fairly in straight.
Ridden early to get forward position but held 3-wide first turn, dropping to midfield. Kept 3-wide back stretch, swung wide into straight, boxed on one-paced.
Ridden early to find cover but held 3-wide in midfield. Remained 3-wide to straight, finishing off one-paced.
Shifted across behind horses from outside draw, dropping to last pair. Stayed well back to straight before running past tired rivals.
Hard ridden from widest gate to get forward position, eventually crossing in to race outside hindquarters of leader at first turn. Tracked leader to straight when ran out of stamina and faded.
Quickly away, pressed forward before settling in box seat at first turn. Came under pressure and given reminders home turn but found nothing and faded.
Began awkwardly, bumped and then lost balance, dropping to rear along fence. Stayed at rear thereafter and never in contention.
Shifted in soon after start but held wide at first turn and allowed to improve 4-wide from 1100m, getting to fourth around home turn before running out of steam and dropping back.
Jumped well, sent forward to race outside the lead, travelled well throughout, kept on well after straightening, took the lead near 200M, scored by 3/4L.
Began well, positioned 2 to 3 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, made very good progress in straight to get 2nd.
Began well from a wide draw, unable to slot in early, travelled 3 wide with no cover in 3rd, same position on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from barrier 11, failed to muster speed, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, improved from near 450M, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly, just missed frame, useful debut. (Lame left front leg.)
Began fairly from the widest draw, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths or so back at rear, improved from near 450M, taken widest in straight and made good progress to be nearest on line.
Taken back to race at tail, 6 to 7 lengths back, improved from near 500M, finished off very strongly, nearest on line.
Out in line, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off one-paced.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide, 3 to 4 lengths back, same position on turn, finished off one-paced.
Awkwardly away, recovered and took the lead, travelled well on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked near 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight, eased in the final stages.
Moderately away from a tricky draw, bumped near 1150M, taken back to race at rear, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, emptied early in straight, finished last.
Pushed forward to take the rail and led by about 1/2L, kept on gamely to the line and held off late challenge to score.
In the one-off one-back position 2-1/4L off, kept on solidly and pushed winner to the line, missed by a short-head.
Rolled forward and raced in the box-seat, sat 1-1/2L off, fought on well to the line to take 3rd.
Sent forward, sat in front of midfield along the rail 3-1/4L off, away from rail after 600M, exited turn wide, ran on fairly.
Ridden and raced just in front of midfield, 3-1/4L behind 2 wide, remained one paced to the line.
Pushed forward to sit outside the lead about 1/2L off, showed no turn of foot, one paced mostly.
Travelled towards the tail, 6L behind the lead 3 wide with cover, improved steadily to the line.
Bumped start, raced towards the rear end, 6-1/4L behind 2 wide, kept on one paced to the line.
Eased after the start, left wide and without cover in about midfield 4-1/2L behind, swung widest and one paced.
Eased and then raced at the rear, 8L behind the lead 3 wide with cover, did not save ground.
Bumped start, in behind midfield, 4-3/4L behind 2 wide, showed no response and went backward. (Blood in trachea)
Hard ridden after the start, settled to race in worse than midfield, 4-3/4L behind along the rail, found nothing.
Jumped well, sat outside early leader to 400m before taking over and pulling clear under hands and heels riding.
Away OK, taken to outer fence 3L from leader. Stoked up approaching 400m and ran on steadily to grab 2nd spot.
Jumped well, shifted out, settling 2L from leader. Made forward move 400m to look a chance but no match for first two.
Outpaced, racing towards rear along outer fence. Remained well back to 400m before picking up bit and finishing nicely.
Ridden early to stay with pace, settling 3L from leader. Kept on gamely final 400m without looking dangerous.
Began well, sharing early pace while shifting towards outer fence. Shaken up passing 400m and kept on fairly.
Settled behind midfield away from outer rail. Tried to improve approaching 400m but only one-paced.
Slow to move, then held in centre track towards rear. Under the pump from 500m and kept on fairly.
Slow into stride, dropping to last along outer fence. Never in the hunt though ran past tired rivals close home.
Raced mostly towards rear well away from outer fence. Never likely.
Showed some speed to hold midfield position along outer fence to 300m before tiring.
Broke well, surged to the front, one-away from outer fence. Overtaken passing 400m and faded.
Bumped start, pressed forward, settling two-away from outer fence 2L from leader. Under pressure approaching 400m and faded.
No pace, racing mostly towards rear. Hard ridden from 400m but failed to respond and eased down concluding stages.
Close up to leaders early stages, shuffled back to midfield back straight, travelled well into straight, kept coming to vie for lead inside 200M, got the upper hand near line.
Dropped back to be 4Ls off the pace middle stages, niggled along from 650M to be just over 2Ls off the pace leaving the bend, ran on well battling for the lead inside 200M, just denied at the finish.
Dropped back from wide gate, settled in last 6Ls off the pace, commenced his run passing 500M, closed off fastest down outside lane making good late impression on first two.
Led early, sat behind leaders passing 1300M, well placed to strike turning in, had every chance but got out-finished final 200M.

Jumped away fairly, bustled along to take lead 1400M, sat just off the pace middle stages before regaining the lead near top of straight, couldn't fend off pursuers 250M, faded towards the line. (Blood in trachea.)
Caught very wide first turn from barrier 12, settled towards the rear 5Ls off the pace middle stages, got too far back raced on only fairly in straight, no impression on leaders.
From draw 10 caught racing wide without cover throughout the trip, strode closer to leaders passing 1200M, didn't run on entering straight, weakened over final 150M.
Bustled along after the jump to hold a rail position fore of midfield, couldn't accelerate on straightening, kept on same pace to line.
Not hurried early stages, towards the rear and no closer than 3-wide for majority of the race, 5Ls to make up 400M, never able to pick up. Weak run home. (Substantial blood on scope / Lame next day.)
Chased leaders, travelled keenly 1200M and pulled its way forward to lead them from 1100M, pressed by rival 500M, gave a brief fight early straight then gave way 300M.
Crowded for room after the jump, guided to the fence to be 5Ls off the pace towards the rear, didn't pick up under pressure, eased when no chance 200M.
Began only fairly, raced in 2nd last 5-6Ls behind leader, failed to finish off when placed under pressure passing 500M, never a factor.

Took charge of its rider 1400M, shifted out to a 4-wide position approaching entrance of back straight, swung widest home turn but already a spent force leaving the bend, tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Hard ridden forward early stages but unable to get closer to the fence, taken wider by rival to be very wide without cover down the back-straight, gave ground 500M, eased when already beaten.
Outpaced early, racing one-out at rear. Taken to centre track on straightening and finished powerfully to win on the line.
Hard ridden to hold forward position, racing wide without cover 1L from leader. Rolled forward on straightening, hit front 200m, run down on line.
Steadied soon after start and taken in for cover, settling close to fence towards rear. Made up some ground home turn, took run between horses in straight, finished strongly.
First out but restrained, dropping to behind midfield one-away from fence. Stoked up turning for home and ran on steadily in straight.
Hard ridden to lead on settling, crossing to fence and setting good pace. Overtaken passing 200m but battled on well until swamped close home.
Jumped OK, ridden to hold forward position one-out 3L from leader. Put under pressure on straightening but only one-paced. (Rider dropped right rein early straight)
Steadied on jumping and taken in for cover, dropping to last. Remained at the rear until straight before running on steadily.
Raced mostly at midfield along rail. Shaken up at turn-in but only one-paced.
Pressed forward from an outside draw to race outside leader on settling. Stayed in contention to 200m before running out of stamina and fading.
Hard ridden from widest draw to go forward, racing 3-wide before settling 3L from leader. Lost position turning for home and weakened badly in straight.
Broke well, pushed forward to hold box seat. Trailed leader to straight when failed to respond to hard riding and faded.
Bumped and unbalanced start, pushed forward to get within 4L of leader before tiring home turn and dropping back. Finished tailed out. (Unacceptable performance. Lame right front leg).
Began very awkwardly, became unbalanced and dropped back to the rear of the field. Still last at the 250m, and showed an enormous turn of foot to accelerate home and win in the shadows of the post.

Allowed to go forward early to be well placed 4th. Badly held up on heels until a run opened up at 300m. Stayed on strongly and led at 100m. Was pulling away from the field, but caught by a huge run on the line.

Fairly away and cruised forward to settle just behind midfield. Came wider on the turn and stayed on solidly in the straight. Well positioned late, but peaked towards the end of the run and lucky to hold 3rd.
Slow away and then pushed forward to settle midfield. No clear run until 300m, and took time to get momentum going. Strong run late was rapidly gaining on 3rd.
Pushed forward from the wide draw to have an early share of the lead. Still in front at 150, but ran out of puff from there and was swamped late.
Dropped back early for the wide draw to sit at the rear of the field. Plugged away early in the straight, before kicking in the last 150m and was staying on well late.
Eased forward early to settle forward of midfield. Struggled for a run in the straight, only clear in the last 50m and not fully tested.
Fairly away and eased into stride to sit towards the rear of the field. Boxed in for most of the straight, and was never fully tested in the run to the line.
Cruised forward to settle around midfield. Awkward on heels 900m. Never got clear until it was too late, and went to the line with a lap full of horse.
Eased across to eventually settle worse than midfield. Bumped and awkward on heels 900m. Clear from 300m, but only plugged away fairly and wasn't pushed hard late.
Pushed forward early to lead. Had nothing left in the straight and dropped out from the 250m.
Crowded on jumping, but recovered to push forward and be handily placed 3rd, 3 wide with no cover. Nothing left in the tank late and dropped out quickly from the 200m.
Cruised forward to settle around midfield, 3 wide with limited cover. Didn't respond to pressure in the straight, and dropped out quickly from the 200m. Jockey questioned.
Struggled for a position early and was stuck 3-4 wide without cover, around midfield. Gave nothing in the straight and eased from the 200m.

Broke well, settled in midfield on the rail, angled out to challenge upon straightening, quickened under pressure to assert authority inside the final 100 metres.
Broke well, settled about 2L off the pace on the rail, quickened upon straightening to hit the front briefly over 100 metres out, hung on well for 2nd placing.
Moderate start, settled well behind, made significant progress down the centre of the straight.
Began from a wide gate, settled towards the rear on the rail, saved ground turning in, ran on steadily without threatening.
Settled towards the rear, commenced move around home bend and switched widest into the straight, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Soon ridden to the fore, ceded lead to settle just off the pace on the rail, tracked the leader throughout back straight and around the bend, unable to sustain effort after straightening.
Slightly slowly away and settled at the back along the rail, made modest progress in the straight.
Soon took up running and attempted to make all, folded up quickly inside the final 200 metres.
Broke well from a wide gate, settled in a prominent position without cover, yielded ground from rounding home bend.
Slightly slow out, quickly recovered to midfield, gave ground under pressure from rounding home bend.
Jumped well, settled just better than midfield, bumped early in straight and weakened out of contention.
Slow start off a wide draw, settled wide without cover in forward of midfield, came under pressure rounding home bend, soon faded in straight.
Pushed to occupy box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, kicked strongly 200M to score with some in hands.
Pushed to take rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on well until 150M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Checked at start, eased back, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, lack room in straight, dashed strongly to the line.
Trapped 3 wide throughout in midfield, harmed by the slow pace, dashed strongly despite not suited by the racing situations.
Pushed early but not muster, sat midfield 2 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, lack room 4-2, dashed well.
Eased at start, 2-3 wide, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Midfield, along the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Pushed forward, sat outside the leader, suited by the slow tempo, weakened 250M.
Eased at start, raced 3-4 wide at rear, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 300M, run ended 100M.
Pushed forward, trapped 3 wide, emptied 250M.
At back along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, no dash.
Eased to sit just off the speed, 2 wide, over-raced badly from 700M, no progress.
Began well, settled midfield, improved approaching 400M, issued a challenge after 100M, finished off strongly to score.
Began only fairly, settled midfield on rail, improved on rail to save ground at Home Turn, worked to the line strongly, just missed by SH.
Fast out and urged along to take lead, battled hard entire straight, finished solidly.
Settled box seat, commenced to improve passing 350M, travelled well and came home nicely.
Ridden to settle outside the leader, asked for effort passing 400M, finished well.
Shortly after start steadied away from heels, settled behind midfield on rail, made up some nice late ground, worked home well.
Urged along to settle behind leaders, tried to improve at Home Turn, limited response in the straight, failed to make impression, blood trachea.
Travelled wide and without cover at handy position, passing 200M gave ground under pressure.
Taken back at start, ran on in the straight and finished fairly.
Taken back at start, drifted to the last passing 650M, remained fairly to the line.
Taken back and settled behind midfield, widest on straightening, no response in the straight.
Always back in the race, never in it.
Jumped well, raced one-out in midfield 3L from leader. Not asked for effort until straightening when taken to centre field and finished strongly to win close home.
Used inside draw to grab box seat on settling. Kept tabs on leader to straight, took split between horses 200m when looked the winner but run down on line.
Crowded out at start, taken to rail and settled 3L from leader. Came off fence at turn-in, ran into traffic near 200m before surging forward to grab minor placing.
Raced in midfield along fence 5L from leader. Caught in traffic near turn-in and forced to shift in 300m to get clear running. Finished off nicely.
Hard ridden from jump to get forward position but failed to muster. Shifted in for cover, grabbing rail towards rear. Shifted out in straight for clear running and finished off well.
Restrained on jumping and shifted across behind horses, dropping one-out towards rear. Swung wide entering straight and ran on well while shifting out under pressure.
Shifted across behind horses from wide draw, dropping to rear. Clear last turning for home, took inside run in straight, making good ground final 200m.
Ridden to hold one-out position behind midfield. Swung wide entering straight and ran on fairly.
Jumped awkwardly, losing ground, shifted in to rail, dropping to last. Made up some ground approaching home turn, boxed on fairly in straight.
Quickly in front, setting soft pace. Put under pressure passing 400m, battled on gamely to 150m when flattened.
Pushed forward to race one-out, 1L from leader. Moved up to share lead at turn-in, kept on gamely to 150m before tiring.
Had the run of the race one-out, one-back. Stayed in contention to 200m before giving ground abruptly. Had substantial amount of blood in trachea.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take race prominently, took the lead near 650M, kicked clear after turning in and scored by a length.
Unbalanced start, positioned 2 wide in 4th, 2 lengths or so back on turn, finished off well to get 2nd.
Bumped start, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place.
Bumped start, unable to slot in, travelled 3 wide with no cover throughout, 4 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Taken back from the widest draw, 7 lengths back on turn, finished off very strongly to be nearest on line.
Moderately away from a tricky draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back on turn, taken widest in straight and made some progress.
Bumped start and lost ground, positioned 3 lengths or so back on rail, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, finished off one-paced.
Hampered start, positioned 4 to 5 lengths back on rail, there to turn, one-paced in straight, bumped and unbalanced in the final stages.
Taken back to race at rear, positioned 5 to 6 lengths back on rail, kept to inside after turning in and finished off evenly.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back, checked away from heels near 500M, made no progress after turning in, bumped and unbalanced in the final stages.

Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2nd on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (Jockey reported that the horse did not stride out comfortably throughout the race.)
Sent forward, sat 1/2L off and outside the lead, kept on going and held on to win by a short-head.
Raced in the box-seat, sat 1-1/2L off, held up until passing 200M, finished strongly only missed by a short-head.
Settled to race in midfield, 3L behind along the rail, kept up and finished off nicely for 3rd.
Raced in the one-off one-back position, sat 1-3/4L off the lead, battled on to the line to take 4th.
Niggled along, raced just in front of midfield, 3L off the lead 2 to 3 wide, kept on one paced to the line.
Settled to race in behind midfield, about 5L behind 3 wide with cover, made ground and ran on well to the line.
Raced towards the rear end, 6-1/2L behind 2 wide, continued to make ground until held up in the final stages.
Sent forward to take the rail and led by about 1/2L, weakened and headed passing 150M.
Travelled in about midfield, 4-1/2L behind 2 wide, swung wide and kept on until flattened late.
Taken back and raced towards the rear, 6-3/4L behind 3 wide with cover, ran on to the finish.
Jumped fairly only, settled to race in behind midfield, 4-1/2L behind along the rail, kept on going to the line.
Always at the rear, never a factor.
Away OK, ridden forward, settling one-out 3L from leader. Shaken up turning for home, ran on strongly, pulling clear final stages.
Jumped well, pushed forward to lead into first turn. Under attack turning for home but kept finding until run down final 50m.
No early pace, racing between horses towards rear. Switched out for clear running home turn, finished strongly down centre track to grab minor placing.
Pressed forward from an outside draw to sit one-out 1L behind leader. Urged forward on straightening to look a chance 200m before tiring final strides.
Pressed forward from widest draw to settling one-out, one-back at first turn. Stoked up turning for home but only one-paced in straight.
Shifted in soon after start, grabbing box seat. Kept tabs to 200m before turning one-paced.
Not pushed early, racing behind midfield along rail. Switched out in straight to make challenge but only one-paced.
Outpaced, racing towards rear away from fence. Shaken up at turn-in but only one-paced.
Began fairly, then crowded, losing ground. Remained at rear thereafter before making ground final 200m.
Outpaced, racing along rail behind midfield. Lost position back stretch, stayed on rail in straight but failed to respond to hard riding.
Hard ridden on jumping but failed to respond and held wide at rear. Moved forward from 800m to get within 3L of leader passing 500m before run ended.
Jumped well, ridden to hold forward position settling along rail 4L from leader. Under pressure turning for home and gave ground gradually.
Tracked leaders in 4th and travelled comfortably to straight, took over 250M and opened up a decisive lead, dug deep to hold on from challengers late.
Towards the rear, just over 8Ls off the pace in early and middle stages, unleashed a strong run passing 200M and closing on the winner with every stride, held by diminishing neck.
Not hurried early stages, held up behind midfield, ran on well from 350M, nearest finish.
Taken back from wide barrier, settled down behind midfield 6-7Ls off leader, pushed along nearing 400M, stayed on well, had to be steadied off heels when making ground final stages.
Reserved in mid-division 5Ls off the pace early stages, niggled along 550M to chase leaders, kept grinding to the line but others finished better.
From draw 9 shifted across behind runners for cover, settled down 2nd last 8Ls behind leader, swung widest home, stayed on without seriously threatening.
Tracked leader 2-wide, vied for the lead passing 700M, briefly led inside 300M, outsprinted by rivals final 150M.
Began awkwardly, shifted across behind runners to be last on settling 10Ls off the pace, saved ground inside but stuck on only fairly final 300M passing tired horses.
Went forward from draw 12, slotted in to race in 5th 3Ls off the pace, moved up to press leaders from 800M, couldn't sustain run inside 250M, faded towards the line.
Jumped well from inside draw to be 3rd tracking the steady pace, came under pressure 600M and hard ridden to hold his position, no extra mid-straight.
Led from 1300M, had uncontested lead to 700M then taken on by rivals, run ended and gave way 200M out.
Caught wide no cover from draw 11, ridden along to obtain a more forward position to find cover but unable to do so, remained wide to turn, gave ground from 500M, tailed out .(Lame RF leg.)
Pressed forward from an outside draw to set up a 2L lead by first turn before slowing pace back stretch. Kicked ahead on straightening and kept finding under pressure for solid win.
Ridden to get forward position, settling one-out, one-back. Got sandwiched between horses turning for home, picked up momentum from 300m, finished strongly.
Ridden to hold forward position, settling along rail 3L from leader. Stayed on rail in straight and finished strongly to grab minor placing.
Away well, settling one-out 2L from leader. Took closer order turning for home, threw out strong challenge in straight but unable close gap.
Allowed to stride at own pace early, settling one-out behind midfield. Made forward move approaching home turn, turned wide, kept on gamely in straight without threatening.
Raced mostly in midfield, one away from rail. Took inside run in straight, finishing off nicely between horses.
Broke well, grabbed box seat and tracked leader. Stayed on rail in straight and boxed on gamely until swamped close home.
Shifted across behind horses soon after start, settling towards rear. Made forward move back stretch, passing a couple of horses but kept wide. One-paced in straight.
Snagged back soon after start and taken in for cover, dropping to last. Remained at rear to straight before running past beaten rivals.
Jumped OK, ridden along but held wide without cover behind midfield. Allowed to stride forward back stretch, getting to within 2L of leader at turn in. One-paced in straight.
Crowded for room shortly after start, losing ground and dropping to rear. Remained at rear throughout and never likely.
Pressed forward, settling along rail 4L from leader. Got shuffled back turning into back stretch. Under pressure to hold position from 500m but failed to respond and faded.

Broke well from a wide gate, wide in forward of midfield early, improved to 2L 3rd 3-wide rounding home bend, sustained effort to hit the front inside the 300 metres, just held on to the line.
Given reminders early settling wide behind midfield, made headway on the outside around home bend, ran on steadily to just fail to get up on line.
Prominent early, settled wide in midfield, ran on steadily in straight to be nearest at finish.

Jumped well from the one draw, settled just off the pace in 2L 3rd on the rail, in similar position but became 4th rounding home bend, baulked for a run early in straight, kept on steadily under pressure without quickening.
Settled in midfield, baulked and switched 200 metres out, made modest headway without threatening.
Soon taken back to last from the widest gate, made headway at about 1200 metres, finished off race strongly inside the final 300 metres.
Pressed forward for a prominent position from a wide gate before settling just off the pace, remained prominent to the straight, unable to sustain effort inside the final 300 metres.
Lacked early speed, settled in last few on the rail, gained closer after a reminder over 1400 metres out, back towards the rear rounding home bend, kept on same pace without quickening.
Soon settled in last few before dropping to last after the first 400 metres, saved ground on the rail turning for home, produced good late impression in the run to the line.
Jumped fairly, niggled along before settling in forward of midfield on the rail in 6th, saved ground turning in, faded under pressure in the straight.
Jumped fairly, ridden and soon led, crossed to the rail 1300 metres out, found no extra when headed and swamped inside the final 250 metres.
Broke well from a wide gate, soon taken back to last few and remained wide, dropped to last entering straight, went past well-beaten horses inside the final 150 metres.
Well there early, settled just over 2L off the pace, faded under pressure after straightening.
Slightly slow out, just worse than midfield early before settling in last few, took closer order round the back-markers on the bend, found no extra in straight.
Failed to muster at rear, 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed strongly 300M to score.
Pushed early, midfield 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 250M.
Settled in front, 2 wide, favoured by the slow tempo, ran on well but only for 3rd.
Pressed forward, just off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the slow sectionals, just held ground in final stages.
Pushed early, behind midfield along the fence, dashed well 250M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, little dash 200M.
Took rail and lead easily, clocked slow sectionals, flattened 250M.
Eased to sit behind midfield, 2 wide, raced keenly, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 250M.
At back, 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, little dash 200M.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, not suited by the slow tempo, no progress.
Very slow away, at rear, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, ran on ok in straight.
Trapped 3 wide behind midfield, harmed by the slow pace, lack turn of foot.
At rear, not suited by the slow tempo, no dash.
Slow away, never a factor.
Raced behind midfield on rail, improve at Home Turn, gradually made ground in the straight, finished strongly to score.
Began awkwardly, settled at tail, asked for effort and shifted out at Home Turn, widest on straightening, made up some nice ground, finished solidly, just missed by SH.
Settled at handy position, fought hard entire straight, finished solidly.
Ridden along to settle outside the leader, commenced to improve passing 450M, battled hard in the straight, came home nicely.
Fractious in barrier and slow to begin, raced at tail on rail, under pressure in the straight, made ground final 50M, finished well. Stalls test.
Cruised well to take lead, asked for effort passing 400M, weakened passing 100M and finished fairly.
Settled midfield, rider's whip dropped after passing 200M, one-paced in the straight.
Began only fairly then raced midfield, one-paced in the straight.
Throughout the race travelled wide and without cover, made the Home Turn awkwardly, in the straight failed to run on.
Away well, allowed to roll forward, settling 2L from leader at first turn. Moved up to a half length from leader 1300m, kicked ahead 500m, under attack 150m, kicked again for solid win.
Jumped well, rolled forward to grab box seat on settling 3L from leader. Not asked for effort until 600m when came off fence to challenge. Looked chance when drew level 150m before winner kicked.
Taken in for cover soon after start, settling one-out in midfield. Shaken up turning for home, swung wide into straight, finished off nicely after a couple of reminders.
Began only fairly, dropping one-out to behind midfield. Stayed at rear to straight, blocked for run until 300m when got split and finished off strongly.
Shifted in for cover soon after start, dropping to rear. Shuffled back to last approaching home turn, hampered shortly after straightening before picking up the bit and running on strongly.
Raced along rail in midfield mostly before making a forward move home turn. Loomed as a chance halfway up the straight before running out of puff final strides.
Taken in for cover soon after start, dropping to behind midfield. Not suited by the sedate pace and dropped further back approaching home turn. Ran on fairly in straight.
Rolled forward, sharing early pace until settling one-back, one-out. Taken to rail home turn, switched out again straight, made ground to 200m before flattened.
Bumped start, slow into stride, last on settling. Made forward move back stretch racing 4-wide to get to within 4L from leader at turn-in before tiring. Lame right front leg.
Ridden to hold forward position, settling one-out 4L from leader. Under the pump to hold position around home turn and gave ground gradually.
Raced mostly at rear. Made forward move home turn but soon out of gas and faded. (Earplugs dislodged 1000m).
Pressed forward to lead on settling, setting sedate pace. Under siege turning for home, overtaken entering straight, faded, finishing tailed out. Unacceptable performance.
Began well, positioned 2 lengths back in 3rd, travelled well throughout, angled out near 550M, took the lead early in straight and kept on strongly to the line, scored by a neck.
Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide behind midfield early, slightly improved on turn, very wide turning in, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Moderately away, positioned 4 lengths or so back on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off well in straight to get a place.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, found daylight final 250M, ran home well to get 4th without threatening.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, improved on turn, made some progress in straight.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, raced at tail, 8 lengths back, still well back on turn, made decent progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced wide with cover behind midfield, 4 lengths back, same position on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 6 lengths or so back at rear, saved ground on turn, made reasonable progress in straight.
Bumped at start, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead near 800M, peaked after turning in, headed near 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well from a wide draw, positioned 2 wide in 4th, no cover in the middle stages, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, taken back to race at rear, travelled keenly near 1000M, still 6 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began fairly, recovered to take the early lead, headed near 800M, peaked after turning in, emptied near 300M, eased in the final stages.
Began only fairly, recovered to race 2 wide in midfield, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight and eased.
Pushed and raced in front of midfield, 3-1/4L off 3 wide without cover, fought to the wire and won by a short-head.
Ridden and settled to race in front of midfield, 3L behind along the rail, fought a close battle, missed by a short-head.
Eased then raced at the rear, 7-3/4L behind 2 wide, shifted wide after 600M, made good ground and finished strongly.
Pushed and settled in one-off one-back position, sat 2-1/4L off the lead, kept on well to the line.
In behind midfield, hampered at 900M then rounded turn 3 wide but with cover, made ground from 300M, ran on well.
Settled in worse than midfield, 6-3/4L behind along the rail, made ground steadily and closed off not bad.
In behind midfield, 6-1/4L behind 2 wide, hampered at 200M when commencing to make ground, ran on fairly.
Niggled and settled to race in midfield, 3-1/2L behind 2 wide, kept on one paced to the line.
Pushed and shared lead early, then settled for the box-seat 1L behind at 700M, couldn't find extra passing 200M.
Raced in about midfield, 4-1/2L off 3 wide with cover, unsettled throughout and remained one paced to the line.
Eased and then raced at the back, 8-1/4L behind along the rail, made ground along the inner straight.
Travelled in just behind midfield, 5L behind along the rail, remained one paced to the line.
In behind midfield, 5-1/4L behind 2 wide, crowded at 800M, did not improve and one paced to the line.
Sent forward, obtained outright lead on the rail by 700M, flattened approaching 200M, faded from thereon.
Strode forward 3-wide to lead before crossing to fence and setting slow pace. Picked up speed approaching home turn, kicked ahead 400m and kept on strongly to the line.
Jumped well, taken forward, settling one-out 2L from leader. Swung a little wide into straight, finished off well but unable mow down leader.
Jumped OK, ridden but no speed, dropping towards rear along fence. Taken wide home turn, wider in straight, finished strongly to grab minor placing.
Began well but no speed, dropping to last on settling. Taken to centre field on straightening and ran on well to finish behind place-getters. Had substantial amount of blood in trachea.
Raced mostly one-out in midfield. Made forward move on straightening to look a chance 200m before turning one-paced.
Pressed forward from an outside draw to race outside hind-quarters of leader. Kept tabs to 200m when flattened and swamped.
Taken in for cover shortly after start, dropping one-out towards rear. Under pump turning for home but only one-paced.
Raced along rail behind midfield before losing position around home turn. Finished off nicely in straight.
Taken in for cover soon after start, settling one-out behind midfield. Took inside run in straight and kept on fairly.
Jumped OK, holding rail in midfield. Stayed on rail around turn but only one-paced in straight.
Bumped and unbalanced start, dropping to rear. Rolled forward 4-wide from 800m to get within 4L of leader at turn-in before tiring. Had substantial amount of blood in trachea.
Pressed forward racing 3-wide without cover 3L from leader to turn. Under pressure on straightening and faded.
Began awkwardly, shifted out and bumped rival before pressing forward along rail 3L from leader. Travelled keenly from 1000m and gave ground quickly in straight.
Ridden along from widest draw looking for cover but held 4-wide behind midfield. Shuffled back to last turning for home, one-paced in straight.
Crossed to the lead 1600M, enjoyed uncontested lead setting slow and steady pace, quickened and shot 2Ls clear 300M, showed no signs of stopping to line. Impressive victory.
Settled down midfield in a steadily run race, 4-5Ls off the pace middle stages, switched away from rails 600M, ran on well to go 2nd near 200M, tried but couldn't get closer to runaway winner.
Jumped well from draw 1, raced keenly when crossed by rival passing 1600M, poised to strike 450M, went 2nd 300M out, kept on well but couldn't bridge the gap on winner, lost 2nd near 150M.
Reserved towards the rear in a steadily run race, 6-7Ls off leader middle stages, into clear 300M, stayed on well.
Moved up gradually to track leader one out one back, had every chance turning home, lost 2nd near 300M, kept battling to the line but well held by leaders.
Held up 3rd last, not helped by slow pace proved very difficult to settle after 1300M, driven widest 600M, ran on mildly on straightening, never looked likely.
Dropped back to the rear on jumping, raced as the back-marker until 900M, didn't quicken enough on straightening, never a serious threat to leaders.
Began well, restrained to a 2-wide position in midfield, from 550M switched wider to challenge, one paced in straight.
Caught 3-wide early stages before finding cover behind leaders entering back-straight, driven along 500M, tried but failed to make any impression.
Behind midfield in the 8th spot, just over 5Ls behind leaders, brought wide 550M, didn't quicken under pressure. No threat at any stage.
Away well enough to be just over 3Ls from leaders in steadily run race, kept to inside throughout, faded in the run to the line.
Crowded for room on jumping, travelled keenly after 1500M, shuffled back to the rear entering back-straight, swung wide 550M but didn't respond to riding, never a factor.
First out but stayed away from pace battle, settling one-out 4L from leader at turn. Shaken up on straightening and ran on strongly to win close home.
Shaky start but hard ridden to hold rail, settling a half length inside leader. Took over lead 400m, kept on strongly in straight but run down close home.
Pressed forward from a wide draw, grabbing box seat 3L from leader at turn. Disappointed for run early in straight but kept on well despite hanging in.
Pressed forward from an outside draw to race behind the pace but held wide without cover. Covered extra ground throughout but kept on gamely in straight.
Jumped well, pressed forward but held wide behind pace. Improved from 1200m to lead but kept away from fence by inside runner. Overtaken 400m but kept on gamely until swamped close home.
Raced mostly one-out in midfield though proved difficult to settle approaching 1200m. One-paced in straight.
Began well, ridden to hold rail, settling 4L from leader. Stayed on rail around turn, made up some ground early in straight before tuning one-paced.
No pace, racing one-out behind midfield. Taken wide entering straight but made little headway under hard riding.
Shifted across behind horses soon after start, dropping one-out towards rear. Taken wide entering straight but only one-paced.
Ridden to hold midfield position along rail. Shifted out at turn-in to make challenge but found little under pressure. Had substantial amount of mucus in trachea.
Shifted across behind horses from wide draw and taken to rail towards rear. Made up some ground around home turn but ran out of stamina halfway up the straight.
Bounded in the air at start and then bumped, dropping to last. Raced at the rear thereafter and never in the hunt.
No pace, dropping one-out towards rear. Shuffled back to last around home turn and never likely.
Ridden early to hold midfield position but wide. Lost ground turning for home and failed to respond to rider's urgings in straight.
Pressed forward early to lead. Pulled away from the top of the straight to a handy lead. Not much left in the tank late, but the result was never in doubt.

Eased forward early to sit around midfield, 1 off the fence. Awkwardly placed and came in off heels at the top of the straight. Weaved through runners in the straight and finished strongly, making ground on the winner late.
Taken up early to be handily placed 4th/5th, 1 off the fence. Ran on solidly in the straight, but no threat to the first 2.
Pressed forward to be well placed, 3rd/4th on the fence. Stayed on well in the straight, but 1 paced over the final 100m.
Began awkwardly, lost ground and settled towards the back of the field. Checked off heels at 1500m. Clear from the 300m and stayed on solidly, without threatening a place.
Eased back early to sit towards the rear of the field. Looked to be gone early in the straight, but kicked over the last 200m, and stayed on well late.
Cruised forward from the inside draw to sit midfield, on the fence. 1 paced in the straight and made no impression.
Dropped back early from the wide draw to sit towards the rear of the field. Widest on the turn. Only plugged away fairly and never threatened.
Pressed forward to share the early lead. Already fading out when checked and lost ground at 100m.
Pressed forward early to be well placed 3rd/4th, but 3 wide with no cover. Lay in at the top of the straight and started fading out soon after.
Slowly away, but recovered to settle just behind midfield. Unsettled on heels early/mid race. Clear run in the straight, but went to the line 1 paced.
Crowded on jumping and dropped back early to sit last. Only plugged away in the straight. Restricted room late, but wasn't running on.
Crowded on jumping, but recovered to push forward and sit around midfield. Prominent on the turn, but gave nothing in the straight and wasn't pushed hard late.
Cruised across from the wide barrier to be stuck 4 wide, worse than midfield. Beaten horse by the turn, and played no part in the straight.
