Jumped fairly and soon took up running setting a robust pace, drew clear upon straightening and won unchallenged.
Began fairly, settled mainly in midfield on the rail, angled out to challenge upon straightening, ran on without threatening.

Gradually taken back towards the rear but remained wide without cover until the 800 metres, commenced move entering straight and swung widest turning in, ran on near the centre of the track to grab 3rd late.
Jumped well, pressed forward to soon join the leader, taken one-out-one-back in 3rd rounding first bend, lost position approaching home turn, kept on steadily under pressure without quickening.
Broke well and raced 3-wide without cover on the first bend, improved to join the leader over 1100 metres out and chased him onto home bend, found nothing in straight.
Broke well, settled one back on the rail within 2L of pace, gradually faded under pressure in the run to the line.
Moderate start, settled towards the rear on the rail, gained slightly closer rounding home bend, kept on steadily without quickening.
Ridden early, settled just over 2L back in 5th, steadied slightly backward to 3L 6th passing the 900 metres, gave ground from entering home straight.
Soon taken back from a wide gate, near seen with a chance.
Settled in rear of midfield, beaten on home bend.
Always in last few, tailed-off from the 500 metres.
Eased to sit in midfield, trapped 3 wide throughout, pace good, progressed steadily 450M and scored.
Eased back, 2 wide, pace good, dashed well 300M for 2nd.
Midfield along the fence, pace good, lack room 400M, progressed steadily 250M.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, pace good, led 300M, out of fuel 150M.
In front of midfield, 2 wide, pace good, just held ground in straight.
Very slow away, hard ridden at rear, 2 wide, lack room in straight, made steady ground.
Eased to sit in midfield, trapped 3 wide throughout, weakened 250M.
Eased back, trapped 3-4 wide throughout, pace good, ran on ok.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, pace good, blocked most straight, not properly tested.
Hard ridden early but not muster, at back along the fence, pace good, lack room in straight, not properly tested.
Pushed to take rail and led at good pace, soon emptied 350M.
Never competitive at rear.
Began well, settled behind leaders, asked effort approaching 350M, responded well and scored unchallenged.
Settled midfield, improved at Home Turn, wide on straightening, quickened passing 100M, worked home solidly.

At start was crowed for room and became badly unbalanced, soon after was bumped and became unbalanced when buffeted for room, settled midfield on rail, gradually made ground in the straight, finished solidly.
Settled behind midfield, commenced to improve passing 350M, made up some late ground, finished nicely.
Ridden along to obtain forward position, passing 600M took lead, gave ground passing 150M.
Urged along to settle at handy position, tried to improve approaching 350M, gave ground passing 100M.
Stood flat-footed in the barrier and lost ground, after that tried hard to make ground, widest on straightening, one-paced in the straight. Must trial.
After the start became badly unbalanced, raced midfield, asked for effort passing 600M, gave ground passing 200M.
Urged along to take lead, the passing 700M drifted back to box seat, kept improving on the rail, weakened passing 100M, failed to run on.
Taken back at start, no response when under pressure, always back.
At start became badly unbalanced, raced behind midfield on rail, always niggling, failed to close off.
Approaching 700M was left racing wide and without cover, never in it. Blood trachea.
Steadied soon after start and taken in for cover, dropping to last pair. Not happy with slow pace and took off 4-wide from first turn to be 3rd into straight. Kept on strongly to win close home.
Pressed forward, taking lead on settling and set slow pace. Kicked 6L ahead turning for home but running on empty passing 100m and caught close home.
Held back early stages, racing one-out towards rear. Taken wide on straightening and finished well down centre track.
Jumped well, pressed forward, settling one-out 3L from leader. Lost position first turn, dropping to behind midfield, took home turn 4-wide, boxed on gamely.

Pressed forward, racing one-out behind leader to first turn, before losing position back stretch, dropping to midfield. Steadied home turn, wide into straight, boxed on. (Lost left front plate at start).
No early pace, racing along rail towards rear. Checked turning for home, switched out on straightening and ran on fairly.
Raced mostly in midfield along rail. Checked home turn, stayed on rail in straight and ran on fairly.
Jumped OK, ridden to hold rail 3L from leader. Kept tabs to turn-in but only one-paced in straight.
Began well but unhappy with slow pace and over-raced, dropping to behind midfield. Proved difficult to settle approaching home turn and spent force in straight.
Ridden forward from outside draw but caught wide behind midfield 1300m. Allowed to improve to sit 3-wide outside leader at home turn. Under pressure on straightening and faded.
Slow into stride, dropping to rear. Last along back stretch and never in the hunt.
Ridden to get forward position but held wide at first turn and allowed to improve to race outside leader 1300m. Under pressure 600m and dropped back quickly. Had irregular heart rhythm.
Away with them, positioned 4 lengths or so back on rail, there to turn, finished off very strongly in straight to score.
Taken back from a wide draw, positioned 2 to 3 wide with cover behind midfield, improved from 400M, very wide turning in, finished off very strongly to be nearest on line.
Began well from gate 1, sat 3 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, made reasonable headway in straight, just missed 2nd.
Moderately away from the widest gate, sent forward to race 2 wide in 2nd, shared lead turning in, kept on well early in straight, headed in the closing stages, stayed on for 4th.
Jumped well from a wide draw, showed early speed to take the lead, travelled well throughout, headed early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths back in midfield, same position on turn, inclined to lay in when placed under pressure in straight, finished off only evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back, similar position on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened in the concluding stages.
Bumped start, raced 8 lengths back at tail early, still 5 to 6 lengths back in the middle stages, there to turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped well, positioned a length behind the leader, easy run to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 6 lengths back at rear, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, similar position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began awkwardly, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with no cover throughout, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight, finished last.
Raced in front of midfield, sat 3-1/4L behind along the rail, ran home nicely to take the prize by 1-1/4L.
Slotted in to race in behind midfield, 6-1/2L behind 2 wide, inconvenienced prior to 200M, finished off strongly thereon.
Niggled along and settled to race in the box-seat, sat 1-1/2L off, kept on well to the line for 3rd.
Taken back and raced at the tail, 7-3/4L behind 2 wide, made nice ground and hit the line fairly well.
Jumped very awkwardly, taken back and raced near the tail, 6-3/4L behind 3 wide with cover, made ground steadily.
Travelled in about midfield, 5L behind and shifted to 3 wide at 700M, swung wide and ran on mostly one paced.
Niggled along to be prominent, trapped wide until took lead outright after 1000M, found no extra and headed at 100M.
Slotted in to race in about midfield, 5L behind along the rail, kept on one paced to the line.
Niggled and then raced prominently, sat 2L off the lead, found nothing and was difficult to ride in the straight.
Pushed and raced in one-off one-back position, improved at 700M to sit outside the lead, emptied after 200M.
Raced at the rear, 8-1/4L behind along the rail, never in it.
Slow to jump, settled towards the rear, 6-1/2L behind along the rail, did not feature.
Jumped straight to the front, racing wide till crossing to rail 1250m. Kicked 2L clear on straightening and went to the post under hands and heels riding.
Away well, pressed forward from wide draw, racing one-out 1L from leader. Left flat-footed when leader kicked 350m but kept chasing to the line.
Raced in midfield along rail to turn. Switched out in straight to make challenge but never looked dangerous.
Jumped well, taken to box seat and tracked leader to straight. Shaken up 300m but only one-paced.
No early pace, racing one-out towards rear. Swung wide into straight and boxed on fairly.
Ridden early to stay with pace but left wide after 1300m. Taken to centre field on straightening but only one-paced.
Traveled comfortably one-back, one-out from start but had to be niggled at passing 600m to hold position before giving ground in straight.
Jumped awkwardly, losing ground, dropping to last pair along rail. Stayed on rail around turn and made up some ground in straight.
Outpaced early, racing along rail behind midfield. Came off rail on straightening but only one-paced.
Began well, taken to rail, settling 3L from leader. Under pressure from home turn and gave ground gradually.
No pace, racing 3-wide towards rear. Covered extra ground throughout and found little in straight when asked for effort.
Steadied soon after start and shifted across behind runners, dropping to last. Never in the hunt after that.
Shaken up early stages, sat 3-wide just behind leaders but no cover to straight, quickened to lead 150M, all out towards the finish and just held on from the fast finishing 2nd.
Never far off from leaders in midfield, picked up well passing 200M, laid down a strong late challenge, just failed by a whisker.
Crossed to a 3-wide spot in midfield after jumping from 12, driven out 400M, kept on steadily to the finish but always held by winner.
Restrained in midfield after the start, 8th at 400M and 4Ls to make up, ran on mildly towards the finish.
Steadied early stages to obtain cover, towards the rear 5Ls back, pulled widest on straightening, worked home well to be nearest at the finish despite shifting out late stages under pressure.
Away well and pressed on to lead along the fence at a steady pace, outgunned final 100M, lost several placing near line.
Crowded for room on jumping then shifted across behind runners, settled in rear 5Ls off the pace for the first half, made 3-wide bid 600M, boxed on fairly early straight, no extra to challenge 150M.
Quickly away, chased leaders 2-wide, bustled along to hold his position 550M, ran home one paced.
Jumped on terms, held back to sit near the rear 5Ls off the pace, stuck to inside throughout, ran on only fairly over final 300M and at no stage a serious threat.
Crowded for room on jumping, shuffled back to last 700M, 7Ls to make up at 400M, passed a couple late but never a threat to leaders.
Did some early work from draw 9, went forward to press leader on the outside, faded mid-straight, eased towards the line. (Lame next day.)
Began well from inside draw, tracked leaders in a steadily run race, found nothing when asked on straightening, first to be beaten, eased when no chance final 200M.

Moderate start, settled in midfield on stands rail early stages, commenced move from the 600 metres and ran on well to hit the front passing the 200 metres, hung on well.
Moderate start, settled just off the pace on stands rail, came to challenge inside the 400 metres, ran on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Disputed lead most of the way, hit the front briefly inside the 200 meters but unable to sustain effort closing stages.
Broke well from the stands side gate, held narrow lead on stands rail, failed to resist challenges and headed passing the 200 metres.
Broke well, taken back for cover in rear of midfield but raced keenly, made up good ground inside the final 250 metres without threatening.
Raced greenly in last few, kept on steadily without quickening.
Travelled just off the pace mainly in 5th without cover, failed to quicken under pressure inside the final 400 metres.
Moderate start, settled in last few, switched in for a run coming onto the course proper, kept on same pace without quickening.
Knuckled over at start losing ground, soon shifted to the stands rail in the rear of the field, took closer order coming onto course proper, never nearer.
Settled well back with cover early stages, switched in to the centre of the track approaching the course proper, fought on past well-beaten horses.
Held up in midfield, travelling only fairly behind midfield when bumped on the hindquarters approaching the course proper and lost momentum, made no impression under pressure in closing stages.
Travelled in midfield without cover, faded under pressure inside the final 300 metres.
Wandering about early stages, settled just worse than midfield near the centre of the track, found nothing.
Niggled along in first few early stages, yielded ground from the 600 metres and dropped out quickly.
Hard ridden early to keep up in midfield, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 400M to score.
Hard ridden forward, box seat, not suited by the fast pace, closed off strongly 300M, just missed by a narrow margin.
Settled along the fence in midfield, suited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M for 3rd.
Pressed forward, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast tempo, led 400M, ran on well until 200M, weakened.
Behind midfield, 2 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, lack room 400M, made some ground when clear.
Eased back, took rail, benefited by the fast tempo, lack room 400M, made minor ground when clear.
Bumped badly at start, behind midfield, 2-3 wide, suited by the fast pace, ran on ok.
Hard ridden to take rail and lead, clocked very fast sectionals, soon out of fuel 400M.
Failed to muster at rear, benefited by the fast pace, ran on fairly in straight.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast sectionals, emptied 350M.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, checked 400M, no progress.
Eased back, raced 2-4 wide, suited by the fast pace, never improved.
Never a factor.
Midfield, faded rapidly 350M.
In the early stages was left racing wide, improved its position to take up the lead after the 700M, after that travelled strongly in the straight, finished unchallenged.
Raced behind leaders, commenced to improve passing 600M, made some late ground, finished strongly.
Urged along to take lead, passing 700M drifted back, fought hard in the straight, finished nicely.
Ridden along to settle box seat, asked for effort passing 700M, battled hard in the straight, came home nicely.
Jumped well then steadied to obtain cover, settled midfield on rail, kept improving on rail at Home Turn and in the straight, finished well.
Fractious in barrier, then on jumping stood flat-footed and lost ground, niggled to make up ground in the mid stages, ran on in the straight, finished fairly. Must trail.
Throughout the race travelled wide and without cover, raced midfield, one-paced in the straight.
Jumped well then ridden along to settle outside the lead, tried to improve at Home Turn, limited response in the straight.
On jumping stood flat-footed and lost ground, failed to run on. Must trail.
Ridden along but still gave ground, raced back and never in it.
Difficult to manage, hung out badly rounding Home Turn, gave ground in the straight. Must series trails.
Pressed forward to lead on settling, crossing to rail 900m. Set good pace to straight, kicked clear 300m, went to the post unchallenged.
Crowded out shortly after start, dropping to behind midfield and taken to rail. Came off fence turning for home, wide in straight, finished strongly.
Pressed forward from outside draw, racing 3-wide without cover 2L from leader. Kept wide around home turn, boxed on gamely in straight to hold minor placing.
Hard ridden early to stay with pace, settling one-out 3L from leader approaching turn. Given reminders in straight and boxed on gamely to finish close behind place-getters.
Steadied on jumping and shifted across behind runners from outside draw, dropping 3-wide at rear. Taken wide in straight and ran on well, doing best work final 200m.
Ridden told hold forward position, settling one-out 2L from leader at turn. Kept tabs to 200m when ran out of fuel.
Race mostly in midfield close to fence. Came off rail turning for home but only one-paced in straight.
Bumped and lost ground shortly after start, ridden but didn't muster, settling one-out in midfield. Taken wide entering straight but only one-paced under pressure.
Ridden early but kept very wide before settling 3-wide behind midfield approaching turn. Lost position turning for home and one-paced in straight.
Slow into stride and last on settling. Last into straight before running past beaten rivals final stages.
Began well, ridden to hold box seat and settled. Under pressure at turn-in, kept on fairly to 200m before giving ground abruptly. Unacceptable performance.
Raced one-out behind midfield to straight when failed to respond to rider's efforts. Lame left front leg.
Began well, positioned 3 lengths or so back in midfield, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off strongly when clear final 200M, impressive debut win.
Began awkwardly, recovered to race outside the leader in 2nd, shared lead on turn, kept on very well in straight, just headed by the winner final 50M.
Jumped well, positioned a length or so back on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on well in straight to get 3rd.
Fast into stride, ridden positively to take the lead, travelled well throughout, headed after turning in, stayed on evenly for 4th.(See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 9 lengths back at tail, still well back on turn, angled out in straight and made good progress to be nearest on line, promising debut.
Began well, positioned 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, there to turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Slowly away, positioned 6 lengths back on rail, slightly improved along the rail on turn, no clear running early in straight, bumped near 250M, finished off evenly thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 4 to 5 lengths back, same position on turn, bumped and unbalanced near 250M, finished off one-paced thereafter.
Moderately away from gate 11, unable to slot in, travelled 3 wide with no cover in 3rd, found cover near 600M, peaked after turning in, weakened thereafter when hard run took toll.
Bumped start, positioned 3 wide with cover, 3 lengths back, lost cover on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Began fairly, raced 8 lengths back at rear, taken wide after turning in, showed no progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 7 to 8 lengths back at rear, still well back on turn, failed to close off in straight, finished last.
Raced in one-off one-back position, sat 2-1/4L off the lead, pulled away from 200M, kept on nicely to score by 2-1/2L.
Crowded at start then raced towards the rear, 6L behind 2 wide, made nice ground and ran on nicely.
Bumped after the start, settled in front of midfield, 3-1/4L behind along the rail, ran on well to take 3rd.
Eased and settled in about midfield, 4-1/2L behind 3 wide with cover, one paced but kept on to the finish.
Taken back and raced at the rear, 8L behind along the rail, made ground steadily to the line.
Bumped after the start, pushed forward and raced in the box-seat, sat 1-1/2L off, ran on fairly to the line.
Bumped start then eased, in worse than midfield, 5-1/2L behind 2 wide, hampered at exit of turn then held up till 200M, closed off fairly.
Rolled forward, sat 3/4L off the lead in a 2 wide position, flattened after passing 200M.
Ridden to be prominent, sat 1-1/2L off 3 wide without cover, couldn't keep up passing 150M.
Bumped start, then niggled to sit front of midfield, 3L off 3 wide with cover, no extra passing 150M.
Bumped start, in midfield, 3-1/2L behind 2 wide, not tested near 200M when in restricted room, one paced to the line.
Crowded at start, sat just behind midfield, 5L behind along the rail, no daylight early, one paced thereafter.
Bumped start, raced near the tail, 6-1/2L behind along the rail, did not make ground.
Ridden forward to take rail and led by 3/4L, showed nothing. (Heart irregularity and bled)
Ridden to find cover soon after jump, settling one-out behind midfield. Improved around turn, ran on steadily between horses in the straight, hit front 200m, kept on well under pressure.
Bumped and unbalanced start, then badly crowded, dropping to midfield. Swung wide into straight and ran on strongly to grab quinella spot.
Jumped well, shifted in for cover, settling one-out towards rear. Blocked for run entering straight, got split 200m out, finished strongly.
Taken in for cover soon after start but held 3-wide in midfield. Travelled keenly passing 1300m but settled better home turn. Taken wide in straight and ran on steadily.
Jumped well, ridden forward settling one-out 3L from leader. Crowded out 1400m but kept position, bumped in straight but boxed on gamely.
Bumped and unbalanced start, dropping to last pair. Remained at rear to turn, taken to centre track in straightening and ran home fairly.
Well positioned early, staying one-out behind pace, but travelled keenly from 1100m. Looked chance when moved forward 300m but ran out of fuel close home.
Lifted front feet when gates opened and lost considerable ground, dropping to last. Remained well back to straight, taken to centre track and ran on fairly.
Shared early lead before settling outside hind-quarters of leader passing 1200m. Retook lead 300m but flattened 200m and faded.
Ridden to hold forward position, racing 3-wide 3L from leader without cover. Stayed in the hunt until well into the straight before running out of steam and fading.
Ridden to grab box seat, settling 2L from leader at turn. Got boxed in on straightening and unable to get run till halfway up the straight.
Beaten for early pace and raced mostly along rail towards rear. Stayed on rail in straight but made little headway.
Hard ridden from an outside draw to lead on settling. Set steady pace to 300m when joined up front. Kept on to 200m before tiring.
Bumped heavily at start, taken to fence and ridden to hold position 3L from leader. Came under pressure home turn, losing ground steadily to finish tailed out. Had irregular heart rhythm.
Guided to the fence, travelled well in midfield 4Ls off leaders, angled into clear passing 300M, quickened to the lead 150M and kept on well towards the finish.
Ahead of midfield along the 2-path, never far away 3Ls back from leaders, into clear 350M, produced good finish.
Reserved behind mid-division 5-6Ls off the good pace, quickened nicely when switched to outside 400M, got up for 3rd late.
Dropped back to a rearward spot 6-7Ls off the good pace, badly held up to 250M and did best work towards the line. Should have done better.
Settled down midfield in a strongly run race, 5-6Ls off leaders middle stages, held up to 300M, ran on when clear but couldn't close gap on leaders.
Held up 2-wide in mid-division, brought wide to challenge, stayed on mildly to the line but always held by leaders.
Tracked leaders along the fence, kept battling to the line but held ground only.
From draw 1 rolled forward to lead, commenced to race keenly when pressed by rivals middle stages, headed inside 200M, weakened towards the line. (Jockey questioned re riding tactics.)
Pressed the pace 2-wide, driven near 400M and vied for the lead until fading passing 200M.
Slotted into a 2-wide spot near the rear, 6Ls off the pace 400M, made his run from wide, battled past a few while never in the reckoning.
From draw 13 crossed to a 3-wide spot ahead of midfield, no cover from 1000M, outsprinted by rivals inside 300M, soon out of contention.
Switched off to last on jumping, over 10Ls off the pace halfway, made no impact in straight.
Chased leaders, kept on same pace in straight, eased when no chance 150M.
Taken back from widest draw, always at the rear, never got going.
Pushed to take rail and lead 1000m, set steady pace to straight, kicked clear 200m, unchallenged.
Hard ridden to stay with pace but kept 3-wide without cover 2L from leader. Shaken up on straightening to challenge but unable mow down leader.
No early pace, travelling along rail towards rear. Made up ground around home turn, ran on well in straight to grab minor placing.
Sat outside leader on settling and kept tabs to 200m when ran out of fuel.
Outpaced, racing at rear along rail. Stayed on rail in straight and ran on steadily to be closest at finish.
Ridden early to obtain box seat 3L from leader. Came under pressure early in straight but only one-paced.
Given early reminder but failed to accelerate and trapped 3-wide at midfield. Had clear running in straight but only one-paced.
Began fairly, no pace, dropping one-out at rear. Taken very wide in straight and ran past beaten rivals.
Slightly inconvenienced start, ridden along before seeking cover behind midfield approaching turn. One-paced in straight.
Ridden to hold rail in midfield before making progress around turn. Kept on fairly to 200m before tiring.
Ridden early to hold midfield position one-away from fence. Under pressure at turn-in and gave ground in straight.
Pressed forward from wide draw to stay with pace, racing 3-wide without cover 3L from leader. Lost position around home turn and dropped out in straight.
Pressed forward early to be well placed 3rd. No clear run until 200m. Ran strongly from that point and was comfortable late.
Got head up early when being dropped back to last. Clear run in the straight and ran strongly. Couldn't match winner late.
Bumped on jumping and dropped back to the rear of the field. Midfield 800m. No run early straight. Stayed on well when clear 300m, despite being inconvenienced at 100m.
Pushed forward early to be well placed 3rd/4th. Clear run in the straight and led from 300m. Peaked late and was swamped in last 50m.
Pushed across early to sit 2nd. Slightly 1 paced in the straight. Bumped, badly unbalanced and hampered, and dropped out from 100m.
Cruised across to sit around midfield. Wide no cover from 1000m. Bumped and badly unbalanced 900m. Never threatened in the straight.
Dropped back early from the wide draw to sit at the rear of the field. Stayed on solidly in the straight and picked up some of the slower ones late.
Pushed forward early to lead. 1 paced in the straight, and had no impact on the finish.
Slow to begin, but recovered to sit midfield. Keen on heels 1000m. Not pushed hard in the straight and eased out late.
Bumped on jumping before settling midfield. 1 paced in straight and eased late. Vet- Blood in trachea.
Cruised out early, and then dropped back to the rear of the field. Plugged away without threatening to run on in the straight.
Slow to begin and got back. Played no part.
Taken out early to sit forward of midfield. Faded out quickly from the 300m.
Cruised forward to sit worse than midfield. Dropped out quickly in the straight.

Began fairly, soon ridden to the lead, kicked over 2L clear upon straightening, just fended off late challenges.
Soon taken back from a wide gate, settled towards the rear on the rail, saved ground turning for home, produced good late impression inside the final 200 metres, did best work late.

Moderate start, quickly ridden up the rail to be just over 2L back in 4th, saved ground turning for home, ran on under pressure to reach 2nd inside the 200 metres only to lose the placing near the line.
Amongst leaders briefly, gradually shifted back to 4th 3-wide without cover and onto 5th 600 metres out, swung wide into the straight, ran on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Soon dropped to second last, remained well back to the straight, saved ground turning in, forced to switch out for a run 200 metres out, sustained progress to be nearest at finish.
Broke well from a wide draw, settled in rear of midfield in 8th, shuffled back to 9th passing the Rock, checked for a run early in straight, made good late recovery closing stages.
Settled in last few from a wide gate, improved along the rail to reach mid-division going up the Rock, angled out for a run turning in, fought on steadily without threatening.
Jumped fairly from the widest gate, gradually shifted in to settle alongside the leader, weakened under pressure soon after straightening.
Very slowly away, trailed the field to the 250 metres, ran on under pressure past well-beaten horses.
Ridden along to hold prominent spot early before settling in 2L 3rd, dropped to 4th rounding home bend and weakened further into the straight.
Jumped fairly, mainly in midfield to the straight, faded under pressure.
Moderate start, made steady headway out wide down far side to reach within 3L of pace approaching the home bend, swung widest into the straight and dropped quickly out of contention.
Midfield, trapped 3 wide throughout, pace good, dashed well 250M to score with some in hand.
Pressed forward, sat 2 wide, pace good, bumped 300M and 50M, ran on strongly for 2nd.
Pushed to take rail and led at good pace, hung on well until 50M overhauled, ran on for 3rd.
Pushed to occupy box seat, pace good, blocked early straight and checked, held ground.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, pace good, lack room 300M, made steady ground when clear.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, pace good, on heels 500M, made ground 200M.
Eased at start, trapped 3 wide in midfield, pace good, held ground in straight.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide throughout, pace good, made ground 200M.
Eased back, took rail, pace good, lack room 300M, ran on fairly.
Eased back, 2 wide, pace good, lack room 300M, no dash.
Very slow away, at rear along the fence, pace good, ran on ok.
Pushed forward, sat outside the leader, pace good, was galloped on near 300M, dropped off afterwards.
Taken back at start, settled behind midfield on rail, kept on rail at Home Turn, lay out and proved difficult to ride in the straight, issued a challenged passing 150M, finished strongly to score.
Urged to take box seat, approaching 200M lay in and awkwardly placed, at the 50M was crowded for room, came home strongly, just missed by 1/2L
Ridden along to settle outside the lead, niggled passing 600M, ran on strongly, just missed by 1/2L.
Raced midfield on rail, improved at Home Turn, gradually made ground in the straight, finished solidly.
On jumped was crowded for room, settled behind midfield, wide on straightening, made up some nice late ground, rider was not able to ride the horse to the end (see incident report).
Raced midfield, improved passing 400M and widest on straightening, travelled nicely in the straight, became unbalanced close to finishing line (see incident report).
On jumped was bumped and became unbalanced, settled midfield, close to finishing line steadied away from heels, finished fairly, bled.
Taken back at start, raced at tail on rail, fought hard in the straight, near the 100M was steadied when disappointed for running.
Travelled at tail, asked for effort passing 550M, one-paced.
Travelled midfield on rail, limited response when asked for effort in the straight.
On jumped was crowded for room, took lead, passing 200M was inconvenienced when giving ground, failed to run on.
Ridden along to settled at handy position, near 1300M was steadied away from heels, gradually gave ground in the straight.
Bounced straight to the front and was never headed. Briefly challenged around home turn but kicked ahead 300m and kept increasing margin to line.
In box seat throughout, chasing leader from start to finish without closing gap.
Crowded out start, recovered and pushed forward between horses to settle 4L from leader at turn. Kept up chase in straight without getting closer. Suffered from epiglottic entrapment.
Jumped OK, ridden but didn't muster, then restrained 1100m and shifted in for cover behind midfield. Shifted ground turn and severly checked, taken wide in straight, ran on fairly.
Hard ridden to hold forward position, settling one-out 2L from leader. Kept tabs to straight where one-paced.
Not far off the pace but wide. Left flat-footed when pace quickened around home turn. Kept on one-paced in straight.
Away well, pressed forward, settling one-out 1L from leader. Took closer order home turn, kept on fairly to 200m when emptied.
Began awkwardly, dropping to behind midfield along rail. At rear to straight when switched out and ran on fairly.
Raced in midfield along rail before bumping into rail 600m and losing ground. Boxed on one-paced in straight.
Outpaced, racing one-out at rear. Well back to straight when ran past well-beaten rivals.
Trailed field throughout and finished tailed out. Unacceptable performance.
Pressed forward 3-wide without cover 1L from leader on settling. Shuffled back to midfield around turn and faded in straight, finishing tailed out. Unacceptable performance.
Taken back from a tricky gate, raced at rear on rail, 6 to 7 lengths back, slightly improved along the rail on turn, finished off very strongly in straight to score.
Jumped well, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths back, saved ground throughout, kept to inside after turning in, closed off well but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Began well from gate 1, took the early lead, enjoyed the easy lead until challenged near 750M, bumped and unbalanced turning in, kept on well in straight, headed final 100M, stayed on for 3rd.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths back in midfield, slightly improved in the middle stages, very wide turning in, finished off well to make frame.

Bumped start, positioned 2 to 3 wide behind midfield, raced tight near 1400M, difficult to settle near 950M, same position on turn, taken very wide in straight and made some progress to be nearest on line.
Began well, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run throughout, angled out near 400M, finished off evenly.
Fast into stride, raced prominently early, shuffled to midfield in the middle stages, 4 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Steadied on jumping, positioned 2 wide, 5 lengths back, raced tight near 1400M, stayed at rear in the middle stages, last turning in, failed to close off in straight. (Blood in trachea.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 6 lengths back at rear, similar position on turn, showed no progress in straight.
Jumped well from gate 10, sent forward to race prominently, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in 5th early, shuffled back to rear in the middle stages, 6 lengths back on turn, emptied early in straight.

Taken back from the widest gate, raced at tail early, sent forward in the middle stages and took the lead near 700M, peaked turning in, weakened gradually in straight, finished last. (See Racing Incidents.)
Raced in midfield, 4-1/4L behind 2 wide, swung widest, improved gradually and kept on well to score by a neck.
Taken back, 7L behind 2 wide, moved prior to 800M, made nice ground and battled on to take 2nd, missed by a neck.
Pushed and travelled in front of midfield, 2-1/2L off the lead 2 wide, kept on well and missed by a neck.
Pushed forward to take the rail and led by 1/2L, headed passing 150M but kept on okay to the finish.
Inconvenienced at start, at the rear 8-1/4L behind along the rail, moved after 800M, continued to make ground.
Niggled and settled to race in front of midfield, 3-3/4L behind along the rail, finished off one paced.
Travelled in worse than midfield, 7-1/4L behind 2 wide, maintained one paced to the line.
Rolled forward and raced outside the lead, sat 1/2L off, found no extra passing 150M.
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, in worse than midfield, 7-3/4L behind along the rail, disappointed for run at 250M, made minor ground thereafter.
Pushed and took up racing in the box-seat, sat 1-1/2L off the lead, kept on till 200M then flattened.
Settled to race in midfield, 5-3/4L behind along the rail, disappointed for run at 250M, showed nothing thereafter.
Crowded at start, raced just behind midfield, 6L behind 2 wide, finished tailed out. Must trial.
Taken in for cover soon after start, settling one-out in midfield. Swung wide entering straight, given reminders and finished strongly to win close home.
Hard ridden to lead 1150m, set strong pace. Kept finding in straight when strongly challenged from 250m, laying out under pressure, until run down final strides.
Hard ridden to hold forward position, settling in box seat 1.5L from leader. Came off fence 350m to challenge, boxed on strongly to line.
Pressed forward from outside gate, settling 3-wide without cover 2L from leader. Covered extra ground turn, battled on strongly in straight though raced tight final stages.
Settled behind midfield along rail. Came off fence entering straight but forced to shift in abruptly 250m when blocked for run. Ran on well to finish just behind place-getters.
Found pace a little hot and settled in midfield along rail. Switched out in straight to make run and kept on fairly.
Outpaced, racing mostly at rear away from fence. Taken wide in straight and ran on fairly.
Jumped well, ridden to hold fence in midfield. Stayed on fence around home turn and kept on fairly in straight.
Steadied on jumping, taken in from widest gate and last on settling. Last into straight before making up good ground final 200m.
Jumped well, pressed forward, settling one-out 3L from leader. Stayed with pace to 200m before tiring.
Began fairly, then crowded, losing ground. Hard ridden but didn't muster, dropping one-out behind midfield. Taken to centre track on straightening but only one-paced.
Hard ridden to race outside leader entering back stretch. Kept position to straight when dropped out abruptly and finished last. Bled from both nostrils, lame left front leg.
Guided to the fence soon after the start, travelled strongly in midfield, quickened to lead 200M and stayed it out well to the line for an overdue win.
Crowded for room at the start, waited with towards the rear, held up momentarily 200M then came with a late surge to get up for 2nd near line.
Began well from draw 1 to be chasing leaders, briefly led 250M, outsprinted by winner nearing 150M, lost 2nd just before line.
Crowded for room on jumping, ended up towards the rear 4-5Ls off the pace, saved ground on the turn, kept on mildly on straightening, well held by leaders.
Held up midfield along the 2-path, 3Ls off leader 400M, soon into clear top of straight, kept chasing but didn't reach leaders.
Reserved in a 2-wide spot behind mid-division, kept battling in the straight but couldn't get closer to leaders.
Up with pace early, eased to sit behind leaders 900M, lacked the turn of foot when driven out top of straight, just battled away final 200M. (Lame LF leg.)
Steadied early stages to obtain cover, settled last 7Ls off the pace along the rail, boxed on without threatening.
Dropped back to near the rear, no closer than 3-wide throughout, ran on only fairly down outside, never a chance. (Jockey : saddle shifted on jumping causing inconvenience early stages.)
Caught wide no cover from draw 12, 4Ls off the pace in midfield, found no extra in the straight.
Sent forward and pressed leader on the outside, driven 300M to hold position, weakened rapidly 150M.
Vied for lead, set good pace to straight, found nothing when asked, dropped away tamely.

Settled just off the pace on the rail, tracked the leader in 3rd to the straight, quickened to hit the front passing the 200 metres while hanging in, just held on under pressure.
Settled in rear of midfield of the strung-out field in back straight, switched out for a run turning in, ran on well to be nearest at finish.
Crowded at the start, travelled in last few to home straight, finished off race well inside the final 200 metres.
Led early, ceded advantage for 1L 2nd on the rail turning into back straight, chased the leader onto home turn, kept on steadily under pressure without quickening.
Pressed forward from a wide gate, moved up to take lead on the rail approaching back straight, led a steady pace to home turn, unable to sustain effort and swamped inside the 200 metres.
Slowly away from the middle gate, settled in midfield on the rail, gained closer to pace entering straight, kept on without quickening under pressure.
Jumped fairly, settled in last few, checked for a run 350 metres out, produced good late impression closing stages.
Settled in midfield, shuffled backward approaching the home bend, raced wide towards the rear into the straight, made modest late progress.
Jumped awkwardly, settled towards the rear, made headway around the field on home bend, found no extra from some 4L back in 5th into the straight.
Settled at the back after beginning from the widest gate, switched widest turning for home, made modest progress near the centre of the track without threatening.
Broke well, gradually shuffled back to 3L 5th on the far side, dropped further back under pressure rounding home bend.
Restrained outside the leader, became 2L 3rd far side, dropped to 4th some 3L back coming onto home bend, weakened after straightening.
Midfield, pace good, made steady ground 400M to score by a narrow margin.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, pace good, progressed steadily 300M, just missed by a narrow margin.
Pushed to take rail and shared the lead at good pace, hung on well until 100M overhauled, ran on for 3rd.
Settled in box seat, pace good, just held ground in final stages.
Hard ridden forward to share the lead at good pace, weakened 250M.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, pace good, just held ground in straight.
Eased back, 2 wide, pace good, improved steadily 250M.
Eased back, took rail, pace good, made some ground 250M.
Very slow away, hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, pace good, emptied 350M.
Eased back, took rail, pace good, lack turn of foot.
Eased at start, trapped 3-4 wide, pace good, made steady ground 200M.
At back, 2 wide, pace good, no progress.
Eased back, trapped 3-4 wide, pace good, never improved.
Eased to rear, never a factor.
Settled outside the lead, commenced to improve on straightening, travelled strongly and finished unchallenged.
Ridden along after start then steadied to settle midfield, commenced to improve passing 500M, gradually made ground in the straight, came home nicely.
Took lead after start, asked for effort passing 400M, fought hard in the straight, finished nicely.
Slow to begin, settled behind midfield on rail, in the straight under pressure but only one-paced.
Slow to begin, travelled back on rail, crowded for room approaching 1100M, one-paced in the straight.
Settled at box seat, limited response when asked for effort in the early straight, gave ground passing final 100M.
Raced at back and wide, no response when asked for effort in the straight.
Raced at tail, crowded for room approaching 1100M, always back, never in it.
Raced behind midfield, passing 150M faded out. Rider reported the horse did not stretch out in the straight
Out well, stayed with pace before being easing to midfield first turn. Lost position back stretch, hard ridden from 600m to move forward, wide into straight, finishing strongly to win on line.
Outpaced, racing towards rear close to fence. Switched out turning for home, pressed forward between horses to lead 130m, run down on line.
Ridden to stayed with pace, settling ahead of midfield. Had clear running on straightening and finished off gamely to snatch minor placing.
Pressed forward from widest draw to race outside leader but held three-wide without cover. Covered extra ground throughout but kept on gamely in straight.
Hard ridden to hold forward position, racing outside leader till taking over 1150m. Kept on strongly in straight until swamped final 120m.
Hard ridden from jump but didn't muster and allowed to settle at rear along fence. Taken 3-wide turning for home and ran on steadily in straight.
Pressed forward from inside draw to hold box seat on settling. Slightly hampered approaching home turn, kept on fairly in straight before running out of steam close home.
Jumped well, used inside draw to lead on settling before racing a half-length inside new leader from 1150m. Kept on well to 120m until swamped.
Ridden to stay with pace but bumped and unbalanced before first turn, settling between horses in midfield. Made some progress turning for home before tuning one-paced in straight.
No pace, racing at rear along fence, Made progress around home tune, took inside run in straight, making further ground until flattened 200m.
Given reminders on jumping, sharing early lead but 3-wide outside leader at first turn. Lost position back stretch and last into straight. Plodded home.
Shifted in for cover soon after start and last on settling. Remained at rear throughout.
No pace, racing at rear but wide. Given reminder on straightening but no response.
Hard ridden early to stay with pace but difficult to settle and raced erratically, losing position. Finished tailed out. Unacceptable performance.
Crowded on jumping, raced at tail, 6 to 7 lengths back, still last turning in, shifted in after straightening and finish off very strongly to score by a head.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back, similar position on turn, closed off well to get 2nd.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, found rail on turn, finished off well to get 3rd.
Began awkwardly, recovered to sit 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, raced 2 wide at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back, there to turn, taken wide early in straight and made some progress without threatening.
Taken back from gate 10, raced 4 wide with cover at rear, still 5 lengths back on turn, taken very wide in straight and made some progress without threatening the first few.
Jumped well from the widest gate, raced very wide at rear early, slightly improved near 900M to obtain a midfield spot with cover, angled out after turning in, finished off evenly.
Fast into stride, positioned outside the leader early, settled one-off one-back in the middle stages, one-paced in straight.
Moderate start and made contact with SPICY KAKA, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.

Moderately away and made contact with WINNING SUPREME, raced in 3rd early, slightly improved after 1000M to race outside to the leader, kept on fairly early in straight, peaked near 200M, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, unable to slot in, travelled wide with no cover throughout, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well from gate 1, raced 5 lengths back at rear, saved ground throughout, inconvenienced early in straight, emptied thereafter and eased.
Bumped start, unable to slot in, travelled wide without cover throughout, emptied early in straight when hard run took effect.

Average to begin, raced 2 to 3 wide with cover in midfield, difficult to settle near 1200M, continued to travel very keenly thereafter, peaked early in straight, weakened sharply thereafter, finished last.
Raced as part of the lead on stand side, never really challenged and kept on well to the line to score by 1-1/4L.
Pushed and raced behind the lead on stand side, kept on going to finish 2nd, 1-1/4L behind the winner.
Settled to race at the rear along the outside rail, made nice ground, awkward to heels at 150M, kept on well to take 3rd.
Rolled forward and sat behind the leaders on the outside rail, ran on fairly to the finish.
Raced towards the rear on the outside rail, made ground and kept on okay to the line.
Sent forward, shared lead on the outside rail, kept up until 250M and found no extra.
Pushed and settled to race in behind midfield on stand side, awkward to heels at 300M, finished off fairly thereafter.
Eased and raced towards the rear on centre track, made ground till 150M and then flattened.
Settled to race behind the leaders on stand side, asked from after 600M, moved backwards.
Jumped very awkwardly and lost ground, in about midfield on centre track, found nothing.
Raced as part of the lead on centre track, gave ground from 400M. (Rider concerned with breathing noise)
Came out running, holding narrow lead till pulling 1.5L clear passing 800m. Kicked ahead on straightening and kept finding which challenged for comfortable win.
Away well, pressed forward, settling one-back, one-out 800m. Shaken up 350m to go after leader but unable to close gap.
Ridden to hold box seat but tended to race keenly before settling better passing 900m. Left fence 400m to issue challenge but unable overhaul leader.
No early pace, racing along fence behind midfield. Switched out 400m to make run and finished off fairly.
Began awkwardly, pushed forward settling midfield but away from fence. Kept on gamely in straight without threatening.
Hard ridden from outside draw to race outside leader on settling. Kept on well to 200m before flattened.
Jumped awkwardly, steadied and taken in for cover, settling one-out behind midfield. Taken very wide in straight and ran on steadily.
Pressed forward from a wide gate but unable find cover and left three-wide without cover at midfield. Covered extra ground throughout and one-paced in straight.
Ridden early to get midfield position, settling one-out. Traveled comfortably to straight but held for run from 300m to 200m, before finishing one-paced.
No early pace, racing along fence towards rear. Stayed at rear throughout though made up some ground in straight.
Away well, taken to fence and settled 3L from leader. Kept position to 200m before giving ground. Lame right front leg.
Began fairly, no pace, dropping one-out to rear. Made little impression thereafter, finishing well back.
Slow into stride and last on settling. Looked well beaten turning for home, no response in straight.
Slow into stride, racing at rear thereafter. Never in the hunt.

Quickly into stride under 7lb claimer and led, pressed by rival from 1200M setting fast pace middle stages, showed no signs of stopping passing 350M, kept on strongly for a dominant win, never challenged.
In 5th spot 4Ls behind leader in a fast run race, saved ground on the inside, stayed on mildly to go 2nd close home but couldn't much threat to the runaway winner.
Travelled well behind midfield in a fast run race, nearly 8Ls behind leader and eventual winner at 400M, closed off strongly to go 3rd near the line.
Jumped well to be tracking leaders in a fast run race, tried hard final 300M but couldn't close the gap on leader, got past by 2nd and 3rd late stages.
Began well from wide gate, settled 2-wide ahead of mid-division, 5Ls to make up on leader and eventual winner at 400M, lacked a turn of foot, battled steadily to the line only.
Positively ridden from the start, chased leaders in 4th, couldn't quicken over final 300M, ran home one paced.
Steadied early stages and shifted across behind runners, held up behind midfield 6Ls behind leader, bustled along passing 600M, just plugged away from there.
Eased back to 2nd last 10Ls off the pace, niggled along 600M,still had plenty to do top of straight, made some progress but never threatened leaders.
From draw 12 caught wide no cover until 1200M when rolled forward and vied for lead, outpaced 500M, found no extra under pressure, faded towards the line.
Restrained to race in midfield, 6Ls off the pace middle stages, 3-wide making home turn, couldn't lift passing 300M. (Lame RF leg)

Fractious in the barriers and missed the start, ended up towards the rear 8Ls behind leader, didn't run on entering straight. Never threatened. (Jockey : appeared uncomfortable racing back in the field.)
Settled down midfield along the fence, came under heavy pressure 600M, gone from the turn, struggled home.
Towards the rear, about 10Ls off the pace middle stages, struggled to make any ground in run home.
Didn't muster speed despite hard ridden from the start, soon detached from the field, finished distanced.
Bumped start, taken in for cover but raced ungenerously, losing position. Taken 3-wide approaching home turn, switched to centre track on straight, finished strongly to win drawing clear.
Bumped start, taken in, dropping to rear, dropped to last back stretch, last into straight, blocked for run until 150m, finished strongly.
Hard ridden to hold one-out position 3L from leader at first turn. Lost position back stretch, taken wide home turn, ran on gamely in straight to snatch minor placing.
Outpaced, taken in for cover, last on settling. Shaken up approaching home turn, wide in straight, ran on well to finish close to place-getters.
Hard ridden to share pace, racing 3-wide outside leader. Taken wide approaching home turn but boxed on gamely in straight to finish behind place-getters.
Allowed to stride at own pace, racing along fence behind midfield. Got shuffled back turning for home, blocked for run early in straight, finished off nicely when clear.
Jumped well, taken in for cover, settling on rail 3L from leader. Lost position back stretch, held up behind horses from 300m to 200m, finished off nicely when clear.
Pressed forward from widest draw but held 6-wide at first turn, dropping back to rear. Started long forward move from 1600m, gradually circling horses to lead 700m. Overtaken 300m and faded.
Unbalanced start, resulting in rider's left foot slipping from stirrup which he regained shortly after. Improved from well back 1600m to look a chance at turn-in before turning one-paced.
Well-position early, holding position one-out behind the pace. Got shuffled back to near last back stretch, one-paced in straight.
Quickly into stride, holding fence, before settling into box seat. Came off fence turning for home to issue challenge but found nothing and dropped back through field.
Hard ridden early but failed to muster and held wide behind midfield. Allowed to improve when pace slacked back stretch but under pressure from home turn and faded.
Pressed forward from an outside gate, racing 3-wide behind the pace until allowed to stride forward to take lead passing 1150m. Overtaken on straightening and faded.
Hard ridden to lead on settling, holding narrow lead until headed 1150m. Under pressure home turn, dropped out in straight. Finished tailed out. Unacceptable performance.
Taken up early to settle forward of midfield. Forced a runt through at 300m, and raced tight from that point. Clear from the 200m and stayed on strongly to hold the win late.
Taken up early to be handily placed 3rd. Nosed in front at 250m. Lost lead when running out of steam at 25m, and just held onto 2nd late.
Slowly away and dropped back to settle last. Still last at 350m, but ran strongly in the straight and was closing on first 2 very quickly late.
Dropped back early to sit towards the rear of the field. Searching for a run top of straight. Bump 300m. Strong to the line and was gaining on first 2 late.
Hampered on jumping before settling midfield, on the fence. Boxed in, on the rail, in the straight and was never tested.
Eased back early to sit towards the rear of the field. Went looking for runs at top of the straight. Clear from 300m, and stayed on solidly late.
Taken forward early to be handily placed 4th. Bumped and unbalanced 350m. Stayed on only fairly under hands and heels late.
Began awkwardly, before eventually settling around midfield. Checked and lost ground at 1100m.Battled on only fairly and picked up some slower ones late.
Pushed out early to be a clear leader. Still in front at 250m, but peaked soon after and dropped back through the field.
Cruised forward early to settle forward of midfield. Didn't respond to pressure in the straight and was eased late. Vet- lame in near hind leg.
Began awkwardly and unbalanced the rider, before settling midfield. 1 paced early in the straight and dropped out late.
Dropped back early to sit 2nd last. Never progressed in the straight and eased late.
Taken forward early to trail the leader, 1 off the fence. Severely checked at 300m and lost momentum. Not persevered with from that point.
Stuck wide early, before easing back towards the rear of the field. Never responded in the straight, and eased a long way from home.

Settled just worse than midfield, circled the field rounding home bend, 5-wide and within 1L of lead turning in, bumped when narrowly in front 200 metres out, soon kicked 1L clear and hung on well to the line.

Prominent early, settled better than midfield in 5th early in back straight, gained closer in 4th when pace slackened near the Rock, close up when badly tightened early in straight, fought on dourly inside the final 150 metres.
Tightened at start, settled towards the rear on the rail, snuck up on the inside turning in, ran on steadily without threatening.
Settled mainly in midfield, angled off rail entering home straight, shifted out for a clear run 200 metres out, ran on without threatening.
Led the first 400 metres, ceded lead to settle just off the pace in 3rd from stables bend, came under pressure turning for home, baulked for a run and steadied at the 200 metres, kept on steadily.
Settled in last few, commenced move out wide rounding home bend, ran on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Soon came to chase the leaders from a wide gate, hit the front under pressure 300 metres out when bumped and unbalanced, never recovered.
Soon took up running setting a sound pace early in back straight, reduced tempo approaching home bend, headed when fading under pressure 300 metres out.
Settled well behind, left flat-footed rounding the home bend, produced good late impression closing stages.
Settled just better than midfield on the rail, given reminders rounding home bend, faded under pressure in the straight.
Settled well back, very wide home turn, ran past one beaten horse.
Settled in midfield, made short-lived effort rounding home bend, no further impression in the run home.
Eased to sit in midfield, trapped 3 wide but with cover, harmed by the slow pace, dashed strongly 300M to score.
Eased at start, trapped 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 250M.
Pushed forward, sat outside the leader, enjoyed the slow sectionals, led 350M, hung on until 100M overhauled, just ran on for 3rd.
Eased at start, 2-3 wide at rear, dashed strongly 250M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pushed to take rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, soon weakened 200M.
Box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Very slow away, midfield along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, lack turn of foot in straight.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide just off the leaders, emptied 250M.
Just behind the leaders, 2 wide, never improved.
Midfield 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, just held ground in straight.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, not suited by the slow tempo, little dash 150M.
Very slow away, took rail at rear, harmed by the slow pace, lack room in straight, not tested.
Ridden along to take lead, travelled comfortably, finished unchallenged.
Rounding the Home Turn was held up and passing 300M shifted in to obtain a run, fought hard and finished nicely.
Pushed to take box seat, kept on in the straight, finished well.
Began only fairly then taken back, niggled passing 700M, made ground passing 200M.
Raced midfield, commenced to improve passing 500M, gradually made ground passing 200M, finished OK.
Urged along to settle outside the lead, gave ground passing 150M, finished fairly.
Restless in barriers and slow to begin, then near 1400M crowded for room and lost ground, settled behind midfield, one-paced in the straight.
Settled behind midfield, approaching 800M was inconvenienced, wide on straightening, near 150M rider momentarily dropped his right rein, one-paced.
Taken back at start, kept on rail to improve but one-paced.
Throughout the race travelled wide and without cover, raced behind leaders, gave ground passing 150M, failed to run on.
Always back, widest on straightening, no response.
Raced midfield on rail, weakened passing 200M, failed to run on.
Pressed forward from an outside draw, racing wide before taking lead 700m and crossing to fence. Kicked ahead 250m and kept finding to score with something in hand.
Hard ridden to hold rail inside early leaders but shuffled 3L back from leader at the turn. Swung wide into straight and ran on gamely under hard riding to snatch 2nd on line.
Ridden to hold midfield position before edging ahead to race outside hindquarters of leader at the turn. Given reminders in straight but unable mow down leader.
Vigorously ridden to lead soon after jumping before being passed 700m. Stayed in box seat to straight and boxed on gamely until flattened close home.
Hard ridden to stay within 3L of leader at turn, swung wide into straight, boxed on in straight without looking dangerous.
Raced mostly one-out in midfield. Took inside run in straight and kept on fairly under pressure.
Jumped awkwardly, losing ground, pressed forward but over-raced before settling one-out in midfield. Taken wide in straight but only one-paced. Had substantial amount of blood in trachea.
Slow into stride, steadied off heels, dropping to rear. Raced greenly early and middle stages but settled better home turn and closed off fairly in straight.
Ridden to hold rail but outpaced, dropping to behind midfield. Switched out in straight to make run but limited response.
Hard ridden from wide draw to stay with pace, racing without cover 3L from leader. Allowed to slide forward home turn but soon out of steam and faded.
Slow into stride and last on settling. Remained at rear throughout and never in the hunt.
Shared early pace but wide before losing position home turn. Faded in straight to finish tailed out.
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, improved from 400M, finished off well to score by a neck.
Began well from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on very well in straight, missed narrowly.
Began fairly, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths back in midfield, similar position on turn, finished off well to take 3rd.

Crowded out start, positioned 3-4L back on rail, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, made minor progress thereafter to make frame. (Jockey reported his horse did not feel entirely comfortable in the race.)
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced at rear, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Crowded on jumping, raced at tail, 6 lengths back, still well back on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made good progress to be nearest on line.

Broke sharply, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 700M, travelled well on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, headed final 100M, faded thereafter. (Lame right hind leg with multiple superficial wounds.)
Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently, 2nd on turn, peaked near 200M, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, taken back to race 3 wide with cover at rear, slightly improved on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, recovered to race 2 lengths or so back on rail, same position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide with no cover throughout, emptied early in straight when hard run took toll. (Blood in trachea.)
Jumped well, raced 3 wide with no cover in midfield, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight and eased.
Sent forward to take the rail and led by 1L, remained in a tight battle to the line but held on to score by a short-head.
Pushed and raced in the box-seat, sat 1L behind the lead, fought in a tight battle to the line, missed by a short-head.
Eased then settled in midfield, 4-1/2L behind 2 wide, made good ground and ran on fairly but was no match to first two.
Niggled and settled in midfield, 3-1/2L behind 3 wide with cover, swung wide and dashed early, kept on to the line.
Pushed and settled to race in midfield, 3-3/4L behind along the rail, continued to be one paced to the line.
Slot to jump, settled in worse than midfield, 5L behind 2 wide, continued to make ground and ran on fairly.
Travelled at the rear, 6-3/4L behind the lead 2 wide, did not make ground but kept on.
Settled in worse than midfield, 5-1/2L behind along the rail, kept on one paced to the line.
Hard ridden forward, sat 1L off and outside the lead, could not keep up approaching 200M and then faded.
Ridden to be prominent, sat 2-1/4L off but 3 wide without cover at turn, flattened soon after straightening.
Pushed to take one-off one-back position, 2-3/4L off the lead, found no extra approaching 200M.
Raced at the rear throughout, never competitive.
Steadied on jumping, shifted across behind horses, last on settling. Started forward move 700m, racing 3 and 4 wide around horses, widest in straight, hit front 150m, pulled clear.
Outpaced, dropping to rear. Last into straight, taken to centre field and finished off strongly to grab 2nd on line.
Broke well, then raced in midfield close to fence. Left rail in straight to make run and finished off gamely.
Jumped OK but not pushed, settling behind midfield. Under pressure 500m, making up ground, before finishing off nicely final 200m.
Pressed forward to race outside leader at first turn before easing one-back, one-out back stretch. Bumped an unbalanced home turn, kept on one-paced in straight.
Ridden positively from an outside draw to hold forward position but tended to over-race and allowed to stride forward to race outside leader home turn. Looked chance 200m before flattened.
Broke well, taken to front along rail and set steady pace back stretch. Joined up front 500m, retook lead on straightening, overtaken 150m, swamped close home.
Raced mostly one-out in midfield. Taken wide in straight but only one-paced under hard riding.
Used inside draw to grab box seat on settling, tracked leader to 200m before running on empty and dropping back.
Raced one-out behind midfield to straight before making ground only to run into a dead-end 250m. One-paced after that.
Steadied soon after start and shifted across behind runners, settling at rear. Held for clear running final 200m and not properly tested.
Hard ridden to go forward, taking first turn 4-wide, before settling one-out in midfield. Shaken up turning for home, but soon out of steam and faded.

Moderately away, positioned on rail in midfield, 7 to 8 lengths back in the early stages, angled out from the rail after entering the back straight, improved from 400M, finished off very strongly to score by a head.
Began fairly from gate 9, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3 lengths in the early stages, still easy lead on turn, kept on very well in straight but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Slightly slow out, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground throughout, kept to inside after straightening and made good progress to take 3rd, good debut.
Began well, positioned in 2nd, 3 lengths back in the early stages, closer on turn, kept on evenly in straight, just missed 3rd.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly, never a threat to the first few.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear throughout, 12 lengths or so back, closer on turn, but still 6 lengths behind the leader, made good progress in straight.
Began well from a middle draw, positioned in 3rd, no cover throughout, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Average to begin, raced 9 lengths back on rail at rear, saved ground throughout, still 5 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 13 to 14 lengths, closer on turn, but still last turning in, taken widest in straight, only made minor progress.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 7 lengths back, improved from near 600M, 4 wide turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from gate 10, raced 2 wide at rear, 9 lengths or so back, still 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 4 lengths back on rail, closer on turn, showed brief response early in straight, weakened from 200M, eased final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
